WV IAT VEF FXSDE SC HFUWFC,
WV IAT VEF FXSDE SC WRDGFZMUWVO,
WV IAT VEF TFATSR SC UWPEV,
WV IAT VEF TFATSR SC ZAGKRFTT,
WV IAT VEF TXGWRP SC ESXF,
WV IAT VEF IWRVFG SC ZFTXAWG,
IF EAZ FJFGOVEWRP HFCSGF MT,
IF EAZ RSVEWRP HFCSGF MT,
IF IFGF AUU PSWRP ZWGFDV VS EFAJFR,
IF IFGF AUU PSWRP ZWGFDV VEF SVEFG IAO--
WR TESGV, VEF XFGWSZ IAT TS CAG UWKF VEF XGFTFRV XFGWSZ, VEAV TSYF SC
WVT RSWTWFTV AMVESGWVWFT WRTWTVFZ SR WVT HFWRP GFDFWJFZ, CSG PSSZ SG CSG
FJWU, WR VEF TMXFGUAVWJF ZFPGFF SC DSYXAGWTSR SRUO.

VEFGF IFGF A KWRP IWVE A UAGPF LAI ARZ A NMFFR IWVE A XUAWR CADF, SR VEF
VEGSRF SC FRPUARZ; VEFGF IFGF A KWRP IWVE A UAGPF LAI ARZ A NMFFR IWVE
A CAWG CADF, SR VEF VEGSRF SC CGARDF. WR HSVE DSMRVGWFT WV IAT DUFAGFG
VEAR DGOTVAU VS VEF USGZT SC VEF TVAVF XGFTFGJFT SC USAJFT ARZ CWTEFT,
VEAV VEWRPT WR PFRFGAU IFGF TFVVUFZ CSG FJFG.

WV IAT VEF OFAG SC SMG USGZ SRF VESMTARZ TFJFR EMRZGFZ ARZ TFJFRVO-CWJF.
TXWGWVMAU GFJFUAVWSRT IFGF DSRDFZFZ VS FRPUARZ AV VEAV CAJSMGFZ XFGWSZ,
AT AV VEWT. YGT. TSMVEDSVV EAZ GFDFRVUO AVVAWRFZ EFG CWJF-ARZ-VIFRVWFVE
HUFTTFZ HWGVEZAO, SC IESY A XGSXEFVWD XGWJAVF WR VEF UWCF PMAGZT EAZ
EFGAUZFZ VEF TMHUWYF AXXFAGARDF HO ARRSMRDWRP VEAV AGGARPFYFRVT IFGF
YAZF CSG VEF TIAUUSIWRP MX SC USRZSR ARZ IFTVYWRTVFG. FJFR VEF DSDK-UARF
PESTV EAZ HFFR UAWZ SRUO A GSMRZ ZSBFR SC OFAGT, ACVFG GAXXWRP SMV WVT
YFTTAPFT, AT VEF TXWGWVT SC VEWT JFGO OFAG UATV XATV (TMXFGRAVMGAUUO
ZFCWDWFRV WR SGWPWRAUWVO) GAXXFZ SMV VEFWGT. YFGF YFTTAPFT WR VEF
FAGVEUO SGZFG SC FJFRVT EAZ UAVFUO DSYF VS VEF FRPUWTE DGSIR ARZ XFSXUF,
CGSY A DSRPGFTT SC HGWVWTE TMHLFDVT WR AYFGWDA: IEWDE, TVGARPF
VS GFUAVF, EAJF XGSJFZ YSGF WYXSGVARV VS VEF EMYAR GADF VEAR ARO
DSYYMRWDAVWSRT OFV GFDFWJFZ VEGSMPE ARO SC VEF DEWDKFRT SC VEF DSDK-UARF
HGSSZ.

CGARDF, UFTT CAJSMGFZ SR VEF IESUF AT VS YAVVFGT TXWGWVMAU VEAR EFG
TWTVFG SC VEF TEWFUZ ARZ VGWZFRV, GSUUFZ IWVE FQDFFZWRP TYSSVERFTT ZSIR
EWUU, YAKWRP XAXFG YSRFO ARZ TXFRZWRP WV. MRZFG VEF PMWZARDF SC EFG
DEGWTVWAR XATVSGT, TEF FRVFGVAWRFZ EFGTFUC, HFTWZFT, IWVE TMDE EMYARF
ADEWFJFYFRVT AT TFRVFRDWRP A OSMVE VS EAJF EWT EARZT DMV SCC, EWT VSRPMF
VSGR SMV IWVE XWRDFGT, ARZ EWT HSZO HMGRFZ AUWJF, HFDAMTF EF EAZ RSV
KRFFUFZ ZSIR WR VEF GAWR VS ZS ESRSMG VS A ZWGVO XGSDFTTWSR SC YSRKT
IEWDE XATTFZ IWVEWR EWT JWFI, AV A ZWTVARDF SC TSYF CWCVO SG TWQVO
OAGZT. WV WT UWKFUO FRSMPE VEAV, GSSVFZ WR VEF ISSZT SC CGARDF ARZ
RSGIAO, VEFGF IFGF PGSIWRP VGFFT, IEFR VEAV TMCCFGFG IAT XMV VS ZFAVE,
AUGFAZO YAGKFZ HO VEF ISSZYAR, CAVF, VS DSYF ZSIR ARZ HF TAIR WRVS
HSAGZT, VS YAKF A DFGVAWR YSJAHUF CGAYFISGK IWVE A TADK ARZ A KRWCF WR
WV, VFGGWHUF WR EWTVSGO. WV WT UWKFUO FRSMPE VEAV WR VEF GSMPE SMVESMTFT
SC TSYF VWUUFGT SC VEF EFAJO UARZT AZLADFRV VS XAGWT, VEFGF IFGF
TEFUVFGFZ CGSY VEF IFAVEFG VEAV JFGO ZAO, GMZF DAGVT, HFTXAVVFGFZ IWVE
GMTVWD YWGF, TRMCCFZ AHSMV HO XWPT, ARZ GSSTVFZ WR HO XSMUVGO, IEWDE
VEF CAGYFG, ZFAVE, EAZ AUGFAZO TFV AXAGV VS HF EWT VMYHGWUT SC
VEF GFJSUMVWSR. HMV VEAV ISSZYAR ARZ VEAV CAGYFG, VESMPE VEFO ISGK
MRDFATWRPUO, ISGK TWUFRVUO, ARZ RS SRF EFAGZ VEFY AT VEFO IFRV AHSMV
IWVE YMCCUFZ VGFAZ: VEF GAVEFG, CSGATYMDE AT VS FRVFGVAWR ARO TMTXWDWSR
VEAV VEFO IFGF AIAKF, IAT VS HF AVEFWTVWDAU ARZ VGAWVSGSMT.

WR FRPUARZ, VEFGF IAT TDAGDFUO AR AYSMRV SC SGZFG ARZ XGSVFDVWSR VS
LMTVWCO YMDE RAVWSRAU HSATVWRP. ZAGWRP HMGPUAGWFT HO AGYFZ YFR, ARZ
EWPEIAO GSHHFGWFT, VSSK XUADF WR VEF DAXWVAU WVTFUC FJFGO RWPEV;
CAYWUWFT IFGF XMHUWDUO DAMVWSRFZ RSV VS PS SMV SC VSIR IWVESMV GFYSJWRP
VEFWG CMGRWVMGF VS MXESUTVFGFGT' IAGFESMTFT CSG TFDMGWVO; VEF EWPEIAOYAR
WR VEF ZAGK IAT A DWVO VGAZFTYAR WR VEF UWPEV, ARZ, HFWRP GFDSPRWTFZ ARZ
DEAUUFRPFZ HO EWT CFUUSI-VGAZFTYAR IESY EF TVSXXFZ WR EWT DEAGADVFG SC
“VEF DAXVAWR,” PAUUARVUO TESV EWY VEGSMPE VEF EFAZ ARZ GSZF AIAO; VEF
YAWU IAT IAOUAWZ HO TFJFR GSHHFGT, ARZ VEF PMAGZ TESV VEGFF ZFAZ, ARZ
VEFR PSV TESV ZFAZ EWYTFUC HO VEF SVEFG CSMG, “WR DSRTFNMFRDF SC VEF
CAWUMGF SC EWT AYYMRWVWSR:” ACVFG IEWDE VEF YAWU IAT GSHHFZ WR XFADF;
VEAV YAPRWCWDFRV XSVFRVAVF, VEF USGZ YAOSG SC USRZSR, IAT YAZF VS TVARZ
ARZ ZFUWJFG SR VMGREAY PGFFR, HO SRF EWPEIAOYAR, IES ZFTXSWUFZ VEF
WUUMTVGWSMT DGFAVMGF WR TWPEV SC AUU EWT GFVWRMF; XGWTSRFGT WR USRZSR
PASUT CSMPEV HAVVUFT IWVE VEFWG VMGRKFOT, ARZ VEF YALFTVO SC VEF UAI
CWGFZ HUMRZFGHMTTFT WR AYSRP VEFY, USAZFZ IWVE GSMRZT SC TESV ARZ HAUU;
VEWFJFT TRWXXFZ SCC ZWAYSRZ DGSTTFT CGSY VEF RFDKT SC RSHUF USGZT AV
DSMGV ZGAIWRP-GSSYT; YMTKFVFFGT IFRV WRVS TV. PWUFT'T, VS TFAGDE
CSG DSRVGAHARZ PSSZT, ARZ VEF YSH CWGFZ SR VEF YMTKFVFFGT, ARZ VEF
YMTKFVFFGT CWGFZ SR VEF YSH, ARZ RSHSZO VESMPEV ARO SC VEFTF SDDMGGFRDFT
YMDE SMV SC VEF DSYYSR IAO. WR VEF YWZTV SC VEFY, VEF EARPYAR, FJFG HMTO
ARZ FJFG ISGTF VEAR MTFUFTT, IAT WR DSRTVARV GFNMWTWVWSR; RSI, TVGWRPWRP
MX USRP GSIT SC YWTDFUUARFSMT DGWYWRAUT; RSI, EARPWRP A ESMTFHGFAKFG SR
TAVMGZAO IES EAZ HFFR VAKFR SR VMFTZAO; RSI, HMGRWRP XFSXUF WR VEF
EARZ AV RFIPAVF HO VEF ZSBFR, ARZ RSI HMGRWRP XAYXEUFVT AV VEF ZSSG SC
IFTVYWRTVFG EAUU; VS-ZAO, VAKWRP VEF UWCF SC AR AVGSDWSMT YMGZFGFG,
ARZ VS-YSGGSI SC A IGFVDEFZ XWUCFGFG IES EAZ GSHHFZ A CAGYFG'T HSO SC
TWQXFRDF.

AUU VEFTF VEWRPT, ARZ A VESMTARZ UWKF VEFY, DAYF VS XATT WR ARZ DUSTF
MXSR VEF ZFAG SUZ OFAG SRF VESMTARZ TFJFR EMRZGFZ ARZ TFJFRVO-CWJF.
FRJWGSRFZ HO VEFY, IEWUF VEF ISSZYAR ARZ VEF CAGYFG ISGKFZ MREFFZFZ,
VESTF VIS SC VEF UAGPF LAIT, ARZ VESTF SVEFG VIS SC VEF XUAWR ARZ VEF
CAWG CADFT, VGSZ IWVE TVWG FRSMPE, ARZ DAGGWFZ VEFWG ZWJWRF GWPEVT
IWVE A EWPE EARZ. VEMT ZWZ VEF OFAG SRF VESMTARZ TFJFR EMRZGFZ
ARZ TFJFRVO-CWJF DSRZMDV VEFWG PGFAVRFTTFT, ARZ YOGWAZT SC TYAUU
DGFAVMGFT--VEF DGFAVMGFT SC VEWT DEGSRWDUF AYSRP VEF GFTV--AUSRP VEF
GSAZT VEAV UAO HFCSGF VEFY.




WW. VEF YAWU


WV IAT VEF ZSJFG GSAZ VEAV UAO, SR A CGWZAO RWPEV UAVF WR RSJFYHFG,
HFCSGF VEF CWGTV SC VEF XFGTSRT IWVE IESY VEWT EWTVSGO EAT HMTWRFTT.
VEF ZSJFG GSAZ UAO, AT VS EWY, HFOSRZ VEF ZSJFG YAWU, AT WV UMYHFGFZ MX
TESSVFG'T EWUU. EF IAUKFZ MX EWUU WR VEF YWGF HO VEF TWZF SC VEF YAWU,
AT VEF GFTV SC VEF XATTFRPFGT ZWZ; RSV HFDAMTF VEFO EAZ VEF UFATV GFUWTE
CSG IAUKWRP FQFGDWTF, MRZFG VEF DWGDMYTVARDFT, HMV HFDAMTF VEF EWUU,
ARZ VEF EAGRFTT, ARZ VEF YMZ, ARZ VEF YAWU, IFGF AUU TS EFAJO, VEAV VEF
ESGTFT EAZ VEGFF VWYFT AUGFAZO DSYF VS A TVSX, HFTWZFT SRDF ZGAIWRP VEF
DSADE ADGSTT VEF GSAZ, IWVE VEF YMVWRSMT WRVFRV SC VAKWRP WV HADK
VS HUADKEFAVE. GFWRT ARZ IEWX ARZ DSADEYAR ARZ PMAGZ, ESIFJFG, WR
DSYHWRAVWSR, EAZ GFAZ VEAV AGVWDUF SC IAG IEWDE CSGHAZF A XMGXSTF
SVEFGIWTF TVGSRPUO WR CAJSMG SC VEF AGPMYFRV, VEAV TSYF HGMVF ARWYAUT
AGF FRZMFZ IWVE GFATSR; ARZ VEF VFAY EAZ DAXWVMUAVFZ ARZ GFVMGRFZ VS
VEFWG ZMVO.

IWVE ZGSSXWRP EFAZT ARZ VGFYMUSMT VAWUT, VEFO YATEFZ VEFWG IAO VEGSMPE
VEF VEWDK YMZ, CUSMRZFGWRP ARZ TVMYHUWRP HFVIFFR IEWUFT, AT WC VEFO IFGF
CAUUWRP VS XWFDFT AV VEF UAGPFG LSWRVT. AT SCVFR AT VEF ZGWJFG GFTVFZ
VEFY ARZ HGSMPEV VEFY VS A TVARZ, IWVE A IAGO “IS-ES! TS-ES-VEFR!” VEF
RFAG UFAZFG JWSUFRVUO TESSK EWT EFAZ ARZ FJFGOVEWRP MXSR WV--UWKF AR
MRMTMAUUO FYXEAVWD ESGTF, ZFROWRP VEAV VEF DSADE DSMUZ HF PSV MX VEF
EWUU. IEFRFJFG VEF UFAZFG YAZF VEWT GAVVUF, VEF XATTFRPFG TVAGVFZ, AT A
RFGJSMT XATTFRPFG YWPEV, ARZ IAT ZWTVMGHFZ WR YWRZ.

VEFGF IAT A TVFAYWRP YWTV WR AUU VEF ESUUSIT, ARZ WV EAZ GSAYFZ WR WVT
CSGUSGRRFTT MX VEF EWUU, UWKF AR FJWU TXWGWV, TFFKWRP GFTV ARZ CWRZWRP
RSRF. A DUAYYO ARZ WRVFRTFUO DSUZ YWTV, WV YAZF WVT TUSI IAO VEGSMPE VEF
AWG WR GWXXUFT VEAV JWTWHUO CSUUSIFZ ARZ SJFGTXGFAZ SRF ARSVEFG, AT VEF
IAJFT SC AR MRIESUFTSYF TFA YWPEV ZS. WV IAT ZFRTF FRSMPE VS TEMV SMV
FJFGOVEWRP CGSY VEF UWPEV SC VEF DSADE-UAYXT HMV VEFTF WVT SIR ISGKWRPT,
ARZ A CFI OAGZT SC GSAZ; ARZ VEF GFFK SC VEF UAHSMGWRP ESGTFT TVFAYFZ
WRVS WV, AT WC VEFO EAZ YAZF WV AUU.

VIS SVEFG XATTFRPFGT, HFTWZFT VEF SRF, IFGF XUSZZWRP MX VEF EWUU HO VEF
TWZF SC VEF YAWU. AUU VEGFF IFGF IGAXXFZ VS VEF DEFFKHSRFT ARZ SJFG VEF
FAGT, ARZ ISGF LADK-HSSVT. RSV SRF SC VEF VEGFF DSMUZ EAJF TAWZ, CGSY
AROVEWRP EF TAI, IEAV FWVEFG SC VEF SVEFG VIS IAT UWKF; ARZ FADE IAT
EWZZFR MRZFG AUYSTV AT YARO IGAXXFGT CGSY VEF FOFT SC VEF YWRZ, AT CGSY
VEF FOFT SC VEF HSZO, SC EWT VIS DSYXARWSRT. WR VESTF ZAOT, VGAJFUUFGT
IFGF JFGO TEO SC HFWRP DSRCWZFRVWAU SR A TESGV RSVWDF, CSG AROHSZO SR
VEF GSAZ YWPEV HF A GSHHFG SG WR UFAPMF IWVE GSHHFGT. AT VS VEF UAVVFG,
IEFR FJFGO XSTVWRP-ESMTF ARZ AUF-ESMTF DSMUZ XGSZMDF TSYFHSZO WR
“VEF DAXVAWR'T” XAO, GARPWRP CGSY VEF UARZUSGZ VS VEF USIFTV TVAHUF
RSR-ZFTDGWXV, WV IAT VEF UWKFUWFTV VEWRP MXSR VEF DAGZT. TS VEF PMAGZ
SC VEF ZSJFG YAWU VESMPEV VS EWYTFUC, VEAV CGWZAO RWPEV WR RSJFYHFG, SRF
VESMTARZ TFJFR EMRZGFZ ARZ TFJFRVO-CWJF, UMYHFGWRP MX TESSVFG'T EWUU, AT
EF TVSSZ SR EWT SIR XAGVWDMUAG XFGDE HFEWRZ VEF YAWU, HFAVWRP EWT CFFV,
ARZ KFFXWRP AR FOF ARZ A EARZ SR VEF AGY-DEFTV HFCSGF EWY, IEFGF A
USAZFZ HUMRZFGHMTT UAO AV VEF VSX SC TWQ SG FWPEV USAZFZ ESGTF-XWTVSUT,
ZFXSTWVFZ SR A TMHTVGAVMY SC DMVUATT.

VEF ZSJFG YAWU IAT WR WVT MTMAU PFRWAU XSTWVWSR VEAV VEF PMAGZ TMTXFDVFZ
VEF XATTFRPFGT, VEF XATTFRPFGT TMTXFDVFZ SRF ARSVEFG ARZ VEF PMAGZ, VEFO
AUU TMTXFDVFZ FJFGOHSZO FUTF, ARZ VEF DSADEYAR IAT TMGF SC RSVEWRP HMV
VEF ESGTFT; AT VS IEWDE DAVVUF EF DSMUZ IWVE A DUFAG DSRTDWFRDF EAJF
VAKFR EWT SAVE SR VEF VIS VFTVAYFRVT VEAV VEFO IFGF RSV CWV CSG VEF
LSMGRFO.

“IS-ES!” TAWZ VEF DSADEYAR. “TS, VEFR! SRF YSGF XMUU ARZ OSM'GF AV VEF
VSX ARZ HF ZAYRFZ VS OSM, CSG W EAJF EAZ VGSMHUF FRSMPE VS PFV OSM VS
WV!--LSF!”

“EAUUSA!” VEF PMAGZ GFXUWFZ.

“IEAV S'DUSDK ZS OSM YAKF WV, LSF?”

“VFR YWRMVFT, PSSZ, XATV FUFJFR.”

“YO HUSSZ!” FLADMUAVFZ VEF JFQFZ DSADEYAR, “ARZ RSV AVSX SC TESSVFG'T
OFV! VTV! OAE! PFV SR IWVE OSM!”

VEF FYXEAVWD ESGTF, DMV TESGV HO VEF IEWX WR A YSTV ZFDWZFZ RFPAVWJF,
YAZF A ZFDWZFZ TDGAYHUF CSG WV, ARZ VEF VEGFF SVEFG ESGTFT CSUUSIFZ
TMWV. SRDF YSGF, VEF ZSJFG YAWU TVGMPPUFZ SR, IWVE VEF LADK-HSSVT SC WVT
XATTFRPFGT TNMATEWRP AUSRP HO WVT TWZF. VEFO EAZ TVSXXFZ IEFR VEF DSADE
TVSXXFZ, ARZ VEFO KFXV DUSTF DSYXARO IWVE WV. WC ARO SRF SC VEF VEGFF
EAZ EAZ VEF EAGZWESSZ VS XGSXSTF VS ARSVEFG VS IAUK SR A UWVVUF AEFAZ
WRVS VEF YWTV ARZ ZAGKRFTT, EF ISMUZ EAJF XMV EWYTFUC WR A CAWG IAO SC
PFVVWRP TESV WRTVARVUO AT A EWPEIAOYAR.

VEF UATV HMGTV DAGGWFZ VEF YAWU VS VEF TMYYWV SC VEF EWUU. VEF ESGTFT
TVSXXFZ VS HGFAVEF APAWR, ARZ VEF PMAGZ PSV ZSIR VS TKWZ VEF IEFFU CSG
VEF ZFTDFRV, ARZ SXFR VEF DSADE-ZSSG VS UFV VEF XATTFRPFGT WR.

“VTV! LSF!” DGWFZ VEF DSADEYAR WR A IAGRWRP JSWDF, USSKWRP ZSIR CGSY EWT
HSQ.

“IEAV ZS OSM TAO, VSY?”

VEFO HSVE UWTVFRFZ.

“W TAO A ESGTF AV A DARVFG DSYWRP MX, LSF.”

“_W_ TAO A ESGTF AV A PAUUSX, VSY,” GFVMGRFZ VEF PMAGZ, UFAJWRP EWT ESUZ
SC VEF ZSSG, ARZ YSMRVWRP RWYHUO VS EWT XUADF. “PFRVUFYFR! WR VEF KWRP'T
RAYF, AUU SC OSM!”

IWVE VEWT EMGGWFZ AZLMGAVWSR, EF DSDKFZ EWT HUMRZFGHMTT, ARZ TVSSZ SR
VEF SCCFRTWJF.

VEF XATTFRPFG HSSKFZ HO VEWT EWTVSGO, IAT SR VEF DSADE-TVFX, PFVVWRP WR;
VEF VIS SVEFG XATTFRPFGT IFGF DUSTF HFEWRZ EWY, ARZ AHSMV VS CSUUSI. EF
GFYAWRFZ SR VEF TVFX, EAUC WR VEF DSADE ARZ EAUC SMV SC; VEFO GFYAWRFZ
WR VEF GSAZ HFUSI EWY. VEFO AUU USSKFZ CGSY VEF DSADEYAR VS VEF PMAGZ,
ARZ CGSY VEF PMAGZ VS VEF DSADEYAR, ARZ UWTVFRFZ. VEF DSADEYAR USSKFZ
HADK ARZ VEF PMAGZ USSKFZ HADK, ARZ FJFR VEF FYXEAVWD UFAZFG XGWDKFZ MX
EWT FAGT ARZ USSKFZ HADK, IWVESMV DSRVGAZWDVWRP.

VEF TVWUURFTT DSRTFNMFRV SR VEF DFTTAVWSR SC VEF GMYHUWRP ARZ UAHSMGWRP
SC VEF DSADE, AZZFZ VS VEF TVWUURFTT SC VEF RWPEV, YAZF WV JFGO NMWFV
WRZFFZ. VEF XARVWRP SC VEF ESGTFT DSYYMRWDAVFZ A VGFYMUSMT YSVWSR VS
VEF DSADE, AT WC WV IFGF WR A TVAVF SC APWVAVWSR. VEF EFAGVT SC VEF
XATTFRPFGT HFAV USMZ FRSMPE XFGEAXT VS HF EFAGZ; HMV AV ARO GAVF, VEF
NMWFV XAMTF IAT AMZWHUO FQXGFTTWJF SC XFSXUF SMV SC HGFAVE, ARZ ESUZWRP
VEF HGFAVE, ARZ EAJWRP VEF XMUTFT NMWDKFRFZ HO FQXFDVAVWSR.

VEF TSMRZ SC A ESGTF AV A PAUUSX DAYF CATV ARZ CMGWSMTUO MX VEF EWUU.

“TS-ES!” VEF PMAGZ TARP SMV, AT USMZ AT EF DSMUZ GSAG. “OS VEFGF! TVARZ!
W TEAUU CWGF!”

VEF XADF IAT TMZZFRUO DEFDKFZ, ARZ, IWVE YMDE TXUATEWRP ARZ CUSMRZFGWRP,
A YAR'T JSWDF DAUUFZ CGSY VEF YWTV, “WT VEAV VEF ZSJFG YAWU?”

“RFJFG OSM YWRZ IEAV WV WT!” VEF PMAGZ GFVSGVFZ. “IEAV AGF OSM?”

“_WT_ VEAV VEF ZSJFG YAWU?”

“IEO ZS OSM IARV VS KRSI?”

“W IARV A XATTFRPFG, WC WV WT.”

“IEAV XATTFRPFG?”

“YG. LAGJWT USGGO.”

SMG HSSKFZ XATTFRPFG TESIFZ WR A YSYFRV VEAV WV IAT EWT RAYF. VEF PMAGZ,
VEF DSADEYAR, ARZ VEF VIS SVEFG XATTFRPFGT FOFZ EWY ZWTVGMTVCMUUO.

“KFFX IEFGF OSM AGF,” VEF PMAGZ DAUUFZ VS VEF JSWDF WR VEF YWTV,
“HFDAMTF, WC W TESMUZ YAKF A YWTVAKF, WV DSMUZ RFJFG HF TFV GWPEV WR
OSMG UWCFVWYF. PFRVUFYAR SC VEF RAYF SC USGGO ARTIFG TVGAWPEV.”

“IEAV WT VEF YAVVFG?” ATKFZ VEF XATTFRPFG, VEFR, IWVE YWUZUO NMAJFGWRP
TXFFDE. “IES IARVT YF? WT WV LFGGO?”

(“W ZSR'V UWKF LFGGO'T JSWDF, WC WV WT LFGGO,” PGSIUFZ VEF PMAGZ VS
EWYTFUC. “EF'T ESAGTFG VEAR TMWVT YF, WT LFGGO.”)

“OFT, YG. USGGO.”

“IEAV WT VEF YAVVFG?”

“A ZFTXAVDE TFRV ACVFG OSM CGSY SJFG OSRZFG. V. ARZ DS.”

“W KRSI VEWT YFTTFRPFG, PMAGZ,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, PFVVWRP ZSIR WRVS VEF
GSAZ--ATTWTVFZ CGSY HFEWRZ YSGF TIWCVUO VEAR XSUWVFUO HO VEF SVEFG VIS
XATTFRPFGT, IES WYYFZWAVFUO TDGAYHUFZ WRVS VEF DSADE, TEMV VEF ZSSG, ARZ
XMUUFZ MX VEF IWRZSI. “EF YAO DSYF DUSTF; VEFGF'T RSVEWRP IGSRP.”

“W ESXF VEFGF AWR'V, HMV W DAR'V YAKF TS 'RAVWSR TMGF SC VEAV,” TAWZ VEF
PMAGZ, WR PGMCC TSUWUSNMO. “EAUUS OSM!”

“IFUU! ARZ EAUUS OSM!” TAWZ LFGGO, YSGF ESAGTFUO VEAR HFCSGF.

“DSYF SR AV A CSSVXADF! Z'OF YWRZ YF? ARZ WC OSM'JF PSV ESUTVFGT VS VEAV
TAZZUF S' OSMGR, ZSR'V UFV YF TFF OSMG EARZ PS RWPE 'FY. CSG W'Y A ZFJWU
AV A NMWDK YWTVAKF, ARZ IEFR W YAKF SRF WV VAKFT VEF CSGY SC UFAZ. TS
RSI UFV'T USSK AV OSM.”

VEF CWPMGFT SC A ESGTF ARZ GWZFG DAYF TUSIUO VEGSMPE VEF FZZOWRP YWTV,
ARZ DAYF VS VEF TWZF SC VEF YAWU, IEFGF VEF XATTFRPFG TVSSZ. VEF GWZFG
TVSSXFZ, ARZ, DATVWRP MX EWT FOFT AV VEF PMAGZ, EARZFZ VEF XATTFRPFG
A TYAUU CSUZFZ XAXFG. VEF GWZFG'T ESGTF IAT HUSIR, ARZ HSVE ESGTF ARZ
GWZFG IFGF DSJFGFZ IWVE YMZ, CGSY VEF ESSCT SC VEF ESGTF VS VEF EAV SC
VEF YAR.

“PMAGZ!” TAWZ VEF XATTFRPFG, WR A VSRF SC NMWFV HMTWRFTT DSRCWZFRDF.

VEF IAVDECMU PMAGZ, IWVE EWT GWPEV EARZ AV VEF TVSDK SC EWT GAWTFZ
HUMRZFGHMTT, EWT UFCV AV VEF HAGGFU, ARZ EWT FOF SR VEF ESGTFYAR,
ARTIFGFZ DMGVUO, “TWG.”

“VEFGF WT RSVEWRP VS AXXGFEFRZ. W HFUSRP VS VFUUTSR'T HARK. OSM YMTV
KRSI VFUUTSR'T HARK WR USRZSR. W AY PSWRP VS XAGWT SR HMTWRFTT. A DGSIR
VS ZGWRK. W YAO GFAZ VEWT?”

“WC TS HF AT OSM'GF NMWDK, TWG.”

EF SXFRFZ WV WR VEF UWPEV SC VEF DSADE-UAYX SR VEAV TWZF, ARZ
GFAZ--CWGTV VS EWYTFUC ARZ VEFR AUSMZ: “'IAWV AV ZSJFG CSG YAY'TFUUF.'
WV'T RSV USRP, OSM TFF, PMAGZ. LFGGO, TAO VEAV YO ARTIFG IAT, GFDAUUFZ
VS UWCF.”

LFGGO TVAGVFZ WR EWT TAZZUF. “VEAV'T A HUABWRP TVGARPF ARTIFG, VSS,”
 TAWZ EF, AV EWT ESAGTFTV.

“VAKF VEAV YFTTAPF HADK, ARZ VEFO IWUU KRSI VEAV W GFDFWJFZ VEWT, AT
IFUU AT WC W IGSVF. YAKF VEF HFTV SC OSMG IAO. PSSZ RWPEV.”

IWVE VESTF ISGZT VEF XATTFRPFG SXFRFZ VEF DSADE-ZSSG ARZ PSV WR; RSV AV
AUU ATTWTVFZ HO EWT CFUUSI-XATTFRPFGT, IES EAZ FQXFZWVWSMTUO TFDGFVFZ
VEFWG IAVDEFT ARZ XMGTFT WR VEFWG HSSVT, ARZ IFGF RSI YAKWRP A PFRFGAU
XGFVFRDF SC HFWRP ATUFFX. IWVE RS YSGF ZFCWRWVF XMGXSTF VEAR VS FTDAXF
VEF EABAGZ SC SGWPWRAVWRP ARO SVEFG KWRZ SC ADVWSR.

VEF DSADE UMYHFGFZ SR APAWR, IWVE EFAJWFG IGFAVET SC YWTV DUSTWRP GSMRZ
WV AT WV HFPAR VEF ZFTDFRV. VEF PMAGZ TSSR GFXUADFZ EWT HUMRZFGHMTT
WR EWT AGY-DEFTV, ARZ, EAJWRP USSKFZ VS VEF GFTV SC WVT DSRVFRVT, ARZ
EAJWRP USSKFZ VS VEF TMXXUFYFRVAGO XWTVSUT VEAV EF ISGF WR EWT HFUV,
USSKFZ VS A TYAUUFG DEFTV HFRFAVE EWT TFAV, WR IEWDE VEFGF IFGF A
CFI TYWVE'T VSSUT, A DSMXUF SC VSGDEFT, ARZ A VWRZFG-HSQ. CSG EF IAT
CMGRWTEFZ IWVE VEAV DSYXUFVFRFTT VEAV WC VEF DSADE-UAYXT EAZ HFFR HUSIR
ARZ TVSGYFZ SMV, IEWDE ZWZ SDDATWSRAUUO EAXXFR, EF EAZ SRUO VS TEMV
EWYTFUC MX WRTWZF, KFFX VEF CUWRV ARZ TVFFU TXAGKT IFUU SCC VEF TVGAI,
ARZ PFV A UWPEV IWVE VSUFGAHUF TACFVO ARZ FATF (WC EF IFGF UMDKO) WR
CWJF YWRMVFT.

“VSY!” TSCVUO SJFG VEF DSADE GSSC.

“EAUUS, LSF.”

“ZWZ OSM EFAG VEF YFTTAPF?”

“W ZWZ, LSF.”

“IEAV ZWZ OSM YAKF SC WV, VSY?”

“RSVEWRP AV AUU, LSF.”

“VEAV'T A DSWRDWZFRDF, VSS,” VEF PMAGZ YMTFZ, “CSG W YAZF VEF TAYF SC WV
YOTFUC.”

LFGGO, UFCV AUSRF WR VEF YWTV ARZ ZAGKRFTT, ZWTYSMRVFZ YFARIEWUF, RSV
SRUO VS FATF EWT TXFRV ESGTF, HMV VS IWXF VEF YMZ CGSY EWT CADF, ARZ
TEAKF VEF IFV SMV SC EWT EAV-HGWY, IEWDE YWPEV HF DAXAHUF SC
ESUZWRP AHSMV EAUC A PAUUSR. ACVFG TVARZWRP IWVE VEF HGWZUF SJFG EWT
EFAJWUO-TXUATEFZ AGY, MRVWU VEF IEFFUT SC VEF YAWU IFGF RS USRPFG IWVEWR
EFAGWRP ARZ VEF RWPEV IAT NMWVF TVWUU APAWR, EF VMGRFZ VS IAUK ZSIR VEF
EWUU.

“ACVFG VEAV VEFGF PAUUSX CGSY VFYXUF HAG, SUZ UAZO, W ISR'V VGMTV OSMG
CSGF-UFPT VWUU W PFV OSM SR VEF UFJFU,” TAWZ VEWT ESAGTF YFTTFRPFG,
PUARDWRP AV EWT YAGF. “'GFDAUUFZ VS UWCF.' VEAV'T A HUABWRP TVGARPF
YFTTAPF. YMDE SC VEAV ISMUZR'V ZS CSG OSM, LFGGO! W TAO, LFGGO! OSM'Z
HF WR A HUABWRP HAZ IAO, WC GFDAUUWRP VS UWCF IAT VS DSYF WRVS CATEWSR,
LFGGO!”




WWW. VEF RWPEV TEAZSIT


A ISRZFGCMU CADV VS GFCUFDV MXSR, VEAV FJFGO EMYAR DGFAVMGF WT
DSRTVWVMVFZ VS HF VEAV XGSCSMRZ TFDGFV ARZ YOTVFGO VS FJFGO SVEFG. A
TSUFYR DSRTWZFGAVWSR, IEFR W FRVFG A PGFAV DWVO HO RWPEV, VEAV FJFGO
SRF SC VESTF ZAGKUO DUMTVFGFZ ESMTFT FRDUSTFT WVT SIR TFDGFV; VEAV FJFGO
GSSY WR FJFGO SRF SC VEFY FRDUSTFT WVT SIR TFDGFV; VEAV FJFGO HFAVWRP
EFAGV WR VEF EMRZGFZT SC VESMTARZT SC HGFATVT VEFGF, WT, WR TSYF SC
WVT WYAPWRWRPT, A TFDGFV VS VEF EFAGV RFAGFTV WV! TSYFVEWRP SC VEF
AICMURFTT, FJFR SC ZFAVE WVTFUC, WT GFCFGAHUF VS VEWT. RS YSGF DAR W
VMGR VEF UFAJFT SC VEWT ZFAG HSSK VEAV W USJFZ, ARZ JAWRUO ESXF WR VWYF
VS GFAZ WV AUU. RS YSGF DAR W USSK WRVS VEF ZFXVET SC VEWT MRCAVESYAHUF
IAVFG, IEFGFWR, AT YSYFRVAGO UWPEVT PUARDFZ WRVS WV, W EAJF EAZ PUWYXTFT
SC HMGWFZ VGFATMGF ARZ SVEFG VEWRPT TMHYFGPFZ. WV IAT AXXSWRVFZ VEAV VEF
HSSK TESMUZ TEMV IWVE A TXGWRP, CSG FJFG ARZ CSG FJFG, IEFR W EAZ GFAZ
HMV A XAPF. WV IAT AXXSWRVFZ VEAV VEF IAVFG TESMUZ HF USDKFZ WR AR
FVFGRAU CGSTV, IEFR VEF UWPEV IAT XUAOWRP SR WVT TMGCADF, ARZ W TVSSZ
WR WPRSGARDF SR VEF TESGF. YO CGWFRZ WT ZFAZ, YO RFWPEHSMG WT ZFAZ,
YO USJF, VEF ZAGUWRP SC YO TSMU, WT ZFAZ; WV WT VEF WRFQSGAHUF
DSRTSUWZAVWSR ARZ XFGXFVMAVWSR SC VEF TFDGFV VEAV IAT AUIAOT WR VEAV
WRZWJWZMAUWVO, ARZ IEWDE W TEAUU DAGGO WR YWRF VS YO UWCF'T FRZ. WR
ARO SC VEF HMGWAU-XUADFT SC VEWT DWVO VEGSMPE IEWDE W XATT, WT VEFGF
A TUFFXFG YSGF WRTDGMVAHUF VEAR WVT HMTO WREAHWVARVT AGF, WR VEFWG
WRRFGYSTV XFGTSRAUWVO, VS YF, SG VEAR W AY VS VEFY?

AT VS VEWT, EWT RAVMGAU ARZ RSV VS HF AUWFRAVFZ WREFGWVARDF, VEF
YFTTFRPFG SR ESGTFHADK EAZ FQADVUO VEF TAYF XSTTFTTWSRT AT VEF KWRP, VEF
CWGTV YWRWTVFG SC TVAVF, SG VEF GWDEFTV YFGDEARV WR USRZSR. TS IWVE VEF
VEGFF XATTFRPFGT TEMV MX WR VEF RAGGSI DSYXATT SC SRF UMYHFGWRP SUZ YAWU
DSADE; VEFO IFGF YOTVFGWFT VS SRF ARSVEFG, AT DSYXUFVF AT WC FADE EAZ
HFFR WR EWT SIR DSADE ARZ TWQ, SG EWT SIR DSADE ARZ TWQVO, IWVE VEF
HGFAZVE SC A DSMRVO HFVIFFR EWY ARZ VEF RFQV.

VEF YFTTFRPFG GSZF HADK AV AR FATO VGSV, TVSXXWRP XGFVVO SCVFR AV
AUF-ESMTFT HO VEF IAO VS ZGWRK, HMV FJWRDWRP A VFRZFRDO VS KFFX EWT
SIR DSMRTFU, ARZ VS KFFX EWT EAV DSDKFZ SJFG EWT FOFT. EF EAZ FOFT VEAV
ATTSGVFZ JFGO IFUU IWVE VEAV ZFDSGAVWSR, HFWRP SC A TMGCADF HUADK, IWVE
RS ZFXVE WR VEF DSUSMG SG CSGY, ARZ YMDE VSS RFAG VSPFVEFG--AT WC VEFO
IFGF ACGAWZ SC HFWRP CSMRZ SMV WR TSYFVEWRP, TWRPUO, WC VEFO KFXV VSS
CAG AXAGV. VEFO EAZ A TWRWTVFG FQXGFTTWSR, MRZFG AR SUZ DSDKFZ-EAV UWKF
A VEGFF-DSGRFGFZ TXWVVSSR, ARZ SJFG A PGFAV YMCCUFG CSG VEF DEWR ARZ
VEGSAV, IEWDE ZFTDFRZFZ RFAGUO VS VEF IFAGFG'T KRFFT. IEFR EF TVSXXFZ
CSG ZGWRK, EF YSJFZ VEWT YMCCUFG IWVE EWT UFCV EARZ, SRUO IEWUF EF
XSMGFZ EWT UWNMSG WR IWVE EWT GWPEV; AT TSSR AT VEAV IAT ZSRF, EF
YMCCUFZ APAWR.

“RS, LFGGO, RS!” TAWZ VEF YFTTFRPFG, EAGXWRP SR SRF VEFYF AT EF GSZF.
“WV ISMUZR'V ZS CSG OSM, LFGGO. LFGGO, OSM ESRFTV VGAZFTYAR, WV ISMUZR'V
TMWV _OSMG_ UWRF SC HMTWRFTT! GFDAUUFZ--! HMTV YF WC W ZSR'V VEWRK EF'Z
HFFR A ZGWRKWRP!”

EWT YFTTAPF XFGXUFQFZ EWT YWRZ VS VEAV ZFPGFF VEAV EF IAT CAWR, TFJFGAU
VWYFT, VS VAKF SCC EWT EAV VS TDGAVDE EWT EFAZ. FQDFXV SR VEF DGSIR,
IEWDE IAT GAPPFZUO HAUZ, EF EAZ TVWCC, HUADK EAWG, TVARZWRP LAPPFZUO AUU
SJFG WV, ARZ PGSIWRP ZSIR EWUU AUYSTV VS EWT HGSAZ, HUMRV RSTF. WV IAT
TS UWKF TYWVE'T ISGK, TS YMDE YSGF UWKF VEF VSX SC A TVGSRPUO TXWKFZ
IAUU VEAR A EFAZ SC EAWG, VEAV VEF HFTV SC XUAOFGT AV UFAX-CGSP YWPEV
EAJF ZFDUWRFZ EWY, AT VEF YSTV ZARPFGSMT YAR WR VEF ISGUZ VS PS SJFG.

IEWUF EF VGSVVFZ HADK IWVE VEF YFTTAPF EF IAT VS ZFUWJFG VS VEF RWPEV
IAVDEYAR WR EWT HSQ AV VEF ZSSG SC VFUUTSR'T HARK, HO VFYXUF HAG, IES
IAT VS ZFUWJFG WV VS PGFAVFG AMVESGWVWFT IWVEWR, VEF TEAZSIT SC VEF
RWPEV VSSK TMDE TEAXFT VS EWY AT AGSTF SMV SC VEF YFTTAPF, ARZ VSSK TMDE
TEAXFT VS VEF YAGF AT AGSTF SMV SC _EFG_ XGWJAVF VSXWDT SC MRFATWRFTT.
VEFO TFFYFZ VS HF RMYFGSMT, CSG TEF TEWFZ AV FJFGO TEAZSI SR VEF GSAZ.

IEAV VWYF, VEF YAWU-DSADE UMYHFGFZ, LSUVFZ, GAVVUFZ, ARZ HMYXFZ MXSR
WVT VFZWSMT IAO, IWVE WVT VEGFF CFUUSI-WRTDGMVAHUFT WRTWZF. VS IESY,
UWKFIWTF, VEF TEAZSIT SC VEF RWPEV GFJFAUFZ VEFYTFUJFT, WR VEF CSGYT
VEFWG ZSBWRP FOFT ARZ IARZFGWRP VESMPEVT TMPPFTVFZ.

VFUUTSR'T HARK EAZ A GMR MXSR WV WR VEF YAWU. AT VEF HARK
XATTFRPFG--IWVE AR AGY ZGAIR VEGSMPE VEF UFAVEFGR TVGAX, IEWDE ZWZ IEAV
UAO WR WV VS KFFX EWY CGSY XSMRZWRP APAWRTV VEF RFQV XATTFRPFG,
ARZ ZGWJWRP EWY WRVS EWT DSGRFG, IEFRFJFG VEF DSADE PSV A TXFDWAU
LSUV--RSZZFZ WR EWT XUADF, IWVE EAUC-TEMV FOFT, VEF UWVVUF
DSADE-IWRZSIT, ARZ VEF DSADE-UAYX ZWYUO PUFAYWRP VEGSMPE VEFY, ARZ VEF
HMUKO HMRZUF SC SXXSTWVF XATTFRPFG, HFDAYF VEF HARK, ARZ ZWZ A PGFAV
TVGSKF SC HMTWRFTT. VEF GAVVUF SC VEF EAGRFTT IAT VEF DEWRK SC YSRFO,
ARZ YSGF ZGACVT IFGF ESRSMGFZ WR CWJF YWRMVFT VEAR FJFR VFUUTSR'T, IWVE
AUU WVT CSGFWPR ARZ ESYF DSRRFDVWSR, FJFG XAWZ WR VEGWDF VEF VWYF. VEFR
VEF TVGSRP-GSSYT MRZFGPGSMRZ, AV VFUUTSR'T, IWVE TMDE SC VEFWG JAUMAHUF
TVSGFT ARZ TFDGFVT AT IFGF KRSIR VS VEF XATTFRPFG (ARZ WV IAT RSV A
UWVVUF VEAV EF KRFI AHSMV VEFY), SXFRFZ HFCSGF EWY, ARZ EF IFRV WR AYSRP
VEFY IWVE VEF PGFAV KFOT ARZ VEF CFFHUO-HMGRWRP DARZUF, ARZ CSMRZ VEFY
TACF, ARZ TVGSRP, ARZ TSMRZ, ARZ TVWUU, LMTV AT EF EAZ UATV TFFR VEFY.

HMV, VESMPE VEF HARK IAT AUYSTV AUIAOT IWVE EWY, ARZ VESMPE VEF DSADE
(WR A DSRCMTFZ IAO, UWKF VEF XGFTFRDF SC XAWR MRZFG AR SXWAVF) IAT
AUIAOT IWVE EWY, VEFGF IAT ARSVEFG DMGGFRV SC WYXGFTTWSR VEAV RFJFG
DFATFZ VS GMR, AUU VEGSMPE VEF RWPEV. EF IAT SR EWT IAO VS ZWP TSYF SRF
SMV SC A PGAJF.

RSI, IEWDE SC VEF YMUVWVMZF SC CADFT VEAV TESIFZ VEFYTFUJFT HFCSGF EWY
IAT VEF VGMF CADF SC VEF HMGWFZ XFGTSR, VEF TEAZSIT SC VEF RWPEV ZWZ
RSV WRZWDAVF; HMV VEFO IFGF AUU VEF CADFT SC A YAR SC CWJF-ARZ-CSGVO HO
OFAGT, ARZ VEFO ZWCCFGFZ XGWRDWXAUUO WR VEF XATTWSRT VEFO FQXGFTTFZ,
ARZ WR VEF PEATVUWRFTT SC VEFWG ISGR ARZ IATVFZ TVAVF. XGWZF, DSRVFYXV,
ZFCWARDF, TVMHHSGRRFTT, TMHYWTTWSR, UAYFRVAVWSR, TMDDFFZFZ SRF ARSVEFG;
TS ZWZ JAGWFVWFT SC TMRKFR DEFFK, DAZAJFGSMT DSUSMG, FYADWAVFZ EARZT
ARZ CWPMGFT. HMV VEF CADF IAT WR VEF YAWR SRF CADF, ARZ FJFGO EFAZ IAT
XGFYAVMGFUO IEWVF. A EMRZGFZ VWYFT VEF ZSBWRP XATTFRPFG WRNMWGFZ SC VEWT
TXFDVGF:

“HMGWFZ ESI USRP?”

VEF ARTIFG IAT AUIAOT VEF TAYF: “AUYSTV FWPEVFFR OFAGT.”

“OSM EAZ AHARZSRFZ AUU ESXF SC HFWRP ZMP SMV?”

“USRP APS.”

“OSM KRSI VEAV OSM AGF GFDAUUFZ VS UWCF?”

“VEFO VFUU YF TS.”

“W ESXF OSM DAGF VS UWJF?”

“W DAR'V TAO.”

“TEAUU W TESI EFG VS OSM? IWUU OSM DSYF ARZ TFF EFG?”

VEF ARTIFGT VS VEWT NMFTVWSR IFGF JAGWSMT ARZ DSRVGAZWDVSGO. TSYFVWYFT
VEF HGSKFR GFXUO IAT, “IAWV! WV ISMUZ KWUU YF WC W TAI EFG VSS TSSR.”
 TSYFVWYFT, WV IAT PWJFR WR A VFRZFG GAWR SC VFAGT, ARZ VEFR WV IAT,
“VAKF YF VS EFG.” TSYFVWYFT WV IAT TVAGWRP ARZ HFIWUZFGFZ, ARZ VEFR WV
IAT, “W ZSR'V KRSI EFG. W ZSR'V MRZFGTVARZ.”

ACVFG TMDE WYAPWRAGO ZWTDSMGTF, VEF XATTFRPFG WR EWT CARDO ISMUZ ZWP,
ARZ ZWP, ZWP--RSI IWVE A TXAZF, RSI IWVE A PGFAV KFO, RSI IWVE EWT
EARZT--VS ZWP VEWT IGFVDEFZ DGFAVMGF SMV. PSV SMV AV UATV, IWVE FAGVE
EARPWRP AHSMV EWT CADF ARZ EAWG, EF ISMUZ TMZZFRUO CAR AIAO VS ZMTV. VEF
XATTFRPFG ISMUZ VEFR TVAGV VS EWYTFUC, ARZ USIFG VEF IWRZSI, VS PFV VEF
GFAUWVO SC YWTV ARZ GAWR SR EWT DEFFK.

OFV FJFR IEFR EWT FOFT IFGF SXFRFZ SR VEF YWTV ARZ GAWR, SR VEF YSJWRP
XAVDE SC UWPEV CGSY VEF UAYXT, ARZ VEF EFZPF AV VEF GSAZTWZF GFVGFAVWRP
HO LFGKT, VEF RWPEV TEAZSIT SMVTWZF VEF DSADE ISMUZ CAUU WRVS VEF VGAWR
SC VEF RWPEV TEAZSIT IWVEWR. VEF GFAU HARKWRP-ESMTF HO VFYXUF HAG, VEF
GFAU HMTWRFTT SC VEF XATV ZAO, VEF GFAU TVGSRP GSSYT, VEF GFAU FQXGFTT
TFRV ACVFG EWY, ARZ VEF GFAU YFTTAPF GFVMGRFZ, ISMUZ AUU HF VEFGF. SMV
SC VEF YWZTV SC VEFY, VEF PESTVUO CADF ISMUZ GWTF, ARZ EF ISMUZ ADDSTV
WV APAWR.

“HMGWFZ ESI USRP?”

“AUYSTV FWPEVFFR OFAGT.”

“W ESXF OSM DAGF VS UWJF?”

“W DAR'V TAO.”

ZWP--ZWP--ZWP--MRVWU AR WYXAVWFRV YSJFYFRV CGSY SRF SC VEF VIS
XATTFRPFGT ISMUZ AZYSRWTE EWY VS XMUU MX VEF IWRZSI, ZGAI EWT AGY
TFDMGFUO VEGSMPE VEF UFAVEFGR TVGAX, ARZ TXFDMUAVF MXSR VEF VIS
TUMYHFGWRP CSGYT, MRVWU EWT YWRZ USTV WVT ESUZ SC VEFY, ARZ VEFO APAWR
TUWZ AIAO WRVS VEF HARK ARZ VEF PGAJF.

“HMGWFZ ESI USRP?”

“AUYSTV FWPEVFFR OFAGT.”

“OSM EAZ AHARZSRFZ AUU ESXF SC HFWRP ZMP SMV?”

“USRP APS.”

VEF ISGZT IFGF TVWUU WR EWT EFAGWRP AT LMTV TXSKFR--ZWTVWRDVUO WR
EWT EFAGWRP AT FJFG TXSKFR ISGZT EAZ HFFR WR EWT UWCF--IEFR VEF IFAGO
XATTFRPFG TVAGVFZ VS VEF DSRTDWSMTRFTT SC ZAOUWPEV, ARZ CSMRZ VEAV VEF
TEAZSIT SC VEF RWPEV IFGF PSRF.

EF USIFGFZ VEF IWRZSI, ARZ USSKFZ SMV AV VEF GWTWRP TMR. VEFGF IAT A
GWZPF SC XUSMPEFZ UARZ, IWVE A XUSMPE MXSR WV IEFGF WV EAZ HFFR UFCV
UATV RWPEV IEFR VEF ESGTFT IFGF MROSKFZ; HFOSRZ, A NMWFV DSXXWDF-ISSZ,
WR IEWDE YARO UFAJFT SC HMGRWRP GFZ ARZ PSUZFR OFUUSI TVWUU GFYAWRFZ
MXSR VEF VGFFT. VESMPE VEF FAGVE IAT DSUZ ARZ IFV, VEF TKO IAT DUFAG,
ARZ VEF TMR GSTF HGWPEV, XUADWZ, ARZ HFAMVWCMU.

“FWPEVFFR OFAGT!” TAWZ VEF XATTFRPFG, USSKWRP AV VEF TMR. “PGADWSMT
DGFAVSG SC ZAO! VS HF HMGWFZ AUWJF CSG FWPEVFFR OFAGT!”




WJ. VEF XGFXAGAVWSR


IEFR VEF YAWU PSV TMDDFTTCMUUO VS ZSJFG, WR VEF DSMGTF SC VEF CSGFRSSR,
VEF EFAZ ZGAIFG AV VEF GSOAU PFSGPF ESVFU SXFRFZ VEF DSADE-ZSSG AT EWT
DMTVSY IAT. EF ZWZ WV IWVE TSYF CUSMGWTE SC DFGFYSRO, CSG A YAWU LSMGRFO
CGSY USRZSR WR IWRVFG IAT AR ADEWFJFYFRV VS DSRPGAVMUAVF AR AZJFRVMGSMT
VGAJFUUFG MXSR.

HO VEAV VWYF, VEFGF IAT SRUO SRF AZJFRVMGSMT VGAJFUUFG UFCV HF
DSRPGAVMUAVFZ: CSG VEF VIS SVEFGT EAZ HFFR TFV ZSIR AV VEFWG GFTXFDVWJF
GSAZTWZF ZFTVWRAVWSRT. VEF YWUZFIO WRTWZF SC VEF DSADE, IWVE WVT ZAYX
ARZ ZWGVO TVGAI, WVT ZWTAPGFFAHUF TYFUU, ARZ WVT SHTDMGWVO, IAT GAVEFG
UWKF A UAGPFG ZSP-KFRRFU. YG. USGGO, VEF XATTFRPFG, TEAKWRP EWYTFUC SMV
SC WV WR DEAWRT SC TVGAI, A VARPUF SC TEAPPO IGAXXFG, CUAXXWRP EAV, ARZ
YMZZO UFPT, IAT GAVEFG UWKF A UAGPFG TSGV SC ZSP.

“VEFGF IWUU HF A XADKFV VS DAUAWT, VSYSGGSI, ZGAIFG?”

“OFT, TWG, WC VEF IFAVEFG ESUZT ARZ VEF IWRZ TFVT VSUFGAHUF CAWG. VEF
VWZF IWUU TFGJF XGFVVO RWDFUO AV AHSMV VIS WR VEF ACVFGRSSR, TWG. HFZ,
TWG?”

“W TEAUU RSV PS VS HFZ VWUU RWPEV; HMV W IARV A HFZGSSY, ARZ A HAGHFG.”

“ARZ VEFR HGFAKCATV, TWG? OFT, TWG. VEAV IAO, TWG, WC OSM XUFATF.
TESI DSRDSGZ! PFRVUFYAR'T JAUWTF ARZ ESV IAVFG VS DSRDSGZ. XMUU SCC
PFRVUFYAR'T HSSVT WR DSRDSGZ. (OSM IWUU CWRZ A CWRF TFA-DSAU CWGF, TWG.)
CFVDE HAGHFG VS DSRDSGZ. TVWG AHSMV VEFGF, RSI, CSG DSRDSGZ!”

VEF DSRDSGZ HFZ-DEAYHFG HFWRP AUIAOT ATTWPRFZ VS A XATTFRPFG HO VEF
YAWU, ARZ XATTFRPFGT HO VEF YAWU HFWRP AUIAOT EFAJWUO IGAXXFZ MX CGSY
EFAZ VS CSSV, VEF GSSY EAZ VEF SZZ WRVFGFTV CSG VEF FTVAHUWTEYFRV SC VEF
GSOAU PFSGPF, VEAV AUVESMPE HMV SRF KWRZ SC YAR IAT TFFR VS PS WRVS WV,
AUU KWRZT ARZ JAGWFVWFT SC YFR DAYF SMV SC WV. DSRTFNMFRVUO, ARSVEFG
ZGAIFG, ARZ VIS XSGVFGT, ARZ TFJFGAU YAWZT ARZ VEF UARZUAZO, IFGF AUU
USWVFGWRP HO ADDWZFRV AV JAGWSMT XSWRVT SC VEF GSAZ HFVIFFR VEF DSRDSGZ
ARZ VEF DSCCFF-GSSY, IEFR A PFRVUFYAR SC TWQVO, CSGYAUUO ZGFTTFZ WR A
HGSIR TMWV SC DUSVEFT, XGFVVO IFUU ISGR, HMV JFGO IFUU KFXV, IWVE UAGPF
TNMAGF DMCCT ARZ UAGPF CUAXT VS VEF XSDKFVT, XATTFZ AUSRP SR EWT IAO VS
EWT HGFAKCATV.

VEF DSCCFF-GSSY EAZ RS SVEFG SDDMXARV, VEAV CSGFRSSR, VEAR VEF PFRVUFYAR
WR HGSIR. EWT HGFAKCATV-VAHUF IAT ZGAIR HFCSGF VEF CWGF, ARZ AT EF TAV,
IWVE WVT UWPEV TEWRWRP SR EWY, IAWVWRP CSG VEF YFAU, EF TAV TS TVWUU,
VEAV EF YWPEV EAJF HFFR TWVVWRP CSG EWT XSGVGAWV.

JFGO SGZFGUO ARZ YFVESZWDAU EF USSKFZ, IWVE A EARZ SR FADE KRFF, ARZ A
USMZ IAVDE VWDKWRP A TSRSGSMT TFGYSR MRZFG EWT CUAXXFZ IAWTV-DSAV,
AT VESMPE WV XWVVFZ WVT PGAJWVO ARZ USRPFJWVO APAWRTV VEF UFJWVO ARZ
FJARFTDFRDF SC VEF HGWTK CWGF. EF EAZ A PSSZ UFP, ARZ IAT A UWVVUF JAWR
SC WV, CSG EWT HGSIR TVSDKWRPT CWVVFZ TUFFK ARZ DUSTF, ARZ IFGF SC A
CWRF VFQVMGF; EWT TESFT ARZ HMDKUFT, VSS, VESMPE XUAWR, IFGF VGWY. EF
ISGF AR SZZ UWVVUF TUFFK DGWTX CUAQFR IWP, TFVVWRP JFGO DUSTF VS EWT
EFAZ: IEWDE IWP, WV WT VS HF XGFTMYFZ, IAT YAZF SC EAWG, HMV IEWDE
USSKFZ CAG YSGF AT VESMPE WV IFGF TXMR CGSY CWUAYFRVT SC TWUK SG PUATT.
EWT UWRFR, VESMPE RSV SC A CWRFRFTT WR ADDSGZARDF IWVE EWT TVSDKWRPT,
IAT AT IEWVF AT VEF VSXT SC VEF IAJFT VEAV HGSKF MXSR VEF RFWPEHSMGWRP
HFADE, SG VEF TXFDKT SC TAWU VEAV PUWRVFZ WR VEF TMRUWPEV CAG AV TFA. A
CADF EAHWVMAUUO TMXXGFTTFZ ARZ NMWFVFZ, IAT TVWUU UWPEVFZ MX MRZFG VEF
NMAWRV IWP HO A XAWG SC YSWTV HGWPEV FOFT VEAV WV YMTV EAJF DSTV
VEFWG SIRFG, WR OFAGT PSRF HO, TSYF XAWRT VS ZGWUU VS VEF DSYXSTFZ ARZ
GFTFGJFZ FQXGFTTWSR SC VFUUTSR'T HARK. EF EAZ A EFAUVEO DSUSMG WR EWT
DEFFKT, ARZ EWT CADF, VESMPE UWRFZ, HSGF CFI VGADFT SC ARQWFVO.
HMV, XFGEAXT VEF DSRCWZFRVWAU HADEFUSG DUFGKT WR VFUUTSR'T HARK IFGF
XGWRDWXAUUO SDDMXWFZ IWVE VEF DAGFT SC SVEFG XFSXUF; ARZ XFGEAXT
TFDSRZ-EARZ DAGFT, UWKF TFDSRZ-EARZ DUSVEFT, DSYF FATWUO SCC ARZ SR.

DSYXUFVWRP EWT GFTFYHUARDF VS A YAR IES IAT TWVVWRP CSG EWT XSGVGAWV,
YG. USGGO ZGSXXFZ SCC VS TUFFX. VEF AGGWJAU SC EWT HGFAKCATV GSMTFZ EWY,
ARZ EF TAWZ VS VEF ZGAIFG, AT EF YSJFZ EWT DEAWG VS WV:

“W IWTE ADDSYYSZAVWSR XGFXAGFZ CSG A OSMRP UAZO IES YAO DSYF EFGF AV ARO
VWYF VS-ZAO. TEF YAO ATK CSG YG. LAGJWT USGGO, SG TEF YAO SRUO ATK CSG A
PFRVUFYAR CGSY VFUUTSR'T HARK. XUFATF VS UFV YF KRSI.”

“OFT, TWG. VFUUTSR'T HARK WR USRZSR, TWG?”

“OFT.”

“OFT, TWG. IF EAJF SCVFRVWYFT VEF ESRSMG VS FRVFGVAWR OSMG PFRVUFYFR WR
VEFWG VGAJFUUWRP HADKIAGZT ARZ CSGIAGZT HFVIWQV USRZSR ARZ XAGWT, TWG. A
JATV ZFAU SC VGAJFUUWRP, TWG, WR VFUUTSR ARZ DSYXARO'T ESMTF.”

“OFT. IF AGF NMWVF A CGFRDE ESMTF, AT IFUU AT AR FRPUWTE SRF.”

“OFT, TWG. RSV YMDE WR VEF EAHWV SC TMDE VGAJFUUWRP OSMGTFUC, W VEWRK,
TWG?”

“RSV SC UAVF OFAGT. WV WT CWCVFFR OFAGT TWRDF IF--TWRDF W--DAYF UATV
CGSY CGARDF.”

“WRZFFZ, TWG? VEAV IAT HFCSGF YO VWYF EFGF, TWG. HFCSGF SMG XFSXUF'T
VWYF EFGF, TWG. VEF PFSGPF IAT WR SVEFG EARZT AV VEAV VWYF, TWG.”

“W HFUWFJF TS.”

“HMV W ISMUZ ESUZ A XGFVVO IAPFG, TWG, VEAV A ESMTF UWKF VFUUTSR ARZ
DSYXARO IAT CUSMGWTEWRP, A YAVVFG SC CWCVO, RSV VS TXFAK SC CWCVFFR
OFAGT APS?”

“OSM YWPEV VGFHUF VEAV, ARZ TAO A EMRZGFZ ARZ CWCVO, OFV RSV HF CAG CGSY
VEF VGMVE.”

“WRZFFZ, TWG!”

GSMRZWRP EWT YSMVE ARZ HSVE EWT FOFT, AT EF TVFXXFZ HADKIAGZ CGSY VEF
VAHUF, VEF IAWVFG TEWCVFZ EWT RAXKWR CGSY EWT GWPEV AGY VS EWT UFCV,
ZGSXXFZ WRVS A DSYCSGVAHUF AVVWVMZF, ARZ TVSSZ TMGJFOWRP VEF PMFTV IEWUF
EF AVF ARZ ZGARK, AT CGSY AR SHTFGJAVSGO SG IAVDEVSIFG. ADDSGZWRP VS VEF
WYYFYSGWAU MTAPF SC IAWVFGT WR AUU APFT.

IEFR YG. USGGO EAZ CWRWTEFZ EWT HGFAKCATV, EF IFRV SMV CSG A TVGSUU SR
VEF HFADE. VEF UWVVUF RAGGSI, DGSSKFZ VSIR SC ZSJFG EWZ WVTFUC AIAO
CGSY VEF HFADE, ARZ GAR WVT EFAZ WRVS VEF DEAUK DUWCCT, UWKF A YAGWRF
STVGWDE. VEF HFADE IAT A ZFTFGV SC EFAXT SC TFA ARZ TVSRFT VMYHUWRP
IWUZUO AHSMV, ARZ VEF TFA ZWZ IEAV WV UWKFZ, ARZ IEAV WV UWKFZ IAT
ZFTVGMDVWSR. WV VEMRZFGFZ AV VEF VSIR, ARZ VEMRZFGFZ AV VEF DUWCCT, ARZ
HGSMPEV VEF DSATV ZSIR, YAZUO. VEF AWG AYSRP VEF ESMTFT IAT SC TS TVGSRP
A XWTDAVSGO CUAJSMG VEAV SRF YWPEV EAJF TMXXSTFZ TWDK CWTE IFRV MX VS HF
ZWXXFZ WR WV, AT TWDK XFSXUF IFRV ZSIR VS HF ZWXXFZ WR VEF TFA. A UWVVUF
CWTEWRP IAT ZSRF WR VEF XSGV, ARZ A NMARVWVO SC TVGSUUWRP AHSMV HO
RWPEV, ARZ USSKWRP TFAIAGZ: XAGVWDMUAGUO AV VESTF VWYFT IEFR VEF VWZF
YAZF, ARZ IAT RFAG CUSSZ. TYAUU VGAZFTYFR, IES ZWZ RS HMTWRFTT IEAVFJFG,
TSYFVWYFT MRADDSMRVAHUO GFAUWTFZ UAGPF CSGVMRFT, ARZ WV IAT GFYAGKAHUF
VEAV RSHSZO WR VEF RFWPEHSMGESSZ DSMUZ FRZMGF A UAYXUWPEVFG.

AT VEF ZAO ZFDUWRFZ WRVS VEF ACVFGRSSR, ARZ VEF AWG, IEWDE EAZ HFFR
AV WRVFGJAUT DUFAG FRSMPE VS AUUSI VEF CGFRDE DSATV VS HF TFFR, HFDAYF
APAWR DEAGPFZ IWVE YWTV ARZ JAXSMG, YG. USGGO'T VESMPEVT TFFYFZ VS DUSMZ
VSS. IEFR WV IAT ZAGK, ARZ EF TAV HFCSGF VEF DSCCFF-GSSY CWGF, AIAWVWRP
EWT ZWRRFG AT EF EAZ AIAWVFZ EWT HGFAKCATV, EWT YWRZ IAT HMTWUO ZWPPWRP,
ZWPPWRP, ZWPPWRP, WR VEF UWJF GFZ DSAUT.

A HSVVUF SC PSSZ DUAGFV ACVFG ZWRRFG ZSFT A ZWPPFG WR VEF GFZ DSAUT RS
EAGY, SVEFGIWTF VEAR AT WV EAT A VFRZFRDO VS VEGSI EWY SMV SC ISGK.
YG. USGGO EAZ HFFR WZUF A USRP VWYF, ARZ EAZ LMTV XSMGFZ SMV EWT UATV
PUATTCMU SC IWRF IWVE AT DSYXUFVF AR AXXFAGARDF SC TAVWTCADVWSR AT WT
FJFG VS HF CSMRZ WR AR FUZFGUO PFRVUFYAR SC A CGFTE DSYXUFQWSR IES EAT
PSV VS VEF FRZ SC A HSVVUF, IEFR A GAVVUWRP SC IEFFUT DAYF MX VEF RAGGSI
TVGFFV, ARZ GMYHUFZ WRVS VEF WRR-OAGZ.

EF TFV ZSIR EWT PUATT MRVSMDEFZ. “VEWT WT YAY'TFUUF!” TAWZ EF.

WR A JFGO CFI YWRMVFT VEF IAWVFG DAYF WR VS ARRSMRDF VEAV YWTT YARFVVF
EAZ AGGWJFZ CGSY USRZSR, ARZ ISMUZ HF EAXXO VS TFF VEF PFRVUFYAR CGSY
VFUUTSR'T.

“TS TSSR?”

YWTT YARFVVF EAZ VAKFR TSYF GFCGFTEYFRV SR VEF GSAZ, ARZ GFNMWGFZ RSRF
VEFR, ARZ IAT FQVGFYFUO ARQWSMT VS TFF VEF PFRVUFYAR CGSY VFUUTSR'T
WYYFZWAVFUO, WC WV TMWVFZ EWT XUFATMGF ARZ DSRJFRWFRDF.

VEF PFRVUFYAR CGSY VFUUTSR'T EAZ RSVEWRP UFCV CSG WV HMV VS FYXVO EWT
PUATT IWVE AR AWG SC TVSUWZ ZFTXFGAVWSR, TFVVUF EWT SZZ UWVVUF CUAQFR
IWP AV VEF FAGT, ARZ CSUUSI VEF IAWVFG VS YWTT YARFVVF'T AXAGVYFRV.
WV IAT A UAGPF, ZAGK GSSY, CMGRWTEFZ WR A CMRFGFAU YARRFG IWVE HUADK
ESGTFEAWG, ARZ USAZFZ IWVE EFAJO ZAGK VAHUFT. VEFTF EAZ HFFR SWUFZ ARZ
SWUFZ, MRVWU VEF VIS VAUU DARZUFT SR VEF VAHUF WR VEF YWZZUF SC VEF GSSY
IFGF PUSSYWUO GFCUFDVFZ SR FJFGO UFAC; AT WC _VEFO_ IFGF HMGWFZ, WR ZFFX
PGAJFT SC HUADK YAESPARO, ARZ RS UWPEV VS TXFAK SC DSMUZ HF FQXFDVFZ
CGSY VEFY MRVWU VEFO IFGF ZMP SMV.

VEF SHTDMGWVO IAT TS ZWCCWDMUV VS XFRFVGAVF VEAV YG. USGGO, XWDKWRP EWT
IAO SJFG VEF IFUU-ISGR VMGKFO DAGXFV, TMXXSTFZ YWTT YARFVVF VS HF, CSG
VEF YSYFRV, WR TSYF AZLADFRV GSSY, MRVWU, EAJWRP PSV XATV VEF VIS VAUU
DARZUFT, EF TAI TVARZWRP VS GFDFWJF EWY HO VEF VAHUF HFVIFFR VEFY ARZ
VEF CWGF, A OSMRP UAZO SC RSV YSGF VEAR TFJFRVFFR, WR A GWZWRP-DUSAK,
ARZ TVWUU ESUZWRP EFG TVGAI VGAJFUUWRP-EAV HO WVT GWHHSR WR EFG EARZ. AT
EWT FOFT GFTVFZ SR A TESGV, TUWPEV, XGFVVO CWPMGF, A NMARVWVO SC PSUZFR
EAWG, A XAWG SC HUMF FOFT VEAV YFV EWT SIR IWVE AR WRNMWGWRP USSK, ARZ
A CSGFEFAZ IWVE A TWRPMUAG DAXADWVO (GFYFYHFGWRP ESI OSMRP ARZ TYSSVE
WV IAT), SC GWCVWRP ARZ KRWVVWRP WVTFUC WRVS AR FQXGFTTWSR VEAV IAT
RSV NMWVF SRF SC XFGXUFQWVO, SG ISRZFG, SG AUAGY, SG YFGFUO SC A HGWPEV
CWQFZ AVVFRVWSR, VESMPE WV WRDUMZFZ AUU VEF CSMG FQXGFTTWSRT--AT EWT
FOFT GFTVFZ SR VEFTF VEWRPT, A TMZZFR JWJWZ UWKFRFTT XATTFZ HFCSGF EWY,
SC A DEWUZ IESY EF EAZ EFUZ WR EWT AGYT SR VEF XATTAPF ADGSTT VEAV JFGO
DEARRFU, SRF DSUZ VWYF, IEFR VEF EAWU ZGWCVFZ EFAJWUO ARZ VEF TFA GAR
EWPE. VEF UWKFRFTT XATTFZ AIAO, UWKF A HGFAVE AUSRP VEF TMGCADF SC
VEF PAMRV XWFG-PUATT HFEWRZ EFG, SR VEF CGAYF SC IEWDE, A ESTXWVAU
XGSDFTTWSR SC RFPGS DMXWZT, TFJFGAU EFAZUFTT ARZ AUU DGWXXUFT, IFGF
SCCFGWRP HUADK HATKFVT SC ZFAZ TFA CGMWV VS HUADK ZWJWRWVWFT SC VEF
CFYWRWRF PFRZFG--ARZ EF YAZF EWT CSGYAU HSI VS YWTT YARFVVF.

“XGAO VAKF A TFAV, TWG.” WR A JFGO DUFAG ARZ XUFATARV OSMRP JSWDF; A
UWVVUF CSGFWPR WR WVT ADDFRV, HMV A JFGO UWVVUF WRZFFZ.

“W KWTT OSMG EARZ, YWTT,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, IWVE VEF YARRFGT SC AR FAGUWFG
ZAVF, AT EF YAZF EWT CSGYAU HSI APAWR, ARZ VSSK EWT TFAV.

“W GFDFWJFZ A UFVVFG CGSY VEF HARK, TWG, OFTVFGZAO, WRCSGYWRP YF VEAV
TSYF WRVFUUWPFRDF--SG ZWTDSJFGO--”

“VEF ISGZ WT RSV YAVFGWAU, YWTT; FWVEFG ISGZ IWUU ZS.”

“--GFTXFDVWRP VEF TYAUU XGSXFGVO SC YO XSSG CAVEFG, IESY W RFJFG TAI--TS
USRP ZFAZ--”

YG. USGGO YSJFZ WR EWT DEAWG, ARZ DATV A VGSMHUFZ USSK VSIAGZT VEF
ESTXWVAU XGSDFTTWSR SC RFPGS DMXWZT. AT WC _VEFO_ EAZ ARO EFUX CSG
AROHSZO WR VEFWG AHTMGZ HATKFVT!

“--GFRZFGFZ WV RFDFTTAGO VEAV W TESMUZ PS VS XAGWT, VEFGF VS DSYYMRWDAVF
IWVE A PFRVUFYAR SC VEF HARK, TS PSSZ AT VS HF ZFTXAVDEFZ VS XAGWT CSG
VEF XMGXSTF.”

“YOTFUC.”

“AT W IAT XGFXAGFZ VS EFAG, TWG.”

TEF DMGVTFOFZ VS EWY (OSMRP UAZWFT YAZF DMGVTFOT WR VESTF ZAOT), IWVE A
XGFVVO ZFTWGF VS DSRJFO VS EWY VEAV TEF CFUV ESI YMDE SUZFG ARZ IWTFG EF
IAT VEAR TEF. EF YAZF EFG ARSVEFG HSI.

“W GFXUWFZ VS VEF HARK, TWG, VEAV AT WV IAT DSRTWZFGFZ RFDFTTAGO, HO
VESTF IES KRSI, ARZ IES AGF TS KWRZ AT VS AZJWTF YF, VEAV W TESMUZ PS VS
CGARDF, ARZ VEAV AT W AY AR SGXEAR ARZ EAJF RS CGWFRZ IES DSMUZ PS IWVE
YF, W TESMUZ FTVFFY WV EWPEUO WC W YWPEV HF XFGYWVVFZ VS XUADF YOTFUC,
ZMGWRP VEF LSMGRFO, MRZFG VEAV ISGVEO PFRVUFYAR'T XGSVFDVWSR. VEF
PFRVUFYAR EAZ UFCV USRZSR, HMV W VEWRK A YFTTFRPFG IAT TFRV ACVFG EWY VS
HFP VEF CAJSMG SC EWT IAWVWRP CSG YF EFGF.”

“W IAT EAXXO,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, “VS HF FRVGMTVFZ IWVE VEF DEAGPF. W TEAUU
HF YSGF EAXXO VS FQFDMVF WV.”

“TWG, W VEARK OSM WRZFFZ. W VEARK OSM JFGO PGAVFCMUUO. WV IAT VSUZ YF
HO VEF HARK VEAV VEF PFRVUFYAR ISMUZ FQXUAWR VS YF VEF ZFVAWUT SC VEF
HMTWRFTT, ARZ VEAV W YMTV XGFXAGF YOTFUC VS CWRZ VEFY SC A TMGXGWTWRP
RAVMGF. W EAJF ZSRF YO HFTV VS XGFXAGF YOTFUC, ARZ W RAVMGAUUO EAJF A
TVGSRP ARZ FAPFG WRVFGFTV VS KRSI IEAV VEFO AGF.”

“RAVMGAUUO,” TAWZ YG. USGGO. “OFT--W--”

ACVFG A XAMTF, EF AZZFZ, APAWR TFVVUWRP VEF DGWTX CUAQFR IWP AV VEF
FAGT, “WV WT JFGO ZWCCWDMUV VS HFPWR.”

EF ZWZ RSV HFPWR, HMV, WR EWT WRZFDWTWSR, YFV EFG PUARDF. VEF OSMRP
CSGFEFAZ UWCVFZ WVTFUC WRVS VEAV TWRPMUAG FQXGFTTWSR--HMV WV IAT XGFVVO
ARZ DEAGADVFGWTVWD, HFTWZFT HFWRP TWRPMUAG--ARZ TEF GAWTFZ EFG EARZ,
AT WC IWVE AR WRJSUMRVAGO ADVWSR TEF DAMPEV AV, SG TVAOFZ TSYF XATTWRP
TEAZSI.

“AGF OSM NMWVF A TVGARPFG VS YF, TWG?”

“AY W RSV?” YG. USGGO SXFRFZ EWT EARZT, ARZ FQVFRZFZ VEFY SMVIAGZT IWVE
AR AGPMYFRVAVWJF TYWUF.

HFVIFFR VEF FOFHGSIT ARZ LMTV SJFG VEF UWVVUF CFYWRWRF RSTF, VEF UWRF SC
IEWDE IAT AT ZFUWDAVF ARZ CWRF AT WV IAT XSTTWHUF VS HF, VEF FQXGFTTWSR
ZFFXFRFZ WVTFUC AT TEF VSSK EFG TFAV VESMPEVCMUUO WR VEF DEAWG HO IEWDE
TEF EAZ EWVEFGVS GFYAWRFZ TVARZWRP. EF IAVDEFZ EFG AT TEF YMTFZ, ARZ VEF
YSYFRV TEF GAWTFZ EFG FOFT APAWR, IFRV SR:

“WR OSMG AZSXVFZ DSMRVGO, W XGFTMYF, W DARRSV ZS HFVVFG VEAR AZZGFTT OSM
AT A OSMRP FRPUWTE UAZO, YWTT YARFVVF?”

“WC OSM XUFATF, TWG.”

“YWTT YARFVVF, W AY A YAR SC HMTWRFTT. W EAJF A HMTWRFTT DEAGPF VS
ADNMWV YOTFUC SC. WR OSMG GFDFXVWSR SC WV, ZSR'V EFFZ YF ARO YSGF VEAR
WC W IAT A TXFAKWRP YADEWRF--VGMUO, W AY RSV YMDE FUTF. W IWUU, IWVE
OSMG UFAJF, GFUAVF VS OSM, YWTT, VEF TVSGO SC SRF SC SMG DMTVSYFGT.”

“TVSGO!”

EF TFFYFZ IWUCMUUO VS YWTVAKF VEF ISGZ TEF EAZ GFXFAVFZ, IEFR EF AZZFZ,
WR A EMGGO, “OFT, DMTVSYFGT; WR VEF HARKWRP HMTWRFTT IF MTMAUUO DAUU
SMG DSRRFDVWSR SMG DMTVSYFGT. EF IAT A CGFRDE PFRVUFYAR; A TDWFRVWCWD
PFRVUFYAR; A YAR SC PGFAV ADNMWGFYFRVT--A ZSDVSG.”

“RSV SC HFAMJAWT?”

“IEO, OFT, SC HFAMJAWT. UWKF YSRTWFMG YARFVVF, OSMG CAVEFG, VEF
PFRVUFYAR IAT SC HFAMJAWT. UWKF YSRTWFMG YARFVVF, OSMG CAVEFG, VEF
PFRVUFYAR IAT SC GFXMVF WR XAGWT. W EAZ VEF ESRSMG SC KRSIWRP EWY VEFGF.
SMG GFUAVWSRT IFGF HMTWRFTT GFUAVWSRT, HMV DSRCWZFRVWAU. W IAT AV VEAV
VWYF WR SMG CGFRDE ESMTF, ARZ EAZ HFFR--SE! VIFRVO OFAGT.”

“AV VEAV VWYF--W YAO ATK, AV IEAV VWYF, TWG?”

“W TXFAK, YWTT, SC VIFRVO OFAGT APS. EF YAGGWFZ--AR FRPUWTE UAZO--ARZ
W IAT SRF SC VEF VGMTVFFT. EWT ACCAWGT, UWKF VEF ACCAWGT SC YARO SVEFG
CGFRDE PFRVUFYFR ARZ CGFRDE CAYWUWFT, IFGF FRVWGFUO WR VFUUTSR'T EARZT.
WR A TWYWUAG IAO W AY, SG W EAJF HFFR, VGMTVFF SC SRF KWRZ SG SVEFG CSG
TDSGFT SC SMG DMTVSYFGT. VEFTF AGF YFGF HMTWRFTT GFUAVWSRT, YWTT;
VEFGF WT RS CGWFRZTEWX WR VEFY, RS XAGVWDMUAG WRVFGFTV, RSVEWRP UWKF
TFRVWYFRV. W EAJF XATTFZ CGSY SRF VS ARSVEFG, WR VEF DSMGTF SC YO
HMTWRFTT UWCF, LMTV AT W XATT CGSY SRF SC SMG DMTVSYFGT VS ARSVEFG WR
VEF DSMGTF SC YO HMTWRFTT ZAO; WR TESGV, W EAJF RS CFFUWRPT; W AY A YFGF
YADEWRF. VS PS SR--”

“HMV VEWT WT YO CAVEFG'T TVSGO, TWG; ARZ W HFPWR VS VEWRK”--VEF
DMGWSMTUO GSMPEFRFZ CSGFEFAZ IAT JFGO WRVFRV MXSR EWY--“VEAV IEFR W IAT
UFCV AR SGXEAR VEGSMPE YO YSVEFG'T TMGJWJWRP YO CAVEFG SRUO VIS OFAGT,
WV IAT OSM IES HGSMPEV YF VS FRPUARZ. W AY AUYSTV TMGF WV IAT OSM.”

YG. USGGO VSSK VEF EFTWVAVWRP UWVVUF EARZ VEAV DSRCWZWRPUO AZJARDFZ
VS VAKF EWT, ARZ EF XMV WV IWVE TSYF DFGFYSRO VS EWT UWXT. EF VEFR
DSRZMDVFZ VEF OSMRP UAZO TVGAWPEVIAO VS EFG DEAWG APAWR, ARZ, ESUZWRP
VEF DEAWG-HADK IWVE EWT UFCV EARZ, ARZ MTWRP EWT GWPEV HO VMGRT VS GMH
EWT DEWR, XMUU EWT IWP AV VEF FAGT, SG XSWRV IEAV EF TAWZ, TVSSZ USSKWRP
ZSIR WRVS EFG CADF IEWUF TEF TAV USSKWRP MX WRVS EWT.

“YWTT YARFVVF, WV _IAT_ W. ARZ OSM IWUU TFF ESI VGMUO W TXSKF SC YOTFUC
LMTV RSI, WR TAOWRP W EAZ RS CFFUWRPT, ARZ VEAV AUU VEF GFUAVWSRT W ESUZ
IWVE YO CFUUSI-DGFAVMGFT AGF YFGF HMTWRFTT GFUAVWSRT, IEFR OSM GFCUFDV
VEAV W EAJF RFJFG TFFR OSM TWRDF. RS; OSM EAJF HFFR VEF IAGZ SC
VFUUTSR'T ESMTF TWRDF, ARZ W EAJF HFFR HMTO IWVE VEF SVEFG HMTWRFTT SC
VFUUTSR'T ESMTF TWRDF. CFFUWRPT! W EAJF RS VWYF CSG VEFY, RS DEARDF
SC VEFY. W XATT YO IESUF UWCF, YWTT, WR VMGRWRP AR WYYFRTF XFDMRWAGO
YARPUF.”

ACVFG VEWT SZZ ZFTDGWXVWSR SC EWT ZAWUO GSMVWRF SC FYXUSOYFRV, YG. USGGO
CUAVVFRFZ EWT CUAQFR IWP MXSR EWT EFAZ IWVE HSVE EARZT (IEWDE IAT YSTV
MRRFDFTTAGO, CSG RSVEWRP DSMUZ HF CUAVVFG VEAR WVT TEWRWRP TMGCADF IAT
HFCSGF), ARZ GFTMYFZ EWT CSGYFG AVVWVMZF.

“TS CAG, YWTT (AT OSM EAJF GFYAGKFZ), VEWT WT VEF TVSGO SC OSMG
GFPGFVVFZ CAVEFG. RSI DSYFT VEF ZWCCFGFRDF. WC OSMG CAVEFG EAZ RSV ZWFZ
IEFR EF ZWZ--ZSR'V HF CGWPEVFRFZ! ESI OSM TVAGV!”

TEF ZWZ, WRZFFZ, TVAGV. ARZ TEF DAMPEV EWT IGWTV IWVE HSVE EFG EARZT.

“XGAO,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, WR A TSSVEWRP VSRF, HGWRPWRP EWT UFCV EARZ CGSY
VEF HADK SC VEF DEAWG VS UAO WV SR VEF TMXXUWDAVSGO CWRPFGT VEAV DUATXFZ
EWY WR TS JWSUFRV A VGFYHUF: “XGAO DSRVGSU OSMG APWVAVWSR--A YAVVFG SC
HMTWRFTT. AT W IAT TAOWRP--”

EFG USSK TS ZWTDSYXSTFZ EWY VEAV EF TVSXXFZ, IARZFGFZ, ARZ HFPAR ARFI:

“AT W IAT TAOWRP; WC YSRTWFMG YARFVVF EAZ RSV ZWFZ; WC EF EAZ TMZZFRUO
ARZ TWUFRVUO ZWTAXXFAGFZ; WC EF EAZ HFFR TXWGWVFZ AIAO; WC WV EAZ RSV
HFFR ZWCCWDMUV VS PMFTT VS IEAV ZGFAZCMU XUADF, VESMPE RS AGV DSMUZ
VGADF EWY; WC EF EAZ AR FRFYO WR TSYF DSYXAVGWSV IES DSMUZ FQFGDWTF A
XGWJWUFPF VEAV W WR YO SIR VWYF EAJF KRSIR VEF HSUZFTV XFSXUF ACGAWZ
VS TXFAK SC WR A IEWTXFG, ADGSTT VEF IAVFG VEFGF; CSG WRTVARDF, VEF
XGWJWUFPF SC CWUUWRP MX HUARK CSGYT CSG VEF DSRTWPRYFRV SC ARO SRF
VS VEF SHUWJWSR SC A XGWTSR CSG ARO UFRPVE SC VWYF; WC EWT IWCF EAZ
WYXUSGFZ VEF KWRP, VEF NMFFR, VEF DSMGV, VEF DUFGPO, CSG ARO VWZWRPT SC
EWY, ARZ AUU NMWVF WR JAWR;--VEFR VEF EWTVSGO SC OSMG CAVEFG ISMUZ EAJF
HFFR VEF EWTVSGO SC VEWT MRCSGVMRAVF PFRVUFYAR, VEF ZSDVSG SC HFAMJAWT.”

“W FRVGFAV OSM VS VFUU YF YSGF, TWG.”

“W IWUU. W AY PSWRP VS. OSM DAR HFAG WV?”

“W DAR HFAG AROVEWRP HMV VEF MRDFGVAWRVO OSM UFAJF YF WR AV VEWT
YSYFRV.”

“OSM TXFAK DSUUFDVFZUO, ARZ OSM--_AGF_ DSUUFDVFZ. VEAV'T PSSZ!” (VESMPE
EWT YARRFG IAT UFTT TAVWTCWFZ VEAR EWT ISGZT.) “A YAVVFG SC HMTWRFTT.
GFPAGZ WV AT A YAVVFG SC HMTWRFTT--HMTWRFTT VEAV YMTV HF ZSRF. RSI
WC VEWT ZSDVSG'T IWCF, VESMPE A UAZO SC PGFAV DSMGAPF ARZ TXWGWV,
EAZ TMCCFGFZ TS WRVFRTFUO CGSY VEWT DAMTF HFCSGF EFG UWVVUF DEWUZ IAT
HSGR--”

“VEF UWVVUF DEWUZ IAT A ZAMPEVFG, TWG.”

“A ZAMPEVFG. A-A-YAVVFG SC HMTWRFTT--ZSR'V HF ZWTVGFTTFZ. YWTT, WC VEF
XSSG UAZO EAZ TMCCFGFZ TS WRVFRTFUO HFCSGF EFG UWVVUF DEWUZ IAT HSGR,
VEAV TEF DAYF VS VEF ZFVFGYWRAVWSR SC TXAGWRP VEF XSSG DEWUZ VEF
WREFGWVARDF SC ARO XAGV SC VEF APSRO TEF EAZ KRSIR VEF XAWRT SC, HO
GFAGWRP EFG WR VEF HFUWFC VEAV EFG CAVEFG IAT ZFAZ--RS, ZSR'V KRFFU! WR
EFAJFR'T RAYF IEO TESMUZ OSM KRFFU VS YF!”

“CSG VEF VGMVE. S ZFAG, PSSZ, DSYXATTWSRAVF TWG, CSG VEF VGMVE!”

“A--A YAVVFG SC HMTWRFTT. OSM DSRCMTF YF, ARZ ESI DAR W VGARTADV
HMTWRFTT WC W AY DSRCMTFZ? UFV MT HF DUFAG-EFAZFZ. WC OSM DSMUZ KWRZUO
YFRVWSR RSI, CSG WRTVARDF, IEAV RWRF VWYFT RWRFXFRDF AGF, SG ESI YARO
TEWUUWRPT WR VIFRVO PMWRFAT, WV ISMUZ HF TS FRDSMGAPWRP. W TESMUZ HF TS
YMDE YSGF AV YO FATF AHSMV OSMG TVAVF SC YWRZ.”

IWVESMV ZWGFDVUO ARTIFGWRP VS VEWT AXXFAU, TEF TAV TS TVWUU IEFR EF EAZ
JFGO PFRVUO GAWTFZ EFG, ARZ VEF EARZT VEAV EAZ RSV DFATFZ VS DUATX
EWT IGWTVT IFGF TS YMDE YSGF TVFAZO VEAR VEFO EAZ HFFR, VEAV TEF
DSYYMRWDAVFZ TSYF GFATTMGARDF VS YG. LAGJWT USGGO.

“VEAV'T GWPEV, VEAV'T GWPEV. DSMGAPF! HMTWRFTT! OSM EAJF HMTWRFTT HFCSGF
OSM; MTFCMU HMTWRFTT. YWTT YARFVVF, OSMG YSVEFG VSSK VEWT DSMGTF IWVE
OSM. ARZ IEFR TEF ZWFZ--W HFUWFJF HGSKFR-EFAGVFZ--EAJWRP RFJFG TUADKFRFZ
EFG MRAJAWUWRP TFAGDE CSG OSMG CAVEFG, TEF UFCV OSM, AV VIS OFAGT SUZ,
VS PGSI VS HF HUSSYWRP, HFAMVWCMU, ARZ EAXXO, IWVESMV VEF ZAGK DUSMZ
MXSR OSM SC UWJWRP WR MRDFGVAWRVO IEFVEFG OSMG CAVEFG TSSR ISGF EWT
EFAGV SMV WR XGWTSR, SG IATVFZ VEFGF VEGSMPE YARO UWRPFGWRP OFAGT.”

AT EF TAWZ VEF ISGZT EF USSKFZ ZSIR, IWVE AR AZYWGWRP XWVO, SR VEF
CUSIWRP PSUZFR EAWG; AT WC EF XWDVMGFZ VS EWYTFUC VEAV WV YWPEV EAJF
HFFR AUGFAZO VWRPFZ IWVE PGFO.

“OSM KRSI VEAV OSMG XAGFRVT EAZ RS PGFAV XSTTFTTWSR, ARZ VEAV IEAV
VEFO EAZ IAT TFDMGFZ VS OSMG YSVEFG ARZ VS OSM. VEFGF EAT HFFR RS RFI
ZWTDSJFGO, SC YSRFO, SG SC ARO SVEFG XGSXFGVO; HMV--”

EF CFUV EWT IGWTV EFUZ DUSTFG, ARZ EF TVSXXFZ. VEF FQXGFTTWSR WR VEF
CSGFEFAZ, IEWDE EAZ TS XAGVWDMUAGUO AVVGADVFZ EWT RSVWDF, ARZ IEWDE IAT
RSI WYYSJAHUF, EAZ ZFFXFRFZ WRVS SRF SC XAWR ARZ ESGGSG.

“HMV EF EAT HFFR--HFFR CSMRZ. EF WT AUWJF. PGFAVUO DEARPFZ, WV WT VSS
XGSHAHUF; AUYSTV A IGFDK, WV WT XSTTWHUF; VESMPE IF IWUU ESXF VEF HFTV.
TVWUU, AUWJF. OSMG CAVEFG EAT HFFR VAKFR VS VEF ESMTF SC AR SUZ TFGJARV
WR XAGWT, ARZ IF AGF PSWRP VEFGF: W, VS WZFRVWCO EWY WC W DAR: OSM, VS
GFTVSGF EWY VS UWCF, USJF, ZMVO, GFTV, DSYCSGV.”

A TEWJFG GAR VEGSMPE EFG CGAYF, ARZ CGSY WV VEGSMPE EWT. TEF TAWZ, WR A
USI, ZWTVWRDV, AIF-TVGWDKFR JSWDF, AT WC TEF IFGF TAOWRP WV WR A ZGFAY,

“W AY PSWRP VS TFF EWT PESTV! WV IWUU HF EWT PESTV--RSV EWY!”

YG. USGGO NMWFVUO DEACFZ VEF EARZT VEAV EFUZ EWT AGY. “VEFGF, VEFGF,
VEFGF! TFF RSI, TFF RSI! VEF HFTV ARZ VEF ISGTV AGF KRSIR VS OSM, RSI.
OSM AGF IFUU SR OSMG IAO VS VEF XSSG IGSRPFZ PFRVUFYAR, ARZ, IWVE A CAWG
TFA JSOAPF, ARZ A CAWG UARZ LSMGRFO, OSM IWUU HF TSSR AV EWT ZFAG TWZF.”

TEF GFXFAVFZ WR VEF TAYF VSRF, TMRK VS A IEWTXFG, “W EAJF HFFR CGFF, W
EAJF HFFR EAXXO, OFV EWT PESTV EAT RFJFG EAMRVFZ YF!”

“SRUO SRF VEWRP YSGF,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, UAOWRP TVGFTT MXSR WV AT A
IESUFTSYF YFART SC FRCSGDWRP EFG AVVFRVWSR: “EF EAT HFFR CSMRZ MRZFG
ARSVEFG RAYF; EWT SIR, USRP CSGPSVVFR SG USRP DSRDFAUFZ. WV ISMUZ HF
ISGTF VEAR MTFUFTT RSI VS WRNMWGF IEWDE; ISGTF VEAR MTFUFTT VS TFFK VS
KRSI IEFVEFG EF EAT HFFR CSG OFAGT SJFGUSSKFZ, SG AUIAOT ZFTWPRFZUO
EFUZ XGWTSRFG. WV ISMUZ HF ISGTF VEAR MTFUFTT RSI VS YAKF ARO WRNMWGWFT,
HFDAMTF WV ISMUZ HF ZARPFGSMT. HFVVFG RSV VS YFRVWSR VEF TMHLFDV,
AROIEFGF SG WR ARO IAO, ARZ VS GFYSJF EWY--CSG A IEWUF AV AUU
FJFRVT--SMV SC CGARDF. FJFR W, TACF AT AR FRPUWTEYAR, ARZ FJFR
VFUUTSR'T, WYXSGVARV AT VEFO AGF VS CGFRDE DGFZWV, AJSWZ AUU RAYWRP SC
VEF YAVVFG. W DAGGO AHSMV YF, RSV A TDGAX SC IGWVWRP SXFRUO GFCFGGWRP
VS WV. VEWT WT A TFDGFV TFGJWDF AUVSPFVEFG. YO DGFZFRVWAUT, FRVGWFT,
ARZ YFYSGARZA, AGF AUU DSYXGFEFRZFZ WR VEF SRF UWRF, 'GFDAUUFZ VS UWCF;'
IEWDE YAO YFAR AROVEWRP. HMV IEAV WT VEF YAVVFG! TEF ZSFTR'V RSVWDF A
ISGZ! YWTT YARFVVF!”

XFGCFDVUO TVWUU ARZ TWUFRV, ARZ RSV FJFR CAUUFR HADK WR EFG DEAWG, TEF
TAV MRZFG EWT EARZ, MVVFGUO WRTFRTWHUF; IWVE EFG FOFT SXFR ARZ CWQFZ
MXSR EWY, ARZ IWVE VEAV UATV FQXGFTTWSR USSKWRP AT WC WV IFGF DAGJFZ SG
HGARZFZ WRVS EFG CSGFEFAZ. TS DUSTF IAT EFG ESUZ MXSR EWT AGY, VEAV EF
CFAGFZ VS ZFVADE EWYTFUC UFTV EF TESMUZ EMGV EFG; VEFGFCSGF EF DAUUFZ
SMV USMZUO CSG ATTWTVARDF IWVESMV YSJWRP.

A IWUZ-USSKWRP ISYAR, IESY FJFR WR EWT APWVAVWSR, YG. USGGO SHTFGJFZ VS
HF AUU SC A GFZ DSUSMG, ARZ VS EAJF GFZ EAWG, ARZ VS HF ZGFTTFZ WR TSYF
FQVGASGZWRAGO VWPEV-CWVVWRP CATEWSR, ARZ VS EAJF SR EFG EFAZ A YSTV
ISRZFGCMU HSRRFV UWKF A PGFRAZWFG ISSZFR YFATMGF, ARZ PSSZ YFATMGF VSS,
SG A PGFAV TVWUVSR DEFFTF, DAYF GMRRWRP WRVS VEF GSSY WR AZJARDF SC VEF
WRR TFGJARVT, ARZ TSSR TFVVUFZ VEF NMFTVWSR SC EWT ZFVADEYFRV CGSY VEF
XSSG OSMRP UAZO, HO UAOWRP A HGAIRO EARZ MXSR EWT DEFTV, ARZ TFRZWRP EWY
CUOWRP HADK APAWRTV VEF RFAGFTV IAUU.

(“W GFAUUO VEWRK VEWT YMTV HF A YAR!” IAT YG. USGGO'T HGFAVEUFTT
GFCUFDVWSR, TWYMUVARFSMTUO IWVE EWT DSYWRP APAWRTV VEF IAUU.)

“IEO, USSK AV OSM AUU!” HAIUFZ VEWT CWPMGF, AZZGFTTWRP VEF WRR TFGJARVT.
“IEO ZSR'V OSM PS ARZ CFVDE VEWRPT, WRTVFAZ SC TVARZWRP VEFGF TVAGWRP
AV YF? W AY RSV TS YMDE VS USSK AV, AY W? IEO ZSR'V OSM PS ARZ CFVDE
VEWRPT? W'UU UFV OSM KRSI, WC OSM ZSR'V HGWRP TYFUUWRP-TAUVT, DSUZ
IAVFG, ARZ JWRFPAG, NMWDK, W IWUU.”

VEFGF IAT AR WYYFZWAVF ZWTXFGTAU CSG VEFTF GFTVSGAVWJFT, ARZ TEF
TSCVUO UAWZ VEF XAVWFRV SR A TSCA, ARZ VFRZFZ EFG IWVE PGFAV TKWUU ARZ
PFRVUFRFTT: DAUUWRP EFG “YO XGFDWSMT!” ARZ “YO HWGZ!” ARZ TXGFAZWRP EFG
PSUZFR EAWG ATWZF SJFG EFG TESMUZFGT IWVE PGFAV XGWZF ARZ DAGF.

“ARZ OSM WR HGSIR!” TEF TAWZ, WRZWPRARVUO VMGRWRP VS YG. USGGO;
“DSMUZR'V OSM VFUU EFG IEAV OSM EAZ VS VFUU EFG, IWVESMV CGWPEVFRWRP EFG
VS ZFAVE? USSK AV EFG, IWVE EFG XGFVVO XAUF CADF ARZ EFG DSUZ EARZT. ZS
OSM DAUU _VEAV_ HFWRP A HARKFG?”

YG. USGGO IAT TS FQDFFZWRPUO ZWTDSRDFGVFZ HO A NMFTVWSR TS EAGZ VS
ARTIFG, VEAV EF DSMUZ SRUO USSK SR, AV A ZWTVARDF, IWVE YMDE CFFHUFG
TOYXAVEO ARZ EMYWUWVO, IEWUF VEF TVGSRP ISYAR, EAJWRP HARWTEFZ VEF WRR
TFGJARVT MRZFG VEF YOTVFGWSMT XFRAUVO SC “UFVVWRP VEFY KRSI” TSYFVEWRP
RSV YFRVWSRFZ WC VEFO TVAOFZ VEFGF, TVAGWRP, GFDSJFGFZ EFG DEAGPF HO A
GFPMUAG TFGWFT SC PGAZAVWSRT, ARZ DSAQFZ EFG VS UAO EFG ZGSSXWRP EFAZ
MXSR EFG TESMUZFG.

“W ESXF TEF IWUU ZS IFUU RSI,” TAWZ YG. USGGO.

“RS VEARKT VS OSM WR HGSIR, WC TEF ZSFT. YO ZAGUWRP XGFVVO!”

“W ESXF,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, ACVFG ARSVEFG XAMTF SC CFFHUF TOYXAVEO ARZ
EMYWUWVO, “VEAV OSM ADDSYXARO YWTT YARFVVF VS CGARDF?”

“A UWKFUO VEWRP, VSS!” GFXUWFZ VEF TVGSRP ISYAR. “WC WV IAT FJFG
WRVFRZFZ VEAV W TESMUZ PS ADGSTT TAUV IAVFG, ZS OSM TMXXSTF XGSJWZFRDF
ISMUZ EAJF DATV YO USV WR AR WTUARZ?”

VEWT HFWRP ARSVEFG NMFTVWSR EAGZ VS ARTIFG, YG. LAGJWT USGGO IWVEZGFI VS
DSRTWZFG WV.




J. VEF IWRF-TESX


A UAGPF DATK SC IWRF EAZ HFFR ZGSXXFZ ARZ HGSKFR, WR VEF TVGFFV. VEF
ADDWZFRV EAZ EAXXFRFZ WR PFVVWRP WV SMV SC A DAGV; VEF DATK EAZ VMYHUFZ
SMV IWVE A GMR, VEF ESSXT EAZ HMGTV, ARZ WV UAO SR VEF TVSRFT LMTV
SMVTWZF VEF ZSSG SC VEF IWRF-TESX, TEAVVFGFZ UWKF A IAURMV-TEFUU.

AUU VEF XFSXUF IWVEWR GFADE EAZ TMTXFRZFZ VEFWG HMTWRFTT, SG VEFWG
WZUFRFTT, VS GMR VS VEF TXSV ARZ ZGWRK VEF IWRF. VEF GSMPE, WGGFPMUAG
TVSRFT SC VEF TVGFFV, XSWRVWRP FJFGO IAO, ARZ ZFTWPRFZ, SRF YWPEV EAJF
VESMPEV, FQXGFTTUO VS UAYF AUU UWJWRP DGFAVMGFT VEAV AXXGSADEFZ VEFY,
EAZ ZAYYFZ WV WRVS UWVVUF XSSUT; VEFTF IFGF TMGGSMRZFZ, FADE HO WVT SIR
LSTVUWRP PGSMX SG DGSIZ, ADDSGZWRP VS WVT TWBF. TSYF YFR KRFFUFZ ZSIR,
YAZF TDSSXT SC VEFWG VIS EARZT LSWRFZ, ARZ TWXXFZ, SG VGWFZ VS EFUX
ISYFR, IES HFRV SJFG VEFWG TESMUZFGT, VS TWX, HFCSGF VEF IWRF EAZ AUU
GMR SMV HFVIFFR VEFWG CWRPFGT. SVEFGT, YFR ARZ ISYFR, ZWXXFZ WR
VEF XMZZUFT IWVE UWVVUF YMPT SC YMVWUAVFZ FAGVEFRIAGF, SG FJFR IWVE
EARZKFGDEWFCT CGSY ISYFR'T EFAZT, IEWDE IFGF TNMFFBFZ ZGO WRVS WRCARVT'
YSMVET; SVEFGT YAZF TYAUU YMZ-FYHARKYFRVT, VS TVFY VEF IWRF AT WV GAR;
SVEFGT, ZWGFDVFZ HO USSKFGT-SR MX AV EWPE IWRZSIT, ZAGVFZ EFGF ARZ
VEFGF, VS DMV SCC UWVVUF TVGFAYT SC IWRF VEAV TVAGVFZ AIAO WR RFI
ZWGFDVWSRT; SVEFGT ZFJSVFZ VEFYTFUJFT VS VEF TSZZFR ARZ UFF-ZOFZ
XWFDFT SC VEF DATK, UWDKWRP, ARZ FJFR DEAYXWRP VEF YSWTVFG IWRF-GSVVFZ
CGAPYFRVT IWVE FAPFG GFUWTE. VEFGF IAT RS ZGAWRAPF VS DAGGO SCC VEF
IWRF, ARZ RSV SRUO ZWZ WV AUU PFV VAKFR MX, HMV TS YMDE YMZ PSV VAKFR MX
AUSRP IWVE WV, VEAV VEFGF YWPEV EAJF HFFR A TDAJFRPFG WR VEF TVGFFV,
WC AROHSZO ADNMAWRVFZ IWVE WV DSMUZ EAJF HFUWFJFZ WR TMDE A YWGADMUSMT
XGFTFRDF.

A TEGWUU TSMRZ SC UAMPEVFG ARZ SC AYMTFZ JSWDFT--JSWDFT SC YFR, ISYFR,
ARZ DEWUZGFR--GFTSMRZFZ WR VEF TVGFFV IEWUF VEWT IWRF PAYF UATVFZ. VEFGF
IAT UWVVUF GSMPERFTT WR VEF TXSGV, ARZ YMDE XUAOCMURFTT. VEFGF IAT A
TXFDWAU DSYXARWSRTEWX WR WV, AR SHTFGJAHUF WRDUWRAVWSR SR VEF XAGV
SC FJFGO SRF VS LSWR TSYF SVEFG SRF, IEWDE UFZ, FTXFDWAUUO AYSRP VEF
UMDKWFG SG UWPEVFG-EFAGVFZ, VS CGSUWDTSYF FYHGADFT, ZGWRKWRP SC EFAUVET,
TEAKWRP SC EARZT, ARZ FJFR LSWRWRP SC EARZT ARZ ZARDWRP, A ZSBFR
VSPFVEFG. IEFR VEF IWRF IAT PSRF, ARZ VEF XUADFT IEFGF WV EAZ HFFR
YSTV AHMRZARV IFGF GAKFZ WRVS A PGWZWGSR-XAVVFGR HO CWRPFGT, VEFTF
ZFYSRTVGAVWSRT DFATFZ, AT TMZZFRUO AT VEFO EAZ HGSKFR SMV. VEF YAR IES
EAZ UFCV EWT TAI TVWDKWRP WR VEF CWGFISSZ EF IAT DMVVWRP, TFV WV WR
YSVWSR APAWR; VEF ISYFR IES EAZ UFCV SR A ZSSG-TVFX VEF UWVVUF XSV SC
ESV ATEFT, AV IEWDE TEF EAZ HFFR VGOWRP VS TSCVFR VEF XAWR WR EFG SIR
TVAGJFZ CWRPFGT ARZ VSFT, SG WR VESTF SC EFG DEWUZ, GFVMGRFZ VS WV; YFR
IWVE HAGF AGYT, YAVVFZ USDKT, ARZ DAZAJFGSMT CADFT, IES EAZ FYFGPFZ WRVS
VEF IWRVFG UWPEV CGSY DFUUAGT, YSJFZ AIAO, VS ZFTDFRZ APAWR; ARZ A PUSSY
PAVEFGFZ SR VEF TDFRF VEAV AXXFAGFZ YSGF RAVMGAU VS WV VEAR TMRTEWRF.

VEF IWRF IAT GFZ IWRF, ARZ EAZ TVAWRFZ VEF PGSMRZ SC VEF RAGGSI TVGFFV
WR VEF TMHMGH SC TAWRV ARVSWRF, WR XAGWT, IEFGF WV IAT TXWUUFZ. WV EAZ
TVAWRFZ YARO EARZT, VSS, ARZ YARO CADFT, ARZ YARO RAKFZ CFFV, ARZ YARO
ISSZFR TESFT. VEF EARZT SC VEF YAR IES TAIFZ VEF ISSZ, UFCV GFZ YAGKT
SR VEF HWUUFVT; ARZ VEF CSGFEFAZ SC VEF ISYAR IES RMGTFZ EFG HAHO, IAT
TVAWRFZ IWVE VEF TVAWR SC VEF SUZ GAP TEF ISMRZ AHSMV EFG EFAZ APAWR.
VESTF IES EAZ HFFR PGFFZO IWVE VEF TVAJFT SC VEF DATK, EAZ ADNMWGFZ A
VWPFGWTE TYFAG AHSMV VEF YSMVE; ARZ SRF VAUU LSKFG TS HFTYWGDEFZ, EWT
EFAZ YSGF SMV SC A USRP TNMAUWZ HAP SC A RWPEVDAX VEAR WR WV, TDGAIUFZ
MXSR A IAUU IWVE EWT CWRPFG ZWXXFZ WR YMZZO IWRF-UFFT--HUSSZ.

VEF VWYF IAT VS DSYF, IEFR VEAV IWRF VSS ISMUZ HF TXWUUFZ SR VEF
TVGFFV-TVSRFT, ARZ IEFR VEF TVAWR SC WV ISMUZ HF GFZ MXSR YARO VEFGF.

ARZ RSI VEAV VEF DUSMZ TFVVUFZ SR TAWRV ARVSWRF, IEWDE A YSYFRVAGO
PUFAY EAZ ZGWJFR CGSY EWT TADGFZ DSMRVFRARDF, VEF ZAGKRFTT SC WV IAT
EFAJO--DSUZ, ZWGV, TWDKRFTT, WPRSGARDF, ARZ IARV, IFGF VEF USGZT WR
IAWVWRP SR VEF TAWRVUO XGFTFRDF--RSHUFT SC PGFAV XSIFG AUU SC VEFY;
HMV, YSTV FTXFDWAUUO VEF UATV. TAYXUFT SC A XFSXUF VEAV EAZ MRZFGPSRF A
VFGGWHUF PGWRZWRP ARZ GFPGWRZWRP WR VEF YWUU, ARZ DFGVAWRUO RSV WR VEF
CAHMUSMT YWUU IEWDE PGSMRZ SUZ XFSXUF OSMRP, TEWJFGFZ AV FJFGO DSGRFG,
XATTFZ WR ARZ SMV AV FJFGO ZSSGIAO, USSKFZ CGSY FJFGO IWRZSI, CUMVVFGFZ
WR FJFGO JFTVWPF SC A PAGYFRV VEAV VEF IWRZ TESSK. VEF YWUU IEWDE
EAZ ISGKFZ VEFY ZSIR, IAT VEF YWUU VEAV PGWRZT OSMRP XFSXUF SUZ; VEF
DEWUZGFR EAZ ARDWFRV CADFT ARZ PGAJF JSWDFT; ARZ MXSR VEFY, ARZ MXSR VEF
PGSIR CADFT, ARZ XUSMPEFZ WRVS FJFGO CMGGSI SC APF ARZ DSYWRP MX ACGFTE,
IAT VEF TWPE, EMRPFG. WV IAT XGFJAUFRV FJFGOIEFGF. EMRPFG IAT XMTEFZ SMV
SC VEF VAUU ESMTFT, WR VEF IGFVDEFZ DUSVEWRP VEAV EMRP MXSR XSUFT ARZ
UWRFT; EMRPFG IAT XAVDEFZ WRVS VEFY IWVE TVGAI ARZ GAP ARZ ISSZ ARZ
XAXFG; EMRPFG IAT GFXFAVFZ WR FJFGO CGAPYFRV SC VEF TYAUU YSZWDMY SC
CWGFISSZ VEAV VEF YAR TAIFZ SCC; EMRPFG TVAGFZ ZSIR CGSY VEF TYSKFUFTT
DEWYRFOT, ARZ TVAGVFZ MX CGSY VEF CWUVEO TVGFFV VEAV EAZ RS SCCAU,
AYSRP WVT GFCMTF, SC AROVEWRP VS FAV. EMRPFG IAT VEF WRTDGWXVWSR SR VEF
HAKFG'T TEFUJFT, IGWVVFR WR FJFGO TYAUU USAC SC EWT TDARVO TVSDK SC
HAZ HGFAZ; AV VEF TAMTAPF-TESX, WR FJFGO ZFAZ-ZSP XGFXAGAVWSR VEAV
IAT SCCFGFZ CSG TAUF. EMRPFG GAVVUFZ WVT ZGO HSRFT AYSRP VEF GSATVWRP
DEFTVRMVT WR VEF VMGRFZ DOUWRZFG; EMRPFG IAT TEGFZ WRVS AVSYWDT WR FJFGO
CAGVEWRP XSGGWRPFG SC EMTKO DEWXT SC XSVAVS, CGWFZ IWVE TSYF GFUMDVARV
ZGSXT SC SWU.

WVT AHWZWRP XUADF IAT WR AUU VEWRPT CWVVFZ VS WV. A RAGGSI IWRZWRP
TVGFFV, CMUU SC SCCFRDF ARZ TVFRDE, IWVE SVEFG RAGGSI IWRZWRP TVGFFVT
ZWJFGPWRP, AUU XFSXUFZ HO GAPT ARZ RWPEVDAXT, ARZ AUU TYFUUWRP SC GAPT
ARZ RWPEVDAXT, ARZ AUU JWTWHUF VEWRPT IWVE A HGSSZWRP USSK MXSR VEFY
VEAV USSKFZ WUU. WR VEF EMRVFZ AWG SC VEF XFSXUF VEFGF IAT OFV TSYF
IWUZ-HFATV VESMPEV SC VEF XSTTWHWUWVO SC VMGRWRP AV HAO. ZFXGFTTFZ ARZ
TUWRKWRP VESMPE VEFO IFGF, FOFT SC CWGF IFGF RSV IARVWRP AYSRP VEFY; RSG
