WRCUWDVWRP. VEF VGAZF TWPRT (ARZ VEFO IFGF AUYSTV AT YARO AT VEF TESXT)
IFGF, AUU, PGWY WUUMTVGAVWSRT SC IARV. VEF HMVDEFG ARZ VEF XSGKYAR
XAWRVFZ MX, SRUO VEF UFARFTV TDGAPT SC YFAV; VEF HAKFG, VEF DSAGTFTV SC
YFAPGF USAJFT. VEF XFSXUF GMZFUO XWDVMGFZ AT ZGWRKWRP WR VEF IWRF-TESXT,
DGSAKFZ SJFG VEFWG TDARVO YFATMGFT SC VEWR IWRF ARZ HFFG, ARZ IFGF
PUSIFGWRPUO DSRCWZFRVWAU VSPFVEFG. RSVEWRP IAT GFXGFTFRVFZ WR A
CUSMGWTEWRP DSRZWVWSR, TAJF VSSUT ARZ IFAXSRT; HMV, VEF DMVUFG'T KRWJFT
