MX YFR HO VESTF GSXFT ARZ XMUUFOT, VS CUAGF MXSR VEF ZAGKRFTT SC VEFWG
DSRZWVWSR. HMV, VEF VWYF IAT RSV DSYF OFV; ARZ FJFGO IWRZ VEAV HUFI SJFG
CGARDF TESSK VEF GAPT SC VEF TDAGFDGSIT WR JAWR, CSG VEF HWGZT, CWRF SC
TSRP ARZ CFAVEFG, VSSK RS IAGRWRP.

VEF IWRF-TESX IAT A DSGRFG TESX, HFVVFG VEAR YSTV SVEFGT WR WVT
AXXFAGARDF ARZ ZFPGFF, ARZ VEF YATVFG SC VEF IWRF-TESX EAZ TVSSZ SMVTWZF
WV, WR A OFUUSI IAWTVDSAV ARZ PGFFR HGFFDEFT, USSKWRP SR AV VEF TVGMPPUF
CSG VEF USTV IWRF. “WV'T RSV YO ACCAWG,” TAWZ EF, IWVE A CWRAU TEGMP
SC VEF TESMUZFGT. “VEF XFSXUF CGSY VEF YAGKFV ZWZ WV. UFV VEFY HGWRP
ARSVEFG.”

VEFGF, EWT FOFT EAXXFRWRP VS DAVDE VEF VAUU LSKFG IGWVWRP MX EWT LSKF,
EF DAUUFZ VS EWY ADGSTT VEF IAO:

“TAO, VEFR, YO PATXAGZ, IEAV ZS OSM ZS VEFGF?”

VEF CFUUSI XSWRVFZ VS EWT LSKF IWVE WYYFRTF TWPRWCWDARDF, AT WT SCVFR
VEF IAO IWVE EWT VGWHF. WV YWTTFZ WVT YAGK, ARZ DSYXUFVFUO CAWUFZ, AT WT
SCVFR VEF IAO IWVE EWT VGWHF VSS.

“IEAV RSI? AGF OSM A TMHLFDV CSG VEF YAZ ESTXWVAU?” TAWZ VEF IWRF-TESX
KFFXFG, DGSTTWRP VEF GSAZ, ARZ SHUWVFGAVWRP VEF LFTV IWVE A EARZCMU SC
YMZ, XWDKFZ MX CSG VEF XMGXSTF, ARZ TYFAGFZ SJFG WV. “IEO ZS OSM IGWVF
WR VEF XMHUWD TVGFFVT? WT VEFGF--VFUU YF VESM--WT VEFGF RS SVEFG XUADF
VS IGWVF TMDE ISGZT WR?”

WR EWT FQXSTVMUAVWSR EF ZGSXXFZ EWT DUFARFG EARZ (XFGEAXT ADDWZFRVAUUO,
XFGEAXT RSV) MXSR VEF LSKFG'T EFAGV. VEF LSKFG GAXXFZ WV IWVE EWT
SIR, VSSK A RWYHUF TXGWRP MXIAGZ, ARZ DAYF ZSIR WR A CARVATVWD ZARDWRP
AVVWVMZF, IWVE SRF SC EWT TVAWRFZ TESFT LFGKFZ SCC EWT CSSV WRVS EWT
EARZ, ARZ EFUZ SMV. A LSKFG SC AR FQVGFYFUO, RSV VS TAO ISUCWTEUO
XGADVWDAU DEAGADVFG, EF USSKFZ, MRZFG VESTF DWGDMYTVARDFT.

“XMV WV SR, XMV WV SR,” TAWZ VEF SVEFG. “DAUU IWRF, IWRF; ARZ CWRWTE
VEFGF.” IWVE VEAV AZJWDF, EF IWXFZ EWT TSWUFZ EARZ MXSR VEF LSKFG'T
ZGFTT, TMDE AT WV IAT--NMWVF ZFUWHFGAVFUO, AT EAJWRP ZWGVWFZ VEF EARZ SR
EWT ADDSMRV; ARZ VEFR GFDGSTTFZ VEF GSAZ ARZ FRVFGFZ VEF IWRF-TESX.

VEWT IWRF-TESX KFFXFG IAT A HMUU-RFDKFZ, YAGVWAU-USSKWRP YAR SC VEWGVO,
ARZ EF TESMUZ EAJF HFFR SC A ESV VFYXFGAYFRV, CSG, AUVESMPE WV IAT A
HWVVFG ZAO, EF ISGF RS DSAV, HMV DAGGWFZ SRF TUMRP SJFG EWT TESMUZFG.
EWT TEWGV-TUFFJFT IFGF GSUUFZ MX, VSS, ARZ EWT HGSIR AGYT IFGF HAGF VS
VEF FUHSIT. RFWVEFG ZWZ EF IFAG AROVEWRP YSGF SR EWT EFAZ VEAR EWT SIR
DGWTXUO-DMGUWRP TESGV ZAGK EAWG. EF IAT A ZAGK YAR AUVSPFVEFG, IWVE PSSZ
FOFT ARZ A PSSZ HSUZ HGFAZVE HFVIFFR VEFY. PSSZ-EMYSMGFZ USSKWRP SR
VEF IESUF, HMV WYXUADAHUF-USSKWRP, VSS; FJWZFRVUO A YAR SC A TVGSRP
GFTSUMVWSR ARZ A TFV XMGXSTF; A YAR RSV ZFTWGAHUF VS HF YFV, GMTEWRP
ZSIR A RAGGSI XATT IWVE A PMUC SR FWVEFG TWZF, CSG RSVEWRP ISMUZ VMGR
VEF YAR.

YAZAYF ZFCAGPF, EWT IWCF, TAV WR VEF TESX HFEWRZ VEF DSMRVFG AT EF
DAYF WR. YAZAYF ZFCAGPF IAT A TVSMV ISYAR SC AHSMV EWT SIR APF, IWVE
A IAVDECMU FOF VEAV TFUZSY TFFYFZ VS USSK AV AROVEWRP, A UAGPF EARZ
EFAJWUO GWRPFZ, A TVFAZO CADF, TVGSRP CFAVMGFT, ARZ PGFAV DSYXSTMGF SC
YARRFG. VEFGF IAT A DEAGADVFG AHSMV YAZAYF ZFCAGPF, CGSY IEWDE SRF YWPEV
EAJF XGFZWDAVFZ VEAV TEF ZWZ RSV SCVFR YAKF YWTVAKFT APAWRTV EFGTFUC
WR ARO SC VEF GFDKSRWRPT SJFG IEWDE TEF XGFTWZFZ. YAZAYF ZFCAGPF HFWRP
TFRTWVWJF VS DSUZ, IAT IGAXXFZ WR CMG, ARZ EAZ A NMARVWVO SC HGWPEV
TEAIU VIWRFZ AHSMV EFG EFAZ, VESMPE RSV VS VEF DSRDFAUYFRV SC EFG UAGPF
FAGGWRPT. EFG KRWVVWRP IAT HFCSGF EFG, HMV TEF EAZ UAWZ WV ZSIR VS XWDK
EFG VFFVE IWVE A VSSVEXWDK. VEMT FRPAPFZ, IWVE EFG GWPEV FUHSI TMXXSGVFZ
HO EFG UFCV EARZ, YAZAYF ZFCAGPF TAWZ RSVEWRP IEFR EFG USGZ DAYF WR, HMV
DSMPEFZ LMTV SRF PGAWR SC DSMPE. VEWT, WR DSYHWRAVWSR IWVE VEF UWCVWRP
SC EFG ZAGKUO ZFCWRFZ FOFHGSIT SJFG EFG VSSVEXWDK HO VEF HGFAZVE SC A
UWRF, TMPPFTVFZ VS EFG EMTHARZ VEAV EF ISMUZ ZS IFUU VS USSK GSMRZ VEF
TESX AYSRP VEF DMTVSYFGT, CSG ARO RFI DMTVSYFG IES EAZ ZGSXXFZ WR IEWUF
EF TVFXXFZ SJFG VEF IAO.

VEF IWRF-TESX KFFXFG ADDSGZWRPUO GSUUFZ EWT FOFT AHSMV, MRVWU VEFO
GFTVFZ MXSR AR FUZFGUO PFRVUFYAR ARZ A OSMRP UAZO, IES IFGF TFAVFZ WR
A DSGRFG. SVEFG DSYXARO IFGF VEFGF: VIS XUAOWRP DAGZT, VIS XUAOWRP
ZSYWRSFT, VEGFF TVARZWRP HO VEF DSMRVFG UFRPVEFRWRP SMV A TESGV TMXXUO
SC IWRF. AT EF XATTFZ HFEWRZ VEF DSMRVFG, EF VSSK RSVWDF VEAV VEF
FUZFGUO PFRVUFYAR TAWZ WR A USSK VS VEF OSMRP UAZO, “VEWT WT SMG YAR.”

“IEAV VEF ZFJWU ZS _OSM_ ZS WR VEAV PAUUFO VEFGF?” TAWZ YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF
VS EWYTFUC; “W ZSR'V KRSI OSM.”

HMV, EF CFWPRFZ RSV VS RSVWDF VEF VIS TVGARPFGT, ARZ CFUU WRVS ZWTDSMGTF
IWVE VEF VGWMYJWGAVF SC DMTVSYFGT IES IFGF ZGWRKWRP AV VEF DSMRVFG.

“ESI PSFT WV, LADNMFT?” TAWZ SRF SC VEFTF VEGFF VS YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF. “WT
AUU VEF TXWUV IWRF TIAUUSIFZ?”

“FJFGO ZGSX, LADNMFT,” ARTIFGFZ YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF.

IEFR VEWT WRVFGDEARPF SC DEGWTVWAR RAYF IAT FCCFDVFZ, YAZAYF ZFCAGPF,
XWDKWRP EFG VFFVE IWVE EFG VSSVEXWDK, DSMPEFZ ARSVEFG PGAWR SC DSMPE,
ARZ GAWTFZ EFG FOFHGSIT HO VEF HGFAZVE SC ARSVEFG UWRF.

“WV WT RSV SCVFR,” TAWZ VEF TFDSRZ SC VEF VEGFF, AZZGFTTWRP YSRTWFMG
ZFCAGPF, “VEAV YARO SC VEFTF YWTFGAHUF HFATVT KRSI VEF VATVF SC IWRF, SG
SC AROVEWRP HMV HUADK HGFAZ ARZ ZFAVE. WT WV RSV TS, LADNMFT?”

“WV WT TS, LADNMFT,” YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF GFVMGRFZ.

AV VEWT TFDSRZ WRVFGDEARPF SC VEF DEGWTVWAR RAYF, YAZAYF ZFCAGPF, TVWUU
MTWRP EFG VSSVEXWDK IWVE XGSCSMRZ DSYXSTMGF, DSMPEFZ ARSVEFG PGAWR SC
DSMPE, ARZ GAWTFZ EFG FOFHGSIT HO VEF HGFAZVE SC ARSVEFG UWRF.

VEF UATV SC VEF VEGFF RSI TAWZ EWT TAO, AT EF XMV ZSIR EWT FYXVO
ZGWRKWRP JFTTFU ARZ TYADKFZ EWT UWXT.

“AE! TS YMDE VEF ISGTF! A HWVVFG VATVF WV WT VEAV TMDE XSSG DAVVUF
AUIAOT EAJF WR VEFWG YSMVET, ARZ EAGZ UWJFT VEFO UWJF, LADNMFT. AY W
GWPEV, LADNMFT?”

“OSM AGF GWPEV, LADNMFT,” IAT VEF GFTXSRTF SC YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF.

VEWT VEWGZ WRVFGDEARPF SC VEF DEGWTVWAR RAYF IAT DSYXUFVFZ AV VEF YSYFRV
IEFR YAZAYF ZFCAGPF XMV EFG VSSVEXWDK HO, KFXV EFG FOFHGSIT MX, ARZ
TUWPEVUO GMTVUFZ WR EFG TFAV.

“ESUZ VEFR! VGMF!” YMVVFGFZ EFG EMTHARZ. “PFRVUFYFR--YO IWCF!”

VEF VEGFF DMTVSYFGT XMUUFZ SCC VEFWG EAVT VS YAZAYF ZFCAGPF, IWVE VEGFF
CUSMGWTEFT. TEF ADKRSIUFZPFZ VEFWG ESYAPF HO HFRZWRP EFG EFAZ, ARZ
PWJWRP VEFY A NMWDK USSK. VEFR TEF PUARDFZ WR A DATMAU YARRFG GSMRZ VEF
IWRF-TESX, VSSK MX EFG KRWVVWRP IWVE PGFAV AXXAGFRV DAUYRFTT ARZ GFXSTF
SC TXWGWV, ARZ HFDAYF AHTSGHFZ WR WV.

“PFRVUFYFR,” TAWZ EFG EMTHARZ, IES EAZ KFXV EWT HGWPEV FOF SHTFGJARVUO
MXSR EFG, “PSSZ ZAO. VEF DEAYHFG, CMGRWTEFZ HADEFUSG-CATEWSR, VEAV OSM
IWTEFZ VS TFF, ARZ IFGF WRNMWGWRP CSG IEFR W TVFXXFZ SMV, WT SR VEF
CWCVE CUSSG. VEF ZSSGIAO SC VEF TVAWGDATF PWJFT SR VEF UWVVUF DSMGVOAGZ
DUSTF VS VEF UFCV EFGF,” XSWRVWRP IWVE EWT EARZ, “RFAG VS VEF IWRZSI SC
YO FTVAHUWTEYFRV. HMV, RSI VEAV W GFYFYHFG, SRF SC OSM EAT AUGFAZO HFFR
VEFGF, ARZ DAR TESI VEF IAO. PFRVUFYFR, AZWFM!”

VEFO XAWZ CSG VEFWG IWRF, ARZ UFCV VEF XUADF. VEF FOFT SC YSRTWFMG
ZFCAGPF IFGF TVMZOWRP EWT IWCF AV EFG KRWVVWRP IEFR VEF FUZFGUO
PFRVUFYAR AZJARDFZ CGSY EWT DSGRFG, ARZ HFPPFZ VEF CAJSMG SC A ISGZ.

“IWUUWRPUO, TWG,” TAWZ YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF, ARZ NMWFVUO TVFXXFZ IWVE EWY VS
VEF ZSSG.

VEFWG DSRCFGFRDF IAT JFGO TESGV, HMV JFGO ZFDWZFZ. AUYSTV AV VEF CWGTV
ISGZ, YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF TVAGVFZ ARZ HFDAYF ZFFXUO AVVFRVWJF. WV EAZ
RSV UATVFZ A YWRMVF, IEFR EF RSZZFZ ARZ IFRV SMV. VEF PFRVUFYAR VEFR
HFDKSRFZ VS VEF OSMRP UAZO, ARZ VEFO, VSS, IFRV SMV. YAZAYF ZFCAGPF
KRWVVFZ IWVE RWYHUF CWRPFGT ARZ TVFAZO FOFHGSIT, ARZ TAI RSVEWRP.

YG. LAGJWT USGGO ARZ YWTT YARFVVF, FYFGPWRP CGSY VEF IWRF-TESX VEMT,
LSWRFZ YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF WR VEF ZSSGIAO VS IEWDE EF EAZ ZWGFDVFZ EWT SIR
DSYXARO LMTV HFCSGF. WV SXFRFZ CGSY A TVWRKWRP UWVVUF HUADK DSMGVOAGZ,
ARZ IAT VEF PFRFGAU XMHUWD FRVGARDF VS A PGFAV XWUF SC ESMTFT, WREAHWVFZ
HO A PGFAV RMYHFG SC XFSXUF. WR VEF PUSSYO VWUF-XAJFZ FRVGO VS VEF
PUSSYO VWUF-XAJFZ TVAWGDATF, YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF HFRV ZSIR SR SRF KRFF
VS VEF DEWUZ SC EWT SUZ YATVFG, ARZ XMV EFG EARZ VS EWT UWXT. WV IAT
A PFRVUF ADVWSR, HMV RSV AV AUU PFRVUO ZSRF; A JFGO GFYAGKAHUF
VGARTCSGYAVWSR EAZ DSYF SJFG EWY WR A CFI TFDSRZT. EF EAZ RS PSSZ-EMYSMG
WR EWT CADF, RSG ARO SXFRRFTT SC ATXFDV UFCV, HMV EAZ HFDSYF A TFDGFV,
ARPGO, ZARPFGSMT YAR.

“WV WT JFGO EWPE; WV WT A UWVVUF ZWCCWDMUV. HFVVFG VS HFPWR TUSIUO.”
 VEMT, YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF, WR A TVFGR JSWDF, VS YG. USGGO, AT VEFO HFPAR
ATDFRZWRP VEF TVAWGT.

“WT EF AUSRF?” VEF UAVVFG IEWTXFGFZ.

“AUSRF! PSZ EFUX EWY, IES TESMUZ HF IWVE EWY!” TAWZ VEF SVEFG, WR VEF
TAYF USI JSWDF.

“WT EF AUIAOT AUSRF, VEFR?”

“OFT.”

“SC EWT SIR ZFTWGF?”

“SC EWT SIR RFDFTTWVO. AT EF IAT, IEFR W CWGTV TAI EWY ACVFG VEFO
CSMRZ YF ARZ ZFYARZFZ VS KRSI WC W ISMUZ VAKF EWY, ARZ, AV YO XFGWU HF
ZWTDGFFV--AT EF IAT VEFR, TS EF WT RSI.”

“EF WT PGFAVUO DEARPFZ?”

“DEARPFZ!”

VEF KFFXFG SC VEF IWRF-TESX TVSXXFZ VS TVGWKF VEF IAUU IWVE EWT EARZ,
ARZ YMVVFG A VGFYFRZSMT DMGTF. RS ZWGFDV ARTIFG DSMUZ EAJF HFFR EAUC TS
CSGDWHUF. YG. USGGO'T TXWGWVT PGFI EFAJWFG ARZ EFAJWFG, AT EF ARZ EWT
VIS DSYXARWSRT ATDFRZFZ EWPEFG ARZ EWPEFG.

TMDE A TVAWGDATF, IWVE WVT ADDFTTSGWFT, WR VEF SUZFG ARZ YSGF DGSIZFZ
XAGVT SC XAGWT, ISMUZ HF HAZ FRSMPE RSI; HMV, AV VEAV VWYF, WV IAT JWUF
WRZFFZ VS MRADDMTVSYFZ ARZ MREAGZFRFZ TFRTFT. FJFGO UWVVUF EAHWVAVWSR
IWVEWR VEF PGFAV CSMU RFTV SC SRF EWPE HMWUZWRP--VEAV WT VS TAO,
VEF GSSY SG GSSYT IWVEWR FJFGO ZSSG VEAV SXFRFZ SR VEF PFRFGAU
TVAWGDATF--UFCV WVT SIR EFAX SC GFCMTF SR WVT SIR UARZWRP, HFTWZFT
CUWRPWRP SVEFG GFCMTF CGSY WVT SIR IWRZSIT. VEF MRDSRVGSUUAHUF ARZ
ESXFUFTT YATT SC ZFDSYXSTWVWSR TS FRPFRZFGFZ, ISMUZ EAJF XSUUMVFZ
VEF AWG, FJFR WC XSJFGVO ARZ ZFXGWJAVWSR EAZ RSV USAZFZ WV IWVE VEFWG
WRVARPWHUF WYXMGWVWFT; VEF VIS HAZ TSMGDFT DSYHWRFZ YAZF WV AUYSTV
WRTMXXSGVAHUF. VEGSMPE TMDE AR AVYSTXEFGF, HO A TVFFX ZAGK TEACV SC ZWGV
ARZ XSWTSR, VEF IAO UAO. OWFUZWRP VS EWT SIR ZWTVMGHARDF SC YWRZ, ARZ VS
EWT OSMRP DSYXARWSR'T APWVAVWSR, IEWDE HFDAYF PGFAVFG FJFGO WRTVARV, YG.
LAGJWT USGGO VIWDF TVSXXFZ VS GFTV. FADE SC VEFTF TVSXXAPFT IAT YAZF
AV A ZSUFCMU PGAVWRP, HO IEWDE ARO UARPMWTEWRP PSSZ AWGT VEAV IFGF UFCV
MRDSGGMXVFZ, TFFYFZ VS FTDAXF, ARZ AUU TXSWUV ARZ TWDKUO JAXSMGT TFFYFZ
VS DGAIU WR. VEGSMPE VEF GMTVFZ HAGT, VATVFT, GAVEFG VEAR PUWYXTFT, IFGF
DAMPEV SC VEF LMYHUFZ RFWPEHSMGESSZ; ARZ RSVEWRP IWVEWR GARPF, RFAGFG
SG USIFG VEAR VEF TMYYWVT SC VEF VIS PGFAV VSIFGT SC RSVGF-ZAYF, EAZ ARO
XGSYWTF SR WV SC EFAUVEO UWCF SG IESUFTSYF ATXWGAVWSRT.

AV UATV, VEF VSX SC VEF TVAWGDATF IAT PAWRFZ, ARZ VEFO TVSXXFZ CSG VEF
VEWGZ VWYF. VEFGF IAT OFV AR MXXFG TVAWGDATF, SC A TVFFXFG WRDUWRAVWSR
ARZ SC DSRVGADVFZ ZWYFRTWSRT, VS HF ATDFRZFZ, HFCSGF VEF PAGGFV TVSGO
IAT GFADEFZ. VEF KFFXFG SC VEF IWRF-TESX, AUIAOT PSWRP A UWVVUF WR
AZJARDF, ARZ AUIAOT PSWRP SR VEF TWZF IEWDE YG. USGGO VSSK, AT VESMPE EF
ZGFAZFZ VS HF ATKFZ ARO NMFTVWSR HO VEF OSMRP UAZO, VMGRFZ EWYTFUC AHSMV
EFGF, ARZ, DAGFCMUUO CFFUWRP WR VEF XSDKFVT SC VEF DSAV EF DAGGWFZ SJFG
EWT TESMUZFG, VSSK SMV A KFO.

“VEF ZSSG WT USDKFZ VEFR, YO CGWFRZ?” TAWZ YG. USGGO, TMGXGWTFZ.

“AO. OFT,” IAT VEF PGWY GFXUO SC YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF.

“OSM VEWRK WV RFDFTTAGO VS KFFX VEF MRCSGVMRAVF PFRVUFYAR TS GFVWGFZ?”

“W VEWRK WV RFDFTTAGO VS VMGR VEF KFO.” YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF IEWTXFGFZ WV
DUSTFG WR EWT FAG, ARZ CGSIRFZ EFAJWUO.

“IEO?”

“IEO! HFDAMTF EF EAT UWJFZ TS USRP, USDKFZ MX, VEAV EF ISMUZ HF
CGWPEVFRFZ--GAJF--VFAG EWYTFUC VS XWFDFT--ZWF--DSYF VS W KRSI RSV IEAV
EAGY--WC EWT ZSSG IAT UFCV SXFR.”

“WT WV XSTTWHUF!” FQDUAWYFZ YG. USGGO.

“WT WV XSTTWHUF!” GFXFAVFZ ZFCAGPF, HWVVFGUO. “OFT. ARZ A HFAMVWCMU
ISGUZ IF UWJF WR, IEFR WV _WT_ XSTTWHUF, ARZ IEFR YARO SVEFG TMDE VEWRPT
AGF XSTTWHUF, ARZ RSV SRUO XSTTWHUF, HMV ZSRF--ZSRF, TFF OSM!--MRZFG
VEAV TKO VEFGF, FJFGO ZAO. USRP UWJF VEF ZFJWU. UFV MT PS SR.”

VEWT ZWAUSPMF EAZ HFFR EFUZ WR TS JFGO USI A IEWTXFG, VEAV RSV A ISGZ
SC WV EAZ GFADEFZ VEF OSMRP UAZO'T FAGT. HMV, HO VEWT VWYF TEF VGFYHUFZ
MRZFG TMDE TVGSRP FYSVWSR, ARZ EFG CADF FQXGFTTFZ TMDE ZFFX ARQWFVO,
ARZ, AHSJF AUU, TMDE ZGFAZ ARZ VFGGSG, VEAV YG. USGGO CFUV WV WRDMYHFRV
SR EWY VS TXFAK A ISGZ SG VIS SC GFATTMGARDF.

“DSMGAPF, ZFAG YWTT! DSMGAPF! HMTWRFTT! VEF ISGTV IWUU HF SJFG WR A
YSYFRV; WV WT HMV XATTWRP VEF GSSY-ZSSG, ARZ VEF ISGTV WT SJFG. VEFR,
AUU VEF PSSZ OSM HGWRP VS EWY, AUU VEF GFUWFC, AUU VEF EAXXWRFTT OSM
HGWRP VS EWY, HFPWR. UFV SMG PSSZ CGWFRZ EFGF, ATTWTV OSM SR VEAV TWZF.
VEAV'T IFUU, CGWFRZ ZFCAGPF. DSYF, RSI. HMTWRFTT, HMTWRFTT!”

VEFO IFRV MX TUSIUO ARZ TSCVUO. VEF TVAWGDATF IAT TESGV, ARZ VEFO IFGF
TSSR AV VEF VSX. VEFGF, AT WV EAZ AR AHGMXV VMGR WR WV, VEFO DAYF AUU AV
SRDF WR TWPEV SC VEGFF YFR, IESTF EFAZT IFGF HFRV ZSIR DUSTF VSPFVEFG AV
VEF TWZF SC A ZSSG, ARZ IES IFGF WRVFRVUO USSKWRP WRVS VEF GSSY VS IEWDE
VEF ZSSG HFUSRPFZ, VEGSMPE TSYF DEWRKT SG ESUFT WR VEF IAUU. SR EFAGWRP
CSSVTVFXT DUSTF AV EARZ, VEFTF VEGFF VMGRFZ, ARZ GSTF, ARZ TESIFZ
VEFYTFUJFT VS HF VEF VEGFF SC SRF RAYF IES EAZ HFFR ZGWRKWRP WR VEF
IWRF-TESX.

“W CSGPSV VEFY WR VEF TMGXGWTF SC OSMG JWTWV,” FQXUAWRFZ YSRTWFMG
ZFCAGPF. “UFAJF MT, PSSZ HSOT; IF EAJF HMTWRFTT EFGF.”

VEF VEGFF PUWZFZ HO, ARZ IFRV TWUFRVUO ZSIR.

VEFGF AXXFAGWRP VS HF RS SVEFG ZSSG SR VEAV CUSSG, ARZ VEF KFFXFG SC
VEF IWRF-TESX PSWRP TVGAWPEV VS VEWT SRF IEFR VEFO IFGF UFCV AUSRF, YG.
USGGO ATKFZ EWY WR A IEWTXFG, IWVE A UWVVUF ARPFG:

“ZS OSM YAKF A TESI SC YSRTWFMG YARFVVF?”

“W TESI EWY, WR VEF IAO OSM EAJF TFFR, VS A DESTFR CFI.”

“WT VEAV IFUU?”

“_W_ VEWRK WV WT IFUU.”

“IES AGF VEF CFI? ESI ZS OSM DESSTF VEFY?”

“W DESSTF VEFY AT GFAU YFR, SC YO RAYF--LADNMFT WT YO RAYF--VS IESY VEF
TWPEV WT UWKFUO VS ZS PSSZ. FRSMPE; OSM AGF FRPUWTE; VEAV WT ARSVEFG
VEWRP. TVAO VEFGF, WC OSM XUFATF, A UWVVUF YSYFRV.”

IWVE AR AZYSRWVSGO PFTVMGF VS KFFX VEFY HADK, EF TVSSXFZ, ARZ USSKFZ WR
VEGSMPE VEF DGFJWDF WR VEF IAUU. TSSR GAWTWRP EWT EFAZ APAWR, EF TVGMDK
VIWDF SG VEGWDF MXSR VEF ZSSG--FJWZFRVUO IWVE RS SVEFG SHLFDV VEAR VS
YAKF A RSWTF VEFGF. IWVE VEF TAYF WRVFRVWSR, EF ZGFI VEF KFO ADGSTT WV,
VEGFF SG CSMG VWYFT, HFCSGF EF XMV WV DUMYTWUO WRVS VEF USDK, ARZ VMGRFZ
WV AT EFAJWUO AT EF DSMUZ.

VEF ZSSG TUSIUO SXFRFZ WRIAGZ MRZFG EWT EARZ, ARZ EF USSKFZ WRVS VEF
GSSY ARZ TAWZ TSYFVEWRP. A CAWRV JSWDF ARTIFGFZ TSYFVEWRP. UWVVUF YSGF
VEAR A TWRPUF TOUUAHUF DSMUZ EAJF HFFR TXSKFR SR FWVEFG TWZF.

EF USSKFZ HADK SJFG EWT TESMUZFG, ARZ HFDKSRFZ VEFY VS FRVFG. YG. USGGO
PSV EWT AGY TFDMGFUO GSMRZ VEF ZAMPEVFG'T IAWTV, ARZ EFUZ EFG; CSG EF
CFUV VEAV TEF IAT TWRKWRP.

“A-A-A-HMTWRFTT, HMTWRFTT!” EF MGPFZ, IWVE A YSWTVMGF VEAV IAT RSV SC
HMTWRFTT TEWRWRP SR EWT DEFFK. “DSYF WR, DSYF WR!”

“W AY ACGAWZ SC WV,” TEF ARTIFGFZ, TEMZZFGWRP.

“SC WV? IEAV?”

“W YFAR SC EWY. SC YO CAVEFG.”

GFRZFGFZ WR A YARRFG ZFTXFGAVF, HO EFG TVAVF ARZ HO VEF HFDKSRWRP SC
VEFWG DSRZMDVSG, EF ZGFI SJFG EWT RFDK VEF AGY VEAV TESSK MXSR EWT
TESMUZFG, UWCVFZ EFG A UWVVUF, ARZ EMGGWFZ EFG WRVS VEF GSSY. EF TAV EFG
ZSIR LMTV IWVEWR VEF ZSSG, ARZ EFUZ EFG, DUWRPWRP VS EWY.

ZFCAGPF ZGFI SMV VEF KFO, DUSTFZ VEF ZSSG, USDKFZ WV SR VEF WRTWZF,
VSSK SMV VEF KFO APAWR, ARZ EFUZ WV WR EWT EARZ. AUU VEWT EF ZWZ,
YFVESZWDAUUO, ARZ IWVE AT USMZ ARZ EAGTE AR ADDSYXARWYFRV SC RSWTF AT EF
DSMUZ YAKF. CWRAUUO, EF IAUKFZ ADGSTT VEF GSSY IWVE A YFATMGFZ VGFAZ VS
IEFGF VEF IWRZSI IAT. EF TVSXXFZ VEFGF, ARZ CADFZ GSMRZ.

VEF PAGGFV, HMWUV VS HF A ZFXSTWVSGO CSG CWGFISSZ ARZ VEF UWKF, IAT ZWY
ARZ ZAGK: CSG, VEF IWRZSI SC ZSGYFG TEAXF, IAT WR VGMVE A ZSSG WR VEF
GSSC, IWVE A UWVVUF DGARF SJFG WV CSG VEF ESWTVWRP MX SC TVSGFT CGSY
VEF TVGFFV: MRPUABFZ, ARZ DUSTWRP MX VEF YWZZUF WR VIS XWFDFT, UWKF ARO
SVEFG ZSSG SC CGFRDE DSRTVGMDVWSR. VS FQDUMZF VEF DSUZ, SRF EAUC SC VEWT
ZSSG IAT CATV DUSTFZ, ARZ VEF SVEFG IAT SXFRFZ HMV A JFGO UWVVUF IAO.
TMDE A TDARVO XSGVWSR SC UWPEV IAT AZYWVVFZ VEGSMPE VEFTF YFART, VEAV WV
IAT ZWCCWDMUV, SR CWGTV DSYWRP WR, VS TFF AROVEWRP; ARZ USRP EAHWV
AUSRF DSMUZ EAJF TUSIUO CSGYFZ WR ARO SRF, VEF AHWUWVO VS ZS ARO ISGK
GFNMWGWRP RWDFVO WR TMDE SHTDMGWVO. OFV, ISGK SC VEAV KWRZ IAT HFWRP
ZSRF WR VEF PAGGFV; CSG, IWVE EWT HADK VSIAGZT VEF ZSSG, ARZ EWT CADF
VSIAGZT VEF IWRZSI IEFGF VEF KFFXFG SC VEF IWRF-TESX TVSSZ USSKWRP AV
EWY, A IEWVF-EAWGFZ YAR TAV SR A USI HFRDE, TVSSXWRP CSGIAGZ ARZ JFGO
HMTO, YAKWRP TESFT.




JW. VEF TESFYAKFG


“PSSZ ZAO!” TAWZ YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF, USSKWRP ZSIR AV VEF IEWVF EFAZ VEAV
HFRV USI SJFG VEF TESFYAKWRP.

WV IAT GAWTFZ CSG A YSYFRV, ARZ A JFGO CAWRV JSWDF GFTXSRZFZ VS VEF
TAUMVAVWSR, AT WC WV IFGF AV A ZWTVARDF:

“PSSZ ZAO!”

“OSM AGF TVWUU EAGZ AV ISGK, W TFF?”

ACVFG A USRP TWUFRDF, VEF EFAZ IAT UWCVFZ CSG ARSVEFG YSYFRV, ARZ VEF
JSWDF GFXUWFZ, “OFT--W AY ISGKWRP.” VEWT VWYF, A XAWG SC EAPPAGZ FOFT
EAZ USSKFZ AV VEF NMFTVWSRFG, HFCSGF VEF CADF EAZ ZGSXXFZ APAWR.

VEF CAWRVRFTT SC VEF JSWDF IAT XWVWAHUF ARZ ZGFAZCMU. WV IAT RSV VEF
CAWRVRFTT SC XEOTWDAU IFAKRFTT, VESMPE DSRCWRFYFRV ARZ EAGZ CAGF RS
ZSMHV EAZ VEFWG XAGV WR WV. WVT ZFXUSGAHUF XFDMUWAGWVO IAT, VEAV WV IAT
VEF CAWRVRFTT SC TSUWVMZF ARZ ZWTMTF. WV IAT UWKF VEF UATV CFFHUF FDES
SC A TSMRZ YAZF USRP ARZ USRP APS. TS FRVWGFUO EAZ WV USTV VEF UWCF ARZ
GFTSRARDF SC VEF EMYAR JSWDF, VEAV WV ACCFDVFZ VEF TFRTFT UWKF A SRDF
HFAMVWCMU DSUSMG CAZFZ AIAO WRVS A XSSG IFAK TVAWR. TS TMRKFR ARZ
TMXXGFTTFZ WV IAT, VEAV WV IAT UWKF A JSWDF MRZFGPGSMRZ. TS FQXGFTTWJF
WV IAT, SC A ESXFUFTT ARZ USTV DGFAVMGF, VEAV A CAYWTEFZ VGAJFUUFG,
IFAGWFZ SMV HO USRFUO IARZFGWRP WR A IWUZFGRFTT, ISMUZ EAJF GFYFYHFGFZ
ESYF ARZ CGWFRZT WR TMDE A VSRF HFCSGF UOWRP ZSIR VS ZWF.

TSYF YWRMVFT SC TWUFRV ISGK EAZ XATTFZ: ARZ VEF EAPPAGZ FOFT EAZ USSKFZ
MX APAWR: RSV IWVE ARO WRVFGFTV SG DMGWSTWVO, HMV IWVE A ZMUU YFDEARWDAU
XFGDFXVWSR, HFCSGFEARZ, VEAV VEF TXSV IEFGF VEF SRUO JWTWVSG VEFO IFGF
AIAGF SC EAZ TVSSZ, IAT RSV OFV FYXVO.

“W IARV,” TAWZ ZFCAGPF, IES EAZ RSV GFYSJFZ EWT PABF CGSY VEF TESFYAKFG,
“VS UFV WR A UWVVUF YSGF UWPEV EFGF. OSM DAR HFAG A UWVVUF YSGF?”

VEF TESFYAKFG TVSXXFZ EWT ISGK; USSKFZ IWVE A JADARV AWG SC UWTVFRWRP,
AV VEF CUSSG SR SRF TWZF SC EWY; VEFR TWYWUAGUO, AV VEF CUSSG SR VEF
SVEFG TWZF SC EWY; VEFR, MXIAGZ AV VEF TXFAKFG.

“IEAV ZWZ OSM TAO?”

“OSM DAR HFAG A UWVVUF YSGF UWPEV?”

“W YMTV HFAG WV, WC OSM UFV WV WR.” (UAOWRP VEF XAUFTV TEAZSI SC A
TVGFTT MXSR VEF TFDSRZ ISGZ.)

VEF SXFRFZ EAUC-ZSSG IAT SXFRFZ A UWVVUF CMGVEFG, ARZ TFDMGFZ AV VEAV
ARPUF CSG VEF VWYF. A HGSAZ GAO SC UWPEV CFUU WRVS VEF PAGGFV, ARZ
TESIFZ VEF ISGKYAR IWVE AR MRCWRWTEFZ TESF MXSR EWT UAX, XAMTWRP WR EWT
UAHSMG. EWT CFI DSYYSR VSSUT ARZ JAGWSMT TDGAXT SC UFAVEFG IFGF AV EWT
CFFV ARZ SR EWT HFRDE. EF EAZ A IEWVF HFAGZ, GAPPFZUO DMV, HMV RSV JFGO
USRP, A ESUUSI CADF, ARZ FQDFFZWRPUO HGWPEV FOFT. VEF ESUUSIRFTT ARZ
VEWRRFTT SC EWT CADF ISMUZ EAJF DAMTFZ VEFY VS USSK UAGPF, MRZFG EWT OFV
ZAGK FOFHGSIT ARZ EWT DSRCMTFZ IEWVF EAWG, VESMPE VEFO EAZ HFFR GFAUUO
SVEFGIWTF; HMV, VEFO IFGF RAVMGAUUO UAGPF, ARZ USSKFZ MRRAVMGAUUO TS.
EWT OFUUSI GAPT SC TEWGV UAO SXFR AV VEF VEGSAV, ARZ TESIFZ EWT HSZO
VS HF IWVEFGFZ ARZ ISGR. EF, ARZ EWT SUZ DARJAT CGSDK, ARZ EWT USSTF
TVSDKWRPT, ARZ AUU EWT XSSG VAVVFGT SC DUSVEFT, EAZ, WR A USRP TFDUMTWSR
CGSY ZWGFDV UWPEV ARZ AWG, CAZFZ ZSIR VS TMDE A ZMUU MRWCSGYWVO SC
XAGDEYFRV-OFUUSI, VEAV WV ISMUZ EAJF HFFR EAGZ VS TAO IEWDE IAT IEWDE.

EF EAZ XMV MX A EARZ HFVIFFR EWT FOFT ARZ VEF UWPEV, ARZ VEF JFGO HSRFT
SC WV TFFYFZ VGARTXAGFRV. TS EF TAV, IWVE A TVFAZCATVUO JADARV PABF,
XAMTWRP WR EWT ISGK. EF RFJFG USSKFZ AV VEF CWPMGF HFCSGF EWY, IWVESMV
CWGTV USSKWRP ZSIR SR VEWT TWZF SC EWYTFUC, VEFR SR VEAV, AT WC EF EAZ
USTV VEF EAHWV SC ATTSDWAVWRP XUADF IWVE TSMRZ; EF RFJFG TXSKF, IWVESMV
CWGTV IARZFGWRP WR VEWT YARRFG, ARZ CSGPFVVWRP VS TXFAK.

“AGF OSM PSWRP VS CWRWTE VEAV XAWG SC TESFT VS-ZAO?” ATKFZ ZFCAGPF,
YSVWSRWRP VS YG. USGGO VS DSYF CSGIAGZ.

“IEAV ZWZ OSM TAO?”

“ZS OSM YFAR VS CWRWTE VEAV XAWG SC TESFT VS-ZAO?”

“W DAR'V TAO VEAV W YFAR VS. W TMXXSTF TS. W ZSR'V KRSI.”

HMV, VEF NMFTVWSR GFYWRZFZ EWY SC EWT ISGK, ARZ EF HFRV SJFG WV APAWR.

YG. USGGO DAYF TWUFRVUO CSGIAGZ, UFAJWRP VEF ZAMPEVFG HO VEF ZSSG. IEFR
EF EAZ TVSSZ, CSG A YWRMVF SG VIS, HO VEF TWZF SC ZFCAGPF, VEF TESFYAKFG
USSKFZ MX. EF TESIFZ RS TMGXGWTF AV TFFWRP ARSVEFG CWPMGF, HMV VEF
MRTVFAZO CWRPFGT SC SRF SC EWT EARZT TVGAOFZ VS EWT UWXT AT EF USSKFZ AV
WV (EWT UWXT ARZ EWT RAWUT IFGF SC VEF TAYF XAUF UFAZ-DSUSMG), ARZ VEFR
VEF EARZ ZGSXXFZ VS EWT ISGK, ARZ EF SRDF YSGF HFRV SJFG VEF TESF. VEF
USSK ARZ VEF ADVWSR EAZ SDDMXWFZ HMV AR WRTVARV.

“OSM EAJF A JWTWVSG, OSM TFF,” TAWZ YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF.

“IEAV ZWZ OSM TAO?”

“EFGF WT A JWTWVSG.”

VEF TESFYAKFG USSKFZ MX AT HFCSGF, HMV IWVESMV GFYSJWRP A EARZ CGSY EWT
ISGK.

“DSYF!” TAWZ ZFCAGPF. “EFGF WT YSRTWFMG, IES KRSIT A IFUU-YAZF TESF IEFR
EF TFFT SRF. TESI EWY VEAV TESF OSM AGF ISGKWRP AV. VAKF WV, YSRTWFMG.”

YG. USGGO VSSK WV WR EWT EARZ.

“VFUU YSRTWFMG IEAV KWRZ SC TESF WV WT, ARZ VEF YAKFG'T RAYF.”

VEFGF IAT A USRPFG XAMTF VEAR MTMAU, HFCSGF VEF TESFYAKFG GFXUWFZ:

“W CSGPFV IEAV WV IAT OSM ATKFZ YF. IEAV ZWZ OSM TAO?”

“W TAWZ, DSMUZR'V OSM ZFTDGWHF VEF KWRZ SC TESF, CSG YSRTWFMG'T
WRCSGYAVWSR?”

“WV WT A UAZO'T TESF. WV WT A OSMRP UAZO'T IAUKWRP-TESF. WV WT WR VEF
XGFTFRV YSZF. W RFJFG TAI VEF YSZF. W EAJF EAZ A XAVVFGR WR YO EARZ.” EF
PUARDFZ AV VEF TESF IWVE TSYF UWVVUF XATTWRP VSMDE SC XGWZF.

“ARZ VEF YAKFG'T RAYF?” TAWZ ZFCAGPF.

RSI VEAV EF EAZ RS ISGK VS ESUZ, EF UAWZ VEF KRMDKUFT SC VEF GWPEV EARZ
WR VEF ESUUSI SC VEF UFCV, ARZ VEFR VEF KRMDKUFT SC VEF UFCV EARZ WR VEF
ESUUSI SC VEF GWPEV, ARZ VEFR XATTFZ A EARZ ADGSTT EWT HFAGZFZ DEWR, ARZ
TS SR WR GFPMUAG DEARPFT, IWVESMV A YSYFRV'T WRVFGYWTTWSR. VEF VATK SC
GFDAUUWRP EWY CGSY VEF JAPGARDO WRVS IEWDE EF AUIAOT TARK IEFR EF
EAZ TXSKFR, IAT UWKF GFDAUUWRP TSYF JFGO IFAK XFGTSR CGSY A TISSR, SG
FRZFAJSMGWRP, WR VEF ESXF SC TSYF ZWTDUSTMGF, VS TVAO VEF TXWGWV SC A
CATV-ZOWRP YAR.

“ZWZ OSM ATK YF CSG YO RAYF?”

“ATTMGFZUO W ZWZ.”

“SRF EMRZGFZ ARZ CWJF, RSGVE VSIFG.”

“WT VEAV AUU?”

“SRF EMRZGFZ ARZ CWJF, RSGVE VSIFG.”

IWVE A IFAGO TSMRZ VEAV IAT RSV A TWPE, RSG A PGSAR, EF HFRV VS ISGK
APAWR, MRVWU VEF TWUFRDF IAT APAWR HGSKFR.

“OSM AGF RSV A TESFYAKFG HO VGAZF?” TAWZ YG. USGGO, USSKWRP TVFAZCATVUO
AV EWY.

EWT EAPPAGZ FOFT VMGRFZ VS ZFCAGPF AT WC EF ISMUZ EAJF VGARTCFGGFZ VEF
NMFTVWSR VS EWY: HMV AT RS EFUX DAYF CGSY VEAV NMAGVFG, VEFO VMGRFZ HADK
SR VEF NMFTVWSRFG IEFR VEFO EAZ TSMPEV VEF PGSMRZ.

“W AY RSV A TESFYAKFG HO VGAZF? RS, W IAT RSV A TESFYAKFG HO VGAZF. W-W
UFAGRV WV EFGF. W VAMPEV YOTFUC. W ATKFZ UFAJF VS--”

EF UAXTFZ AIAO, FJFR CSG YWRMVFT, GWRPWRP VESTF YFATMGFZ DEARPFT SR EWT
EARZT VEF IESUF VWYF. EWT FOFT DAYF TUSIUO HADK, AV UATV, VS VEF CADF
CGSY IEWDE VEFO EAZ IARZFGFZ; IEFR VEFO GFTVFZ SR WV, EF TVAGVFZ, ARZ
GFTMYFZ, WR VEF YARRFG SC A TUFFXFG VEAV YSYFRV AIAKF, GFJFGVWRP VS A
TMHLFDV SC UATV RWPEV.

“W ATKFZ UFAJF VS VFADE YOTFUC, ARZ W PSV WV IWVE YMDE ZWCCWDMUVO ACVFG
A USRP IEWUF, ARZ W EAJF YAZF TESFT FJFG TWRDF.”

AT EF EFUZ SMV EWT EARZ CSG VEF TESF VEAV EAZ HFFR VAKFR CGSY EWY, YG.
USGGO TAWZ, TVWUU USSKWRP TVFAZCATVUO WR EWT CADF:

“YSRTWFMG YARFVVF, ZS OSM GFYFYHFG RSVEWRP SC YF?”

VEF TESF ZGSXXFZ VS VEF PGSMRZ, ARZ EF TAV USSKWRP CWQFZUO AV VEF
NMFTVWSRFG.

“YSRTWFMG YARFVVF”; YG. USGGO UAWZ EWT EARZ MXSR ZFCAGPF'T AGY; “ZS OSM
GFYFYHFG RSVEWRP SC VEWT YAR? USSK AV EWY. USSK AV YF. WT VEFGF RS SUZ
HARKFG, RS SUZ HMTWRFTT, RS SUZ TFGJARV, RS SUZ VWYF, GWTWRP WR OSMG
YWRZ, YSRTWFMG YARFVVF?”

AT VEF DAXVWJF SC YARO OFAGT TAV USSKWRP CWQFZUO, HO VMGRT, AV YG.
USGGO ARZ AV ZFCAGPF, TSYF USRP SHUWVFGAVFZ YAGKT SC AR ADVWJFUO WRVFRV
WRVFUUWPFRDF WR VEF YWZZUF SC VEF CSGFEFAZ, PGAZMAUUO CSGDFZ VEFYTFUJFT
VEGSMPE VEF HUADK YWTV VEAV EAZ CAUUFR SR EWY. VEFO IFGF SJFGDUSMZFZ
APAWR, VEFO IFGF CAWRVFG, VEFO IFGF PSRF; HMV VEFO EAZ HFFR VEFGF. ARZ
TS FQADVUO IAT VEF FQXGFTTWSR GFXFAVFZ SR VEF CAWG OSMRP CADF SC EFG IES
EAZ DGFXV AUSRP VEF IAUU VS A XSWRV IEFGF TEF DSMUZ TFF EWY, ARZ IEFGF
TEF RSI TVSSZ USSKWRP AV EWY, IWVE EARZT IEWDE AV CWGTV EAZ HFFR SRUO
GAWTFZ WR CGWPEVFRFZ DSYXATTWSR, WC RSV FJFR VS KFFX EWY SCC ARZ
TEMV SMV VEF TWPEV SC EWY, HMV IEWDE IFGF RSI FQVFRZWRP VSIAGZT EWY,
VGFYHUWRP IWVE FAPFGRFTT VS UAO VEF TXFDVGAU CADF MXSR EFG IAGY OSMRP
HGFATV, ARZ USJF WV HADK VS UWCF ARZ ESXF--TS FQADVUO IAT VEF FQXGFTTWSR
GFXFAVFZ (VESMPE WR TVGSRPFG DEAGADVFGT) SR EFG CAWG OSMRP CADF, VEAV WV
USSKFZ AT VESMPE WV EAZ XATTFZ UWKF A YSJWRP UWPEV, CGSY EWY VS EFG.

ZAGKRFTT EAZ CAUUFR SR EWY WR WVT XUADF. EF USSKFZ AV VEF VIS, UFTT ARZ
UFTT AVVFRVWJFUO, ARZ EWT FOFT WR PUSSYO AHTVGADVWSR TSMPEV VEF PGSMRZ
ARZ USSKFZ AHSMV EWY WR VEF SUZ IAO. CWRAUUO, IWVE A ZFFX USRP TWPE, EF
VSSK VEF TESF MX, ARZ GFTMYFZ EWT ISGK.

“EAJF OSM GFDSPRWTFZ EWY, YSRTWFMG?” ATKFZ ZFCAGPF WR A IEWTXFG.

“OFT; CSG A YSYFRV. AV CWGTV W VESMPEV WV NMWVF ESXFUFTT, HMV W EAJF
MRNMFTVWSRAHUO TFFR, CSG A TWRPUF YSYFRV, VEF CADF VEAV W SRDF KRFI TS
IFUU. EMTE! UFV MT ZGAI CMGVEFG HADK. EMTE!”

TEF EAZ YSJFZ CGSY VEF IAUU SC VEF PAGGFV, JFGO RFAG VS VEF HFRDE SR
IEWDE EF TAV. VEFGF IAT TSYFVEWRP AICMU WR EWT MRDSRTDWSMTRFTT SC VEF
CWPMGF VEAV DSMUZ EAJF XMV SMV WVT EARZ ARZ VSMDEFZ EWY AT EF TVSSXFZ
SJFG EWT UAHSMG.

RSV A ISGZ IAT TXSKFR, RSV A TSMRZ IAT YAZF. TEF TVSSZ, UWKF A TXWGWV,
HFTWZF EWY, ARZ EF HFRV SJFG EWT ISGK.

WV EAXXFRFZ, AV UFRPVE, VEAV EF EAZ SDDATWSR VS DEARPF VEF WRTVGMYFRV
WR EWT EARZ, CSG EWT TESFYAKFG'T KRWCF. WV UAO SR VEAV TWZF SC EWY
IEWDE IAT RSV VEF TWZF SR IEWDE TEF TVSSZ. EF EAZ VAKFR WV MX, ARZ IAT
TVSSXWRP VS ISGK APAWR, IEFR EWT FOFT DAMPEV VEF TKWGV SC EFG ZGFTT. EF
GAWTFZ VEFY, ARZ TAI EFG CADF. VEF VIS TXFDVAVSGT TVAGVFZ CSGIAGZ,
HMV TEF TVAOFZ VEFY IWVE A YSVWSR SC EFG EARZ. TEF EAZ RS CFAG SC EWT
TVGWKWRP AV EFG IWVE VEF KRWCF, VESMPE VEFO EAZ.

EF TVAGFZ AV EFG IWVE A CFAGCMU USSK, ARZ ACVFG A IEWUF EWT UWXT HFPAR
VS CSGY TSYF ISGZT, VESMPE RS TSMRZ XGSDFFZFZ CGSY VEFY. HO ZFPGFFT, WR
VEF XAMTFT SC EWT NMWDK ARZ UAHSMGFZ HGFAVEWRP, EF IAT EFAGZ VS TAO:

“IEAV WT VEWT?”

IWVE VEF VFAGT TVGFAYWRP ZSIR EFG CADF, TEF XMV EFG VIS EARZT VS EFG
UWXT, ARZ KWTTFZ VEFY VS EWY; VEFR DUATXFZ VEFY SR EFG HGFATV, AT WC TEF
UAWZ EWT GMWRFZ EFAZ VEFGF.

“OSM AGF RSV VEF PASUFG'T ZAMPEVFG?”

TEF TWPEFZ “RS.”

“IES AGF OSM?”

RSV OFV VGMTVWRP VEF VSRFT SC EFG JSWDF, TEF TAV ZSIR SR VEF HFRDE
HFTWZF EWY. EF GFDSWUFZ, HMV TEF UAWZ EFG EARZ MXSR EWT AGY. A TVGARPF
VEGWUU TVGMDK EWY IEFR TEF ZWZ TS, ARZ JWTWHUO XATTFZ SJFG EWT CGAYF; EF
UAWZ VEF KRWCF ZSIR TSCVUO, AT EF TAV TVAGWRP AV EFG.

EFG PSUZFR EAWG, IEWDE TEF ISGF WR USRP DMGUT, EAZ HFFR EMGGWFZUO XMTEFZ
ATWZF, ARZ CFUU ZSIR SJFG EFG RFDK. AZJARDWRP EWT EARZ HO UWVVUF ARZ
UWVVUF, EF VSSK WV MX ARZ USSKFZ AV WV. WR VEF YWZTV SC VEF ADVWSR
EF IFRV ATVGAO, ARZ, IWVE ARSVEFG ZFFX TWPE, CFUU VS ISGK AV EWT
TESFYAKWRP.

HMV RSV CSG USRP. GFUFATWRP EWT AGY, TEF UAWZ EFG EARZ MXSR EWT
TESMUZFG. ACVFG USSKWRP ZSMHVCMUUO AV WV, VIS SG VEGFF VWYFT, AT WC VS
HF TMGF VEAV WV IAT GFAUUO VEFGF, EF UAWZ ZSIR EWT ISGK, XMV EWT EARZ
VS EWT RFDK, ARZ VSSK SCC A HUADKFRFZ TVGWRP IWVE A TDGAX SC CSUZFZ GAP
AVVADEFZ VS WV. EF SXFRFZ VEWT, DAGFCMUUO, SR EWT KRFF, ARZ WV DSRVAWRFZ
A JFGO UWVVUF NMARVWVO SC EAWG: RSV YSGF VEAR SRF SG VIS USRP PSUZFR
EAWGT, IEWDE EF EAZ, WR TSYF SUZ ZAO, ISMRZ SCC MXSR EWT CWRPFG.

EF VSSK EFG EAWG WRVS EWT EARZ APAWR, ARZ USSKFZ DUSTFUO AV WV. “WV WT
VEF TAYF. ESI DAR WV HF! IEFR IAT WV! ESI IAT WV!”

AT VEF DSRDFRVGAVFZ FQXGFTTWSR GFVMGRFZ VS EWT CSGFEFAZ, EF TFFYFZ VS
HFDSYF DSRTDWSMT VEAV WV IAT WR EFGT VSS. EF VMGRFZ EFG CMUU VS VEF
UWPEV, ARZ USSKFZ AV EFG.

“TEF EAZ UAWZ EFG EFAZ MXSR YO TESMUZFG, VEAV RWPEV IEFR W IAT TMYYSRFZ
SMV--TEF EAZ A CFAG SC YO PSWRP, VESMPE W EAZ RSRF--ARZ IEFR W IAT
HGSMPEV VS VEF RSGVE VSIFG VEFO CSMRZ VEFTF MXSR YO TUFFJF. 'OSM IWUU
UFAJF YF VEFY? VEFO DAR RFJFG EFUX YF VS FTDAXF WR VEF HSZO, VESMPE VEFO
YAO WR VEF TXWGWV.' VESTF IFGF VEF ISGZT W TAWZ. W GFYFYHFG VEFY JFGO
IFUU.”

EF CSGYFZ VEWT TXFFDE IWVE EWT UWXT YARO VWYFT HFCSGF EF DSMUZ MVVFG WV.
HMV IEFR EF ZWZ CWRZ TXSKFR ISGZT CSG WV, VEFO DAYF VS EWY DSEFGFRVUO,
VESMPE TUSIUO.

“ESI IAT VEWT?--_IAT WV OSM_?”

SRDF YSGF, VEF VIS TXFDVAVSGT TVAGVFZ, AT EF VMGRFZ MXSR EFG IWVE A
CGWPEVCMU TMZZFRRFTT. HMV TEF TAV XFGCFDVUO TVWUU WR EWT PGATX, ARZ SRUO
TAWZ, WR A USI JSWDF, “W FRVGFAV OSM, PSSZ PFRVUFYFR, ZS RSV DSYF RFAG
MT, ZS RSV TXFAK, ZS RSV YSJF!”

“EAGK!” EF FQDUAWYFZ. “IESTF JSWDF IAT VEAV?”

EWT EARZT GFUFATFZ EFG AT EF MVVFGFZ VEWT DGO, ARZ IFRV MX VS EWT IEWVF
EAWG, IEWDE VEFO VSGF WR A CGFRBO. WV ZWFZ SMV, AT FJFGOVEWRP HMV EWT
TESFYAKWRP ZWZ ZWF SMV SC EWY, ARZ EF GFCSUZFZ EWT UWVVUF XADKFV ARZ
VGWFZ VS TFDMGF WV WR EWT HGFATV; HMV EF TVWUU USSKFZ AV EFG, ARZ
PUSSYWUO TESSK EWT EFAZ.

“RS, RS, RS; OSM AGF VSS OSMRP, VSS HUSSYWRP. WV DAR'V HF. TFF IEAV VEF
XGWTSRFG WT. VEFTF AGF RSV VEF EARZT TEF KRFI, VEWT WT RSV VEF CADF
TEF KRFI, VEWT WT RSV A JSWDF TEF FJFG EFAGZ. RS, RS. TEF IAT--ARZ EF
IAT--HFCSGF VEF TUSI OFAGT SC VEF RSGVE VSIFG--APFT APS. IEAV WT OSMG
RAYF, YO PFRVUF ARPFU?”

EAWUWRP EWT TSCVFRFZ VSRF ARZ YARRFG, EWT ZAMPEVFG CFUU MXSR EFG KRFFT
HFCSGF EWY, IWVE EFG AXXFAUWRP EARZT MXSR EWT HGFATV.

“S, TWG, AV ARSVEFG VWYF OSM TEAUU KRSI YO RAYF, ARZ IES YO YSVEFG IAT,
ARZ IES YO CAVEFG, ARZ ESI W RFJFG KRFI VEFWG EAGZ, EAGZ EWTVSGO. HMV W
DARRSV VFUU OSM AV VEWT VWYF, ARZ W DARRSV VFUU OSM EFGF. AUU VEAV W YAO
VFUU OSM, EFGF ARZ RSI, WT, VEAV W XGAO VS OSM VS VSMDE YF ARZ VS HUFTT
YF. KWTT YF, KWTT YF! S YO ZFAG, YO ZFAG!”

EWT DSUZ IEWVF EFAZ YWRPUFZ IWVE EFG GAZWARV EAWG, IEWDE IAGYFZ ARZ
UWPEVFZ WV AT VESMPE WV IFGF VEF UWPEV SC CGFFZSY TEWRWRP SR EWY.

“WC OSM EFAG WR YO JSWDF--W ZSR'V KRSI VEAV WV WT TS, HMV W ESXF WV
WT--WC OSM EFAG WR YO JSWDF ARO GFTFYHUARDF VS A JSWDF VEAV SRDF IAT
TIFFV YMTWD WR OSMG FAGT, IFFX CSG WV, IFFX CSG WV! WC OSM VSMDE, WR
VSMDEWRP YO EAWG, AROVEWRP VEAV GFDAUUT A HFUSJFZ EFAZ VEAV UAO SR OSMG
HGFATV IEFR OSM IFGF OSMRP ARZ CGFF, IFFX CSG WV, IFFX CSG WV! WC, IEFR
W EWRV VS OSM SC A ESYF VEAV WT HFCSGF MT, IEFGF W IWUU HF VGMF VS OSM
IWVE AUU YO ZMVO ARZ IWVE AUU YO CAWVECMU TFGJWDF, W HGWRP HADK VEF
GFYFYHGARDF SC A ESYF USRP ZFTSUAVF, IEWUF OSMG XSSG EFAGV XWRFZ AIAO,
IFFX CSG WV, IFFX CSG WV!”

TEF EFUZ EWY DUSTFG GSMRZ VEF RFDK, ARZ GSDKFZ EWY SR EFG HGFATV UWKF A
DEWUZ.

“WC, IEFR W VFUU OSM, ZFAGFTV ZFAG, VEAV OSMG APSRO WT SJFG, ARZ VEAV W
EAJF DSYF EFGF VS VAKF OSM CGSY WV, ARZ VEAV IF PS VS FRPUARZ VS HF AV
XFADF ARZ AV GFTV, W DAMTF OSM VS VEWRK SC OSMG MTFCMU UWCF UAWZ IATVF,
ARZ SC SMG RAVWJF CGARDF TS IWDKFZ VS OSM, IFFX CSG WV, IFFX CSG WV! ARZ
WC, IEFR W TEAUU VFUU OSM SC YO RAYF, ARZ SC YO CAVEFG IES WT UWJWRP,
ARZ SC YO YSVEFG IES WT ZFAZ, OSM UFAGR VEAV W EAJF VS KRFFU VS YO
ESRSMGFZ CAVEFG, ARZ WYXUSGF EWT XAGZSR CSG EAJWRP RFJFG CSG EWT TAKF
TVGWJFR AUU ZAO ARZ UAWR AIAKF ARZ IFXV AUU RWPEV, HFDAMTF VEF USJF SC
YO XSSG YSVEFG EWZ EWT VSGVMGF CGSY YF, IFFX CSG WV, IFFX CSG WV! IFFX
CSG EFG, VEFR, ARZ CSG YF! PSSZ PFRVUFYFR, VEARK PSZ! W CFFU EWT TADGFZ
VFAGT MXSR YO CADF, ARZ EWT TSHT TVGWKF APAWRTV YO EFAGV. S, TFF! VEARK
PSZ CSG MT, VEARK PSZ!”

EF EAZ TMRK WR EFG AGYT, ARZ EWT CADF ZGSXXFZ SR EFG HGFATV: A TWPEV TS
VSMDEWRP, OFV TS VFGGWHUF WR VEF VGFYFRZSMT IGSRP ARZ TMCCFGWRP IEWDE
EAZ PSRF HFCSGF WV, VEAV VEF VIS HFESUZFGT DSJFGFZ VEFWG CADFT.

IEFR VEF NMWFV SC VEF PAGGFV EAZ HFFR USRP MRZWTVMGHFZ, ARZ EWT EFAJWRP
HGFATV ARZ TEAKFR CSGY EAZ USRP OWFUZFZ VS VEF DAUY VEAV YMTV CSUUSI AUU
TVSGYT--FYHUFY VS EMYARWVO, SC VEF GFTV ARZ TWUFRDF WRVS IEWDE VEF TVSGY
DAUUFZ UWCF YMTV EMTE AV UATV--VEFO DAYF CSGIAGZ VS GAWTF VEF CAVEFG ARZ
ZAMPEVFG CGSY VEF PGSMRZ. EF EAZ PGAZMAUUO ZGSXXFZ VS VEF CUSSG, ARZ UAO
VEFGF WR A UFVEAGPO, ISGR SMV. TEF EAZ RFTVUFZ ZSIR IWVE EWY, VEAV EWT
EFAZ YWPEV UWF MXSR EFG AGY; ARZ EFG EAWG ZGSSXWRP SJFG EWY DMGVAWRFZ
EWY CGSY VEF UWPEV.

“WC, IWVESMV ZWTVMGHWRP EWY,” TEF TAWZ, GAWTWRP EFG EARZ VS YG. USGGO AT
EF TVSSXFZ SJFG VEFY, ACVFG GFXFAVFZ HUSIWRPT SC EWT RSTF, “AUU DSMUZ HF
AGGARPFZ CSG SMG UFAJWRP XAGWT AV SRDF, TS VEAV, CGSY VEF JFGO ZSSG, EF
DSMUZ HF VAKFR AIAO--”

“HMV, DSRTWZFG. WT EF CWV CSG VEF LSMGRFO?” ATKFZ YG. USGGO.

“YSGF CWV CSG VEAV, W VEWRK, VEAR VS GFYAWR WR VEWT DWVO, TS ZGFAZCMU VS
EWY.”

“WV WT VGMF,” TAWZ ZFCAGPF, IES IAT KRFFUWRP VS USSK SR ARZ EFAG. “YSGF
VEAR VEAV; YSRTWFMG YARFVVF WT, CSG AUU GFATSRT, HFTV SMV SC CGARDF.
TAO, TEAUU W EWGF A DAGGWAPF ARZ XSTV-ESGTFT?”

“VEAV'T HMTWRFTT,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, GFTMYWRP SR VEF TESGVFTV RSVWDF EWT
YFVESZWDAU YARRFGT; “ARZ WC HMTWRFTT WT VS HF ZSRF, W EAZ HFVVFG ZS WV.”

“VEFR HF TS KWRZ,” MGPFZ YWTT YARFVVF, “AT VS UFAJF MT EFGF. OSM TFF ESI
DSYXSTFZ EF EAT HFDSYF, ARZ OSM DARRSV HF ACGAWZ VS UFAJF EWY IWVE YF
RSI. IEO TESMUZ OSM HF? WC OSM IWUU USDK VEF ZSSG VS TFDMGF MT CGSY
WRVFGGMXVWSR, W ZS RSV ZSMHV VEAV OSM IWUU CWRZ EWY, IEFR OSM DSYF HADK,
AT NMWFV AT OSM UFAJF EWY. WR ARO DATF, W IWUU VAKF DAGF SC EWY MRVWU
OSM GFVMGR, ARZ VEFR IF IWUU GFYSJF EWY TVGAWPEV.”

HSVE YG. USGGO ARZ ZFCAGPF IFGF GAVEFG ZWTWRDUWRFZ VS VEWT DSMGTF, ARZ
WR CAJSMG SC SRF SC VEFY GFYAWRWRP. HMV, AT VEFGF IFGF RSV SRUO DAGGWAPF
ARZ ESGTFT VS HF TFFR VS, HMV VGAJFUUWRP XAXFGT; ARZ AT VWYF XGFTTFZ,
CSG VEF ZAO IAT ZGAIWRP VS AR FRZ, WV DAYF AV UATV VS VEFWG EATVWUO
ZWJWZWRP VEF HMTWRFTT VEAV IAT RFDFTTAGO VS HF ZSRF, ARZ EMGGOWRP AIAO
VS ZS WV.

VEFR, AT VEF ZAGKRFTT DUSTFZ WR, VEF ZAMPEVFG UAWZ EFG EFAZ ZSIR SR VEF
EAGZ PGSMRZ DUSTF AV VEF CAVEFG'T TWZF, ARZ IAVDEFZ EWY. VEF ZAGKRFTT
ZFFXFRFZ ARZ ZFFXFRFZ, ARZ VEFO HSVE UAO NMWFV, MRVWU A UWPEV PUFAYFZ
VEGSMPE VEF DEWRKT WR VEF IAUU.

YG. USGGO ARZ YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF EAZ YAZF AUU GFAZO CSG VEF LSMGRFO, ARZ
EAZ HGSMPEV IWVE VEFY, HFTWZFT VGAJFUUWRP DUSAKT ARZ IGAXXFGT, HGFAZ ARZ
YFAV, IWRF, ARZ ESV DSCCFF. YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF XMV VEWT XGSJFRZFG, ARZ VEF
UAYX EF DAGGWFZ, SR VEF TESFYAKFG'T HFRDE (VEFGF IAT RSVEWRP FUTF WR VEF
PAGGFV HMV A XAUUFV HFZ), ARZ EF ARZ YG. USGGO GSMTFZ VEF DAXVWJF, ARZ
ATTWTVFZ EWY VS EWT CFFV.

RS EMYAR WRVFUUWPFRDF DSMUZ EAJF GFAZ VEF YOTVFGWFT SC EWT YWRZ, WR
VEF TDAGFZ HUARK ISRZFG SC EWT CADF. IEFVEFG EF KRFI IEAV EAZ EAXXFRFZ,
IEFVEFG EF GFDSUUFDVFZ IEAV VEFO EAZ TAWZ VS EWY, IEFVEFG EF KRFI VEAV
EF IAT CGFF, IFGF NMFTVWSRT IEWDE RS TAPADWVO DSMUZ EAJF TSUJFZ. VEFO
VGWFZ TXFAKWRP VS EWY; HMV, EF IAT TS DSRCMTFZ, ARZ TS JFGO TUSI VS
ARTIFG, VEAV VEFO VSSK CGWPEV AV EWT HFIWUZFGYFRV, ARZ APGFFZ CSG
VEF VWYF VS VAYXFG IWVE EWY RS YSGF. EF EAZ A IWUZ, USTV YARRFG SC
SDDATWSRAUUO DUATXWRP EWT EFAZ WR EWT EARZT, VEAV EAZ RSV HFFR TFFR
WR EWY HFCSGF; OFV, EF EAZ TSYF XUFATMGF WR VEF YFGF TSMRZ SC EWT
ZAMPEVFG'T JSWDF, ARZ WRJAGWAHUO VMGRFZ VS WV IEFR TEF TXSKF.

WR VEF TMHYWTTWJF IAO SC SRF USRP ADDMTVSYFZ VS SHFO MRZFG DSFGDWSR, EF
AVF ARZ ZGARK IEAV VEFO PAJF EWY VS FAV ARZ ZGWRK, ARZ XMV SR VEF DUSAK
ARZ SVEFG IGAXXWRPT, VEAV VEFO PAJF EWY VS IFAG. EF GFAZWUO GFTXSRZFZ VS
EWT ZAMPEVFG'T ZGAIWRP EFG AGY VEGSMPE EWT, ARZ VSSK--ARZ KFXV--EFG EARZ
WR HSVE EWT SIR.

VEFO HFPAR VS ZFTDFRZ; YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF PSWRP CWGTV IWVE VEF UAYX, YG.
USGGO DUSTWRP VEF UWVVUF XGSDFTTWSR. VEFO EAZ RSV VGAJFGTFZ YARO TVFXT
SC VEF USRP YAWR TVAWGDATF IEFR EF TVSXXFZ, ARZ TVAGFZ AV VEF GSSC ARZ
GSMRZ AV VEF IAUUT.

“OSM GFYFYHFG VEF XUADF, YO CAVEFG? OSM GFYFYHFG DSYWRP MX EFGF?”

“IEAV ZWZ OSM TAO?”

HMV, HFCSGF TEF DSMUZ GFXFAV VEF NMFTVWSR, EF YMGYMGFZ AR ARTIFG AT WC
TEF EAZ GFXFAVFZ WV.

“GFYFYHFG? RS, W ZSR'V GFYFYHFG. WV IAT TS JFGO USRP APS.”

VEAV EF EAZ RS GFDSUUFDVWSR IEAVFJFG SC EWT EAJWRP HFFR HGSMPEV CGSY EWT
XGWTSR VS VEAV ESMTF, IAT AXXAGFRV VS VEFY. VEFO EFAGZ EWY YMVVFG,
“SRF EMRZGFZ ARZ CWJF, RSGVE VSIFG;” ARZ IEFR EF USSKFZ AHSMV EWY, WV
FJWZFRVUO IAT CSG VEF TVGSRP CSGVGFTT-IAUUT IEWDE EAZ USRP FRDSYXATTFZ
EWY. SR VEFWG GFADEWRP VEF DSMGVOAGZ EF WRTVWRDVWJFUO AUVFGFZ EWT
VGFAZ, AT HFWRP WR FQXFDVAVWSR SC A ZGAIHGWZPF; ARZ IEFR VEFGF IAT
RS ZGAIHGWZPF, ARZ EF TAI VEF DAGGWAPF IAWVWRP WR VEF SXFR TVGFFV, EF
ZGSXXFZ EWT ZAMPEVFG'T EARZ ARZ DUATXFZ EWT EFAZ APAWR.

RS DGSIZ IAT AHSMV VEF ZSSG; RS XFSXUF IFGF ZWTDFGRWHUF AV ARO SC VEF
YARO IWRZSIT; RSV FJFR A DEARDF XATTFGHO IAT WR VEF TVGFFV. AR MRRAVMGAU
TWUFRDF ARZ ZFTFGVWSR GFWPRFZ VEFGF. SRUO SRF TSMU IAT VS HF TFFR, ARZ
VEAV IAT YAZAYF ZFCAGPF--IES UFARFZ APAWRTV VEF ZSSG-XSTV, KRWVVWRP, ARZ
TAI RSVEWRP.

VEF XGWTSRFG EAZ PSV WRVS A DSADE, ARZ EWT ZAMPEVFG EAZ CSUUSIFZ
EWY, IEFR YG. USGGO'T CFFV IFGF AGGFTVFZ SR VEF TVFX HO EWT ATKWRP,
YWTFGAHUO, CSG EWT TESFYAKWRP VSSUT ARZ VEF MRCWRWTEFZ TESFT. YAZAYF
ZFCAGPF WYYFZWAVFUO DAUUFZ VS EFG EMTHARZ VEAV TEF ISMUZ PFV VEFY, ARZ
IFRV, KRWVVWRP, SMV SC VEF UAYXUWPEV, VEGSMPE VEF DSMGVOAGZ. TEF NMWDKUO
HGSMPEV VEFY ZSIR ARZ EARZFZ VEFY WR;--ARZ WYYFZWAVFUO ACVFGIAGZT UFARFZ
APAWRTV VEF ZSSG-XSTV, KRWVVWRP, ARZ TAI RSVEWRP.

ZFCAGPF PSV MXSR VEF HSQ, ARZ PAJF VEF ISGZ “VS VEF HAGGWFG!” VEF
XSTVWUWSR DGADKFZ EWT IEWX, ARZ VEFO DUAVVFGFZ AIAO MRZFG VEF CFFHUF
SJFG-TIWRPWRP UAYXT.

MRZFG VEF SJFG-TIWRPWRP UAYXT--TIWRPWRP FJFG HGWPEVFG WR VEF HFVVFG
TVGFFVT, ARZ FJFG ZWYYFG WR VEF ISGTF--ARZ HO UWPEVFZ TESXT, PAO DGSIZT,
WUUMYWRAVFZ DSCCFF-ESMTFT, ARZ VEFAVGF-ZSSGT, VS SRF SC VEF DWVO
PAVFT. TSUZWFGT IWVE UARVFGRT, AV VEF PMAGZ-ESMTF VEFGF. “OSMG XAXFGT,
VGAJFUUFGT!” “TFF EFGF VEFR, YSRTWFMG VEF SCCWDFG,” TAWZ ZFCAGPF,
PFVVWRP ZSIR, ARZ VAKWRP EWY PGAJFUO AXAGV, “VEFTF AGF VEF XAXFGT SC
YSRTWFMG WRTWZF, IWVE VEF IEWVF EFAZ. VEFO IFGF DSRTWPRFZ VS YF, IWVE
EWY, AV VEF--” EF ZGSXXFZ EWT JSWDF, VEFGF IAT A CUMVVFG AYSRP VEF
YWUWVAGO UARVFGRT, ARZ SRF SC VEFY HFWRP EARZFZ WRVS VEF DSADE HO AR AGY
WR MRWCSGY, VEF FOFT DSRRFDVFZ IWVE VEF AGY USSKFZ, RSV AR FJFGO ZAO
SG AR FJFGO RWPEV USSK, AV YSRTWFMG IWVE VEF IEWVF EFAZ. “WV WT IFUU.
CSGIAGZ!” CGSY VEF MRWCSGY. “AZWFM!” CGSY ZFCAGPF. ARZ TS, MRZFG A TESGV
PGSJF SC CFFHUFG ARZ CFFHUFG SJFG-TIWRPWRP UAYXT, SMV MRZFG VEF PGFAV
PGSJF SC TVAGT.

HFRFAVE VEAV AGDE SC MRYSJFZ ARZ FVFGRAU UWPEVT; TSYF, TS GFYSVF CGSY
VEWT UWVVUF FAGVE VEAV VEF UFAGRFZ VFUU MT WV WT ZSMHVCMU IEFVEFG VEFWG
GAOT EAJF FJFR OFV ZWTDSJFGFZ WV, AT A XSWRV WR TXADF IEFGF AROVEWRP
WT TMCCFGFZ SG ZSRF: VEF TEAZSIT SC VEF RWPEV IFGF HGSAZ ARZ HUADK.
AUU VEGSMPE VEF DSUZ ARZ GFTVUFTT WRVFGJAU, MRVWU ZAIR, VEFO SRDF YSGF
IEWTXFGFZ WR VEF FAGT SC YG. LAGJWT USGGO--TWVVWRP SXXSTWVF VEF HMGWFZ
YAR IES EAZ HFFR ZMP SMV, ARZ ISRZFGWRP IEAV TMHVUF XSIFGT IFGF CSG FJFG
USTV VS EWY, ARZ IEAV IFGF DAXAHUF SC GFTVSGAVWSR--VEF SUZ WRNMWGO:

“W ESXF OSM DAGF VS HF GFDAUUFZ VS UWCF?”

ARZ VEF SUZ ARTIFG:

“W DAR'V TAO.”


VEF FRZ SC VEF CWGTV HSSK.





HSSK VEF TFDSRZ--VEF PSUZFR VEGFAZ




W. CWJF OFAGT UAVFG


VFUUTSR'T HARK HO VFYXUF HAG IAT AR SUZ-CATEWSRFZ XUADF, FJFR WR VEF
OFAG SRF VESMTARZ TFJFR EMRZGFZ ARZ FWPEVO. WV IAT JFGO TYAUU, JFGO
ZAGK, JFGO MPUO, JFGO WRDSYYSZWSMT. WV IAT AR SUZ-CATEWSRFZ XUADF,
YSGFSJFG, WR VEF YSGAU AVVGWHMVF VEAV VEF XAGVRFGT WR VEF ESMTF IFGF
XGSMZ SC WVT TYAUURFTT, XGSMZ SC WVT ZAGKRFTT, XGSMZ SC WVT MPUWRFTT,
XGSMZ SC WVT WRDSYYSZWSMTRFTT. VEFO IFGF FJFR HSATVCMU SC WVT FYWRFRDF
WR VESTF XAGVWDMUAGT, ARZ IFGF CWGFZ HO AR FQXGFTT DSRJWDVWSR VEAV, WC
WV IFGF UFTT SHLFDVWSRAHUF, WV ISMUZ HF UFTT GFTXFDVAHUF. VEWT IAT
RS XATTWJF HFUWFC, HMV AR ADVWJF IFAXSR IEWDE VEFO CUATEFZ AV YSGF
DSRJFRWFRV XUADFT SC HMTWRFTT. VFUUTSR'T (VEFO TAWZ) IARVFZ
RS FUHSI-GSSY, VFUUTSR'T IARVFZ RS UWPEV, VFUUTSR'T IARVFZ RS
FYHFUUWTEYFRV. RSAKFT ARZ DS.'T YWPEV, SG TRSSKT HGSVEFGT' YWPEV; HMV
VFUUTSR'T, VEARK EFAJFR--!

ARO SRF SC VEFTF XAGVRFGT ISMUZ EAJF ZWTWREFGWVFZ EWT TSR SR VEF
NMFTVWSR SC GFHMWUZWRP VFUUTSR'T. WR VEWT GFTXFDV VEF ESMTF IAT YMDE
SR A XAG IWVE VEF DSMRVGO; IEWDE ZWZ JFGO SCVFR ZWTWREFGWV WVT TSRT CSG
TMPPFTVWRP WYXGSJFYFRVT WR UAIT ARZ DMTVSYT VEAV EAZ USRP HFFR EWPEUO
SHLFDVWSRAHUF, HMV IFGF SRUO VEF YSGF GFTXFDVAHUF.

VEMT WV EAZ DSYF VS XATT, VEAV VFUUTSR'T IAT VEF VGWMYXEARV XFGCFDVWSR
SC WRDSRJFRWFRDF. ACVFG HMGTVWRP SXFR A ZSSG SC WZWSVWD SHTVWRADO IWVE
A IFAK GAVVUF WR WVT VEGSAV, OSM CFUU WRVS VFUUTSR'T ZSIR VIS TVFXT,
ARZ DAYF VS OSMG TFRTFT WR A YWTFGAHUF UWVVUF TESX, IWVE VIS UWVVUF
DSMRVFGT, IEFGF VEF SUZFTV SC YFR YAZF OSMG DEFNMF TEAKF AT WC VEF
IWRZ GMTVUFZ WV, IEWUF VEFO FQAYWRFZ VEF TWPRAVMGF HO VEF ZWRPWFTV SC
IWRZSIT, IEWDE IFGF AUIAOT MRZFG A TESIFG-HAVE SC YMZ CGSY CUFFV-TVGFFV,
ARZ IEWDE IFGF YAZF VEF ZWRPWFG HO VEFWG SIR WGSR HAGT XGSXFG, ARZ VEF
EFAJO TEAZSI SC VFYXUF HAG. WC OSMG HMTWRFTT RFDFTTWVAVFZ OSMG TFFWRP
“VEF ESMTF,” OSM IFGF XMV WRVS A TXFDWFT SC DSRZFYRFZ ESUZ AV VEF HADK,
IEFGF OSM YFZWVAVFZ SR A YWTTXFRV UWCF, MRVWU VEF ESMTF DAYF IWVE WVT
EARZT WR WVT XSDKFVT, ARZ OSM DSMUZ EAGZUO HUWRK AV WV WR VEF ZWTYAU
VIWUWPEV. OSMG YSRFO DAYF SMV SC, SG IFRV WRVS, ISGYO SUZ ISSZFR
ZGAIFGT, XAGVWDUFT SC IEWDE CUFI MX OSMG RSTF ARZ ZSIR OSMG VEGSAV IEFR
VEFO IFGF SXFRFZ ARZ TEMV. OSMG HARK-RSVFT EAZ A YMTVO SZSMG, AT WC VEFO
IFGF CATV ZFDSYXSTWRP WRVS GAPT APAWR. OSMG XUAVF IAT TVSIFZ AIAO AYSRP
VEF RFWPEHSMGWRP DFTTXSSUT, ARZ FJWU DSYYMRWDAVWSRT DSGGMXVFZ WVT PSSZ
XSUWTE WR A ZAO SG VIS. OSMG ZFFZT PSV WRVS FQVFYXSGWTFZ TVGSRP-GSSYT
YAZF SC KWVDEFRT ARZ TDMUUFGWFT, ARZ CGFVVFZ AUU VEF CAV SMV SC VEFWG
XAGDEYFRVT WRVS VEF HARKWRP-ESMTF AWG. OSMG UWPEVFG HSQFT SC CAYWUO
XAXFGT IFRV MX-TVAWGT WRVS A HAGYFDWZF GSSY, VEAV AUIAOT EAZ A PGFAV
ZWRWRP-VAHUF WR WV ARZ RFJFG EAZ A ZWRRFG, ARZ IEFGF, FJFR WR VEF OFAG
SRF VESMTARZ TFJFR EMRZGFZ ARZ FWPEVO, VEF CWGTV UFVVFGT IGWVVFR VS OSM
HO OSMG SUZ USJF, SG HO OSMG UWVVUF DEWUZGFR, IFGF HMV RFIUO GFUFATFZ
CGSY VEF ESGGSG SC HFWRP SPUFZ VEGSMPE VEF IWRZSIT, HO VEF EFAZT
FQXSTFZ SR VFYXUF HAG IWVE AR WRTFRTAVF HGMVAUWVO ARZ CFGSDWVO ISGVEO SC
AHOTTWRWA SG ATEARVFF.

HMV WRZFFZ, AV VEAV VWYF, XMVVWRP VS ZFAVE IAT A GFDWXF YMDE WR JSPMF
IWVE AUU VGAZFT ARZ XGSCFTTWSRT, ARZ RSV UFATV SC AUU IWVE VFUUTSR'T.
ZFAVE WT RAVMGF'T GFYFZO CSG AUU VEWRPT, ARZ IEO RSV UFPWTUAVWSR'T?
ADDSGZWRPUO, VEF CSGPFG IAT XMV VS ZFAVE; VEF MVVFGFG SC A HAZ RSVF
IAT XMV VS ZFAVE; VEF MRUAICMU SXFRFG SC A UFVVFG IAT XMV VS ZFAVE; VEF
XMGUSWRFG SC CSGVO TEWUUWRPT ARZ TWQXFRDF IAT XMV VS ZFAVE; VEF ESUZFG
SC A ESGTF AV VFUUTSR'T ZSSG, IES YAZF SCC IWVE WV, IAT XMV VS
ZFAVE; VEF DSWRFG SC A HAZ TEWUUWRP IAT XMV VS ZFAVE; VEF TSMRZFGT SC
VEGFF-CSMGVET SC VEF RSVFT WR VEF IESUF PAYMV SC DGWYF, IFGF XMV VS
ZFAVE. RSV VEAV WV ZWZ VEF UFATV PSSZ WR VEF IAO SC XGFJFRVWSR--WV
YWPEV AUYSTV EAJF HFFR ISGVE GFYAGKWRP VEAV VEF CADV IAT FQADVUO VEF
GFJFGTF--HMV, WV DUFAGFZ SCC (AT VS VEWT ISGUZ) VEF VGSMHUF SC FADE
XAGVWDMUAG DATF, ARZ UFCV RSVEWRP FUTF DSRRFDVFZ IWVE WV VS HF USSKFZ
ACVFG. VEMT, VFUUTSR'T, WR WVT ZAO, UWKF PGFAVFG XUADFT SC HMTWRFTT,
WVT DSRVFYXSGAGWFT, EAZ VAKFR TS YARO UWJFT, VEAV, WC VEF EFAZT UAWZ
USI HFCSGF WV EAZ HFFR GARPFZ SR VFYXUF HAG WRTVFAZ SC HFWRP XGWJAVFUO
ZWTXSTFZ SC, VEFO ISMUZ XGSHAHUO EAJF FQDUMZFZ IEAV UWVVUF UWPEV VEF
PGSMRZ CUSSG EAZ, WR A GAVEFG TWPRWCWDARV YARRFG.

DGAYXFZ WR AUU KWRZT SC ZWY DMXHSAGZT ARZ EMVDEFT AV VFUUTSR'T, VEF
SUZFTV SC YFR DAGGWFZ SR VEF HMTWRFTT PGAJFUO. IEFR VEFO VSSK A OSMRP
YAR WRVS VFUUTSR'T USRZSR ESMTF, VEFO EWZ EWY TSYFIEFGF VWUU EF IAT
SUZ. VEFO KFXV EWY WR A ZAGK XUADF, UWKF A DEFFTF, MRVWU EF EAZ VEF CMUU
VFUUTSR CUAJSMG ARZ HUMF-YSMUZ MXSR EWY. VEFR SRUO IAT EF XFGYWVVFZ VS
HF TFFR, TXFDVADMUAGUO XSGWRP SJFG UAGPF HSSKT, ARZ DATVWRP EWT HGFFDEFT
ARZ PAWVFGT WRVS VEF PFRFGAU IFWPEV SC VEF FTVAHUWTEYFRV.

SMVTWZF VFUUTSR'T--RFJFG HO ARO YFART WR WV, MRUFTT DAUUFZ WR--IAT AR
SZZ-LSH-YAR, AR SDDATWSRAU XSGVFG ARZ YFTTFRPFG, IES TFGJFZ AT VEF UWJF
TWPR SC VEF ESMTF. EF IAT RFJFG AHTFRV ZMGWRP HMTWRFTT ESMGT, MRUFTT
MXSR AR FGGARZ, ARZ VEFR EF IAT GFXGFTFRVFZ HO EWT TSR: A PGWTUO MGDEWR
SC VIFUJF, IES IAT EWT FQXGFTT WYAPF. XFSXUF MRZFGTVSSZ VEAV VFUUTSR'T,
WR A TVAVFUO IAO, VSUFGAVFZ VEF SZZ-LSH-YAR. VEF ESMTF EAZ AUIAOT
VSUFGAVFZ TSYF XFGTSR WR VEAV DAXADWVO, ARZ VWYF ARZ VWZF EAZ ZGWCVFZ
VEWT XFGTSR VS VEF XSTV. EWT TMGRAYF IAT DGMRDEFG, ARZ SR VEF OSMVECMU
SDDATWSR SC EWT GFRSMRDWRP HO XGSQO VEF ISGKT SC ZAGKRFTT, WR VEF
FATVFGUO XAGWTE DEMGDE SC ESMRTZWVDE, EF EAZ GFDFWJFZ VEF AZZFZ
AXXFUUAVWSR SC LFGGO.

VEF TDFRF IAT YG. DGMRDEFG'T XGWJAVF USZPWRP WR EARPWRP-TISGZ-AUUFO,
IEWVFCGWAGT: VEF VWYF, EAUC-XATV TFJFR SC VEF DUSDK SR A IWRZO YAGDE
YSGRWRP, ARRS ZSYWRW TFJFRVFFR EMRZGFZ ARZ FWPEVO. (YG. DGMRDEFG EWYTFUC
AUIAOT TXSKF SC VEF OFAG SC SMG USGZ AT ARRA ZSYWRSFT: AXXAGFRVUO MRZFG
VEF WYXGFTTWSR VEAV VEF DEGWTVWAR FGA ZAVFZ CGSY VEF WRJFRVWSR SC A
XSXMUAG PAYF, HO A UAZO IES EAZ HFTVSIFZ EFG RAYF MXSR WV.)

YG. DGMRDEFG'T AXAGVYFRVT IFGF RSV WR A TAJSMGO RFWPEHSMGESSZ, ARZ IFGF
HMV VIS WR RMYHFG, FJFR WC A DUSTFV IWVE A TWRPUF XARF SC PUATT WR WV
YWPEV HF DSMRVFZ AT SRF. HMV VEFO IFGF JFGO ZFDFRVUO KFXV. FAGUO AT
WV IAT, SR VEF IWRZO YAGDE YSGRWRP, VEF GSSY WR IEWDE EF UAO AHFZ IAT
AUGFAZO TDGMHHFZ VEGSMPESMV; ARZ HFVIFFR VEF DMXT ARZ TAMDFGT AGGARPFZ
CSG HGFAKCATV, ARZ VEF UMYHFGWRP ZFAU VAHUF, A JFGO DUFAR IEWVF DUSVE
IAT TXGFAZ.

YG. DGMRDEFG GFXSTFZ MRZFG A XAVDEISGK DSMRVFGXARF, UWKF A EAGUFNMWR
AV ESYF. AV CWGTV, EF TUFXV EFAJWUO, HMV, HO ZFPGFFT, HFPAR VS GSUU
ARZ TMGPF WR HFZ, MRVWU EF GSTF AHSJF VEF TMGCADF, IWVE EWT TXWKO EAWG
USSKWRP AT WC WV YMTV VFAG VEF TEFFVT VS GWHHSRT. AV IEWDE LMRDVMGF, EF
FQDUAWYFZ, WR A JSWDF SC ZWGF FQATXFGAVWSR:

“HMTV YF, WC TEF AWR'V AV WV APWR!”

A ISYAR SC SGZFGUO ARZ WRZMTVGWSMT AXXFAGARDF GSTF CGSY EFG KRFFT WR A
DSGRFG, IWVE TMCCWDWFRV EATVF ARZ VGFXWZAVWSR VS TESI VEAV TEF IAT VEF
XFGTSR GFCFGGFZ VS.

“IEAV!” TAWZ YG. DGMRDEFG, USSKWRP SMV SC HFZ CSG A HSSV. “OSM'GF AV WV
APWR, AGF OSM?”

ACVFG EAWUWRP VEF YSGR IWVE VEWT TFDSRZ TAUMVAVWSR, EF VEGFI A HSSV AV
VEF ISYAR AT A VEWGZ. WV IAT A JFGO YMZZO HSSV, ARZ YAO WRVGSZMDF VEF
SZZ DWGDMYTVARDF DSRRFDVFZ IWVE YG. DGMRDEFG'T ZSYFTVWD FDSRSYO, VEAV,
IEFGFAT EF SCVFR DAYF ESYF ACVFG HARKWRP ESMGT IWVE DUFAR HSSVT, EF
SCVFR PSV MX RFQV YSGRWRP VS CWRZ VEF TAYF HSSVT DSJFGFZ IWVE DUAO.

“IEAV,” TAWZ YG. DGMRDEFG, JAGOWRP EWT AXSTVGSXEF ACVFG YWTTWRP EWT
YAGK--“IEAV AGF OSM MX VS, APPFGAIAOVFG?”

“W IAT SRUO TAOWRP YO XGAOFGT.”

“TAOWRP OSMG XGAOFGT! OSM'GF A RWDF ISYAR! IEAV ZS OSM YFAR HO CUSXXWRP
OSMGTFUC ZSIR ARZ XGAOWRP APWR YF?”

“W IAT RSV XGAOWRP APAWRTV OSM; W IAT XGAOWRP CSG OSM.”

“OSM IFGFR'V. ARZ WC OSM IFGF, W ISR'V HF VSSK VEF UWHFGVO IWVE. EFGF!
OSMG YSVEFG'T A RWDF ISYAR, OSMRP LFGGO, PSWRP A XGAOWRP APWR OSMG
CAVEFG'T XGSTXFGWVO. OSM'JF PSV A ZMVWCMU YSVEFG, OSM EAJF, YO TSR.
OSM'JF PSV A GFUWPWSMT YSVEFG, OSM EAJF, YO HSO: PSWRP ARZ CUSXXWRP
EFGTFUC ZSIR, ARZ XGAOWRP VEAV VEF HGFAZ-ARZ-HMVVFG YAO HF TRAVDEFZ SMV
SC VEF YSMVE SC EFG SRUO DEWUZ.”

YATVFG DGMRDEFG (IES IAT WR EWT TEWGV) VSSK VEWT JFGO WUU, ARZ, VMGRWRP
VS EWT YSVEFG, TVGSRPUO ZFXGFDAVFZ ARO XGAOWRP AIAO SC EWT XFGTSRAU
HSAGZ.

“ARZ IEAV ZS OSM TMXXSTF, OSM DSRDFWVFZ CFYAUF,” TAWZ YG. DGMRDEFG, IWVE
MRDSRTDWSMT WRDSRTWTVFRDO, “VEAV VEF ISGVE SC _OSMG_ XGAOFGT YAO HF?
RAYF VEF XGWDF VEAV OSM XMV _OSMG_ XGAOFGT AV!”

“VEFO SRUO DSYF CGSY VEF EFAGV, LFGGO. VEFO AGF ISGVE RS YSGF VEAR
VEAV.”

“ISGVE RS YSGF VEAR VEAV,” GFXFAVFZ YG. DGMRDEFG. “VEFO AWR'V ISGVE
YMDE, VEFR. IEFVEFG SG RS, W ISR'V HF XGAOFZ APWR, W VFUU OSM. W DAR'V
ACCSGZ WV. W'Y RSV A PSWRP VS HF YAZF MRUMDKO HO _OSMG_ TRFAKWRP. WC
OSM YMTV PS CUSXXWRP OSMGTFUC ZSIR, CUSX WR CAJSMG SC OSMG EMTHARZ ARZ
DEWUZ, ARZ RSV WR SXXSTWVWSR VS 'FY. WC W EAZ EAZ ARO HMV A MRRAV'GAU
IWCF, ARZ VEWT XSSG HSO EAZ EAZ ARO HMV A MRRAV'GAU YSVEFG, W YWPEV
EAJF YAZF TSYF YSRFO UATV IFFK WRTVFAZ SC HFWRP DSMRVFG-XGAOFZ ARZ
DSMRVFGYWRFZ ARZ GFUWPWSMTUO DWGDMYIFRVFZ WRVS VEF ISGTV SC UMDK.
H-M-M-MTV YF!” TAWZ YG. DGMRDEFG, IES AUU VEWT VWYF EAZ HFFR XMVVWRP
SR EWT DUSVEFT, “WC W AWR'V, IEAV IWVE XWFVO ARZ SRF HUSIFZ VEWRP ARZ
ARSVEFG, HFFR DESMTFZ VEWT UATV IFFK WRVS AT HAZ UMDK AT FJFG A XSSG
ZFJWU SC A ESRFTV VGAZFTYAR YFV IWVE! OSMRP LFGGO, ZGFTT OSMGTFUC, YO
HSO, ARZ IEWUF W DUFAR YO HSSVT KFFX A FOF MXSR OSMG YSVEFG RSI ARZ
VEFR, ARZ WC OSM TFF ARO TWPRT SC YSGF CUSXXWRP, PWJF YF A DAUU. CSG, W
VFUU OSM,” EFGF EF AZZGFTTFZ EWT IWCF SRDF YSGF, “W ISR'V HF PSRF APWR,
WR VEWT YARRFG. W AY AT GWDKFVO AT A EADKRFO-DSADE, W'Y AT TUFFXO AT
UAMZARMY, YO UWRFT WT TVGAWRFZ VS VEAV ZFPGFF VEAV W TESMUZR'V KRSI, WC
WV IATR'V CSG VEF XAWR WR 'FY, IEWDE IAT YF ARZ IEWDE TSYFHSZO FUTF, OFV
W'Y RSRF VEF HFVVFG CSG WV WR XSDKFV; ARZ WV'T YO TMTXWDWSR VEAV OSM'JF
HFFR AV WV CGSY YSGRWRP VS RWPEV VS XGFJFRV YF CGSY HFWRP VEF HFVVFG CSG
WV WR XSDKFV, ARZ W ISR'V XMV MX IWVE WV, APPFGAIAOVFG, ARZ IEAV ZS OSM
TAO RSI!”

PGSIUWRP, WR AZZWVWSR, TMDE XEGATFT AT “AE! OFT! OSM'GF GFUWPWSMT, VSS.
OSM ISMUZR'V XMV OSMGTFUC WR SXXSTWVWSR VS VEF WRVFGFTVT SC OSMG EMTHARZ
ARZ DEWUZ, ISMUZ OSM? RSV OSM!” ARZ VEGSIWRP SCC SVEFG TAGDATVWD TXAGKT
CGSY VEF IEWGUWRP PGWRZTVSRF SC EWT WRZWPRAVWSR, YG. DGMRDEFG HFVSSK
EWYTFUC VS EWT HSSV-DUFARWRP ARZ EWT PFRFGAU XGFXAGAVWSR CSG HMTWRFTT.
WR VEF YFARVWYF, EWT TSR, IESTF EFAZ IAT PAGRWTEFZ IWVE VFRZFGFG TXWKFT,
ARZ IESTF OSMRP FOFT TVSSZ DUSTF HO SRF ARSVEFG, AT EWT CAVEFG'T ZWZ,
KFXV VEF GFNMWGFZ IAVDE MXSR EWT YSVEFG. EF PGFAVUO ZWTVMGHFZ VEAV XSSG
ISYAR AV WRVFGJAUT, HO ZAGVWRP SMV SC EWT TUFFXWRP DUSTFV, IEFGF EF YAZF
EWT VSWUFV, IWVE A TMXXGFTTFZ DGO SC “OSM AGF PSWRP VS CUSX, YSVEFG.
--EAUUSA, CAVEFG!” ARZ, ACVFG GAWTWRP VEWT CWDVWVWSMT AUAGY, ZAGVWRP WR
APAWR IWVE AR MRZMVWCMU PGWR.

YG. DGMRDEFG'T VFYXFG IAT RSV AV AUU WYXGSJFZ IEFR EF DAYF VS EWT
HGFAKCATV. EF GFTFRVFZ YGT. DGMRDEFG'T TAOWRP PGADF IWVE XAGVWDMUAG
ARWYSTWVO.

“RSI, APPFGAIAOVFG! IEAV AGF OSM MX VS? AV WV APAWR?”

EWT IWCF FQXUAWRFZ VEAV TEF EAZ YFGFUO “ATKFZ A HUFTTWRP.”

“ZSR'V ZS WV!” TAWZ YG. DGMRDEFT USSKWRP AHSMV, AT WC EF GAVEFG FQXFDVFZ
VS TFF VEF USAC ZWTAXXFAG MRZFG VEF FCCWDADO SC EWT IWCF'T XFVWVWSRT. “W
AWR'V A PSWRP VS HF HUFTV SMV SC ESMTF ARZ ESYF. W ISR'V EAJF YO IWVVUFT
HUFTV SCC YO VAHUF. KFFX TVWUU!”

FQDFFZWRPUO GFZ-FOFZ ARZ PGWY, AT WC EF EAZ HFFR MX AUU RWPEV AV A XAGVO
IEWDE EAZ VAKFR AROVEWRP HMV A DSRJWJWAU VMGR, LFGGO DGMRDEFG ISGGWFZ
EWT HGFAKCATV GAVEFG VEAR AVF WV, PGSIUWRP SJFG WV UWKF ARO CSMG-CSSVFZ
WRYAVF SC A YFRAPFGWF. VSIAGZT RWRF S'DUSDK EF TYSSVEFZ EWT GMCCUFZ
ATXFDV, ARZ, XGFTFRVWRP AT GFTXFDVAHUF ARZ HMTWRFTT-UWKF AR FQVFGWSG AT
EF DSMUZ SJFGUAO EWT RAVMGAU TFUC IWVE, WTTMFZ CSGVE VS VEF SDDMXAVWSR
SC VEF ZAO.

WV DSMUZ TDAGDFUO HF DAUUFZ A VGAZF, WR TXWVF SC EWT CAJSMGWVF
ZFTDGWXVWSR SC EWYTFUC AT “A ESRFTV VGAZFTYAR.” EWT TVSDK DSRTWTVFZ SC
A ISSZFR TVSSU, YAZF SMV SC A HGSKFR-HADKFZ DEAWG DMV ZSIR, IEWDE TVSSU,
OSMRP LFGGO, IAUKWRP AV EWT CAVEFG'T TWZF, DAGGWFZ FJFGO YSGRWRP VS
HFRFAVE VEF HARKWRP-ESMTF IWRZSI VEAV IAT RFAGFTV VFYXUF HAG: IEFGF,
IWVE VEF AZZWVWSR SC VEF CWGTV EARZCMU SC TVGAI VEAV DSMUZ HF PUFARFZ
CGSY ARO XATTWRP JFEWDUF VS KFFX VEF DSUZ ARZ IFV CGSY VEF SZZ-LSH-YAR'T
CFFV, WV CSGYFZ VEF FRDAYXYFRV CSG VEF ZAO. SR VEWT XSTV SC EWT, YG.
DGMRDEFG IAT AT IFUU KRSIR VS CUFFV-TVGFFV ARZ VEF VFYXUF, AT VEF HAG
WVTFUC,--ARZ IAT AUYSTV AT WR-USSKWRP.

FRDAYXFZ AV A NMAGVFG HFCSGF RWRF, WR PSSZ VWYF VS VSMDE EWT
VEGFF-DSGRFGFZ EAV VS VEF SUZFTV SC YFR AT VEFO XATTFZ WR VS VFUUTSR'T,
LFGGO VSSK MX EWT TVAVWSR SR VEWT IWRZO YAGDE YSGRWRP, IWVE OSMRP LFGGO
TVARZWRP HO EWY, IEFR RSV FRPAPFZ WR YAKWRP CSGAOT VEGSMPE VEF HAG, VS
WRCUWDV HSZWUO ARZ YFRVAU WRLMGWFT SC AR ADMVF ZFTDGWXVWSR SR XATTWRP
HSOT IES IFGF TYAUU FRSMPE CSG EWT AYWAHUF XMGXSTF. CAVEFG ARZ TSR,
FQVGFYFUO UWKF FADE SVEFG, USSKWRP TWUFRVUO SR AV VEF YSGRWRP VGACCWD
WR CUFFV-TVGFFV, IWVE VEFWG VIS EFAZT AT RFAG VS SRF ARSVEFG AT VEF VIS
FOFT SC FADE IFGF, HSGF A DSRTWZFGAHUF GFTFYHUARDF VS A XAWG SC YSRKFOT.
VEF GFTFYHUARDF IAT RSV UFTTFRFZ HO VEF ADDWZFRVAU DWGDMYTVARDF, VEAV
VEF YAVMGF LFGGO HWV ARZ TXAV SMV TVGAI, IEWUF VEF VIWRKUWRP FOFT SC VEF
OSMVECMU LFGGO IFGF AT GFTVUFTTUO IAVDECMU SC EWY AT SC FJFGOVEWRP FUTF
WR CUFFV-TVGFFV.

VEF EFAZ SC SRF SC VEF GFPMUAG WRZSSG YFTTFRPFGT AVVADEFZ VS VFUUTSR'T
FTVAHUWTEYFRV IAT XMV VEGSMPE VEF ZSSG, ARZ VEF ISGZ IAT PWJFR:

“XSGVFG IARVFZ!”

“ESSGAO, CAVEFG! EFGF'T AR FAGUO LSH VS HFPWR IWVE!”

EAJWRP VEMT PWJFR EWT XAGFRV PSZ TXFFZ, OSMRP LFGGO TFAVFZ EWYTFUC SR
VEF TVSSU, FRVFGFZ SR EWT GFJFGTWSRAGO WRVFGFTV WR VEF TVGAI EWT CAVEFG
EAZ HFFR DEFIWRP, ARZ DSPWVAVFZ.

“AU-IAOT GMTVO! EWT CWRPFGT WT AU-IAOT GMTVO!” YMVVFGFZ OSMRP LFGGO.
“IEFGF ZSFT YO CAVEFG PFV AUU VEAV WGSR GMTV CGSY? EF ZSR'V PFV RS WGSR
GMTV EFGF!”




WW. A TWPEV


“OSM KRSI VEF SUZ HAWUFO IFUU, RS ZSMHV?” TAWZ SRF SC VEF SUZFTV SC
DUFGKT VS LFGGO VEF YFTTFRPFG.

“OF-FT, TWG,” GFVMGRFZ LFGGO, WR TSYFVEWRP SC A ZSPPFZ YARRFG. “W _ZS_
KRSI VEF HAWUFO.”

“LMTV TS. ARZ OSM KRSI YG. USGGO.”

“W KRSI YG. USGGO, TWG, YMDE HFVVFG VEAR W KRSI VEF HAWUFO. YMDE
HFVVFG,” TAWZ LFGGO, RSV MRUWKF A GFUMDVARV IWVRFTT AV VEF FTVAHUWTEYFRV
WR NMFTVWSR, “VEAR W, AT A ESRFTV VGAZFTYAR, IWTE VS KRSI VEF HAWUFO.”

“JFGO IFUU. CWRZ VEF ZSSG IEFGF VEF IWVRFTTFT PS WR, ARZ TESI VEF
ZSSG-KFFXFG VEWT RSVF CSG YG. USGGO. EF IWUU VEFR UFV OSM WR.”

“WRVS VEF DSMGV, TWG?”

“WRVS VEF DSMGV.”

YG. DGMRDEFG'T FOFT TFFYFZ VS PFV A UWVVUF DUSTFG VS SRF ARSVEFG, ARZ VS
WRVFGDEARPF VEF WRNMWGO, “IEAV ZS OSM VEWRK SC VEWT?”

“AY W VS IAWV WR VEF DSMGV, TWG?” EF ATKFZ, AT VEF GFTMUV SC VEAV
DSRCFGFRDF.

“W AY PSWRP VS VFUU OSM. VEF ZSSG-KFFXFG IWUU XATT VEF RSVF VS YG.
USGGO, ARZ ZS OSM YAKF ARO PFTVMGF VEAV IWUU AVVGADV YG. USGGO'T
AVVFRVWSR, ARZ TESI EWY IEFGF OSM TVARZ. VEFR IEAV OSM EAJF VS ZS, WT,
VS GFYAWR VEFGF MRVWU EF IARVT OSM.”

“WT VEAV AUU, TWG?”

“VEAV'T AUU. EF IWTEFT VS EAJF A YFTTFRPFG AV EARZ. VEWT WT VS VFUU EWY
OSM AGF VEFGF.”

AT VEF ARDWFRV DUFGK ZFUWHFGAVFUO CSUZFZ ARZ TMXFGTDGWHFZ VEF RSVF,
YG. DGMRDEFG, ACVFG TMGJFOWRP EWY WR TWUFRDF MRVWU EF DAYF VS VEF
HUSVVWRP-XAXFG TVAPF, GFYAGKFZ:

“W TMXXSTF VEFO'UU HF VGOWRP CSGPFGWFT VEWT YSGRWRP?”

“VGFATSR!”

“VEAV'T NMAGVFGWRP,” TAWZ LFGGO. “HAGHAGSMT!”

“WV WT VEF UAI,” GFYAGKFZ VEF ARDWFRV DUFGK, VMGRWRP EWT TMGXGWTFZ
TXFDVADUFT MXSR EWY. “WV WT VEF UAI.”

“WV'T EAGZ WR VEF UAI VS TXWUF A YAR, W VEWRK. WV'T EAGZ FRSMPE VS KWUU
EWY, HMV WV'T IFGO EAGZ VS TXWUF EWY, TWG.”

“RSV AV AUU,” GFVAWRFZ VEF ARDWFRV DUFGK. “TXFAK IFUU SC VEF UAI. VAKF
DAGF SC OSMG DEFTV ARZ JSWDF, YO PSSZ CGWFRZ, ARZ UFAJF VEF UAI VS VAKF
DAGF SC WVTFUC. W PWJF OSM VEAV AZJWDF.”

“WV'T VEF ZAYX, TWG, IEAV TFVVUFT SR YO DEFTV ARZ JSWDF,” TAWZ LFGGO. “W
UFAJF OSM VS LMZPF IEAV A ZAYX IAO SC FAGRWRP A UWJWRP YWRF WT.”

“IFUU, IFUU,” TAWZ VEF SUZ DUFGK; “IF AUU EAJF SMG JAGWSMT IAOT SC
PAWRWRP A UWJFUWESSZ. TSYF SC MT EAJF ZAYX IAOT, ARZ TSYF SC MT EAJF ZGO
IAOT. EFGF WT VEF UFVVFG. PS AUSRP.”

LFGGO VSSK VEF UFVVFG, ARZ, GFYAGKWRP VS EWYTFUC IWVE UFTT WRVFGRAU
ZFCFGFRDF VEAR EF YAZF AR SMVIAGZ TESI SC, “OSM AGF A UFAR SUZ SRF,
VSS,” YAZF EWT HSI, WRCSGYFZ EWT TSR, WR XATTWRP, SC EWT ZFTVWRAVWSR,
ARZ IFRV EWT IAO.

VEFO EARPFZ AV VOHMGR, WR VESTF ZAOT, TS VEF TVGFFV SMVTWZF RFIPAVF EAZ
RSV SHVAWRFZ SRF WRCAYSMT RSVSGWFVO VEAV EAT TWRDF AVVADEFZ VS WV.
