WR VEF DSCCFF-GSSY SC AR ESVFU WR VEAV PAGGWTSR-ARZ-ZSDKOAGZ VSIR,
IAWVWRP CSG ARSVEFG XFGTSR. VEF XGWTSRFG'T DSMRTFU IAT DGSTT-FQAYWRWRP
