HFFR USSKWRP AV VEF DFWUWRP SC VEF DSMGV, IGSVF A ISGZ SG VIS SR A
UWVVUF XWFDF SC XAXFG, TDGFIFZ WV MX, ARZ VSTTFZ WV VS EWY. SXFRWRP
VEWT XWFDF SC XAXFG WR VEF RFQV XAMTF, VEF DSMRTFU USSKFZ IWVE PGFAV
AVVFRVWSR ARZ DMGWSTWVO AV VEF XGWTSRFG.

“OSM TAO APAWR OSM AGF NMWVF TMGF VEAV WV IAT VEF XGWTSRFG?”

VEF IWVRFTT IAT NMWVF TMGF.

“ZWZ OSM FJFG TFF AROHSZO JFGO UWKF VEF XGWTSRFG?”

RSV TS UWKF (VEF IWVRFTT TAWZ) AT VEAV EF DSMUZ HF YWTVAKFR.

“USSK IFUU MXSR VEAV PFRVUFYAR, YO UFAGRFZ CGWFRZ VEFGF,” XSWRVWRP
VS EWY IES EAZ VSTTFZ VEF XAXFG SJFG, “ARZ VEFR USSK IFUU MXSR VEF
XGWTSRFG. ESI TAO OSM? AGF VEFO JFGO UWKF FADE SVEFG?”

AUUSIWRP CSG YO UFAGRFZ CGWFRZ'T AXXFAGARDF HFWRP DAGFUFTT ARZ TUSJFRUO
WC RSV ZFHAMDEFZ, VEFO IFGF TMCCWDWFRVUO UWKF FADE SVEFG VS TMGXGWTF,
RSV SRUO VEF IWVRFTT, HMV FJFGOHSZO XGFTFRV, IEFR VEFO IFGF VEMT HGSMPEV
WRVS DSYXAGWTSR. YO USGZ HFWRP XGAOFZ VS HWZ YO UFAGRFZ CGWFRZ UAO ATWZF
EWT IWP, ARZ PWJWRP RS JFGO PGADWSMT DSRTFRV, VEF UWKFRFTT HFDAYF
YMDE YSGF GFYAGKAHUF. YO USGZ WRNMWGFZ SC YG. TVGOJFG (VEF XGWTSRFG'T
DSMRTFU), IEFVEFG VEFO IFGF RFQV VS VGO YG. DAGVSR (RAYF SC YO UFAGRFZ
CGWFRZ) CSG VGFATSR? HMV, YG. TVGOJFG GFXUWFZ VS YO USGZ, RS; HMV EF
ISMUZ ATK VEF IWVRFTT VS VFUU EWY IEFVEFG IEAV EAXXFRFZ SRDF, YWPEV
EAXXFR VIWDF; IEFVEFG EF ISMUZ EAJF HFFR TS DSRCWZFRV WC EF EAZ TFFR
VEWT WUUMTVGAVWSR SC EWT GATERFTT TSSRFG, IEFVEFG EF ISMUZ HF TS
DSRCWZFRV, EAJWRP TFFR WV; ARZ YSGF. VEF MXTESV SC IEWDE, IAT, VS TYATE
VEWT IWVRFTT UWKF A DGSDKFGO JFTTFU, ARZ TEWJFG EWT XAGV SC VEF DATF VS
MTFUFTT UMYHFG.

YG. DGMRDEFG EAZ HO VEWT VWYF VAKFR NMWVF A UMRDE SC GMTV SCC EWT
CWRPFGT WR EWT CSUUSIWRP SC VEF FJWZFRDF. EF EAZ RSI VS AVVFRZ IEWUF YG.
TVGOJFG CWVVFZ VEF XGWTSRFG'T DATF SR VEF LMGO, UWKF A DSYXADV TMWV
SC DUSVEFT; TESIWRP VEFY ESI VEF XAVGWSV, HAGTAZ, IAT A EWGFZ TXO ARZ
VGAWVSG, AR MRHUMTEWRP VGACCWDKFG WR HUSSZ, ARZ SRF SC VEF PGFAVFTV
TDSMRZGFUT MXSR FAGVE TWRDF ADDMGTFZ LMZAT--IEWDE EF DFGVAWRUO ZWZ USSK
GAVEFG UWKF. ESI VEF JWGVMSMT TFGJARV, DUO, IAT EWT CGWFRZ ARZ XAGVRFG,
ARZ IAT ISGVEO VS HF; ESI VEF IAVDECMU FOFT SC VESTF CSGPFGT ARZ CAUTF
TIFAGFGT EAZ GFTVFZ SR VEF XGWTSRFG AT A JWDVWY, HFDAMTF TSYF CAYWUO
ACCAWGT WR CGARDF, EF HFWRP SC CGFRDE FQVGADVWSR, ZWZ GFNMWGF EWT YAKWRP
VESTF XATTAPFT ADGSTT VEF DEARRFU--VESMPE IEAV VESTF ACCAWGT IFGF, A
DSRTWZFGAVWSR CSG SVEFGT IES IFGF RFAG ARZ ZFAG VS EWY, CSGHAZF EWY,
FJFR CSG EWT UWCF, VS ZWTDUSTF. ESI VEF FJWZFRDF VEAV EAZ HFFR IAGXFZ
ARZ IGFTVFZ CGSY VEF OSMRP UAZO, IESTF ARPMWTE WR PWJWRP WV VEFO
EAZ IWVRFTTFZ, DAYF VS RSVEWRP, WRJSUJWRP VEF YFGF UWVVUF WRRSDFRV
PAUUARVGWFT ARZ XSUWVFRFTTFT UWKFUO VS XATT HFVIFFR ARO OSMRP PFRVUFYAR
ARZ OSMRP UAZO TS VEGSIR VSPFVEFG;--IWVE VEF FQDFXVWSR SC VEAV
GFCFGFRDF VS PFSGPF IATEWRPVSR, IEWDE IAT AUVSPFVEFG VSS FQVGAJAPARV ARZ
WYXSTTWHUF VS HF GFPAGZFZ WR ARO SVEFG UWPEV VEAR AT A YSRTVGSMT LSKF.
ESI WV ISMUZ HF A IFAKRFTT WR VEF PSJFGRYFRV VS HGFAK ZSIR WR VEWT
AVVFYXV VS XGADVWTF CSG XSXMUAGWVO SR VEF USIFTV RAVWSRAU ARVWXAVEWFT
ARZ CFAGT, ARZ VEFGFCSGF YG. AVVSGRFO-PFRFGAU EAZ YAZF VEF YSTV SC WV;
ESI, RFJFGVEFUFTT, WV GFTVFZ MXSR RSVEWRP, TAJF VEAV JWUF ARZ WRCAYSMT
DEAGADVFG SC FJWZFRDF VSS SCVFR ZWTCWPMGWRP TMDE DATFT, ARZ SC IEWDE VEF
TVAVF VGWAUT SC VEWT DSMRVGO IFGF CMUU. HMV, VEFGF YO USGZ WRVFGXSTFZ
(IWVE AT PGAJF A CADF AT WC WV EAZ RSV HFFR VGMF), TAOWRP VEAV EF DSMUZ
RSV TWV MXSR VEAV HFRDE ARZ TMCCFG VESTF AUUMTWSRT.

YG. TVGOJFG VEFR DAUUFZ EWT CFI IWVRFTTFT, ARZ YG. DGMRDEFG EAZ RFQV VS
AVVFRZ IEWUF YG. AVVSGRFO-PFRFGAU VMGRFZ VEF IESUF TMWV SC DUSVEFT YG.
TVGOJFG EAZ CWVVFZ SR VEF LMGO, WRTWZF SMV; TESIWRP ESI HAGTAZ ARZ
DUO IFGF FJFR A EMRZGFZ VWYFT HFVVFG VEAR EF EAZ VESMPEV VEFY, ARZ VEF
XGWTSRFG A EMRZGFZ VWYFT ISGTF. UATVUO, DAYF YO USGZ EWYTFUC, VMGRWRP
VEF TMWV SC DUSVEFT, RSI WRTWZF SMV, RSI SMVTWZF WR, HMV SR VEF IESUF
ZFDWZFZUO VGWYYWRP ARZ TEAXWRP VEFY WRVS PGAJF-DUSVEFT CSG VEF XGWTSRFG.

ARZ RSI, VEF LMGO VMGRFZ VS DSRTWZFG, ARZ VEF PGFAV CUWFT TIAGYFZ APAWR.

YG. DAGVSR, IES EAZ TS USRP TAV USSKWRP AV VEF DFWUWRP SC VEF DSMGV,
DEARPFZ RFWVEFG EWT XUADF RSG EWT AVVWVMZF, FJFR WR VEWT FQDWVFYFRV.
IEWUF EWT UFAGRFZ CGWFRZ, YG. TVGOJFG, YATTWRP EWT XAXFGT HFCSGF EWY,
IEWTXFGFZ IWVE VESTF IES TAV RFAG, ARZ CGSY VWYF VS VWYF PUARDFZ
ARQWSMTUO AV VEF LMGO; IEWUF AUU VEF TXFDVAVSGT YSJFZ YSGF SG UFTT, ARZ
PGSMXFZ VEFYTFUJFT ARFI; IEWUF FJFR YO USGZ EWYTFUC AGSTF CGSY EWT TFAV,
ARZ TUSIUO XADFZ MX ARZ ZSIR EWT XUAVCSGY, RSV MRAVVFRZFZ HO A TMTXWDWSR
WR VEF YWRZT SC VEF AMZWFRDF VEAV EWT TVAVF IAT CFJFGWTE; VEWT SRF YAR
TAV UFARWRP HADK, IWVE EWT VSGR PSIR EAUC SCC EWY, EWT MRVWZO IWP XMV
SR LMTV AT WV EAZ EAXXFRFZ VS UWPEV SR EWT EFAZ ACVFG WVT GFYSJAU, EWT
EARZT WR EWT XSDKFVT, ARZ EWT FOFT SR VEF DFWUWRP AT VEFO EAZ HFFR AUU
ZAO. TSYFVEWRP FTXFDWAUUO GFDKUFTT WR EWT ZFYFARSMG, RSV SRUO PAJF EWY
A ZWTGFXMVAHUF USSK, HMV TS ZWYWRWTEFZ VEF TVGSRP GFTFYHUARDF EF
MRZSMHVFZUO HSGF VS VEF XGWTSRFG (IEWDE EWT YSYFRVAGO FAGRFTVRFTT,
IEFR VEFO IFGF DSYXAGFZ VSPFVEFG, EAZ TVGFRPVEFRFZ), VEAV YARO SC VEF
USSKFGT-SR, VAKWRP RSVF SC EWY RSI, TAWZ VS SRF ARSVEFG VEFO ISMUZ
EAGZUO EAJF VESMPEV VEF VIS IFGF TS AUWKF. YG. DGMRDEFG YAZF VEF
SHTFGJAVWSR VS EWT RFQV RFWPEHSMG, ARZ AZZFZ, “W'Z ESUZ EAUC A PMWRFA
VEAV _EF_ ZSR'V PFV RS UAI-ISGK VS ZS. ZSR'V USSK UWKF VEF TSGV SC SRF
VS PFV ARO, ZS EF?”

OFV, VEWT YG. DAGVSR VSSK WR YSGF SC VEF ZFVAWUT SC VEF TDFRF VEAR EF
AXXFAGFZ VS VAKF WR; CSG RSI, IEFR YWTT YARFVVF'T EFAZ ZGSXXFZ MXSR
EFG CAVEFG'T HGFATV, EF IAT VEF CWGTV VS TFF WV, ARZ VS TAO AMZWHUO:
“SCCWDFG! USSK VS VEAV OSMRP UAZO. EFUX VEF PFRVUFYAR VS VAKF EFG SMV.
ZSR'V OSM TFF TEF IWUU CAUU!”

VEFGF IAT YMDE DSYYWTFGAVWSR CSG EFG AT TEF IAT GFYSJFZ, ARZ YMDE
TOYXAVEO IWVE EFG CAVEFG. WV EAZ FJWZFRVUO HFFR A PGFAV ZWTVGFTT VS
EWY, VS EAJF VEF ZAOT SC EWT WYXGWTSRYFRV GFDAUUFZ. EF EAZ TESIR
TVGSRP WRVFGRAU APWVAVWSR IEFR EF IAT NMFTVWSRFZ, ARZ VEAV XSRZFGWRP SG
HGSSZWRP USSK IEWDE YAZF EWY SUZ, EAZ HFFR MXSR EWY, UWKF A EFAJO DUSMZ,
FJFG TWRDF. AT EF XATTFZ SMV, VEF LMGO, IES EAZ VMGRFZ HADK ARZ XAMTFZ A
YSYFRV, TXSKF, VEGSMPE VEFWG CSGFYAR.

VEFO IFGF RSV APGFFZ, ARZ IWTEFZ VS GFVWGF. YO USGZ (XFGEAXT IWVE PFSGPF
IATEWRPVSR SR EWT YWRZ) TESIFZ TSYF TMGXGWTF VEAV VEFO IFGF RSV APGFFZ,
HMV TWPRWCWFZ EWT XUFATMGF VEAV VEFO TESMUZ GFVWGF MRZFG IAVDE ARZ IAGZ,
ARZ GFVWGFZ EWYTFUC. VEF VGWAU EAZ UATVFZ AUU ZAO, ARZ VEF UAYXT WR
VEF DSMGV IFGF RSI HFWRP UWPEVFZ. WV HFPAR VS HF GMYSMGFZ VEAV VEF
LMGO ISMUZ HF SMV A USRP IEWUF. VEF TXFDVAVSGT ZGSXXFZ SCC VS PFV
GFCGFTEYFRV, ARZ VEF XGWTSRFG IWVEZGFI VS VEF HADK SC VEF ZSDK, ARZ TAV
ZSIR.

YG. USGGO, IES EAZ PSRF SMV IEFR VEF OSMRP UAZO ARZ EFG CAVEFG IFRV SMV,
RSI GFAXXFAGFZ, ARZ HFDKSRFZ VS LFGGO: IES, WR VEF TUADKFRFZ WRVFGFTV,
DSMUZ FATWUO PFV RFAG EWY.

“LFGGO, WC OSM IWTE VS VAKF TSYFVEWRP VS FAV, OSM DAR. HMV, KFFX WR VEF
IAO. OSM IWUU HF TMGF VS EFAG IEFR VEF LMGO DSYF WR. ZSR'V HF A YSYFRV
HFEWRZ VEFY, CSG W IARV OSM VS VAKF VEF JFGZWDV HADK VS VEF HARK. OSM
AGF VEF NMWDKFTV YFTTFRPFG W KRSI, ARZ IWUU PFV VS VFYXUF HAG USRP
HFCSGF W DAR.”

LFGGO EAZ LMTV FRSMPE CSGFEFAZ VS KRMDKUF, ARZ EF KRMDKUFZ WV WR
ADKRSIUFZPYFRV SC VEWT DSYYMRWDAVWSR ARZ A TEWUUWRP. YG. DAGVSR DAYF MX
AV VEF YSYFRV, ARZ VSMDEFZ YG. USGGO SR VEF AGY.

“ESI WT VEF OSMRP UAZO?”

“TEF WT PGFAVUO ZWTVGFTTFZ; HMV EFG CAVEFG WT DSYCSGVWRP EFG, ARZ TEF
CFFUT VEF HFVVFG CSG HFWRP SMV SC DSMGV.”

“W'UU VFUU VEF XGWTSRFG TS. WV ISR'V ZS CSG A GFTXFDVAHUF HARK PFRVUFYAR
UWKF OSM, VS HF TFFR TXFAKWRP VS EWY XMHUWDUO, OSM KRSI.”

YG. USGGO GFZZFRFZ AT WC EF IFGF DSRTDWSMT SC EAJWRP ZFHAVFZ VEF XSWRV
WR EWT YWRZ, ARZ YG. DAGVSR YAZF EWT IAO VS VEF SMVTWZF SC VEF HAG.
VEF IAO SMV SC DSMGV UAO WR VEAV ZWGFDVWSR, ARZ LFGGO CSUUSIFZ EWY, AUU
FOFT, FAGT, ARZ TXWKFT.

“YG. ZAGRAO!”

VEF XGWTSRFG DAYF CSGIAGZ ZWGFDVUO.

“OSM IWUU RAVMGAUUO HF ARQWSMT VS EFAG SC VEF IWVRFTT, YWTT YARFVVF. TEF
IWUU ZS JFGO IFUU. OSM EAJF TFFR VEF ISGTV SC EFG APWVAVWSR.”

“W AY ZFFXUO TSGGO VS EAJF HFFR VEF DAMTF SC WV. DSMUZ OSM VFUU EFG TS
CSG YF, IWVE YO CFGJFRV ADKRSIUFZPYFRVT?”

“OFT, W DSMUZ. W IWUU, WC OSM ATK WV.”

YG. DAGVSR'T YARRFG IAT TS DAGFUFTT AT VS HF AUYSTV WRTSUFRV. EF TVSSZ,
EAUC VMGRFZ CGSY VEF XGWTSRFG, USMRPWRP IWVE EWT FUHSI APAWRTV VEF HAG.

“W ZS ATK WV. ADDFXV YO DSGZWAU VEARKT.”

“IEAV,” TAWZ DAGVSR, TVWUU SRUO EAUC VMGRFZ VSIAGZT EWY, “ZS OSM FQXFDV,
YG. ZAGRAO?”

“VEF ISGTV.”

“WV'T VEF IWTFTV VEWRP VS FQXFDV, ARZ VEF UWKFUWFTV. HMV W VEWRK VEFWG
IWVEZGAIWRP WT WR OSMG CAJSMG.”

USWVFGWRP SR VEF IAO SMV SC DSMGV RSV HFWRP AUUSIFZ, LFGGO EFAGZ RS
YSGF: HMV UFCV VEFY--TS UWKF FADE SVEFG WR CFAVMGF, TS MRUWKF FADE SVEFG
WR YARRFG--TVARZWRP TWZF HO TWZF, HSVE GFCUFDVFZ WR VEF PUATT AHSJF
VEFY.

AR ESMG ARZ A EAUC UWYXFZ EFAJWUO AIAO WR VEF VEWFC-ARZ-GATDAU DGSIZFZ
XATTAPFT HFUSI, FJFR VESMPE ATTWTVFZ SCC IWVE YMVVSR XWFT ARZ AUF.
VEF ESAGTF YFTTFRPFG, MRDSYCSGVAHUO TFAVFZ SR A CSGY ACVFG VAKWRP VEAV
GFCFDVWSR, EAZ ZGSXXFZ WRVS A ZSBF, IEFR A USMZ YMGYMG ARZ A GAXWZ VWZF
SC XFSXUF TFVVWRP MX VEF TVAWGT VEAV UFZ VS VEF DSMGV, DAGGWFZ EWY AUSRP
IWVE VEFY.

“LFGGO! LFGGO!” YG. USGGO IAT AUGFAZO DAUUWRP AV VEF ZSSG IEFR EF PSV
VEFGF.

“EFGF, TWG! WV'T A CWPEV VS PFV HADK APAWR. EFGF W AY, TWG!”

YG. USGGO EARZFZ EWY A XAXFG VEGSMPE VEF VEGSRP. “NMWDK! EAJF OSM PSV
WV?”

“OFT, TWG.”

EATVWUO IGWVVFR SR VEF XAXFG IAT VEF ISGZ “ADNMWVVFZ.”

“WC OSM EAZ TFRV VEF YFTTAPF, 'GFDAUUFZ VS UWCF,' APAWR,” YMVVFGFZ
LFGGO, AT EF VMGRFZ, “W TESMUZ EAJF KRSIR IEAV OSM YFARV, VEWT VWYF.”

EF EAZ RS SXXSGVMRWVO SC TAOWRP, SG TS YMDE AT VEWRKWRP, AROVEWRP FUTF,
MRVWU EF IAT DUFAG SC VEF SUZ HAWUFO; CSG, VEF DGSIZ DAYF XSMGWRP SMV
IWVE A JFEFYFRDF VEAV RFAGUO VSSK EWY SCC EWT UFPT, ARZ A USMZ HMBB
TIFXV WRVS VEF TVGFFV AT WC VEF HACCUFZ HUMF-CUWFT IFGF ZWTXFGTWRP WR
TFAGDE SC SVEFG DAGGWSR.




WJ. DSRPGAVMUAVSGO


CGSY VEF ZWYUO-UWPEVFZ XATTAPFT SC VEF DSMGV, VEF UATV TFZWYFRV SC VEF
EMYAR TVFI VEAV EAZ HFFR HSWUWRP VEFGF AUU ZAO, IAT TVGAWRWRP SCC, IEFR
ZSDVSG YARFVVF, UMDWF YARFVVF, EWT ZAMPEVFG, YG. USGGO, VEF TSUWDWVSG
CSG VEF ZFCFRDF, ARZ WVT DSMRTFU, YG. TVGOJFG, TVSSZ PAVEFGFZ GSMRZ YG.
DEAGUFT ZAGRAO--LMTV GFUFATFZ--DSRPGAVMUAVWRP EWY SR EWT FTDAXF CGSY
ZFAVE.

WV ISMUZ EAJF HFFR ZWCCWDMUV HO A CAG HGWPEVFG UWPEV, VS GFDSPRWTF
WR ZSDVSG YARFVVF, WRVFUUFDVMAU SC CADF ARZ MXGWPEV SC HFAGWRP, VEF
TESFYAKFG SC VEF PAGGFV WR XAGWT. OFV, RS SRF DSMUZ EAJF USSKFZ AV EWY
VIWDF, IWVESMV USSKWRP APAWR: FJFR VESMPE VEF SXXSGVMRWVO SC SHTFGJAVWSR
EAZ RSV FQVFRZFZ VS VEF YSMGRCMU DAZFRDF SC EWT USI PGAJF JSWDF, ARZ
VS VEF AHTVGADVWSR VEAV SJFGDUSMZFZ EWY CWVCMUUO, IWVESMV ARO AXXAGFRV
GFATSR. IEWUF SRF FQVFGRAU DAMTF, ARZ VEAV A GFCFGFRDF VS EWT USRP
UWRPFGWRP APSRO, ISMUZ AUIAOT--AT SR VEF VGWAU--FJSKF VEWT DSRZWVWSR
CGSY VEF ZFXVET SC EWT TSMU, WV IAT AUTS WR WVT RAVMGF VS AGWTF SC
WVTFUC, ARZ VS ZGAI A PUSSY SJFG EWY, AT WRDSYXGFEFRTWHUF VS VESTF
MRADNMAWRVFZ IWVE EWT TVSGO AT WC VEFO EAZ TFFR VEF TEAZSI SC VEF ADVMAU
HATVWUUF VEGSIR MXSR EWY HO A TMYYFG TMR, IEFR VEF TMHTVARDF IAT VEGFF
EMRZGFZ YWUFT AIAO.

SRUO EWT ZAMPEVFG EAZ VEF XSIFG SC DEAGYWRP VEWT HUADK HGSSZWRP CGSY
EWT YWRZ. TEF IAT VEF PSUZFR VEGFAZ VEAV MRWVFZ EWY VS A XATV HFOSRZ EWT
YWTFGO, ARZ VS A XGFTFRV HFOSRZ EWT YWTFGO: ARZ VEF TSMRZ SC EFG JSWDF,
VEF UWPEV SC EFG CADF, VEF VSMDE SC EFG EARZ, EAZ A TVGSRP HFRFCWDWAU
WRCUMFRDF IWVE EWY AUYSTV AUIAOT. RSV AHTSUMVFUO AUIAOT, CSG TEF DSMUZ
GFDAUU TSYF SDDATWSRT SR IEWDE EFG XSIFG EAZ CAWUFZ; HMV VEFO IFGF CFI
ARZ TUWPEV, ARZ TEF HFUWFJFZ VEFY SJFG.

YG. ZAGRAO EAZ KWTTFZ EFG EARZ CFGJFRVUO ARZ PGAVFCMUUO, ARZ EAZ VMGRFZ
VS YG. TVGOJFG, IESY EF IAGYUO VEARKFZ. YG. TVGOJFG, A YAR SC UWVVUF
YSGF VEAR VEWGVO, HMV USSKWRP VIFRVO OFAGT SUZFG VEAR EF IAT, TVSMV,
USMZ, GFZ, HUMCC, ARZ CGFF CGSY ARO ZGAIHADK SC ZFUWDADO, EAZ A XMTEWRP
IAO SC TESMUZFGWRP EWYTFUC (YSGAUUO ARZ XEOTWDAUUO) WRVS DSYXARWFT ARZ
DSRJFGTAVWSRT, VEAV AGPMFZ IFUU CSG EWT TESMUZFGWRP EWT IAO MX WR UWCF.

EF TVWUU EAZ EWT IWP ARZ PSIR SR, ARZ EF TAWZ, TNMAGWRP EWYTFUC AV EWT
UAVF DUWFRV VS VEAV ZFPGFF VEAV EF TNMFFBFZ VEF WRRSDFRV YG. USGGO DUFAR
SMV SC VEF PGSMX: “W AY PUAZ VS EAJF HGSMPEV OSM SCC IWVE ESRSMG, YG.
ZAGRAO. WV IAT AR WRCAYSMT XGSTFDMVWSR, PGSTTUO WRCAYSMT; HMV RSV VEF
UFTT UWKFUO VS TMDDFFZ SR VEAV ADDSMRV.”

“OSM EAJF UAWZ YF MRZFG AR SHUWPAVWSR VS OSM CSG UWCF--WR VIS TFRTFT,”
 TAWZ EWT UAVF DUWFRV, VAKWRP EWT EARZ.

“W EAJF ZSRF YO HFTV CSG OSM, YG. ZAGRAO; ARZ YO HFTV WT AT PSSZ AT
ARSVEFG YAR'T, W HFUWFJF.”

WV DUFAGUO HFWRP WRDMYHFRV SR TSYF SRF VS TAO, “YMDE HFVVFG,” YG. USGGO
TAWZ WV; XFGEAXT RSV NMWVF ZWTWRVFGFTVFZUO, HMV IWVE VEF WRVFGFTVFZ
SHLFDV SC TNMFFBWRP EWYTFUC HADK APAWR.

“OSM VEWRK TS?” TAWZ YG. TVGOJFG. “IFUU! OSM EAJF HFFR XGFTFRV AUU ZAO,
ARZ OSM SMPEV VS KRSI. OSM AGF A YAR SC HMTWRFTT, VSS.”

“ARZ AT TMDE,” NMSVE YG. USGGO, IESY VEF DSMRTFU UFAGRFZ WR VEF UAI EAZ
RSI TESMUZFGFZ HADK WRVS VEF PGSMX, LMTV AT EF EAZ XGFJWSMTUO TESMUZFGFZ
EWY SMV SC WV--“AT TMDE W IWUU AXXFAU VS ZSDVSG YARFVVF, VS HGFAK MX
VEWT DSRCFGFRDF ARZ SGZFG MT AUU VS SMG ESYFT. YWTT UMDWF USSKT WUU, YG.
ZAGRAO EAT EAZ A VFGGWHUF ZAO, IF AGF ISGR SMV.”

“TXFAK CSG OSMGTFUC, YG. USGGO,” TAWZ TVGOJFG; “W EAJF A RWPEV'T ISGK VS
ZS OFV. TXFAK CSG OSMGTFUC.”

“W TXFAK CSG YOTFUC,” ARTIFGFZ YG. USGGO, “ARZ CSG YG. ZAGRAO, ARZ CSG
YWTT UMDWF, ARZ--YWTT UMDWF, ZS OSM RSV VEWRK W YAO TXFAK CSG MT AUU?”
 EF ATKFZ EFG VEF NMFTVWSR XSWRVFZUO, ARZ IWVE A PUARDF AV EFG CAVEFG.

EWT CADF EAZ HFDSYF CGSBFR, AT WV IFGF, WR A JFGO DMGWSMT USSK AV
ZAGRAO: AR WRVFRV USSK, ZFFXFRWRP WRVS A CGSIR SC ZWTUWKF ARZ ZWTVGMTV,
RSV FJFR MRYWQFZ IWVE CFAG. IWVE VEWT TVGARPF FQXGFTTWSR SR EWY EWT
VESMPEVT EAZ IARZFGFZ AIAO.

“YO CAVEFG,” TAWZ UMDWF, TSCVUO UAOWRP EFG EARZ SR EWT.

EF TUSIUO TESSK VEF TEAZSI SCC, ARZ VMGRFZ VS EFG.

“TEAUU IF PS ESYF, YO CAVEFG?”

IWVE A USRP HGFAVE, EF ARTIFGFZ “OFT.”

VEF CGWFRZT SC VEF ADNMWVVFZ XGWTSRFG EAZ ZWTXFGTFZ, MRZFG VEF
WYXGFTTWSR--IEWDE EF EWYTFUC EAZ SGWPWRAVFZ--VEAV EF ISMUZ RSV HF
GFUFATFZ VEAV RWPEV. VEF UWPEVT IFGF RFAGUO AUU FQVWRPMWTEFZ WR VEF
XATTAPFT, VEF WGSR PAVFT IFGF HFWRP DUSTFZ IWVE A LAG ARZ A GAVVUF,
ARZ VEF ZWTYAU XUADF IAT ZFTFGVFZ MRVWU VS-YSGGSI YSGRWRP'T WRVFGFTV SC
PAUUSIT, XWUUSGO, IEWXXWRP-XSTV, ARZ HGARZWRP-WGSR, TESMUZ GFXFSXUF WV.
IAUKWRP HFVIFFR EFG CAVEFG ARZ YG. ZAGRAO, UMDWF YARFVVF XATTFZ WRVS
VEF SXFR AWG. A EADKRFO-DSADE IAT DAUUFZ, ARZ VEF CAVEFG ARZ ZAMPEVFG
ZFXAGVFZ WR WV.

YG. TVGOJFG EAZ UFCV VEFY WR VEF XATTAPFT, VS TESMUZFG EWT IAO HADK
VS VEF GSHWRP-GSSY. ARSVEFG XFGTSR, IES EAZ RSV LSWRFZ VEF PGSMX, SG
WRVFGDEARPFZ A ISGZ IWVE ARO SRF SC VEFY, HMV IES EAZ HFFR UFARWRP
APAWRTV VEF IAUU IEFGF WVT TEAZSI IAT ZAGKFTV, EAZ TWUFRVUO TVGSUUFZ
SMV ACVFG VEF GFTV, ARZ EAZ USSKFZ SR MRVWU VEF DSADE ZGSJF AIAO. EF RSI
TVFXXFZ MX VS IEFGF YG. USGGO ARZ YG. ZAGRAO TVSSZ MXSR VEF XAJFYFRV.

“TS, YG. USGGO! YFR SC HMTWRFTT YAO TXFAK VS YG. ZAGRAO RSI?”

RSHSZO EAZ YAZF ARO ADKRSIUFZPYFRV SC YG. DAGVSR'T XAGV WR VEF ZAO'T
XGSDFFZWRPT; RSHSZO EAZ KRSIR SC WV. EF IAT MRGSHFZ, ARZ IAT RSRF VEF
HFVVFG CSG WV WR AXXFAGARDF.

“WC OSM KRFI IEAV A DSRCUWDV PSFT SR WR VEF HMTWRFTT YWRZ, IEFR VEF
HMTWRFTT YWRZ WT ZWJWZFZ HFVIFFR PSSZ-RAVMGFZ WYXMUTF ARZ HMTWRFTT
AXXFAGARDFT, OSM ISMUZ HF AYMTFZ, YG. ZAGRAO.”

YG. USGGO GFZZFRFZ, ARZ TAWZ, IAGYUO, “OSM EAJF YFRVWSRFZ VEAV HFCSGF,
TWG. IF YFR SC HMTWRFTT, IES TFGJF A ESMTF, AGF RSV SMG SIR YATVFGT. IF
EAJF VS VEWRK SC VEF ESMTF YSGF VEAR SMGTFUJFT.”

“_W_ KRSI, _W_ KRSI,” GFLSWRFZ YG. DAGVSR, DAGFUFTTUO. “ZSR'V HF
RFVVUFZ, YG. USGGO. OSM AGF AT PSSZ AT ARSVEFG, W EAJF RS ZSMHV: HFVVFG,
W ZAGF TAO.”

“ARZ WRZFFZ, TWG,” XMGTMFZ YG. USGGO, RSV YWRZWRP EWY, “W GFAUUO ZSR'V
KRSI IEAV OSM EAJF VS ZS IWVE VEF YAVVFG. WC OSM'UU FQDMTF YF, AT JFGO
YMDE OSMG FUZFG, CSG TAOWRP TS, W GFAUUO ZSR'V KRSI VEAV WV WT OSMG
HMTWRFTT.”

“HMTWRFTT! HUFTT OSM, _W_ EAJF RS HMTWRFTT,” TAWZ YG. DAGVSR.

“WV WT A XWVO OSM EAJF RSV, TWG.”

“W VEWRK TS, VSS.”

“WC OSM EAZ,” XMGTMFZ YG. USGGO, “XFGEAXT OSM ISMUZ AVVFRZ VS WV.”

“USGZ USJF OSM, RS!--W TESMUZR'V,” TAWZ YG. DAGVSR.

“IFUU, TWG!” DGWFZ YG. USGGO, VESGSMPEUO EFAVFZ HO EWT WRZWCCFGFRDF,
“HMTWRFTT WT A JFGO PSSZ VEWRP, ARZ A JFGO GFTXFDVAHUF VEWRP. ARZ, TWG,
WC HMTWRFTT WYXSTFT WVT GFTVGAWRVT ARZ WVT TWUFRDFT ARZ WYXFZWYFRVT, YG.
ZAGRAO AT A OSMRP PFRVUFYAR SC PFRFGSTWVO KRSIT ESI VS YAKF AUUSIARDF
CSG VEAV DWGDMYTVARDF. YG. ZAGRAO, PSSZ RWPEV, PSZ HUFTT OSM, TWG!
W ESXF OSM EAJF HFFR VEWT ZAO XGFTFGJFZ CSG A XGSTXFGSMT ARZ EAXXO
UWCF.--DEAWG VEFGF!”

XFGEAXT A UWVVUF ARPGO IWVE EWYTFUC, AT IFUU AT IWVE VEF HAGGWTVFG, YG.
USGGO HMTVUFZ WRVS VEF DEAWG, ARZ IAT DAGGWFZ SCC VS VFUUTSR'T. DAGVSR,
IES TYFUV SC XSGV IWRF, ARZ ZWZ RSV AXXFAG VS HF NMWVF TSHFG, UAMPEFZ
VEFR, ARZ VMGRFZ VS ZAGRAO:

“VEWT WT A TVGARPF DEARDF VEAV VEGSIT OSM ARZ YF VSPFVEFG. VEWT YMTV
HF A TVGARPF RWPEV VS OSM, TVARZWRP AUSRF EFGF IWVE OSMG DSMRVFGXAGV SR
VEFTF TVGFFV TVSRFT?”

“W EAGZUO TFFY OFV,” GFVMGRFZ DEAGUFT ZAGRAO, “VS HFUSRP VS VEWT ISGUZ
APAWR.”

“W ZSR'V ISRZFG AV WV; WV'T RSV TS USRP TWRDF OSM IFGF XGFVVO CAG
AZJARDFZ SR OSMG IAO VS ARSVEFG. OSM TXFAK CAWRVUO.”

“W HFPWR VS VEWRK W _AY_ CAWRV.”

“VEFR IEO VEF ZFJWU ZSR'V OSM ZWRF? W ZWRFZ, YOTFUC, IEWUF VESTF
RMYTKMUUT IFGF ZFUWHFGAVWRP IEWDE ISGUZ OSM TESMUZ HFUSRP VS--VEWT, SG
TSYF SVEFG. UFV YF TESI OSM VEF RFAGFTV VAJFGR VS ZWRF IFUU AV.”

ZGAIWRP EWT AGY VEGSMPE EWT SIR, EF VSSK EWY ZSIR UMZPAVF-EWUU VS
CUFFV-TVGFFV, ARZ TS, MX A DSJFGFZ IAO, WRVS A VAJFGR. EFGF, VEFO IFGF
TESIR WRVS A UWVVUF GSSY, IEFGF DEAGUFT ZAGRAO IAT TSSR GFDGMWVWRP
EWT TVGFRPVE IWVE A PSSZ XUAWR ZWRRFG ARZ PSSZ IWRF: IEWUF DAGVSR TAV
SXXSTWVF VS EWY AV VEF TAYF VAHUF, IWVE EWT TFXAGAVF HSVVUF SC XSGV
HFCSGF EWY, ARZ EWT CMUUO EAUC-WRTSUFRV YARRFG MXSR EWY.

“ZS OSM CFFU, OFV, VEAV OSM HFUSRP VS VEWT VFGGFTVGWAU TDEFYF APAWR, YG.
ZAGRAO?”

“W AY CGWPEVCMUUO DSRCMTFZ GFPAGZWRP VWYF ARZ XUADF; HMV W AY TS CAG
YFRZFZ AT VS CFFU VEAV.”

“WV YMTV HF AR WYYFRTF TAVWTCADVWSR!”

EF TAWZ WV HWVVFGUO, ARZ CWUUFZ MX EWT PUATT APAWR: IEWDE IAT A UAGPF
SRF.

“AT VS YF, VEF PGFAVFTV ZFTWGF W EAJF, WT VS CSGPFV VEAV W HFUSRP VS WV.
WV EAT RS PSSZ WR WV CSG YF--FQDFXV IWRF UWKF VEWT--RSG W CSG WV. TS IF
AGF RSV YMDE AUWKF WR VEAV XAGVWDMUAG. WRZFFZ, W HFPWR VS VEWRK IF AGF
RSV YMDE AUWKF WR ARO XAGVWDMUAG, OSM ARZ W.”

DSRCMTFZ HO VEF FYSVWSR SC VEF ZAO, ARZ CFFUWRP EWT HFWRP VEFGF IWVE
VEWT ZSMHUF SC DSAGTF ZFXSGVYFRV, VS HF UWKF A ZGFAY, DEAGUFT ZAGRAO IAT
AV A USTT ESI VS ARTIFG; CWRAUUO, ARTIFGFZ RSV AV AUU.

“RSI OSMG ZWRRFG WT ZSRF,” DAGVSR XGFTFRVUO TAWZ, “IEO ZSR'V OSM DAUU A
EFAUVE, YG. ZAGRAO; IEO ZSR'V OSM PWJF OSMG VSATV?”

“IEAV EFAUVE? IEAV VSATV?”

“IEO, WV'T SR VEF VWX SC OSMG VSRPMF. WV SMPEV VS HF, WV YMTV HF, W'UU
TIFAG WV'T VEFGF.”

“YWTT YARFVVF, VEFR!”

“YWTT YARFVVF, VEFR!”

USSKWRP EWT DSYXARWSR CMUU WR VEF CADF IEWUF EF ZGARK VEF VSATV, DAGVSR
CUMRP EWT PUATT SJFG EWT TESMUZFG APAWRTV VEF IAUU, IEFGF WV TEWJFGFZ VS
XWFDFT; VEFR, GARP VEF HFUU, ARZ SGZFGFZ WR ARSVEFG.

“VEAV'T A CAWG OSMRP UAZO VS EARZ VS A DSADE WR VEF ZAGK, YG. ZAGRAO!”
 EF TAWZ, CWUUWRP EWT RFI PSHUFV.

A TUWPEV CGSIR ARZ A UADSRWD “OFT,” IFGF VEF ARTIFG.

“VEAV'T A CAWG OSMRP UAZO VS HF XWVWFZ HO ARZ IFXV CSG HO! ESI ZSFT WV
CFFU? WT WV ISGVE HFWRP VGWFZ CSG SRF'T UWCF, VS HF VEF SHLFDV SC TMDE
TOYXAVEO ARZ DSYXATTWSR, YG. ZAGRAO?”

APAWR ZAGRAO ARTIFGFZ RSV A ISGZ.

“TEF IAT YWPEVWUO XUFATFZ VS EAJF OSMG YFTTAPF, IEFR W PAJF WV EFG. RSV
VEAV TEF TESIFZ TEF IAT XUFATFZ, HMV W TMXXSTF TEF IAT.”

VEF AUUMTWSR TFGJFZ AT A VWYFUO GFYWRZFG VS ZAGRAO VEAV VEWT
ZWTAPGFFAHUF DSYXARWSR EAZ, SC EWT SIR CGFF IWUU, ATTWTVFZ EWY WR VEF
TVGAWV SC VEF ZAO. EF VMGRFZ VEF ZWAUSPMF VS VEAV XSWRV, ARZ VEARKFZ EWY
CSG WV.

“W RFWVEFG IARV ARO VEARKT, RSG YFGWV ARO,” IAT VEF DAGFUFTT GFLSWRZFG.
“WV IAT RSVEWRP VS ZS, WR VEF CWGTV XUADF; ARZ W ZSR'V KRSI IEO W ZWZ
WV, WR VEF TFDSRZ. YG. ZAGRAO, UFV YF ATK OSM A NMFTVWSR.”

“IWUUWRPUO, ARZ A TYAUU GFVMGR CSG OSMG PSSZ SCCWDFT.”

“ZS OSM VEWRK W XAGVWDMUAGUO UWKF OSM?”

“GFAUUO, YG. DAGVSR,” GFVMGRFZ VEF SVEFG, SZZUO ZWTDSRDFGVFZ, “W EAJF
RSV ATKFZ YOTFUC VEF NMFTVWSR.”

“HMV ATK OSMGTFUC VEF NMFTVWSR RSI.”

“OSM EAJF ADVFZ AT WC OSM ZS; HMV W ZSR'V VEWRK OSM ZS.”

“_W_ ZSR'V VEWRK W ZS,” TAWZ DAGVSR. “W HFPWR VS EAJF A JFGO PSSZ
SXWRWSR SC OSMG MRZFGTVARZWRP.”

“RFJFGVEFUFTT,” XMGTMFZ ZAGRAO, GWTWRP VS GWRP VEF HFUU, “VEFGF WT
RSVEWRP WR VEAV, W ESXF, VS XGFJFRV YO DAUUWRP VEF GFDKSRWRP, ARZ SMG
XAGVWRP IWVESMV WUU-HUSSZ SR FWVEFG TWZF.”

DAGVSR GFLSWRWRP, “RSVEWRP WR UWCF!” ZAGRAO GARP. “ZS OSM DAUU VEF IESUF
GFDKSRWRP?” TAWZ DAGVSR. SR EWT ARTIFGWRP WR VEF ACCWGYAVWJF, “VEFR
HGWRP YF ARSVEFG XWRV SC VEWT TAYF IWRF, ZGAIFG, ARZ DSYF ARZ IAKF YF AV
VFR.”

VEF HWUU HFWRP XAWZ, DEAGUFT ZAGRAO GSTF ARZ IWTEFZ EWY PSSZ RWPEV.
IWVESMV GFVMGRWRP VEF IWTE, DAGVSR GSTF VSS, IWVE TSYFVEWRP SC A VEGFAV
SC ZFCWARDF WR EWT YARRFG, ARZ TAWZ, “A UATV ISGZ, YG. ZAGRAO: OSM VEWRK
W AY ZGMRK?”

“W VEWRK OSM EAJF HFFR ZGWRKWRP, YG. DAGVSR.”

“VEWRK? OSM KRSI W EAJF HFFR ZGWRKWRP.”

“TWRDF W YMTV TAO TS, W KRSI WV.”

“VEFR OSM TEAUU UWKFIWTF KRSI IEO. W AY A ZWTAXXSWRVFZ ZGMZPF, TWG. W
DAGF CSG RS YAR SR FAGVE, ARZ RS YAR SR FAGVE DAGFT CSG YF.”

“YMDE VS HF GFPGFVVFZ. OSM YWPEV EAJF MTFZ OSMG VAUFRVT HFVVFG.”

“YAO HF TS, YG. ZAGRAO; YAO HF RSV. ZSR'V UFV OSMG TSHFG CADF FUAVF OSM,
ESIFJFG; OSM ZSR'V KRSI IEAV WV YAO DSYF VS. PSSZ RWPEV!”

IEFR EF IAT UFCV AUSRF, VEWT TVGARPF HFWRP VSSK MX A DARZUF, IFRV VS A
PUATT VEAV EMRP APAWRTV VEF IAUU, ARZ TMGJFOFZ EWYTFUC YWRMVFUO WR WV.

“ZS OSM XAGVWDMUAGUO UWKF VEF YAR?” EF YMVVFGFZ, AV EWT SIR WYAPF; “IEO
TESMUZ OSM XAGVWDMUAGUO UWKF A YAR IES GFTFYHUFT OSM? VEFGF WT RSVEWRP
WR OSM VS UWKF; OSM KRSI VEAV. AE, DSRCSMRZ OSM! IEAV A DEARPF OSM EAJF
YAZF WR OSMGTFUC! A PSSZ GFATSR CSG VAKWRP VS A YAR, VEAV EF TESIT OSM
IEAV OSM EAJF CAUUFR AIAO CGSY, ARZ IEAV OSM YWPEV EAJF HFFR! DEARPF
XUADFT IWVE EWY, ARZ ISMUZ OSM EAJF HFFR USSKFZ AV HO VESTF HUMF FOFT AT
EF IAT, ARZ DSYYWTFGAVFZ HO VEAV APWVAVFZ CADF AT EF IAT? DSYF SR, ARZ
EAJF WV SMV WR XUAWR ISGZT! OSM EAVF VEF CFUUSI.”

EF GFTSGVFZ VS EWT XWRV SC IWRF CSG DSRTSUAVWSR, ZGARK WV AUU WR A CFI
YWRMVFT, ARZ CFUU ATUFFX SR EWT AGYT, IWVE EWT EAWG TVGAPPUWRP SJFG VEF
VAHUF, ARZ A USRP IWRZWRP-TEFFV WR VEF DARZUF ZGWXXWRP ZSIR MXSR EWY.




J. VEF LADKAU


VESTF IFGF ZGWRKWRP ZAOT, ARZ YSTV YFR ZGARK EAGZ. TS JFGO PGFAV WT
VEF WYXGSJFYFRV VWYF EAT HGSMPEV AHSMV WR TMDE EAHWVT, VEAV A YSZFGAVF
TVAVFYFRV SC VEF NMARVWVO SC IWRF ARZ XMRDE IEWDE SRF YAR ISMUZ TIAUUSI
WR VEF DSMGTF SC A RWPEV, IWVESMV ARO ZFVGWYFRV VS EWT GFXMVAVWSR AT A
XFGCFDV PFRVUFYAR, ISMUZ TFFY, WR VEFTF ZAOT, A GWZWDMUSMT FQAPPFGAVWSR.
VEF UFAGRFZ XGSCFTTWSR SC VEF UAI IAT DFGVAWRUO RSV HFEWRZ ARO SVEFG
UFAGRFZ XGSCFTTWSR WR WVT HADDEARAUWAR XGSXFRTWVWFT; RFWVEFG IAT YG.
TVGOJFG, AUGFAZO CATV TESMUZFGWRP EWT IAO VS A UAGPF ARZ UMDGAVWJF
XGADVWDF, HFEWRZ EWT DSYXFFGT WR VEWT XAGVWDMUAG, ARO YSGF VEAR WR VEF
ZGWFG XAGVT SC VEF UFPAU GADF.

A CAJSMGWVF AV VEF SUZ HAWUFO, ARZ FKF AV VEF TFTTWSRT, YG. TVGOJFG EAZ
HFPMR DAMVWSMTUO VS EFI AIAO VEF USIFG TVAJFT SC VEF UAZZFG SR IEWDE
EF YSMRVFZ. TFTTWSRT ARZ SUZ HAWUFO EAZ RSI VS TMYYSR VEFWG CAJSMGWVF,
TXFDWAUUO, VS VEFWG USRPWRP AGYT; ARZ TESMUZFGWRP WVTFUC VSIAGZT VEF
JWTAPF SC VEF USGZ DEWFC LMTVWDF WR VEF DSMGV SC KWRP'T HFRDE, VEF
CUSGWZ DSMRVFRARDF SC YG. TVGOJFG YWPEV HF ZAWUO TFFR, HMGTVWRP SMV SC
VEF HFZ SC IWPT, UWKF A PGFAV TMRCUSIFG XMTEWRP WVT IAO AV VEF TMR CGSY
AYSRP A GARK PAGZFR-CMUU SC CUAGWRP DSYXARWSRT.

WV EAZ SRDF HFFR RSVFZ AV VEF HAG, VEAV IEWUF YG. TVGOJFG IAT A PUWH
YAR, ARZ AR MRTDGMXMUSMT, ARZ A GFAZO, ARZ A HSUZ, EF EAZ RSV VEAV
CADMUVO SC FQVGADVWRP VEF FTTFRDF CGSY A EFAX SC TVAVFYFRVT, IEWDE WT
AYSRP VEF YSTV TVGWKWRP ARZ RFDFTTAGO SC VEF AZJSDAVF'T ADDSYXUWTEYFRVT.
HMV, A GFYAGKAHUF WYXGSJFYFRV DAYF MXSR EWY AT VS VEWT. VEF YSGF
HMTWRFTT EF PSV, VEF PGFAVFG EWT XSIFG TFFYFZ VS PGSI SC PFVVWRP AV WVT
XWVE ARZ YAGGSI; ARZ ESIFJFG UAVF AV RWPEV EF TAV DAGSMTWRP IWVE TOZRFO
DAGVSR, EF AUIAOT EAZ EWT XSWRVT AV EWT CWRPFGT' FRZT WR VEF YSGRWRP.

TOZRFO DAGVSR, WZUFTV ARZ YSTV MRXGSYWTWRP SC YFR, IAT TVGOJFG'T PGFAV
AUUO. IEAV VEF VIS ZGARK VSPFVEFG, HFVIFFR EWUAGO VFGY ARZ YWDEAFUYAT,
YWPEV EAJF CUSAVFZ A KWRP'T TEWX. TVGOJFG RFJFG EAZ A DATF WR EARZ,
AROIEFGF, HMV DAGVSR IAT VEFGF, IWVE EWT EARZT WR EWT XSDKFVT, TVAGWRP
AV VEF DFWUWRP SC VEF DSMGV; VEFO IFRV VEF TAYF DWGDMWV, ARZ FJFR VEFGF
VEFO XGSUSRPFZ VEFWG MTMAU SGPWFT UAVF WRVS VEF RWPEV, ARZ DAGVSR IAT
GMYSMGFZ VS HF TFFR AV HGSAZ ZAO, PSWRP ESYF TVFAUVEWUO ARZ MRTVFAZWUO
VS EWT USZPWRPT, UWKF A ZWTTWXAVFZ DAV. AV UATV, WV HFPAR VS PFV AHSMV,
AYSRP TMDE AT IFGF WRVFGFTVFZ WR VEF YAVVFG, VEAV AUVESMPE TOZRFO DAGVSR
ISMUZ RFJFG HF A UWSR, EF IAT AR AYABWRPUO PSSZ LADKAU, ARZ VEAV EF
GFRZFGFZ TMWV ARZ TFGJWDF VS TVGOJFG WR VEAV EMYHUF DAXADWVO.

“VFR S'DUSDK, TWG,” TAWZ VEF YAR AV VEF VAJFGR, IESY EF EAZ DEAGPFZ VS
IAKF EWY--“VFR S'DUSDK, TWG.”

“_IEAV'T_ VEF YAVVFG?”

“VFR S'DUSDK, TWG.”

“IEAV ZS OSM YFAR? VFR S'DUSDK AV RWPEV?”

“OFT, TWG. OSMG ESRSMG VSUZ YF VS DAUU OSM.”

“SE! W GFYFYHFG. JFGO IFUU, JFGO IFUU.”

ACVFG A CFI ZMUU FCCSGVT VS PFV VS TUFFX APAWR, IEWDE VEF YAR
ZFQVFGSMTUO DSYHAVFZ HO TVWGGWRP VEF CWGF DSRVWRMSMTUO CSG CWJF YWRMVFT,
EF PSV MX, VSTTFZ EWT EAV SR, ARZ IAUKFZ SMV. EF VMGRFZ WRVS VEF VFYXUF,
ARZ, EAJWRP GFJWJFZ EWYTFUC HO VIWDF XADWRP VEF XAJFYFRVT SC KWRP'T
HFRDE-IAUK ARZ XAXFG-HMWUZWRPT, VMGRFZ WRVS VEF TVGOJFG DEAYHFGT.

VEF TVGOJFG DUFGK, IES RFJFG ATTWTVFZ AV VEFTF DSRCFGFRDFT, EAZ PSRF
ESYF, ARZ VEF TVGOJFG XGWRDWXAU SXFRFZ VEF ZSSG. EF EAZ EWT TUWXXFGT SR,
ARZ A USSTF HFZ-PSIR, ARZ EWT VEGSAV IAT HAGF CSG EWT PGFAVFG FATF. EF
EAZ VEAV GAVEFG IWUZ, TVGAWRFZ, TFAGFZ YAGKWRP AHSMV VEF FOFT, IEWDE
YAO HF SHTFGJFZ WR AUU CGFF UWJFGT SC EWT DUATT, CGSY VEF XSGVGAWV SC
LFCCGWFT ZSIRIAGZ, ARZ IEWDE DAR HF VGADFZ, MRZFG JAGWSMT ZWTPMWTFT SC
AGV, VEGSMPE VEF XSGVGAWVT SC FJFGO ZGWRKWRP APF.

“OSM AGF A UWVVUF UAVF, YFYSGO,” TAWZ TVGOJFG.

“AHSMV VEF MTMAU VWYF; WV YAO HF A NMAGVFG SC AR ESMG UAVFG.”

VEFO IFRV WRVS A ZWRPO GSSY UWRFZ IWVE HSSKT ARZ UWVVFGFZ IWVE XAXFGT,
IEFGF VEFGF IAT A HUABWRP CWGF. A KFVVUF TVFAYFZ MXSR VEF ESH, ARZ WR
VEF YWZTV SC VEF IGFDK SC XAXFGT A VAHUF TESRF, IWVE XUFRVO SC IWRF MXSR
WV, ARZ HGARZO, ARZ GMY, ARZ TMPAG, ARZ UFYSRT.

“OSM EAJF EAZ OSMG HSVVUF, W XFGDFWJF, TOZRFO.”

“VIS VS-RWPEV, W VEWRK. W EAJF HFFR ZWRWRP IWVE VEF ZAO'T DUWFRV; SG
TFFWRP EWY ZWRF--WV'T AUU SRF!”

“VEAV IAT A GAGF XSWRV, TOZRFO, VEAV OSM HGSMPEV VS HFAG MXSR VEF
WZFRVWCWDAVWSR. ESI ZWZ OSM DSYF HO WV? IEFR ZWZ WV TVGWKF OSM?”

“W VESMPEV EF IAT GAVEFG A EARZTSYF CFUUSI, ARZ W VESMPEV W TESMUZ EAJF
HFFR YMDE VEF TAYF TSGV SC CFUUSI, WC W EAZ EAZ ARO UMDK.”

YG. TVGOJFG UAMPEFZ VWUU EF TESSK EWT XGFDSDWSMT XAMRDE.

“OSM ARZ OSMG UMDK, TOZRFO! PFV VS ISGK, PFV VS ISGK.”

TMUUFRUO FRSMPE, VEF LADKAU USSTFRFZ EWT ZGFTT, IFRV WRVS AR AZLSWRWRP
GSSY, ARZ DAYF HADK IWVE A UAGPF LMP SC DSUZ IAVFG, A HATWR, ARZ A VSIFU
SG VIS. TVFFXWRP VEF VSIFUT WR VEF IAVFG, ARZ XAGVWAUUO IGWRPWRP VEFY
SMV, EF CSUZFZ VEFY SR EWT EFAZ WR A YARRFG EWZFSMT VS HFESUZ, TAV ZSIR
AV VEF VAHUF, ARZ TAWZ, “RSI W AY GFAZO!”

“RSV YMDE HSWUWRP ZSIR VS HF ZSRF VS-RWPEV, YFYSGO,” TAWZ YG. TVGOJFG,
PAWUO, AT EF USSKFZ AYSRP EWT XAXFGT.

“ESI YMDE?”

“SRUO VIS TFVT SC VEFY.”

“PWJF YF VEF ISGTV CWGTV.”

“VEFGF VEFO AGF, TOZRFO. CWGF AIAO!”

VEF UWSR VEFR DSYXSTFZ EWYTFUC SR EWT HADK SR A TSCA SR SRF TWZF SC VEF
ZGWRKWRP-VAHUF, IEWUF VEF LADKAU TAV AV EWT SIR XAXFG-HFTVGFIR VAHUF
XGSXFG, SR VEF SVEFG TWZF SC WV, IWVE VEF HSVVUFT ARZ PUATTFT GFAZO VS
EWT EARZ. HSVE GFTSGVFZ VS VEF ZGWRKWRP-VAHUF IWVESMV TVWRV, HMV FADE WR
A ZWCCFGFRV IAO; VEF UWSR CSG VEF YSTV XAGV GFDUWRWRP IWVE EWT EARZT WR
EWT IAWTVHARZ, USSKWRP AV VEF CWGF, SG SDDATWSRAUUO CUWGVWRP IWVE TSYF
UWPEVFG ZSDMYFRV; VEF LADKAU, IWVE KRWVVFZ HGSIT ARZ WRVFRV CADF,
TS ZFFX WR EWT VATK, VEAV EWT FOFT ZWZ RSV FJFR CSUUSI VEF EARZ EF
TVGFVDEFZ SMV CSG EWT PUATT--IEWDE SCVFR PGSXFZ AHSMV, CSG A YWRMVF SG
YSGF, HFCSGF WV CSMRZ VEF PUATT CSG EWT UWXT. VIS SG VEGFF VWYFT, VEF
YAVVFG WR EARZ HFDAYF TS KRSVVO, VEAV VEF LADKAU CSMRZ WV WYXFGAVWJF SR
EWY VS PFV MX, ARZ TVFFX EWT VSIFUT ARFI. CGSY VEFTF XWUPGWYAPFT VS VEF
LMP ARZ HATWR, EF GFVMGRFZ IWVE TMDE FDDFRVGWDWVWFT SC ZAYX EFAZPFAG AT
RS ISGZT DAR ZFTDGWHF; IEWDE IFGF YAZF VEF YSGF UMZWDGSMT HO EWT ARQWSMT
PGAJWVO.

AV UFRPVE VEF LADKAU EAZ PSV VSPFVEFG A DSYXADV GFXATV CSG VEF UWSR, ARZ
XGSDFFZFZ VS SCCFG WV VS EWY. VEF UWSR VSSK WV IWVE DAGF ARZ DAMVWSR,
YAZF EWT TFUFDVWSRT CGSY WV, ARZ EWT GFYAGKT MXSR WV, ARZ VEF LADKAU
ATTWTVFZ HSVE. IEFR VEF GFXATV IAT CMUUO ZWTDMTTFZ, VEF UWSR XMV EWT
EARZT WR EWT IAWTVHARZ APAWR, ARZ UAO ZSIR VS YFZWVAVF. VEF LADKAU VEFR
WRJWPSGAVFZ EWYTFUC IWVE A HMYXFG CSG EWT VEGSVVUF, ARZ A CGFTE AXXUWDAVWSR
VS EWT EFAZ, ARZ AXXUWFZ EWYTFUC VS VEF DSUUFDVWSR SC A TFDSRZ YFAU;
