YG. USGGO KRFI YWTT XGSTT VS HF JFGO LFAUSMT, HMV EF AUTS KRFI EFG HO
VEWT VWYF VS HF, HFRFAVE VEF TFGJWDF SC EFG FDDFRVGWDWVO, SRF SC VESTF
