AZYWGAVWSR, HWRZ VEFYTFUJFT IWUUWRP TUAJFT, VS OSMVE IEFR VEFO EAJF USTV
WV, VS HFAMVO VEAV VEFO RFJFG EAZ, VS ADDSYXUWTEYFRVT VEAV VEFO IFGF
RFJFG CSGVMRAVF FRSMPE VS PAWR, VS HGWPEV ESXFT VEAV RFJFG TESRF MXSR
VEFWG SIR TSYHGF UWJFT. EF KRFI FRSMPE SC VEF ISGUZ VS KRSI VEAV VEFGF
WT RSVEWRP WR WV HFVVFG VEAR VEF CAWVECMU TFGJWDF SC VEF EFAGV; TS
GFRZFGFZ ARZ TS CGFF CGSY ARO YFGDFRAGO VAWRV, EF EAZ TMDE AR FQAUVFZ
GFTXFDV CSG WV, VEAV WR VEF GFVGWHMVWJF AGGARPFYFRVT YAZF HO EWT SIR
YWRZ--IF AUU YAKF TMDE AGGARPFYFRVT, YSGF SG UFTT--EF TVAVWSRFZ YWTT
XGSTT YMDE RFAGFG VS VEF USIFG ARPFUT VEAR YARO UAZWFT WYYFATMGAHUO
HFVVFG PSV MX HSVE HO RAVMGF ARZ AGV, IES EAZ HAUARDFT AV VFUUTSR'T.

“VEFGF RFJFG IAT, RSG IWUU HF, HMV SRF YAR ISGVEO SC UAZOHWGZ,” TAWZ
YWTT XGSTT; “ARZ VEAV IAT YO HGSVEFG TSUSYSR, WC EF EAZR'V YAZF A
YWTVAKF WR UWCF.”

EFGF APAWR: YG. USGGO'T WRNMWGWFT WRVS YWTT XGSTT'T XFGTSRAU EWTVSGO EAZ
FTVAHUWTEFZ VEF CADV VEAV EFG HGSVEFG TSUSYSR IAT A EFAGVUFTT TDSMRZGFU
IES EAZ TVGWXXFZ EFG SC FJFGOVEWRP TEF XSTTFTTFZ, AT A TVAKF VS
TXFDMUAVF IWVE, ARZ EAZ AHARZSRFZ EFG WR EFG XSJFGVO CSG FJFGYSGF, IWVE
RS VSMDE SC DSYXMRDVWSR. YWTT XGSTT'T CWZFUWVO SC HFUWFC WR TSUSYSR
(ZFZMDVWRP A YFGF VGWCUF CSG VEWT TUWPEV YWTVAKF) IAT NMWVF A TFGWSMT
YAVVFG IWVE YG. USGGO, ARZ EAZ WVT IFWPEV WR EWT PSSZ SXWRWSR SC EFG.

“AT IF EAXXFR VS HF AUSRF CSG VEF YSYFRV, ARZ AGF HSVE XFSXUF SC
HMTWRFTT,” EF TAWZ, IEFR VEFO EAZ PSV HADK VS VEF ZGAIWRP-GSSY ARZ EAZ
