WR VAUKWRP IWVE UMDWF, RFJFG GFCFG VS VEF TESFYAKWRP VWYF, OFV?”

“RFJFG.”

“ARZ OFV KFFXT VEAV HFRDE ARZ VESTF VSSUT HFTWZF EWY?”

“AE!” GFVMGRFZ YWTT XGSTT, TEAKWRP EFG EFAZ. “HMV W ZSR'V TAO EF ZSR'V
GFCFG VS WV IWVEWR EWYTFUC.”

“ZS OSM HFUWFJF VEAV EF VEWRKT SC WV YMDE?”

“W ZS,” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT.

“ZS OSM WYAPWRF--” YG. USGGO EAZ HFPMR, IEFR YWTT XGSTT VSSK EWY MX
TESGV IWVE:

“RFJFG WYAPWRF AROVEWRP. EAJF RS WYAPWRAVWSR AV AUU.”

“W TVARZ DSGGFDVFZ; ZS OSM TMXXSTF--OSM PS TS CAG AT VS TMXXSTF,
TSYFVWYFT?”

“RSI ARZ VEFR,” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT.

“ZS OSM TMXXSTF,” YG. USGGO IFRV SR, IWVE A UAMPEWRP VIWRKUF WR EWT
