VEF DAMTF SC EWT HFWRP TS SXXGFTTFZ; XFGEAXT, FJFR VS VEF RAYF SC EWT
SXXGFTTSG?”

“W ZSR'V TMXXSTF AROVEWRP AHSMV WV HMV IEAV UAZOHWGZ VFUUT YF.”

“ARZ VEAV WT--?”

“VEAV TEF VEWRKT EF EAT.”

“RSI ZSR'V HF ARPGO AV YO ATKWRP AUU VEFTF NMFTVWSRT; HFDAMTF W AY A
YFGF ZMUU YAR SC HMTWRFTT, ARZ OSM AGF A ISYAR SC HMTWRFTT.”

“ZMUU?” YWTT XGSTT WRNMWGFZ, IWVE XUADWZWVO.

GAVEFG IWTEWRP EWT YSZFTV AZLFDVWJF AIAO, YG. USGGO GFXUWFZ, “RS, RS,
