YWTT XGSTT IAT A XUFATARV TWPEV, AUHFWV IWUZ, ARZ GFZ, ARZ PGWY, VAKWRP
SCC EFG ZAGUWRP'T HSRRFV IEFR TEF DAYF MX-TVAWGT, ARZ VSMDEWRP WV MX
