IEWTXFGFZ VS VEFY WR WVT SIR IAO AHSJF VEFWG EFAZT.

TVWUU, VEF EMRZGFZT SC XFSXUF ZWZ RSV XGFTFRV VEFYTFUJFT. YG. ZAGRAO
XGFTFRVFZ EWYTFUC IEWUF VEFO IFGF TWVVWRP MRZFG VEF XUARF-VGFF, HMV EF
IAT SRUO SRF.

ZSDVSG YARFVVF GFDFWJFZ EWY KWRZUO, ARZ TS ZWZ UMDWF. HMV, YWTT XGSTT
TMZZFRUO HFDAYF ACCUWDVFZ IWVE A VIWVDEWRP WR VEF EFAZ ARZ HSZO, ARZ
GFVWGFZ WRVS VEF ESMTF. TEF IAT RSV MRCGFNMFRVUO VEF JWDVWY SC VEWT
ZWTSGZFG, ARZ TEF DAUUFZ WV, WR CAYWUWAG DSRJFGTAVWSR, “A CWV SC VEF
