“UMDWF ARZ W EAJF HFFR VEFGF; HMV SRUO DATMAUUO. IF EAJF TFFR FRSMPE SC
WV, VS KRSI VEAV WV VFFYT IWVE WRVFGFTV; UWVVUF YSGF.”

“_W_ EAJF HFFR VEFGF, AT OSM GFYFYHFG,” TAWZ ZAGRAO, IWVE A TYWUF,
