DEAGADVFG VEAV PWJFT CADWUWVWFT CSG TFFWRP YMDE SC WV. VEFO VSUZ YF A
DMGWSMT VEWRP IEFR W IAT VEFGF.”

“IEAV IAT VEAV?” UMDWF ATKFZ.

“WR YAKWRP TSYF AUVFGAVWSRT, VEF ISGKYFR DAYF MXSR AR SUZ ZMRPFSR, IEWDE
EAZ HFFR, CSG YARO OFAGT, HMWUV MX ARZ CSGPSVVFR. FJFGO TVSRF SC
WVT WRRFG IAUU IAT DSJFGFZ HO WRTDGWXVWSRT IEWDE EAZ HFFR DAGJFZ HO
