TSYF JFGO XSSG WRTVGMYFRV, ARZ EMGGWFZUO, IWVE AR MRTVFAZO EARZ.
AV CWGTV, VEFO IFGF GFAZ AT Z. W. D.; HMV, SR HFWRP YSGF DAGFCMUUO
FQAYWRFZ, VEF UATV UFVVFG IAT CSMRZ VS HF P. VEFGF IAT RS GFDSGZ SG
UFPFRZ SC ARO XGWTSRFG IWVE VESTF WRWVWAUT, ARZ YARO CGMWVUFTT PMFTTFT
IFGF YAZF IEAV VEF RAYF DSMUZ EAJF HFFR. AV UFRPVE, WV IAT TMPPFTVFZ
VEAV VEF UFVVFGT IFGF RSV WRWVWAUT, HMV VEF DSYXUFVF ISGZ, ZWP. VEF
CUSSG IAT FQAYWRFZ JFGO DAGFCMUUO MRZFG VEF WRTDGWXVWSR, ARZ, WR VEF
FAGVE HFRFAVE A TVSRF, SG VWUF, SG TSYF CGAPYFRV SC XAJWRP, IFGF CSMRZ
VEF ATEFT SC A XAXFG, YWRPUFZ IWVE VEF ATEFT SC A TYAUU UFAVEFGR DATF
SG HAP. IEAV VEF MRKRSIR XGWTSRFG EAZ IGWVVFR IWUU RFJFG HF GFAZ, HMV EF
EAZ IGWVVFR TSYFVEWRP, ARZ EWZZFR WV AIAO VS KFFX WV CGSY VEF PASUFG.”

“YO CAVEFG,” FQDUAWYFZ UMDWF, “OSM AGF WUU!”

EF EAZ TMZZFRUO TVAGVFZ MX, IWVE EWT EARZ VS EWT EFAZ. EWT YARRFG ARZ
