“VEF GAWR-ZGSXT AGF TVWUU CAUUWRP, UAGPF, EFAJO, ARZ CFI,” TAWZ ZSDVSG
YARFVVF. “WV DSYFT TUSIUO.”

“WV DSYFT TMGFUO,” TAWZ DAGVSR.

VEFO TXSKF USI, AT XFSXUF IAVDEWRP ARZ IAWVWRP YSTVUO ZS; AT XFSXUF WR A
ZAGK GSSY, IAVDEWRP ARZ IAWVWRP CSG UWPEVRWRP, AUIAOT ZS.

VEFGF IAT A PGFAV EMGGO WR VEF TVGFFVT SC XFSXUF TXFFZWRP AIAO VS
PFV TEFUVFG HFCSGF VEF TVSGY HGSKF; VEF ISRZFGCMU DSGRFG CSG FDESFT
