“A YMUVWVMZF SC XFSXUF, ARZ OFV A TSUWVMZF!” TAWZ ZAGRAO, IEFR VEFO EAZ
UWTVFRFZ CSG A IEWUF.

“WT WV RSV WYXGFTTWJF, YG. ZAGRAO?” ATKFZ UMDWF. “TSYFVWYFT, W EAJF
TAV EFGF SC AR FJFRWRP, MRVWU W EAJF CARDWFZ--HMV FJFR VEF TEAZF SC
A CSSUWTE CARDO YAKFT YF TEMZZFG VS-RWPEV, IEFR AUU WT TS HUADK ARZ
TSUFYR--”

“UFV MT TEMZZFG VSS. IF YAO KRSI IEAV WV WT.”

“WV IWUU TFFY RSVEWRP VS OSM. TMDE IEWYT AGF SRUO WYXGFTTWJF AT IF
SGWPWRAVF VEFY, W VEWRK; VEFO AGF RSV VS HF DSYYMRWDAVFZ. W EAJF
TSYFVWYFT TAV AUSRF EFGF SC AR FJFRWRP, UWTVFRWRP, MRVWU W EAJF YAZF
VEF FDESFT SMV VS HF VEF FDESFT SC AUU VEF CSSVTVFXT VEAV AGF DSYWRP
HO-ARZ-HOF WRVS SMG UWJFT.”

“VEFGF WT A PGFAV DGSIZ DSYWRP SRF ZAO WRVS SMG UWJFT, WC VEAV HF TS,”
 TOZRFO DAGVSR TVGMDK WR, WR EWT YSSZO IAO.

VEF CSSVTVFXT IFGF WRDFTTARV, ARZ VEF EMGGO SC VEFY HFDAYF YSGF ARZ YSGF
GAXWZ. VEF DSGRFG FDESFZ ARZ GF-FDESFZ IWVE VEF VGFAZ SC CFFV; TSYF,
AT WV TFFYFZ, MRZFG VEF IWRZSIT; TSYF, AT WV TFFYFZ, WR VEF GSSY; TSYF
DSYWRP, TSYF PSWRP, TSYF HGFAKWRP SCC, TSYF TVSXXWRP AUVSPFVEFG; AUU WR
VEF ZWTVARV TVGFFVT, ARZ RSV SRF IWVEWR TWPEV.

“AGF AUU VEFTF CSSVTVFXT ZFTVWRFZ VS DSYF VS AUU SC MT, YWTT YARFVVF, SG
AGF IF VS ZWJWZF VEFY AYSRP MT?”

“W ZSR'V KRSI, YG. ZAGRAO; W VSUZ OSM WV IAT A CSSUWTE CARDO, HMV OSM
ATKFZ CSG WV. IEFR W EAJF OWFUZFZ YOTFUC VS WV, W EAJF HFFR AUSRF, ARZ
VEFR W EAJF WYAPWRFZ VEFY VEF CSSVTVFXT SC VEF XFSXUF IES AGF VS DSYF
WRVS YO UWCF, ARZ YO CAVEFG'T.”

“W VAKF VEFY WRVS YWRF!” TAWZ DAGVSR. “_W_ ATK RS NMFTVWSRT ARZ YAKF RS
TVWXMUAVWSRT. VEFGF WT A PGFAV DGSIZ HFAGWRP ZSIR MXSR MT, YWTT YARFVVF,
ARZ W TFF VEFY--HO VEF UWPEVRWRP.” EF AZZFZ VEF UATV ISGZT, ACVFG VEFGF
EAZ HFFR A JWJWZ CUATE IEWDE EAZ TESIR EWY USMRPWRP WR VEF IWRZSI.

“ARZ W EFAG VEFY!” EF AZZFZ APAWR, ACVFG A XFAU SC VEMRZFG. “EFGF VEFO
DSYF, CATV, CWFGDF, ARZ CMGWSMT!”

WV IAT VEF GMTE ARZ GSAG SC GAWR VEAV EF VOXWCWFZ, ARZ WV TVSXXFZ EWY,
CSG RS JSWDF DSMUZ HF EFAGZ WR WV. A YFYSGAHUF TVSGY SC VEMRZFG ARZ
UWPEVRWRP HGSKF IWVE VEAV TIFFX SC IAVFG, ARZ VEFGF IAT RSV A YSYFRV'T
WRVFGJAU WR DGATE, ARZ CWGF, ARZ GAWR, MRVWU ACVFG VEF YSSR GSTF AV
YWZRWPEV.

VEF PGFAV HFUU SC TAWRV XAMU'T IAT TVGWKWRP SRF WR VEF DUFAGFZ AWG, IEFR
YG. USGGO, FTDSGVFZ HO LFGGO, EWPE-HSSVFZ ARZ HFAGWRP A UARVFGR, TFV
CSGVE SR EWT GFVMGR-XATTAPF VS DUFGKFRIFUU. VEFGF IFGF TSUWVAGO XAVDEFT
SC GSAZ SR VEF IAO HFVIFFR TSES ARZ DUFGKFRIFUU, ARZ YG. USGGO, YWRZCMU
SC CSSV-XAZT, AUIAOT GFVAWRFZ LFGGO CSG VEWT TFGJWDF: VESMPE WV IAT
MTMAUUO XFGCSGYFZ A PSSZ VIS ESMGT FAGUWFG.

“IEAV A RWPEV WV EAT HFFR! AUYSTV A RWPEV, LFGGO,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, “VS
HGWRP VEF ZFAZ SMV SC VEFWG PGAJFT.”

“W RFJFG TFF VEF RWPEV YOTFUC, YATVFG--RSG OFV W ZSR'V FQXFDV VS--IEAV
ISMUZ ZS VEAV,” ARTIFGFZ LFGGO.

“PSSZ RWPEV, YG. DAGVSR,” TAWZ VEF YAR SC HMTWRFTT. “PSSZ RWPEV, YG.
ZAGRAO. TEAUU IF FJFG TFF TMDE A RWPEV APAWR, VSPFVEFG!”

XFGEAXT. XFGEAXT, TFF VEF PGFAV DGSIZ SC XFSXUF IWVE WVT GMTE ARZ GSAG,
HFAGWRP ZSIR MXSR VEFY, VSS.




JWW. YSRTFWPRFMG WR VSIR


YSRTFWPRFMG, SRF SC VEF PGFAV USGZT WR XSIFG AV VEF DSMGV, EFUZ EWT
CSGVRWPEVUO GFDFXVWSR WR EWT PGARZ ESVFU WR XAGWT. YSRTFWPRFMG IAT WR
EWT WRRFG GSSY, EWT TARDVMAGO SC TARDVMAGWFT, VEF ESUWFTV SC ESUWFTVT VS
VEF DGSIZ SC ISGTEWXXFGT WR VEF TMWVF SC GSSYT IWVESMV. YSRTFWPRFMG
IAT AHSMV VS VAKF EWT DESDSUAVF. YSRTFWPRFMG DSMUZ TIAUUSI A PGFAV YARO
VEWRPT IWVE FATF, ARZ IAT HO TSYF CFI TMUUFR YWRZT TMXXSTFZ VS HF GAVEFG
GAXWZUO TIAUUSIWRP CGARDF; HMV, EWT YSGRWRP'T DESDSUAVF DSMUZ RSV TS
YMDE AT PFV WRVS VEF VEGSAV SC YSRTFWPRFMG, IWVESMV VEF AWZ SC CSMG
TVGSRP YFR HFTWZFT VEF DSSK.

OFT. WV VSSK CSMG YFR, AUU CSMG AHUABF IWVE PSGPFSMT ZFDSGAVWSR, ARZ VEF
DEWFC SC VEFY MRAHUF VS FQWTV IWVE CFIFG VEAR VIS PSUZ IAVDEFT WR EWT
XSDKFV, FYMUAVWJF SC VEF RSHUF ARZ DEATVF CATEWSR TFV HO YSRTFWPRFMG, VS
DSRZMDV VEF EAXXO DESDSUAVF VS YSRTFWPRFMG'T UWXT. SRF UADNMFO DAGGWFZ
VEF DESDSUAVF-XSV WRVS VEF TADGFZ XGFTFRDF; A TFDSRZ, YWUUFZ ARZ CGSVEFZ
VEF DESDSUAVF IWVE VEF UWVVUF WRTVGMYFRV EF HSGF CSG VEAV CMRDVWSR;
A VEWGZ, XGFTFRVFZ VEF CAJSMGFZ RAXKWR; A CSMGVE (EF SC VEF VIS PSUZ
IAVDEFT), XSMGFZ VEF DESDSUAVF SMV. WV IAT WYXSTTWHUF CSG YSRTFWPRFMG VS
ZWTXFRTF IWVE SRF SC VEFTF AVVFRZARVT SR VEF DESDSUAVF ARZ ESUZ EWT EWPE
XUADF MRZFG VEF AZYWGWRP EFAJFRT. ZFFX ISMUZ EAJF HFFR VEF HUSV MXSR
EWT FTDMVDEFSR WC EWT DESDSUAVF EAZ HFFR WPRSHUO IAWVFZ SR HO SRUO VEGFF
YFR; EF YMTV EAJF ZWFZ SC VIS.

YSRTFWPRFMG EAZ HFFR SMV AV A UWVVUF TMXXFG UATV RWPEV, IEFGF VEF DSYFZO
ARZ VEF PGARZ SXFGA IFGF DEAGYWRPUO GFXGFTFRVFZ. YSRTFWPRFMG IAT SMV AV
A UWVVUF TMXXFG YSTV RWPEVT, IWVE CATDWRAVWRP DSYXARO. TS XSUWVF ARZ TS
WYXGFTTWHUF IAT YSRTFWPRFMG, VEAV VEF DSYFZO ARZ VEF PGARZ SXFGA EAZ CAG
YSGF WRCUMFRDF IWVE EWY WR VEF VWGFTSYF AGVWDUFT SC TVAVF ACCAWGT ARZ
TVAVF TFDGFVT, VEAR VEF RFFZT SC AUU CGARDF. A EAXXO DWGDMYTVARDF
CSG CGARDF, AT VEF UWKF AUIAOT WT CSG AUU DSMRVGWFT TWYWUAGUO
CAJSMGFZ!--AUIAOT IAT CSG FRPUARZ (HO IAO SC FQAYXUF), WR VEF GFPGFVVFZ
ZAOT SC VEF YFGGO TVMAGV IES TSUZ WV.

YSRTFWPRFMG EAZ SRF VGMUO RSHUF WZFA SC PFRFGAU XMHUWD HMTWRFTT, IEWDE
IAT, VS UFV FJFGOVEWRP PS SR WR WVT SIR IAO; SC XAGVWDMUAG XMHUWD
