IAT YAZF CSG VEFY. VEF VFQV SC EWT SGZFG (AUVFGFZ CGSY VEF SGWPWRAU
HO SRUO A XGSRSMR, IEWDE WT RSV YMDE) GAR: “VEF FAGVE ARZ VEF CMURFTT
VEFGFSC AGF YWRF, TAWVE YSRTFWPRFMG.”

OFV, YSRTFWPRFMG EAZ TUSIUO CSMRZ VEAV JMUPAG FYHAGGATTYFRVT DGFXV WRVS
