VEGFF IES EAZ GMTEFZ WRVS ARSVEFG TFDV, IEWDE YFRZFZ YAVVFGT IWVE A
LAGPSR AHSMV “VEF DFRVGF SC VGMVE:” ESUZWRP VEAV YAR EAZ PSV SMV SC VEF
DFRVGF SC VGMVE--IEWDE ZWZ RSV RFFZ YMDE ZFYSRTVGAVWSR--HMV EAZ RSV PSV
