UARPMWZUO YSJFZ; VEFTF PSUZFR CFVVFGT GARP UWKF XGFDWSMT UWVVUF HFUUT;
ARZ IEAV IWVE VEAV GWRPWRP, ARZ IWVE VEF GMTVUF SC TWUK ARZ HGSDAZF ARZ
CWRF UWRFR, VEFGF IAT A CUMVVFG WR VEF AWG VEAV CARRFZ TAWRV ARVSWRF ARZ
EWT ZFJSMGWRP EMRPFG CAG AIAO.

ZGFTT IAT VEF SRF MRCAWUWRP VAUWTYAR ARZ DEAGY MTFZ CSG KFFXWRP AUU
VEWRPT WR VEFWG XUADFT. FJFGOHSZO IAT ZGFTTFZ CSG A CARDO HAUU VEAV
IAT RFJFG VS UFAJF SCC. CGSY VEF XAUADF SC VEF VMWUFGWFT, VEGSMPE
YSRTFWPRFMG ARZ VEF IESUF DSMGV, VEGSMPE VEF DEAYHFGT, VEF VGWHMRAUT
SC LMTVWDF, ARZ AUU TSDWFVO (FQDFXV VEF TDAGFDGSIT), VEF CARDO HAUU
