YSRTFWPRFMG'T GFDFXVWSR WR VEAV TFJFRVFFR EMRZGFZ ARZ FWPEVWFVE OFAG
SC SMG USGZ, DSMUZ XSTTWHUO ZSMHV, VEAV A TOTVFY GSSVFZ WR A CGWBBUFZ
EARPYAR, XSIZFGFZ, PSUZ-UADFZ, XMYXFZ, ARZ IEWVF-TWUK TVSDKWRPFZ, ISMUZ
TFF VEF JFGO TVAGT SMV!

YSRTFWPRFMG EAJWRP FATFZ EWT CSMG YFR SC VEFWG HMGZFRT ARZ VAKFR EWT
DESDSUAVF, DAMTFZ VEF ZSSGT SC VEF ESUWFTV SC ESUWFTVT VS HF VEGSIR
SXFR, ARZ WTTMFZ CSGVE. VEFR, IEAV TMHYWTTWSR, IEAV DGWRPWRP ARZ
CAIRWRP, IEAV TFGJWUWVO, IEAV AHLFDV EMYWUWAVWSR! AT VS HSIWRP ZSIR WR
