HFFR SRF AYSRP SVEFG GFATSRT IEO VEF ISGTEWXXFGT SC YSRTFWPRFMG RFJFG
VGSMHUFZ WV.

HFTVSIWRP A ISGZ SC XGSYWTF EFGF ARZ A TYWUF VEFGF, A IEWTXFG SR SRF
EAXXO TUAJF ARZ A IAJF SC VEF EARZ SR ARSVEFG, YSRTFWPRFMG ACCAHUO
XATTFZ VEGSMPE EWT GSSYT VS VEF GFYSVF GFPWSR SC VEF DWGDMYCFGFRDF SC
VGMVE. VEFGF, YSRTFWPRFMG VMGRFZ, ARZ DAYF HADK APAWR, ARZ TS WR ZMF
DSMGTF SC VWYF PSV EWYTFUC TEMV MX WR EWT TARDVMAGO HO VEF DESDSUAVF
TXGWVFT, ARZ IAT TFFR RS YSGF.

VEF TESI HFWRP SJFG, VEF CUMVVFG WR VEF AWG HFDAYF NMWVF A UWVVUF TVSGY,
ARZ VEF XGFDWSMT UWVVUF HFUUT IFRV GWRPWRP ZSIRTVAWGT. VEFGF IAT TSSR
