ARZ EWT TRMCC-HSQ WR EWT EARZ, TUSIUO XATTFZ AYSRP VEF YWGGSGT SR EWT
IAO SMV.

“W ZFJSVF OSM,” TAWZ VEWT XFGTSR, TVSXXWRP AV VEF UATV ZSSG SR EWT IAO,
ARZ VMGRWRP WR VEF ZWGFDVWSR SC VEF TARDVMAGO, “VS VEF ZFJWU!”

IWVE VEAV, EF TESSK VEF TRMCC CGSY EWT CWRPFGT AT WC EF EAZ TEAKFR VEF
ZMTV CGSY EWT CFFV, ARZ NMWFVUO IAUKFZ ZSIRTVAWGT.

EF IAT A YAR SC AHSMV TWQVO, EARZTSYFUO ZGFTTFZ, EAMPEVO WR YARRFG, ARZ
IWVE A CADF UWKF A CWRF YATK. A CADF SC A VGARTXAGFRV XAUFRFTT; FJFGO
CFAVMGF WR WV DUFAGUO ZFCWRFZ; SRF TFV FQXGFTTWSR SR WV. VEF RSTF,
HFAMVWCMUUO CSGYFZ SVEFGIWTF, IAT JFGO TUWPEVUO XWRDEFZ AV VEF VSX
SC FADE RSTVGWU. WR VESTF VIS DSYXGFTTWSRT, SG ZWRVT, VEF SRUO UWVVUF
DEARPF VEAV VEF CADF FJFG TESIFZ, GFTWZFZ. VEFO XFGTWTVFZ WR DEARPWRP
DSUSMG TSYFVWYFT, ARZ VEFO ISMUZ HF SDDATWSRAUUO ZWUAVFZ ARZ DSRVGADVFZ
HO TSYFVEWRP UWKF A CAWRV XMUTAVWSR; VEFR, VEFO PAJF A USSK SC
VGFADEFGO, ARZ DGMFUVO, VS VEF IESUF DSMRVFRARDF. FQAYWRFZ IWVE
AVVFRVWSR, WVT DAXADWVO SC EFUXWRP TMDE A USSK IAT VS HF CSMRZ WR VEF
UWRF SC VEF YSMVE, ARZ VEF UWRFT SC VEF SGHWVT SC VEF FOFT, HFWRP YMDE
VSS ESGWBSRVAU ARZ VEWR; TVWUU, WR VEF FCCFDV SC VEF CADF YAZF, WV IAT A
EARZTSYF CADF, ARZ A GFYAGKAHUF SRF.

WVT SIRFG IFRV ZSIRTVAWGT WRVS VEF DSMGVOAGZ, PSV WRVS EWT DAGGWAPF, ARZ
ZGSJF AIAO. RSV YARO XFSXUF EAZ VAUKFZ IWVE EWY AV VEF GFDFXVWSR; EF EAZ
TVSSZ WR A UWVVUF TXADF AXAGV, ARZ YSRTFWPRFMG YWPEV EAJF HFFR IAGYFG
WR EWT YARRFG. WV AXXFAGFZ, MRZFG VEF DWGDMYTVARDFT, GAVEFG APGFFAHUF
VS EWY VS TFF VEF DSYYSR XFSXUF ZWTXFGTFZ HFCSGF EWT ESGTFT, ARZ
SCVFR HAGFUO FTDAXWRP CGSY HFWRP GMR ZSIR. EWT YAR ZGSJF AT WC EF IFGF
DEAGPWRP AR FRFYO, ARZ VEF CMGWSMT GFDKUFTTRFTT SC VEF YAR HGSMPEV RS
DEFDK WRVS VEF CADF, SG VS VEF UWXT, SC VEF YATVFG. VEF DSYXUAWRV EAZ
TSYFVWYFT YAZF WVTFUC AMZWHUF, FJFR WR VEAV ZFAC DWVO ARZ ZMYH APF,
VEAV, WR VEF RAGGSI TVGFFVT IWVESMV CSSVIAOT, VEF CWFGDF XAVGWDWAR
DMTVSY SC EAGZ ZGWJWRP FRZARPFGFZ ARZ YAWYFZ VEF YFGF JMUPAG WR A
HAGHAGSMT YARRFG. HMV, CFI DAGFZ FRSMPE CSG VEAV VS VEWRK SC WV A TFDSRZ
VWYF, ARZ, WR VEWT YAVVFG, AT WR AUU SVEFGT, VEF DSYYSR IGFVDEFT IFGF
UFCV VS PFV SMV SC VEFWG ZWCCWDMUVWFT AT VEFO DSMUZ.

IWVE A IWUZ GAVVUF ARZ DUAVVFG, ARZ AR WREMYAR AHARZSRYFRV SC
DSRTWZFGAVWSR RSV FATO VS HF MRZFGTVSSZ WR VEFTF ZAOT, VEF DAGGWAPF
