WVT IAO. AV UATV, TISSXWRP AV A TVGFFV DSGRFG HO A CSMRVAWR, SRF SC WVT
IEFFUT DAYF VS A TWDKFRWRP UWVVUF LSUV, ARZ VEFGF IAT A USMZ DGO CGSY A
RMYHFG SC JSWDFT, ARZ VEF ESGTFT GFAGFZ ARZ XUMRPFZ.

HMV CSG VEF UAVVFG WRDSRJFRWFRDF, VEF DAGGWAPF XGSHAHUO ISMUZ RSV EAJF
TVSXXFZ; DAGGWAPFT IFGF SCVFR KRSIR VS ZGWJF SR, ARZ UFAJF VEFWG ISMRZFZ
HFEWRZ, ARZ IEO RSV? HMV VEF CGWPEVFRFZ JAUFV EAZ PSV ZSIR WR A EMGGO,
ARZ VEFGF IFGF VIFRVO EARZT AV VEF ESGTFT' HGWZUFT.

“IEAV EAT PSRF IGSRP?” TAWZ YSRTWFMG, DAUYUO USSKWRP SMV.

A VAUU YAR WR A RWPEVDAX EAZ DAMPEV MX A HMRZUF CGSY AYSRP VEF CFFV SC
VEF ESGTFT, ARZ EAZ UAWZ WV SR VEF HATFYFRV SC VEF CSMRVAWR, ARZ IAT
ZSIR WR VEF YMZ ARZ IFV, ESIUWRP SJFG WV UWKF A IWUZ ARWYAU.

“XAGZSR, YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT!” TAWZ A GAPPFZ ARZ TMHYWTTWJF YAR, “WV WT
A DEWUZ.”

“IEO ZSFT EF YAKF VEAV AHSYWRAHUF RSWTF? WT WV EWT DEWUZ?”

“FQDMTF YF, YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT--WV WT A XWVO--OFT.”

VEF CSMRVAWR IAT A UWVVUF GFYSJFZ; CSG VEF TVGFFV SXFRFZ, IEFGF WV IAT,
WRVS A TXADF TSYF VFR SG VIFUJF OAGZT TNMAGF. AT VEF VAUU YAR TMZZFRUO
