“KWUUFZ!” TEGWFKFZ VEF YAR, WR IWUZ ZFTXFGAVWSR, FQVFRZWRP HSVE AGYT AV
VEFWG UFRPVE AHSJF EWT EFAZ, ARZ TVAGWRP AV EWY. “ZFAZ!”

VEF XFSXUF DUSTFZ GSMRZ, ARZ USSKFZ AV YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT. VEFGF IAT
RSVEWRP GFJFAUFZ HO VEF YARO FOFT VEAV USSKFZ AV EWY HMV IAVDECMURFTT
ARZ FAPFGRFTT; VEFGF IAT RS JWTWHUF YFRADWRP SG ARPFG. RFWVEFG ZWZ VEF
XFSXUF TAO AROVEWRP; ACVFG VEF CWGTV DGO, VEFO EAZ HFFR TWUFRV, ARZ VEFO
GFYAWRFZ TS. VEF JSWDF SC VEF TMHYWTTWJF YAR IES EAZ TXSKFR, IAT CUAV
ARZ VAYF WR WVT FQVGFYF TMHYWTTWSR. YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT GAR EWT FOFT
SJFG VEFY AUU, AT WC VEFO EAZ HFFR YFGF GAVT DSYF SMV SC VEFWG ESUFT.

EF VSSK SMV EWT XMGTF.

“WV WT FQVGASGZWRAGO VS YF,” TAWZ EF, “VEAV OSM XFSXUF DARRSV VAKF DAGF
SC OSMGTFUJFT ARZ OSMG DEWUZGFR. SRF SG VEF SVEFG SC OSM WT CSG FJFG WR
VEF IAO. ESI ZS W KRSI IEAV WRLMGO OSM EAJF ZSRF YO ESGTFT. TFF! PWJF
EWY VEAV.”

EF VEGFI SMV A PSUZ DSWR CSG VEF JAUFV VS XWDK MX, ARZ AUU VEF EFAZT
DGARFZ CSGIAGZ VEAV AUU VEF FOFT YWPEV USSK ZSIR AV WV AT WV CFUU. VEF
VAUU YAR DAUUFZ SMV APAWR IWVE A YSTV MRFAGVEUO DGO, “ZFAZ!”

EF IAT AGGFTVFZ HO VEF NMWDK AGGWJAU SC ARSVEFG YAR, CSG IESY VEF GFTV
YAZF IAO. SR TFFWRP EWY, VEF YWTFGAHUF DGFAVMGF CFUU MXSR EWT TESMUZFG,
TSHHWRP ARZ DGOWRP, ARZ XSWRVWRP VS VEF CSMRVAWR, IEFGF TSYF ISYFR IFGF
TVSSXWRP SJFG VEF YSVWSRUFTT HMRZUF, ARZ YSJWRP PFRVUO AHSMV WV. VEFO
IFGF AT TWUFRV, ESIFJFG, AT VEF YFR.

“W KRSI AUU, W KRSI AUU,” TAWZ VEF UATV DSYFG. “HF A HGAJF YAR, YO
PATXAGZ! WV WT HFVVFG CSG VEF XSSG UWVVUF XUAOVEWRP VS ZWF TS, VEAR VS
UWJF. WV EAT ZWFZ WR A YSYFRV IWVESMV XAWR. DSMUZ WV EAJF UWJFZ AR ESMG
AT EAXXWUO?”

“OSM AGF A XEWUSTSXEFG, OSM VEFGF,” TAWZ VEF YAGNMWT, TYWUWRP. “ESI ZS
VEFO DAUU OSM?”

“VEFO DAUU YF ZFCAGPF.”

“SC IEAV VGAZF?”

“YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT, JFRZSG SC IWRF.”

“XWDK MX VEAV, XEWUSTSXEFG ARZ JFRZSG SC IWRF,” TAWZ VEF YAGNMWT,
VEGSIWRP EWY ARSVEFG PSUZ DSWR, “ARZ TXFRZ WV AT OSM IWUU. VEF ESGTFT
