IWVESMV ZFWPRWRP VS USSK AV VEF ATTFYHUAPF A TFDSRZ VWYF, YSRTWFMG VEF
YAGNMWT UFARFZ HADK WR EWT TFAV, ARZ IAT LMTV HFWRP ZGWJFR AIAO IWVE VEF
AWG SC A PFRVUFYAR IES EAZ ADDWZFRVAUUO HGSKF TSYF DSYYSR VEWRP, ARZ EAZ
