ZWTVMGHFZ HO A DSWR CUOWRP WRVS EWT DAGGWAPF, ARZ GWRPWRP SR WVT CUSSG.

“ESUZ!” TAWZ YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT. “ESUZ VEF ESGTFT! IES VEGFI VEAV?”

EF USSKFZ VS VEF TXSV IEFGF ZFCAGPF VEF JFRZSG SC IWRF EAZ TVSSZ, A
YSYFRV HFCSGF; HMV VEF IGFVDEFZ CAVEFG IAT PGSJFUUWRP SR EWT CADF SR
VEF XAJFYFRV WR VEAV TXSV, ARZ VEF CWPMGF VEAV TVSSZ HFTWZF EWY IAT VEF
CWPMGF SC A ZAGK TVSMV ISYAR, KRWVVWRP.

“OSM ZSPT!” TAWZ VEF YAGNMWT, HMV TYSSVEUO, ARZ IWVE AR MRDEARPFZ CGSRV,
FQDFXV AT VS VEF TXSVT SR EWT RSTF: “W ISMUZ GWZF SJFG ARO SC OSM JFGO
IWUUWRPUO, ARZ FQVFGYWRAVF OSM CGSY VEF FAGVE. WC W KRFI IEWDE GATDAU
VEGFI AV VEF DAGGWAPF, ARZ WC VEAV HGWPARZ IFGF TMCCWDWFRVUO RFAG WV, EF
TESMUZ HF DGMTEFZ MRZFG VEF IEFFUT.”

TS DSIFZ IAT VEFWG DSRZWVWSR, ARZ TS USRP ARZ EAGZ VEFWG FQXFGWFRDF SC
IEAV TMDE A YAR DSMUZ ZS VS VEFY, IWVEWR VEF UAI ARZ HFOSRZ WV, VEAV RSV
A JSWDF, SG A EARZ, SG FJFR AR FOF IAT GAWTFZ. AYSRP VEF YFR, RSV SRF.
HMV VEF ISYAR IES TVSSZ KRWVVWRP USSKFZ MX TVFAZWUO, ARZ USSKFZ VEF
YAGNMWT WR VEF CADF. WV IAT RSV CSG EWT ZWPRWVO VS RSVWDF WV; EWT
DSRVFYXVMSMT FOFT XATTFZ SJFG EFG, ARZ SJFG AUU VEF SVEFG GAVT; ARZ EF
UFARFZ HADK WR EWT TFAV APAWR, ARZ PAJF VEF ISGZ “PS SR!”

EF IAT ZGWJFR SR, ARZ SVEFG DAGGWAPFT DAYF IEWGUWRP HO WR NMWDK
TMDDFTTWSR; VEF YWRWTVFG, VEF TVAVF-XGSLFDVSG, VEF CAGYFG-PFRFGAU, VEF
ZSDVSG, VEF UAIOFG, VEF FDDUFTWATVWD, VEF PGARZ SXFGA, VEF DSYFZO, VEF
