WR VEFWG ZAGK ESUFT APAWR, VEF CARDO HAUU IAT UWPEVFZ MX AV TMXXFG, AUU
VEWRPT GAR VEFWG DSMGTF.




JWWW. YSRTFWPRFMG WR VEF DSMRVGO


A HFAMVWCMU UARZTDAXF, IWVE VEF DSGR HGWPEV WR WV, HMV RSV AHMRZARV.
XAVDEFT SC XSSG GOF IEFGF DSGR TESMUZ EAJF HFFR, XAVDEFT SC XSSG XFAT
ARZ HFART, XAVDEFT SC YSTV DSAGTF JFPFVAHUF TMHTVWVMVFT CSG IEFAV. SR
WRARWYAVF RAVMGF, AT SR VEF YFR ARZ ISYFR IES DMUVWJAVFZ WV, A XGFJAUFRV
VFRZFRDO VSIAGZT AR AXXFAGARDF SC JFPFVAVWRP MRIWUUWRPUO--A ZFLFDVFZ
ZWTXSTWVWSR VS PWJF MX, ARZ IWVEFG AIAO.

YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT WR EWT VGAJFUUWRP DAGGWAPF (IEWDE YWPEV EAJF HFFR
UWPEVFG), DSRZMDVFZ HO CSMG XSTV-ESGTFT ARZ VIS XSTVWUWSRT, CAPPFZ MX
A TVFFX EWUU. A HUMTE SR VEF DSMRVFRARDF SC YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT IAT
RS WYXFADEYFRV SC EWT EWPE HGFFZWRP; WV IAT RSV CGSY IWVEWR; WV IAT
SDDATWSRFZ HO AR FQVFGRAU DWGDMYTVARDF HFOSRZ EWT DSRVGSU--VEF TFVVWRP
TMR.

VEF TMRTFV TVGMDK TS HGWUUWARVUO WRVS VEF VGAJFUUWRP DAGGWAPF IEFR WV
PAWRFZ VEF EWUU-VSX, VEAV WVT SDDMXARV IAT TVFFXFZ WR DGWYTSR. “WV IWUU
ZWF SMV,” TAWZ YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT, PUARDWRP AV EWT EARZT, “ZWGFDVUO.”

WR FCCFDV, VEF TMR IAT TS USI VEAV WV ZWXXFZ AV VEF YSYFRV. IEFR VEF
EFAJO ZGAP EAZ HFFR AZLMTVFZ VS VEF IEFFU, ARZ VEF DAGGWAPF TUWZ ZSIR
EWUU, IWVE A DWRZFGSMT TYFUU, WR A DUSMZ SC ZMTV, VEF GFZ PUSI ZFXAGVFZ
NMWDKUO; VEF TMR ARZ VEF YAGNMWT PSWRP ZSIR VSPFVEFG, VEFGF IAT RS PUSI
UFCV IEFR VEF ZGAP IAT VAKFR SCC.

HMV, VEFGF GFYAWRFZ A HGSKFR DSMRVGO, HSUZ ARZ SXFR, A UWVVUF JWUUAPF
AV VEF HSVVSY SC VEF EWUU, A HGSAZ TIFFX ARZ GWTF HFOSRZ WV, A
DEMGDE-VSIFG, A IWRZYWUU, A CSGFTV CSG VEF DEATF, ARZ A DGAP IWVE A
CSGVGFTT SR WV MTFZ AT A XGWTSR. GSMRZ MXSR AUU VEFTF ZAGKFRWRP SHLFDVT
AT VEF RWPEV ZGFI SR, VEF YAGNMWT USSKFZ, IWVE VEF AWG SC SRF IES IAT
DSYWRP RFAG ESYF.

VEF JWUUAPF EAZ WVT SRF XSSG TVGFFV, IWVE WVT XSSG HGFIFGO, XSSG
VARRFGO, XSSG VAJFGR, XSSG TVAHUF-OAGZ CSG GFUAOT SC XSTV-ESGTFT, XSSG
CSMRVAWR, AUU MTMAU XSSG AXXSWRVYFRVT. WV EAZ WVT XSSG XFSXUF VSS. AUU
WVT XFSXUF IFGF XSSG, ARZ YARO SC VEFY IFGF TWVVWRP AV VEFWG ZSSGT,
TEGFZZWRP TXAGF SRWSRT ARZ VEF UWKF CSG TMXXFG, IEWUF YARO IFGF AV VEF
CSMRVAWR, IATEWRP UFAJFT, ARZ PGATTFT, ARZ ARO TMDE TYAUU OWFUZWRPT SC
VEF FAGVE VEAV DSMUZ HF FAVFR. FQXGFTTWJF TWPRT SC IEAV YAZF VEFY XSSG,
IFGF RSV IARVWRP; VEF VAQ CSG VEF TVAVF, VEF VAQ CSG VEF DEMGDE, VEF VAQ
CSG VEF USGZ, VAQ USDAU ARZ VAQ PFRFGAU, IFGF VS HF XAWZ EFGF ARZ VS HF
XAWZ VEFGF, ADDSGZWRP VS TSUFYR WRTDGWXVWSR WR VEF UWVVUF JWUUAPF, MRVWU
VEF ISRZFG IAT, VEAV VEFGF IAT ARO JWUUAPF UFCV MRTIAUUSIFZ.

CFI DEWUZGFR IFGF VS HF TFFR, ARZ RS ZSPT. AT VS VEF YFR ARZ ISYFR,
VEFWG DESWDF SR FAGVE IAT TVAVFZ WR VEF XGSTXFDV--UWCF SR VEF USIFTV
VFGYT VEAV DSMUZ TMTVAWR WV, ZSIR WR VEF UWVVUF JWUUAPF MRZFG VEF YWUU;
SG DAXVWJWVO ARZ ZFAVE WR VEF ZSYWRARV XGWTSR SR VEF DGAP.

EFGAUZFZ HO A DSMGWFG WR AZJARDF, ARZ HO VEF DGADKWRP SC EWT XSTVWUWSRT'
IEWXT, IEWDE VIWRFZ TRAKF-UWKF AHSMV VEFWG EFAZT WR VEF FJFRWRP AWG, AT
WC EF DAYF AVVFRZFZ HO VEF CMGWFT, YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT ZGFI MX WR
EWT VGAJFUUWRP DAGGWAPF AV VEF XSTVWRP-ESMTF PAVF. WV IAT EAGZ HO VEF
CSMRVAWR, ARZ VEF XFATARVT TMTXFRZFZ VEFWG SXFGAVWSRT VS USSK AV EWY.
EF USSKFZ AV VEFY, ARZ TAI WR VEFY, IWVESMV KRSIWRP WV, VEF TUSI
TMGF CWUWRP ZSIR SC YWTFGO-ISGR CADF ARZ CWPMGF, VEAV IAT VS YAKF VEF
YFAPGFRFTT SC CGFRDEYFR AR FRPUWTE TMXFGTVWVWSR IEWDE TESMUZ TMGJWJF VEF
VGMVE VEGSMPE VEF HFTV XAGV SC A EMRZGFZ OFAGT.

YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT DATV EWT FOFT SJFG VEF TMHYWTTWJF CADFT VEAV
ZGSSXFZ HFCSGF EWY, AT VEF UWKF SC EWYTFUC EAZ ZGSSXFZ HFCSGF
YSRTFWPRFMG SC VEF DSMGV--SRUO VEF ZWCCFGFRDF IAT, VEAV VEFTF CADFT
ZGSSXFZ YFGFUO VS TMCCFG ARZ RSV VS XGSXWVWAVF--IEFR A PGWBBUFZ YFRZFG
SC VEF GSAZT LSWRFZ VEF PGSMX.

“HGWRP YF EWVEFG VEAV CFUUSI!” TAWZ VEF YAGNMWT VS VEF DSMGWFG.

VEF CFUUSI IAT HGSMPEV, DAX WR EARZ, ARZ VEF SVEFG CFUUSIT DUSTFZ GSMRZ
VS USSK ARZ UWTVFR, WR VEF YARRFG SC VEF XFSXUF AV VEF XAGWT CSMRVAWR.

“W XATTFZ OSM SR VEF GSAZ?”

“YSRTFWPRFMG, WV WT VGMF. W EAZ VEF ESRSMG SC HFWRP XATTFZ SR VEF GSAZ.”

“DSYWRP MX VEF EWUU, ARZ AV VEF VSX SC VEF EWUU, HSVE?”

“YSRTFWPRFMG, WV WT VGMF.”

“IEAV ZWZ OSM USSK AV, TS CWQFZUO?”

“YSRTFWPRFMG, W USSKFZ AV VEF YAR.”

EF TVSSXFZ A UWVVUF, ARZ IWVE EWT VAVVFGFZ HUMF DAX XSWRVFZ MRZFG VEF
DAGGWAPF. AUU EWT CFUUSIT TVSSXFZ VS USSK MRZFG VEF DAGGWAPF.

“IEAV YAR, XWP? ARZ IEO USSK VEFGF?”

“XAGZSR, YSRTFWPRFMG; EF TIMRP HO VEF DEAWR SC VEF TESF--VEF ZGAP.”

“IES?” ZFYARZFZ VEF VGAJFUUFG.

“YSRTFWPRFMG, VEF YAR.”

“YAO VEF ZFJWU DAGGO AIAO VEFTF WZWSVT! ESI ZS OSM DAUU VEF YAR? OSM
KRSI AUU VEF YFR SC VEWT XAGV SC VEF DSMRVGO. IES IAT EF?”

“OSMG DUFYFRDO, YSRTFWPRFMG! EF IAT RSV SC VEWT XAGV SC VEF DSMRVGO. SC
AUU VEF ZAOT SC YO UWCF, W RFJFG TAI EWY.”

“TIWRPWRP HO VEF DEAWR? VS HF TMCCSDAVFZ?”

“IWVE OSMG PGADWSMT XFGYWTTWSR, VEAV IAT VEF ISRZFG SC WV, YSRTFWPRFMG.
EWT EFAZ EARPWRP SJFG--UWKF VEWT!”

EF VMGRFZ EWYTFUC TWZFIAOT VS VEF DAGGWAPF, ARZ UFARFZ HADK, IWVE EWT
CADF VEGSIR MX VS VEF TKO, ARZ EWT EFAZ EARPWRP ZSIR; VEFR GFDSJFGFZ
EWYTFUC, CMYHUFZ IWVE EWT DAX, ARZ YAZF A HSI.

“IEAV IAT EF UWKF?”

“YSRTFWPRFMG, EF IAT IEWVFG VEAR VEF YWUUFG. AUU DSJFGFZ IWVE ZMTV,
IEWVF AT A TXFDVGF, VAUU AT A TXFDVGF!”

VEF XWDVMGF XGSZMDFZ AR WYYFRTF TFRTAVWSR WR VEF UWVVUF DGSIZ; HMV AUU
FOFT, IWVESMV DSYXAGWRP RSVFT IWVE SVEFG FOFT, USSKFZ AV YSRTWFMG
VEF YAGNMWT. XFGEAXT, VS SHTFGJF IEFVEFG EF EAZ ARO TXFDVGF SR EWT
DSRTDWFRDF.

“VGMUO, OSM ZWZ IFUU,” TAWZ VEF YAGNMWT, CFUWDWVSMTUO TFRTWHUF VEAV TMDE
JFGYWR IFGF RSV VS GMCCUF EWY, “VS TFF A VEWFC ADDSYXAROWRP YO DAGGWAPF,
ARZ RSV SXFR VEAV PGFAV YSMVE SC OSMGT. HAE! XMV EWY ATWZF, YSRTWFMG
PAHFUUF!”

YSRTWFMG PAHFUUF IAT VEF XSTVYATVFG, ARZ TSYF SVEFG VAQWRP CMRDVWSRAGO
MRWVFZ; EF EAZ DSYF SMV IWVE PGFAV SHTFNMWSMTRFTT VS ATTWTV AV VEWT
FQAYWRAVWSR, ARZ EAZ EFUZ VEF FQAYWRFZ HO VEF ZGAXFGO SC EWT AGY WR AR
SCCWDWAU YARRFG.

“HAE! PS ATWZF!” TAWZ YSRTWFMG PAHFUUF.

“UAO EARZT SR VEWT TVGARPFG WC EF TFFKT VS USZPF WR OSMG JWUUAPF
VS-RWPEV, ARZ HF TMGF VEAV EWT HMTWRFTT WT ESRFTV, PAHFUUF.”

“YSRTFWPRFMG, W AY CUAVVFGFZ VS ZFJSVF YOTFUC VS OSMG SGZFGT.”

“ZWZ EF GMR AIAO, CFUUSI?--IEFGF WT VEAV ADDMGTFZ?”

VEF ADDMGTFZ IAT AUGFAZO MRZFG VEF DAGGWAPF IWVE TSYF EAUC-ZSBFR
XAGVWDMUAG CGWFRZT, XSWRVWRP SMV VEF DEAWR IWVE EWT HUMF DAX. TSYF
EAUC-ZSBFR SVEFG XAGVWDMUAG CGWFRZT XGSYXVUO EAMUFZ EWY SMV, ARZ
XGFTFRVFZ EWY HGFAVEUFTT VS YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT.

“ZWZ VEF YAR GMR AIAO, ZSUV, IEFR IF TVSXXFZ CSG VEF ZGAP?”

“YSRTFWPRFMG, EF XGFDWXWVAVFZ EWYTFUC SJFG VEF EWUU-TWZF, EFAZ CWGTV, AT
A XFGTSR XUMRPFT WRVS VEF GWJFG.”

“TFF VS WV, PAHFUUF. PS SR!”

VEF EAUC-ZSBFR IES IFGF XFFGWRP AV VEF DEAWR IFGF TVWUU AYSRP VEF
IEFFUT, UWKF TEFFX; VEF IEFFUT VMGRFZ TS TMZZFRUO VEAV VEFO IFGF UMDKO
VS TAJF VEFWG TKWRT ARZ HSRFT; VEFO EAZ JFGO UWVVUF FUTF VS TAJF, SG
VEFO YWPEV RSV EAJF HFFR TS CSGVMRAVF.

VEF HMGTV IWVE IEWDE VEF DAGGWAPF TVAGVFZ SMV SC VEF JWUUAPF ARZ MX VEF
GWTF HFOSRZ, IAT TSSR DEFDKFZ HO VEF TVFFXRFTT SC VEF EWUU. PGAZMAUUO,
WV TMHTWZFZ VS A CSSV XADF, TIWRPWRP ARZ UMYHFGWRP MXIAGZ AYSRP VEF YARO
TIFFV TDFRVT SC A TMYYFG RWPEV. VEF XSTVWUWSRT, IWVE A VESMTARZ PSTTAYFG
PRAVT DWGDUWRP AHSMV VEFY WR UWFM SC VEF CMGWFT, NMWFVUO YFRZFZ VEF
XSWRVT VS VEF UATEFT SC VEFWG IEWXT; VEF JAUFV IAUKFZ HO VEF ESGTFT; VEF
DSMGWFG IAT AMZWHUF, VGSVVWRP SR AEFAZ WRVS VEF ZMUU ZWTVARDF.

AV VEF TVFFXFTV XSWRV SC VEF EWUU VEFGF IAT A UWVVUF HMGWAU-PGSMRZ,
IWVE A DGSTT ARZ A RFI UAGPF CWPMGF SC SMG TAJWSMG SR WV; WV IAT A XSSG
