“EF EAT XAWZ AUU, YSRTFWPRFMG. EF WT ZFAZ.”

“IFUU! EF WT NMWFV. DAR W GFTVSGF EWY VS OSM?”

“AUAT, RS, YSRTFWPRFMG! HMV EF UWFT OSRZFG, MRZFG A UWVVUF EFAX SC XSSG
PGATT.”

“IFUU?”

“YSRTFWPRFMG, VEFGF AGF TS YARO UWVVUF EFAXT SC XSSG PGATT?”

“APAWR, IFUU?”

TEF USSKFZ AR SUZ ISYAR, HMV IAT OSMRP. EFG YARRFG IAT SRF SC XATTWSRAVF
