“YSRTFWPRFMG, RSV OFV.”




WQ. VEF PSGPSR'T EFAZ


WV IAT A EFAJO YATT SC HMWUZWRP, VEAV DEAVFAM SC YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT,
IWVE A UAGPF TVSRF DSMGVOAGZ HFCSGF WV, ARZ VIS TVSRF TIFFXT SC
TVAWGDATF YFFVWRP WR A TVSRF VFGGADF HFCSGF VEF XGWRDWXAU ZSSG. A TVSRO
