TVSRF CUSIFGT, ARZ TVSRF CADFT SC YFR, ARZ TVSRF EFAZT SC UWSRT, WR
AUU ZWGFDVWSRT. AT WC VEF PSGPSR'T EFAZ EAZ TMGJFOFZ WV, IEFR WV IAT
CWRWTEFZ, VIS DFRVMGWFT APS.

MX VEF HGSAZ CUWPEV SC TEAUUSI TVFXT, YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT, CUAYHFAM
XGFDFZFZ, IFRV CGSY EWT DAGGWAPF, TMCCWDWFRVUO ZWTVMGHWRP VEF ZAGKRFTT
VS FUWDWV USMZ GFYSRTVGARDF CGSY AR SIU WR VEF GSSC SC VEF PGFAV XWUF
SC TVAHUF HMWUZWRP AIAO AYSRP VEF VGFFT. AUU FUTF IAT TS NMWFV, VEAV VEF
CUAYHFAM DAGGWFZ MX VEF TVFXT, ARZ VEF SVEFG CUAYHFAM EFUZ AV VEF PGFAV
ZSSG, HMGRV AT WC VEFO IFGF WR A DUSTF GSSY SC TVAVF, WRTVFAZ SC HFWRP
WR VEF SXFR RWPEV-AWG. SVEFG TSMRZ VEAR VEF SIU'T JSWDF VEFGF IAT RSRF,
TAJF VEF CAUUWRP SC A CSMRVAWR WRVS WVT TVSRF HATWR; CSG, WV IAT SRF SC
VESTF ZAGK RWPEVT VEAV ESUZ VEFWG HGFAVE HO VEF ESMG VSPFVEFG, ARZ VEFR
EFAJF A USRP USI TWPE, ARZ ESUZ VEFWG HGFAVE APAWR.

VEF PGFAV ZSSG DUARPFZ HFEWRZ EWY, ARZ YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT DGSTTFZ A
EAUU PGWY IWVE DFGVAWR SUZ HSAG-TXFAGT, TISGZT, ARZ KRWJFT SC VEF DEATF;
PGWYYFG IWVE DFGVAWR EFAJO GWZWRP-GSZT ARZ GWZWRP-IEWXT, SC IEWDE YARO A
XFATARV, PSRF VS EWT HFRFCADVSG ZFAVE, EAZ CFUV VEF IFWPEV IEFR EWT USGZ
IAT ARPGO.

AJSWZWRP VEF UAGPFG GSSYT, IEWDE IFGF ZAGK ARZ YAZF CATV CSG VEF RWPEV,
