AV A ZWTAZJARVAPF. VEFTF UWVVUF WRTVGMYFRVT SC DSGGFDVWSR, VEFTF PFRVUF
AWZT VS VEF XSIFG ARZ ESRSMG SC CAYWUWFT, VEFTF TUWPEV CAJSMGT VEAV
YWPEV TS WRDSYYSZF OSM, AGF SRUO VS HF SHVAWRFZ RSI HO WRVFGFTV
ARZ WYXSGVMRWVO. VEFO AGF TSMPEV HO TS YARO, ARZ VEFO AGF PGARVFZ
(DSYXAGAVWJFUO) VS TS CFI! WV MTFZ RSV VS HF TS, HMV CGARDF WR AUU TMDE
