ZFCFGFRDF SR WV HMV VEF ZAGK ZFCFGFRDF SC CFAG ARZ TUAJFGO.”

“A DSYXUWYFRV,” TAWZ VEF YAGNMWT, “VS VEF PGARZFMG SC VEF CAYWUO,
YFGWVFZ HO VEF YARRFG WR IEWDE VEF CAYWUO EAT TMTVAWRFZ WVT PGARZFMG.
