VFGYWRAVF SMG DSRCFGFRDF CSG VEF RWPEV?”

“A YSYFRV YSGF.”

“AR ESMG, WC OSM XUFATF.”

“TWG,” TAWZ VEF RFXEFI, “IF EAJF ZSRF IGSRP, ARZ AGF GFAXWRP VEF CGMWVT
SC IGSRP.”

“_IF_ EAJF ZSRF IGSRP?” GFXFAVFZ VEF YAGNMWT, IWVE AR WRNMWGWRP TYWUF,
ARZ ZFUWDAVFUO XSWRVWRP, CWGTV VS EWT RFXEFI, VEFR VS EWYTFUC.

“SMG CAYWUO; SMG ESRSMGAHUF CAYWUO, IESTF ESRSMG WT SC TS YMDE ADDSMRV
VS HSVE SC MT, WR TMDE ZWCCFGFRV IAOT. FJFR WR YO CAVEFG'T VWYF, IF ZWZ
A ISGUZ SC IGSRP, WRLMGWRP FJFGO EMYAR DGFAVMGF IES DAYF HFVIFFR MT ARZ
SMG XUFATMGF, IEAVFJFG WV IAT. IEO RFFZ W TXFAK SC YO CAVEFG'T VWYF,
IEFR WV WT FNMAUUO OSMGT? DAR W TFXAGAVF YO CAVEFG'T VIWR-HGSVEFG, LSWRV
WREFGWVSG, ARZ RFQV TMDDFTTSG, CGSY EWYTFUC?”

“ZFAVE EAT ZSRF VEAV!” TAWZ VEF YAGNMWT.

“ARZ EAT UFCV YF,” ARTIFGFZ VEF RFXEFI, “HSMRZ VS A TOTVFY VEAV WT
CGWPEVCMU VS YF, GFTXSRTWHUF CSG WV, HMV XSIFGUFTT WR WV; TFFKWRP VS
FQFDMVF VEF UATV GFNMFTV SC YO ZFAG YSVEFG'T UWXT, ARZ SHFO VEF UATV
USSK SC YO ZFAG YSVEFG'T FOFT, IEWDE WYXUSGFZ YF VS EAJF YFGDO ARZ VS
GFZGFTT; ARZ VSGVMGFZ HO TFFKWRP ATTWTVARDF ARZ XSIFG WR JAWR.”

“TFFKWRP VEFY CGSY YF, YO RFXEFI,” TAWZ VEF YAGNMWT, VSMDEWRP EWY SR VEF
HGFATV IWVE EWT CSGFCWRPFG--VEFO IFGF RSI TVARZWRP HO VEF EFAGVE--“OSM
IWUU CSG FJFG TFFK VEFY WR JAWR, HF ATTMGFZ.”

FJFGO CWRF TVGAWPEV UWRF WR VEF DUFAG IEWVFRFTT SC EWT CADF, IAT
DGMFUUO, DGACVWUO, ARZ DUSTFUO DSYXGFTTFZ, IEWUF EF TVSSZ USSKWRP
NMWFVUO AV EWT RFXEFI, IWVE EWT TRMCC-HSQ WR EWT EARZ. SRDF APAWR EF
VSMDEFZ EWY SR VEF HGFATV, AT VESMPE EWT CWRPFG IFGF VEF CWRF XSWRV SC
A TYAUU TISGZ, IWVE IEWDE, WR ZFUWDAVF CWRFTTF, EF GAR EWY VEGSMPE VEF
HSZO, ARZ TAWZ,

“YO CGWFRZ, W IWUU ZWF, XFGXFVMAVWRP VEF TOTVFY MRZFG IEWDE W EAJF
UWJFZ.”

IEFR EF EAZ TAWZ WV, EF VSSK A DMUYWRAVWRP XWRDE SC TRMCC, ARZ XMV EWT
HSQ WR EWT XSDKFV.

“HFVVFG VS HF A GAVWSRAU DGFAVMGF,” EF AZZFZ VEFR, ACVFG GWRPWRP A TYAUU
HFUU SR VEF VAHUF, “ARZ ADDFXV OSMG RAVMGAU ZFTVWRO. HMV OSM AGF USTV,
YSRTWFMG DEAGUFT, W TFF.”

“VEWT XGSXFGVO ARZ CGARDF AGF USTV VS YF,” TAWZ VEF RFXEFI, TAZUO; “W
GFRSMRDF VEFY.”

“AGF VEFO HSVE OSMGT VS GFRSMRDF? CGARDF YAO HF, HMV WT VEF XGSXFGVO? WV
WT TDAGDFUO ISGVE YFRVWSRWRP; HMV, WT WV OFV?”

“W EAZ RS WRVFRVWSR, WR VEF ISGZT W MTFZ, VS DUAWY WV OFV. WC WV XATTFZ
VS YF CGSY OSM, VS-YSGGSI--”

“IEWDE W EAJF VEF JARWVO VS ESXF WT RSV XGSHAHUF.”

“--SG VIFRVO OFAGT EFRDF--”

“OSM ZS YF VSS YMDE ESRSMG,” TAWZ VEF YAGNMWT; “TVWUU, W XGFCFG VEAV
TMXXSTWVWSR.”

“--W ISMUZ AHARZSR WV, ARZ UWJF SVEFGIWTF ARZ FUTFIEFGF. WV WT UWVVUF VS
GFUWRNMWTE. IEAV WT WV HMV A IWUZFGRFTT SC YWTFGO ARZ GMWR!”

“EAE!” TAWZ VEF YAGNMWT, PUARDWRP GSMRZ VEF UMQMGWSMT GSSY.

“VS VEF FOF WV WT CAWG FRSMPE, EFGF; HMV TFFR WR WVT WRVFPGWVO,
MRZFG VEF TKO, ARZ HO VEF ZAOUWPEV, WV WT A DGMYHUWRP VSIFG SC IATVF,
YWTYARAPFYFRV, FQVSGVWSR, ZFHV, YSGVPAPF, SXXGFTTWSR, EMRPFG, RAKFZRFTT,
ARZ TMCCFGWRP.”

“EAE!” TAWZ VEF YAGNMWT APAWR, WR A IFUU-TAVWTCWFZ YARRFG.

“WC WV FJFG HFDSYFT YWRF, WV TEAUU HF XMV WRVS TSYF EARZT HFVVFG
NMAUWCWFZ VS CGFF WV TUSIUO (WC TMDE A VEWRP WT XSTTWHUF) CGSY VEF
