“ARZ OSM?” TAWZ VEF MRDUF. “CSGPWJF YO DMGWSTWVO; ZS OSM, MRZFG OSMG RFI
XEWUSTSXEO, PGADWSMTUO WRVFRZ VS UWJF?”

“W YMTV ZS, VS UWJF, IEAV SVEFGT SC YO DSMRVGOYFR, FJFR IWVE RSHWUWVO AV
VEFWG HADKT, YAO EAJF VS ZS TSYF ZAO--ISGK.”

“WR FRPUARZ, CSG FQAYXUF?”

“OFT. VEF CAYWUO ESRSMG, TWG, WT TACF CGSY YF WR VEWT DSMRVGO. VEF
CAYWUO RAYF DAR TMCCFG CGSY YF WR RS SVEFG, CSG W HFAG WV WR RS SVEFG.”

VEF GWRPWRP SC VEF HFUU EAZ DAMTFZ VEF AZLSWRWRP HFZ-DEAYHFG VS HF
UWPEVFZ. WV RSI TESRF HGWPEVUO, VEGSMPE VEF ZSSG SC DSYYMRWDAVWSR. VEF
