“W EAJF AUGFAZO TAWZ, VEAV CSG YO XGSTXFGWRP VEFGF, W AY TFRTWHUF W YAO
HF WRZFHVFZ VS OSM, TWG. CSG VEF GFTV, WV WT YO GFCMPF.”

“VEFO TAO, VESTF HSATVCMU FRPUWTE, VEAV WV WT VEF GFCMPF SC YARO. OSM
KRSI A DSYXAVGWSV IES EAT CSMRZ A GFCMPF VEFGF? A ZSDVSG?”

“OFT.”

“IWVE A ZAMPEVFG?”

“OFT.”

“OFT,” TAWZ VEF YAGNMWT. “OSM AGF CAVWPMFZ. PSSZ RWPEV!”

AT EF HFRV EWT EFAZ WR EWT YSTV DSMGVUO YARRFG, VEFGF IAT A TFDGFDO
WR EWT TYWUWRP CADF, ARZ EF DSRJFOFZ AR AWG SC YOTVFGO VS VESTF ISGZT,
