TVGAWPEV UWXT, ARZ VEF YAGKWRPT WR VEF RSTF, DMGJFZ IWVE A TAGDATY VEAV
USSKFZ EARZTSYFUO ZWAHSUWD.

“OFT,” GFXFAVFZ VEF YAGNMWT. “A ZSDVSG IWVE A ZAMPEVFG. OFT. TS
DSYYFRDFT VEF RFI XEWUSTSXEO! OSM AGF CAVWPMFZ. PSSZ RWPEV!”

WV ISMUZ EAJF HFFR SC AT YMDE AJAWU VS WRVFGGSPAVF ARO TVSRF CADF
SMVTWZF VEF DEAVFAM AT VS WRVFGGSPAVF VEAV CADF SC EWT. VEF RFXEFI
USSKFZ AV EWY, WR JAWR, WR XATTWRP SR VS VEF ZSSG.

“PSSZ RWPEV!” TAWZ VEF MRDUF. “W USSK VS VEF XUFATMGF SC TFFWRP OSM
APAWR WR VEF YSGRWRP. PSSZ GFXSTF! UWPEV YSRTWFMG YO RFXEFI VS EWT
