VEF JAUFV DSYF ARZ PSRF, YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT IAUKFZ VS ARZ CGS WR EWT
USSTF DEAYHFG-GSHF, VS XGFXAGF EWYTFUC PFRVUO CSG TUFFX, VEAV ESV TVWUU
RWPEV. GMTVUWRP AHSMV VEF GSSY, EWT TSCVUO-TUWXXFGFZ CFFV YAKWRP RS
RSWTF SR VEF CUSSG, EF YSJFZ UWKF A GFCWRFZ VWPFG:--USSKFZ UWKF TSYF
FRDEARVFZ YAGNMWT SC VEF WYXFRWVFRVUO IWDKFZ TSGV, WR TVSGO, IESTF
XFGWSZWDAU DEARPF WRVS VWPFG CSGY IAT FWVEFG LMTV PSWRP SCC, SG LMTV
DSYWRP SR.

EF YSJFZ CGSY FRZ VS FRZ SC EWT JSUMXVMSMT HFZGSSY, USSKWRP APAWR AV VEF
TDGAXT SC VEF ZAO'T LSMGRFO VEAV DAYF MRHWZZFR WRVS EWT YWRZ; VEF TUSI
VSWU MX VEF EWUU AV TMRTFV, VEF TFVVWRP TMR, VEF ZFTDFRV, VEF YWUU, VEF
