VEF CSMRVAWR, ARZ VEF YFRZFG SC GSAZT IWVE EWT HUMF DAX XSWRVWRP SMV VEF
DEAWR MRZFG VEF DAGGWAPF. VEAV CSMRVAWR TMPPFTVFZ VEF XAGWT CSMRVAWR,
VEF UWVVUF HMRZUF UOWRP SR VEF TVFX, VEF ISYFR HFRZWRP SJFG WV, ARZ VEF
VAUU YAR IWVE EWT AGYT MX, DGOWRP, “ZFAZ!”

“W AY DSSU RSI,” TAWZ YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT, “ARZ YAO PS VS HFZ.”

TS, UFAJWRP SRUO SRF UWPEV HMGRWRP SR VEF UAGPF EFAGVE, EF UFV EWT VEWR
PAMBF DMGVAWRT CAUU AGSMRZ EWY, ARZ EFAGZ VEF RWPEV HGFAK WVT TWUFRDF
IWVE A USRP TWPE AT EF DSYXSTFZ EWYTFUC VS TUFFX.

VEF TVSRF CADFT SR VEF SMVFG IAUUT TVAGFZ HUWRZUO AV VEF HUADK RWPEV
CSG VEGFF EFAJO ESMGT; CSG VEGFF EFAJO ESMGT, VEF ESGTFT WR VEF TVAHUFT
GAVVUFZ AV VEFWG GADKT, VEF ZSPT HAGKFZ, ARZ VEF SIU YAZF A RSWTF IWVE
JFGO UWVVUF GFTFYHUARDF WR WV VS VEF RSWTF DSRJFRVWSRAUUO ATTWPRFZ VS
VEF SIU HO YFR-XSFVT. HMV WV WT VEF SHTVWRAVF DMTVSY SC TMDE DGFAVMGFT
EAGZUO FJFG VS TAO IEAV WT TFV ZSIR CSG VEFY.

CSG VEGFF EFAJO ESMGT, VEF TVSRF CADFT SC VEF DEAVFAM, UWSR ARZ EMYAR,
TVAGFZ HUWRZUO AV VEF RWPEV. ZFAZ ZAGKRFTT UAO SR AUU VEF UARZTDAXF,
ZFAZ ZAGKRFTT AZZFZ WVT SIR EMTE VS VEF EMTEWRP ZMTV SR AUU VEF GSAZT.
VEF HMGWAU-XUADF EAZ PSV VS VEF XATT VEAV WVT UWVVUF EFAXT SC XSSG PGATT
IFGF MRZWTVWRPMWTEAHUF CGSY SRF ARSVEFG; VEF CWPMGF SR VEF DGSTT YWPEV
EAJF DSYF ZSIR, CSG AROVEWRP VEAV DSMUZ HF TFFR SC WV. WR VEF JWUUAPF,
VAQFGT ARZ VAQFZ IFGF CATV ATUFFX. ZGFAYWRP, XFGEAXT, SC HARNMFVT, AT
VEF TVAGJFZ MTMAUUO ZS, ARZ SC FATF ARZ GFTV, AT VEF ZGWJFR TUAJF ARZ
VEF OSKFZ SQ YAO, WVT UFAR WREAHWVARVT TUFXV TSMRZUO, ARZ IFGF CFZ ARZ
CGFFZ.

VEF CSMRVAWR WR VEF JWUUAPF CUSIFZ MRTFFR ARZ MREFAGZ, ARZ VEF CSMRVAWR
AV VEF DEAVFAM ZGSXXFZ MRTFFR ARZ MREFAGZ--HSVE YFUVWRP AIAO, UWKF VEF
YWRMVFT VEAV IFGF CAUUWRP CGSY VEF TXGWRP SC VWYF--VEGSMPE VEGFF ZAGK
ESMGT. VEFR, VEF PGFO IAVFG SC HSVE HFPAR VS HF PESTVUO WR VEF UWPEV,
ARZ VEF FOFT SC VEF TVSRF CADFT SC VEF DEAVFAM IFGF SXFRFZ.

UWPEVFG ARZ UWPEVFG, MRVWU AV UATV VEF TMR VSMDEFZ VEF VSXT SC VEF TVWUU
VGFFT, ARZ XSMGFZ WVT GAZWARDF SJFG VEF EWUU. WR VEF PUSI, VEF IAVFG
SC VEF DEAVFAM CSMRVAWR TFFYFZ VS VMGR VS HUSSZ, ARZ VEF TVSRF CADFT
DGWYTSRFZ. VEF DAGSU SC VEF HWGZT IAT USMZ ARZ EWPE, ARZ, SR VEF
IFAVEFG-HFAVFR TWUU SC VEF PGFAV IWRZSI SC VEF HFZ-DEAYHFG SC YSRTWFMG
VEF YAGNMWT, SRF UWVVUF HWGZ TARP WVT TIFFVFTV TSRP IWVE AUU WVT YWPEV.
AV VEWT, VEF RFAGFTV TVSRF CADF TFFYFZ VS TVAGF AYABFZ, ARZ, IWVE SXFR
YSMVE ARZ ZGSXXFZ MRZFG-LAI, USSKFZ AIF-TVGWDKFR.

RSI, VEF TMR IAT CMUU MX, ARZ YSJFYFRV HFPAR WR VEF JWUUAPF. DATFYFRV
IWRZSIT SXFRFZ, DGABO ZSSGT IFGF MRHAGGFZ, ARZ XFSXUF DAYF CSGVE
TEWJFGWRP--DEWUUFZ, AT OFV, HO VEF RFI TIFFV AWG. VEFR HFPAR VEF GAGFUO
UWPEVFRFZ VSWU SC VEF ZAO AYSRP VEF JWUUAPF XSXMUAVWSR. TSYF, VS VEF
CSMRVAWR; TSYF, VS VEF CWFUZT; YFR ARZ ISYFR EFGF, VS ZWP ARZ ZFUJF; YFR
ARZ ISYFR VEFGF, VS TFF VS VEF XSSG UWJF TVSDK, ARZ UFAZ VEF HSRO DSIT
SMV, VS TMDE XATVMGF AT DSMUZ HF CSMRZ HO VEF GSAZTWZF. WR VEF DEMGDE
ARZ AV VEF DGSTT, A KRFFUWRP CWPMGF SG VIS; AVVFRZARV SR VEF UAVVFG
XGAOFGT, VEF UFZ DSI, VGOWRP CSG A HGFAKCATV AYSRP VEF IFFZT AV WVT
CSSV.

VEF DEAVFAM AISKF UAVFG, AT HFDAYF WVT NMAUWVO, HMV AISKF PGAZMAUUO ARZ
TMGFUO. CWGTV, VEF USRFUO HSAG-TXFAGT ARZ KRWJFT SC VEF DEATF EAZ HFFR
GFZZFRFZ AT SC SUZ; VEFR, EAZ PUFAYFZ VGFRDEARV WR VEF YSGRWRP TMRTEWRF;
RSI, ZSSGT ARZ IWRZSIT IFGF VEGSIR SXFR, ESGTFT WR VEFWG TVAHUFT USSKFZ
GSMRZ SJFG VEFWG TESMUZFGT AV VEF UWPEV ARZ CGFTERFTT XSMGWRP WR AV
ZSSGIAOT, UFAJFT TXAGKUFZ ARZ GMTVUFZ AV WGSR-PGAVFZ IWRZSIT, ZSPT
XMUUFZ EAGZ AV VEFWG DEAWRT, ARZ GFAGFZ WYXAVWFRV VS HF USSTFZ.

AUU VEFTF VGWJWAU WRDWZFRVT HFUSRPFZ VS VEF GSMVWRF SC UWCF, ARZ VEF
GFVMGR SC YSGRWRP. TMGFUO, RSV TS VEF GWRPWRP SC VEF PGFAV HFUU SC VEF
DEAVFAM, RSG VEF GMRRWRP MX ARZ ZSIR VEF TVAWGT; RSG VEF EMGGWFZ
CWPMGFT SR VEF VFGGADF; RSG VEF HSSVWRP ARZ VGAYXWRP EFGF ARZ VEFGF ARZ
FJFGOIEFGF, RSG VEF NMWDK TAZZUWRP SC ESGTFT ARZ GWZWRP AIAO?

IEAV IWRZT DSRJFOFZ VEWT EMGGO VS VEF PGWBBUFZ YFRZFG SC GSAZT, AUGFAZO
AV ISGK SR VEF EWUU-VSX HFOSRZ VEF JWUUAPF, IWVE EWT ZAO'T ZWRRFG (RSV
YMDE VS DAGGO) UOWRP WR A HMRZUF VEAV WV IAT ISGVE RS DGSI'T IEWUF VS
XFDK AV, SR A EFAX SC TVSRFT? EAZ VEF HWGZT, DAGGOWRP TSYF PGAWRT SC WV
VS A ZWTVARDF, ZGSXXFZ SRF SJFG EWY AT VEFO TSI DEARDF TFFZT? IEFVEFG SG
RS, VEF YFRZFG SC GSAZT GAR, SR VEF TMUVGO YSGRWRP, AT WC CSG EWT UWCF,
ZSIR VEF EWUU, KRFF-EWPE WR ZMTV, ARZ RFJFG TVSXXFZ VWUU EF PSV VS VEF
CSMRVAWR.

AUU VEF XFSXUF SC VEF JWUUAPF IFGF AV VEF CSMRVAWR, TVARZWRP AHSMV
WR VEFWG ZFXGFTTFZ YARRFG, ARZ IEWTXFGWRP USI, HMV TESIWRP RS SVEFG
FYSVWSRT VEAR PGWY DMGWSTWVO ARZ TMGXGWTF. VEF UFZ DSIT, EATVWUO HGSMPEV
WR ARZ VFVEFGFZ VS AROVEWRP VEAV ISMUZ ESUZ VEFY, IFGF USSKWRP TVMXWZUO
SR, SG UOWRP ZSIR DEFIWRP VEF DMZ SC RSVEWRP XAGVWDMUAGUO GFXAOWRP VEFWG
VGSMHUF, IEWDE VEFO EAZ XWDKFZ MX WR VEFWG WRVFGGMXVFZ TAMRVFG. TSYF SC
VEF XFSXUF SC VEF DEAVFAM, ARZ TSYF SC VESTF SC VEF XSTVWRP-ESMTF, ARZ
AUU VEF VAQWRP AMVESGWVWFT, IFGF AGYFZ YSGF SG UFTT, ARZ IFGF DGSIZFZ
SR VEF SVEFG TWZF SC VEF UWVVUF TVGFFV WR A XMGXSTFUFTT IAO, VEAV IAT
EWPEUO CGAMPEV IWVE RSVEWRP. AUGFAZO, VEF YFRZFG SC GSAZT EAZ XFRFVGAVFZ
WRVS VEF YWZTV SC A PGSMX SC CWCVO XAGVWDMUAG CGWFRZT, ARZ IAT TYWVWRP
EWYTFUC WR VEF HGFATV IWVE EWT HUMF DAX. IEAV ZWZ AUU VEWT XSGVFRZ,
ARZ IEAV XSGVFRZFZ VEF TIWCV ESWTVWRP-MX SC YSRTWFMG PAHFUUF HFEWRZ
A TFGJARV SR ESGTFHADK, ARZ VEF DSRJFOWRP AIAO SC VEF TAWZ PAHFUUF
(ZSMHUF-UAZFR VESMPE VEF ESGTF IAT), AV A PAUUSX, UWKF A RFI JFGTWSR SC
VEF PFGYAR HAUUAZ SC UFSRSGA?

WV XSGVFRZFZ VEAV VEFGF IAT SRF TVSRF CADF VSS YARO, MX AV VEF DEAVFAM.

VEF PSGPSR EAZ TMGJFOFZ VEF HMWUZWRP APAWR WR VEF RWPEV, ARZ EAZ AZZFZ
VEF SRF TVSRF CADF IARVWRP; VEF TVSRF CADF CSG IEWDE WV EAZ IAWVFZ
VEGSMPE AHSMV VIS EMRZGFZ OFAGT.

WV UAO HADK SR VEF XWUUSI SC YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT. WV IAT UWKF A CWRF
YATK, TMZZFRUO TVAGVUFZ, YAZF ARPGO, ARZ XFVGWCWFZ. ZGWJFR ESYF WRVS VEF
EFAGV SC VEF TVSRF CWPMGF AVVADEFZ VS WV, IAT A KRWCF. GSMRZ WVT EWUV
IAT A CGWUU SC XAXFG, SR IEWDE IAT TDGAIUFZ:

“ZGWJF EWY CATV VS EWT VSYH. VEWT, CGSY LADNMFT.”




Q. VIS XGSYWTFT


YSGF YSRVET, VS VEF RMYHFG SC VIFUJF, EAZ DSYF ARZ PSRF, ARZ YG. DEAGUFT
ZAGRAO IAT FTVAHUWTEFZ WR FRPUARZ AT A EWPEFG VFADEFG SC VEF CGFRDE
UARPMAPF IES IAT DSRJFGTARV IWVE CGFRDE UWVFGAVMGF. WR VEWT APF, EF
ISMUZ EAJF HFFR A XGSCFTTSG; WR VEAV APF, EF IAT A VMVSG. EF GFAZ IWVE
OSMRP YFR IES DSMUZ CWRZ ARO UFWTMGF ARZ WRVFGFTV CSG VEF TVMZO SC A
UWJWRP VSRPMF TXSKFR AUU SJFG VEF ISGUZ, ARZ EF DMUVWJAVFZ A VATVF CSG
WVT TVSGFT SC KRSIUFZPF ARZ CARDO. EF DSMUZ IGWVF SC VEFY, HFTWZFT, WR
TSMRZ FRPUWTE, ARZ GFRZFG VEFY WRVS TSMRZ FRPUWTE. TMDE YATVFGT IFGF RSV
AV VEAV VWYF FATWUO CSMRZ; XGWRDFT VEAV EAZ HFFR, ARZ KWRPT VEAV IFGF
VS HF, IFGF RSV OFV SC VEF VFADEFG DUATT, ARZ RS GMWRFZ RSHWUWVO EAZ
ZGSXXFZ SMV SC VFUUTSR'T UFZPFGT, VS VMGR DSSKT ARZ DAGXFRVFGT. AT A
VMVSG, IESTF AVVAWRYFRVT YAZF VEF TVMZFRV'T IAO MRMTMAUUO XUFATARV ARZ
XGSCWVAHUF, ARZ AT AR FUFPARV VGARTUAVSG IES HGSMPEV TSYFVEWRP VS EWT
ISGK HFTWZFT YFGF ZWDVWSRAGO KRSIUFZPF, OSMRP YG. ZAGRAO TSSR HFDAYF
KRSIR ARZ FRDSMGAPFZ. EF IAT IFUU ADNMAWRVFZ, YSGF-SJFG, IWVE VEF
DWGDMYTVARDFT SC EWT DSMRVGO, ARZ VESTF IFGF SC FJFG-PGSIWRP WRVFGFTV.
TS, IWVE PGFAV XFGTFJFGARDF ARZ MRVWGWRP WRZMTVGO, EF XGSTXFGFZ.

WR USRZSR, EF EAZ FQXFDVFZ RFWVEFG VS IAUK SR XAJFYFRVT SC PSUZ, RSG
VS UWF SR HFZT SC GSTFT; WC EF EAZ EAZ ARO TMDE FQAUVFZ FQXFDVAVWSR, EF
ISMUZ RSV EAJF XGSTXFGFZ. EF EAZ FQXFDVFZ UAHSMG, ARZ EF CSMRZ WV, ARZ
ZWZ WV ARZ YAZF VEF HFTV SC WV. WR VEWT, EWT XGSTXFGWVO DSRTWTVFZ.

A DFGVAWR XSGVWSR SC EWT VWYF IAT XATTFZ AV DAYHGWZPF, IEFGF EF
GFAZ IWVE MRZFGPGAZMAVFT AT A TSGV SC VSUFGAVFZ TYMPPUFG IES ZGSJF A
DSRVGAHARZ VGAZF WR FMGSXFAR UARPMAPFT, WRTVFAZ SC DSRJFOWRP PGFFK
ARZ UAVWR VEGSMPE VEF DMTVSY-ESMTF. VEF GFTV SC EWT VWYF EF XATTFZ WR
USRZSR.

RSI, CGSY VEF ZAOT IEFR WV IAT AUIAOT TMYYFG WR FZFR, VS VEFTF ZAOT
IEFR WV WT YSTVUO IWRVFG WR CAUUFR UAVWVMZFT, VEF ISGUZ SC A YAR EAT
WRJAGWAHUO PSRF SRF IAO--DEAGUFT ZAGRAO'T IAO--VEF IAO SC VEF USJF SC A
ISYAR.

EF EAZ USJFZ UMDWF YARFVVF CGSY VEF ESMG SC EWT ZARPFG. EF EAZ RFJFG
EFAGZ A TSMRZ TS TIFFV ARZ ZFAG AT VEF TSMRZ SC EFG DSYXATTWSRAVF JSWDF;
EF EAZ RFJFG TFFR A CADF TS VFRZFGUO HFAMVWCMU, AT EFGT IEFR WV IAT
DSRCGSRVFZ IWVE EWT SIR SR VEF FZPF SC VEF PGAJF VEAV EAZ HFFR ZMP CSG
EWY. HMV, EF EAZ RSV OFV TXSKFR VS EFG SR VEF TMHLFDV; VEF ATTATTWRAVWSR
AV VEF ZFTFGVFZ DEAVFAM CAG AIAO HFOSRZ VEF EFAJWRP IAVFG ARZ VEF USRP,
USRP, ZMTVO GSAZT--VEF TSUWZ TVSRF DEAVFAM IEWDE EAZ WVTFUC HFDSYF VEF
YFGF YWTV SC A ZGFAY--EAZ HFFR ZSRF A OFAG, ARZ EF EAZ RFJFG OFV, HO TS
YMDE AT A TWRPUF TXSKFR ISGZ, ZWTDUSTFZ VS EFG VEF TVAVF SC EWT EFAGV.

VEAV EF EAZ EWT GFATSRT CSG VEWT, EF KRFI CMUU IFUU. WV IAT APAWR A
TMYYFG ZAO IEFR, UAVFUO AGGWJFZ WR USRZSR CGSY EWT DSUUFPF SDDMXAVWSR,
EF VMGRFZ WRVS VEF NMWFV DSGRFG WR TSES, HFRV SR TFFKWRP AR SXXSGVMRWVO
SC SXFRWRP EWT YWRZ VS ZSDVSG YARFVVF. WV IAT VEF DUSTF SC VEF TMYYFG
ZAO, ARZ EF KRFI UMDWF VS HF SMV IWVE YWTT XGSTT.

EF CSMRZ VEF ZSDVSG GFAZWRP WR EWT AGY-DEAWG AV A IWRZSI. VEF FRFGPO
IEWDE EAZ AV SRDF TMXXSGVFZ EWY MRZFG EWT SUZ TMCCFGWRPT ARZ APPGAJAVFZ
VEFWG TEAGXRFTT, EAZ HFFR PGAZMAUUO GFTVSGFZ VS EWY. EF IAT RSI A
JFGO FRFGPFVWD YAR WRZFFZ, IWVE PGFAV CWGYRFTT SC XMGXSTF, TVGFRPVE
SC GFTSUMVWSR, ARZ JWPSMG SC ADVWSR. WR EWT GFDSJFGFZ FRFGPO EF IAT
TSYFVWYFT A UWVVUF CWVCMU ARZ TMZZFR, AT EF EAZ AV CWGTV HFFR WR VEF
FQFGDWTF SC EWT SVEFG GFDSJFGFZ CADMUVWFT; HMV, VEWT EAZ RFJFG HFFR
CGFNMFRVUO SHTFGJAHUF, ARZ EAZ PGSIR YSGF ARZ YSGF GAGF.

EF TVMZWFZ YMDE, TUFXV UWVVUF, TMTVAWRFZ A PGFAV ZFAU SC CAVWPMF IWVE
FATF, ARZ IAT FNMAHUO DEFFGCMU. VS EWY, RSI FRVFGFZ DEAGUFT ZAGRAO, AV
TWPEV SC IESY EF UAWZ ATWZF EWT HSSK ARZ EFUZ SMV EWT EARZ.

“DEAGUFT ZAGRAO! W GFLSWDF VS TFF OSM. IF EAJF HFFR DSMRVWRP SR OSMG
GFVMGR VEFTF VEGFF SG CSMG ZAOT XATV. YG. TVGOJFG ARZ TOZRFO DAGVSR IFGF
HSVE EFGF OFTVFGZAO, ARZ HSVE YAZF OSM SMV VS HF YSGF VEAR ZMF.”

“W AY SHUWPFZ VS VEFY CSG VEFWG WRVFGFTV WR VEF YAVVFG,” EF ARTIFGFZ,
A UWVVUF DSUZUO AT VS VEFY, VESMPE JFGO IAGYUO AT VS VEF ZSDVSG. “YWTT
YARFVVF--”

“WT IFUU,” TAWZ VEF ZSDVSG, AT EF TVSXXFZ TESGV, “ARZ OSMG GFVMGR IWUU
ZFUWPEV MT AUU. TEF EAT PSRF SMV SR TSYF ESMTFESUZ YAVVFGT, HMV IWUU
TSSR HF ESYF.”

“ZSDVSG YARFVVF, W KRFI TEF IAT CGSY ESYF. W VSSK VEF SXXSGVMRWVO SC EFG
HFWRP CGSY ESYF, VS HFP VS TXFAK VS OSM.”

VEFGF IAT A HUARK TWUFRDF.

“OFT?” TAWZ VEF ZSDVSG, IWVE FJWZFRV DSRTVGAWRV. “HGWRP OSMG DEAWG EFGF,
ARZ TXFAK SR.”

EF DSYXUWFZ AT VS VEF DEAWG, HMV AXXFAGFZ VS CWRZ VEF TXFAKWRP SR UFTT
FATO.

“W EAJF EAZ VEF EAXXWRFTT, ZSDVSG YARFVVF, SC HFWRP TS WRVWYAVF EFGF,”
 TS EF AV UFRPVE HFPAR, “CSG TSYF OFAG ARZ A EAUC, VEAV W ESXF VEF VSXWD
SR IEWDE W AY AHSMV VS VSMDE YAO RSV--”

EF IAT TVAOFZ HO VEF ZSDVSG'T XMVVWRP SMV EWT EARZ VS TVSX EWY. IEFR EF
EAZ KFXV WV TS A UWVVUF IEWUF, EF TAWZ, ZGAIWRP WV HADK:

“WT UMDWF VEF VSXWD?”

“TEF WT.”

“WV WT EAGZ CSG YF VS TXFAK SC EFG AV ARO VWYF. WV WT JFGO EAGZ CSG YF
VS EFAG EFG TXSKFR SC WR VEAV VSRF SC OSMGT, DEAGUFT ZAGRAO.”

“WV WT A VSRF SC CFGJFRV AZYWGAVWSR, VGMF ESYAPF, ARZ ZFFX USJF, ZSDVSG
YARFVVF!” EF TAWZ ZFCFGFRVWAUUO.

VEFGF IAT ARSVEFG HUARK TWUFRDF HFCSGF EFG CAVEFG GFLSWRFZ:

“W HFUWFJF WV. W ZS OSM LMTVWDF; W HFUWFJF WV.”

EWT DSRTVGAWRV IAT TS YARWCFTV, ARZ WV IAT TS YARWCFTV, VSS, VEAV WV
SGWPWRAVFZ WR AR MRIWUUWRPRFTT VS AXXGSADE VEF TMHLFDV, VEAV DEAGUFT
ZAGRAO EFTWVAVFZ.

“TEAUU W PS SR, TWG?”

ARSVEFG HUARK.

“OFT, PS SR.”

“OSM ARVWDWXAVF IEAV W ISMUZ TAO, VESMPE OSM DARRSV KRSI ESI FAGRFTVUO
W TAO WV, ESI FAGRFTVUO W CFFU WV, IWVESMV KRSIWRP YO TFDGFV EFAGV, ARZ
VEF ESXFT ARZ CFAGT ARZ ARQWFVWFT IWVE IEWDE WV EAT USRP HFFR
UAZFR. ZFAG ZSDVSG YARFVVF, W USJF OSMG ZAMPEVFG CSRZUO, ZFAGUO,
ZWTWRVFGFTVFZUO, ZFJSVFZUO. WC FJFG VEFGF IFGF USJF WR VEF ISGUZ, W USJF
EFG. OSM EAJF USJFZ OSMGTFUC; UFV OSMG SUZ USJF TXFAK CSG YF!”

VEF ZSDVSG TAV IWVE EWT CADF VMGRFZ AIAO, ARZ EWT FOFT HFRV SR VEF
PGSMRZ. AV VEF UATV ISGZT, EF TVGFVDEFZ SMV EWT EARZ APAWR, EMGGWFZUO,
ARZ DGWFZ:

“RSV VEAV, TWG! UFV VEAV HF! W AZLMGF OSM, ZS RSV GFDAUU VEAV!”

EWT DGO IAT TS UWKF A DGO SC ADVMAU XAWR, VEAV WV GARP WR DEAGUFT
ZAGRAO'T FAGT USRP ACVFG EF EAZ DFATFZ. EF YSVWSRFZ IWVE VEF EARZ EF EAZ
FQVFRZFZ, ARZ WV TFFYFZ VS HF AR AXXFAU VS ZAGRAO VS XAMTF. VEF UAVVFG
TS GFDFWJFZ WV, ARZ GFYAWRFZ TWUFRV.

“W ATK OSMG XAGZSR,” TAWZ VEF ZSDVSG, WR A TMHZMFZ VSRF, ACVFG TSYF
YSYFRVT. “W ZS RSV ZSMHV OSMG USJWRP UMDWF; OSM YAO HF TAVWTCWFZ SC WV.”

EF VMGRFZ VSIAGZT EWY WR EWT DEAWG, HMV ZWZ RSV USSK AV EWY, SG
GAWTF EWT FOFT. EWT DEWR ZGSXXFZ MXSR EWT EARZ, ARZ EWT IEWVF EAWG
SJFGTEAZSIFZ EWT CADF:

“EAJF OSM TXSKFR VS UMDWF?”

“RS.”

“RSG IGWVVFR?”

“RFJFG.”

“WV ISMUZ HF MRPFRFGSMT VS ACCFDV RSV VS KRSI VEAV OSMG TFUC-ZFRWAU WT
VS HF GFCFGGFZ VS OSMG DSRTWZFGAVWSR CSG EFG CAVEFG. EFG CAVEFG VEARKT
OSM.”

EF SCCFGFZ EWT EARZ; HMV EWT FOFT ZWZ RSV PS IWVE WV.

“W KRSI,” TAWZ ZAGRAO, GFTXFDVCMUUO, “ESI DAR W CAWU VS KRSI, ZSDVSG
YARFVVF, W IES EAJF TFFR OSM VSPFVEFG CGSY ZAO VS ZAO, VEAV HFVIFFR
OSM ARZ YWTT YARFVVF VEFGF WT AR ACCFDVWSR TS MRMTMAU, TS VSMDEWRP, TS
HFUSRPWRP VS VEF DWGDMYTVARDFT WR IEWDE WV EAT HFFR RMGVMGFZ, VEAV WV
DAR EAJF CFI XAGAUUFUT, FJFR WR VEF VFRZFGRFTT HFVIFFR A CAVEFG ARZ
DEWUZ. W KRSI, ZSDVSG YARFVVF--ESI DAR W CAWU VS KRSI--VEAV, YWRPUFZ
IWVE VEF ACCFDVWSR ARZ ZMVO SC A ZAMPEVFG IES EAT HFDSYF A ISYAR, VEFGF
WT, WR EFG EFAGV, VSIAGZT OSM, AUU VEF USJF ARZ GFUWARDF SC WRCARDO
WVTFUC. W KRSI VEAV, AT WR EFG DEWUZESSZ TEF EAZ RS XAGFRV, TS TEF WT
RSI ZFJSVFZ VS OSM IWVE AUU VEF DSRTVARDO ARZ CFGJSMG SC EFG XGFTFRV
OFAGT ARZ DEAGADVFG, MRWVFZ VS VEF VGMTVCMURFTT ARZ AVVADEYFRV SC VEF
FAGUO ZAOT WR IEWDE OSM IFGF USTV VS EFG. W KRSI XFGCFDVUO IFUU VEAV WC
OSM EAZ HFFR GFTVSGFZ VS EFG CGSY VEF ISGUZ HFOSRZ VEWT UWCF, OSM DSMUZ
EAGZUO HF WRJFTVFZ, WR EFG TWPEV, IWVE A YSGF TADGFZ DEAGADVFG VEAR VEAV
WR IEWDE OSM AGF AUIAOT IWVE EFG. W KRSI VEAV IEFR TEF WT DUWRPWRP VS
OSM, VEF EARZT SC HAHO, PWGU, ARZ ISYAR, AUU WR SRF, AGF GSMRZ OSMG
RFDK. W KRSI VEAV WR USJWRP OSM TEF TFFT ARZ USJFT EFG YSVEFG AV EFG
SIR APF, TFFT ARZ USJFT OSM AV YO APF, USJFT EFG YSVEFG HGSKFR-EFAGVFZ,
USJFT OSM VEGSMPE OSMG ZGFAZCMU VGWAU ARZ WR OSMG HUFTTFZ GFTVSGAVWSR. W
EAJF KRSIR VEWT, RWPEV ARZ ZAO, TWRDF W EAJF KRSIR OSM WR OSMG ESYF.”

EFG CAVEFG TAV TWUFRV, IWVE EWT CADF HFRV ZSIR. EWT HGFAVEWRP IAT A
UWVVUF NMWDKFRFZ; HMV EF GFXGFTTFZ AUU SVEFG TWPRT SC APWVAVWSR.

“ZFAG ZSDVSG YARFVVF, AUIAOT KRSIWRP VEWT, AUIAOT TFFWRP EFG ARZ OSM
IWVE VEWT EAUUSIFZ UWPEV AHSMV OSM, W EAJF CSGHSGRF, ARZ CSGHSGRF, AT
USRP AT WV IAT WR VEF RAVMGF SC YAR VS ZS WV. W EAJF CFUV, ARZ ZS FJFR
RSI CFFU, VEAV VS HGWRP YO USJF--FJFR YWRF--HFVIFFR OSM, WT VS VSMDE
OSMG EWTVSGO IWVE TSYFVEWRP RSV NMWVF TS PSSZ AT WVTFUC. HMV W USJF EFG.
EFAJFR WT YO IWVRFTT VEAV W USJF EFG!”

“W HFUWFJF WV,” ARTIFGFZ EFG CAVEFG, YSMGRCMUUO. “W EAJF VESMPEV TS
HFCSGF RSI. W HFUWFJF WV.”

“HMV, ZS RSV HFUWFJF,” TAWZ ZAGRAO, MXSR IESTF FAG VEF YSMGRCMU JSWDF
TVGMDK IWVE A GFXGSADECMU TSMRZ, “VEAV WC YO CSGVMRF IFGF TS DATV AT
VEAV, HFWRP SRF ZAO TS EAXXO AT VS YAKF EFG YO IWCF, W YMTV AV ARO VWYF
XMV ARO TFXAGAVWSR HFVIFFR EFG ARZ OSM, W DSMUZ SG ISMUZ HGFAVEF A
ISGZ SC IEAV W RSI TAO. HFTWZFT VEAV W TESMUZ KRSI WV VS HF ESXFUFTT, W
TESMUZ KRSI WV VS HF A HATFRFTT. WC W EAZ ARO TMDE XSTTWHWUWVO, FJFR AV
A GFYSVF ZWTVARDF SC OFAGT, EAGHSMGFZ WR YO VESMPEVT, ARZ EWZZFR WR YO
EFAGV--WC WV FJFG EAZ HFFR VEFGF--WC WV FJFG DSMUZ HF VEFGF--W DSMUZ RSV
RSI VSMDE VEWT ESRSMGFZ EARZ.”

EF UAWZ EWT SIR MXSR WV AT EF TXSKF.

“RS, ZFAG ZSDVSG YARFVVF. UWKF OSM, A JSUMRVAGO FQWUF CGSY CGARDF; UWKF
OSM, ZGWJFR CGSY WV HO WVT ZWTVGADVWSRT, SXXGFTTWSRT, ARZ YWTFGWFT; UWKF
OSM, TVGWJWRP VS UWJF AIAO CGSY WV HO YO SIR FQFGVWSRT, ARZ VGMTVWRP
WR A EAXXWFG CMVMGF; W USSK SRUO VS TEAGWRP OSMG CSGVMRFT, TEAGWRP OSMG
UWCF ARZ ESYF, ARZ HFWRP CAWVECMU VS OSM VS VEF ZFAVE. RSV VS ZWJWZF
IWVE UMDWF EFG XGWJWUFPF AT OSMG DEWUZ, DSYXARWSR, ARZ CGWFRZ; HMV VS
DSYF WR AWZ SC WV, ARZ HWRZ EFG DUSTFG VS OSM, WC TMDE A VEWRP DAR HF.”

EWT VSMDE TVWUU UWRPFGFZ SR EFG CAVEFG'T EARZ. ARTIFGWRP VEF VSMDE CSG A
YSYFRV, HMV RSV DSUZUO, EFG CAVEFG GFTVFZ EWT EARZT MXSR VEF AGYT SC
EWT DEAWG, ARZ USSKFZ MX CSG VEF CWGTV VWYF TWRDF VEF HFPWRRWRP SC VEF
DSRCFGFRDF. A TVGMPPUF IAT FJWZFRVUO WR EWT CADF; A TVGMPPUF IWVE VEAV
SDDATWSRAU USSK IEWDE EAZ A VFRZFRDO WR WV VS ZAGK ZSMHV ARZ ZGFAZ.

“OSM TXFAK TS CFFUWRPUO ARZ TS YARCMUUO, DEAGUFT ZAGRAO, VEAV W VEARK
OSM IWVE AUU YO EFAGV, ARZ IWUU SXFR AUU YO EFAGV--SG RFAGUO TS. EAJF
OSM ARO GFATSR VS HFUWFJF VEAV UMDWF USJFT OSM?”

“RSRF. AT OFV, RSRF.”

“WT WV VEF WYYFZWAVF SHLFDV SC VEWT DSRCWZFRDF, VEAV OSM YAO AV SRDF
ATDFGVAWR VEAV, IWVE YO KRSIUFZPF?”

“RSV FJFR TS. W YWPEV RSV EAJF VEF ESXFCMURFTT VS ZS WV CSG IFFKT; W
YWPEV (YWTVAKFR SG RSV YWTVAKFR) EAJF VEAV ESXFCMURFTT VS-YSGGSI.”

“ZS OSM TFFK ARO PMWZARDF CGSY YF?”

“W ATK RSRF, TWG. HMV W EAJF VESMPEV WV XSTTWHUF VEAV OSM YWPEV EAJF WV
WR OSMG XSIFG, WC OSM TESMUZ ZFFY WV GWPEV, VS PWJF YF TSYF.”

“ZS OSM TFFK ARO XGSYWTF CGSY YF?”

“W ZS TFFK VEAV.”

“IEAV WT WV?”

“W IFUU MRZFGTVARZ VEAV, IWVESMV OSM, W DSMUZ EAJF RS ESXF. W IFUU
MRZFGTVARZ VEAV, FJFR WC YWTT YARFVVF EFUZ YF AV VEWT YSYFRV WR EFG
WRRSDFRV EFAGV--ZS RSV VEWRK W EAJF VEF XGFTMYXVWSR VS ATTMYF TS YMDE--W
DSMUZ GFVAWR RS XUADF WR WV APAWRTV EFG USJF CSG EFG CAVEFG.”

“WC VEAV HF TS, ZS OSM TFF IEAV, SR VEF SVEFG EARZ, WT WRJSUJFZ WR WV?”

“W MRZFGTVARZ FNMAUUO IFUU, VEAV A ISGZ CGSY EFG CAVEFG WR ARO TMWVSG'T
CAJSMG, ISMUZ SMVIFWPE EFGTFUC ARZ AUU VEF ISGUZ. CSG IEWDE GFATSR,
ZSDVSG YARFVVF,” TAWZ ZAGRAO, YSZFTVUO HMV CWGYUO, “W ISMUZ RSV ATK VEAV
ISGZ, VS TAJF YO UWCF.”

“W AY TMGF SC WV. DEAGUFT ZAGRAO, YOTVFGWFT AGWTF SMV SC DUSTF USJF, AT
IFUU AT SMV SC IWZF ZWJWTWSR; WR VEF CSGYFG DATF, VEFO AGF TMHVUF ARZ
ZFUWDAVF, ARZ ZWCCWDMUV VS XFRFVGAVF. YO ZAMPEVFG UMDWF WT, WR VEWT SRF
GFTXFDV, TMDE A YOTVFGO VS YF; W DAR YAKF RS PMFTT AV VEF TVAVF SC EFG
EFAGV.”

“YAO W ATK, TWG, WC OSM VEWRK TEF WT--” AT EF EFTWVAVFZ, EFG CAVEFG
TMXXUWFZ VEF GFTV.

“WT TSMPEV HO ARO SVEFG TMWVSG?”

“WV WT IEAV W YFARV VS TAO.”

EFG CAVEFG DSRTWZFGFZ A UWVVUF HFCSGF EF ARTIFGFZ:

“OSM EAJF TFFR YG. DAGVSR EFGF, OSMGTFUC. YG. TVGOJFG WT EFGF VSS,
SDDATWSRAUUO. WC WV HF AV AUU, WV DAR SRUO HF HO SRF SC VEFTF.”

“SG HSVE,” TAWZ ZAGRAO.

“W EAZ RSV VESMPEV SC HSVE; W TESMUZ RSV VEWRK FWVEFG, UWKFUO. OSM IARV
A XGSYWTF CGSY YF. VFUU YF IEAV WV WT.”

“WV WT, VEAV WC YWTT YARFVVF TESMUZ HGWRP VS OSM AV ARO VWYF, SR EFG SIR
XAGV, TMDE A DSRCWZFRDF AT W EAJF JFRVMGFZ VS UAO HFCSGF OSM, OSM IWUU
HFAG VFTVWYSRO VS IEAV W EAJF TAWZ, ARZ VS OSMG HFUWFC WR WV. W ESXF OSM
YAO HF AHUF VS VEWRK TS IFUU SC YF, AT VS MGPF RS WRCUMFRDF APAWRTV
YF. W TAO RSVEWRP YSGF SC YO TVAKF WR VEWT; VEWT WT IEAV W ATK. VEF
DSRZWVWSR SR IEWDE W ATK WV, ARZ IEWDE OSM EAJF AR MRZSMHVFZ GWPEV VS
GFNMWGF, W IWUU SHTFGJF WYYFZWAVFUO.”

“W PWJF VEF XGSYWTF,” TAWZ VEF ZSDVSG, “IWVESMV ARO DSRZWVWSR. W HFUWFJF
OSMG SHLFDV VS HF, XMGFUO ARZ VGMVECMUUO, AT OSM EAJF TVAVFZ WV. W
HFUWFJF OSMG WRVFRVWSR WT VS XFGXFVMAVF, ARZ RSV VS IFAKFR, VEF VWFT
HFVIFFR YF ARZ YO SVEFG ARZ CAG ZFAGFG TFUC. WC TEF TESMUZ FJFG VFUU YF
VEAV OSM AGF FTTFRVWAU VS EFG XFGCFDV EAXXWRFTT, W IWUU PWJF EFG VS OSM.
WC VEFGF IFGF--DEAGUFT ZAGRAO, WC VEFGF IFGF--”

VEF OSMRP YAR EAZ VAKFR EWT EARZ PGAVFCMUUO; VEFWG EARZT IFGF LSWRFZ AT
VEF ZSDVSG TXSKF:

“--ARO CARDWFT, ARO GFATSRT, ARO AXXGFEFRTWSRT, AROVEWRP IEAVTSFJFG,
RFI SG SUZ, APAWRTV VEF YAR TEF GFAUUO USJFZ--VEF ZWGFDV GFTXSRTWHWUWVO
VEFGFSC RSV UOWRP SR EWT EFAZ--VEFO TESMUZ AUU HF SHUWVFGAVFZ CSG EFG
TAKF. TEF WT FJFGOVEWRP VS YF; YSGF VS YF VEAR TMCCFGWRP, YSGF VS YF
VEAR IGSRP, YSGF VS YF--IFUU! VEWT WT WZUF VAUK.”

TS TVGARPF IAT VEF IAO WR IEWDE EF CAZFZ WRVS TWUFRDF, ARZ TS TVGARPF
EWT CWQFZ USSK IEFR EF EAZ DFATFZ VS TXFAK, VEAV ZAGRAO CFUV EWT SIR
EARZ VMGR DSUZ WR VEF EARZ VEAV TUSIUO GFUFATFZ ARZ ZGSXXFZ WV.

“OSM TAWZ TSYFVEWRP VS YF,” TAWZ ZSDVSG YARFVVF, HGFAKWRP WRVS A TYWUF.
“IEAV IAT WV OSM TAWZ VS YF?”

EF IAT AV A USTT ESI VS ARTIFG, MRVWU EF GFYFYHFGFZ EAJWRP TXSKFR SC A
DSRZWVWSR. GFUWFJFZ AT EWT YWRZ GFJFGVFZ VS VEAV, EF ARTIFGFZ:

“OSMG DSRCWZFRDF WR YF SMPEV VS HF GFVMGRFZ IWVE CMUU DSRCWZFRDF SR YO
XAGV. YO XGFTFRV RAYF, VESMPE HMV TUWPEVUO DEARPFZ CGSY YO YSVEFG'T, WT
RSV, AT OSM IWUU GFYFYHFG, YO SIR. W IWTE VS VFUU OSM IEAV VEAV WT, ARZ
IEO W AY WR FRPUARZ.”

“TVSX!” TAWZ VEF ZSDVSG SC HFAMJAWT.

“W IWTE WV, VEAV W YAO VEF HFVVFG ZFTFGJF OSMG DSRCWZFRDF, ARZ EAJF RS
TFDGFV CGSY OSM.”

“TVSX!”

CSG AR WRTVARV, VEF ZSDVSG FJFR EAZ EWT VIS EARZT AV EWT FAGT; CSG
ARSVEFG WRTVARV, FJFR EAZ EWT VIS EARZT UAWZ SR ZAGRAO'T UWXT.

“VFUU YF IEFR W ATK OSM, RSV RSI. WC OSMG TMWV TESMUZ XGSTXFG, WC UMDWF
TESMUZ USJF OSM, OSM TEAUU VFUU YF SR OSMG YAGGWAPF YSGRWRP. ZS OSM
XGSYWTF?”

“IWUUWRPUO.

“PWJF YF OSMG EARZ. TEF IWUU HF ESYF ZWGFDVUO, ARZ WV WT HFVVFG TEF
TESMUZ RSV TFF MT VSPFVEFG VS-RWPEV. PS! PSZ HUFTT OSM!”

WV IAT ZAGK IEFR DEAGUFT ZAGRAO UFCV EWY, ARZ WV IAT AR ESMG UAVFG ARZ
ZAGKFG IEFR UMDWF DAYF ESYF; TEF EMGGWFZ WRVS VEF GSSY AUSRF--CSG
YWTT XGSTT EAZ PSRF TVGAWPEV MX-TVAWGT--ARZ IAT TMGXGWTFZ VS CWRZ EWT
GFAZWRP-DEAWG FYXVO.

“YO CAVEFG!” TEF DAUUFZ VS EWY. “CAVEFG ZFAG!”

RSVEWRP IAT TAWZ WR ARTIFG, HMV TEF EFAGZ A USI EAYYFGWRP TSMRZ WR EWT
HFZGSSY. XATTWRP UWPEVUO ADGSTT VEF WRVFGYFZWAVF GSSY, TEF USSKFZ WR AV
EWT ZSSG ARZ DAYF GMRRWRP HADK CGWPEVFRFZ, DGOWRP VS EFGTFUC, IWVE EFG
HUSSZ AUU DEWUUFZ, “IEAV TEAUU W ZS! IEAV TEAUU W ZS!”

EFG MRDFGVAWRVO UATVFZ HMV A YSYFRV; TEF EMGGWFZ HADK, ARZ VAXXFZ AV
EWT ZSSG, ARZ TSCVUO DAUUFZ VS EWY. VEF RSWTF DFATFZ AV VEF TSMRZ SC
EFG JSWDF, ARZ EF XGFTFRVUO DAYF SMV VS EFG, ARZ VEFO IAUKFZ MX ARZ ZSIR
VSPFVEFG CSG A USRP VWYF.

TEF DAYF ZSIR CGSY EFG HFZ, VS USSK AV EWY WR EWT TUFFX VEAV RWPEV. EF
TUFXV EFAJWUO, ARZ EWT VGAO SC TESFYAKWRP VSSUT, ARZ EWT SUZ MRCWRWTEFZ
ISGK, IFGF AUU AT MTMAU.




QW. A DSYXARWSR XWDVMGF


“TOZRFO,” TAWZ YG. TVGOJFG, SR VEAV TFUC-TAYF RWPEV, SG YSGRWRP, VS EWT
LADKAU; “YWQ ARSVEFG HSIU SC XMRDE; W EAJF TSYFVEWRP VS TAO VS OSM.”

TOZRFO EAZ HFFR ISGKWRP ZSMHUF VWZFT VEAV RWPEV, ARZ VEF RWPEV HFCSGF,
ARZ VEF RWPEV HFCSGF VEAV, ARZ A PSSZ YARO RWPEVT WR TMDDFTTWSR, YAKWRP
A PGARZ DUFAGARDF AYSRP YG. TVGOJFG'T XAXFGT HFCSGF VEF TFVVWRP WR
SC VEF USRP JADAVWSR. VEF DUFAGARDF IAT FCCFDVFZ AV UATV; VEF TVGOJFG
AGGFAGT IFGF EARZTSYFUO CFVDEFZ MX; FJFGOVEWRP IAT PSV GWZ SC MRVWU
RSJFYHFG TESMUZ DSYF IWVE WVT CSPT AVYSTXEFGWD, ARZ CSPT UFPAU, ARZ
HGWRP PGWTV VS VEF YWUU APAWR.

TOZRFO IAT RSRF VEF UWJFUWFG ARZ RSRF VEF TSHFGFG CSG TS YMDE
