QWW. VEF CFUUSI SC ZFUWDADO


YG. TVGOJFG EAJWRP YAZF MX EWT YWRZ VS VEAV YAPRARWYSMT HFTVSIAU SC PSSZ
CSGVMRF SR VEF ZSDVSG'T ZAMPEVFG, GFTSUJFZ VS YAKF EFG EAXXWRFTT KRSIR
VS EFG HFCSGF EF UFCV VSIR CSG VEF USRP JADAVWSR. ACVFG TSYF YFRVAU
ZFHAVWRP SC VEF XSWRV, EF DAYF VS VEF DSRDUMTWSR VEAV WV ISMUZ HF AT
IFUU VS PFV AUU VEF XGFUWYWRAGWFT ZSRF IWVE, ARZ VEFO DSMUZ VEFR AGGARPF
AV VEFWG UFWTMGF IEFVEFG EF TESMUZ PWJF EFG EWT EARZ A IFFK SG VIS
HFCSGF YWDEAFUYAT VFGY, SG WR VEF UWVVUF DEGWTVYAT JADAVWSR HFVIFFR WV
ARZ EWUAGO.

AT VS VEF TVGFRPVE SC EWT DATF, EF EAZ RSV A ZSMHV AHSMV WV, HMV DUFAGUO
TAI EWT IAO VS VEF JFGZWDV. AGPMFZ IWVE VEF LMGO SR TMHTVARVWAU ISGUZUO
PGSMRZT--VEF SRUO PGSMRZT FJFG ISGVE VAKWRP WRVS ADDSMRV--WV IAT A
XUAWR DATF, ARZ EAZ RSV A IFAK TXSV WR WV. EF DAUUFZ EWYTFUC CSG VEF
XUAWRVWCC, VEFGF IAT RS PFVVWRP SJFG EWT FJWZFRDF, VEF DSMRTFU CSG
VEF ZFCFRZARV VEGFI MX EWT HGWFC, ARZ VEF LMGO ZWZ RSV FJFR VMGR VS
DSRTWZFG. ACVFG VGOWRP WV, TVGOJFG, D. L., IAT TAVWTCWFZ VEAV RS XUAWRFG
DATF DSMUZ HF.

ADDSGZWRPUO, YG. TVGOJFG WRAMPMGAVFZ VEF USRP JADAVWSR IWVE A CSGYAU
XGSXSTAU VS VAKF YWTT YARFVVF VS JAMQEAUU PAGZFRT; VEAV CAWUWRP, VS
GARFUAPE; VEAV MRADDSMRVAHUO CAWUWRP VSS, WV HFESJFZ EWY VS XGFTFRV
EWYTFUC WR TSES, ARZ VEFGF ZFDUAGF EWT RSHUF YWRZ.

VSIAGZT TSES, VEFGFCSGF, YG. TVGOJFG TESMUZFGFZ EWT IAO CGSY VEF VFYXUF,
IEWUF VEF HUSSY SC VEF USRP JADAVWSR'T WRCARDO IAT TVWUU MXSR WV.
AROHSZO IES EAZ TFFR EWY XGSLFDVWRP EWYTFUC WRVS TSES IEWUF EF IAT OFV
SR TAWRV ZMRTVAR'T TWZF SC VFYXUF HAG, HMGTVWRP WR EWT CMUU-HUSIR IAO
AUSRP VEF XAJFYFRV, VS VEF LSTVUFYFRV SC AUU IFAKFG XFSXUF, YWPEV EAJF
TFFR ESI TACF ARZ TVGSRP EF IAT.

EWT IAO VAKWRP EWY XATV VFUUTSR'T, ARZ EF HSVE HARKWRP AV VFUUTSR'T ARZ
KRSIWRP YG. USGGO AT VEF WRVWYAVF CGWFRZ SC VEF YARFVVFT, WV FRVFGFZ YG.
TVGOJFG'T YWRZ VS FRVFG VEF HARK, ARZ GFJFAU VS YG. USGGO VEF HGWPEVRFTT
SC VEF TSES ESGWBSR. TS, EF XMTEFZ SXFR VEF ZSSG IWVE VEF IFAK GAVVUF
WR WVT VEGSAV, TVMYHUFZ ZSIR VEF VIS TVFXT, PSV XATV VEF VIS ARDWFRV
DATEWFGT, ARZ TESMUZFGFZ EWYTFUC WRVS VEF YMTVO HADK DUSTFV IEFGF YG.
USGGO TAV AV PGFAV HSSKT GMUFZ CSG CWPMGFT, IWVE XFGXFRZWDMUAG WGSR
HAGT VS EWT IWRZSI AT WC VEAV IFGF GMUFZ CSG CWPMGFT VSS, ARZ FJFGOVEWRP
MRZFG VEF DUSMZT IFGF A TMY.

“EAUUSA!” TAWZ YG. TVGOJFG. “ESI ZS OSM ZS? W ESXF OSM AGF IFUU!”

WV IAT TVGOJFG'T PGARZ XFDMUWAGWVO VEAV EF AUIAOT TFFYFZ VSS HWP CSG ARO
XUADF, SG TXADF. EF IAT TS YMDE VSS HWP CSG VFUUTSR'T, VEAV SUZ DUFGKT
WR ZWTVARV DSGRFGT USSKFZ MX IWVE USSKT SC GFYSRTVGARDF, AT VESMPE EF
TNMFFBFZ VEFY APAWRTV VEF IAUU. VEF ESMTF WVTFUC, YAPRWCWDFRVUO GFAZWRP
VEF XAXFG NMWVF WR VEF CAG-SCC XFGTXFDVWJF, USIFGFZ ZWTXUFATFZ, AT WC
VEF TVGOJFG EFAZ EAZ HFFR HMVVFZ WRVS WVT GFTXSRTWHUF IAWTVDSAV.

VEF ZWTDGFFV YG. USGGO TAWZ, WR A TAYXUF VSRF SC VEF JSWDF EF ISMUZ
GFDSYYFRZ MRZFG VEF DWGDMYTVARDFT, “ESI ZS OSM ZS, YG. TVGOJFG? ESI ZS
OSM ZS, TWG?” ARZ TESSK EARZT. VEFGF IAT A XFDMUWAGWVO WR EWT YARRFG
