“IFUU! W--IFGF OSM PSWRP VEFGF RSI?” ATKFZ YG. USGGO.

“TVGAWPEV!” TAWZ TVGOJFG, IWVE A XUMYX SC EWT CWTV SR VEF ZFTK.

“VEFR W VEWRK W ISMUZR'V, WC W IAT OSM.”

“IEO?” TAWZ TVGOJFG. “RSI, W'UU XMV OSM WR A DSGRFG,” CSGFRTWDAUUO
