“IEFR W TXFAK SC TMDDFTT, W TXFAK SC TMDDFTT IWVE VEF OSMRP UAZO; ARZ
IEFR W TXFAK SC DAMTFT ARZ GFATSRT VS YAKF TMDDFTT XGSHAHUF, W TXFAK SC
