OSMRP UAZO. VEF OSMRP UAZO PSFT HFCSGF AUU.”

“VEFR OSM YFAR VS VFUU YF, YG. USGGO,” TAWZ TVGOJFG, TNMAGWRP EWT
FUHSIT, “VEAV WV WT OSMG ZFUWHFGAVF SXWRWSR VEAV VEF OSMRP UAZO AV
XGFTFRV WR NMFTVWSR WT A YWRDWRP CSSU?”

“RSV FQADVUO TS. W YFAR VS VFUU OSM, YG. TVGOJFG,” TAWZ YG. USGGO,
GFZZFRWRP, “VEAV W IWUU EFAG RS ZWTGFTXFDVCMU ISGZ SC VEAV OSMRP UAZO
CGSY ARO UWXT; ARZ VEAV WC W KRFI ARO YAR--IEWDE W ESXF W ZS RSV--IESTF
VATVF IAT TS DSAGTF, ARZ IESTF VFYXFG IAT TS SJFGHFAGWRP, VEAV EF DSMUZ
RSV GFTVGAWR EWYTFUC CGSY TXFAKWRP ZWTGFTXFDVCMUUO SC VEAV OSMRP UAZO AV
VEWT ZFTK, RSV FJFR VFUUTSR'T TESMUZ XGFJFRV YO PWJWRP EWY A XWFDF SC YO
YWRZ.”

VEF RFDFTTWVO SC HFWRP ARPGO WR A TMXXGFTTFZ VSRF EAZ XMV YG. TVGOJFG'T
HUSSZ-JFTTFUT WRVS A ZARPFGSMT TVAVF IEFR WV IAT EWT VMGR VS HF ARPGO;
