RS HFVVFG TVAVF RSI WV IAT EWT VMGR.

“VEAV WT IEAV W YFAR VS VFUU OSM, TWG,” TAWZ YG. USGGO. “XGAO UFV VEFGF
HF RS YWTVAKF AHSMV WV.”

YG. TVGOJFG TMDKFZ VEF FRZ SC A GMUFG CSG A UWVVUF IEWUF, ARZ VEFR TVSSZ
EWVVWRP A VMRF SMV SC EWT VFFVE IWVE WV, IEWDE XGSHAHUO PAJF EWY VEF
VSSVEADEF. EF HGSKF VEF AIKIAGZ TWUFRDF HO TAOWRP:

“VEWT WT TSYFVEWRP RFI VS YF, YG. USGGO. OSM ZFUWHFGAVFUO AZJWTF YF RSV
VS PS MX VS TSES ARZ SCCFG YOTFUC--_YO_TFUC, TVGOJFG SC VEF KWRP'T HFRDE
HAG?”

“ZS OSM ATK YF CSG YO AZJWDF, YG. TVGOJFG?”

“OFT, W ZS.”

“JFGO PSSZ. VEFR W PWJF WV, ARZ OSM EAJF GFXFAVFZ WV DSGGFDVUO.”

“ARZ AUU W DAR TAO SC WV WT,” UAMPEFZ TVGOJFG IWVE A JFQFZ UAMPE, “VEAV
VEWT--EA, EA!--HFAVT FJFGOVEWRP XATV, XGFTFRV, ARZ VS DSYF.”

“RSI MRZFGTVARZ YF,” XMGTMFZ YG. USGGO. “AT A YAR SC HMTWRFTT, W AY
RSV LMTVWCWFZ WR TAOWRP AROVEWRP AHSMV VEWT YAVVFG, CSG, AT A YAR SC
HMTWRFTT, W KRSI RSVEWRP SC WV. HMV, AT AR SUZ CFUUSI, IES EAT DAGGWFZ
YWTT YARFVVF WR EWT AGYT, IES WT VEF VGMTVFZ CGWFRZ SC YWTT YARFVVF ARZ
