TXSKFR. VEF DSRCWZFRDF WT RSV SC YO TFFKWRP, GFDSUUFDV. RSI, OSM VEWRK W
YAO RSV HF GWPEV?”

“RSV W!” TAWZ TVGOJFG, IEWTVUWRP. “W DAR'V MRZFGVAKF VS CWRZ VEWGZ
XAGVWFT WR DSYYSR TFRTF; W DAR SRUO CWRZ WV CSG YOTFUC. W TMXXSTF TFRTF
