HFTV TXAGFZ. IEAV ZS OSM TAO?”

“ESI USRP ISMUZ OSM KFFX YF WR VSIR?”

“SE! WV WT SRUO A NMFTVWSR SC A CFI ESMGT. W DSMUZ PS VS TSES WR VEF
FJFRWRP, ARZ DSYF VS OSMG DEAYHFGT ACVFGIAGZT.”

“VEFR W TAO OFT,” TAWZ TVGOJFG: “W ISR'V PS MX VEFGF RSI, W AY RSV TS
ESV MXSR WV AT VEAV DSYFT VS; W TAO OFT, ARZ W TEAUU FQXFDV OSM VS USSK
WR VS-RWPEV. PSSZ YSGRWRP.”

VEFR YG. TVGOJFG VMGRFZ ARZ HMGTV SMV SC VEF HARK, DAMTWRP TMDE A
DSRDMTTWSR SC AWG SR EWT XATTAPF VEGSMPE, VEAV VS TVARZ MX APAWRTV WV
