WV IAT A HWV SC VEF AGV SC AR SUZ HAWUFO VADVWDWAR, WR IEWDE EF CSMRZ
PGFAV GFUWFC. “OSM TEAUU RSV XMV YF WR VEF IGSRP, OSMRP UAZO,” TAWZ YG.
TVGOJFG; “W'UU ZS VEAV CSG OSM.”

ADDSGZWRPUO, IEFR YG. USGGO DAUUFZ VEAV RWPEV AT UAVF AT VFR S'DUSDK,
