YG. USGGO IAT SMV WR VEF RWPEV, HFCSGF EF KRFI IEFGF EF IAT. YG. TVGOJFG
IAT UOWRP HADK SR EWT TSCA, IWRKWRP AV EWT DFWUWRP.




QWWW. VEF CFUUSI SC RS ZFUWDADO


WC TOZRFO DAGVSR FJFG TESRF AROIEFGF, EF DFGVAWRUO RFJFG TESRF WR VEF
ESMTF SC ZSDVSG YARFVVF. EF EAZ HFFR VEFGF SCVFR, ZMGWRP A IESUF OFAG,
ARZ EAZ AUIAOT HFFR VEF TAYF YSSZO ARZ YSGSTF USMRPFG VEFGF. IEFR EF
DAGFZ VS VAUK, EF VAUKFZ IFUU; HMV, VEF DUSMZ SC DAGWRP CSG RSVEWRP,
IEWDE SJFGTEAZSIFZ EWY IWVE TMDE A CAVAU ZAGKRFTT, IAT JFGO GAGFUO
XWFGDFZ HO VEF UWPEV IWVEWR EWY.

ARZ OFV EF ZWZ DAGF TSYFVEWRP CSG VEF TVGFFVT VEAV FRJWGSRFZ VEAV ESMTF,
ARZ CSG VEF TFRTFUFTT TVSRFT VEAV YAZF VEFWG XAJFYFRVT. YARO A RWPEV
EF JAPMFUO ARZ MREAXXWUO IARZFGFZ VEFGF, IEFR IWRF EAZ HGSMPEV RS
VGARTWVSGO PUAZRFTT VS EWY; YARO A ZGFAGO ZAOHGFAK GFJFAUFZ EWT TSUWVAGO
CWPMGF UWRPFGWRP VEFGF, ARZ TVWUU UWRPFGWRP VEFGF IEFR VEF CWGTV HFAYT
SC VEF TMR HGSMPEV WRVS TVGSRP GFUWFC, GFYSJFZ HFAMVWFT SC AGDEWVFDVMGF
WR TXWGFT SC DEMGDEFT ARZ USCVO HMWUZWRPT, AT XFGEAXT VEF NMWFV VWYF
HGSMPEV TSYF TFRTF SC HFVVFG VEWRPT, FUTF CSGPSVVFR ARZ MRAVVAWRAHUF,
WRVS EWT YWRZ. SC UAVF, VEF RFPUFDVFZ HFZ WR VEF VFYXUF DSMGV EAZ KRSIR
EWY YSGF TDARVWUO VEAR FJFG; ARZ SCVFR IEFR EF EAZ VEGSIR EWYTFUC MXSR
WV RS USRPFG VEAR A CFI YWRMVFT, EF EAZ PSV MX APAWR, ARZ EAMRVFZ VEAV
RFWPEHSMGESSZ.

SR A ZAO WR AMPMTV, IEFR YG. TVGOJFG (ACVFG RSVWCOWRP VS EWT LADKAU
VEAV “EF EAZ VESMPEV HFVVFG SC VEAV YAGGOWRP YAVVFG”) EAZ DAGGWFZ EWT
ZFUWDADO WRVS ZFJSRTEWGF, ARZ IEFR VEF TWPEV ARZ TDFRV SC CUSIFGT WR VEF
DWVO TVGFFVT EAZ TSYF IAWCT SC PSSZRFTT WR VEFY CSG VEF ISGTV, SC EFAUVE
