VESTF TVSRFT. CGSY HFWRP WGGFTSUMVF ARZ XMGXSTFUFTT, EWT CFFV HFDAYF
ARWYAVFZ HO AR WRVFRVWSR, ARZ, WR VEF ISGKWRP SMV SC VEAV WRVFRVWSR,
VEFO VSSK EWY VS VEF ZSDVSG'T ZSSG.

EF IAT TESIR MX-TVAWGT, ARZ CSMRZ UMDWF AV EFG ISGK, AUSRF. TEF EAZ
RFJFG HFFR NMWVF AV EFG FATF IWVE EWY, ARZ GFDFWJFZ EWY IWVE TSYF UWVVUF
FYHAGGATTYFRV AT EF TFAVFZ EWYTFUC RFAG EFG VAHUF. HMV, USSKWRP MX AV
EWT CADF WR VEF WRVFGDEARPF SC VEF CWGTV CFI DSYYSR-XUADFT, TEF SHTFGJFZ
A DEARPF WR WV.

“W CFAG OSM AGF RSV IFUU, YG. DAGVSR!”

“RS. HMV VEF UWCF W UFAZ, YWTT YARFVVF, WT RSV DSRZMDWJF VS EFAUVE. IEAV
WT VS HF FQXFDVFZ SC, SG HO, TMDE XGSCUWPAVFT?”

“WT WV RSV--CSGPWJF YF; W EAJF HFPMR VEF NMFTVWSR SR YO UWXT--A XWVO VS
UWJF RS HFVVFG UWCF?”

“PSZ KRSIT WV WT A TEAYF!”

“VEFR IEO RSV DEARPF WV?”

USSKWRP PFRVUO AV EWY APAWR, TEF IAT TMGXGWTFZ ARZ TAZZFRFZ VS TFF VEAV
