“XGAO CSGPWJF YF, YWTT YARFVVF. W HGFAK ZSIR HFCSGF VEF KRSIUFZPF SC
IEAV W IARV VS TAO VS OSM. IWUU OSM EFAG YF?”

“WC WV IWUU ZS OSM ARO PSSZ, YG. DAGVSR, WC WV ISMUZ YAKF OSM EAXXWFG,
WV ISMUZ YAKF YF JFGO PUAZ!”

“PSZ HUFTT OSM CSG OSMG TIFFV DSYXATTWSR!”

EF MRTEAZFZ EWT CADF ACVFG A UWVVUF IEWUF, ARZ TXSKF TVFAZWUO.

“ZSR'V HF ACGAWZ VS EFAG YF. ZSR'V TEGWRK CGSY AROVEWRP W TAO. W AY UWKF
SRF IES ZWFZ OSMRP. AUU YO UWCF YWPEV EAJF HFFR.”

“RS, YG. DAGVSR. W AY TMGF VEAV VEF HFTV XAGV SC WV YWPEV TVWUU HF; W AY
TMGF VEAV OSM YWPEV HF YMDE, YMDE ISGVEWFG SC OSMGTFUC.”

“TAO SC OSM, YWTT YARFVVF, ARZ AUVESMPE W KRSI HFVVFG--AUVESMPE WR VEF
