“IWUU RSVEWRP SC WV GFYAWR? S YG. DAGVSR, VEWRK APAWR! VGO APAWR!”

“RS, YWTT YARFVVF; AUU VEGSMPE WV, W EAJF KRSIR YOTFUC VS HF NMWVF
MRZFTFGJWRP. ARZ OFV W EAJF EAZ VEF IFAKRFTT, ARZ EAJF TVWUU VEF
