“IEWDE W FRVGFAVFZ OSM VS HFUWFJF, APAWR ARZ APAWR, YSTV CFGJFRVUO, IWVE
AUU YO EFAGV, IAT DAXAHUF SC HFVVFG VEWRPT, YG. DAGVSR!”

“FRVGFAV YF VS HFUWFJF WV RS YSGF, YWTT YARFVVF. W EAJF XGSJFZ YOTFUC,
ARZ W KRSI HFVVFG. W ZWTVGFTT OSM; W ZGAI CATV VS AR FRZ. IWUU OSM UFV
YF HFUWFJF, IEFR W GFDAUU VEWT ZAO, VEAV VEF UATV DSRCWZFRDF SC YO UWCF
