AUSRF, ARZ IWUU HF TEAGFZ HO RS SRF?”

“WC VEAV IWUU HF A DSRTSUAVWSR VS OSM, OFT.”

“RSV FJFR HO VEF ZFAGFTV SRF FJFG VS HF KRSIR VS OSM?”

“YG. DAGVSR,” TEF ARTIFGFZ, ACVFG AR APWVAVFZ XAMTF, “VEF TFDGFV WT
