“VEARK OSM. ARZ APAWR, PSZ HUFTT OSM.”

EF XMV EFG EARZ VS EWT UWXT, ARZ YSJFZ VSIAGZT VEF ZSSG.

“HF MRZFG RS AXXGFEFRTWSR, YWTT YARFVVF, SC YO FJFG GFTMYWRP VEWT
DSRJFGTAVWSR HO TS YMDE AT A XATTWRP ISGZ. W IWUU RFJFG GFCFG VS WV
APAWR. WC W IFGF ZFAZ, VEAV DSMUZ RSV HF TMGFG VEAR WV WT EFRDFCSGVE. WR
VEF ESMG SC YO ZFAVE, W TEAUU ESUZ TADGFZ VEF SRF PSSZ GFYFYHGARDF--ARZ
TEAUU VEARK ARZ HUFTT OSM CSG WV--VEAV YO UATV AJSIAU SC YOTFUC IAT YAZF
VS OSM, ARZ VEAV YO RAYF, ARZ CAMUVT, ARZ YWTFGWFT IFGF PFRVUO DAGGWFZ
WR OSMG EFAGV. YAO WV SVEFGIWTF HF UWPEV ARZ EAXXO!”

EF IAT TS MRUWKF IEAV EF EAZ FJFG TESIR EWYTFUC VS HF, ARZ WV IAT TS
TAZ VS VEWRK ESI YMDE EF EAZ VEGSIR AIAO, ARZ ESI YMDE EF FJFGO ZAO KFXV
ZSIR ARZ XFGJFGVFZ, VEAV UMDWF YARFVVF IFXV YSMGRCMUUO CSG EWY AT EF
TVSSZ USSKWRP HADK AV EFG.

“HF DSYCSGVFZ!” EF TAWZ, “W AY RSV ISGVE TMDE CFFUWRP, YWTT YARFVVF. AR
ESMG SG VIS EFRDF, ARZ VEF USI DSYXARWSRT ARZ USI EAHWVT VEAV W TDSGR
