VS OSM, WT, VEAV OSM IWUU HFUWFJF VEWT SC YF.”

“W IWUU, YG. DAGVSR.”

“YO UATV TMXXUWDAVWSR SC AUU, WT VEWT; ARZ IWVE WV, W IWUU GFUWFJF
OSM SC A JWTWVSG IWVE IESY W IFUU KRSI OSM EAJF RSVEWRP WR MRWTSR, ARZ
