QJ. KRWVVWRP


VEFGF EAZ HFFR FAGUWFG ZGWRKWRP VEAR MTMAU WR VEF IWRF-TESX SC YSRTWFMG
ZFCAGPF. AT FAGUO AT TWQ S'DUSDK WR VEF YSGRWRP, TAUUSI CADFT XFFXWRP
