SC VWYFT, HMV WV ISMUZ TFFY VS EAJF HFFR AR MRMTMAUUO VEWR IWRF VEAV
EF TSUZ AV VEWT VWYF. A TSMG IWRF, YSGFSJFG, SG A TSMGWRP, CSG WVT
WRCUMFRDF SR VEF YSSZ SC VESTF IES ZGARK WV IAT VS YAKF VEFY PUSSYO. RS
JWJADWSMT HADDEARAUWAR CUAYF UFAXFZ SMV SC VEF XGFTTFZ PGAXF SC YSRTWFMG
ZFCAGPF: HMV, A TYSMUZFGWRP CWGF VEAV HMGRV WR VEF ZAGK, UAO EWZZFR WR
VEF ZGFPT SC WV.

VEWT EAZ HFFR VEF VEWGZ YSGRWRP WR TMDDFTTWSR, SR IEWDE VEFGF EAZ HFFR
FAGUO ZGWRKWRP AV VEF IWRF-TESX SC YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF. WV EAZ HFPMR
SR YSRZAO, ARZ EFGF IAT IFZRFTZAO DSYF. VEFGF EAZ HFFR YSGF SC FAGUO
HGSSZWRP VEAR ZGWRKWRP; CSG, YARO YFR EAZ UWTVFRFZ ARZ IEWTXFGFZ ARZ
TUMRK AHSMV VEFGF CGSY VEF VWYF SC VEF SXFRWRP SC VEF ZSSG, IES DSMUZ
RSV EAJF UAWZ A XWFDF SC YSRFO SR VEF DSMRVFG VS TAJF VEFWG TSMUT. VEFTF
IFGF VS VEF CMUU AT WRVFGFTVFZ WR VEF XUADF, ESIFJFG, AT WC VEFO DSMUZ
EAJF DSYYARZFZ IESUF HAGGFUT SC IWRF; ARZ VEFO PUWZFZ CGSY TFAV VS TFAV,
ARZ CGSY DSGRFG VS DSGRFG, TIAUUSIWRP VAUK WR UWFM SC ZGWRK, IWVE PGFFZO
USSKT.

RSVIWVETVARZWRP AR MRMTMAU CUSI SC DSYXARO, VEF YATVFG SC VEF IWRF-TESX
IAT RSV JWTWHUF. EF IAT RSV YWTTFZ; CSG, RSHSZO IES DGSTTFZ VEF
