“WV WT HAZ IFAVEFG, PFRVUFYFR,” TAWZ ZFCAGPF, TEAKWRP EWT EFAZ.

MXSR IEWDE, FJFGO YAR USSKFZ AV EWT RFWPEHSMG, ARZ VEFR AUU DATV ZSIR
