“EAJF OSM CWRWTEFZ OSMG GFXATV, CGWFRZ?” EF ATKFZ, WR ZMF TFATSR.

“OFT, VEARK OSM.”

“DSYF, VEFR! OSM TEAUU TFF VEF AXAGVYFRV VEAV W VSUZ OSM OSM DSMUZ
