SMV SC VEF IWRF-TESX WRVS VEF TVGFFV, SMV SC VEF TVGFFV WRVS A
DSMGVOAGZ, SMV SC VEF DSMGVOAGZ MX A TVFFX TVAWGDATF, SMV SC VEF
TVAWGDATF WRVS A PAGGFV--CSGYFGUO VEF PAGGFV IEFGF A IEWVF-EAWGFZ YAR
TAV SR A USI HFRDE, TVSSXWRP CSGIAGZ ARZ JFGO HMTO, YAKWRP TESFT.

RS IEWVF-EAWGFZ YAR IAT VEFGF RSI; HMV, VEF VEGFF YFR IFGF VEFGF IES EAZ
PSRF SMV SC VEF IWRF-TESX TWRPUO. ARZ HFVIFFR VEFY ARZ VEF IEWVF-EAWGFZ
YAR ACAG SCC, IAT VEF SRF TYAUU UWRK, VEAV VEFO EAZ SRDF USSKFZ WR AV
EWY VEGSMPE VEF DEWRKT WR VEF IAUU.

ZFCAGPF DUSTFZ VEF ZSSG DAGFCMUUO, ARZ TXSKF WR A TMHZMFZ JSWDF:

“LADNMFT SRF, LADNMFT VIS, LADNMFT VEGFF! VEWT WT VEF IWVRFTT
FRDSMRVFGFZ HO AXXSWRVYFRV, HO YF, LADNMFT CSMG. EF IWUU VFUU OSM AUU.
TXFAK, LADNMFT CWJF!”

VEF YFRZFG SC GSAZT, HUMF DAX WR EARZ, IWXFZ EWT TIAGVEO CSGFEFAZ IWVE
