RSVEWRP YSGF IAT TAWZ, ARZ VEF YFRZFG SC GSAZT, HFWRP CSMRZ AUGFAZO
ZSBWRP SR VEF VSXYSTV TVAWG, IAT AZJWTFZ VS UAO EWYTFUC ZSIR SR VEF
