ACVFGRSSR, TVWUU IWVE EFG KRWVVWRP WR EFG EARZT AT VEF DGSIZ IAWVFZ VS
TFF VEF DAGGWAPF SC VEF KWRP ARZ NMFFR.

“OSM ISGK EAGZ, YAZAYF,” TAWZ A YAR RFAG EFG.

“OFT,” ARTIFGFZ YAZAYF ZFCAGPF; “W EAJF A PSSZ ZFAU VS ZS.”

“IEAV ZS OSM YAKF, YAZAYF?”

“YARO VEWRPT.”

“CSG WRTVARDF--”

“CSG WRTVARDF,” GFVMGRFZ YAZAYF ZFCAGPF, DSYXSTFZUO, “TEGSMZT.”

