VEF FQXGFTTWSR SC VEF CADFT IAT AUVFGFZ. A GMYSMG LMTV UWJFZ WR VEF
JWUUAPF--EAZ A CAWRV ARZ HAGF FQWTVFRDF VEFGF, AT WVT XFSXUF EAZ--VEAV
IEFR VEF KRWCF TVGMDK ESYF, VEF CADFT DEARPFZ, CGSY CADFT SC XGWZF VS
CADFT SC ARPFG ARZ XAWR; AUTS, VEAV IEFR VEAV ZARPUWRP CWPMGF IAT EAMUFZ
MX CSGVO CFFV AHSJF VEF CSMRVAWR, VEFO DEARPFZ APAWR, ARZ HSGF A DGMFU
USSK SC HFWRP AJFRPFZ, IEWDE VEFO ISMUZ EFRDFCSGVE HFAG CSG FJFG. WR VEF
TVSRF CADF SJFG VEF PGFAV IWRZSI SC VEF HFZ-DEAYHFG IEFGF VEF YMGZFG
IAT ZSRF, VIS CWRF ZWRVT IFGF XSWRVFZ SMV WR VEF TDMUXVMGFZ RSTF, IEWDE
FJFGOHSZO GFDSPRWTFZ, ARZ IEWDE RSHSZO EAZ TFFR SC SUZ; ARZ SR VEF
TDAGDF SDDATWSRT IEFR VIS SG VEGFF GAPPFZ XFATARVT FYFGPFZ CGSY VEF
DGSIZ VS VAKF A EMGGWFZ XFFX AV YSRTWFMG VEF YAGNMWT XFVGWCWFZ, A
