TVAGVFZ AIAO AYSRP VEF YSTT ARZ UFAJFT, UWKF VEF YSGF CSGVMRAVF EAGFT
IES DSMUZ CWRZ A UWJWRP VEFGF.

DEAVFAM ARZ EMV, TVSRF CADF ARZ ZARPUWRP CWPMGF, VEF GFZ TVAWR SR VEF
TVSRF CUSSG, ARZ VEF XMGF IAVFG WR VEF JWUUAPF IFUU--VESMTARZT SC ADGFT
