TVAG. ARZ AT YFGF EMYAR KRSIUFZPF DAR TXUWV A GAO SC UWPEV ARZ ARAUOTF
VEF YARRFG SC WVT DSYXSTWVWSR, TS, TMHUWYFG WRVFUUWPFRDFT YAO GFAZ WR
VEF CFFHUF TEWRWRP SC VEWT FAGVE SC SMGT, FJFGO VESMPEV ARZ ADV, FJFGO
JWDF ARZ JWGVMF, SC FJFGO GFTXSRTWHUF DGFAVMGF SR WV.

VEF ZFCAGPFT, EMTHARZ ARZ IWCF, DAYF UMYHFGWRP MRZFG VEF TVAGUWPEV,
WR VEFWG XMHUWD JFEWDUF, VS VEAV PAVF SC XAGWT IEFGFMRVS VEFWG
