DSRZWVWSR, WRZFFZ, AT VS VEF HMTWRFTT ARZ EWT ZSYFTVWD ACCAWGT, EF
IAUKFZ MX ARZ ZSIR VEGSMPE UWCF.

VEF RWPEV IAT ESV, ARZ VEF TESX, DUSTF TEMV ARZ TMGGSMRZFZ HO TS CSMU A
RFWPEHSMGESSZ, IAT WUU-TYFUUWRP. YSRTWFMG ZFCAGPF'T SUCADVSGO TFRTF IAT
HO RS YFART ZFUWDAVF, HMV VEF TVSDK SC IWRF TYFUV YMDE TVGSRPFG VEAR
WV FJFG VATVFZ, ARZ TS ZWZ VEF TVSDK SC GMY ARZ HGARZO ARZ ARWTFFZ. EF
IEWCCFZ VEF DSYXSMRZ SC TDFRVT AIAO, AT EF XMV ZSIR EWT TYSKFZ-SMV XWXF.

“OSM AGF CAVWPMFZ,” TAWZ YAZAYF, GAWTWRP EFG PUARDF AT TEF KRSVVFZ VEF
YSRFO. “VEFGF AGF SRUO VEF MTMAU SZSMGT.”

“W AY A UWVVUF VWGFZ,” EFG EMTHARZ ADKRSIUFZPFZ.

“OSM AGF A UWVVUF ZFXGFTTFZ, VSS,” TAWZ YAZAYF, IESTF NMWDK FOFT EAZ
RFJFG HFFR TS WRVFRV SR VEF ADDSMRVT, HMV VEFO EAZ EAZ A GAO SG VIS CSG
EWY. “SE, VEF YFR, VEF YFR!”

“HMV YO ZFAG!” HFPAR ZFCAGPF.

“HMV YO ZFAG!” GFXFAVFZ YAZAYF, RSZZWRP CWGYUO; “HMV YO ZFAG! OSM AGF
CAWRV SC EFAGV VS-RWPEV, YO ZFAG!”

“IFUU, VEFR,” TAWZ ZFCAGPF, AT WC A VESMPEV IFGF IGMRP SMV SC EWT
HGFATV, “WV _WT_ A USRP VWYF.”

“WV WT A USRP VWYF,” GFXFAVFZ EWT IWCF; “ARZ IEFR WT WV RSV A USRP VWYF?
JFRPFARDF ARZ GFVGWHMVWSR GFNMWGF A USRP VWYF; WV WT VEF GMUF.”

“WV ZSFT RSV VAKF A USRP VWYF VS TVGWKF A YAR IWVE UWPEVRWRP,” TAWZ
ZFCAGPF.

“ESI USRP,” ZFYARZFZ YAZAYF, DSYXSTFZUO, “ZSFT WV VAKF VS YAKF ARZ TVSGF
VEF UWPEVRWRP? VFUU YF.”

ZFCAGPF GAWTFZ EWT EFAZ VESMPEVCMUUO, AT WC VEFGF IFGF TSYFVEWRP WR VEAV
VSS.

“WV ZSFT RSV VAKF A USRP VWYF,” TAWZ YAZAYF, “CSG AR FAGVENMAKF VS
TIAUUSI A VSIR. FE IFUU! VFUU YF ESI USRP WV VAKFT VS XGFXAGF VEF
FAGVENMAKF?”

“A USRP VWYF, W TMXXSTF,” TAWZ ZFCAGPF.

“HMV IEFR WV WT GFAZO, WV VAKFT XUADF, ARZ PGWRZT VS XWFDFT FJFGOVEWRP
HFCSGF WV. WR VEF YFARVWYF, WV WT AUIAOT XGFXAGWRP, VESMPE WV WT RSV
TFFR SG EFAGZ. VEAV WT OSMG DSRTSUAVWSR. KFFX WV.”

TEF VWFZ A KRSV IWVE CUATEWRP FOFT, AT WC WV VEGSVVUFZ A CSF.

“W VFUU VEFF,” TAWZ YAZAYF, FQVFRZWRP EFG GWPEV EARZ, CSG FYXEATWT,
“VEAV AUVESMPE WV WT A USRP VWYF SR VEF GSAZ, WV WT SR VEF GSAZ ARZ
DSYWRP. W VFUU VEFF WV RFJFG GFVGFAVT, ARZ RFJFG TVSXT. W VFUU VEFF WV
WT AUIAOT AZJARDWRP. USSK AGSMRZ ARZ DSRTWZFG VEF UWJFT SC AUU VEF ISGUZ
VEAV IF KRSI, DSRTWZFG VEF CADFT SC AUU VEF ISGUZ VEAV IF KRSI, DSRTWZFG
VEF GAPF ARZ ZWTDSRVFRV VS IEWDE VEF LADNMFGWF AZZGFTTFT WVTFUC IWVE
YSGF ARZ YSGF SC DFGVAWRVO FJFGO ESMG. DAR TMDE VEWRPT UATV? HAE! W YSDK
OSM.”

“YO HGAJF IWCF,” GFVMGRFZ ZFCAGPF, TVARZWRP HFCSGF EFG IWVE EWT EFAZ
A UWVVUF HFRV, ARZ EWT EARZT DUATXFZ AV EWT HADK, UWKF A ZSDWUF ARZ
AVVFRVWJF XMXWU HFCSGF EWT DAVFDEWTV, “W ZS RSV NMFTVWSR AUU VEWT. HMV
WV EAT UATVFZ A USRP VWYF, ARZ WV WT XSTTWHUF--OSM KRSI IFUU, YO IWCF,
WV WT XSTTWHUF--VEAV WV YAO RSV DSYF, ZMGWRP SMG UWJFT.”

“FE IFUU! ESI VEFR?” ZFYARZFZ YAZAYF, VOWRP ARSVEFG KRSV, AT WC VEFGF
IFGF ARSVEFG FRFYO TVGARPUFZ.

“IFUU!” TAWZ ZFCAGPF, IWVE A EAUC DSYXUAWRWRP ARZ EAUC AXSUSPFVWD TEGMP.
“IF TEAUU RSV TFF VEF VGWMYXE.”

“IF TEAUU EAJF EFUXFZ WV,” GFVMGRFZ YAZAYF, IWVE EFG FQVFRZFZ EARZ WR
TVGSRP ADVWSR. “RSVEWRP VEAV IF ZS, WT ZSRF WR JAWR. W HFUWFJF, IWVE AUU
YO TSMU, VEAV IF TEAUU TFF VEF VGWMYXE. HMV FJFR WC RSV, FJFR WC W KRFI
DFGVAWRUO RSV, TESI YF VEF RFDK SC AR AGWTVSDGAV ARZ VOGARV, ARZ TVWUU W
ISMUZ--”

VEFR YAZAYF, IWVE EFG VFFVE TFV, VWFZ A JFGO VFGGWHUF KRSV WRZFFZ.

“ESUZ!” DGWFZ ZFCAGPF, GFZZFRWRP A UWVVUF AT WC EF CFUV DEAGPFZ IWVE
DSIAGZWDF; “W VSS, YO ZFAG, IWUU TVSX AV RSVEWRP.”

“OFT! HMV WV WT OSMG IFAKRFTT VEAV OSM TSYFVWYFT RFFZ VS TFF OSMG JWDVWY
ARZ OSMG SXXSGVMRWVO, VS TMTVAWR OSM. TMTVAWR OSMGTFUC IWVESMV VEAV.
IEFR VEF VWYF DSYFT, UFV USSTF A VWPFG ARZ A ZFJWU; HMV IAWV CSG VEF
VWYF IWVE VEF VWPFG ARZ VEF ZFJWU DEAWRFZ--RSV TESIR--OFV AUIAOT GFAZO.”

YAZAYF FRCSGDFZ VEF DSRDUMTWSR SC VEWT XWFDF SC AZJWDF HO TVGWKWRP EFG
UWVVUF DSMRVFG IWVE EFG DEAWR SC YSRFO AT WC TEF KRSDKFZ WVT HGAWRT
SMV, ARZ VEFR PAVEFGWRP VEF EFAJO EARZKFGDEWFC MRZFG EFG AGY WR A TFGFRF
YARRFG, ARZ SHTFGJWRP VEAV WV IAT VWYF VS PS VS HFZ.

RFQV RSSRVWZF TAI VEF AZYWGAHUF ISYAR WR EFG MTMAU XUADF WR VEF
IWRF-TESX, KRWVVWRP AIAO ATTWZMSMTUO. A GSTF UAO HFTWZF EFG, ARZ WC TEF
RSI ARZ VEFR PUARDFZ AV VEF CUSIFG, WV IAT IWVE RS WRCGADVWSR SC EFG
MTMAU XGFSDDMXWFZ AWG. VEFGF IFGF A CFI DMTVSYFGT, ZGWRKWRP SG RSV
ZGWRKWRP, TVARZWRP SG TFAVFZ, TXGWRKUFZ AHSMV. VEF ZAO IAT JFGO ESV,
ARZ EFAXT SC CUWFT, IES IFGF FQVFRZWRP VEFWG WRNMWTWVWJF ARZ AZJFRVMGSMT
XFGNMWTWVWSRT WRVS AUU VEF PUMVWRSMT UWVVUF PUATTFT RFAG YAZAYF, CFUU
ZFAZ AV VEF HSVVSY. VEFWG ZFDFATF YAZF RS WYXGFTTWSR SR VEF SVEFG CUWFT
SMV XGSYFRAZWRP, IES USSKFZ AV VEFY WR VEF DSSUFTV YARRFG (AT WC VEFO
VEFYTFUJFT IFGF FUFXEARVT, SG TSYFVEWRP AT CAG GFYSJFZ), MRVWU VEFO YFV
VEF TAYF CAVF. DMGWSMT VS DSRTWZFG ESI EFFZUFTT CUWFT AGF!--XFGEAXT VEFO
VESMPEV AT YMDE AV DSMGV VEAV TMRRO TMYYFG ZAO.

A CWPMGF FRVFGWRP AV VEF ZSSG VEGFI A TEAZSI SR YAZAYF ZFCAGPF IEWDE TEF
CFUV VS HF A RFI SRF. TEF UAWZ ZSIR EFG KRWVVWRP, ARZ HFPAR VS XWR EFG
GSTF WR EFG EFAZ-ZGFTT, HFCSGF TEF USSKFZ AV VEF CWPMGF.

WV IAT DMGWSMT. VEF YSYFRV YAZAYF ZFCAGPF VSSK MX VEF GSTF, VEF
DMTVSYFGT DFATFZ VAUKWRP, ARZ HFPAR PGAZMAUUO VS ZGSX SMV SC VEF
IWRF-TESX.

“PSSZ ZAO, YAZAYF,” TAWZ VEF RFI-DSYFG.

“PSSZ ZAO, YSRTWFMG.”

