QJWW. SRF RWPEV


RFJFG ZWZ VEF TMR PS ZSIR IWVE A HGWPEVFG PUSGO SR VEF NMWFV DSGRFG WR
TSES, VEAR SRF YFYSGAHUF FJFRWRP IEFR VEF ZSDVSG ARZ EWT ZAMPEVFG TAV
MRZFG VEF XUARF-VGFF VSPFVEFG. RFJFG ZWZ VEF YSSR GWTF IWVE A YWUZFG
GAZWARDF SJFG PGFAV USRZSR, VEAR SR VEAV RWPEV IEFR WV CSMRZ VEFY TVWUU
TFAVFZ MRZFG VEF VGFF, ARZ TESRF MXSR VEFWG CADFT VEGSMPE WVT UFAJFT.

UMDWF IAT VS HF YAGGWFZ VS-YSGGSI. TEF EAZ GFTFGJFZ VEWT UATV FJFRWRP
CSG EFG CAVEFG, ARZ VEFO TAV AUSRF MRZFG VEF XUARF-VGFF.

“OSM AGF EAXXO, YO ZFAG CAVEFG?”

“NMWVF, YO DEWUZ.”

VEFO EAZ TAWZ UWVVUF, VESMPE VEFO EAZ HFFR VEFGF A USRP VWYF. IEFR WV
IAT OFV UWPEV FRSMPE VS ISGK ARZ GFAZ, TEF EAZ RFWVEFG FRPAPFZ EFGTFUC
WR EFG MTMAU ISGK, RSG EAZ TEF GFAZ VS EWY. TEF EAZ FYXUSOFZ EFGTFUC WR
HSVE IAOT, AV EWT TWZF MRZFG VEF VGFF, YARO ARZ YARO A VWYF; HMV, VEWT
VWYF IAT RSV NMWVF UWKF ARO SVEFG, ARZ RSVEWRP DSMUZ YAKF WV TS.

“ARZ W AY JFGO EAXXO VS-RWPEV, ZFAG CAVEFG. W AY ZFFXUO EAXXO WR VEF
USJF VEAV EFAJFR EAT TS HUFTTFZ--YO USJF CSG DEAGUFT, ARZ DEAGUFT'T USJF
CSG YF. HMV, WC YO UWCF IFGF RSV VS HF TVWUU DSRTFDGAVFZ VS OSM, SG
WC YO YAGGWAPF IFGF TS AGGARPFZ AT VEAV WV ISMUZ XAGV MT, FJFR HO
VEF UFRPVE SC A CFI SC VEFTF TVGFFVT, W TESMUZ HF YSGF MREAXXO ARZ
TFUC-GFXGSADECMU RSI VEAR W DAR VFUU OSM. FJFR AT WV WT--”

FJFR AT WV IAT, TEF DSMUZ RSV DSYYARZ EFG JSWDF.

WR VEF TAZ YSSRUWPEV, TEF DUATXFZ EWY HO VEF RFDK, ARZ UAWZ EFG CADF
MXSR EWT HGFATV. WR VEF YSSRUWPEV IEWDE WT AUIAOT TAZ, AT VEF UWPEV SC
VEF TMR WVTFUC WT--AT VEF UWPEV DAUUFZ EMYAR UWCF WT--AV WVT DSYWRP ARZ
WVT PSWRP.

“ZFAGFTV ZFAG! DAR OSM VFUU YF, VEWT UATV VWYF, VEAV OSM CFFU NMWVF,
NMWVF TMGF, RS RFI ACCFDVWSRT SC YWRF, ARZ RS RFI ZMVWFT SC YWRF, IWUU
FJFG WRVFGXSTF HFVIFFR MT? _W_ KRSI WV IFUU, HMV ZS OSM KRSI WV? WR OSMG
SIR EFAGV, ZS OSM CFFU NMWVF DFGVAWR?”

EFG CAVEFG ARTIFGFZ, IWVE A DEFFGCMU CWGYRFTT SC DSRJWDVWSR EF DSMUZ
TDAGDFUO EAJF ATTMYFZ, “NMWVF TMGF, YO ZAGUWRP! YSGF VEAR VEAV,” EF
AZZFZ, AT EF VFRZFGUO KWTTFZ EFG: “YO CMVMGF WT CAG HGWPEVFG, UMDWF,
TFFR VEGSMPE OSMG YAGGWAPF, VEAR WV DSMUZ EAJF HFFR--RAO, VEAR WV FJFG
IAT--IWVESMV WV.”

“WC W DSMUZ ESXF _VEAV_, YO CAVEFG!--”

“HFUWFJF WV, USJF! WRZFFZ WV WT TS. DSRTWZFG ESI RAVMGAU ARZ ESI XUAWR
WV WT, YO ZFAG, VEAV WV TESMUZ HF TS. OSM, ZFJSVFZ ARZ OSMRP, DARRSV
CMUUO AXXGFDWAVF VEF ARQWFVO W EAJF CFUV VEAV OSMG UWCF TESMUZ RSV HF
IATVFZ--”

TEF YSJFZ EFG EARZ VSIAGZT EWT UWXT, HMV EF VSSK WV WR EWT, ARZ GFXFAVFZ
VEF ISGZ.

“--IATVFZ, YO DEWUZ--TESMUZ RSV HF IATVFZ, TVGMDK ATWZF CGSY VEF
RAVMGAU SGZFG SC VEWRPT--CSG YO TAKF. OSMG MRTFUCWTERFTT DARRSV FRVWGFUO
DSYXGFEFRZ ESI YMDE YO YWRZ EAT PSRF SR VEWT; HMV, SRUO ATK OSMGTFUC,
ESI DSMUZ YO EAXXWRFTT HF XFGCFDV, IEWUF OSMGT IAT WRDSYXUFVF?”

“WC W EAZ RFJFG TFFR DEAGUFT, YO CAVEFG, W TESMUZ EAJF HFFR NMWVF EAXXO
IWVE OSM.”

EF TYWUFZ AV EFG MRDSRTDWSMT AZYWTTWSR VEAV TEF ISMUZ EAJF HFFR MREAXXO
IWVESMV DEAGUFT, EAJWRP TFFR EWY; ARZ GFXUWFZ:

“YO DEWUZ, OSM ZWZ TFF EWY, ARZ WV WT DEAGUFT. WC WV EAZ RSV HFFR
DEAGUFT, WV ISMUZ EAJF HFFR ARSVEFG. SG, WC WV EAZ HFFR RS SVEFG, W
TESMUZ EAJF HFFR VEF DAMTF, ARZ VEFR VEF ZAGK XAGV SC YO UWCF ISMUZ EAJF
DATV WVT TEAZSI HFOSRZ YOTFUC, ARZ ISMUZ EAJF CAUUFR SR OSM.”

WV IAT VEF CWGTV VWYF, FQDFXV AV VEF VGWAU, SC EFG FJFG EFAGWRP EWY
GFCFG VS VEF XFGWSZ SC EWT TMCCFGWRP. WV PAJF EFG A TVGARPF ARZ RFI
TFRTAVWSR IEWUF EWT ISGZT IFGF WR EFG FAGT; ARZ TEF GFYFYHFGFZ WV USRP
ACVFGIAGZT.

“TFF!” TAWZ VEF ZSDVSG SC HFAMJAWT, GAWTWRP EWT EARZ VSIAGZT VEF YSSR.
“W EAJF USSKFZ AV EFG CGSY YO XGWTSR-IWRZSI, IEFR W DSMUZ RSV HFAG EFG
UWPEV. W EAJF USSKFZ AV EFG IEFR WV EAT HFFR TMDE VSGVMGF VS YF VS VEWRK
SC EFG TEWRWRP MXSR IEAV W EAZ USTV, VEAV W EAJF HFAVFR YO EFAZ APAWRTV
YO XGWTSR-IAUUT. W EAJF USSKFZ AV EFG, WR A TVAVF TS ZMUU ARZ UFVEAGPWD,
VEAV W EAJF VESMPEV SC RSVEWRP HMV VEF RMYHFG SC ESGWBSRVAU UWRFT W
DSMUZ ZGAI ADGSTT EFG AV VEF CMUU, ARZ VEF RMYHFG SC XFGXFRZWDMUAG UWRFT
IWVE IEWDE W DSMUZ WRVFGTFDV VEFY.” EF AZZFZ WR EWT WRIAGZ ARZ XSRZFGWRP
YARRFG, AT EF USSKFZ AV VEF YSSR, “WV IAT VIFRVO FWVEFG IAO, W GFYFYHFG,
ARZ VEF VIFRVWFVE IAT ZWCCWDMUV VS TNMFFBF WR.”

VEF TVGARPF VEGWUU IWVE IEWDE TEF EFAGZ EWY PS HADK VS VEAV VWYF,
ZFFXFRFZ AT EF ZIFUV MXSR WV; HMV, VEFGF IAT RSVEWRP VS TESDK EFG WR
VEF YARRFG SC EWT GFCFGFRDF. EF SRUO TFFYFZ VS DSRVGATV EWT XGFTFRV
DEFFGCMURFTT ARZ CFUWDWVO IWVE VEF ZWGF FRZMGARDF VEAV IAT SJFG.

“W EAJF USSKFZ AV EFG, TXFDMUAVWRP VESMTARZT SC VWYFT MXSR VEF MRHSGR
DEWUZ CGSY IESY W EAZ HFFR GFRV. IEFVEFG WV IAT AUWJF. IEFVEFG WV EAZ
HFFR HSGR AUWJF, SG VEF XSSG YSVEFG'T TESDK EAZ KWUUFZ WV. IEFVEFG WV
IAT A TSR IES ISMUZ TSYF ZAO AJFRPF EWT CAVEFG. (VEFGF IAT A VWYF WR YO
WYXGWTSRYFRV, IEFR YO ZFTWGF CSG JFRPFARDF IAT MRHFAGAHUF.) IEFVEFG WV
IAT A TSR IES ISMUZ RFJFG KRSI EWT CAVEFG'T TVSGO; IES YWPEV FJFR UWJF
VS IFWPE VEF XSTTWHWUWVO SC EWT CAVEFG'T EAJWRP ZWTAXXFAGFZ SC EWT SIR
IWUU ARZ ADV. IEFVEFG WV IAT A ZAMPEVFG IES ISMUZ PGSI VS HF A ISYAR.”

TEF ZGFI DUSTFG VS EWY, ARZ KWTTFZ EWT DEFFK ARZ EWT EARZ.

“W EAJF XWDVMGFZ YO ZAMPEVFG, VS YOTFUC, AT XFGCFDVUO CSGPFVCMU SC
YF--GAVEFG, AUVSPFVEFG WPRSGARV SC YF, ARZ MRDSRTDWSMT SC YF. W EAJF
DATV MX VEF OFAGT SC EFG APF, OFAG ACVFG OFAG. W EAJF TFFR EFG YAGGWFZ
VS A YAR IES KRFI RSVEWRP SC YO CAVF. W EAJF AUVSPFVEFG XFGWTEFZ CGSY
VEF GFYFYHGARDF SC VEF UWJWRP, ARZ WR VEF RFQV PFRFGAVWSR YO XUADF IAT A
HUARK.”

“YO CAVEFG! FJFR VS EFAG VEAV OSM EAZ TMDE VESMPEVT SC A ZAMPEVFG IES
RFJFG FQWTVFZ, TVGWKFT VS YO EFAGV AT WC W EAZ HFFR VEAV DEWUZ.”

“OSM, UMDWF? WV WT SMV SC VEF DSRTSUAVWSR ARZ GFTVSGAVWSR OSM EAJF
HGSMPEV VS YF, VEAV VEFTF GFYFYHGARDFT AGWTF, ARZ XATT HFVIFFR MT ARZ
VEF YSSR SR VEWT UATV RWPEV.--IEAV ZWZ W TAO LMTV RSI?”

“TEF KRFI RSVEWRP SC OSM. TEF DAGFZ RSVEWRP CSG OSM.”

“TS! HMV SR SVEFG YSSRUWPEV RWPEVT, IEFR VEF TAZRFTT ARZ VEF TWUFRDF
EAJF VSMDEFZ YF WR A ZWCCFGFRV IAO--EAJF ACCFDVFZ YF IWVE TSYFVEWRP AT
UWKF A TSGGSICMU TFRTF SC XFADF, AT ARO FYSVWSR VEAV EAZ XAWR CSG WVT
CSMRZAVWSRT DSMUZ--W EAJF WYAPWRFZ EFG AT DSYWRP VS YF WR YO DFUU, ARZ
UFAZWRP YF SMV WRVS VEF CGFFZSY HFOSRZ VEF CSGVGFTT. W EAJF TFFR EFG
WYAPF WR VEF YSSRUWPEV SCVFR, AT W RSI TFF OSM; FQDFXV VEAV W RFJFG EFUZ
EFG WR YO AGYT; WV TVSSZ HFVIFFR VEF UWVVUF PGAVFZ IWRZSI ARZ VEF ZSSG.
HMV, OSM MRZFGTVARZ VEAV VEAV IAT RSV VEF DEWUZ W AY TXFAKWRP SC?”

“VEF CWPMGF IAT RSV; VEF--VEF--WYAPF; VEF CARDO?”

“RS. VEAV IAT ARSVEFG VEWRP. WV TVSSZ HFCSGF YO ZWTVMGHFZ TFRTF SC
TWPEV, HMV WV RFJFG YSJFZ. VEF XEARVSY VEAV YO YWRZ XMGTMFZ, IAT ARSVEFG
ARZ YSGF GFAU DEWUZ. SC EFG SMVIAGZ AXXFAGARDF W KRSI RS YSGF VEAR
VEAV TEF IAT UWKF EFG YSVEFG. VEF SVEFG EAZ VEAV UWKFRFTT VSS--AT OSM
EAJF--HMV IAT RSV VEF TAYF. DAR OSM CSUUSI YF, UMDWF? EAGZUO, W VEWRK?
W ZSMHV OSM YMTV EAJF HFFR A TSUWVAGO XGWTSRFG VS MRZFGTVARZ VEFTF
XFGXUFQFZ ZWTVWRDVWSRT.”

EWT DSUUFDVFZ ARZ DAUY YARRFG DSMUZ RSV XGFJFRV EFG HUSSZ CGSY GMRRWRP
DSUZ, AT EF VEMT VGWFZ VS ARAVSYWTF EWT SUZ DSRZWVWSR.

“WR VEAV YSGF XFADFCMU TVAVF, W EAJF WYAPWRFZ EFG, WR VEF YSSRUWPEV,
DSYWRP VS YF ARZ VAKWRP YF SMV VS TESI YF VEAV VEF ESYF SC EFG YAGGWFZ
UWCF IAT CMUU SC EFG USJWRP GFYFYHGARDF SC EFG USTV CAVEFG. YO XWDVMGF
IAT WR EFG GSSY, ARZ W IAT WR EFG XGAOFGT. EFG UWCF IAT ADVWJF,
DEFFGCMU, MTFCMU; HMV YO XSSG EWTVSGO XFGJAZFZ WV AUU.”

“W IAT VEAV DEWUZ, YO CAVEFG, W IAT RSV EAUC TS PSSZ, HMV WR YO USJF
VEAV IAT W.”

“ARZ TEF TESIFZ YF EFG DEWUZGFR,” TAWZ VEF ZSDVSG SC HFAMJAWT, “ARZ
VEFO EAZ EFAGZ SC YF, ARZ EAZ HFFR VAMPEV VS XWVO YF. IEFR VEFO XATTFZ
A XGWTSR SC VEF TVAVF, VEFO KFXV CAG CGSY WVT CGSIRWRP IAUUT, ARZ USSKFZ
MX AV WVT HAGT, ARZ TXSKF WR IEWTXFGT. TEF DSMUZ RFJFG ZFUWJFG YF; W
WYAPWRFZ VEAV TEF AUIAOT HGSMPEV YF HADK ACVFG TESIWRP YF TMDE VEWRPT.
HMV VEFR, HUFTTFZ IWVE VEF GFUWFC SC VFAGT, W CFUU MXSR YO KRFFT, ARZ
HUFTTFZ EFG.”

“W AY VEAV DEWUZ, W ESXF, YO CAVEFG. S YO ZFAG, YO ZFAG, IWUU OSM HUFTT
YF AT CFGJFRVUO VS-YSGGSI?”

“UMDWF, W GFDAUU VEFTF SUZ VGSMHUFT WR VEF GFATSR VEAV W EAJF VS-RWPEV
CSG USJWRP OSM HFVVFG VEAR ISGZT DAR VFUU, ARZ VEARKWRP PSZ CSG YO PGFAV
EAXXWRFTT. YO VESMPEVT, IEFR VEFO IFGF IWUZFTV, RFJFG GSTF RFAG VEF
EAXXWRFTT VEAV W EAJF KRSIR IWVE OSM, ARZ VEAV IF EAJF HFCSGF MT.”

EF FYHGADFZ EFG, TSUFYRUO DSYYFRZFZ EFG VS EFAJFR, ARZ EMYHUO VEARKFZ
EFAJFR CSG EAJWRP HFTVSIFZ EFG SR EWY. HO-ARZ-HOF, VEFO IFRV WRVS VEF
ESMTF.

VEFGF IAT RS SRF HWZZFR VS VEF YAGGWAPF HMV YG. USGGO; VEFGF IAT FJFR VS
HF RS HGWZFTYAWZ HMV VEF PAMRV YWTT XGSTT. VEF YAGGWAPF IAT VS YAKF RS
DEARPF WR VEFWG XUADF SC GFTWZFRDF; VEFO EAZ HFFR AHUF VS FQVFRZ WV,
HO VAKWRP VS VEFYTFUJFT VEF MXXFG GSSYT CSGYFGUO HFUSRPWRP VS VEF
AXSDGOXEAU WRJWTWHUF USZPFG, ARZ VEFO ZFTWGFZ RSVEWRP YSGF.

ZSDVSG YARFVVF IAT JFGO DEFFGCMU AV VEF UWVVUF TMXXFG. VEFO IFGF SRUO
VEGFF AV VAHUF, ARZ YWTT XGSTT YAZF VEF VEWGZ. EF GFPGFVVFZ VEAV DEAGUFT
IAT RSV VEFGF; IAT YSGF VEAR EAUC ZWTXSTFZ VS SHLFDV VS VEF USJWRP
UWVVUF XUSV VEAV KFXV EWY AIAO; ARZ ZGARK VS EWY ACCFDVWSRAVFUO.

TS, VEF VWYF DAYF CSG EWY VS HWZ UMDWF PSSZ RWPEV, ARZ VEFO TFXAGAVFZ.
HMV, WR VEF TVWUURFTT SC VEF VEWGZ ESMG SC VEF YSGRWRP, UMDWF DAYF
ZSIRTVAWGT APAWR, ARZ TVSUF WRVS EWT GSSY; RSV CGFF CGSY MRTEAXFZ CFAGT,
HFCSGFEARZ.

AUU VEWRPT, ESIFJFG, IFGF WR VEFWG XUADFT; AUU IAT NMWFV; ARZ EF UAO
ATUFFX, EWT IEWVF EAWG XWDVMGFTNMF SR VEF MRVGSMHUFZ XWUUSI, ARZ EWT
EARZT UOWRP NMWFV SR VEF DSJFGUFV. TEF XMV EFG RFFZUFTT DARZUF WR VEF
TEAZSI AV A ZWTVARDF, DGFXV MX VS EWT HFZ, ARZ XMV EFG UWXT VS EWT;
VEFR, UFARFZ SJFG EWY, ARZ USSKFZ AV EWY.

WRVS EWT EARZTSYF CADF, VEF HWVVFG IAVFGT SC DAXVWJWVO EAZ ISGR; HMV, EF
DSJFGFZ MX VEFWG VGADKT IWVE A ZFVFGYWRAVWSR TS TVGSRP, VEAV EF EFUZ VEF
YATVFGO SC VEFY FJFR WR EWT TUFFX. A YSGF GFYAGKAHUF CADF WR WVT NMWFV,
GFTSUMVF, ARZ PMAGZFZ TVGMPPUF IWVE AR MRTFFR ATTAWUARV, IAT RSV VS HF
HFEFUZ WR AUU VEF IWZF ZSYWRWSRT SC TUFFX, VEAV RWPEV.

TEF VWYWZUO UAWZ EFG EARZ SR EWT ZFAG HGFATV, ARZ XMV MX A XGAOFG VEAV
TEF YWPEV FJFG HF AT VGMF VS EWY AT EFG USJF ATXWGFZ VS HF, ARZ AT EWT
TSGGSIT ZFTFGJFZ. VEFR, TEF IWVEZGFI EFG EARZ, ARZ KWTTFZ EWT UWXT SRDF
YSGF, ARZ IFRV AIAO. TS, VEF TMRGWTF DAYF, ARZ VEF TEAZSIT SC VEF UFAJFT
SC VEF XUARF-VGFF YSJFZ MXSR EWT CADF, AT TSCVUO AT EFG UWXT EAZ YSJFZ
WR XGAOWRP CSG EWY.




QJWWW. RWRF ZAOT


VEF YAGGWAPF-ZAO IAT TEWRWRP HGWPEVUO, ARZ VEFO IFGF GFAZO SMVTWZF VEF
DUSTFZ ZSSG SC VEF ZSDVSG'T GSSY, IEFGF EF IAT TXFAKWRP IWVE DEAGUFT
ZAGRAO. VEFO IFGF GFAZO VS PS VS DEMGDE; VEF HFAMVWCMU HGWZF, YG.
USGGO, ARZ YWTT XGSTT--VS IESY VEF FJFRV, VEGSMPE A PGAZMAU XGSDFTT SC
GFDSRDWUFYFRV VS VEF WRFJWVAHUF, ISMUZ EAJF HFFR SRF SC AHTSUMVF HUWTT,
HMV CSG VEF OFV UWRPFGWRP DSRTWZFGAVWSR VEAV EFG HGSVEFG TSUSYSR TESMUZ
EAJF HFFR VEF HGWZFPGSSY.

“ARZ TS,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, IES DSMUZ RSV TMCCWDWFRVUO AZYWGF VEF HGWZF,
ARZ IES EAZ HFFR YSJWRP GSMRZ EFG VS VAKF WR FJFGO XSWRV SC EFG NMWFV,
XGFVVO ZGFTT; “ARZ TS WV IAT CSG VEWT, YO TIFFV UMDWF, VEAV W HGSMPEV
OSM ADGSTT VEF DEARRFU, TMDE A HAHO! USGZ HUFTT YF! ESI UWVVUF W VESMPEV
IEAV W IAT ZSWRP! ESI UWPEVUO W JAUMFZ VEF SHUWPAVWSR W IAT DSRCFGGWRP
SR YO CGWFRZ YG. DEAGUFT!”

“OSM ZWZR'V YFAR WV,” GFYAGKFZ VEF YAVVFG-SC-CADV YWTT XGSTT, “ARZ
VEFGFCSGF ESI DSMUZ OSM KRSI WV? RSRTFRTF!”

“GFAUUO? IFUU; HMV ZSR'V DGO,” TAWZ VEF PFRVUF YG. USGGO.

“W AY RSV DGOWRP,” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT; “_OSM_ AGF.”

“W, YO XGSTT?” (HO VEWT VWYF, YG. USGGO ZAGFZ VS HF XUFATARV IWVE EFG,
SR SDDATWSR.)

“OSM IFGF, LMTV RSI; W TAI OSM ZS WV, ARZ W ZSR'V ISRZFG AV WV. TMDE
A XGFTFRV SC XUAVF AT OSM EAJF YAZF 'FY, WT FRSMPE VS HGWRP VFAGT WRVS
AROHSZO'T FOFT. VEFGF'T RSV A CSGK SG A TXSSR WR VEF DSUUFDVWSR,” TAWZ
YWTT XGSTT, “VEAV W ZWZR'V DGO SJFG, UATV RWPEV ACVFG VEF HSQ DAYF, VWUU
W DSMUZR'V TFF WV.”

“W AY EWPEUO PGAVWCWFZ,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, “VESMPE, MXSR YO ESRSMG, W
EAZ RS WRVFRVWSR SC GFRZFGWRP VESTF VGWCUWRP AGVWDUFT SC GFYFYHGARDF
WRJWTWHUF VS ARO SRF. ZFAG YF! VEWT WT AR SDDATWSR VEAV YAKFT A YAR
TXFDMUAVF SR AUU EF EAT USTV. ZFAG, ZFAG, ZFAG! VS VEWRK VEAV VEFGF
YWPEV EAJF HFFR A YGT. USGGO, ARO VWYF VEFTF CWCVO OFAGT AUYSTV!”

“RSV AV AUU!” CGSY YWTT XGSTT.

“OSM VEWRK VEFGF RFJFG YWPEV EAJF HFFR A YGT. USGGO?” ATKFZ VEF
PFRVUFYAR SC VEAV RAYF.

“XSSE!” GFLSWRFZ YWTT XGSTT; “OSM IFGF A HADEFUSG WR OSMG DGAZUF.”

“IFUU!” SHTFGJFZ YG. USGGO, HFAYWRPUO AZLMTVWRP EWT UWVVUF IWP, “VEAV
TFFYT XGSHAHUF, VSS.”

“ARZ OSM IFGF DMV SMV CSG A HADEFUSG,” XMGTMFZ YWTT XGSTT, “HFCSGF OSM
IFGF XMV WR OSMG DGAZUF.”

“VEFR, W VEWRK,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, “VEAV W IAT JFGO MREARZTSYFUO ZFAUV
IWVE, ARZ VEAV W SMPEV VS EAJF EAZ A JSWDF WR VEF TFUFDVWSR SC YO
XAVVFGR. FRSMPE! RSI, YO ZFAG UMDWF,” ZGAIWRP EWT AGY TSSVEWRPUO GSMRZ
EFG IAWTV, “W EFAG VEFY YSJWRP WR VEF RFQV GSSY, ARZ YWTT XGSTT ARZ
W, AT VIS CSGYAU CSUKT SC HMTWRFTT, AGF ARQWSMT RSV VS USTF VEF CWRAU
SXXSGVMRWVO SC TAOWRP TSYFVEWRP VS OSM VEAV OSM IWTE VS EFAG. OSM UFAJF
OSMG PSSZ CAVEFG, YO ZFAG, WR EARZT AT FAGRFTV ARZ AT USJWRP AT OSMG
SIR; EF TEAUU HF VAKFR FJFGO DSRDFWJAHUF DAGF SC; ZMGWRP VEF RFQV
CSGVRWPEV, IEWUF OSM AGF WR IAGIWDKTEWGF ARZ VEFGFAHSMVT, FJFR VFUUTSR'T
TEAUU PS VS VEF IAUU (DSYXAGAVWJFUO TXFAKWRP) HFCSGF EWY. ARZ IEFR, AV
VEF CSGVRWPEV'T FRZ, EF DSYFT VS LSWR OSM ARZ OSMG HFUSJFZ EMTHARZ, SR
OSMG SVEFG CSGVRWPEV'T VGWX WR IAUFT, OSM TEAUU TAO VEAV IF EAJF TFRV
EWY VS OSM WR VEF HFTV EFAUVE ARZ WR VEF EAXXWFTV CGAYF. RSI, W EFAG
TSYFHSZO'T TVFX DSYWRP VS VEF ZSSG. UFV YF KWTT YO ZFAG PWGU IWVE AR
SUZ-CATEWSRFZ HADEFUSG HUFTTWRP, HFCSGF TSYFHSZO DSYFT VS DUAWY EWT
SIR.”

CSG A YSYFRV, EF EFUZ VEF CAWG CADF CGSY EWY VS USSK AV VEF
IFUU-GFYFYHFGFZ FQXGFTTWSR SR VEF CSGFEFAZ, ARZ VEFR UAWZ VEF HGWPEV
PSUZFR EAWG APAWRTV EWT UWVVUF HGSIR IWP, IWVE A PFRMWRF VFRZFGRFTT ARZ
ZFUWDADO IEWDE, WC TMDE VEWRPT HF SUZ-CATEWSRFZ, IFGF AT SUZ AT AZAY.

VEF ZSSG SC VEF ZSDVSG'T GSSY SXFRFZ, ARZ EF DAYF SMV IWVE DEAGUFT
ZAGRAO. EF IAT TS ZFAZUO XAUF--IEWDE EAZ RSV HFFR VEF DATF IEFR VEFO
IFRV WR VSPFVEFG--VEAV RS JFTVWPF SC DSUSMG IAT VS HF TFFR WR EWT CADF.
HMV, WR VEF DSYXSTMGF SC EWT YARRFG EF IAT MRAUVFGFZ, FQDFXV VEAV VS VEF
TEGFIZ PUARDF SC YG. USGGO WV ZWTDUSTFZ TSYF TEAZSIO WRZWDAVWSR VEAV VEF
SUZ AWG SC AJSWZARDF ARZ ZGFAZ EAZ UAVFUO XATTFZ SJFG EWY, UWKF A DSUZ
IWRZ.

EF PAJF EWT AGY VS EWT ZAMPEVFG, ARZ VSSK EFG ZSIR-TVAWGT VS VEF DEAGWSV
IEWDE YG. USGGO EAZ EWGFZ WR ESRSMG SC VEF ZAO. VEF GFTV CSUUSIFZ WR
ARSVEFG DAGGWAPF, ARZ TSSR, WR A RFWPEHSMGWRP DEMGDE, IEFGF RS TVGARPF
FOFT USSKFZ SR, DEAGUFT ZAGRAO ARZ UMDWF YARFVVF IFGF EAXXWUO YAGGWFZ.

HFTWZFT VEF PUARDWRP VFAGT VEAV TESRF AYSRP VEF TYWUFT SC VEF UWVVUF
PGSMX IEFR WV IAT ZSRF, TSYF ZWAYSRZT, JFGO HGWPEV ARZ TXAGKUWRP,
PUARDFZ SR VEF HGWZF'T EARZ, IEWDE IFGF RFIUO GFUFATFZ CGSY VEF
ZAGK SHTDMGWVO SC SRF SC YG. USGGO'T XSDKFVT. VEFO GFVMGRFZ ESYF VS
HGFAKCATV, ARZ AUU IFRV IFUU, ARZ WR ZMF DSMGTF VEF PSUZFR EAWG VEAV EAZ
YWRPUFZ IWVE VEF XSSG TESFYAKFG'T IEWVF USDKT WR VEF XAGWT PAGGFV, IFGF
YWRPUFZ IWVE VEFY APAWR WR VEF YSGRWRP TMRUWPEV, SR VEF VEGFTESUZ SC VEF
ZSSG AV XAGVWRP.

WV IAT A EAGZ XAGVWRP, VESMPE WV IAT RSV CSG USRP. HMV EFG CAVEFG
DEFFGFZ EFG, ARZ TAWZ AV UATV, PFRVUO ZWTFRPAPWRP EWYTFUC CGSY EFG
FRCSUZWRP AGYT, “VAKF EFG, DEAGUFT! TEF WT OSMGT!”

ARZ EFG APWVAVFZ EARZ IAJFZ VS VEFY CGSY A DEAWTF IWRZSI, ARZ TEF IAT
PSRF.

VEF DSGRFG HFWRP SMV SC VEF IAO SC VEF WZUF ARZ DMGWSMT, ARZ VEF
XGFXAGAVWSRT EAJWRP HFFR JFGO TWYXUF ARZ CFI, VEF ZSDVSG, YG. USGGO,
ARZ YWTT XGSTT, IFGF UFCV NMWVF AUSRF. WV IAT IEFR VEFO VMGRFZ WRVS
VEF IFUDSYF TEAZF SC VEF DSSU SUZ EAUU, VEAV YG. USGGO SHTFGJFZ A PGFAV
DEARPF VS EAJF DSYF SJFG VEF ZSDVSG; AT WC VEF PSUZFR AGY MXUWCVFZ
VEFGF, EAZ TVGMDK EWY A XSWTSRFZ HUSI.

EF EAZ RAVMGAUUO GFXGFTTFZ YMDE, ARZ TSYF GFJMUTWSR YWPEV EAJF HFFR
FQXFDVFZ WR EWY IEFR VEF SDDATWSR CSG GFXGFTTWSR IAT PSRF. HMV, WV IAT
VEF SUZ TDAGFZ USTV USSK VEAV VGSMHUFZ YG. USGGO; ARZ VEGSMPE EWT AHTFRV
YARRFG SC DUATXWRP EWT EFAZ ARZ ZGFAGWUO IARZFGWRP AIAO WRVS EWT SIR
GSSY IEFR VEFO PSV MX-TVAWGT, YG. USGGO IAT GFYWRZFZ SC ZFCAGPF VEF
IWRF-TESX KFFXFG, ARZ VEF TVAGUWPEV GWZF.

“W VEWRK,” EF IEWTXFGFZ VS YWTT XGSTT, ACVFG ARQWSMT DSRTWZFGAVWSR, “W
VEWRK IF EAZ HFTV RSV TXFAK VS EWY LMTV RSI, SG AV AUU ZWTVMGH EWY.
W YMTV USSK WR AV VFUUTSR'T; TS W IWUU PS VEFGF AV SRDF ARZ DSYF HADK
XGFTFRVUO. VEFR, IF IWUU VAKF EWY A GWZF WRVS VEF DSMRVGO, ARZ ZWRF
VEFGF, ARZ AUU IWUU HF IFUU.”

WV IAT FATWFG CSG YG. USGGO VS USSK WR AV VFUUTSR'T, VEAR VS USSK SMV SC
VFUUTSR'T. EF IAT ZFVAWRFZ VIS ESMGT. IEFR EF DAYF HADK, EF ATDFRZFZ VEF
SUZ TVAWGDATF AUSRF, EAJWRP ATKFZ RS NMFTVWSR SC VEF TFGJARV; PSWRP VEMT
WRVS VEF ZSDVSG'T GSSYT, EF IAT TVSXXFZ HO A USI TSMRZ SC KRSDKWRP.

“PSSZ PSZ!” EF TAWZ, IWVE A TVAGV. “IEAV'T VEAV?”

YWTT XGSTT, IWVE A VFGGWCWFZ CADF, IAT AV EWT FAG. “S YF, S YF! AUU WT
USTV!” DGWFZ TEF, IGWRPWRP EFG EARZT. “IEAV WT VS HF VSUZ VS UAZOHWGZ?
EF ZSFTR'V KRSI YF, ARZ WT YAKWRP TESFT!”

YG. USGGO TAWZ IEAV EF DSMUZ VS DAUY EFG, ARZ IFRV EWYTFUC WRVS VEF
ZSDVSG'T GSSY. VEF HFRDE IAT VMGRFZ VSIAGZT VEF UWPEV, AT WV EAZ HFFR
IEFR EF EAZ TFFR VEF TESFYAKFG AV EWT ISGK HFCSGF, ARZ EWT EFAZ IAT HFRV
ZSIR, ARZ EF IAT JFGO HMTO.

“ZSDVSG YARFVVF. YO ZFAG CGWFRZ, ZSDVSG YARFVVF!”

VEF ZSDVSG USSKFZ AV EWY CSG A YSYFRV--EAUC WRNMWGWRPUO, EAUC AT WC EF
IFGF ARPGO AV HFWRP TXSKFR VS--ARZ HFRV SJFG EWT ISGK APAWR.

EF EAZ UAWZ ATWZF EWT DSAV ARZ IAWTVDSAV; EWT TEWGV IAT SXFR AV VEF
VEGSAV, AT WV MTFZ VS HF IEFR EF ZWZ VEAV ISGK; ARZ FJFR VEF SUZ
EAPPAGZ, CAZFZ TMGCADF SC CADF EAZ DSYF HADK VS EWY. EF ISGKFZ
EAGZ--WYXAVWFRVUO--AT WC WR TSYF TFRTF SC EAJWRP HFFR WRVFGGMXVFZ.

YG. USGGO PUARDFZ AV VEF ISGK WR EWT EARZ, ARZ SHTFGJFZ VEAV WV IAT A
TESF SC VEF SUZ TWBF ARZ TEAXF. EF VSSK MX ARSVEFG VEAV IAT UOWRP HO
EWY, ARZ ATKFZ IEAV WV IAT.

“A OSMRP UAZO'T IAUKWRP TESF,” EF YMVVFGFZ, IWVESMV USSKWRP MX. “WV
SMPEV VS EAJF HFFR CWRWTEFZ USRP APS. UFV WV HF.”

“HMV, ZSDVSG YARFVVF. USSK AV YF!”

EF SHFOFZ, WR VEF SUZ YFDEARWDAUUO TMHYWTTWJF YARRFG, IWVESMV XAMTWRP WR
EWT ISGK.

“OSM KRSI YF, YO ZFAG CGWFRZ? VEWRK APAWR. VEWT WT RSV OSMG XGSXFG
SDDMXAVWSR. VEWRK, ZFAG CGWFRZ!”

RSVEWRP ISMUZ WRZMDF EWY VS TXFAK YSGF. EF USSKFZ MX, CSG AR WRTVARV AV
A VWYF, IEFR EF IAT GFNMFTVFZ VS ZS TS; HMV, RS XFGTMATWSR ISMUZ FQVGADV
A ISGZ CGSY EWY. EF ISGKFZ, ARZ ISGKFZ, ARZ ISGKFZ, WR TWUFRDF, ARZ
ISGZT CFUU SR EWY AT VEFO ISMUZ EAJF CAUUFR SR AR FDESUFTT IAUU, SG SR
VEF AWG. VEF SRUO GAO SC ESXF VEAV YG. USGGO DSMUZ ZWTDSJFG, IAT, VEAV
EF TSYFVWYFT CMGVWJFUO USSKFZ MX IWVESMV HFWRP ATKFZ. WR VEAV, VEFGF
TFFYFZ A CAWRV FQXGFTTWSR SC DMGWSTWVO SG XFGXUFQWVO--AT VESMPE EF IFGF
VGOWRP VS GFDSRDWUF TSYF ZSMHVT WR EWT YWRZ.

VIS VEWRPT AV SRDF WYXGFTTFZ VEFYTFUJFT SR YG. USGGO, AT WYXSGVARV AHSJF
AUU SVEFGT; VEF CWGTV, VEAV VEWT YMTV HF KFXV TFDGFV CGSY UMDWF;
VEF TFDSRZ, VEAV WV YMTV HF KFXV TFDGFV CGSY AUU IES KRFI EWY. WR
DSRLMRDVWSR IWVE YWTT XGSTT, EF VSSK WYYFZWAVF TVFXT VSIAGZT VEF UAVVFG
XGFDAMVWSR, HO PWJWRP SMV VEAV VEF ZSDVSG IAT RSV IFUU, ARZ GFNMWGFZ A
CFI ZAOT SC DSYXUFVF GFTV. WR AWZ SC VEF KWRZ ZFDFXVWSR VS HF XGADVWTFZ
SR EWT ZAMPEVFG, YWTT XGSTT IAT VS IGWVF, ZFTDGWHWRP EWT EAJWRP HFFR
DAUUFZ AIAO XGSCFTTWSRAUUO, ARZ GFCFGGWRP VS AR WYAPWRAGO UFVVFG SC
VIS SG VEGFF EMGGWFZ UWRFT WR EWT SIR EARZ, GFXGFTFRVFZ VS EAJF HFFR
AZZGFTTFZ VS EFG HO VEF TAYF XSTV.

VEFTF YFATMGFT, AZJWTAHUF VS HF VAKFR WR ARO DATF, YG. USGGO VSSK WR
VEF ESXF SC EWT DSYWRP VS EWYTFUC. WC VEAV TESMUZ EAXXFR TSSR, EF KFXV
ARSVEFG DSMGTF WR GFTFGJF; IEWDE IAT, VS EAJF A DFGVAWR SXWRWSR VEAV EF
VESMPEV VEF HFTV, SR VEF ZSDVSG'T DATF.

WR VEF ESXF SC EWT GFDSJFGO, ARZ SC GFTSGV VS VEWT VEWGZ DSMGTF
HFWRP VEFGFHO GFRZFGFZ XGADVWDAHUF, YG. USGGO GFTSUJFZ VS IAVDE EWY
AVVFRVWJFUO, IWVE AT UWVVUF AXXFAGARDF AT XSTTWHUF SC ZSWRP TS. EF
VEFGFCSGF YAZF AGGARPFYFRVT VS AHTFRV EWYTFUC CGSY VFUUTSR'T CSG VEF
CWGTV VWYF WR EWT UWCF, ARZ VSSK EWT XSTV HO VEF IWRZSI WR VEF TAYF
GSSY.

EF IAT RSV USRP WR ZWTDSJFGWRP VEAV WV IAT ISGTF VEAR MTFUFTT VS TXFAK
VS EWY, TWRDF, SR HFWRP XGFTTFZ, EF HFDAYF ISGGWFZ. EF AHARZSRFZ VEAV
AVVFYXV SR VEF CWGTV ZAO, ARZ GFTSUJFZ YFGFUO VS KFFX EWYTFUC AUIAOT
HFCSGF EWY, AT A TWUFRV XGSVFTV APAWRTV VEF ZFUMTWSR WRVS IEWDE EF EAZ
CAUUFR, SG IAT CAUUWRP. EF GFYAWRFZ, VEFGFCSGF, WR EWT TFAV RFAG VEF
IWRZSI, GFAZWRP ARZ IGWVWRP, ARZ FQXGFTTWRP WR AT YARO XUFATARV ARZ
RAVMGAU IAOT AT EF DSMUZ VEWRK SC, VEAV WV IAT A CGFF XUADF.

ZSDVSG YARFVVF VSSK IEAV IAT PWJFR EWY VS FAV ARZ ZGWRK, ARZ ISGKFZ SR,
VEAV CWGTV ZAO, MRVWU WV IAT VSS ZAGK VS TFF--ISGKFZ SR, EAUC AR ESMG
ACVFG YG. USGGO DSMUZ RSV EAJF TFFR, CSG EWT UWCF, VS GFAZ SG IGWVF.
IEFR EF XMV EWT VSSUT ATWZF AT MTFUFTT, MRVWU YSGRWRP, YG. USGGO GSTF
ARZ TAWZ VS EWY:

“IWUU OSM PS SMV?”

EF USSKFZ ZSIR AV VEF CUSSG SR FWVEFG TWZF SC EWY WR VEF SUZ YARRFG,
USSKFZ MX WR VEF SUZ YARRFG, ARZ GFXFAVFZ WR VEF SUZ USI JSWDF:

“SMV?”

“OFT; CSG A IAUK IWVE YF. IEO RSV?”

EF YAZF RS FCCSGV VS TAO IEO RSV, ARZ TAWZ RSV A ISGZ YSGF. HMV, YG.
USGGO VESMPEV EF TAI, AT EF UFARFZ CSGIAGZ SR EWT HFRDE WR VEF ZMTK,
IWVE EWT FUHSIT SR EWT KRFFT ARZ EWT EFAZ WR EWT EARZT, VEAV EF IAT WR
TSYF YWTVO IAO ATKWRP EWYTFUC, “IEO RSV?” VEF TAPADWVO SC VEF YAR SC
HMTWRFTT XFGDFWJFZ AR AZJARVAPF EFGF, ARZ ZFVFGYWRFZ VS ESUZ WV.

YWTT XGSTT ARZ EF ZWJWZFZ VEF RWPEV WRVS VIS IAVDEFT, ARZ SHTFGJFZ EWY
AV WRVFGJAUT CGSY VEF AZLSWRWRP GSSY. EF XADFZ MX ARZ ZSIR CSG A USRP
VWYF HFCSGF EF UAO ZSIR; HMV, IEFR EF ZWZ CWRAUUO UAO EWYTFUC ZSIR, EF
CFUU ATUFFX. WR VEF YSGRWRP, EF IAT MX HFVWYFT, ARZ IFRV TVGAWPEV VS EWT
HFRDE ARZ VS ISGK.

SR VEWT TFDSRZ ZAO, YG. USGGO TAUMVFZ EWY DEFFGCMUUO HO EWT RAYF,
ARZ TXSKF VS EWY SR VSXWDT VEAV EAZ HFFR SC UAVF CAYWUWAG VS VEFY. EF
GFVMGRFZ RS GFXUO, HMV WV IAT FJWZFRV VEAV EF EFAGZ IEAV IAT TAWZ, ARZ
VEAV EF VESMPEV AHSMV WV, ESIFJFG DSRCMTFZUO. VEWT FRDSMGAPFZ YG. USGGO
VS EAJF YWTT XGSTT WR IWVE EFG ISGK, TFJFGAU VWYFT ZMGWRP VEF ZAO;
AV VESTF VWYFT, VEFO NMWFVUO TXSKF SC UMDWF, ARZ SC EFG CAVEFG VEFR
XGFTFRV, XGFDWTFUO WR VEF MTMAU YARRFG, ARZ AT WC VEFGF IFGF RSVEWRP
AYWTT. VEWT IAT ZSRF IWVESMV ARO ZFYSRTVGAVWJF ADDSYXARWYFRV, RSV USRP
FRSMPE, SG SCVFR FRSMPE VS EAGATT EWY; ARZ WV UWPEVFRFZ YG. USGGO'T
CGWFRZUO EFAGV VS HFUWFJF VEAV EF USSKFZ MX SCVFRFG, ARZ VEAV EF
AXXFAGFZ VS HF TVWGGFZ HO TSYF XFGDFXVWSR SC WRDSRTWTVFRDWFT TMGGSMRZWRP
EWY.

IEFR WV CFUU ZAGK APAWR, YG. USGGO ATKFZ EWY AT HFCSGF:

“ZFAG ZSDVSG, IWUU OSM PS SMV?”

AT HFCSGF, EF GFXFAVFZ, “SMV?”

“OFT; CSG A IAUK IWVE YF. IEO RSV?”

VEWT VWYF, YG. USGGO CFWPRFZ VS PS SMV IEFR EF DSMUZ FQVGADV RS ARTIFG
CGSY EWY, ARZ, ACVFG GFYAWRWRP AHTFRV CSG AR ESMG, GFVMGRFZ. WR VEF
YFARIEWUF, VEF ZSDVSG EAZ GFYSJFZ VS VEF TFAV WR VEF IWRZSI, ARZ EAZ
TAV VEFGF USSKWRP ZSIR AV VEF XUARF-VGFF; HMV, SR YG. USGGO'T GFVMGR, EF
TUWXXFZ AIAO VS EWT HFRDE.

VEF VWYF IFRV JFGO TUSIUO SR, ARZ YG. USGGO'T ESXF ZAGKFRFZ, ARZ EWT
EFAGV PGFI EFAJWFG APAWR, ARZ PGFI OFV EFAJWFG ARZ EFAJWFG FJFGO ZAO.
VEF VEWGZ ZAO DAYF ARZ IFRV, VEF CSMGVE, VEF CWCVE. CWJF ZAOT, TWQ ZAOT,
TFJFR ZAOT, FWPEV ZAOT, RWRF ZAOT.

IWVE A ESXF FJFG ZAGKFRWRP, ARZ IWVE A EFAGV AUIAOT PGSIWRP EFAJWFG ARZ
EFAJWFG, YG. USGGO XATTFZ VEGSMPE VEWT ARQWSMT VWYF. VEF TFDGFV IAT
IFUU KFXV, ARZ UMDWF IAT MRDSRTDWSMT ARZ EAXXO; HMV EF DSMUZ RSV CAWU VS
SHTFGJF VEAV VEF TESFYAKFG, IESTF EARZ EAZ HFFR A UWVVUF SMV AV CWGTV,
IAT PGSIWRP ZGFAZCMUUO TKWUCMU, ARZ VEAV EF EAZ RFJFG HFFR TS WRVFRV SR
EWT ISGK, ARZ VEAV EWT EARZT EAZ RFJFG HFFR TS RWYHUF ARZ FQXFGV, AT WR
VEF ZMTK SC VEF RWRVE FJFRWRP.




QWQ. AR SXWRWSR


ISGR SMV HO ARQWSMT IAVDEWRP, YG. USGGO CFUU ATUFFX AV EWT XSTV. SR VEF
VFRVE YSGRWRP SC EWT TMTXFRTF, EF IAT TVAGVUFZ HO VEF TEWRWRP SC VEF TMR
WRVS VEF GSSY IEFGF A EFAJO TUMYHFG EAZ SJFGVAKFR EWY IEFR WV IAT ZAGK
RWPEV.

EF GMHHFZ EWT FOFT ARZ GSMTFZ EWYTFUC; HMV EF ZSMHVFZ, IEFR EF EAZ
ZSRF TS, IEFVEFG EF IAT RSV TVWUU ATUFFX. CSG, PSWRP VS VEF ZSSG SC VEF
ZSDVSG'T GSSY ARZ USSKWRP WR, EF XFGDFWJFZ VEAV VEF TESFYAKFG'T HFRDE
ARZ VSSUT IFGF XMV ATWZF APAWR, ARZ VEAV VEF ZSDVSG EWYTFUC TAV GFAZWRP
AV VEF IWRZSI. EF IAT WR EWT MTMAU YSGRWRP ZGFTT, ARZ EWT CADF (IEWDE
YG. USGGO DSMUZ ZWTVWRDVUO TFF), VESMPE TVWUU JFGO XAUF, IAT DAUYUO
TVMZWSMT ARZ AVVFRVWJF.

FJFR IEFR EF EAZ TAVWTCWFZ EWYTFUC VEAV EF IAT AIAKF, YG. USGGO CFUV
PWZZWUO MRDFGVAWR CSG TSYF CFI YSYFRVT IEFVEFG VEF UAVF TESFYAKWRP YWPEV
RSV HF A ZWTVMGHFZ ZGFAY SC EWT SIR; CSG, ZWZ RSV EWT FOFT TESI EWY EWT
CGWFRZ HFCSGF EWY WR EWT ADDMTVSYFZ DUSVEWRP ARZ ATXFDV, ARZ FYXUSOFZ
AT MTMAU; ARZ IAT VEFGF ARO TWPR IWVEWR VEFWG GARPF, VEAV VEF DEARPF SC
IEWDE EF EAZ TS TVGSRP AR WYXGFTTWSR EAZ ADVMAUUO EAXXFRFZ?

WV IAT HMV VEF WRNMWGO SC EWT CWGTV DSRCMTWSR ARZ ATVSRWTEYFRV, VEF
ARTIFG HFWRP SHJWSMT. WC VEF WYXGFTTWSR IFGF RSV XGSZMDFZ HO A GFAU
DSGGFTXSRZWRP ARZ TMCCWDWFRV DAMTF, ESI DAYF EF, LAGJWT USGGO, VEFGF?
ESI DAYF EF VS EAJF CAUUFR ATUFFX, WR EWT DUSVEFT, SR VEF TSCA WR ZSDVSG
YARFVVF'T DSRTMUVWRP-GSSY, ARZ VS HF ZFHAVWRP VEFTF XSWRVT SMVTWZF VEF
ZSDVSG'T HFZGSSY ZSSG WR VEF FAGUO YSGRWRP?

IWVEWR A CFI YWRMVFT, YWTT XGSTT TVSSZ IEWTXFGWRP AV EWT TWZF. WC EF
EAZ EAZ ARO XAGVWDUF SC ZSMHV UFCV, EFG VAUK ISMUZ SC RFDFTTWVO EAJF
GFTSUJFZ WV; HMV EF IAT HO VEAV VWYF DUFAG-EFAZFZ, ARZ EAZ RSRF.
EF AZJWTFZ VEAV VEFO TESMUZ UFV VEF VWYF PS HO MRVWU VEF GFPMUAG
HGFAKCATV-ESMG, ARZ TESMUZ VEFR YFFV VEF ZSDVSG AT WC RSVEWRP MRMTMAU
EAZ SDDMGGFZ. WC EF AXXFAGFZ VS HF WR EWT DMTVSYAGO TVAVF SC YWRZ, YG.
USGGO ISMUZ VEFR DAMVWSMTUO XGSDFFZ VS TFFK ZWGFDVWSR ARZ PMWZARDF CGSY
VEF SXWRWSR EF EAZ HFFR, WR EWT ARQWFVO, TS ARQWSMT VS SHVAWR.

YWTT XGSTT, TMHYWVVWRP EFGTFUC VS EWT LMZPYFRV, VEF TDEFYF IAT ISGKFZ
SMV IWVE DAGF. EAJWRP AHMRZARDF SC VWYF CSG EWT MTMAU YFVESZWDAU
VSWUFVVF, YG. USGGO XGFTFRVFZ EWYTFUC AV VEF HGFAKCATV-ESMG WR EWT MTMAU
IEWVF UWRFR, ARZ IWVE EWT MTMAU RFAV UFP. VEF ZSDVSG IAT TMYYSRFZ WR VEF
MTMAU IAO, ARZ DAYF VS HGFAKCATV.

TS CAG AT WV IAT XSTTWHUF VS DSYXGFEFRZ EWY IWVESMV SJFGTVFXXWRP VESTF
ZFUWDAVF ARZ PGAZMAU AXXGSADEFT IEWDE YG. USGGO CFUV VS HF VEF SRUO TACF
AZJARDF, EF AV CWGTV TMXXSTFZ VEAV EWT ZAMPEVFG'T YAGGWAPF EAZ VAKFR
XUADF OFTVFGZAO. AR WRDWZFRVAU AUUMTWSR, XMGXSTFUO VEGSIR SMV, VS
VEF ZAO SC VEF IFFK, ARZ VEF ZAO SC VEF YSRVE, TFV EWY VEWRKWRP ARZ
DSMRVWRP, ARZ FJWZFRVUO YAZF EWY MRFATO. WR AUU SVEFG GFTXFDVT, ESIFJFG,
EF IAT TS DSYXSTFZUO EWYTFUC, VEAV YG. USGGO ZFVFGYWRFZ VS EAJF VEF AWZ
EF TSMPEV. ARZ VEAV AWZ IAT EWT SIR.

VEFGFCSGF, IEFR VEF HGFAKCATV IAT ZSRF ARZ DUFAGFZ AIAO, ARZ EF ARZ VEF
ZSDVSG IFGF UFCV VSPFVEFG, YG. USGGO TAWZ, CFFUWRPUO:

“YO ZFAG YARFVVF, W AY ARQWSMT VS EAJF OSMG SXWRWSR, WR DSRCWZFRDF, SR A
JFGO DMGWSMT DATF WR IEWDE W AY ZFFXUO WRVFGFTVFZ; VEAV WT VS TAO, WV WT
JFGO DMGWSMT VS YF; XFGEAXT, VS OSMG HFVVFG WRCSGYAVWSR WV YAO HF UFTT
TS.”

PUARDWRP AV EWT EARZT, IEWDE IFGF ZWTDSUSMGFZ HO EWT UAVF ISGK, VEF
ZSDVSG USSKFZ VGSMHUFZ, ARZ UWTVFRFZ AVVFRVWJFUO. EF EAZ AUGFAZO PUARDFZ
AV EWT EARZT YSGF VEAR SRDF.

“ZSDVSG YARFVVF,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, VSMDEWRP EWY ACCFDVWSRAVFUO SR VEF
AGY, “VEF DATF WT VEF DATF SC A XAGVWDMUAGUO ZFAG CGWFRZ SC YWRF. XGAO
PWJF OSMG YWRZ VS WV, ARZ AZJWTF YF IFUU CSG EWT TAKF--ARZ AHSJF AUU,
CSG EWT ZAMPEVFG'T--EWT ZAMPEVFG'T, YO ZFAG YARFVVF.”

“WC W MRZFGTVARZ,” TAWZ VEF ZSDVSG, WR A TMHZMFZ VSRF, “TSYF YFRVAU
TESDK--?”

“OFT!”

“HF FQXUWDWV,” TAWZ VEF ZSDVSG. “TXAGF RS ZFVAWU.”

YG. USGGO TAI VEAV VEFO MRZFGTVSSZ SRF ARSVEFG, ARZ XGSDFFZFZ.

“YO ZFAG YARFVVF, WV WT VEF DATF SC AR SUZ ARZ A XGSUSRPFZ TESDK,
SC PGFAV ADMVFRFTT ARZ TFJFGWVO VS VEF ACCFDVWSRT, VEF CFFUWRPT,
VEF--VEF--AT OSM FQXGFTT WV--VEF YWRZ. VEF YWRZ. WV WT VEF DATF SC A
TESDK MRZFG IEWDE VEF TMCCFGFG IAT HSGRF ZSIR, SRF DARRSV TAO CSG ESI
USRP, HFDAMTF W HFUWFJF EF DARRSV DAUDMUAVF VEF VWYF EWYTFUC, ARZ VEFGF
AGF RS SVEFG YFART SC PFVVWRP AV WV. WV WT VEF DATF SC A TESDK CGSY
IEWDE VEF TMCCFGFG GFDSJFGFZ, HO A XGSDFTT VEAV EF DARRSV VGADF
EWYTFUC--AT W SRDF EFAGZ EWY XMHUWDUO GFUAVF WR A TVGWKWRP YARRFG. WV WT
VEF DATF SC A TESDK CGSY IEWDE EF EAT GFDSJFGFZ, TS DSYXUFVFUO, AT VS
HF A EWPEUO WRVFUUWPFRV YAR, DAXAHUF SC DUSTF AXXUWDAVWSR SC YWRZ, ARZ
PGFAV FQFGVWSR SC HSZO, ARZ SC DSRTVARVUO YAKWRP CGFTE AZZWVWSRT VS EWT
TVSDK SC KRSIUFZPF, IEWDE IAT AUGFAZO JFGO UAGPF. HMV, MRCSGVMRAVFUO,
VEFGF EAT HFFR,” EF XAMTFZ ARZ VSSK A ZFFX HGFAVE--“A TUWPEV GFUAXTF.”

VEF ZSDVSG, WR A USI JSWDF, ATKFZ, “SC ESI USRP ZMGAVWSR?”

“RWRF ZAOT ARZ RWPEVT.”

“ESI ZWZ WV TESI WVTFUC? W WRCFG,” PUARDWRP AV EWT EARZT APAWR, “WR VEF
GFTMYXVWSR SC TSYF SUZ XMGTMWV DSRRFDVFZ IWVE VEF TESDK?”

“VEAV WT VEF CADV.”

“RSI, ZWZ OSM FJFG TFF EWY,” ATKFZ VEF ZSDVSG, ZWTVWRDVUO ARZ
DSUUFDVFZUO, VESMPE WR VEF TAYF USI JSWDF, “FRPAPFZ WR VEAV XMGTMWV
SGWPWRAUUO?”

“SRDF.”

“ARZ IEFR VEF GFUAXTF CFUU SR EWY, IAT EF WR YSTV GFTXFDVT--SG WR AUU
GFTXFDVT--AT EF IAT VEFR?”

“W VEWRK WR AUU GFTXFDVT.”

“OSM TXSKF SC EWT ZAMPEVFG. ZSFT EWT ZAMPEVFG KRSI SC VEF GFUAXTF?”

“RS. WV EAT HFFR KFXV CGSY EFG, ARZ W ESXF IWUU AUIAOT HF KFXV CGSY EFG.
WV WT KRSIR SRUO VS YOTFUC, ARZ VS SRF SVEFG IES YAO HF VGMTVFZ.”

VEF ZSDVSG PGATXFZ EWT EARZ, ARZ YMGYMGFZ, “VEAV IAT JFGO KWRZ. VEAV IAT
JFGO VESMPEVCMU!” YG. USGGO PGATXFZ EWT EARZ WR GFVMGR, ARZ RFWVEFG SC
VEF VIS TXSKF CSG A UWVVUF IEWUF.

“RSI, YO ZFAG YARFVVF,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, AV UFRPVE, WR EWT YSTV
DSRTWZFGAVF ARZ YSTV ACCFDVWSRAVF IAO, “W AY A YFGF YAR SC HMTWRFTT,
ARZ MRCWV VS DSXF IWVE TMDE WRVGWDAVF ARZ ZWCCWDMUV YAVVFGT. W ZS RSV
XSTTFTT VEF KWRZ SC WRCSGYAVWSR RFDFTTAGO; W ZS RSV XSTTFTT VEF KWRZ SC
WRVFUUWPFRDF; W IARV PMWZWRP. VEFGF WT RS YAR WR VEWT ISGUZ SR IESY
W DSMUZ TS GFUO CSG GWPEV PMWZARDF, AT SR OSM. VFUU YF, ESI ZSFT VEWT
GFUAXTF DSYF AHSMV? WT VEFGF ZARPFG SC ARSVEFG? DSMUZ A GFXFVWVWSR SC WV
HF XGFJFRVFZ? ESI TESMUZ A GFXFVWVWSR SC WV HF VGFAVFZ? ESI ZSFT WV DSYF
AHSMV AV AUU? IEAV DAR W ZS CSG YO CGWFRZ? RS YAR FJFG DAR EAJF HFFR
YSGF ZFTWGSMT WR EWT EFAGV VS TFGJF A CGWFRZ, VEAR W AY VS TFGJF YWRF,
WC W KRFI ESI.

“HMV W ZSR'V KRSI ESI VS SGWPWRAVF, WR TMDE A DATF. WC OSMG TAPADWVO,
KRSIUFZPF, ARZ FQXFGWFRDF, DSMUZ XMV YF SR VEF GWPEV VGADK, W YWPEV HF
AHUF VS ZS TS YMDE; MRFRUWPEVFRFZ ARZ MRZWGFDVFZ, W DAR ZS TS UWVVUF.
XGAO ZWTDMTT WV IWVE YF; XGAO FRAHUF YF VS TFF WV A UWVVUF YSGF DUFAGUO,
ARZ VFADE YF ESI VS HF A UWVVUF YSGF MTFCMU.”

ZSDVSG YARFVVF TAV YFZWVAVWRP ACVFG VEFTF FAGRFTV ISGZT IFGF TXSKFR, ARZ
YG. USGGO ZWZ RSV XGFTT EWY.

“W VEWRK WV XGSHAHUF,” TAWZ VEF ZSDVSG, HGFAKWRP TWUFRDF IWVE AR FCCSGV,
“VEAV VEF GFUAXTF OSM EAJF ZFTDGWHFZ, YO ZFAG CGWFRZ, IAT RSV NMWVF
MRCSGFTFFR HO WVT TMHLFDV.”

“IAT WV ZGFAZFZ HO EWY?” YG. USGGO JFRVMGFZ VS ATK.

“JFGO YMDE.” EF TAWZ WV IWVE AR WRJSUMRVAGO TEMZZFG.

“OSM EAJF RS WZFA ESI TMDE AR AXXGFEFRTWSR IFWPET SR VEF TMCCFGFG'T
YWRZ, ARZ ESI ZWCCWDMUV--ESI AUYSTV WYXSTTWHUF--WV WT, CSG EWY VS CSGDF
EWYTFUC VS MVVFG A ISGZ MXSR VEF VSXWD VEAV SXXGFTTFT EWY.”

“ISMUZ EF,” ATKFZ YG. USGGO, “HF TFRTWHUO GFUWFJFZ WC EF DSMUZ XGFJAWU
MXSR EWYTFUC VS WYXAGV VEAV TFDGFV HGSSZWRP VS ARO SRF, IEFR WV WT SR
EWY?”

“W VEWRK TS. HMV WV WT, AT W EAJF VSUZ OSM, RFQV VS WYXSTTWHUF. W FJFR
HFUWFJF WV--WR TSYF DATFT--VS HF NMWVF WYXSTTWHUF.”

“RSI,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, PFRVUO UAOWRP EWT EARZ SR VEF ZSDVSG'T AGY APAWR,
ACVFG A TESGV TWUFRDF SR HSVE TWZFT, “VS IEAV ISMUZ OSM GFCFG VEWT
AVVADK?”

“W HFUWFJF,” GFVMGRFZ ZSDVSG YARFVVF, “VEAV VEFGF EAZ HFFR A TVGSRP ARZ
FQVGASGZWRAGO GFJWJAU SC VEF VGAWR SC VESMPEV ARZ GFYFYHGARDF VEAV
IAT VEF CWGTV DAMTF SC VEF YAUAZO. TSYF WRVFRTF ATTSDWAVWSRT SC A YSTV
ZWTVGFTTWRP RAVMGF IFGF JWJWZUO GFDAUUFZ, W VEWRK. WV WT XGSHAHUF VEAV
VEFGF EAZ USRP HFFR A ZGFAZ UMGKWRP WR EWT YWRZ, VEAV VESTF ATTSDWAVWSRT
ISMUZ HF GFDAUUFZ--TAO, MRZFG DFGVAWR DWGDMYTVARDFT--TAO, SR A
XAGVWDMUAG SDDATWSR. EF VGWFZ VS XGFXAGF EWYTFUC WR JAWR; XFGEAXT VEF
FCCSGV VS XGFXAGF EWYTFUC YAZF EWY UFTT AHUF VS HFAG WV.”

“ISMUZ EF GFYFYHFG IEAV VSSK XUADF WR VEF GFUAXTF?” ATKFZ YG. USGGO,
IWVE RAVMGAU EFTWVAVWSR.

VEF ZSDVSG USSKFZ ZFTSUAVFUO GSMRZ VEF GSSY, TESSK EWT EFAZ, ARZ
ARTIFGFZ, WR A USI JSWDF, “RSV AV AUU.”

“RSI, AT VS VEF CMVMGF,” EWRVFZ YG. USGGO.

“AT VS VEF CMVMGF,” TAWZ VEF ZSDVSG, GFDSJFGWRP CWGYRFTT, “W TESMUZ EAJF
PGFAV ESXF. AT WV XUFATFZ EFAJFR WR WVT YFGDO VS GFTVSGF EWY TS TSSR, W
TESMUZ EAJF PGFAV ESXF. EF, OWFUZWRP MRZFG VEF XGFTTMGF SC A DSYXUWDAVFZ
TSYFVEWRP, USRP ZGFAZFZ ARZ USRP JAPMFUO CSGFTFFR ARZ DSRVFRZFZ APAWRTV,
ARZ GFDSJFGWRP ACVFG VEF DUSMZ EAZ HMGTV ARZ XATTFZ, W TESMUZ ESXF VEAV
VEF ISGTV IAT SJFG.”

“IFUU, IFUU! VEAV'T PSSZ DSYCSGV. W AY VEARKCMU!” TAWZ YG. USGGO.

“W AY VEARKCMU!” GFXFAVFZ VEF ZSDVSG, HFRZWRP EWT EFAZ IWVE GFJFGFRDF.

“VEFGF AGF VIS SVEFG XSWRVT,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, “SR IEWDE W AY ARQWSMT VS
HF WRTVGMDVFZ. W YAO PS SR?”

“OSM DARRSV ZS OSMG CGWFRZ A HFVVFG TFGJWDF.” VEF ZSDVSG PAJF EWY EWT
EARZ.

“VS VEF CWGTV, VEFR. EF WT SC A TVMZWSMT EAHWV, ARZ MRMTMAUUO FRFGPFVWD;
EF AXXUWFT EWYTFUC IWVE PGFAV AGZSMG VS VEF ADNMWTWVWSR SC XGSCFTTWSRAU
KRSIUFZPF, VS VEF DSRZMDVWRP SC FQXFGWYFRVT, VS YARO VEWRPT. RSI, ZSFT
EF ZS VSS YMDE?”

“W VEWRK RSV. WV YAO HF VEF DEAGADVFG SC EWT YWRZ, VS HF AUIAOT WR
TWRPMUAG RFFZ SC SDDMXAVWSR. VEAV YAO HF, WR XAGV, RAVMGAU VS WV; WR
XAGV, VEF GFTMUV SC ACCUWDVWSR. VEF UFTT WV IAT SDDMXWFZ IWVE EFAUVEO
VEWRPT, VEF YSGF WV ISMUZ HF WR ZARPFG SC VMGRWRP WR VEF MREFAUVEO
ZWGFDVWSR. EF YAO EAJF SHTFGJFZ EWYTFUC, ARZ YAZF VEF ZWTDSJFGO.”

“OSM AGF TMGF VEAV EF WT RSV MRZFG VSS PGFAV A TVGAWR?”

“W VEWRK W AY NMWVF TMGF SC WV.”

“YO ZFAG YARFVVF, WC EF IFGF SJFGISGKFZ RSI--”

“YO ZFAG USGGO, W ZSMHV WC VEAV DSMUZ FATWUO HF. VEFGF EAT HFFR A
JWSUFRV TVGFTT WR SRF ZWGFDVWSR, ARZ WV RFFZT A DSMRVFGIFWPEV.”

“FQDMTF YF, AT A XFGTWTVFRV YAR SC HMTWRFTT. ATTMYWRP CSG A YSYFRV,
VEAV EF _IAT_ SJFGISGKFZ; WV ISMUZ TESI WVTFUC WR TSYF GFRFIAU SC VEWT
ZWTSGZFG?”

“W ZS RSV VEWRK TS. W ZS RSV VEWRK,” TAWZ ZSDVSG YARFVVF IWVE VEF
CWGYRFTT SC TFUC-DSRJWDVWSR, “VEAV AROVEWRP HMV VEF SRF VGAWR SC
ATTSDWAVWSR ISMUZ GFRFI WV. W VEWRK VEAV, EFRDFCSGVE, RSVEWRP HMV TSYF
FQVGASGZWRAGO LAGGWRP SC VEAV DESGZ DSMUZ GFRFI WV. ACVFG IEAV EAT
EAXXFRFZ, ARZ ACVFG EWT GFDSJFGO, W CWRZ WV ZWCCWDMUV VS WYAPWRF ARO
TMDE JWSUFRV TSMRZWRP SC VEAV TVGWRP APAWR. W VGMTV, ARZ W AUYSTV
HFUWFJF, VEAV VEF DWGDMYTVARDFT UWKFUO VS GFRFI WV AGF FQEAMTVFZ.”

EF TXSKF IWVE VEF ZWCCWZFRDF SC A YAR IES KRFI ESI TUWPEV A VEWRP
ISMUZ SJFGTFV VEF ZFUWDAVF SGPARWTAVWSR SC VEF YWRZ, ARZ OFV IWVE VEF
DSRCWZFRDF SC A YAR IES EAZ TUSIUO ISR EWT ATTMGARDF SMV SC XFGTSRAU
FRZMGARDF ARZ ZWTVGFTT. WV IAT RSV CSG EWT CGWFRZ VS AHAVF VEAV
DSRCWZFRDF. EF XGSCFTTFZ EWYTFUC YSGF GFUWFJFZ ARZ FRDSMGAPFZ VEAR EF
GFAUUO IAT, ARZ AXXGSADEFZ EWT TFDSRZ ARZ UATV XSWRV. EF CFUV WV VS
HF VEF YSTV ZWCCWDMUV SC AUU; HMV, GFYFYHFGWRP EWT SUZ TMRZAO YSGRWRP
DSRJFGTAVWSR IWVE YWTT XGSTT, ARZ GFYFYHFGWRP IEAV EF EAZ TFFR WR VEF
UATV RWRF ZAOT, EF KRFI VEAV EF YMTV CADF WV.

“VEF SDDMXAVWSR GFTMYFZ MRZFG VEF WRCUMFRDF SC VEWT XATTWRP ACCUWDVWSR
TS EAXXWUO GFDSJFGFZ CGSY,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, DUFAGWRP EWT VEGSAV, “IF
IWUU DAUU--HUADKTYWVE'T ISGK, HUADKTYWVE'T ISGK. IF IWUU TAO, VS XMV A
DATF ARZ CSG VEF TAKF SC WUUMTVGAVWSR, VEAV EF EAZ HFFR MTFZ, WR EWT HAZ
VWYF, VS ISGK AV A UWVVUF CSGPF. IF IWUU TAO VEAV EF IAT MRFQXFDVFZUO
CSMRZ AV EWT CSGPF APAWR. WT WV RSV A XWVO VEAV EF TESMUZ KFFX WV HO
EWY?”

VEF ZSDVSG TEAZFZ EWT CSGFEFAZ IWVE EWT EARZ, ARZ HFAV EWT CSSV
RFGJSMTUO SR VEF PGSMRZ.

“EF EAT AUIAOT KFXV WV HO EWY,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, IWVE AR ARQWSMT USSK AV
EWT CGWFRZ. “RSI, ISMUZ WV RSV HF HFVVFG VEAV EF TESMUZ UFV WV PS?”

TVWUU, VEF ZSDVSG, IWVE TEAZFZ CSGFEFAZ, HFAV EWT CSSV RFGJSMTUO SR VEF
PGSMRZ.

“OSM ZS RSV CWRZ WV FATO VS AZJWTF YF?” TAWZ YG. USGGO. “W NMWVF
MRZFGTVARZ WV VS HF A RWDF NMFTVWSR. ARZ OFV W VEWRK--” ARZ VEFGF EF
TESSK EWT EFAZ, ARZ TVSXXFZ.

“OSM TFF,” TAWZ ZSDVSG YARFVVF, VMGRWRP VS EWY ACVFG AR MRFATO XAMTF,
“WV WT JFGO EAGZ VS FQXUAWR, DSRTWTVFRVUO, VEF WRRFGYSTV ISGKWRPT
SC VEWT XSSG YAR'T YWRZ. EF SRDF OFAGRFZ TS CGWPEVCMUUO CSG VEAV
SDDMXAVWSR, ARZ WV IAT TS IFUDSYF IEFR WV DAYF; RS ZSMHV WV GFUWFJFZ
EWT XAWR TS YMDE, HO TMHTVWVMVWRP VEF XFGXUFQWVO SC VEF CWRPFGT CSG
VEF XFGXUFQWVO SC VEF HGAWR, ARZ HO TMHTVWVMVWRP, AT EF HFDAYF YSGF
XGADVWTFZ, VEF WRPFRMWVO SC VEF EARZT, CSG VEF WRPFRMWVO SC VEF YFRVAU
VSGVMGF; VEAV EF EAT RFJFG HFFR AHUF VS HFAG VEF VESMPEV SC XMVVWRP WV
NMWVF SMV SC EWT GFADE. FJFR RSI, IEFR W HFUWFJF EF WT YSGF ESXFCMU SC
EWYTFUC VEAR EF EAT FJFG HFFR, ARZ FJFR TXFAKT SC EWYTFUC IWVE A KWRZ
SC DSRCWZFRDF, VEF WZFA VEAV EF YWPEV RFFZ VEAV SUZ FYXUSOYFRV, ARZ RSV
CWRZ WV, PWJFT EWY A TMZZFR TFRTF SC VFGGSG, UWKF VEAV IEWDE SRF YAO
CARDO TVGWKFT VS VEF EFAGV SC A USTV DEWUZ.”

EF USSKFZ UWKF EWT WUUMTVGAVWSR, AT EF GAWTFZ EWT FOFT VS YG. USGGO'T
CADF.

“HMV YAO RSV--YWRZ! W ATK CSG WRCSGYAVWSR, AT A XUSZZWRP YAR SC HMTWRFTT
IES SRUO ZFAUT IWVE TMDE YAVFGWAU SHLFDVT AT PMWRFAT, TEWUUWRPT, ARZ
HARK-RSVFT--YAO RSV VEF GFVFRVWSR SC VEF VEWRP WRJSUJF VEF GFVFRVWSR SC
VEF WZFA? WC VEF VEWRP IFGF PSRF, YO ZFAG YARFVVF, YWPEV RSV VEF CFAG PS
IWVE WV? WR TESGV, WT WV RSV A DSRDFTTWSR VS VEF YWTPWJWRP, VS KFFX VEF
CSGPF?”

VEFGF IAT ARSVEFG TWUFRDF.

“OSM TFF, VSS,” TAWZ VEF ZSDVSG, VGFYMUSMTUO, “WV WT TMDE AR SUZ
DSYXARWSR.”

“W ISMUZ RSV KFFX WV,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, TEAKWRP EWT EFAZ; CSG EF PAWRFZ
WR CWGYRFTT AT EF TAI VEF ZSDVSG ZWTNMWFVFZ. “W ISMUZ GFDSYYFRZ EWY VS
TADGWCWDF WV. W SRUO IARV OSMG AMVESGWVO. W AY TMGF WV ZSFT RS PSSZ.
DSYF! PWJF YF OSMG AMVESGWVO, UWKF A ZFAG PSSZ YAR. CSG EWT ZAMPEVFG'T
TAKF, YO ZFAG YARFVVF!”

JFGO TVGARPF VS TFF IEAV A TVGMPPUF VEFGF IAT IWVEWR EWY!

“WR EFG RAYF, VEFR, UFV WV HF ZSRF; W TARDVWSR WV. HMV, W ISMUZ RSV VAKF
WV AIAO IEWUF EF IAT XGFTFRV. UFV WV HF GFYSJFZ IEFR EF WT RSV VEFGF;
UFV EWY YWTT EWT SUZ DSYXARWSR ACVFG AR AHTFRDF.”

YG. USGGO GFAZWUO FRPAPFZ CSG VEAV, ARZ VEF DSRCFGFRDF IAT FRZFZ. VEFO
XATTFZ VEF ZAO WR VEF DSMRVGO, ARZ VEF ZSDVSG IAT NMWVF GFTVSGFZ. SR VEF
VEGFF CSUUSIWRP ZAOT EF GFYAWRFZ XFGCFDVUO IFUU, ARZ SR VEF CSMGVFFRVE
ZAO EF IFRV AIAO VS LSWR UMDWF ARZ EFG EMTHARZ. VEF XGFDAMVWSR VEAV
EAZ HFFR VAKFR VS ADDSMRV CSG EWT TWUFRDF, YG. USGGO EAZ XGFJWSMTUO
FQXUAWRFZ VS EWY, ARZ EF EAZ IGWVVFR VS UMDWF WR ADDSGZARDF IWVE WV, ARZ
TEF EAZ RS TMTXWDWSRT.

SR VEF RWPEV SC VEF ZAO SR IEWDE EF UFCV VEF ESMTF, YG. USGGO IFRV WRVS
EWT GSSY IWVE A DESXXFG, TAI, DEWTFU, ARZ EAYYFG, AVVFRZFZ HO YWTT XGSTT
DAGGOWRP A UWPEV. VEFGF, IWVE DUSTFZ ZSSGT, ARZ WR A YOTVFGWSMT ARZ
PMWUVO YARRFG, YG. USGGO EADKFZ VEF TESFYAKFG'T HFRDE VS XWFDFT, IEWUF
YWTT XGSTT EFUZ VEF DARZUF AT WC TEF IFGF ATTWTVWRP AV A YMGZFG--CSG
IEWDE, WRZFFZ, WR EFG PGWYRFTT, TEF IAT RS MRTMWVAHUF CWPMGF. VEF
HMGRWRP SC VEF HSZO (XGFJWSMTUO GFZMDFZ VS XWFDFT DSRJFRWFRV CSG VEF
XMGXSTF) IAT DSYYFRDFZ IWVESMV ZFUAO WR VEF KWVDEFR CWGF; ARZ VEF VSSUT,
TESFT, ARZ UFAVEFG, IFGF HMGWFZ WR VEF PAGZFR. TS IWDKFZ ZS ZFTVGMDVWSR
ARZ TFDGFDO AXXFAG VS ESRFTV YWRZT, VEAV YG. USGGO ARZ YWTT XGSTT,
IEWUF FRPAPFZ WR VEF DSYYWTTWSR SC VEFWG ZFFZ ARZ WR VEF GFYSJAU SC WVT
VGADFT, AUYSTV CFUV, ARZ AUYSTV USSKFZ, UWKF ADDSYXUWDFT WR A ESGGWHUF
DGWYF.




QQ. A XUFA


IEFR VEF RFIUO-YAGGWFZ XAWG DAYF ESYF, VEF CWGTV XFGTSR IES AXXFAGFZ, VS
SCCFG EWT DSRPGAVMUAVWSRT, IAT TOZRFO DAGVSR. VEFO EAZ RSV HFFR AV ESYF
YARO ESMGT, IEFR EF XGFTFRVFZ EWYTFUC. EF IAT RSV WYXGSJFZ WR EAHWVT, SG
WR USSKT, SG WR YARRFG; HMV VEFGF IAT A DFGVAWR GMPPFZ AWG SC CWZFUWVO
AHSMV EWY, IEWDE IAT RFI VS VEF SHTFGJAVWSR SC DEAGUFT ZAGRAO.

EF IAVDEFZ EWT SXXSGVMRWVO SC VAKWRP ZAGRAO ATWZF WRVS A IWRZSI, ARZ SC
TXFAKWRP VS EWY IEFR RS SRF SJFGEFAGZ.

“YG. ZAGRAO,” TAWZ DAGVSR, “W IWTE IF YWPEV HF CGWFRZT.”

“IF AGF AUGFAZO CGWFRZT, W ESXF.”

“OSM AGF PSSZ FRSMPE VS TAO TS, AT A CATEWSR SC TXFFDE; HMV, W ZSR'V
YFAR ARO CATEWSR SC TXFFDE. WRZFFZ, IEFR W TAO W IWTE IF YWPEV HF
CGWFRZT, W TDAGDFUO YFAR NMWVF VEAV, FWVEFG.”

DEAGUFT ZAGRAO--AT IAT RAVMGAU--ATKFZ EWY, WR AUU PSSZ-EMYSMG ARZ
PSSZ-CFUUSITEWX, IEAV EF ZWZ YFAR?

“MXSR YO UWCF,” TAWZ DAGVSR, TYWUWRP, “W CWRZ VEAV FATWFG VS DSYXGFEFRZ
WR YO SIR YWRZ, VEAR VS DSRJFO VS OSMGT. ESIFJFG, UFV YF VGO. OSM
GFYFYHFG A DFGVAWR CAYSMT SDDATWSR IEFR W IAT YSGF ZGMRK VEAR--VEAR
MTMAU?”

“W GFYFYHFG A DFGVAWR CAYSMT SDDATWSR IEFR OSM CSGDFZ YF VS DSRCFTT VEAV
OSM EAZ HFFR ZGWRKWRP.”

“W GFYFYHFG WV VSS. VEF DMGTF SC VESTF SDDATWSRT WT EFAJO MXSR YF, CSG W
AUIAOT GFYFYHFG VEFY. W ESXF WV YAO HF VAKFR WRVS ADDSMRV SRF ZAO,
IEFR AUU ZAOT AGF AV AR FRZ CSG YF! ZSR'V HF AUAGYFZ; W AY RSV PSWRP VS
XGFADE.”

“W AY RSV AV AUU AUAGYFZ. FAGRFTVRFTT WR OSM, WT AROVEWRP HMV AUAGYWRP
VS YF.”

“AE!” TAWZ DAGVSR, IWVE A DAGFUFTT IAJF SC EWT EARZ, AT WC EF IAJFZ VEAV
AIAO. “SR VEF ZGMRKFR SDDATWSR WR NMFTVWSR (SRF SC A UAGPF RMYHFG, AT
OSM KRSI), W IAT WRTMCCFGAHUF AHSMV UWKWRP OSM, ARZ RSV UWKWRP OSM. W
IWTE OSM ISMUZ CSGPFV WV.”

“W CSGPSV WV USRP APS.”

“CATEWSR SC TXFFDE APAWR! HMV, YG. ZAGRAO, SHUWJWSR WT RSV TS FATO VS
YF, AT OSM GFXGFTFRV WV VS HF VS OSM. W EAJF HO RS YFART CSGPSVVFR WV,
ARZ A UWPEV ARTIFG ZSFT RSV EFUX YF VS CSGPFV WV.”

“WC WV IAT A UWPEV ARTIFG,” GFVMGRFZ ZAGRAO, “W HFP OSMG CSGPWJFRFTT
CSG WV. W EAZ RS SVEFG SHLFDV VEAR VS VMGR A TUWPEV VEWRP, IEWDE, VS YO
TMGXGWTF, TFFYT VS VGSMHUF OSM VSS YMDE, ATWZF. W ZFDUAGF VS OSM, SR VEF
CAWVE SC A PFRVUFYAR, VEAV W EAJF USRP ZWTYWTTFZ WV CGSY YO YWRZ. PSSZ
EFAJFR, IEAV IAT VEFGF VS ZWTYWTT! EAJF W EAZ RSVEWRP YSGF WYXSGVARV VS
GFYFYHFG, WR VEF PGFAV TFGJWDF OSM GFRZFGFZ YF VEAV ZAO?”

“AT VS VEF PGFAV TFGJWDF,” TAWZ DAGVSR, “W AY HSMRZ VS AJSI VS OSM, IEFR
OSM TXFAK SC WV WR VEAV IAO, VEAV WV IAT YFGF XGSCFTTWSRAU DUAXVGAX, W
ZSR'V KRSI VEAV W DAGFZ IEAV HFDAYF SC OSM, IEFR W GFRZFGFZ WV.--YWRZ! W
TAO IEFR W GFRZFGFZ WV; W AY TXFAKWRP SC VEF XATV.”

“OSM YAKF UWPEV SC VEF SHUWPAVWSR,” GFVMGRFZ ZAGRAO, “HMV W IWUU RSV
NMAGGFU IWVE _OSMG_ UWPEV ARTIFG.”

“PFRMWRF VGMVE, YG. ZAGRAO, VGMTV YF! W EAJF PSRF ATWZF CGSY YO XMGXSTF;
W IAT TXFAKWRP AHSMV SMG HFWRP CGWFRZT. RSI, OSM KRSI YF; OSM KRSI W AY
WRDAXAHUF SC AUU VEF EWPEFG ARZ HFVVFG CUWPEVT SC YFR. WC OSM ZSMHV WV,
ATK TVGOJFG, ARZ EF'UU VFUU OSM TS.”

“W XGFCFG VS CSGY YO SIR SXWRWSR, IWVESMV VEF AWZ SC EWT.”

“IFUU! AV ARO GAVF OSM KRSI YF AT A ZWTTSUMVF ZSP, IES EAT RFJFG ZSRF
ARO PSSZ, ARZ RFJFG IWUU.”

“W ZSR'V KRSI VEAV OSM 'RFJFG IWUU.'”

“HMV W ZS, ARZ OSM YMTV VAKF YO ISGZ CSG WV. IFUU! WC OSM DSMUZ FRZMGF
VS EAJF TMDE A ISGVEUFTT CFUUSI, ARZ A CFUUSI SC TMDE WRZWCCFGFRV
GFXMVAVWSR, DSYWRP ARZ PSWRP AV SZZ VWYFT, W TESMUZ ATK VEAV W YWPEV HF
XFGYWVVFZ VS DSYF ARZ PS AT A XGWJWUFPFZ XFGTSR EFGF; VEAV W YWPEV
HF GFPAGZFZ AT AR MTFUFTT (ARZ W ISMUZ AZZ, WC WV IFGF RSV CSG VEF
GFTFYHUARDF W ZFVFDVFZ HFVIFFR OSM ARZ YF, AR MRSGRAYFRVAU) XWFDF SC
CMGRWVMGF, VSUFGAVFZ CSG WVT SUZ TFGJWDF, ARZ VAKFR RS RSVWDF SC. W
ZSMHV WC W TESMUZ AHMTF VEF XFGYWTTWSR. WV WT A EMRZGFZ VS SRF WC W
TESMUZ AJAWU YOTFUC SC WV CSMG VWYFT WR A OFAG. WV ISMUZ TAVWTCO YF, W
ZAGF TAO, VS KRSI VEAV W EAZ WV.”

“IWUU OSM VGO?”

“VEAV WT ARSVEFG IAO SC TAOWRP VEAV W AY XUADFZ SR VEF CSSVWRP W EAJF
WRZWDAVFZ. W VEARK OSM, ZAGRAO. W YAO MTF VEAV CGFFZSY IWVE OSMG RAYF?”

“W VEWRK TS, DAGVSR, HO VEWT VWYF.”

VEFO TESSK EARZT MXSR WV, ARZ TOZRFO VMGRFZ AIAO. IWVEWR A YWRMVF
ACVFGIAGZT, EF IAT, VS AUU SMVIAGZ AXXFAGARDF, AT MRTMHTVARVWAU AT FJFG.

IEFR EF IAT PSRF, ARZ WR VEF DSMGTF SC AR FJFRWRP XATTFZ IWVE YWTT
XGSTT, VEF ZSDVSG, ARZ YG. USGGO, DEAGUFT ZAGRAO YAZF TSYF YFRVWSR SC
VEWT DSRJFGTAVWSR WR PFRFGAU VFGYT, ARZ TXSKF SC TOZRFO DAGVSR AT A
XGSHUFY SC DAGFUFTTRFTT ARZ GFDKUFTTRFTT. EF TXSKF SC EWY, WR TESGV, RSV
HWVVFGUO SG YFARWRP VS HFAG EAGZ MXSR EWY, HMV AT AROHSZO YWPEV IES TAI
EWY AT EF TESIFZ EWYTFUC.

EF EAZ RS WZFA VEAV VEWT DSMUZ ZIFUU WR VEF VESMPEVT SC EWT CAWG OSMRP
IWCF; HMV, IEFR EF ACVFGIAGZT LSWRFZ EFG WR VEFWG SIR GSSYT, EF CSMRZ
EFG IAWVWRP CSG EWY IWVE VEF SUZ XGFVVO UWCVWRP SC VEF CSGFEFAZ TVGSRPUO
YAGKFZ.

“IF AGF VESMPEVCMU VS-RWPEV!” TAWZ ZAGRAO, ZGAIWRP EWT AGY AHSMV EFG.

“OFT, ZFAGFTV DEAGUFT,” IWVE EFG EARZT SR EWT HGFATV, ARZ VEF WRNMWGWRP
ARZ AVVFRVWJF FQXGFTTWSR CWQFZ MXSR EWY; “IF AGF GAVEFG VESMPEVCMU
VS-RWPEV, CSG IF EAJF TSYFVEWRP SR SMG YWRZ VS-RWPEV.”

“IEAV WT WV, YO UMDWF?”

“IWUU OSM XGSYWTF RSV VS XGFTT SRF NMFTVWSR SR YF, WC W HFP OSM RSV VS
ATK WV?”

“IWUU W XGSYWTF? IEAV IWUU W RSV XGSYWTF VS YO USJF?”

IEAV, WRZFFZ, IWVE EWT EARZ XMVVWRP ATWZF VEF PSUZFR EAWG CGSY VEF
DEFFK, ARZ EWT SVEFG EARZ APAWRTV VEF EFAGV VEAV HFAV CSG EWY!

“W VEWRK, DEAGUFT, XSSG YG. DAGVSR ZFTFGJFT YSGF DSRTWZFGAVWSR ARZ
GFTXFDV VEAR OSM FQXGFTTFZ CSG EWY VS-RWPEV.”

“WRZFFZ, YO SIR? IEO TS?”

“VEAV WT IEAV OSM AGF RSV VS ATK YF. HMV W VEWRK--W KRSI--EF ZSFT.”

“WC OSM KRSI WV, WV WT FRSMPE. IEAV ISMUZ OSM EAJF YF ZS, YO UWCF?”

“W ISMUZ ATK OSM, ZFAGFTV, VS HF JFGO PFRFGSMT IWVE EWY AUIAOT, ARZ JFGO
UFRWFRV SR EWT CAMUVT IEFR EF WT RSV HO. W ISMUZ ATK OSM VS HFUWFJF VEAV
EF EAT A EFAGV EF JFGO, JFGO TFUZSY GFJFAUT, ARZ VEAV VEFGF AGF ZFFX
ISMRZT WR WV. YO ZFAG, W EAJF TFFR WV HUFFZWRP.”

“WV WT A XAWRCMU GFCUFDVWSR VS YF,” TAWZ DEAGUFT ZAGRAO, NMWVF
ATVSMRZFZ, “VEAV W TESMUZ EAJF ZSRF EWY ARO IGSRP. W RFJFG VESMPEV VEWT
SC EWY.”

“YO EMTHARZ, WV WT TS. W CFAG EF WT RSV VS HF GFDUAWYFZ; VEFGF WT
TDAGDFUO A ESXF VEAV AROVEWRP WR EWT DEAGADVFG SG CSGVMRFT WT GFXAGAHUF
RSI. HMV, W AY TMGF VEAV EF WT DAXAHUF SC PSSZ VEWRPT, PFRVUF VEWRPT,
FJFR YAPRARWYSMT VEWRPT.”

TEF USSKFZ TS HFAMVWCMU WR VEF XMGWVO SC EFG CAWVE WR VEWT USTV YAR,
VEAV EFG EMTHARZ DSMUZ EAJF USSKFZ AV EFG AT TEF IAT CSG ESMGT.

“ARZ, S YO ZFAGFTV USJF!” TEF MGPFZ, DUWRPWRP RFAGFG VS EWY, UAOWRP EFG
EFAZ MXSR EWT HGFATV, ARZ GAWTWRP EFG FOFT VS EWT, “GFYFYHFG ESI TVGSRP
IF AGF WR SMG EAXXWRFTT, ARZ ESI IFAK EF WT WR EWT YWTFGO!”

VEF TMXXUWDAVWSR VSMDEFZ EWY ESYF. “W IWUU AUIAOT GFYFYHFG WV, ZFAG
EFAGV! W IWUU GFYFYHFG WV AT USRP AT W UWJF.”

EF HFRV SJFG VEF PSUZFR EFAZ, ARZ XMV VEF GSTO UWXT VS EWT, ARZ CSUZFZ
EFG WR EWT AGYT. WC SRF CSGUSGR IARZFGFG VEFR XADWRP VEF ZAGK TVGFFVT,
DSMUZ EAJF EFAGZ EFG WRRSDFRV ZWTDUSTMGF, ARZ DSMUZ EAJF TFFR VEF ZGSXT
SC XWVO KWTTFZ AIAO HO EFG EMTHARZ CGSY VEF TSCV HUMF FOFT TS USJWRP SC
VEAV EMTHARZ, EF YWPEV EAJF DGWFZ VS VEF RWPEV--ARZ VEF ISGZT ISMUZ RSV
EAJF XAGVFZ CGSY EWT UWXT CSG VEF CWGTV VWYF--

“PSZ HUFTT EFG CSG EFG TIFFV DSYXATTWSR!”




QQW. FDESWRP CSSVTVFXT


A ISRZFGCMU DSGRFG CSG FDESFT, WV EAT HFFR GFYAGKFZ, VEAV DSGRFG IEFGF
VEF ZSDVSG UWJFZ. FJFG HMTWUO IWRZWRP VEF PSUZFR VEGFAZ IEWDE HSMRZ
EFG EMTHARZ, ARZ EFG CAVEFG, ARZ EFGTFUC, ARZ EFG SUZ ZWGFDVGFTT ARZ
DSYXARWSR, WR A UWCF SC NMWFV HUWTT, UMDWF TAV WR VEF TVWUU ESMTF WR
VEF VGARNMWUUO GFTSMRZWRP DSGRFG, UWTVFRWRP VS VEF FDESWRP CSSVTVFXT SC
OFAGT.

AV CWGTV, VEFGF IFGF VWYFT, VESMPE TEF IAT A XFGCFDVUO EAXXO OSMRP IWCF,
IEFR EFG ISGK ISMUZ TUSIUO CAUU CGSY EFG EARZT, ARZ EFG FOFT ISMUZ HF
ZWYYFZ. CSG, VEFGF IAT TSYFVEWRP DSYWRP WR VEF FDESFT, TSYFVEWRP UWPEV,
ACAG SCC, ARZ TDAGDFUO AMZWHUF OFV, VEAV TVWGGFZ EFG EFAGV VSS YMDE.
CUMVVFGWRP ESXFT ARZ ZSMHVT--ESXFT, SC A USJF AT OFV MRKRSIR VS EFG:
ZSMHVT, SC EFG GFYAWRWRP MXSR FAGVE, VS FRLSO VEAV RFI ZFUWPEV--ZWJWZFZ
EFG HGFATV. AYSRP VEF FDESFT VEFR, VEFGF ISMUZ AGWTF VEF TSMRZ SC
CSSVTVFXT AV EFG SIR FAGUO PGAJF; ARZ VESMPEVT SC VEF EMTHARZ IES ISMUZ
HF UFCV TS ZFTSUAVF, ARZ IES ISMUZ YSMGR CSG EFG TS YMDE, TIFUUFZ VS EFG
FOFT, ARZ HGSKF UWKF IAJFT.

VEAV VWYF XATTFZ, ARZ EFG UWVVUF UMDWF UAO SR EFG HSTSY. VEFR, AYSRP VEF
AZJARDWRP FDESFT, VEFGF IAT VEF VGFAZ SC EFG VWRO CFFV ARZ VEF TSMRZ SC
EFG XGAVVUWRP ISGZT. UFV PGFAVFG FDESFT GFTSMRZ AT VEFO ISMUZ, VEF OSMRP
YSVEFG AV VEF DGAZUF TWZF DSMUZ AUIAOT EFAG VESTF DSYWRP. VEFO DAYF, ARZ
VEF TEAZO ESMTF IAT TMRRO IWVE A DEWUZ'T UAMPE, ARZ VEF ZWJWRF CGWFRZ SC
DEWUZGFR, VS IESY WR EFG VGSMHUF TEF EAZ DSRCWZFZ EFGT, TFFYFZ VS VAKF
EFG DEWUZ WR EWT AGYT, AT EF VSSK VEF DEWUZ SC SUZ, ARZ YAZF WV A TADGFZ
LSO VS EFG.

FJFG HMTWUO IWRZWRP VEF PSUZFR VEGFAZ VEAV HSMRZ VEFY AUU VSPFVEFG,
IFAJWRP VEF TFGJWDF SC EFG EAXXO WRCUMFRDF VEGSMPE VEF VWTTMF SC AUU
VEFWG UWJFT, ARZ YAKWRP WV XGFZSYWRAVF RSIEFGF, UMDWF EFAGZ WR VEF
FDESFT SC OFAGT RSRF HMV CGWFRZUO ARZ TSSVEWRP TSMRZT. EFG EMTHARZ'T
TVFX IAT TVGSRP ARZ XGSTXFGSMT AYSRP VEFY; EFG CAVEFG'T CWGY ARZ FNMAU.
US, YWTT XGSTT, WR EAGRFTT SC TVGWRP, AIAKFRWRP VEF FDESFT, AT AR
MRGMUO DEAGPFG, IEWX-DSGGFDVFZ, TRSGVWRP ARZ XAIWRP VEF FAGVE MRZFG VEF
XUARF-VGFF WR VEF PAGZFR!

FJFR IEFR VEFGF IFGF TSMRZT SC TSGGSI AYSRP VEF GFTV, VEFO IFGF RSV
EAGTE RSG DGMFU. FJFR IEFR PSUZFR EAWG, UWKF EFG SIR, UAO WR A EAUS SR A
XWUUSI GSMRZ VEF ISGR CADF SC A UWVVUF HSO, ARZ EF TAWZ, IWVE A GAZWARV
TYWUF, “ZFAG XAXA ARZ YAYYA, W AY JFGO TSGGO VS UFAJF OSM HSVE, ARZ VS
UFAJF YO XGFVVO TWTVFG; HMV W AY DAUUFZ, ARZ W YMTV PS!” VESTF IFGF RSV
VFAGT AUU SC APSRO VEAV IFVVFZ EWT OSMRP YSVEFG'T DEFFK, AT VEF TXWGWV
ZFXAGVFZ CGSY EFG FYHGADF VEAV EAZ HFFR FRVGMTVFZ VS WV. TMCCFG VEFY ARZ
CSGHWZ VEFY RSV. VEFO TFF YO CAVEFG'T CADF. S CAVEFG, HUFTTFZ ISGZT!

VEMT, VEF GMTVUWRP SC AR ARPFU'T IWRPT PSV HUFRZFZ IWVE VEF SVEFG
FDESFT, ARZ VEFO IFGF RSV IESUUO SC FAGVE, HMV EAZ WR VEFY VEAV HGFAVE
SC EFAJFR. TWPET SC VEF IWRZT VEAV HUFI SJFG A UWVVUF PAGZFR-VSYH IFGF
YWRPUFZ IWVE VEFY AUTS, ARZ HSVE IFGF AMZWHUF VS UMDWF, WR A EMTEFZ
YMGYMG--UWKF VEF HGFAVEWRP SC A TMYYFG TFA ATUFFX MXSR A TARZO TESGF--AT
VEF UWVVUF UMDWF, DSYWDAUUO TVMZWSMT AV VEF VATK SC VEF YSGRWRP, SG
ZGFTTWRP A ZSUU AV EFG YSVEFG'T CSSVTVSSU, DEAVVFGFZ WR VEF VSRPMFT SC
VEF VIS DWVWFT VEAV IFGF HUFRZFZ WR EFG UWCF.

VEF FDESFT GAGFUO ARTIFGFZ VS VEF ADVMAU VGFAZ SC TOZRFO DAGVSR. TSYF
EAUC-ZSBFR VWYFT A OFAG, AV YSTV, EF DUAWYFZ EWT XGWJWUFPF SC DSYWRP WR
MRWRJWVFZ, ARZ ISMUZ TWV AYSRP VEFY VEGSMPE VEF FJFRWRP, AT EF EAZ SRDF
ZSRF SCVFR. EF RFJFG DAYF VEFGF EFAVFZ IWVE IWRF. ARZ SRF SVEFG VEWRP
GFPAGZWRP EWY IAT IEWTXFGFZ WR VEF FDESFT, IEWDE EAT HFFR IEWTXFGFZ HO
AUU VGMF FDESFT CSG APFT ARZ APFT.

RS YAR FJFG GFAUUO USJFZ A ISYAR, USTV EFG, ARZ KRFI EFG IWVE A
HUAYFUFTT VESMPE AR MRDEARPFZ YWRZ, IEFR TEF IAT A IWCF ARZ A YSVEFG,
HMV EFG DEWUZGFR EAZ A TVGARPF TOYXAVEO IWVE EWY--AR WRTVWRDVWJF
ZFUWDADO SC XWVO CSG EWY. IEAV CWRF EWZZFR TFRTWHWUWVWFT AGF VSMDEFZ WR
TMDE A DATF, RS FDESFT VFUU; HMV WV WT TS, ARZ WV IAT TS EFGF. DAGVSR
IAT VEF CWGTV TVGARPFG VS IESY UWVVUF UMDWF EFUZ SMV EFG DEMHHO AGYT,
ARZ EF KFXV EWT XUADF IWVE EFG AT TEF PGFI. VEF UWVVUF HSO EAZ TXSKFR SC
EWY, AUYSTV AV VEF UATV. “XSSG DAGVSR! KWTT EWY CSG YF!”

YG. TVGOJFG TESMUZFGFZ EWT IAO VEGSMPE VEF UAI, UWKF TSYF PGFAV FRPWRF
CSGDWRP WVTFUC VEGSMPE VMGHWZ IAVFG, ARZ ZGAPPFZ EWT MTFCMU CGWFRZ WR
EWT IAKF, UWKF A HSAV VSIFZ ATVFGR. AT VEF HSAV TS CAJSMGFZ WT MTMAUUO
WR A GSMPE XUWPEV, ARZ YSTVUO MRZFG IAVFG, TS, TOZRFO EAZ A TIAYXFZ
UWCF SC WV. HMV, FATO ARZ TVGSRP DMTVSY, MREAXXWUO TS YMDE FATWFG ARZ
TVGSRPFG WR EWY VEAR ARO TVWYMUAVWRP TFRTF SC ZFTFGV SG ZWTPGADF, YAZF
WV VEF UWCF EF IAT VS UFAZ; ARZ EF RS YSGF VESMPEV SC FYFGPWRP CGSY EWT
TVAVF SC UWSR'T LADKAU, VEAR ARO GFAU LADKAU YAO HF TMXXSTFZ VS VEWRK SC
GWTWRP VS HF A UWSR. TVGOJFG IAT GWDE; EAZ YAGGWFZ A CUSGWZ IWZSI IWVE
XGSXFGVO ARZ VEGFF HSOT, IES EAZ RSVEWRP XAGVWDMUAGUO TEWRWRP AHSMV VEFY
HMV VEF TVGAWPEV EAWG SC VEFWG ZMYXUWRP EFAZT.

VEFTF VEGFF OSMRP PFRVUFYFR, YG. TVGOJFG, FQMZWRP XAVGSRAPF SC VEF YSTV
SCCFRTWJF NMAUWVO CGSY FJFGO XSGF, EAZ IAUKFZ HFCSGF EWY UWKF VEGFF
TEFFX VS VEF NMWFV DSGRFG WR TSES, ARZ EAZ SCCFGFZ AT XMXWUT VS
UMDWF'T EMTHARZ: ZFUWDAVFUO TAOWRP “EAUUSA! EFGF AGF VEGFF UMYXT SC
HGFAZ-ARZ-DEFFTF VSIAGZT OSMG YAVGWYSRWAU XWDRWD, ZAGRAO!” VEF XSUWVF
GFLFDVWSR SC VEF VEGFF UMYXT SC HGFAZ-ARZ-DEFFTF EAZ NMWVF HUSAVFZ YG.
TVGOJFG IWVE WRZWPRAVWSR, IEWDE EF ACVFGIAGZT VMGRFZ VS ADDSMRV WR VEF
VGAWRWRP SC VEF OSMRP PFRVUFYFR, HO ZWGFDVWRP VEFY VS HFIAGF SC VEF
XGWZF SC HFPPAGT, UWKF VEAV VMVSG-CFUUSI. EF IAT AUTS WR VEF EAHWV SC
ZFDUAWYWRP VS YGT. TVGOJFG, SJFG EWT CMUU-HSZWFZ IWRF, SR VEF AGVT
YGT. ZAGRAO EAZ SRDF XMV WR XGADVWDF VS “DAVDE” EWY, ARZ SR VEF
ZWAYSRZ-DMV-ZWAYSRZ AGVT WR EWYTFUC, YAZAY, IEWDE EAZ GFRZFGFZ EWY “RSV
VS HF DAMPEV.” TSYF SC EWT KWRP'T HFRDE CAYWUWAGT, IES IFGF SDDATWSRAUUO
XAGVWFT VS VEF CMUU-HSZWFZ IWRF ARZ VEF UWF, FQDMTFZ EWY CSG VEF
UAVVFG HO TAOWRP VEAV EF EAZ VSUZ WV TS SCVFR, VEAV EF HFUWFJFZ
WV EWYTFUC--IEWDE WT TMGFUO TMDE AR WRDSGGWPWHUF APPGAJAVWSR SC AR
SGWPWRAUUO HAZ SCCFRDF, AT VS LMTVWCO ARO TMDE SCCFRZFG'T HFWRP DAGGWFZ
SCC VS TSYF TMWVAHUO GFVWGFZ TXSV, ARZ VEFGF EARPFZ SMV SC VEF IAO.

VEFTF IFGF AYSRP VEF FDESFT VS IEWDE UMDWF, TSYFVWYFT XFRTWJF, TSYFVWYFT
AYMTFZ ARZ UAMPEWRP, UWTVFRFZ WR VEF FDESWRP DSGRFG, MRVWU EFG UWVVUF
ZAMPEVFG IAT TWQ OFAGT SUZ. ESI RFAG VS EFG EFAGV VEF FDESFT SC EFG
DEWUZ'T VGFAZ DAYF, ARZ VESTF SC EFG SIR ZFAG CAVEFG'T, AUIAOT ADVWJF
ARZ TFUC-XSTTFTTFZ, ARZ VESTF SC EFG ZFAG EMTHARZ'T, RFFZ RSV HF VSUZ.
RSG, ESI VEF UWPEVFTV FDES SC VEFWG MRWVFZ ESYF, ZWGFDVFZ HO EFGTFUC
IWVE TMDE A IWTF ARZ FUFPARV VEGWCV VEAV WV IAT YSGF AHMRZARV VEAR ARO
IATVF, IAT YMTWD VS EFG. RSG, ESI VEFGF IFGF FDESFT AUU AHSMV EFG, TIFFV
WR EFG FAGT, SC VEF YARO VWYFT EFG CAVEFG EAZ VSUZ EFG VEAV EF CSMRZ EFG
YSGF ZFJSVFZ VS EWY YAGGWFZ (WC VEAV DSMUZ HF) VEAR TWRPUF, ARZ SC VEF
YARO VWYFT EFG EMTHARZ EAZ TAWZ VS EFG VEAV RS DAGFT ARZ ZMVWFT TFFYFZ
VS ZWJWZF EFG USJF CSG EWY SG EFG EFUX VS EWY, ARZ ATKFZ EFG “IEAV WT
VEF YAPWD TFDGFV, YO ZAGUWRP, SC OSMG HFWRP FJFGOVEWRP VS AUU SC MT,
AT WC VEFGF IFGF SRUO SRF SC MT, OFV RFJFG TFFYWRP VS HF EMGGWFZ, SG VS
EAJF VSS YMDE VS ZS?”

HMV, VEFGF IFGF SVEFG FDESFT, CGSY A ZWTVARDF, VEAV GMYHUFZ YFRADWRPUO
WR VEF DSGRFG AUU VEGSMPE VEWT TXADF SC VWYF. ARZ WV IAT RSI, AHSMV
UWVVUF UMDWF'T TWQVE HWGVEZAO, VEAV VEFO HFPAR VS EAJF AR AICMU TSMRZ,
AT SC A PGFAV TVSGY WR CGARDF IWVE A ZGFAZCMU TFA GWTWRP.

SR A RWPEV WR YWZ-LMUO, SRF VESMTARZ TFJFR EMRZGFZ ARZ FWPEVO-RWRF, YG.
USGGO DAYF WR UAVF, CGSY VFUUTSR'T, ARZ TAV EWYTFUC ZSIR HO UMDWF ARZ
EFG EMTHARZ WR VEF ZAGK IWRZSI. WV IAT A ESV, IWUZ RWPEV, ARZ VEFO IFGF
AUU VEGFF GFYWRZFZ SC VEF SUZ TMRZAO RWPEV IEFR VEFO EAZ USSKFZ AV VEF
UWPEVRWRP CGSY VEF TAYF XUADF.

“W HFPAR VS VEWRK,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, XMTEWRP EWT HGSIR IWP HADK, “VEAV
W TESMUZ EAJF VS XATT VEF RWPEV AV VFUUTSR'T. IF EAJF HFFR TS CMUU SC
HMTWRFTT AUU ZAO, VEAV IF EAJF RSV KRSIR IEAV VS ZS CWGTV, SG IEWDE IAO
VS VMGR. VEFGF WT TMDE AR MRFATWRFTT WR XAGWT, VEAV IF EAJF ADVMAUUO A
GMR SC DSRCWZFRDF MXSR MT! SMG DMTVSYFGT SJFG VEFGF, TFFY RSV VS HF AHUF
VS DSRCWZF VEFWG XGSXFGVO VS MT CATV FRSMPE. VEFGF WT XSTWVWJFUO A YARWA
AYSRP TSYF SC VEFY CSG TFRZWRP WV VS FRPUARZ.”

“VEAV EAT A HAZ USSK,” TAWZ ZAGRAO--

“A HAZ USSK, OSM TAO, YO ZFAG ZAGRAO? OFT, HMV IF ZSR'V KRSI IEAV GFATSR
VEFGF WT WR WV. XFSXUF AGF TS MRGFATSRAHUF! TSYF SC MT AV VFUUTSR'T AGF
PFVVWRP SUZ, ARZ IF GFAUUO DAR'V HF VGSMHUFZ SMV SC VEF SGZWRAGO DSMGTF
IWVESMV ZMF SDDATWSR.”

“TVWUU,” TAWZ ZAGRAO, “OSM KRSI ESI PUSSYO ARZ VEGFAVFRWRP VEF TKO WT.”

“W KRSI VEAV, VS HF TMGF,” ATTFRVFZ YG. USGGO, VGOWRP VS XFGTMAZF
EWYTFUC VEAV EWT TIFFV VFYXFG IAT TSMGFZ, ARZ VEAV EF PGMYHUFZ, “HMV W
AY ZFVFGYWRFZ VS HF XFFJWTE ACVFG YO USRP ZAO'T HSVEFGAVWSR. IEFGF WT
YARFVVF?”

“EFGF EF WT,” TAWZ VEF ZSDVSG, FRVFGWRP VEF ZAGK GSSY AV VEF YSYFRV.

“W AY NMWVF PUAZ OSM AGF AV ESYF; CSG VEFTF EMGGWFT ARZ CSGFHSZWRPT HO
IEWDE W EAJF HFFR TMGGSMRZFZ AUU ZAO USRP, EAJF YAZF YF RFGJSMT IWVESMV
GFATSR. OSM AGF RSV PSWRP SMV, W ESXF?”

“RS; W AY PSWRP VS XUAO HADKPAYYSR IWVE OSM, WC OSM UWKF,” TAWZ VEF
ZSDVSG.

“W ZSR'V VEWRK W ZS UWKF, WC W YAO TXFAK YO YWRZ. W AY RSV CWV VS HF
XWVVFZ APAWRTV OSM VS-RWPEV. WT VEF VFAHSAGZ TVWUU VEFGF, UMDWF? W DAR'V
TFF.”

“SC DSMGTF, WV EAT HFFR KFXV CSG OSM.”

“VEARK OF, YO ZFAG. VEF XGFDWSMT DEWUZ WT TACF WR HFZ?”

“ARZ TUFFXWRP TSMRZUO.”

“VEAV'T GWPEV; AUU TACF ARZ IFUU! W ZSR'V KRSI IEO AROVEWRP TESMUZ HF
SVEFGIWTF VEAR TACF ARZ IFUU EFGF, VEARK PSZ; HMV W EAJF HFFR TS XMV SMV
AUU ZAO, ARZ W AY RSV AT OSMRP AT W IAT! YO VFA, YO ZFAG! VEARK OF. RSI,
DSYF ARZ VAKF OSMG XUADF WR VEF DWGDUF, ARZ UFV MT TWV NMWFV, ARZ EFAG
VEF FDESFT AHSMV IEWDE OSM EAJF OSMG VEFSGO.”

“RSV A VEFSGO; WV IAT A CARDO.”

“A CARDO, VEFR, YO IWTF XFV,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, XAVVWRP EFG EARZ. “VEFO
AGF JFGO RMYFGSMT ARZ JFGO USMZ, VESMPE, AGF VEFO RSV? SRUO EFAG VEFY!”

EFAZUSRP, YAZ, ARZ ZARPFGSMT CSSVTVFXT VS CSGDF VEFWG IAO WRVS AROHSZO'T
UWCF, CSSVTVFXT RSV FATWUO YAZF DUFAR APAWR WC SRDF TVAWRFZ GFZ, VEF
CSSVTVFXT GAPWRP WR TAWRV ARVSWRF ACAG SCC, AT VEF UWVVUF DWGDUF TAV WR
VEF ZAGK USRZSR IWRZSI.

TAWRV ARVSWRF EAZ HFFR, VEAV YSGRWRP, A JATV ZMTKO YATT SC TDAGFDGSIT
EFAJWRP VS ARZ CGS, IWVE CGFNMFRV PUFAYT SC UWPEV AHSJF VEF HWUUSIO
EFAZT, IEFGF TVFFU HUAZFT ARZ HAOSRFVT TESRF WR VEF TMR. A VGFYFRZSMT
GSAG AGSTF CGSY VEF VEGSAV SC TAWRV ARVSWRF, ARZ A CSGFTV SC RAKFZ AGYT
TVGMPPUFZ WR VEF AWG UWKF TEGWJFUUFZ HGARDEFT SC VGFFT WR A IWRVFG IWRZ:
AUU VEF CWRPFGT DSRJMUTWJFUO DUMVDEWRP AV FJFGO IFAXSR SG TFYHUARDF SC A
IFAXSR VEAV IAT VEGSIR MX CGSY VEF ZFXVET HFUSI, RS YAVVFG ESI CAG SCC.

IES PAJF VEFY SMV, IEFRDF VEFO UATV DAYF, IEFGF VEFO HFPAR, VEGSMPE IEAV
APFRDO VEFO DGSSKFZUO NMWJFGFZ ARZ LFGKFZ, TDSGFT AV A VWYF, SJFG VEF
EFAZT SC VEF DGSIZ, UWKF A KWRZ SC UWPEVRWRP, RS FOF WR VEF VEGSRP DSMUZ
EAJF VSUZ; HMV, YMTKFVT IFGF HFWRP ZWTVGWHMVFZ--TS IFGF DAGVGWZPFT,
XSIZFG, ARZ HAUU, HAGT SC WGSR ARZ ISSZ, KRWJFT, AQFT, XWKFT, FJFGO
IFAXSR VEAV ZWTVGADVFZ WRPFRMWVO DSMUZ ZWTDSJFG SG ZFJWTF. XFSXUF IES
DSMUZ UAO ESUZ SC RSVEWRP FUTF, TFV VEFYTFUJFT IWVE HUFFZWRP EARZT VS
CSGDF TVSRFT ARZ HGWDKT SMV SC VEFWG XUADFT WR IAUUT. FJFGO XMUTF ARZ
EFAGV WR TAWRV ARVSWRF IAT SR EWPE-CFJFG TVGAWR ARZ AV EWPE-CFJFG EFAV.
FJFGO UWJWRP DGFAVMGF VEFGF EFUZ UWCF AT SC RS ADDSMRV, ARZ IAT ZFYFRVFZ
IWVE A XATTWSRAVF GFAZWRFTT VS TADGWCWDF WV.

AT A IEWGUXSSU SC HSWUWRP IAVFGT EAT A DFRVGF XSWRV, TS, AUU VEWT GAPWRP
DWGDUFZ GSMRZ ZFCAGPF'T IWRF-TESX, ARZ FJFGO EMYAR ZGSX WR VEF DAUZGSR
EAZ A VFRZFRDO VS HF TMDKFZ VSIAGZT VEF JSGVFQ IEFGF ZFCAGPF EWYTFUC,
AUGFAZO HFPGWYFZ IWVE PMRXSIZFG ARZ TIFAV, WTTMFZ SGZFGT, WTTMFZ AGYT,
VEGMTV VEWT YAR HADK, ZGAPPFZ VEWT YAR CSGIAGZ, ZWTAGYFZ SRF VS AGY
ARSVEFG, UAHSMGFZ ARZ TVGSJF WR VEF VEWDKFTV SC VEF MXGSAG.

“KFFX RFAG VS YF, LADNMFT VEGFF,” DGWFZ ZFCAGPF; “ARZ ZS OSM, LADNMFT
SRF ARZ VIS, TFXAGAVF ARZ XMV OSMGTFUJFT AV VEF EFAZ SC AT YARO SC VEFTF
XAVGWSVT AT OSM DAR. IEFGF WT YO IWCF?”

“FE, IFUU! EFGF OSM TFF YF!” TAWZ YAZAYF, DSYXSTFZ AT FJFG, HMV RSV
KRWVVWRP VS-ZAO. YAZAYF'T GFTSUMVF GWPEV EARZ IAT SDDMXWFZ IWVE AR AQF,
WR XUADF SC VEF MTMAU TSCVFG WYXUFYFRVT, ARZ WR EFG PWGZUF IFGF A XWTVSU
ARZ A DGMFU KRWCF.

“IEFGF ZS OSM PS, YO IWCF?”

“W PS,” TAWZ YAZAYF, “IWVE OSM AV XGFTFRV. OSM TEAUU TFF YF AV VEF EFAZ
SC ISYFR, HO-ARZ-HOF.”

“DSYF, VEFR!” DGWFZ ZFCAGPF, WR A GFTSMRZWRP JSWDF. “XAVGWSVT ARZ
CGWFRZT, IF AGF GFAZO! VEF HATVWUUF!”

IWVE A GSAG VEAV TSMRZFZ AT WC AUU VEF HGFAVE WR CGARDF EAZ HFFR TEAXFZ
WRVS VEF ZFVFTVFZ ISGZ, VEF UWJWRP TFA GSTF, IAJF SR IAJF, ZFXVE SR
ZFXVE, ARZ SJFGCUSIFZ VEF DWVO VS VEAV XSWRV. AUAGY-HFUUT GWRPWRP, ZGMYT
HFAVWRP, VEF TFA GAPWRP ARZ VEMRZFGWRP SR WVT RFI HFADE, VEF AVVADK
HFPAR.

ZFFX ZWVDEFT, ZSMHUF ZGAIHGWZPF, YATTWJF TVSRF IAUUT, FWPEV PGFAV
VSIFGT, DARRSR, YMTKFVT, CWGF ARZ TYSKF. VEGSMPE VEF CWGF ARZ VEGSMPE
VEF TYSKF--WR VEF CWGF ARZ WR VEF TYSKF, CSG VEF TFA DATV EWY MX APAWRTV
A DARRSR, ARZ SR VEF WRTVARV EF HFDAYF A DARRSRWFG--ZFCAGPF SC VEF
IWRF-TESX ISGKFZ UWKF A YARCMU TSUZWFG, VIS CWFGDF ESMGT.

ZFFX ZWVDE, TWRPUF ZGAIHGWZPF, YATTWJF TVSRF IAUUT, FWPEV PGFAV VSIFGT,
DARRSR, YMTKFVT, CWGF ARZ TYSKF. SRF ZGAIHGWZPF ZSIR! “ISGK, DSYGAZFT
AUU, ISGK! ISGK, LADNMFT SRF, LADNMFT VIS, LADNMFT SRF VESMTARZ, LADNMFT
VIS VESMTARZ, LADNMFT CWJF-ARZ-VIFRVO VESMTARZ; WR VEF RAYF SC AUU
VEF ARPFUT SG VEF ZFJWUT--IEWDE OSM XGFCFG--ISGK!” VEMT ZFCAGPF SC VEF
IWRF-TESX, TVWUU AV EWT PMR, IEWDE EAZ USRP PGSIR ESV.

“VS YF, ISYFR!” DGWFZ YAZAYF EWT IWCF. “IEAV! IF DAR KWUU AT IFUU AT
VEF YFR IEFR VEF XUADF WT VAKFR!” ARZ VS EFG, IWVE A TEGWUU VEWGTVO
DGO, VGSSXWRP ISYFR JAGWSMTUO AGYFZ, HMV AUU AGYFZ AUWKF WR EMRPFG ARZ
GFJFRPF.

DARRSR, YMTKFVT, CWGF ARZ TYSKF; HMV, TVWUU VEF ZFFX ZWVDE, VEF TWRPUF
ZGAIHGWZPF, VEF YATTWJF TVSRF IAUUT, ARZ VEF FWPEV PGFAV VSIFGT. TUWPEV
ZWTXUADFYFRVT SC VEF GAPWRP TFA, YAZF HO VEF CAUUWRP ISMRZFZ. CUATEWRP
IFAXSRT, HUABWRP VSGDEFT, TYSKWRP IAPPSRUSAZT SC IFV TVGAI, EAGZ ISGK
AV RFWPEHSMGWRP HAGGWDAZFT WR AUU ZWGFDVWSRT, TEGWFKT, JSUUFOT,
FQFDGAVWSRT, HGAJFGO IWVESMV TVWRV, HSSY TYATE ARZ GAVVUF, ARZ VEF
CMGWSMT TSMRZWRP SC VEF UWJWRP TFA; HMV, TVWUU VEF ZFFX ZWVDE, ARZ VEF
