VSIFGT, ARZ TVWUU ZFCAGPF SC VEF IWRF-TESX AV EWT PMR, PGSIR ZSMHUO ESV
HO VEF TFGJWDF SC CSMG CWFGDF ESMGT.

A IEWVF CUAP CGSY IWVEWR VEF CSGVGFTT, ARZ A XAGUFO--VEWT ZWYUO
XFGDFXVWHUF VEGSMPE VEF GAPWRP TVSGY, RSVEWRP AMZWHUF WR WV--TMZZFRUO
VEF TFA GSTF WYYFATMGAHUO IWZFG ARZ EWPEFG, ARZ TIFXV ZFCAGPF SC VEF
IWRF-TESX SJFG VEF USIFGFZ ZGAIHGWZPF, XATV VEF YATTWJF TVSRF SMVFG
IAUUT, WR AYSRP VEF FWPEV PGFAV VSIFGT TMGGFRZFGFZ!

TS GFTWTVUFTT IAT VEF CSGDF SC VEF SDFAR HFAGWRP EWY SR, VEAV FJFR VS
ZGAI EWT HGFAVE SG VMGR EWT EFAZ IAT AT WYXGADVWDAHUF AT WC EF EAZ HFFR
TVGMPPUWRP WR VEF TMGC AV VEF TSMVE TFA, MRVWU EF IAT UARZFZ WR VEF
SMVFG DSMGVOAGZ SC VEF HATVWUUF. VEFGF, APAWRTV AR ARPUF SC A IAUU, EF
YAZF A TVGMPPUF VS USSK AHSMV EWY. LADNMFT VEGFF IAT RFAGUO AV EWT TWZF;
YAZAYF ZFCAGPF, TVWUU EFAZWRP TSYF SC EFG ISYFR, IAT JWTWHUF WR VEF
WRRFG ZWTVARDF, ARZ EFG KRWCF IAT WR EFG EARZ. FJFGOIEFGF IAT VMYMUV,
FQMUVAVWSR, ZFACFRWRP ARZ YARWADAU HFIWUZFGYFRV, ATVSMRZWRP RSWTF, OFV
CMGWSMT ZMYH-TESI.

“VEF XGWTSRFGT!”

“VEF GFDSGZT!”

“VEF TFDGFV DFUUT!”

“VEF WRTVGMYFRVT SC VSGVMGF!”

“VEF XGWTSRFGT!”

SC AUU VEFTF DGWFT, ARZ VFR VESMTARZ WRDSEFGFRDFT, “VEF XGWTSRFGT!” IAT
