IAUU.

“TESI YF VEF RSGVE VSIFG!” TAWZ ZFCAGPF. “NMWDK!”

“W IWUU CAWVECMUUO,” GFXUWFZ VEF YAR, “WC OSM IWUU DSYF IWVE YF. HMV
VEFGF WT RS SRF VEFGF.”

“IEAV WT VEF YFARWRP SC SRF EMRZGFZ ARZ CWJF, RSGVE VSIFG?” ATKFZ
ZFCAGPF. “NMWDK!”

“VEF YFARWRP, YSRTWFMG?”

“ZSFT WV YFAR A DAXVWJF, SG A XUADF SC DAXVWJWVO? SG ZS OSM YFAR VEAV W
