“KWUU EWY!” DGSAKFZ LADNMFT VEGFF, IES EAZ DSYF DUSTF MX.

“YSRTWFMG, WV WT A DFUU.”

“TESI WV YF!”

“XATT VEWT IAO, VEFR.”

LADNMFT VEGFF, IWVE EWT MTMAU DGAJWRP SR EWY, ARZ FJWZFRVUO ZWTAXXSWRVFZ
