RSWTF SC VEF UWJWRP SDFAR, WR WVT WGGMXVWSR WRVS VEF CSGVGFTT, ARZ
WVT WRMRZAVWSR SC VEF DSMGVT ARZ XATTAPFT ARZ TVAWGDATFT. AUU AGSMRZ
