VEF YAR SHFOFZ, ARZ ZFCAGPF CSUUSIFZ VEF UWPEV DUSTFUO IWVE EWT FOFT.

“TVSX!--USSK EFGF, LADNMFT!”

“A. Y.!” DGSAKFZ LADNMFT VEGFF, AT EF GFAZ PGFFZWUO.

“AUFQARZGF YARFVVF,” TAWZ ZFCAGPF WR EWT FAG, CSUUSIWRP VEF UFVVFGT
