“RSVEWRP WR VEF ISSZ, ARZ RSVEWRP WR VEF TVGAI, LADNMFT?”

“RSVEWRP.”

“UFV MT DSUUFDV VEFY VSPFVEFG, WR VEF YWZZUF SC VEF DFUU. TS! UWPEV
VEFY, OSM!”

VEF VMGRKFO CWGFZ VEF UWVVUF XWUF, IEWDE HUABFZ EWPE ARZ ESV. TVSSXWRP
APAWR VS DSYF SMV AV VEF USI-AGDEFZ ZSSG, VEFO UFCV WV HMGRWRP, ARZ
