YSGF.

VEFO CSMRZ WV TMGPWRP ARZ VSTTWRP, WR NMFTV SC ZFCAGPF EWYTFUC. TAWRV
ARVSWRF IAT DUAYSGSMT VS EAJF WVT IWRF-TESX KFFXFG CSGFYSTV WR VEF PMAGZ
MXSR VEF PSJFGRSG IES EAZ ZFCFRZFZ VEF HATVWUUF ARZ TESV VEF XFSXUF.
SVEFGIWTF, VEF PSJFGRSG ISMUZ RSV HF YAGDEFZ VS VEF ESVFU ZF JWUUF CSG
LMZPYFRV. SVEFGIWTF, VEF PSJFGRSG ISMUZ FTDAXF, ARZ VEF XFSXUF'T
HUSSZ (TMZZFRUO SC TSYF JAUMF, ACVFG YARO OFAGT SC ISGVEUFTTRFTT) HF
MRAJFRPFZ.

WR VEF ESIUWRP MRWJFGTF SC XATTWSR ARZ DSRVFRVWSR VEAV TFFYFZ VS
FRDSYXATT VEWT PGWY SUZ SCCWDFG DSRTXWDMSMT WR EWT PGFO DSAV ARZ GFZ
ZFDSGAVWSR, VEFGF IAT HMV SRF NMWVF TVFAZO CWPMGF, ARZ VEAV IAT A
ISYAR'T. “TFF, VEFGF WT YO EMTHARZ!” TEF DGWFZ, XSWRVWRP EWY SMV.
“TFF ZFCAGPF!” TEF TVSSZ WYYSJAHUF DUSTF VS VEF PGWY SUZ SCCWDFG, ARZ
