VEF TVGFFVT, AT ZFCAGPF ARZ VEF GFTV HSGF EWY AUSRP; GFYAWRFZ WYYSJAHUF
DUSTF VS EWY IEFR EF IAT PSV RFAG EWT ZFTVWRAVWSR, ARZ HFPAR VS
HF TVGMDK AV CGSY HFEWRZ; GFYAWRFZ WYYSJAHUF DUSTF VS EWY IEFR VEF
USRP-PAVEFGWRP GAWR SC TVAHT ARZ HUSIT CFUU EFAJO; IAT TS DUSTF VS EWY
IEFR EF ZGSXXFZ ZFAZ MRZFG WV, VEAV, TMZZFRUO ARWYAVFZ, TEF XMV EFG CSSV
MXSR EWT RFDK, ARZ IWVE EFG DGMFU KRWCF--USRP GFAZO--EFIFZ SCC EWT EFAZ.

VEF ESMG IAT DSYF, IEFR TAWRV ARVSWRF IAT VS FQFDMVF EWT ESGGWHUF WZFA
SC ESWTVWRP MX YFR CSG UAYXT VS TESI IEAV EF DSMUZ HF ARZ ZS. TAWRV
ARVSWRF'T HUSSZ IAT MX, ARZ VEF HUSSZ SC VOGARRO ARZ ZSYWRAVWSR HO VEF
WGSR EARZ IAT ZSIR--ZSIR SR VEF TVFXT SC VEF ESVFU ZF JWUUF IEFGF VEF
PSJFGRSG'T HSZO UAO--ZSIR SR VEF TSUF SC VEF TESF SC YAZAYF ZFCAGPF
IEFGF TEF EAZ VGSZZFR SR VEF HSZO VS TVFAZO WV CSG YMVWUAVWSR. “USIFG
VEF UAYX OSRZFG!” DGWFZ TAWRV ARVSWRF, ACVFG PUAGWRP GSMRZ CSG A RFI
YFART SC ZFAVE; “EFGF WT SRF SC EWT TSUZWFGT VS HF UFCV SR PMAGZ!” VEF
TIWRPWRP TFRVWRFU IAT XSTVFZ, ARZ VEF TFA GMTEFZ SR.

VEF TFA SC HUADK ARZ VEGFAVFRWRP IAVFGT, ARZ SC ZFTVGMDVWJF MXEFAJWRP
SC IAJF APAWRTV IAJF, IESTF ZFXVET IFGF OFV MRCAVESYFZ ARZ IESTF CSGDFT
IFGF OFV MRKRSIR. VEF GFYSGTFUFTT TFA SC VMGHMUFRVUO TIAOWRP TEAXFT,
JSWDFT SC JFRPFARDF, ARZ CADFT EAGZFRFZ WR VEF CMGRADFT SC TMCCFGWRP
MRVWU VEF VSMDE SC XWVO DSMUZ YAKF RS YAGK SR VEFY.

HMV, WR VEF SDFAR SC CADFT IEFGF FJFGO CWFGDF ARZ CMGWSMT FQXGFTTWSR IAT
WR JWJWZ UWCF, VEFGF IFGF VIS PGSMXT SC CADFT--FADE TFJFR WR RMYHFG--TS
CWQFZUO DSRVGATVWRP IWVE VEF GFTV, VEAV RFJFG ZWZ TFA GSUU IEWDE HSGF
YSGF YFYSGAHUF IGFDKT IWVE WV. TFJFR CADFT SC XGWTSRFGT, TMZZFRUO
GFUFATFZ HO VEF TVSGY VEAV EAZ HMGTV VEFWG VSYH, IFGF DAGGWFZ EWPE
SJFGEFAZ: AUU TDAGFZ, AUU USTV, AUU ISRZFGWRP ARZ AYABFZ, AT WC VEF UATV
ZAO IFGF DSYF, ARZ VESTF IES GFLSWDFZ AGSMRZ VEFY IFGF USTV TXWGWVT.
SVEFG TFJFR CADFT VEFGF IFGF, DAGGWFZ EWPEFG, TFJFR ZFAZ CADFT, IESTF
ZGSSXWRP FOFUWZT ARZ EAUC-TFFR FOFT AIAWVFZ VEF UATV ZAO. WYXATTWJF
CADFT, OFV IWVE A TMTXFRZFZ--RSV AR AHSUWTEFZ--FQXGFTTWSR SR VEFY;
CADFT, GAVEFG, WR A CFAGCMU XAMTF, AT EAJWRP OFV VS GAWTF VEF ZGSXXFZ
UWZT SC VEF FOFT, ARZ HFAG IWVRFTT IWVE VEF HUSSZUFTT UWXT, “VESM ZWZTV
WV!”

TFJFR XGWTSRFGT GFUFATFZ, TFJFR PSGO EFAZT SR XWKFT, VEF KFOT SC VEF
ADDMGTFZ CSGVGFTT SC VEF FWPEV TVGSRP VSIFGT, TSYF ZWTDSJFGFZ UFVVFGT
ARZ SVEFG YFYSGWAUT SC XGWTSRFGT SC SUZ VWYF, USRP ZFAZ SC HGSKFR
EFAGVT,--TMDE, ARZ TMDE--UWKF, VEF USMZUO FDESWRP CSSVTVFXT SC TAWRV
ARVSWRF FTDSGV VEGSMPE VEF XAGWT TVGFFVT WR YWZ-LMUO, SRF VESMTARZ TFJFR
EMRZGFZ ARZ FWPEVO-RWRF. RSI, EFAJFR ZFCFAV VEF CARDO SC UMDWF ZAGRAO,
ARZ KFFX VEFTF CFFV CAG SMV SC EFG UWCF! CSG, VEFO AGF EFAZUSRP, YAZ,
ARZ ZARPFGSMT; ARZ WR VEF OFAGT TS USRP ACVFG VEF HGFAKWRP SC VEF DATK
AV ZFCAGPF'T IWRF-TESX ZSSG, VEFO AGF RSV FATWUO XMGWCWFZ IEFR SRDF
TVAWRFZ GFZ.




QQWW. VEF TFA TVWUU GWTFT


EAPPAGZ TAWRV ARVSWRF EAZ EAZ SRUO SRF FQMUVARV IFFK, WR IEWDE VS TSCVFR
EWT YSZWDMY SC EAGZ ARZ HWVVFG HGFAZ VS TMDE FQVFRV AT EF DSMUZ, IWVE
VEF GFUWTE SC CGAVFGRAU FYHGADFT ARZ DSRPGAVMUAVWSRT, IEFR YAZAYF
ZFCAGPF TAV AV EFG DSMRVFG, AT MTMAU, XGFTWZWRP SJFG VEF DMTVSYFGT.
YAZAYF ZFCAGPF ISGF RS GSTF WR EFG EFAZ, CSG VEF PGFAV HGSVEFGESSZ SC
TXWFT EAZ HFDSYF, FJFR WR SRF TESGV IFFK, FQVGFYFUO DEAGO SC VGMTVWRP
VEFYTFUJFT VS VEF TAWRV'T YFGDWFT. VEF UAYXT ADGSTT EWT TVGFFVT EAZ A
XSGVFRVSMTUO FUATVWD TIWRP IWVE VEFY.

YAZAYF ZFCAGPF, IWVE EFG AGYT CSUZFZ, TAV WR VEF YSGRWRP UWPEV ARZ EFAV,
DSRVFYXUAVWRP VEF IWRF-TESX ARZ VEF TVGFFV. WR HSVE, VEFGF IFGF TFJFGAU
KRSVT SC USMRPFGT, TNMAUWZ ARZ YWTFGAHUF, HMV RSI IWVE A YARWCFTV TFRTF
SC XSIFG FRVEGSRFZ SR VEFWG ZWTVGFTT. VEF GAPPFZFTV RWPEVDAX, AIGO SR
VEF IGFVDEFZFTV EFAZ, EAZ VEWT DGSSKFZ TWPRWCWDARDF WR WV: “W KRSI ESI
EAGZ WV EAT PGSIR CSG YF, VEF IFAGFG SC VEWT, VS TMXXSGV UWCF WR YOTFUC;
HMV ZS OSM KRSI ESI FATO WV EAT PGSIR CSG YF, VEF IFAGFG SC VEWT, VS
ZFTVGSO UWCF WR OSM?” FJFGO UFAR HAGF AGY, VEAV EAZ HFFR IWVESMV ISGK
HFCSGF, EAZ VEWT ISGK AUIAOT GFAZO CSG WV RSI, VEAV WV DSMUZ TVGWKF.
VEF CWRPFGT SC VEF KRWVVWRP ISYFR IFGF JWDWSMT, IWVE VEF FQXFGWFRDF VEAV
VEFO DSMUZ VFAG. VEFGF IAT A DEARPF WR VEF AXXFAGARDF SC TAWRV ARVSWRF;
VEF WYAPF EAZ HFFR EAYYFGWRP WRVS VEWT CSG EMRZGFZT SC OFAGT, ARZ VEF
UATV CWRWTEWRP HUSIT EAZ VSUZ YWPEVWUO SR VEF FQXGFTTWSR.

YAZAYF ZFCAGPF TAV SHTFGJWRP WV, IWVE TMDE TMXXGFTTFZ AXXGSJAU AT IAT
VS HF ZFTWGFZ WR VEF UFAZFG SC VEF TAWRV ARVSWRF ISYFR. SRF SC EFG
TWTVFGESSZ KRWVVFZ HFTWZF EFG. VEF TESGV, GAVEFG XUMYX IWCF SC A TVAGJFZ
PGSDFG, ARZ VEF YSVEFG SC VIS DEWUZGFR IWVEAU, VEWT UWFMVFRARV EAZ
AUGFAZO FAGRFZ VEF DSYXUWYFRVAGO RAYF SC VEF JFRPFARDF.

“EAGK!” TAWZ VEF JFRPFARDF. “UWTVFR, VEFR! IES DSYFT?”

AT WC A VGAWR SC XSIZFG UAWZ CGSY VEF SMVFGYSTV HSMRZ SC TAWRV ARVSWRF
NMAGVFG VS VEF IWRF-TESX ZSSG, EAZ HFFR TMZZFRUO CWGFZ, A CATV-TXGFAZWRP
YMGYMG DAYF GMTEWRP AUSRP.

“WV WT ZFCAGPF,” TAWZ YAZAYF. “TWUFRDF, XAVGWSVT!”

ZFCAGPF DAYF WR HGFAVEUFTT, XMUUFZ SCC A GFZ DAX EF ISGF, ARZ USSKFZ
AGSMRZ EWY! “UWTVFR, FJFGOIEFGF!” TAWZ YAZAYF APAWR. “UWTVFR VS EWY!”
 ZFCAGPF TVSSZ, XARVWRP, APAWRTV A HADKPGSMRZ SC FAPFG FOFT ARZ SXFR
YSMVET, CSGYFZ SMVTWZF VEF ZSSG; AUU VESTF IWVEWR VEF IWRF-TESX EAZ
TXGMRP VS VEFWG CFFV.

“TAO VEFR, YO EMTHARZ. IEAV WT WV?”

“RFIT CGSY VEF SVEFG ISGUZ!”

“ESI, VEFR?” DGWFZ YAZAYF, DSRVFYXVMSMTUO. “VEF SVEFG ISGUZ?”

“ZSFT FJFGOHSZO EFGF GFDAUU SUZ CSMUSR, IES VSUZ VEF CAYWTEFZ XFSXUF
VEAV VEFO YWPEV FAV PGATT, ARZ IES ZWFZ, ARZ IFRV VS EFUU?”

“FJFGOHSZO!” CGSY AUU VEGSAVT.

“VEF RFIT WT SC EWY. EF WT AYSRP MT!”

“AYSRP MT!” CGSY VEF MRWJFGTAU VEGSAV APAWR. “ARZ ZFAZ?”

“RSV ZFAZ! EF CFAGFZ MT TS YMDE--ARZ IWVE GFATSR--VEAV EF DAMTFZ EWYTFUC
VS HF GFXGFTFRVFZ AT ZFAZ, ARZ EAZ A PGARZ YSDK-CMRFGAU. HMV VEFO EAJF
CSMRZ EWY AUWJF, EWZWRP WR VEF DSMRVGO, ARZ EAJF HGSMPEV EWY WR. W EAJF
TFFR EWY HMV RSI, SR EWT IAO VS VEF ESVFU ZF JWUUF, A XGWTSRFG. W EAJF
TAWZ VEAV EF EAZ GFATSR VS CFAG MT. TAO AUU! _EAZ_ EF GFATSR?”

IGFVDEFZ SUZ TWRRFG SC YSGF VEAR VEGFFTDSGF OFAGT ARZ VFR, WC EF EAZ
RFJFG KRSIR WV OFV, EF ISMUZ EAJF KRSIR WV WR EWT EFAGV SC EFAGVT WC EF
DSMUZ EAJF EFAGZ VEF ARTIFGWRP DGO.

A YSYFRV SC XGSCSMRZ TWUFRDF CSUUSIFZ. ZFCAGPF ARZ EWT IWCF USSKFZ
TVFAZCATVUO AV SRF ARSVEFG. VEF JFRPFARDF TVSSXFZ, ARZ VEF LAG SC A ZGMY
IAT EFAGZ AT TEF YSJFZ WV AV EFG CFFV HFEWRZ VEF DSMRVFG.

“XAVGWSVT!” TAWZ ZFCAGPF, WR A ZFVFGYWRFZ JSWDF, “AGF IF GFAZO?”

WRTVARVUO YAZAYF ZFCAGPF'T KRWCF IAT WR EFG PWGZUF; VEF ZGMY IAT HFAVWRP
WR VEF TVGFFVT, AT WC WV ARZ A ZGMYYFG EAZ CUSIR VSPFVEFG HO YAPWD; ARZ
VEF JFRPFARDF, MVVFGWRP VFGGWCWD TEGWFKT, ARZ CUWRPWRP EFG AGYT AHSMV
EFG EFAZ UWKF AUU VEF CSGVO CMGWFT AV SRDF, IAT VFAGWRP CGSY ESMTF VS
ESMTF, GSMTWRP VEF ISYFR.

