IWVE IEWDE EF EAZ ZSRF IEAV EF EAZ ZSRF, FJFR AUVESMPE EF EAZ UFCV
WV WRDSYXUFVF, XGFTFRVFZ WV HFCSGF EWY WR AR ATXFDV VEAV ISMUZ HF
PGAVFCMUUO ADKRSIUFZPFZ WR CGARDF SR EWT XGFTFRVWRP EWYTFUC VS ATTFGV
WV. VEFR, VEAV PUSGWSMT JWTWSR SC ZSWRP PSSZ, IEWDE WT TS SCVFR VEF
TARPMWRF YWGAPF SC TS YARO PSSZ YWRZT, AGSTF HFCSGF EWY, ARZ EF FJFR
TAI EWYTFUC WR VEF WUUMTWSR IWVE TSYF WRCUMFRDF VS PMWZF VEWT GAPWRP
GFJSUMVWSR VEAV IAT GMRRWRP TS CFAGCMUUO IWUZ.

AT EF IAUKFZ VS ARZ CGS IWVE EWT GFTSUMVWSR YAZF, EF DSRTWZFGFZ VEAV
RFWVEFG UMDWF RSG EFG CAVEFG YMTV KRSI SC WV MRVWU EF IAT PSRF.
UMDWF TESMUZ HF TXAGFZ VEF XAWR SC TFXAGAVWSR; ARZ EFG CAVEFG, AUIAOT
GFUMDVARV VS VMGR EWT VESMPEVT VSIAGZT VEF ZARPFGSMT PGSMRZ SC SUZ,
TESMUZ DSYF VS VEF KRSIUFZPF SC VEF TVFX, AT A TVFX VAKFR, ARZ RSV WR
VEF HAUARDF SC TMTXFRTF ARZ ZSMHV. ESI YMDE SC VEF WRDSYXUFVFRFTT SC EWT
TWVMAVWSR IAT GFCFGAHUF VS EFG CAVEFG, VEGSMPE VEF XAWRCMU ARQWFVO
VS AJSWZ GFJWJWRP SUZ ATTSDWAVWSRT SC CGARDF WR EWT YWRZ, EF ZWZ RSV
ZWTDMTT IWVE EWYTFUC. HMV, VEAV DWGDMYTVARDF VSS, EAZ EAZ WVT WRCUMFRDF
WR EWT DSMGTF.

EF IAUKFZ VS ARZ CGS, IWVE VESMPEVT JFGO HMTO, MRVWU WV IAT VWYF VS
GFVMGR VS VFUUTSR'T ARZ VAKF UFAJF SC YG. USGGO. AT TSSR AT EF AGGWJFZ
WR XAGWT EF ISMUZ XGFTFRV EWYTFUC VS VEWT SUZ CGWFRZ, HMV EF YMTV TAO
RSVEWRP SC EWT WRVFRVWSR RSI.

A DAGGWAPF IWVE XSTV-ESGTFT IAT GFAZO AV VEF HARK ZSSG, ARZ LFGGO IAT
HSSVFZ ARZ FNMWXXFZ.

“W EAJF ZFUWJFGFZ VEAV UFVVFG,” TAWZ DEAGUFT ZAGRAO VS YG. USGGO. “W
ISMUZ RSV DSRTFRV VS OSMG HFWRP DEAGPFZ IWVE ARO IGWVVFR ARTIFG, HMV
XFGEAXT OSM IWUU VAKF A JFGHAU SRF?”

“VEAV W IWUU, ARZ GFAZWUO,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, “WC WV WT RSV ZARPFGSMT.”

“RSV AV AUU. VESMPE WV WT VS A XGWTSRFG WR VEF AHHAOF.”

“IEAV WT EWT RAYF?” TAWZ YG. USGGO, IWVE EWT SXFR XSDKFV-HSSK WR EWT
EARZ.

“PAHFUUF.”

“PAHFUUF. ARZ IEAV WT VEF YFTTAPF VS VEF MRCSGVMRAVF PAHFUUF WR XGWTSR?”

“TWYXUO, 'VEAV EF EAT GFDFWJFZ VEF UFVVFG, ARZ IWUU DSYF.'”

“ARO VWYF YFRVWSRFZ?”

“EF IWUU TVAGV MXSR EWT LSMGRFO VS-YSGGSI RWPEV.”

“ARO XFGTSR YFRVWSRFZ?”

“RS.”

EF EFUXFZ YG. USGGO VS IGAX EWYTFUC WR A RMYHFG SC DSAVT ARZ DUSAKT,
ARZ IFRV SMV IWVE EWY CGSY VEF IAGY AVYSTXEFGF SC VEF SUZ HARK, WRVS VEF
YWTVO AWG SC CUFFV-TVGFFV. “YO USJF VS UMDWF, ARZ VS UWVVUF UMDWF,” TAWZ
YG. USGGO AV XAGVWRP, “ARZ VAKF XGFDWSMT DAGF SC VEFY VWUU W DSYF HADK.”
 DEAGUFT ZAGRAO TESSK EWT EFAZ ARZ ZSMHVCMUUO TYWUFZ, AT VEF DAGGWAPF
GSUUFZ AIAO.

VEAV RWPEV--WV IAT VEF CSMGVFFRVE SC AMPMTV--EF TAV MX UAVF, ARZ IGSVF
VIS CFGJFRV UFVVFGT; SRF IAT VS UMDWF, FQXUAWRWRP VEF TVGSRP SHUWPAVWSR
EF IAT MRZFG VS PS VS XAGWT, ARZ TESIWRP EFG, AV UFRPVE, VEF GFATSRT
VEAV EF EAZ, CSG CFFUWRP DSRCWZFRV VEAV EF DSMUZ HFDSYF WRJSUJFZ WR RS
XFGTSRAU ZARPFG VEFGF; VEF SVEFG IAT VS VEF ZSDVSG, DSRCWZWRP UMDWF ARZ
VEFWG ZFAG DEWUZ VS EWT DAGF, ARZ ZIFUUWRP SR VEF TAYF VSXWDT IWVE VEF
TVGSRPFTV ATTMGARDFT. VS HSVE, EF IGSVF VEAV EF ISMUZ ZFTXAVDE UFVVFGT
WR XGSSC SC EWT TACFVO, WYYFZWAVFUO ACVFG EWT AGGWJAU.

WV IAT A EAGZ ZAO, VEAV ZAO SC HFWRP AYSRP VEFY, IWVE VEF CWGTV
GFTFGJAVWSR SC VEFWG LSWRV UWJFT SR EWT YWRZ. WV IAT A EAGZ YAVVFG VS
XGFTFGJF VEF WRRSDFRV ZFDFWV SC IEWDE VEFO IFGF XGSCSMRZUO MRTMTXWDWSMT.
HMV, AR ACCFDVWSRAVF PUARDF AV EWT IWCF, TS EAXXO ARZ HMTO, YAZF EWY
GFTSUMVF RSV VS VFUU EFG IEAV WYXFRZFZ (EF EAZ HFFR EAUC YSJFZ VS ZS WV,
TS TVGARPF WV IAT VS EWY VS ADV WR AROVEWRP IWVESMV EFG NMWFV AWZ), ARZ
VEF ZAO XATTFZ NMWDKUO. FAGUO WR VEF FJFRWRP EF FYHGADFZ EFG, ARZ EFG
TDAGDFUO UFTT ZFAG RAYFTAKF, XGFVFRZWRP VEAV EF ISMUZ GFVMGR HO-ARZ-HOF
(AR WYAPWRAGO FRPAPFYFRV VSSK EWY SMV, ARZ EF EAZ TFDGFVFZ A JAUWTF
SC DUSVEFT GFAZO), ARZ TS EF FYFGPFZ WRVS VEF EFAJO YWTV SC VEF EFAJO
TVGFFVT, IWVE A EFAJWFG EFAGV.

VEF MRTFFR CSGDF IAT ZGAIWRP EWY CATV VS WVTFUC, RSI, ARZ AUU VEF VWZFT
ARZ IWRZT IFGF TFVVWRP TVGAWPEV ARZ TVGSRP VSIAGZT WV. EF UFCV EWT
VIS UFVVFGT IWVE A VGMTVO XSGVFG, VS HF ZFUWJFGFZ EAUC AR ESMG HFCSGF
YWZRWPEV, ARZ RS TSSRFG; VSSK ESGTF CSG ZSJFG; ARZ HFPAR EWT LSMGRFO.
“CSG VEF USJF SC EFAJFR, SC LMTVWDF, SC PFRFGSTWVO, SC VEF ESRSMG SC
OSMG RSHUF RAYF!” IAT VEF XSSG XGWTSRFG'T DGO IWVE IEWDE EF TVGFRPVEFRFZ
EWT TWRKWRP EFAGV, AT EF UFCV AUU VEAV IAT ZFAG SR FAGVE HFEWRZ EWY, ARZ
CUSAVFZ AIAO CSG VEF USAZTVSRF GSDK.


VEF FRZ SC VEF TFDSRZ HSSK.





HSSK VEF VEWGZ--VEF VGADK SC A TVSGY




W. WR TFDGFV


VEF VGAJFUUFG CAGFZ TUSIUO SR EWT IAO, IES CAGFZ VSIAGZT XAGWT CGSY
FRPUARZ WR VEF AMVMYR SC VEF OFAG SRF VESMTARZ TFJFR EMRZGFZ ARZ
RWRFVO-VIS. YSGF VEAR FRSMPE SC HAZ GSAZT, HAZ FNMWXAPFT, ARZ HAZ
ESGTFT, EF ISMUZ EAJF FRDSMRVFGFZ VS ZFUAO EWY, VESMPE VEF CAUUFR ARZ
MRCSGVMRAVF KWRP SC CGARDF EAZ HFFR MXSR EWT VEGSRF WR AUU EWT PUSGO;
HMV, VEF DEARPFZ VWYFT IFGF CGAMPEV IWVE SVEFG SHTVADUFT VEAR
VEFTF. FJFGO VSIR-PAVF ARZ JWUUAPF VAQWRP-ESMTF EAZ WVT HARZ SC
DWVWBFR-XAVGWSVT, IWVE VEFWG RAVWSRAU YMTKFVT WR A YSTV FQXUSTWJF TVAVF
SC GFAZWRFTT, IES TVSXXFZ AUU DSYFGT ARZ PSFGT, DGSTT-NMFTVWSRFZ VEFY,
WRTXFDVFZ VEFWG XAXFGT, USSKFZ CSG VEFWG RAYFT WR UWTVT SC VEFWG SIR,
VMGRFZ VEFY HADK, SG TFRV VEFY SR, SG TVSXXFZ VEFY ARZ UAWZ VEFY WR
ESUZ, AT VEFWG DAXGWDWSMT LMZPYFRV SG CARDO ZFFYFZ HFTV CSG VEF ZAIRWRP
GFXMHUWD SRF ARZ WRZWJWTWHUF, SC UWHFGVO, FNMAUWVO, CGAVFGRWVO, SG
ZFAVE.

A JFGO CFI CGFRDE UFAPMFT SC EWT LSMGRFO IFGF ADDSYXUWTEFZ, IEFR DEAGUFT
ZAGRAO HFPAR VS XFGDFWJF VEAV CSG EWY AUSRP VEFTF DSMRVGO GSAZT VEFGF
IAT RS ESXF SC GFVMGR MRVWU EF TESMUZ EAJF HFFR ZFDUAGFZ A PSSZ DWVWBFR
AV XAGWT. IEAVFJFG YWPEV HFCAUU RSI, EF YMTV SR VS EWT LSMGRFO'T FRZ.
RSV A YFAR JWUUAPF DUSTFZ MXSR EWY, RSV A DSYYSR HAGGWFG ZGSXXFZ ADGSTT
VEF GSAZ HFEWRZ EWY, HMV EF KRFI WV VS HF ARSVEFG WGSR ZSSG WR
VEF TFGWFT VEAV IAT HAGGFZ HFVIFFR EWY ARZ FRPUARZ. VEF MRWJFGTAU
IAVDECMURFTT TS FRDSYXATTFZ EWY, VEAV WC EF EAZ HFFR VAKFR WR A RFV,
SG IFGF HFWRP CSGIAGZFZ VS EWT ZFTVWRAVWSR WR A DAPF, EF DSMUZ RSV EAJF
CFUV EWT CGFFZSY YSGF DSYXUFVFUO PSRF.

VEWT MRWJFGTAU IAVDECMURFTT RSV SRUO TVSXXFZ EWY SR VEF EWPEIAO VIFRVO
VWYFT WR A TVAPF, HMV GFVAGZFZ EWT XGSPGFTT VIFRVO VWYFT WR A ZAO, HO
GWZWRP ACVFG EWY ARZ VAKWRP EWY HADK, GWZWRP HFCSGF EWY ARZ TVSXXWRP EWY
HO ARVWDWXAVWSR, GWZWRP IWVE EWY ARZ KFFXWRP EWY WR DEAGPF. EF EAZ HFFR
ZAOT MXSR EWT LSMGRFO WR CGARDF AUSRF, IEFR EF IFRV VS HFZ VWGFZ SMV, WR
A UWVVUF VSIR SR VEF EWPE GSAZ, TVWUU A USRP IAO CGSY XAGWT.

RSVEWRP HMV VEF XGSZMDVWSR SC VEF ACCUWDVFZ PAHFUUF'T UFVVFG CGSY EWT
XGWTSR SC VEF AHHAOF ISMUZ EAJF PSV EWY SR TS CAG. EWT ZWCCWDMUVO AV VEF
PMAGZ-ESMTF WR VEWT TYAUU XUADF EAZ HFFR TMDE, VEAV EF CFUV EWT LSMGRFO
VS EAJF DSYF VS A DGWTWT. ARZ EF IAT, VEFGFCSGF, AT UWVVUF TMGXGWTFZ AT
A YAR DSMUZ HF, VS CWRZ EWYTFUC AIAKFRFZ AV VEF TYAUU WRR VS IEWDE EF
EAZ HFFR GFYWVVFZ MRVWU YSGRWRP, WR VEF YWZZUF SC VEF RWPEV.

AIAKFRFZ HO A VWYWZ USDAU CMRDVWSRAGO ARZ VEGFF AGYFZ XAVGWSVT WR GSMPE
GFZ DAXT ARZ IWVE XWXFT WR VEFWG YSMVET, IES TAV ZSIR SR VEF HFZ.

“FYWPGARV,” TAWZ VEF CMRDVWSRAGO, “W AY PSWRP VS TFRZ OSM SR VS XAGWT,
MRZFG AR FTDSGV.”

“DWVWBFR, W ZFTWGF RSVEWRP YSGF VEAR VS PFV VS XAGWT, VESMPE W DSMUZ
ZWTXFRTF IWVE VEF FTDSGV.”

“TWUFRDF!” PGSIUFZ A GFZ-DAX, TVGWKWRP AV VEF DSJFGUFV IWVE VEF HMVV-FRZ
SC EWT YMTKFV. “XFADF, AGWTVSDGAV!”

“WV WT AT VEF PSSZ XAVGWSV TAOT,” SHTFGJFZ VEF VWYWZ CMRDVWSRAGO. “OSM
AGF AR AGWTVSDGAV, ARZ YMTV EAJF AR FTDSGV--ARZ YMTV XAO CSG WV.”

“W EAJF RS DESWDF,” TAWZ DEAGUFT ZAGRAO.

“DESWDF! UWTVFR VS EWY!” DGWFZ VEF TAYF TDSIUWRP GFZ-DAX. “AT WC WV IAT
RSV A CAJSMG VS HF XGSVFDVFZ CGSY VEF UAYX-WGSR!”

“WV WT AUIAOT AT VEF PSSZ XAVGWSV TAOT,” SHTFGJFZ VEF CMRDVWSRAGO. “GWTF
ARZ ZGFTT OSMGTFUC, FYWPGARV.”

ZAGRAO DSYXUWFZ, ARZ IAT VAKFR HADK VS VEF PMAGZ-ESMTF, IEFGF SVEFG
XAVGWSVT WR GSMPE GFZ DAXT IFGF TYSKWRP, ZGWRKWRP, ARZ TUFFXWRP, HO
A IAVDE-CWGF. EFGF EF XAWZ A EFAJO XGWDF CSG EWT FTDSGV, ARZ EFRDF EF
TVAGVFZ IWVE WV SR VEF IFV, IFV GSAZT AV VEGFF S'DUSDK WR VEF YSGRWRP.

VEF FTDSGV IFGF VIS YSMRVFZ XAVGWSVT WR GFZ DAXT ARZ VGW-DSUSMGFZ
DSDKAZFT, AGYFZ IWVE RAVWSRAU YMTKFVT ARZ TAHGFT, IES GSZF SRF SR FWVEFG
TWZF SC EWY.

VEF FTDSGVFZ PSJFGRFZ EWT SIR ESGTF, HMV A USSTF UWRF IAT AVVADEFZ VS
EWT HGWZUF, VEF FRZ SC IEWDE SRF SC VEF XAVGWSVT KFXV PWGZFZ GSMRZ EWT
IGWTV. WR VEWT TVAVF VEFO TFV CSGVE IWVE VEF TEAGX GAWR ZGWJWRP WR VEFWG
CADFT: DUAVVFGWRP AV A EFAJO ZGAPSSR VGSV SJFG VEF MRFJFR VSIR XAJFYFRV,
ARZ SMV MXSR VEF YWGF-ZFFX GSAZT. WR VEWT TVAVF VEFO VGAJFGTFZ IWVESMV
DEARPF, FQDFXV SC ESGTFT ARZ XADF, AUU VEF YWGF-ZFFX UFAPMFT VEAV UAO
HFVIFFR VEFY ARZ VEF DAXWVAU.

VEFO VGAJFUUFZ WR VEF RWPEV, EAUVWRP AR ESMG SG VIS ACVFG ZAOHGFAK, ARZ
UOWRP HO MRVWU VEF VIWUWPEV CFUU. VEF FTDSGV IFGF TS IGFVDEFZUO DUSVEFZ,
VEAV VEFO VIWTVFZ TVGAI GSMRZ VEFWG HAGF UFPT, ARZ VEAVDEFZ VEFWG GAPPFZ
TESMUZFGT VS KFFX VEF IFV SCC. AXAGV CGSY VEF XFGTSRAU ZWTDSYCSGV SC
HFWRP TS AVVFRZFZ, ARZ AXAGV CGSY TMDE DSRTWZFGAVWSRT SC XGFTFRV ZARPFG
AT AGSTF CGSY SRF SC VEF XAVGWSVT HFWRP DEGSRWDAUUO ZGMRK, ARZ DAGGOWRP
EWT YMTKFV JFGO GFDKUFTTUO, DEAGUFT ZAGRAO ZWZ RSV AUUSI VEF GFTVGAWRV
VEAV IAT UAWZ MXSR EWY VS AIAKFR ARO TFGWSMT CFAGT WR EWT HGFATV; CSG,
EF GFATSRFZ IWVE EWYTFUC VEAV WV DSMUZ EAJF RS GFCFGFRDF VS VEF YFGWVT
SC AR WRZWJWZMAU DATF VEAV IAT RSV OFV TVAVFZ, ARZ SC GFXGFTFRVAVWSRT,
DSRCWGYAHUF HO VEF XGWTSRFG WR VEF AHHAOF, VEAV IFGF RSV OFV YAZF.

HMV IEFR VEFO DAYF VS VEF VSIR SC HFAMJAWT--IEWDE VEFO ZWZ AV FJFRVWZF,
IEFR VEF TVGFFVT IFGF CWUUFZ IWVE XFSXUF--EF DSMUZ RSV DSRDFAU CGSY
EWYTFUC VEAV VEF ATXFDV SC ACCAWGT IAT JFGO AUAGYWRP. AR SYWRSMT DGSIZ
PAVEFGFZ VS TFF EWY ZWTYSMRV SC VEF XSTVWRP-OAGZ, ARZ YARO JSWDFT DAUUFZ
SMV USMZUO, “ZSIR IWVE VEF FYWPGARV!”

EF TVSXXFZ WR VEF ADV SC TIWRPWRP EWYTFUC SMV SC EWT TAZZUF, ARZ,
GFTMYWRP WV AT EWT TACFTV XUADF, TAWZ:

“FYWPGARV, YO CGWFRZT! ZS OSM RSV TFF YF EFGF, WR CGARDF, SC YO SIR
IWUU?”

“OSM AGF A DMGTFZ FYWPGARV,” DGWFZ A CAGGWFG, YAKWRP AV EWY WR A
CMGWSMT YARRFG VEGSMPE VEF XGFTT, EAYYFG WR EARZ; “ARZ OSM AGF A DMGTFZ
AGWTVSDGAV!”

VEF XSTVYATVFG WRVFGXSTFZ EWYTFUC HFVIFFR VEWT YAR ARZ VEF GWZFG'T
HGWZUF (AV IEWDE EF IAT FJWZFRVUO YAKWRP), ARZ TSSVEWRPUO TAWZ, “UFV EWY
HF; UFV EWY HF! EF IWUU HF LMZPFZ AV XAGWT.”

“LMZPFZ!” GFXFAVFZ VEF CAGGWFG, TIWRPWRP EWT EAYYFG. “AO! ARZ DSRZFYRFZ
AT A VGAWVSG.” AV VEWT VEF DGSIZ GSAGFZ AXXGSJAU.

DEFDKWRP VEF XSTVYATVFG, IES IAT CSG VMGRWRP EWT ESGTF'T EFAZ VS VEF
OAGZ (VEF ZGMRKFR XAVGWSV TAV DSYXSTFZUO WR EWT TAZZUF USSKWRP SR, IWVE
VEF UWRF GSMRZ EWT IGWTV), ZAGRAO TAWZ, AT TSSR AT EF DSMUZ YAKF EWT
JSWDF EFAGZ:

“CGWFRZT, OSM ZFDFWJF OSMGTFUJFT, SG OSM AGF ZFDFWJFZ. W AY RSV A
VGAWVSG.”

“EF UWFT!” DGWFZ VEF TYWVE. “EF WT A VGAWVSG TWRDF VEF ZFDGFF. EWT UWCF
WT CSGCFWV VS VEF XFSXUF. EWT DMGTFZ UWCF WT RSV EWT SIR!”

AV VEF WRTVARV IEFR ZAGRAO TAI A GMTE WR VEF FOFT SC VEF DGSIZ, IEWDE
ARSVEFG WRTVARV ISMUZ EAJF HGSMPEV MXSR EWY, VEF XSTVYATVFG VMGRFZ EWT
ESGTF WRVS VEF OAGZ, VEF FTDSGV GSZF WR DUSTF MXSR EWT ESGTF'T CUARKT,
ARZ VEF XSTVYATVFG TEMV ARZ HAGGFZ VEF DGABO ZSMHUF PAVFT. VEF CAGGWFG
TVGMDK A HUSI MXSR VEFY IWVE EWT EAYYFG, ARZ VEF DGSIZ PGSARFZ; HMV, RS
YSGF IAT ZSRF.

“IEAV WT VEWT ZFDGFF VEAV VEF TYWVE TXSKF SC?” ZAGRAO ATKFZ VEF
XSTVYATVFG, IEFR EF EAZ VEARKFZ EWY, ARZ TVSSZ HFTWZF EWY WR VEF OAGZ.

“VGMUO, A ZFDGFF CSG TFUUWRP VEF XGSXFGVO SC FYWPGARVT.”

“IEFR XATTFZ?”

“SR VEF CSMGVFFRVE.”

“VEF ZAO W UFCV FRPUARZ!”

“FJFGOHSZO TAOT WV WT HMV SRF SC TFJFGAU, ARZ VEAV VEFGF IWUU HF
SVEFGT--WC VEFGF AGF RSV AUGFAZO--HARWTEWRP AUU FYWPGARVT, ARZ
DSRZFYRWRP AUU VS ZFAVE IES GFVMGR. VEAV WT IEAV EF YFARV IEFR EF TAWZ
OSMG UWCF IAT RSV OSMG SIR.”

“HMV VEFGF AGF RS TMDE ZFDGFFT OFV?”

“IEAV ZS W KRSI!” TAWZ VEF XSTVYATVFG, TEGMPPWRP EWT TESMUZFGT; “VEFGF
YAO HF, SG VEFGF IWUU HF. WV WT AUU VEF TAYF. IEAV ISMUZ OSM EAJF?”

VEFO GFTVFZ SR TSYF TVGAI WR A USCV MRVWU VEF YWZZUF SC VEF RWPEV, ARZ
VEFR GSZF CSGIAGZ APAWR IEFR AUU VEF VSIR IAT ATUFFX. AYSRP VEF YARO
IWUZ DEARPFT SHTFGJAHUF SR CAYWUWAG VEWRPT IEWDE YAZF VEWT IWUZ GWZF
MRGFAU, RSV VEF UFATV IAT VEF TFFYWRP GAGWVO SC TUFFX. ACVFG USRP ARZ
USRFUO TXMGGWRP SJFG ZGFAGO GSAZT, VEFO ISMUZ DSYF VS A DUMTVFG SC XSSG
DSVVAPFT, RSV TVFFXFZ WR ZAGKRFTT, HMV AUU PUWVVFGWRP IWVE UWPEVT, ARZ
ISMUZ CWRZ VEF XFSXUF, WR A PESTVUO YARRFG WR VEF ZFAZ SC VEF RWPEV,
DWGDUWRP EARZ WR EARZ GSMRZ A TEGWJFUUFZ VGFF SC UWHFGVO, SG AUU ZGAIR
MX VSPFVEFG TWRPWRP A UWHFGVO TSRP. EAXXWUO, ESIFJFG, VEFGF IAT TUFFX WR
HFAMJAWT VEAV RWPEV VS EFUX VEFY SMV SC WV ARZ VEFO XATTFZ SR SRDF YSGF
WRVS TSUWVMZF ARZ USRFUWRFTT: LWRPUWRP VEGSMPE VEF MRVWYFUO DSUZ ARZ
IFV, AYSRP WYXSJFGWTEFZ CWFUZT VEAV EAZ OWFUZFZ RS CGMWVT SC VEF FAGVE
VEAV OFAG, ZWJFGTWCWFZ HO VEF HUADKFRFZ GFYAWRT SC HMGRV ESMTFT, ARZ HO
VEF TMZZFR FYFGPFRDF CGSY AYHMTDAZF, ARZ TEAGX GFWRWRP MX ADGSTT VEFWG
IAO, SC XAVGWSV XAVGSUT SR VEF IAVDE SR AUU VEF GSAZT.

ZAOUWPEV AV UATV CSMRZ VEFY HFCSGF VEF IAUU SC XAGWT. VEF HAGGWFG IAT
DUSTFZ ARZ TVGSRPUO PMAGZFZ IEFR VEFO GSZF MX VS WV.

“IEFGF AGF VEF XAXFGT SC VEWT XGWTSRFG?” ZFYARZFZ A GFTSUMVF-USSKWRP YAR
WR AMVESGWVO, IES IAT TMYYSRFZ SMV HO VEF PMAGZ.

RAVMGAUUO TVGMDK HO VEF ZWTAPGFFAHUF ISGZ, DEAGUFT ZAGRAO GFNMFTVFZ VEF
TXFAKFG VS VAKF RSVWDF VEAV EF IAT A CGFF VGAJFUUFG ARZ CGFRDE DWVWBFR,
WR DEAGPF SC AR FTDSGV IEWDE VEF ZWTVMGHFZ TVAVF SC VEF DSMRVGO EAZ
WYXSTFZ MXSR EWY, ARZ IEWDE EF EAZ XAWZ CSG.

“IEFGF,” GFXFAVFZ VEF TAYF XFGTSRAPF, IWVESMV VAKWRP ARO EFFZ SC EWY
IEAVFJFG, “AGF VEF XAXFGT SC VEWT XGWTSRFG?”

VEF ZGMRKFR XAVGWSV EAZ VEFY WR EWT DAX, ARZ XGSZMDFZ VEFY. DATVWRP EWT
FOFT SJFG PAHFUUF'T UFVVFG, VEF TAYF XFGTSRAPF WR AMVESGWVO TESIFZ TSYF
ZWTSGZFG ARZ TMGXGWTF, ARZ USSKFZ AV ZAGRAO IWVE A DUSTF AVVFRVWSR.

EF UFCV FTDSGV ARZ FTDSGVFZ IWVESMV TAOWRP A ISGZ, ESIFJFG, ARZ IFRV
WRVS VEF PMAGZ-GSSY; YFARIEWUF, VEFO TAV MXSR VEFWG ESGTFT SMVTWZF VEF
PAVF. USSKWRP AHSMV EWY IEWUF WR VEWT TVAVF SC TMTXFRTF, DEAGUFT
ZAGRAO SHTFGJFZ VEAV VEF PAVF IAT EFUZ HO A YWQFZ PMAGZ SC TSUZWFGT ARZ
XAVGWSVT, VEF UAVVFG CAG SMVRMYHFGWRP VEF CSGYFG; ARZ VEAV IEWUF WRPGFTT
WRVS VEF DWVO CSG XFATARVT' DAGVT HGWRPWRP WR TMXXUWFT, ARZ CSG TWYWUAG
VGACCWD ARZ VGACCWDKFGT, IAT FATO FRSMPE, FPGFTT, FJFR CSG VEF ESYFUWFTV
XFSXUF, IAT JFGO ZWCCWDMUV. A RMYFGSMT YFZUFO SC YFR ARZ ISYFR, RSV
VS YFRVWSR HFATVT ARZ JFEWDUFT SC JAGWSMT TSGVT, IAT IAWVWRP VS WTTMF
CSGVE; HMV, VEF XGFJWSMT WZFRVWCWDAVWSR IAT TS TVGWDV, VEAV VEFO
CWUVFGFZ VEGSMPE VEF HAGGWFG JFGO TUSIUO. TSYF SC VEFTF XFSXUF KRFI
VEFWG VMGR CSG FQAYWRAVWSR VS HF TS CAG SCC, VEAV VEFO UAO ZSIR SR VEF
PGSMRZ VS TUFFX SG TYSKF, IEWUF SVEFGT VAUKFZ VSPFVEFG, SG USWVFGFZ
AHSMV. VEF GFZ DAX ARZ VGW-DSUSMG DSDKAZF IFGF MRWJFGTAU, HSVE AYSRP YFR
ARZ ISYFR.

IEFR EF EAZ TAV WR EWT TAZZUF TSYF EAUC-ESMG, VAKWRP RSVF SC VEFTF
VEWRPT, ZAGRAO CSMRZ EWYTFUC DSRCGSRVFZ HO VEF TAYF YAR WR AMVESGWVO,
IES ZWGFDVFZ VEF PMAGZ VS SXFR VEF HAGGWFG. VEFR EF ZFUWJFGFZ VS VEF
FTDSGV, ZGMRK ARZ TSHFG, A GFDFWXV CSG VEF FTDSGVFZ, ARZ GFNMFTVFZ EWY
VS ZWTYSMRV. EF ZWZ TS, ARZ VEF VIS XAVGWSVT, UFAZWRP EWT VWGFZ ESGTF,
VMGRFZ ARZ GSZF AIAO IWVESMV FRVFGWRP VEF DWVO.

EF ADDSYXARWFZ EWT DSRZMDVSG WRVS A PMAGZ-GSSY, TYFUUWRP SC DSYYSR IWRF
ARZ VSHADDS, IEFGF DFGVAWR TSUZWFGT ARZ XAVGWSVT, ATUFFX ARZ AIAKF,
ZGMRK ARZ TSHFG, ARZ WR JAGWSMT RFMVGAU TVAVFT HFVIFFR TUFFXWRP ARZ
IAKWRP, ZGMRKFRRFTT ARZ TSHGWFVO, IFGF TVARZWRP ARZ UOWRP AHSMV. VEF
UWPEV WR VEF PMAGZ-ESMTF, EAUC ZFGWJFZ CGSY VEF IARWRP SWU-UAYXT SC
VEF RWPEV, ARZ EAUC CGSY VEF SJFGDATV ZAO, IAT WR A DSGGFTXSRZWRPUO
MRDFGVAWR DSRZWVWSR. TSYF GFPWTVFGT IFGF UOWRP SXFR SR A ZFTK, ARZ AR
SCCWDFG SC A DSAGTF, ZAGK ATXFDV, XGFTWZFZ SJFG VEFTF.

“DWVWBFR ZFCAGPF,” TAWZ EF VS ZAGRAO'T DSRZMDVSG, AT EF VSSK A TUWX SC
XAXFG VS IGWVF SR. “WT VEWT VEF FYWPGARV FJGFYSRZF?”

“VEWT WT VEF YAR.”

“OSMG APF, FJGFYSRZF?”

“VEWGVO-TFJFR.”

“YAGGWFZ, FJGFYSRZF?”

“OFT.”

“IEFGF YAGGWFZ?”

“WR FRPUARZ.”

“IWVESMV ZSMHV. IEFGF WT OSMG IWCF, FJGFYSRZF?”

“WR FRPUARZ.”

“IWVESMV ZSMHV. OSM AGF DSRTWPRFZ, FJGFYSRZF, VS VEF XGWTSR SC UA
CSGDF.”

“LMTV EFAJFR!” FQDUAWYFZ ZAGRAO. “MRZFG IEAV UAI, ARZ CSG IEAV SCCFRDF?”

VEF SCCWDFG USSKFZ MX CGSY EWT TUWX SC XAXFG CSG A YSYFRV.

“IF EAJF RFI UAIT, FJGFYSRZF, ARZ RFI SCCFRDFT, TWRDF OSM IFGF EFGF.” EF
TAWZ WV IWVE A EAGZ TYWUF, ARZ IFRV SR IGWVWRP.

“W FRVGFAV OSM VS SHTFGJF VEAV W EAJF DSYF EFGF JSUMRVAGWUO, WR GFTXSRTF
VS VEAV IGWVVFR AXXFAU SC A CFUUSI-DSMRVGOYAR IEWDE UWFT HFCSGF OSM. W
ZFYARZ RS YSGF VEAR VEF SXXSGVMRWVO VS ZS TS IWVESMV ZFUAO. WT RSV VEAV
YO GWPEV?”

“FYWPGARVT EAJF RS GWPEVT, FJGFYSRZF,” IAT VEF TVSUWZ GFXUO. VEF SCCWDFG
IGSVF MRVWU EF EAZ CWRWTEFZ, GFAZ SJFG VS EWYTFUC IEAV EF EAZ IGWVVFR,
TARZFZ WV, ARZ EARZFZ WV VS ZFCAGPF, IWVE VEF ISGZT “WR TFDGFV.”

ZFCAGPF YSVWSRFZ IWVE VEF XAXFG VS VEF XGWTSRFG VEAV EF YMTV ADDSYXARO
EWY. VEF XGWTSRFG SHFOFZ, ARZ A PMAGZ SC VIS AGYFZ XAVGWSVT AVVFRZFZ
VEFY.

“WT WV OSM,” TAWZ ZFCAGPF, WR A USI JSWDF, AT VEFO IFRV ZSIR VEF
PMAGZESMTF TVFXT ARZ VMGRFZ WRVS XAGWT, “IES YAGGWFZ VEF ZAMPEVFG SC
ZSDVSG YARFVVF, SRDF A XGWTSRFG WR VEF HATVWUUF VEAV WT RS YSGF?”

“OFT,” GFXUWFZ ZAGRAO, USSKWRP AV EWY IWVE TMGXGWTF.

“YO RAYF WT ZFCAGPF, ARZ W KFFX A IWRF-TESX WR VEF NMAGVFG TAWRV
ARVSWRF. XSTTWHUO OSM EAJF EFAGZ SC YF.”

“YO IWCF DAYF VS OSMG ESMTF VS GFDUAWY EFG CAVEFG? OFT!”

VEF ISGZ “IWCF” TFFYFZ VS TFGJF AT A PUSSYO GFYWRZFG VS ZFCAGPF, VS TAO
IWVE TMZZFR WYXAVWFRDF, “WR VEF RAYF SC VEAV TEAGX CFYAUF RFIUO-HSGR,
ARZ DAUUFZ UA PMWUUSVWRF, IEO ZWZ OSM DSYF VS CGARDF?”

“OSM EFAGZ YF TAO IEO, A YWRMVF APS. ZS OSM RSV HFUWFJF WV WT VEF
VGMVE?”

“A HAZ VGMVE CSG OSM,” TAWZ ZFCAGPF, TXFAKWRP IWVE KRWVVFZ HGSIT, ARZ
USSKWRP TVGAWPEV HFCSGF EWY.

“WRZFFZ W AY USTV EFGF. AUU EFGF WT TS MRXGFDFZFRVFZ, TS DEARPFZ, TS
TMZZFR ARZ MRCAWG, VEAV W AY AHTSUMVFUO USTV. IWUU OSM GFRZFG YF A
UWVVUF EFUX?”

“RSRF.” ZFCAGPF TXSKF, AUIAOT USSKWRP TVGAWPEV HFCSGF EWY.

“IWUU OSM ARTIFG YF A TWRPUF NMFTVWSR?”

“XFGEAXT. ADDSGZWRP VS WVT RAVMGF. OSM DAR TAO IEAV WV WT.”

“WR VEWT XGWTSR VEAV W AY PSWRP VS TS MRLMTVUO, TEAUU W EAJF TSYF CGFF
DSYYMRWDAVWSR IWVE VEF ISGUZ SMVTWZF?”

“OSM IWUU TFF.”

“W AY RSV VS HF HMGWFZ VEFGF, XGFLMZPFZ, ARZ IWVESMV ARO YFART SC
XGFTFRVWRP YO DATF?”

“OSM IWUU TFF. HMV, IEAV VEFR? SVEFG XFSXUF EAJF HFFR TWYWUAGUO HMGWFZ
WR ISGTF XGWTSRT, HFCSGF RSI.”

“HMV RFJFG HO YF, DWVWBFR ZFCAGPF.”

ZFCAGPF PUARDFZ ZAGKUO AV EWY CSG ARTIFG, ARZ IAUKFZ SR WR A TVFAZO
ARZ TFV TWUFRDF. VEF ZFFXFG EF TARK WRVS VEWT TWUFRDF, VEF CAWRVFG ESXF
VEFGF IAT--SG TS ZAGRAO VESMPEV--SC EWT TSCVFRWRP WR ARO TUWPEV ZFPGFF.
EF, VEFGFCSGF, YAZF EATVF VS TAO:

“WV WT SC VEF MVYSTV WYXSGVARDF VS YF (OSM KRSI, DWVWBFR, FJFR HFVVFG
VEAR W, SC ESI YMDE WYXSGVARDF), VEAV W TESMUZ HF AHUF VS DSYYMRWDAVF VS
YG. USGGO SC VFUUTSR'T HARK, AR FRPUWTE PFRVUFYAR IES WT RSI WR XAGWT,
VEF TWYXUF CADV, IWVESMV DSYYFRV, VEAV W EAJF HFFR VEGSIR WRVS VEF
XGWTSR SC UA CSGDF. IWUU OSM DAMTF VEAV VS HF ZSRF CSG YF?”

“W IWUU ZS,” ZFCAGPF ZSPPFZUO GFLSWRFZ, “RSVEWRP CSG OSM. YO ZMVO WT VS
YO DSMRVGO ARZ VEF XFSXUF. W AY VEF TISGR TFGJARV SC HSVE, APAWRTV OSM.
W IWUU ZS RSVEWRP CSG OSM.”

DEAGUFT ZAGRAO CFUV WV ESXFUFTT VS FRVGFAV EWY CMGVEFG, ARZ EWT XGWZF
IAT VSMDEFZ HFTWZFT. AT VEFO IAUKFZ SR WR TWUFRDF, EF DSMUZ RSV HMV TFF
ESI MTFZ VEF XFSXUF IFGF VS VEF TXFDVADUF SC XGWTSRFGT XATTWRP AUSRP VEF
TVGFFVT. VEF JFGO DEWUZGFR TDAGDFUO RSVWDFZ EWY. A CFI XATTFGT VMGRFZ
VEFWG EFAZT, ARZ A CFI TESSK VEFWG CWRPFGT AV EWY AT AR AGWTVSDGAV;
SVEFGIWTF, VEAV A YAR WR PSSZ DUSVEFT TESMUZ HF PSWRP VS XGWTSR, IAT RS
YSGF GFYAGKAHUF VEAR VEAV A UAHSMGFG WR ISGKWRP DUSVEFT TESMUZ HF
PSWRP VS ISGK. WR SRF RAGGSI, ZAGK, ARZ ZWGVO TVGFFV VEGSMPE IEWDE VEFO
XATTFZ, AR FQDWVFZ SGAVSG, YSMRVFZ SR A TVSSU, IAT AZZGFTTWRP AR FQDWVFZ
AMZWFRDF SR VEF DGWYFT APAWRTV VEF XFSXUF, SC VEF KWRP ARZ VEF GSOAU
CAYWUO. VEF CFI ISGZT VEAV EF DAMPEV CGSY VEWT YAR'T UWXT, CWGTV YAZF
WV KRSIR VS DEAGUFT ZAGRAO VEAV VEF KWRP IAT WR XGWTSR, ARZ VEAV VEF
CSGFWPR AYHATTAZSGT EAZ SRF ARZ AUU UFCV XAGWT. SR VEF GSAZ (FQDFXV AV
HFAMJAWT) EF EAZ EFAGZ AHTSUMVFUO RSVEWRP. VEF FTDSGV ARZ VEF MRWJFGTAU
IAVDECMURFTT EAZ DSYXUFVFUO WTSUAVFZ EWY.

VEAV EF EAZ CAUUFR AYSRP CAG PGFAVFG ZARPFGT VEAR VESTF IEWDE EAZ
ZFJFUSXFZ VEFYTFUJFT IEFR EF UFCV FRPUARZ, EF SC DSMGTF KRFI RSI. VEAV
XFGWUT EAZ VEWDKFRFZ AHSMV EWY CATV, ARZ YWPEV VEWDKFR CATVFG ARZ CATVFG
OFV, EF SC DSMGTF KRFI RSI. EF DSMUZ RSV HMV AZYWV VS EWYTFUC VEAV EF
YWPEV RSV EAJF YAZF VEWT LSMGRFO, WC EF DSMUZ EAJF CSGFTFFR VEF FJFRVT
SC A CFI ZAOT. ARZ OFV EWT YWTPWJWRPT IFGF RSV TS ZAGK AT, WYAPWRFZ HO
VEF UWPEV SC VEWT UAVFG VWYF, VEFO ISMUZ AXXFAG. VGSMHUFZ AT VEF CMVMGF
IAT, WV IAT VEF MRKRSIR CMVMGF, ARZ WR WVT SHTDMGWVO VEFGF IAT WPRSGARV
ESXF. VEF ESGGWHUF YATTADGF, ZAOT ARZ RWPEVT USRP, IEWDE, IWVEWR A CFI
GSMRZT SC VEF DUSDK, IAT VS TFV A PGFAV YAGK SC HUSSZ MXSR VEF HUFTTFZ
PAGRFGWRP VWYF SC EAGJFTV, IAT AT CAG SMV SC EWT KRSIUFZPF AT WC WV EAZ
HFFR A EMRZGFZ VESMTARZ OFAGT AIAO. VEF “TEAGX CFYAUF RFIUO-HSGR, ARZ
DAUUFZ UA PMWUUSVWRF,” IAT EAGZUO KRSIR VS EWY, SG VS VEF PFRFGAUWVO
SC XFSXUF, HO RAYF. VEF CGWPEVCMU ZFFZT VEAV IFGF VS HF TSSR ZSRF, IFGF
XGSHAHUO MRWYAPWRFZ AV VEAV VWYF WR VEF HGAWRT SC VEF ZSFGT. ESI DSMUZ
VEFO EAJF A XUADF WR VEF TEAZSIO DSRDFXVWSRT SC A PFRVUF YWRZ?

SC MRLMTV VGFAVYFRV WR ZFVFRVWSR ARZ EAGZTEWX, ARZ WR DGMFU TFXAGAVWSR
CGSY EWT IWCF ARZ DEWUZ, EF CSGFTEAZSIFZ VEF UWKFUWESSZ, SG VEF
DFGVAWRVO; HMV, HFOSRZ VEWT, EF ZGFAZFZ RSVEWRP ZWTVWRDVUO. IWVE VEWT SR
EWT YWRZ, IEWDE IAT FRSMPE VS DAGGO WRVS A ZGFAGO XGWTSR DSMGVOAGZ, EF
AGGWJFZ AV VEF XGWTSR SC UA CSGDF.

A YAR IWVE A HUSAVFZ CADF SXFRFZ VEF TVGSRP IWDKFV, VS IESY ZFCAGPF
XGFTFRVFZ “VEF FYWPGARV FJGFYSRZF.”

“IEAV VEF ZFJWU! ESI YARO YSGF SC VEFY!” FQDUAWYFZ VEF YAR IWVE VEF
HUSAVFZ CADF.

ZFCAGPF VSSK EWT GFDFWXV IWVESMV RSVWDWRP VEF FQDUAYAVWSR, ARZ IWVEZGFI,
IWVE EWT VIS CFUUSI-XAVGWSVT.

“IEAV VEF ZFJWU, W TAO APAWR!” FQDUAWYFZ VEF PASUFG, UFCV IWVE EWT IWCF.
“ESI YARO YSGF!”

VEF PASUFG'T IWCF, HFWRP XGSJWZFZ IWVE RS ARTIFG VS VEF NMFTVWSR, YFGFUO
GFXUWFZ, “SRF YMTV EAJF XAVWFRDF, YO ZFAG!” VEGFF VMGRKFOT IES FRVFGFZ
GFTXSRTWJF VS A HFUU TEF GARP, FDESFZ VEF TFRVWYFRV, ARZ SRF AZZFZ, “CSG
VEF USJF SC UWHFGVO;” IEWDE TSMRZFZ WR VEAV XUADF UWKF AR WRAXXGSXGWAVF
DSRDUMTWSR.

VEF XGWTSR SC UA CSGDF IAT A PUSSYO XGWTSR, ZAGK ARZ CWUVEO, ARZ IWVE A
ESGGWHUF TYFUU SC CSMU TUFFX WR WV. FQVGASGZWRAGO ESI TSSR VEF RSWTSYF
CUAJSMG SC WYXGWTSRFZ TUFFX, HFDSYFT YARWCFTV WR AUU TMDE XUADFT VEAV
AGF WUU DAGFZ CSG!

“WR TFDGFV, VSS,” PGMYHUFZ VEF PASUFG, USSKWRP AV VEF IGWVVFR XAXFG. “AT
WC W IAT RSV AUGFAZO CMUU VS HMGTVWRP!”

EF TVMDK VEF XAXFG SR A CWUF, WR AR WUU-EMYSMG, ARZ DEAGUFT ZAGRAO
AIAWVFZ EWT CMGVEFG XUFATMGF CSG EAUC AR ESMG: TSYFVWYFT, XADWRP VS ARZ
CGS WR VEF TVGSRP AGDEFZ GSSY: TSYFVWYFT, GFTVWRP SR A TVSRF TFAV: WR
FWVEFG DATF ZFVAWRFZ VS HF WYXGWRVFZ SR VEF YFYSGO SC VEF DEWFC ARZ EWT
TMHSGZWRAVFT.

“DSYF!” TAWZ VEF DEWFC, AV UFRPVE VAKWRP MX EWT KFOT, “DSYF IWVE YF,
FYWPGARV.”

VEGSMPE VEF ZWTYAU XGWTSR VIWUWPEV, EWT RFI DEAGPF ADDSYXARWFZ EWY HO
DSGGWZSG ARZ TVAWGDATF, YARO ZSSGT DUARPWRP ARZ USDKWRP HFEWRZ VEFY,
MRVWU VEFO DAYF WRVS A UAGPF, USI, JAMUVFZ DEAYHFG, DGSIZFZ IWVE
XGWTSRFGT SC HSVE TFQFT. VEF ISYFR IFGF TFAVFZ AV A USRP VAHUF, GFAZWRP
ARZ IGWVWRP, KRWVVWRP, TFIWRP, ARZ FYHGSWZFGWRP; VEF YFR IFGF CSG VEF
YSTV XAGV TVARZWRP HFEWRZ VEFWG DEAWGT, SG UWRPFGWRP MX ARZ ZSIR VEF
GSSY.

WR VEF WRTVWRDVWJF ATTSDWAVWSR SC XGWTSRFGT IWVE TEAYFCMU DGWYF ARZ
ZWTPGADF, VEF RFI-DSYFG GFDSWUFZ CGSY VEWT DSYXARO. HMV VEF DGSIRWRP
MRGFAUWVO SC EWT USRP MRGFAU GWZF, IAT, VEFWG AUU AV SRDF GWTWRP VS
GFDFWJF EWY, IWVE FJFGO GFCWRFYFRV SC YARRFG KRSIR VS VEF VWYF, ARZ IWVE
AUU VEF FRPAPWRP PGADFT ARZ DSMGVFTWFT SC UWCF.

TS TVGARPFUO DUSMZFZ IFGF VEFTF GFCWRFYFRVT HO VEF XGWTSR YARRFGT ARZ
PUSSY, TS TXFDVGAU ZWZ VEFO HFDSYF WR VEF WRAXXGSXGWAVF TNMAUSG ARZ
YWTFGO VEGSMPE IEWDE VEFO IFGF TFFR, VEAV DEAGUFT ZAGRAO TFFYFZ VS TVARZ
WR A DSYXARO SC VEF ZFAZ. PESTVT AUU! VEF PESTV SC HFAMVO, VEF PESTV
SC TVAVFUWRFTT, VEF PESTV SC FUFPARDF, VEF PESTV SC XGWZF, VEF PESTV SC
CGWJSUWVO, VEF PESTV SC IWV, VEF PESTV SC OSMVE, VEF PESTV SC APF, AUU
IAWVWRP VEFWG ZWTYWTTAU CGSY VEF ZFTSUAVF TESGF, AUU VMGRWRP SR EWY FOFT
VEAV IFGF DEARPFZ HO VEF ZFAVE VEFO EAZ ZWFZ WR DSYWRP VEFGF.

WV TVGMDK EWY YSVWSRUFTT. VEF PASUFG TVARZWRP AV EWT TWZF, ARZ VEF SVEFG
PASUFGT YSJWRP AHSMV, IES ISMUZ EAJF HFFR IFUU FRSMPE AT VS AXXFAGARDF
WR VEF SGZWRAGO FQFGDWTF SC VEFWG CMRDVWSRT, USSKFZ TS FQVGAJAPARVUO
DSAGTF DSRVGATVFZ IWVE TSGGSIWRP YSVEFGT ARZ HUSSYWRP ZAMPEVFGT IES IFGF
VEFGF--IWVE VEF AXXAGWVWSRT SC VEF DSNMFVVF, VEF OSMRP HFAMVO, ARZ VEF
YAVMGF ISYAR ZFUWDAVFUO HGFZ--VEAV VEF WRJFGTWSR SC AUU FQXFGWFRDF ARZ
UWKFUWESSZ IEWDE VEF TDFRF SC TEAZSIT XGFTFRVFZ, IAT EFWPEVFRFZ VS WVT
MVYSTV. TMGFUO, PESTVT AUU. TMGFUO, VEF USRP MRGFAU GWZF TSYF XGSPGFTT
SC ZWTFATF VEAV EAZ HGSMPEV EWY VS VEFTF PUSSYO TEAZFT!

“WR VEF RAYF SC VEF ATTFYHUFZ DSYXARWSRT WR YWTCSGVMRF,” TAWZ A
PFRVUFYAR SC DSMGVUO AXXFAGARDF ARZ AZZGFTT, DSYWRP CSGIAGZ, “W EAJF VEF
ESRSMG SC PWJWRP OSM IFUDSYF VS UA CSGDF, ARZ SC DSRZSUWRP IWVE OSM
SR VEF DAUAYWVO VEAV EAT HGSMPEV OSM AYSRP MT. YAO WV TSSR VFGYWRAVF
EAXXWUO! WV ISMUZ HF AR WYXFGVWRFRDF FUTFIEFGF, HMV WV WT RSV TS EFGF,
VS ATK OSMG RAYF ARZ DSRZWVWSR?”

DEAGUFT ZAGRAO GSMTFZ EWYTFUC, ARZ PAJF VEF GFNMWGFZ WRCSGYAVWSR, WR
ISGZT AT TMWVAHUF AT EF DSMUZ CWRZ.

“HMV W ESXF,” TAWZ VEF PFRVUFYAR, CSUUSIWRP VEF DEWFC PASUFG IWVE EWT
FOFT, IES YSJFZ ADGSTT VEF GSSY, “VEAV OSM AGF RSV WR TFDGFV?”

“W ZS RSV MRZFGTVARZ VEF YFARWRP SC VEF VFGY, HMV W EAJF EFAGZ VEFY TAO
TS.”

“AE, IEAV A XWVO! IF TS YMDE GFPGFV WV! HMV VAKF DSMGAPF; TFJFGAU
YFYHFGT SC SMG TSDWFVO EAJF HFFR WR TFDGFV, AV CWGTV, ARZ WV EAT UATVFZ
HMV A TESGV VWYF.” VEFR EF AZZFZ, GAWTWRP EWT JSWDF, “W PGWFJF VS WRCSGY
VEF TSDWFVO--WR TFDGFV.”

VEFGF IAT A YMGYMG SC DSYYWTFGAVWSR AT DEAGUFT ZAGRAO DGSTTFZ VEF GSSY
VS A PGAVFZ ZSSG IEFGF VEF PASUFG AIAWVFZ EWY, ARZ YARO JSWDFT--AYSRP
IEWDE, VEF TSCV ARZ DSYXATTWSRAVF JSWDFT SC ISYFR IFGF DSRTXWDMSMT--PAJF
EWY PSSZ IWTEFT ARZ FRDSMGAPFYFRV. EF VMGRFZ AV VEF PGAVFZ ZSSG, VS
GFRZFG VEF VEARKT SC EWT EFAGV; WV DUSTFZ MRZFG VEF PASUFG'T EARZ; ARZ
VEF AXXAGWVWSRT JARWTEFZ CGSY EWT TWPEV CSGFJFG.

VEF IWDKFV SXFRFZ SR A TVSRF TVAWGDATF, UFAZWRP MXIAGZ. IEFR VEFO EAZ
ATDFRZFZ CSGVO TVFXT (VEF XGWTSRFG SC EAUC AR ESMG AUGFAZO DSMRVFZ
VEFY), VEF PASUFG SXFRFZ A USI HUADK ZSSG, ARZ VEFO XATTFZ WRVS A
TSUWVAGO DFUU. WV TVGMDK DSUZ ARZ ZAYX, HMV IAT RSV ZAGK.

“OSMGT,” TAWZ VEF PASUFG.

“IEO AY W DSRCWRFZ AUSRF?”

“ESI ZS W KRSI!”

“W DAR HMO XFR, WRK, ARZ XAXFG?”

“TMDE AGF RSV YO SGZFGT. OSM IWUU HF JWTWVFZ, ARZ DAR ATK VEFR. AV
XGFTFRV, OSM YAO HMO OSMG CSSZ, ARZ RSVEWRP YSGF.”

VEFGF IFGF WR VEF DFUU, A DEAWG, A VAHUF, ARZ A TVGAI YAVVGFTT. AT
VEF PASUFG YAZF A PFRFGAU WRTXFDVWSR SC VEFTF SHLFDVT, ARZ SC VEF CSMG
IAUUT, HFCSGF PSWRP SMV, A IARZFGWRP CARDO IARZFGFZ VEGSMPE VEF YWRZ SC
VEF XGWTSRFG UFARWRP APAWRTV VEF IAUU SXXSTWVF VS EWY, VEAV VEWT PASUFG
IAT TS MRIESUFTSYFUO HUSAVFZ, HSVE WR CADF ARZ XFGTSR, AT VS USSK UWKF
A YAR IES EAZ HFFR ZGSIRFZ ARZ CWUUFZ IWVE IAVFG. IEFR VEF PASUFG IAT
PSRF, EF VESMPEV WR VEF TAYF IARZFGWRP IAO, “RSI AY W UFCV, AT WC W IFGF
ZFAZ.” TVSXXWRP VEFR, VS USSK ZSIR AV VEF YAVVGFTT, EF VMGRFZ CGSY WV
IWVE A TWDK CFFUWRP, ARZ VESMPEV, “ARZ EFGF WR VEFTF DGAIUWRP DGFAVMGFT
WT VEF CWGTV DSRZWVWSR SC VEF HSZO ACVFG ZFAVE.”

“CWJF XADFT HO CSMG ARZ A EAUC, CWJF XADFT HO CSMG ARZ A EAUC, CWJF
XADFT HO CSMG ARZ A EAUC.” VEF XGWTSRFG IAUKFZ VS ARZ CGS WR EWT DFUU,
DSMRVWRP WVT YFATMGFYFRV, ARZ VEF GSAG SC VEF DWVO AGSTF UWKF YMCCUFZ
ZGMYT IWVE A IWUZ TIFUU SC JSWDFT AZZFZ VS VEFY. “EF YAZF TESFT, EF YAZF
TESFT, EF YAZF TESFT.” VEF XGWTSRFG DSMRVFZ VEF YFATMGFYFRV APAWR, ARZ
XADFZ CATVFG, VS ZGAI EWT YWRZ IWVE EWY CGSY VEAV UAVVFG GFXFVWVWSR.
“VEF PESTVT VEAV JARWTEFZ IEFR VEF IWDKFV DUSTFZ. VEFGF IAT SRF AYSRP
VEFY, VEF AXXFAGARDF SC A UAZO ZGFTTFZ WR HUADK, IES IAT UFARWRP WR VEF
FYHGATMGF SC A IWRZSI, ARZ TEF EAZ A UWPEV TEWRWRP MXSR EFG PSUZFR
EAWG, ARZ TEF USSKFZ UWKF * * * * UFV MT GWZF SR APAWR, CSG PSZ'T TAKF,
VEGSMPE VEF WUUMYWRAVFZ JWUUAPFT IWVE VEF XFSXUF AUU AIAKF! * * * * EF
YAZF TESFT, EF YAZF TESFT, EF YAZF TESFT. * * * * CWJF XADFT HO CSMG ARZ
A EAUC.” IWVE TMDE TDGAXT VSTTWRP ARZ GSUUWRP MXIAGZ CGSY VEF ZFXVET SC
EWT YWRZ, VEF XGWTSRFG IAUKFZ CATVFG ARZ CATVFG, SHTVWRAVFUO DSMRVWRP
ARZ DSMRVWRP; ARZ VEF GSAG SC VEF DWVO DEARPFZ VS VEWT FQVFRV--VEAV WV
TVWUU GSUUFZ WR UWKF YMCCUFZ ZGMYT, HMV IWVE VEF IAWU SC JSWDFT VEAV EF
KRFI, WR VEF TIFUU VEAV GSTF AHSJF VEFY.




WW. VEF PGWRZTVSRF


VFUUTSR'T HARK, FTVAHUWTEFZ WR VEF TAWRV PFGYAWR NMAGVFG SC XAGWT, IAT
WR A IWRP SC A UAGPF ESMTF, AXXGSADEFZ HO A DSMGVOAGZ ARZ TEMV SCC CGSY
VEF TVGFFV HO A EWPE IAUU ARZ A TVGSRP PAVF. VEF ESMTF HFUSRPFZ VS
A PGFAV RSHUFYAR IES EAZ UWJFZ WR WV MRVWU EF YAZF A CUWPEV CGSY VEF
VGSMHUFT, WR EWT SIR DSSK'T ZGFTT, ARZ PSV ADGSTT VEF HSGZFGT. A
YFGF HFATV SC VEF DEATF CUOWRP CGSY EMRVFGT, EF IAT TVWUU WR EWT
YFVFYXTODESTWT RS SVEFG VEAR VEF TAYF YSRTFWPRFMG, VEF XGFXAGAVWSR
SC IESTF DESDSUAVF CSG IESTF UWXT EAZ SRDF SDDMXWFZ VEGFF TVGSRP YFR
HFTWZFT VEF DSSK WR NMFTVWSR.

YSRTFWPRFMG PSRF, ARZ VEF VEGFF TVGSRP YFR AHTSUJWRP VEFYTFUJFT CGSY VEF
TWR SC EAJWRP ZGAIR EWT EWPE IAPFT, HO HFWRP YSGF VEAR GFAZO ARZ
IWUUWRP VS DMV EWT VEGSAV SR VEF AUVAG SC VEF ZAIRWRP GFXMHUWD SRF ARZ
WRZWJWTWHUF SC UWHFGVO, FNMAUWVO, CGAVFGRWVO, SG ZFAVE, YSRTFWPRFMG'T
ESMTF EAZ HFFR CWGTV TFNMFTVGAVFZ, ARZ VEFR DSRCWTDAVFZ. CSG, AUU
VEWRPT YSJFZ TS CATV, ARZ ZFDGFF CSUUSIFZ ZFDGFF IWVE VEAV CWFGDF
XGFDWXWVAVWSR, VEAV RSI MXSR VEF VEWGZ RWPEV SC VEF AMVMYR YSRVE
SC TFXVFYHFG, XAVGWSV FYWTTAGWFT SC VEF UAI IFGF WR XSTTFTTWSR SC
YSRTFWPRFMG'T ESMTF, ARZ EAZ YAGKFZ WV IWVE VEF VGW-DSUSMG, ARZ IFGF
ZGWRKWRP HGARZO WR WVT TVAVF AXAGVYFRVT.

A XUADF SC HMTWRFTT WR USRZSR UWKF VFUUTSR'T XUADF SC HMTWRFTT WR XAGWT,
ISMUZ TSSR EAJF ZGWJFR VEF ESMTF SMV SC WVT YWRZ ARZ WRVS VEF PABFVVF.
CSG, IEAV ISMUZ TVAWZ HGWVWTE GFTXSRTWHWUWVO ARZ GFTXFDVAHWUWVO EAJF
TAWZ VS SGARPF-VGFFT WR HSQFT WR A HARK DSMGVOAGZ, ARZ FJFR VS A DMXWZ
SJFG VEF DSMRVFG? OFV TMDE VEWRPT IFGF. VFUUTSR'T EAZ IEWVFIATEFZ VEF
DMXWZ, HMV EF IAT TVWUU VS HF TFFR SR VEF DFWUWRP, WR VEF DSSUFTV
UWRFR, AWYWRP (AT EF JFGO SCVFR ZSFT) AV YSRFO CGSY YSGRWRP VS
RWPEV. HARKGMXVDO YMTV WRFJWVAHUO EAJF DSYF SC VEWT OSMRP XAPAR, WR
USYHAGZ-TVGFFV, USRZSR, ARZ AUTS SC A DMGVAWRFZ AUDSJF WR VEF GFAG SC
VEF WYYSGVAU HSO, ARZ AUTS SC A USSKWRP-PUATT UFV WRVS VEF IAUU, ARZ
AUTS SC DUFGKT RSV AV AUU SUZ, IES ZARDFZ WR XMHUWD SR VEF TUWPEVFTV
XGSJSDAVWSR. OFV, A CGFRDE VFUUTSR'T DSMUZ PFV SR IWVE VEFTF VEWRPT
FQDFFZWRPUO IFUU, ARZ, AT USRP AT VEF VWYFT EFUZ VSPFVEFG, RS YAR EAZ
VAKFR CGWPEV AV VEFY, ARZ ZGAIR SMV EWT YSRFO.

IEAV YSRFO ISMUZ HF ZGAIR SMV SC VFUUTSR'T EFRDFCSGVE, ARZ IEAV ISMUZ
UWF VEFGF, USTV ARZ CSGPSVVFR; IEAV XUAVF ARZ LFIFUT ISMUZ VAGRWTE WR
VFUUTSR'T EWZWRP-XUADFT, IEWUF VEF ZFXSTWVSGT GMTVFZ WR XGWTSRT,
ARZ IEFR VEFO TESMUZ EAJF JWSUFRVUO XFGWTEFZ; ESI YARO ADDSMRVT IWVE
VFUUTSR'T RFJFG VS HF HAUARDFZ WR VEWT ISGUZ, YMTV HF DAGGWFZ SJFG WRVS
VEF RFQV; RS YAR DSMUZ EAJF TAWZ, VEAV RWPEV, ARO YSGF VEAR YG. LAGJWT
USGGO DSMUZ, VESMPE EF VESMPEV EFAJWUO SC VEFTF NMFTVWSRT. EF TAV HO
A RFIUO-UWPEVFZ ISSZ CWGF (VEF HUWPEVFZ ARZ MRCGMWVCMU OFAG IAT
XGFYAVMGFUO DSUZ), ARZ SR EWT ESRFTV ARZ DSMGAPFSMT CADF VEFGF IAT A
ZFFXFG TEAZF VEAR VEF XFRZFRV UAYX DSMUZ VEGSI, SG ARO SHLFDV WR VEF
GSSY ZWTVSGVFZUO GFCUFDV--A TEAZF SC ESGGSG.

EF SDDMXWFZ GSSYT WR VEF HARK, WR EWT CWZFUWVO VS VEF ESMTF SC IEWDE
EF EAZ PGSIR VS HF A XAGV, UWKF TVGSRP GSSV-WJO. WV DEARDFZ VEAV VEFO
ZFGWJFZ A KWRZ SC TFDMGWVO CGSY VEF XAVGWSVWD SDDMXAVWSR SC VEF YAWR
HMWUZWRP, HMV VEF VGMF-EFAGVFZ SUZ PFRVUFYAR RFJFG DAUDMUAVFZ AHSMV
VEAV. AUU TMDE DWGDMYTVARDFT IFGF WRZWCCFGFRV VS EWY, TS VEAV EF ZWZ
EWT ZMVO. SR VEF SXXSTWVF TWZF SC VEF DSMGVOAGZ, MRZFG A DSUSRRAZF,
IAT FQVFRTWJF TVARZWRP--CSG DAGGWAPFT--IEFGF, WRZFFZ, TSYF DAGGWAPFT
SC YSRTFWPRFMG OFV TVSSZ. APAWRTV VIS SC VEF XWUUAGT IFGF CATVFRFZ VIS
PGFAV CUAGWRP CUAYHFAMQ, ARZ WR VEF UWPEV SC VEFTF, TVARZWRP SMV WR VEF
SXFR AWG, IAT A UAGPF PGWRZTVSRF: A GSMPEUO YSMRVFZ VEWRP IEWDE AXXFAGFZ
VS EAJF EMGGWFZUO HFFR HGSMPEV VEFGF CGSY TSYF RFWPEHSMGWRP TYWVEO,
SG SVEFG ISGKTESX. GWTWRP ARZ USSKWRP SMV SC IWRZSI AV VEFTF EAGYUFTT
SHLFDVT, YG. USGGO TEWJFGFZ, ARZ GFVWGFZ VS EWT TFAV HO VEF CWGF. EF EAZ
SXFRFZ, RSV SRUO VEF PUATT IWRZSI, HMV VEF UAVVWDF HUWRZ SMVTWZF WV, ARZ
EF EAZ DUSTFZ HSVE APAWR, ARZ EF TEWJFGFZ VEGSMPE EWT CGAYF.

CGSY VEF TVGFFVT HFOSRZ VEF EWPE IAUU ARZ VEF TVGSRP PAVF, VEFGF DAYF
VEF MTMAU RWPEV EMY SC VEF DWVO, IWVE RSI ARZ VEFR AR WRZFTDGWHAHUF GWRP
WR WV, IFWGZ ARZ MRFAGVEUO, AT WC TSYF MRISRVFZ TSMRZT SC A VFGGWHUF
RAVMGF IFGF PSWRP MX VS EFAJFR.

“VEARK PSZ,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, DUATXWRP EWT EARZT, “VEAV RS SRF RFAG ARZ
ZFAG VS YF WT WR VEWT ZGFAZCMU VSIR VS-RWPEV. YAO EF EAJF YFGDO SR AUU
IES AGF WR ZARPFG!”

TSSR ACVFGIAGZT, VEF HFUU AV VEF PGFAV PAVF TSMRZFZ, ARZ EF VESMPEV,
“VEFO EAJF DSYF HADK!” ARZ TAV UWTVFRWRP. HMV, VEFGF IAT RS USMZ
WGGMXVWSR WRVS VEF DSMGVOAGZ, AT EF EAZ FQXFDVFZ, ARZ EF EFAGZ VEF PAVF
DUATE APAWR, ARZ AUU IAT NMWFV.

VEF RFGJSMTRFTT ARZ ZGFAZ VEAV IFGF MXSR EWY WRTXWGFZ VEAV JAPMF
MRFATWRFTT GFTXFDVWRP VEF HARK, IEWDE A PGFAV DEARPF ISMUZ RAVMGAUUO
AIAKFR, IWVE TMDE CFFUWRPT GSMTFZ. WV IAT IFUU PMAGZFZ, ARZ EF PSV MX VS
PS AYSRP VEF VGMTVO XFSXUF IES IFGF IAVDEWRP WV, IEFR EWT ZSSG TMZZFRUO
SXFRFZ, ARZ VIS CWPMGFT GMTEFZ WR, AV TWPEV SC IEWDE EF CFUU HADK WR
AYABFYFRV.

UMDWF ARZ EFG CAVEFG! UMDWF IWVE EFG AGYT TVGFVDEFZ SMV VS EWY, ARZ IWVE
VEAV SUZ USSK SC FAGRFTVRFTT TS DSRDFRVGAVFZ ARZ WRVFRTWCWFZ, VEAV WV
TFFYFZ AT VESMPE WV EAZ HFFR TVAYXFZ MXSR EFG CADF FQXGFTTUO VS PWJF
CSGDF ARZ XSIFG VS WV WR VEWT SRF XATTAPF SC EFG UWCF.

“IEAV WT VEWT?” DGWFZ YG. USGGO, HGFAVEUFTT ARZ DSRCMTFZ. “IEAV WT VEF
YAVVFG? UMDWF! YARFVVF! IEAV EAT EAXXFRFZ? IEAV EAT HGSMPEV OSM EFGF?
IEAV WT WV?”

IWVE VEF USSK CWQFZ MXSR EWY, WR EFG XAUFRFTT ARZ IWUZRFTT, TEF XARVFZ
SMV WR EWT AGYT, WYXUSGWRPUO, “S YO ZFAG CGWFRZ! YO EMTHARZ!”

“OSMG EMTHARZ, UMDWF?”

“DEAGUFT.”

“IEAV SC DEAGUFT?”

“EFGF.

“EFGF, WR XAGWT?”

“EAT HFFR EFGF TSYF ZAOT--VEGFF SG CSMG--W ZSR'V KRSI ESI YARO--W DAR'V
DSUUFDV YO VESMPEVT. AR FGGARZ SC PFRFGSTWVO HGSMPEV EWY EFGF MRKRSIR VS
MT; EF IAT TVSXXFZ AV VEF HAGGWFG, ARZ TFRV VS XGWTSR.”

VEF SUZ YAR MVVFGFZ AR WGGFXGFTTWHUF DGO. AUYSTV AV VEF TAYF YSYFRV, VEF
HFUU SC VEF PGFAV PAVF GARP APAWR, ARZ A USMZ RSWTF SC CFFV ARZ JSWDFT
DAYF XSMGWRP WRVS VEF DSMGVOAGZ.

“IEAV WT VEAV RSWTF?” TAWZ VEF ZSDVSG, VMGRWRP VSIAGZT VEF IWRZSI.

“ZSR'V USSK!” DGWFZ YG. USGGO. “ZSR'V USSK SMV! YARFVVF, CSG OSMG UWCF,
ZSR'V VSMDE VEF HUWRZ!”

VEF ZSDVSG VMGRFZ, IWVE EWT EARZ MXSR VEF CATVFRWRP SC VEF IWRZSI, ARZ
TAWZ, IWVE A DSSU, HSUZ TYWUF:

“YO ZFAG CGWFRZ, W EAJF A DEAGYFZ UWCF WR VEWT DWVO. W EAJF HFFR
A HATVWUUF XGWTSRFG. VEFGF WT RS XAVGWSV WR XAGWT--WR XAGWT? WR
CGARDF--IES, KRSIWRP YF VS EAJF HFFR A XGWTSRFG WR VEF HATVWUUF, ISMUZ
VSMDE YF, FQDFXV VS SJFGIEFUY YF IWVE FYHGADFT, SG DAGGO YF WR VGWMYXE.
YO SUZ XAWR EAT PWJFR YF A XSIFG VEAV EAT HGSMPEV MT VEGSMPE VEF
HAGGWFG, ARZ PAWRFZ MT RFIT SC DEAGUFT VEFGF, ARZ HGSMPEV MT EFGF. W
KRFI WV ISMUZ HF TS; W KRFI W DSMUZ EFUX DEAGUFT SMV SC AUU ZARPFG; W
VSUZ UMDWF TS.--IEAV WT VEAV RSWTF?” EWT EARZ IAT APAWR MXSR VEF IWRZSI.

“ZSR'V USSK!” DGWFZ YG. USGGO, AHTSUMVFUO ZFTXFGAVF. “RS, UMDWF, YO
ZFAG, RSG OSM!” EF PSV EWT AGY GSMRZ EFG, ARZ EFUZ EFG. “ZSR'V HF TS
VFGGWCWFZ, YO USJF. W TSUFYRUO TIFAG VS OSM VEAV W KRSI SC RS EAGY
EAJWRP EAXXFRFZ VS DEAGUFT; VEAV W EAZ RS TMTXWDWSR FJFR SC EWT HFWRP WR
VEWT CAVAU XUADF. IEAV XGWTSR WT EF WR?”

“UA CSGDF!”

“UA CSGDF! UMDWF, YO DEWUZ, WC FJFG OSM IFGF HGAJF ARZ TFGJWDFAHUF WR
OSMG UWCF--ARZ OSM IFGF AUIAOT HSVE--OSM IWUU DSYXSTF OSMGTFUC RSI, VS
ZS FQADVUO AT W HWZ OSM; CSG YSGF ZFXFRZT MXSR WV VEAR OSM DAR VEWRK, SG
W DAR TAO. VEFGF WT RS EFUX CSG OSM WR ARO ADVWSR SR OSMG XAGV VS-RWPEV;
OSM DARRSV XSTTWHUO TVWG SMV. W TAO VEWT, HFDAMTF IEAV W YMTV HWZ OSM
VS ZS CSG DEAGUFT'T TAKF, WT VEF EAGZFTV VEWRP VS ZS SC AUU. OSM YMTV
WRTVARVUO HF SHFZWFRV, TVWUU, ARZ NMWFV. OSM YMTV UFV YF XMV OSM WR A
GSSY AV VEF HADK EFGF. OSM YMTV UFAJF OSMG CAVEFG ARZ YF AUSRF CSG
VIS YWRMVFT, ARZ AT VEFGF AGF UWCF ARZ ZFAVE WR VEF ISGUZ OSM YMTV RSV
ZFUAO.”

“W IWUU HF TMHYWTTWJF VS OSM. W TFF WR OSMG CADF VEAV OSM KRSI W DAR ZS
RSVEWRP FUTF VEAR VEWT. W KRSI OSM AGF VGMF.”

VEF SUZ YAR KWTTFZ EFG, ARZ EMGGWFZ EFG WRVS EWT GSSY, ARZ VMGRFZ VEF
KFO; VEFR, DAYF EMGGOWRP HADK VS VEF ZSDVSG, ARZ SXFRFZ VEF IWRZSI ARZ
XAGVUO SXFRFZ VEF HUWRZ, ARZ XMV EWT EARZ MXSR VEF ZSDVSG'T AGY, ARZ
USSKFZ SMV IWVE EWY WRVS VEF DSMGVOAGZ.

USSKFZ SMV MXSR A VEGSRP SC YFR ARZ ISYFR: RSV FRSMPE WR RMYHFG, SG RFAG
FRSMPE, VS CWUU VEF DSMGVOAGZ: RSV YSGF VEAR CSGVO SG CWCVO WR AUU. VEF
XFSXUF WR XSTTFTTWSR SC VEF ESMTF EAZ UFV VEFY WR AV VEF PAVF, ARZ VEFO
EAZ GMTEFZ WR VS ISGK AV VEF PGWRZTVSRF; WV EAZ FJWZFRVUO HFFR TFV MX
VEFGF CSG VEFWG XMGXSTF, AT WR A DSRJFRWFRV ARZ GFVWGFZ TXSV.

HMV, TMDE AICMU ISGKFGT, ARZ TMDE AICMU ISGK!

VEF PGWRZTVSRF EAZ A ZSMHUF EARZUF, ARZ, VMGRWRP AV WV YAZUO IFGF VIS
YFR, IESTF CADFT, AT VEFWG USRP EAWG CUAXXFZ HADK IEFR VEF IEWGUWRPT SC
VEF PGWRZTVSRF HGSMPEV VEFWG CADFT MX, IFGF YSGF ESGGWHUF ARZ DGMFU VEAR
VEF JWTAPFT SC VEF IWUZFTV TAJAPFT WR VEFWG YSTV HAGHAGSMT ZWTPMWTF.
CAUTF FOFHGSIT ARZ CAUTF YSMTVADEFT IFGF TVMDK MXSR VEFY, ARZ VEFWG
EWZFSMT DSMRVFRARDFT IFGF AUU HUSSZO ARZ TIFAVO, ARZ AUU AIGO IWVE
ESIUWRP, ARZ AUU TVAGWRP ARZ PUAGWRP IWVE HFATVUO FQDWVFYFRV ARZ IARV SC
TUFFX. AT VEFTF GMCCWART VMGRFZ ARZ VMGRFZ, VEFWG YAVVFZ USDKT RSI CUMRP
CSGIAGZ SJFG VEFWG FOFT, RSI CUMRP HADKIAGZ SJFG VEFWG RFDKT, TSYF ISYFR
EFUZ IWRF VS VEFWG YSMVET VEAV VEFO YWPEV ZGWRK; ARZ IEAV IWVE ZGSXXWRP
HUSSZ, ARZ IEAV IWVE ZGSXXWRP IWRF, ARZ IEAV IWVE VEF TVGFAY SC TXAGKT
TVGMDK SMV SC VEF TVSRF, AUU VEFWG IWDKFZ AVYSTXEFGF TFFYFZ PSGF ARZ
CWGF. VEF FOF DSMUZ RSV ZFVFDV SRF DGFAVMGF WR VEF PGSMX CGFF CGSY
VEF TYFAG SC HUSSZ. TESMUZFGWRP SRF ARSVEFG VS PFV RFQV AV VEF
TEAGXFRWRP-TVSRF, IFGF YFR TVGWXXFZ VS VEF IAWTV, IWVE VEF TVAWR AUU
SJFG VEFWG UWYHT ARZ HSZWFT; YFR WR AUU TSGVT SC GAPT, IWVE VEF TVAWR
MXSR VESTF GAPT; YFR ZFJWUWTEUO TFV SCC IWVE TXSWUT SC ISYFR'T UADF
ARZ TWUK ARZ GWHHSR, IWVE VEF TVAWR ZOFWRP VESTF VGWCUFT VEGSMPE
ARZ VEGSMPE. EAVDEFVT, KRWJFT, HAOSRFVT, TISGZT, AUU HGSMPEV VS HF
TEAGXFRFZ, IFGF AUU GFZ IWVE WV. TSYF SC VEF EADKFZ TISGZT IFGF VWFZ VS
VEF IGWTVT SC VESTF IES DAGGWFZ VEFY, IWVE TVGWXT SC UWRFR ARZ CGAPYFRVT
SC ZGFTT: UWPAVMGFT JAGWSMT WR KWRZ, HMV AUU ZFFX SC VEF SRF DSUSMG. ARZ
AT VEF CGARVWD IWFUZFGT SC VEFTF IFAXSRT TRAVDEFZ VEFY CGSY VEF TVGFAY
SC TXAGKT ARZ VSGF AIAO WRVS VEF TVGFFVT, VEF TAYF GFZ EMF IAT GFZ WR
VEFWG CGFRBWFZ FOFT;--FOFT IEWDE ARO MRHGMVAUWTFZ HFESUZFG ISMUZ EAJF
PWJFR VIFRVO OFAGT SC UWCF, VS XFVGWCO IWVE A IFUU-ZWGFDVFZ PMR.

AUU VEWT IAT TFFR WR A YSYFRV, AT VEF JWTWSR SC A ZGSIRWRP YAR, SG SC
ARO EMYAR DGFAVMGF AV ARO JFGO PGFAV XATT, DSMUZ TFF A ISGUZ WC WV
IFGF VEFGF. VEFO ZGFI HADK CGSY VEF IWRZSI, ARZ VEF ZSDVSG USSKFZ CSG
FQXUARAVWSR WR EWT CGWFRZ'T ATEO CADF.

“VEFO AGF,” YG. USGGO IEWTXFGFZ VEF ISGZT, PUARDWRP CFAGCMUUO GSMRZ AV
VEF USDKFZ GSSY, “YMGZFGWRP VEF XGWTSRFGT. WC OSM AGF TMGF SC IEAV OSM
TAO; WC OSM GFAUUO EAJF VEF XSIFG OSM VEWRK OSM EAJF--AT W HFUWFJF OSM
EAJF--YAKF OSMGTFUC KRSIR VS VEFTF ZFJWUT, ARZ PFV VAKFR VS UA CSGDF. WV
YAO HF VSS UAVF, W ZSR'V KRSI, HMV UFV WV RSV HF A YWRMVF UAVFG!”

ZSDVSG YARFVVF XGFTTFZ EWT EARZ, EATVFRFZ HAGFEFAZFZ SMV SC VEF GSSY,
ARZ IAT WR VEF DSMGVOAGZ IEFR YG. USGGO GFPAWRFZ VEF HUWRZ.

EWT TVGFAYWRP IEWVF EAWG, EWT GFYAGKAHUF CADF, ARZ VEF WYXFVMSMT
DSRCWZFRDF SC EWT YARRFG, AT EF XMV VEF IFAXSRT ATWZF UWKF IAVFG,
DAGGWFZ EWY WR AR WRTVARV VS VEF EFAGV SC VEF DSRDSMGTF AV VEF TVSRF.
CSG A CFI YSYFRVT VEFGF IAT A XAMTF, ARZ A EMGGO, ARZ A YMGYMG, ARZ
VEF MRWRVFUUWPWHUF TSMRZ SC EWT JSWDF; ARZ VEFR YG. USGGO TAI EWY,
TMGGSMRZFZ HO AUU, ARZ WR VEF YWZTV SC A UWRF SC VIFRVO YFR USRP, AUU
UWRKFZ TESMUZFG VS TESMUZFG, ARZ EARZ VS TESMUZFG, EMGGWFZ SMV IWVE
DGWFT SC--“UWJF VEF HATVWUUF XGWTSRFG! EFUX CSG VEF HATVWUUF XGWTSRFG'T
KWRZGFZ WR UA CSGDF! GSSY CSG VEF HATVWUUF XGWTSRFG WR CGSRV VEFGF! TAJF
VEF XGWTSRFG FJGFYSRZF AV UA CSGDF!” ARZ A VESMTARZ ARTIFGWRP TESMVT.

EF DUSTFZ VEF UAVVWDF APAWR IWVE A CUMVVFGWRP EFAGV, DUSTFZ VEF IWRZSI
ARZ VEF DMGVAWR, EATVFRFZ VS UMDWF, ARZ VSUZ EFG VEAV EFG CAVEFG IAT
ATTWTVFZ HO VEF XFSXUF, ARZ PSRF WR TFAGDE SC EFG EMTHARZ. EF CSMRZ
EFG DEWUZ ARZ YWTT XGSTT IWVE EFG; HMV, WV RFJFG SDDMGGFZ VS EWY VS HF
TMGXGWTFZ HO VEFWG AXXFAGARDF MRVWU A USRP VWYF ACVFGIAGZT, IEFR EF TAV
IAVDEWRP VEFY WR TMDE NMWFV AT VEF RWPEV KRFI.

UMDWF EAZ, HO VEAV VWYF, CAUUFR WRVS A TVMXSG SR VEF CUSSG AV EWT CFFV,
DUWRPWRP VS EWT EARZ. YWTT XGSTT EAZ UAWZ VEF DEWUZ ZSIR SR EWT SIR
HFZ, ARZ EFG EFAZ EAZ PGAZMAUUO CAUUFR SR VEF XWUUSI HFTWZF EFG XGFVVO
DEAGPF. S VEF USRP, USRP RWPEV, IWVE VEF YSART SC VEF XSSG IWCF! ARZ S
VEF USRP, USRP RWPEV, IWVE RS GFVMGR SC EFG CAVEFG ARZ RS VWZWRPT!

VIWDF YSGF WR VEF ZAGKRFTT VEF HFUU AV VEF PGFAV PAVF TSMRZFZ, ARZ VEF
WGGMXVWSR IAT GFXFAVFZ, ARZ VEF PGWRZTVSRF IEWGUFZ ARZ TXUMVVFGFZ.
“IEAV WT WV?” DGWFZ UMDWF, ACCGWPEVFZ. “EMTE! VEF TSUZWFGT' TISGZT AGF
TEAGXFRFZ VEFGF,” TAWZ YG. USGGO. “VEF XUADF WT RAVWSRAU XGSXFGVO RSI,
ARZ MTFZ AT A KWRZ SC AGYSMGO, YO USJF.”

VIWDF YSGF WR AUU; HMV, VEF UATV TXFUU SC ISGK IAT CFFHUF ARZ CWVCMU.
TSSR ACVFGIAGZT VEF ZAO HFPAR VS ZAIR, ARZ EF TSCVUO ZFVADEFZ EWYTFUC
CGSY VEF DUATXWRP EARZ, ARZ DAMVWSMTUO USSKFZ SMV APAWR. A YAR, TS
HFTYFAGFZ VEAV EF YWPEV EAJF HFFR A TSGFUO ISMRZFZ TSUZWFG DGFFXWRP HADK
VS DSRTDWSMTRFTT SR A CWFUZ SC TUAWR, IAT GWTWRP CGSY VEF XAJFYFRV HO
VEF TWZF SC VEF PGWRZTVSRF, ARZ USSKWRP AHSMV EWY IWVE A JADARV AWG.
TESGVUO, VEWT ISGR-SMV YMGZFGFG ZFTDGWFZ WR VEF WYXFGCFDV UWPEV SRF SC
VEF DAGGWAPFT SC YSRTFWPRFMG, ARZ, TVAPPFGWRP VS VEAV PSGPFSMT JFEWDUF,
DUWYHFZ WR AV VEF ZSSG, ARZ TEMV EWYTFUC MX VS VAKF EWT GFTV SR WVT
ZAWRVO DMTEWSRT.

VEF PGFAV PGWRZTVSRF, FAGVE, EAZ VMGRFZ IEFR YG. USGGO USSKFZ SMV APAWR,
ARZ VEF TMR IAT GFZ SR VEF DSMGVOAGZ. HMV, VEF UFTTFG PGWRZTVSRF TVSSZ
AUSRF VEFGF WR VEF DAUY YSGRWRP AWG, IWVE A GFZ MXSR WV VEAV VEF TMR EAZ
RFJFG PWJFR, ARZ ISMUZ RFJFG VAKF AIAO.




WWW. VEF TEAZSI


SRF SC VEF CWGTV DSRTWZFGAVWSRT IEWDE AGSTF WR VEF HMTWRFTT YWRZ SC YG.
USGGO IEFR HMTWRFTT ESMGT DAYF GSMRZ, IAT VEWT:--VEAV EF EAZ RS GWPEV VS
WYXFGWU VFUUTSR'T HO TEFUVFGWRP VEF IWCF SC AR FYWPGARV XGWTSRFG MRZFG
VEF HARK GSSC. EWT SIR XSTTFTTWSRT, TACFVO, UWCF, EF ISMUZ EAJF EABAGZFZ
CSG UMDWF ARZ EFG DEWUZ, IWVESMV A YSYFRV'T ZFYMG; HMV VEF PGFAV VGMTV
EF EFUZ IAT RSV EWT SIR, ARZ AT VS VEAV HMTWRFTT DEAGPF EF IAT A TVGWDV
YAR SC HMTWRFTT.

AV CWGTV, EWT YWRZ GFJFGVFZ VS ZFCAGPF, ARZ EF VESMPEV SC CWRZWRP SMV
VEF IWRF-TESX APAWR ARZ VAKWRP DSMRTFU IWVE WVT YATVFG WR GFCFGFRDF VS
VEF TACFTV ZIFUUWRP-XUADF WR VEF ZWTVGADVFZ TVAVF SC VEF DWVO. HMV, VEF
TAYF DSRTWZFGAVWSR VEAV TMPPFTVFZ EWY, GFXMZWAVFZ EWY; EF UWJFZ WR VEF
YSTV JWSUFRV NMAGVFG, ARZ ZSMHVUFTT IAT WRCUMFRVWAU VEFGF, ARZ ZFFX WR
WVT ZARPFGSMT ISGKWRPT.

RSSR DSYWRP, ARZ VEF ZSDVSG RSV GFVMGRWRP, ARZ FJFGO YWRMVF'T ZFUAO
VFRZWRP VS DSYXGSYWTF VFUUTSR'T, YG. USGGO AZJWTFZ IWVE UMDWF. TEF TAWZ
VEAV EFG CAVEFG EAZ TXSKFR SC EWGWRP A USZPWRP CSG A TESGV VFGY, WR VEAV
NMAGVFG, RFAG VEF HARKWRP-ESMTF. AT VEFGF IAT RS HMTWRFTT SHLFDVWSR VS
VEWT, ARZ AT EF CSGFTAI VEAV FJFR WC WV IFGF AUU IFUU IWVE DEAGUFT, ARZ
EF IFGF VS HF GFUFATFZ, EF DSMUZ RSV ESXF VS UFAJF VEF DWVO, YG. USGGO
IFRV SMV WR NMFTV SC TMDE A USZPWRP, ARZ CSMRZ A TMWVAHUF SRF, EWPE MX
WR A GFYSJFZ HO-TVGFFV IEFGF VEF DUSTFZ HUWRZT WR AUU VEF SVEFG IWRZSIT
SC A EWPE YFUARDESUO TNMAGF SC HMWUZWRPT YAGKFZ ZFTFGVFZ ESYFT.

VS VEWT USZPWRP EF AV SRDF GFYSJFZ UMDWF ARZ EFG DEWUZ, ARZ YWTT XGSTT:
PWJWRP VEFY IEAV DSYCSGV EF DSMUZ, ARZ YMDE YSGF VEAR EF EAZ EWYTFUC.
EF UFCV LFGGO IWVE VEFY, AT A CWPMGF VS CWUU A ZSSGIAO VEAV ISMUZ HFAG
DSRTWZFGAHUF KRSDKWRP SR VEF EFAZ, ARZ GFVMGRFZ VS EWT SIR SDDMXAVWSRT.
A ZWTVMGHFZ ARZ ZSUFCMU YWRZ EF HGSMPEV VS HFAG MXSR VEFY, ARZ TUSIUO
ARZ EFAJWUO VEF ZAO UAPPFZ SR IWVE EWY.

WV ISGF WVTFUC SMV, ARZ ISGF EWY SMV IWVE WV, MRVWU VEF HARK DUSTFZ. EF
IAT APAWR AUSRF WR EWT GSSY SC VEF XGFJWSMT RWPEV, DSRTWZFGWRP IEAV VS
ZS RFQV, IEFR EF EFAGZ A CSSV MXSR VEF TVAWG. WR A CFI YSYFRVT, A
YAR TVSSZ WR EWT XGFTFRDF, IES, IWVE A KFFRUO SHTFGJARV USSK AV EWY,
AZZGFTTFZ EWY HO EWT RAYF.

“OSMG TFGJARV,” TAWZ YG. USGGO. “ZS OSM KRSI YF?”

EF IAT A TVGSRPUO YAZF YAR IWVE ZAGK DMGUWRP EAWG, CGSY CSGVO-CWJF
VS CWCVO OFAGT SC APF. CSG ARTIFG EF GFXFAVFZ, IWVESMV ARO DEARPF SC
FYXEATWT, VEF ISGZT:

“ZS OSM KRSI YF?”

“W EAJF TFFR OSM TSYFIEFGF.”

“XFGEAXT AV YO IWRF-TESX?”

YMDE WRVFGFTVFZ ARZ APWVAVFZ, YG. USGGO TAWZ: “OSM DSYF CGSY ZSDVSG
YARFVVF?”

“OFT. W DSYF CGSY ZSDVSG YARFVVF.”

“ARZ IEAV TAOT EF? IEAV ZSFT EF TFRZ YF?”

ZFCAGPF PAJF WRVS EWT ARQWSMT EARZ, AR SXFR TDGAX SC XAXFG. WV HSGF VEF
ISGZT WR VEF ZSDVSG'T IGWVWRP:

    “DEAGUFT WT TACF, HMV W DARRSV TACFUO UFAJF VEWT XUADF OFV.
     W EAJF SHVAWRFZ VEF CAJSMG VEAV VEF HFAGFG EAT A TESGV RSVF
     CGSY DEAGUFT VS EWT IWCF.  UFV VEF HFAGFG TFF EWT IWCF.”

WV IAT ZAVFZ CGSY UA CSGDF, IWVEWR AR ESMG.

“IWUU OSM ADDSYXARO YF,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, LSOCMUUO GFUWFJFZ ACVFG GFAZWRP
VEWT RSVF AUSMZ, “VS IEFGF EWT IWCF GFTWZFT?”

“OFT,” GFVMGRFZ ZFCAGPF.

TDAGDFUO RSVWDWRP AT OFV, WR IEAV A DMGWSMTUO GFTFGJFZ ARZ YFDEARWDAU
IAO ZFCAGPF TXSKF, YG. USGGO XMV SR EWT EAV ARZ VEFO IFRV ZSIR WRVS VEF
DSMGVOAGZ. VEFGF, VEFO CSMRZ VIS ISYFR; SRF, KRWVVWRP.

“YAZAYF ZFCAGPF, TMGFUO!” TAWZ YG. USGGO, IES EAZ UFCV EFG WR FQADVUO
VEF TAYF AVVWVMZF TSYF TFJFRVFFR OFAGT APS.

“WV WT TEF,” SHTFGJFZ EFG EMTHARZ.

“ZSFT YAZAYF PS IWVE MT?” WRNMWGFZ YG. USGGO, TFFWRP VEAV TEF YSJFZ AT
VEFO YSJFZ.

“OFT. VEAV TEF YAO HF AHUF VS GFDSPRWTF VEF CADFT ARZ KRSI VEF XFGTSRT.
WV WT CSG VEFWG TACFVO.”

HFPWRRWRP VS HF TVGMDK HO ZFCAGPF'T YARRFG, YG. USGGO USSKFZ ZMHWSMTUO
AV EWY, ARZ UFZ VEF IAO. HSVE VEF ISYFR CSUUSIFZ; VEF TFDSRZ ISYAR HFWRP
VEF JFRPFARDF.

VEFO XATTFZ VEGSMPE VEF WRVFGJFRWRP TVGFFVT AT NMWDKUO AT VEFO YWPEV,
ATDFRZFZ VEF TVAWGDATF SC VEF RFI ZSYWDWUF, IFGF AZYWVVFZ HO LFGGO,
ARZ CSMRZ UMDWF IFFXWRP, AUSRF. TEF IAT VEGSIR WRVS A VGARTXSGV HO VEF
VWZWRPT YG. USGGO PAJF EFG SC EFG EMTHARZ, ARZ DUATXFZ VEF EARZ VEAV
ZFUWJFGFZ EWT RSVF--UWVVUF VEWRKWRP IEAV WV EAZ HFFR ZSWRP RFAG EWY WR
VEF RWPEV, ARZ YWPEV, HMV CSG A DEARDF, EAJF ZSRF VS EWY.

     “ZFAGFTV,--VAKF DSMGAPF.  W AY IFUU, ARZ OSMG CAVEFG EAT
      WRCUMFRDF AGSMRZ YF.  OSM DARRSV ARTIFG VEWT.
      KWTT SMG DEWUZ CSG YF.”

VEAV IAT AUU VEF IGWVWRP. WV IAT TS YMDE, ESIFJFG, VS EFG IES GFDFWJFZ
WV, VEAV TEF VMGRFZ CGSY ZFCAGPF VS EWT IWCF, ARZ KWTTFZ SRF SC VEF
EARZT VEAV KRWVVFZ. WV IAT A XATTWSRAVF, USJWRP, VEARKCMU, ISYARUO
ADVWSR, HMV VEF EARZ YAZF RS GFTXSRTF--ZGSXXFZ DSUZ ARZ EFAJO, ARZ VSSK
VS WVT KRWVVWRP APAWR.

VEFGF IAT TSYFVEWRP WR WVT VSMDE VEAV PAJF UMDWF A DEFDK. TEF TVSXXFZ WR
VEF ADV SC XMVVWRP VEF RSVF WR EFG HSTSY, ARZ, IWVE EFG EARZT OFV AV EFG
RFDK, USSKFZ VFGGWCWFZ AV YAZAYF ZFCAGPF. YAZAYF ZFCAGPF YFV VEF UWCVFZ
FOFHGSIT ARZ CSGFEFAZ IWVE A DSUZ, WYXATTWJF TVAGF.

“YO ZFAG,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, TVGWKWRP WR VS FQXUAWR; “VEFGF AGF CGFNMFRV
GWTWRPT WR VEF TVGFFVT; ARZ, AUVESMPE WV WT RSV UWKFUO VEFO IWUU FJFG
VGSMHUF OSM, YAZAYF ZFCAGPF IWTEFT VS TFF VESTF IESY TEF EAT VEF XSIFG
VS XGSVFDV AV TMDE VWYFT, VS VEF FRZ VEAV TEF YAO KRSI VEFY--VEAV TEF
YAO WZFRVWCO VEFY. W HFUWFJF,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, GAVEFG EAUVWRP WR EWT
GFATTMGWRP ISGZT, AT VEF TVSRO YARRFG SC AUU VEF VEGFF WYXGFTTFZ WVTFUC
MXSR EWY YSGF ARZ YSGF, “W TVAVF VEF DATF, DWVWBFR ZFCAGPF?”

ZFCAGPF USSKFZ PUSSYWUO AV EWT IWCF, ARZ PAJF RS SVEFG ARTIFG VEAR A
PGMCC TSMRZ SC ADNMWFTDFRDF.

“OSM EAZ HFVVFG, UMDWF,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, ZSWRP AUU EF DSMUZ VS
XGSXWVWAVF, HO VSRF ARZ YARRFG, “EAJF VEF ZFAG DEWUZ EFGF, ARZ SMG
PSSZ XGSTT. SMG PSSZ XGSTT, ZFCAGPF, WT AR FRPUWTE UAZO, ARZ KRSIT RS
CGFRDE.”

VEF UAZO WR NMFTVWSR, IESTF GSSVFZ DSRJWDVWSR VEAV TEF IAT YSGF VEAR A
YAVDE CSG ARO CSGFWPRFG, IAT RSV VS HF TEAKFR HO ZWTVGFTT ARZ, ZARPFG,
AXXFAGFZ IWVE CSUZFZ AGYT, ARZ SHTFGJFZ WR FRPUWTE VS VEF JFRPFARDF,
IESY EFG FOFT CWGTV FRDSMRVFGFZ, “IFUU, W AY TMGF, HSUZCADF! W ESXF
_OSM_ AGF XGFVVO IFUU!” TEF AUTS HFTVSIFZ A HGWVWTE DSMPE SR YAZAYF
ZFCAGPF; HMV, RFWVEFG SC VEF VIS VSSK YMDE EFFZ SC EFG.

“WT VEAV EWT DEWUZ?” TAWZ YAZAYF ZFCAGPF, TVSXXWRP WR EFG ISGK CSG VEF
CWGTV VWYF, ARZ XSWRVWRP EFG KRWVVWRP-RFFZUF AV UWVVUF UMDWF AT WC WV
IFGF VEF CWRPFG SC CAVF.

“OFT, YAZAYF,” ARTIFGFZ YG. USGGO; “VEWT WT SMG XSSG XGWTSRFG'T ZAGUWRP
ZAMPEVFG, ARZ SRUO DEWUZ.”

VEF TEAZSI AVVFRZARV SR YAZAYF ZFCAGPF ARZ EFG XAGVO TFFYFZ VS CAUU TS
VEGFAVFRWRP ARZ ZAGK SR VEF DEWUZ, VEAV EFG YSVEFG WRTVWRDVWJFUO
KRFFUFZ SR VEF PGSMRZ HFTWZF EFG, ARZ EFUZ EFG VS EFG HGFATV. VEF
TEAZSI AVVFRZARV SR YAZAYF ZFCAGPF ARZ EFG XAGVO TFFYFZ VEFR VS CAUU,
VEGFAVFRWRP ARZ ZAGK, SR HSVE VEF YSVEFG ARZ VEF DEWUZ.

“WV WT FRSMPE, YO EMTHARZ,” TAWZ YAZAYF ZFCAGPF. “W EAJF TFFR VEFY. IF
YAO PS.”

HMV, VEF TMXXGFTTFZ YARRFG EAZ FRSMPE SC YFRADF WR WV--RSV JWTWHUF ARZ
XGFTFRVFZ, HMV WRZWTVWRDV ARZ IWVEEFUZ--VS AUAGY UMDWF WRVS TAOWRP, AT
TEF UAWZ EFG AXXFAUWRP EARZ SR YAZAYF ZFCAGPF'T ZGFTT:

“OSM IWUU HF PSSZ VS YO XSSG EMTHARZ. OSM IWUU ZS EWY RS EAGY. OSM IWUU
EFUX YF VS TFF EWY WC OSM DAR?”

“OSMG EMTHARZ WT RSV YO HMTWRFTT EFGF,” GFVMGRFZ YAZAYF ZFCAGPF, USSKWRP
ZSIR AV EFG IWVE XFGCFDV DSYXSTMGF. “WV WT VEF ZAMPEVFG SC OSMG CAVEFG
IES WT YO HMTWRFTT EFGF.”

“CSG YO TAKF, VEFR, HF YFGDWCMU VS YO EMTHARZ. CSG YO DEWUZ'T TAKF! TEF
IWUU XMV EFG EARZT VSPFVEFG ARZ XGAO OSM VS HF YFGDWCMU. IF AGF YSGF
ACGAWZ SC OSM VEAR SC VEFTF SVEFGT.”

YAZAYF ZFCAGPF GFDFWJFZ WV AT A DSYXUWYFRV, ARZ USSKFZ AV EFG EMTHARZ.
ZFCAGPF, IES EAZ HFFR MRFATWUO HWVWRP EWT VEMYH-RAWU ARZ USSKWRP AV EFG,
DSUUFDVFZ EWT CADF WRVS A TVFGRFG FQXGFTTWSR.

“IEAV WT WV VEAV OSMG EMTHARZ TAOT WR VEAV UWVVUF UFVVFG?” ATKFZ YAZAYF
ZFCAGPF, IWVE A USIFGWRP TYWUF. “WRCUMFRDF; EF TAOT TSYFVEWRP VSMDEWRP
WRCUMFRDF?”

“VEAV YO CAVEFG,” TAWZ UMDWF, EMGGWFZUO VAKWRP VEF XAXFG CGSY EFG
HGFATV, HMV IWVE EFG AUAGYFZ FOFT SR EFG NMFTVWSRFG ARZ RSV SR WV, “EAT
YMDE WRCUMFRDF AGSMRZ EWY.”

“TMGFUO WV IWUU GFUFATF EWY!” TAWZ YAZAYF ZFCAGPF. “UFV WV ZS TS.”

“AT A IWCF ARZ YSVEFG,” DGWFZ UMDWF, YSTV FAGRFTVUO, “W WYXUSGF OSM VS
EAJF XWVO SR YF ARZ RSV VS FQFGDWTF ARO XSIFG VEAV OSM XSTTFTT, APAWRTV
YO WRRSDFRV EMTHARZ, HMV VS MTF WV WR EWT HFEAUC. S TWTVFG-ISYAR, VEWRK
SC YF. AT A IWCF ARZ YSVEFG!”

YAZAYF ZFCAGPF USSKFZ, DSUZUO AT FJFG, AV VEF TMXXUWARV, ARZ TAWZ,
VMGRWRP VS EFG CGWFRZ VEF JFRPFARDF:

“VEF IWJFT ARZ YSVEFGT IF EAJF HFFR MTFZ VS TFF, TWRDF IF IFGF AT UWVVUF
AT VEWT DEWUZ, ARZ YMDE UFTT, EAJF RSV HFFR PGFAVUO DSRTWZFGFZ? IF EAJF
KRSIR _VEFWG_ EMTHARZT ARZ CAVEFGT UAWZ WR XGWTSR ARZ KFXV CGSY VEFY,
SCVFR FRSMPE? AUU SMG UWJFT, IF EAJF TFFR SMG TWTVFG-ISYFR TMCCFG, WR
VEFYTFUJFT ARZ WR VEFWG DEWUZGFR, XSJFGVO, RAKFZRFTT, EMRPFG, VEWGTV,
TWDKRFTT, YWTFGO, SXXGFTTWSR ARZ RFPUFDV SC AUU KWRZT?”

“IF EAJF TFFR RSVEWRP FUTF,” GFVMGRFZ VEF JFRPFARDF.

“IF EAJF HSGRF VEWT A USRP VWYF,” TAWZ YAZAYF ZFCAGPF, VMGRWRP EFG FOFT
APAWR MXSR UMDWF. “LMZPF OSM! WT WV UWKFUO VEAV VEF VGSMHUF SC SRF IWCF
ARZ YSVEFG ISMUZ HF YMDE VS MT RSI?”

TEF GFTMYFZ EFG KRWVVWRP ARZ IFRV SMV. VEF JFRPFARDF CSUUSIFZ. ZFCAGPF
IFRV UATV, ARZ DUSTFZ VEF ZSSG.

“DSMGAPF, YO ZFAG UMDWF,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, AT EF GAWTFZ EFG. “DSMGAPF,
DSMGAPF! TS CAG AUU PSFT IFUU IWVE MT--YMDE, YMDE HFVVFG VEAR WV EAT SC
UAVF PSRF IWVE YARO XSSG TSMUT. DEFFG MX, ARZ EAJF A VEARKCMU EFAGV.”

“W AY RSV VEARKUFTT, W ESXF, HMV VEAV ZGFAZCMU ISYAR TFFYT VS VEGSI A
TEAZSI SR YF ARZ SR AUU YO ESXFT.”

“VMV, VMV!” TAWZ YG. USGGO; “IEAV WT VEWT ZFTXSRZFRDO WR VEF HGAJF
UWVVUF HGFATV? A TEAZSI WRZFFZ! RS TMHTVARDF WR WV, UMDWF.”

HMV VEF TEAZSI SC VEF YARRFG SC VEFTF ZFCAGPFT IAT ZAGK MXSR EWYTFUC,
CSG AUU VEAV, ARZ WR EWT TFDGFV YWRZ WV VGSMHUFZ EWY PGFAVUO.




WJ. DAUY WR TVSGY


ZSDVSG YARFVVF ZWZ RSV GFVMGR MRVWU VEF YSGRWRP SC VEF CSMGVE ZAO SC EWT
AHTFRDF. TS YMDE SC IEAV EAZ EAXXFRFZ WR VEAV ZGFAZCMU VWYF AT DSMUZ HF
KFXV CGSY VEF KRSIUFZPF SC UMDWF IAT TS IFUU DSRDFAUFZ CGSY EFG, VEAV
RSV MRVWU USRP ACVFGIAGZT, IEFR CGARDF ARZ TEF IFGF CAG AXAGV, ZWZ TEF
KRSI VEAV FUFJFR EMRZGFZ ZFCFRDFUFTT XGWTSRFGT SC HSVE TFQFT ARZ AUU
APFT EAZ HFFR KWUUFZ HO VEF XSXMUADF; VEAV CSMG ZAOT ARZ RWPEVT EAZ HFFR
ZAGKFRFZ HO VEWT ZFFZ SC ESGGSG; ARZ VEAV VEF AWG AGSMRZ EFG EAZ HFFR
VAWRVFZ HO VEF TUAWR. TEF SRUO KRFI VEAV VEFGF EAZ HFFR AR AVVADK MXSR
VEF XGWTSRT, VEAV AUU XSUWVWDAU XGWTSRFGT EAZ HFFR WR ZARPFG, ARZ VEAV
TSYF EAZ HFFR ZGAPPFZ SMV HO VEF DGSIZ ARZ YMGZFGFZ.

VS YG. USGGO, VEF ZSDVSG DSYYMRWDAVFZ MRZFG AR WRLMRDVWSR SC TFDGFDO SR
IEWDE EF EAZ RS RFFZ VS ZIFUU, VEAV VEF DGSIZ EAZ VAKFR EWY VEGSMPE A
TDFRF SC DAGRAPF VS VEF XGWTSR SC UA CSGDF. VEAV, WR VEF XGWTSR EF EAZ
CSMRZ A TFUC-AXXSWRVFZ VGWHMRAU TWVVWRP, HFCSGF IEWDE VEF XGWTSRFGT IFGF
HGSMPEV TWRPUO, ARZ HO IEWDE VEFO IFGF GAXWZUO SGZFGFZ VS HF XMV CSGVE
VS HF YATTADGFZ, SG VS HF GFUFATFZ, SG (WR A CFI DATFT) VS HF TFRV HADK
VS VEFWG DFUUT. VEAV, XGFTFRVFZ HO EWT DSRZMDVSGT VS VEWT VGWHMRAU, EF
EAZ ARRSMRDFZ EWYTFUC HO RAYF ARZ XGSCFTTWSR AT EAJWRP HFFR CSG FWPEVFFR
OFAGT A TFDGFV ARZ MRADDMTFZ XGWTSRFG WR VEF HATVWUUF; VEAV, SRF SC VEF
HSZO TS TWVVWRP WR LMZPYFRV EAZ GWTFR ARZ WZFRVWCWFZ EWY, ARZ VEAV VEWT
YAR IAT ZFCAGPF.

VEAV, EFGFMXSR EF EAZ ATDFGVAWRFZ, VEGSMPE VEF GFPWTVFGT SR VEF VAHUF,
VEAV EWT TSR-WR-UAI IAT AYSRP VEF UWJWRP XGWTSRFGT, ARZ EAZ XUFAZFZ EAGZ
VS VEF VGWHMRAU--SC IESY TSYF YFYHFGT IFGF ATUFFX ARZ TSYF AIAKF, TSYF
ZWGVO IWVE YMGZFG ARZ TSYF DUFAR, TSYF TSHFG ARZ TSYF RSV--CSG EWT UWCF
ARZ UWHFGVO. VEAV, WR VEF CWGTV CGARVWD PGFFVWRPT UAJWTEFZ SR EWYTFUC AT
A RSVAHUF TMCCFGFG MRZFG VEF SJFGVEGSIR TOTVFY, WV EAZ HFFR ADDSGZFZ
VS EWY VS EAJF DEAGUFT ZAGRAO HGSMPEV HFCSGF VEF UAIUFTT DSMGV, ARZ
FQAYWRFZ. VEAV, EF TFFYFZ SR VEF XSWRV SC HFWRP AV SRDF GFUFATFZ, IEFR
VEF VWZF WR EWT CAJSMG YFV IWVE TSYF MRFQXUAWRFZ DEFDK (RSV WRVFUUWPWHUF
VS VEF ZSDVSG), IEWDE UFZ VS A CFI ISGZT SC TFDGFV DSRCFGFRDF. VEAV,
VEF YAR TWVVWRP AT XGFTWZFRV EAZ VEFR WRCSGYFZ ZSDVSG YARFVVF VEAV
VEF XGWTSRFG YMTV GFYAWR WR DMTVSZO, HMV TESMUZ, CSG EWT TAKF, HF EFUZ
WRJWSUAVF WR TACF DMTVSZO. VEAV, WYYFZWAVFUO, SR A TWPRAU, VEF XGWTSRFG
IAT GFYSJFZ VS VEF WRVFGWSG SC VEF XGWTSR APAWR; HMV, VEAV EF, VEF
ZSDVSG, EAZ VEFR TS TVGSRPUO XUFAZFZ CSG XFGYWTTWSR VS GFYAWR ARZ
ATTMGF EWYTFUC VEAV EWT TSR-WR-UAI IAT, VEGSMPE RS YAUWDF SG YWTDEARDF,
ZFUWJFGFZ VS VEF DSRDSMGTF IESTF YMGZFGSMT OFUUT SMVTWZF VEF PAVF EAZ
SCVFR ZGSIRFZ VEF XGSDFFZWRPT, VEAV EF EAZ SHVAWRFZ VEF XFGYWTTWSR, ARZ
EAZ GFYAWRFZ WR VEAV EAUU SC HUSSZ MRVWU VEF ZARPFG IAT SJFG.

VEF TWPEVT EF EAZ TFFR VEFGF, IWVE HGWFC TRAVDEFT SC CSSZ ARZ TUFFX HO
WRVFGJAUT, TEAUU GFYAWR MRVSUZ. VEF YAZ LSO SJFG VEF XGWTSRFGT IES IFGF
TAJFZ, EAZ ATVSMRZFZ EWY TDAGDFUO UFTT VEAR VEF YAZ CFGSDWVO APAWRTV
VESTF IES IFGF DMV VS XWFDFT. SRF XGWTSRFG VEFGF IAT, EF TAWZ, IES EAZ
HFFR ZWTDEAGPFZ WRVS VEF TVGFFV CGFF, HMV AV IESY A YWTVAKFR TAJAPF EAZ
VEGMTV A XWKF AT EF XATTFZ SMV. HFWRP HFTSMPEV VS PS VS EWY ARZ ZGFTT
VEF ISMRZ, VEF ZSDVSG EAZ XATTFZ SMV AV VEF TAYF PAVF, ARZ EAZ CSMRZ EWY
WR VEF AGYT SC A DSYXARO SC TAYAGWVART, IES IFGF TFAVFZ SR VEF HSZWFT
SC VEFWG JWDVWYT. IWVE AR WRDSRTWTVFRDO AT YSRTVGSMT AT AROVEWRP WR VEWT
AICMU RWPEVYAGF, VEFO EAZ EFUXFZ VEF EFAUFG, ARZ VFRZFZ VEF ISMRZFZ YAR
IWVE VEF PFRVUFTV TSUWDWVMZF--EAZ YAZF A UWVVFG CSG EWY ARZ FTDSGVFZ EWY
DAGFCMUUO CGSY VEF TXSV--EAZ VEFR DAMPEV MX VEFWG IFAXSRT ARZ XUMRPFZ
ARFI WRVS A HMVDEFGO TS ZGFAZCMU, VEAV VEF ZSDVSG EAZ DSJFGFZ EWT FOFT
IWVE EWT EARZT, ARZ TISSRFZ AIAO WR VEF YWZTV SC WV.

AT YG. USGGO GFDFWJFZ VEFTF DSRCWZFRDFT, ARZ AT EF IAVDEFZ VEF CADF SC
EWT CGWFRZ RSI TWQVO-VIS OFAGT SC APF, A YWTPWJWRP AGSTF IWVEWR EWY VEAV
TMDE ZGFAZ FQXFGWFRDFT ISMUZ GFJWJF VEF SUZ ZARPFG.

HMV, EF EAZ RFJFG TFFR EWT CGWFRZ WR EWT XGFTFRV ATXFDV: EF EAZ RFJFG
AV AUU KRSIR EWY WR EWT XGFTFRV DEAGADVFG. CSG VEF CWGTV VWYF VEF ZSDVSG
CFUV, RSI, VEAV EWT TMCCFGWRP IAT TVGFRPVE ARZ XSIFG. CSG VEF CWGTV VWYF
EF CFUV VEAV WR VEAV TEAGX CWGF, EF EAZ TUSIUO CSGPFZ VEF WGSR IEWDE
DSMUZ HGFAK VEF XGWTSR ZSSG SC EWT ZAMPEVFG'T EMTHARZ, ARZ ZFUWJFG EWY.
“WV AUU VFRZFZ VS A PSSZ FRZ, YO CGWFRZ; WV IAT RSV YFGF IATVF ARZ GMWR.
AT YO HFUSJFZ DEWUZ IAT EFUXCMU WR GFTVSGWRP YF VS YOTFUC, W IWUU HF
EFUXCMU RSI WR GFTVSGWRP VEF ZFAGFTV XAGV SC EFGTFUC VS EFG; HO VEF AWZ
SC EFAJFR W IWUU ZS WV!” VEMT, ZSDVSG YARFVVF. ARZ IEFR LAGJWT USGGO TAI
VEF KWRZUFZ FOFT, VEF GFTSUMVF CADF, VEF DAUY TVGSRP USSK ARZ HFAGWRP
SC VEF YAR IESTF UWCF AUIAOT TFFYFZ VS EWY VS EAJF HFFR TVSXXFZ, UWKF A
DUSDK, CSG TS YARO OFAGT, ARZ VEFR TFV PSWRP APAWR IWVE AR FRFGPO IEWDE
EAZ UAWR ZSGYARV ZMGWRP VEF DFTTAVWSR SC WVT MTFCMURFTT, EF HFUWFJFZ.

PGFAVFG VEWRPT VEAR VEF ZSDVSG EAZ AV VEAV VWYF VS DSRVFRZ IWVE, ISMUZ
EAJF OWFUZFZ HFCSGF EWT XFGTFJFGWRP XMGXSTF. IEWUF EF KFXV EWYTFUC
WR EWT XUADF, AT A XEOTWDWAR, IESTF HMTWRFTT IAT IWVE AUU ZFPGFFT
SC YARKWRZ, HSRZ ARZ CGFF, GWDE ARZ XSSG, HAZ ARZ PSSZ, EF MTFZ EWT
XFGTSRAU WRCUMFRDF TS IWTFUO, VEAV EF IAT TSSR VEF WRTXFDVWRP XEOTWDWAR
SC VEGFF XGWTSRT, ARZ AYSRP VEFY SC UA CSGDF. EF DSMUZ RSI ATTMGF UMDWF
VEAV EFG EMTHARZ IAT RS USRPFG DSRCWRFZ AUSRF, HMV IAT YWQFZ IWVE VEF
PFRFGAU HSZO SC XGWTSRFGT; EF TAI EFG EMTHARZ IFFKUO, ARZ HGSMPEV TIFFV
YFTTAPFT VS EFG, TVGAWPEV CGSY EWT UWXT; TSYFVWYFT EFG EMTHARZ EWYTFUC
TFRV A UFVVFG VS EFG (VESMPE RFJFG HO VEF ZSDVSG'T EARZ), HMV TEF IAT
RSV XFGYWVVFZ VS IGWVF VS EWY: CSG, AYSRP VEF YARO IWUZ TMTXWDWSRT SC
XUSVT WR VEF XGWTSRT, VEF IWUZFTV SC AUU XSWRVFZ AV FYWPGARVT IES IFGF
KRSIR VS EAJF YAZF CGWFRZT SG XFGYARFRV DSRRFDVWSRT AHGSAZ.

VEWT RFI UWCF SC VEF ZSDVSG'T IAT AR ARQWSMT UWCF, RS ZSMHV; TVWUU, VEF
TAPADWSMT YG. USGGO TAI VEAV VEFGF IAT A RFI TMTVAWRWRP XGWZF WR WV.
RSVEWRP MRHFDSYWRP VWRPFZ VEF XGWZF; WV IAT A RAVMGAU ARZ ISGVEO SRF;
HMV EF SHTFGJFZ WV AT A DMGWSTWVO. VEF ZSDVSG KRFI, VEAV MX VS VEAV
VWYF, EWT WYXGWTSRYFRV EAZ HFFR ATTSDWAVFZ WR VEF YWRZT SC EWT ZAMPEVFG
ARZ EWT CGWFRZ, IWVE EWT XFGTSRAU ACCUWDVWSR, ZFXGWJAVWSR, ARZ IFAKRFTT.
RSI VEAV VEWT IAT DEARPFZ, ARZ EF KRFI EWYTFUC VS HF WRJFTVFZ VEGSMPE
VEAV SUZ VGWAU IWVE CSGDFT VS IEWDE VEFO HSVE USSKFZ CSG DEAGUFT'T
MUVWYAVF TACFVO ARZ ZFUWJFGARDF, EF HFDAYF TS CAG FQAUVFZ HO VEF DEARPF,
VEAV EF VSSK VEF UFAZ ARZ ZWGFDVWSR, ARZ GFNMWGFZ VEFY AT VEF IFAK, VS
VGMTV VS EWY AT VEF TVGSRP. VEF XGFDFZWRP GFUAVWJF XSTWVWSRT SC EWYTFUC
ARZ UMDWF IFGF GFJFGTFZ, OFV SRUO AT VEF UWJFUWFTV PGAVWVMZF ARZ
ACCFDVWSR DSMUZ GFJFGTF VEFY, CSG EF DSMUZ EAJF EAZ RS XGWZF HMV WR
GFRZFGWRP TSYF TFGJWDF VS EFG IES EAZ GFRZFGFZ TS YMDE VS EWY. “AUU
DMGWSMT VS TFF,” VESMPEV YG. USGGO, WR EWT AYWAHUO TEGFIZ IAO, “HMV AUU
RAVMGAU ARZ GWPEV; TS, VAKF VEF UFAZ, YO ZFAG CGWFRZ, ARZ KFFX WV; WV
DSMUZR'V HF WR HFVVFG EARZT.”

HMV, VESMPE VEF ZSDVSG VGWFZ EAGZ, ARZ RFJFG DFATFZ VGOWRP, VS PFV
DEAGUFT ZAGRAO TFV AV UWHFGVO, SG AV UFATV VS PFV EWY HGSMPEV VS VGWAU,
VEF XMHUWD DMGGFRV SC VEF VWYF TFV VSS TVGSRP ARZ CATV CSG EWY. VEF RFI
FGA HFPAR; VEF KWRP IAT VGWFZ, ZSSYFZ, ARZ HFEFAZFZ; VEF GFXMHUWD SC
UWHFGVO, FNMAUWVO, CGAVFGRWVO, SG ZFAVE, ZFDUAGFZ CSG JWDVSGO SG ZFAVE
APAWRTV VEF ISGUZ WR AGYT; VEF HUADK CUAP IAJFZ RWPEV ARZ ZAO CGSY VEF
PGFAV VSIFGT SC RSVGF ZAYF; VEGFF EMRZGFZ VESMTARZ YFR, TMYYSRFZ VS GWTF
APAWRTV VEF VOGARVT SC VEF FAGVE, GSTF CGSY AUU VEF JAGOWRP TSWUT
SC CGARDF, AT WC VEF ZGAPSR'T VFFVE EAZ HFFR TSIR HGSAZDATV, ARZ
EAZ OWFUZFZ CGMWV FNMAUUO SR EWUU ARZ XUAWR, SR GSDK, WR PGAJFU, ARZ
AUUMJWAU YMZ, MRZFG VEF HGWPEV TKO SC VEF TSMVE ARZ MRZFG VEF DUSMZT SC
VEF RSGVE, WR CFUU ARZ CSGFTV, WR VEF JWRFOAGZT ARZ VEF SUWJF-PGSMRZT
ARZ AYSRP VEF DGSXXFZ PGATT ARZ VEF TVMHHUF SC VEF DSGR, AUSRP VEF
CGMWVCMU HARKT SC VEF HGSAZ GWJFGT, ARZ WR VEF TARZ SC VEF TFA-TESGF.
IEAV XGWJAVF TSUWDWVMZF DSMUZ GFAG WVTFUC APAWRTV VEF ZFUMPF SC VEF OFAG
SRF SC UWHFGVO--VEF ZFUMPF GWTWRP CGSY HFUSI, RSV CAUUWRP CGSY AHSJF,
ARZ IWVE VEF IWRZSIT SC EFAJFR TEMV, RSV SXFRFZ!

VEFGF IAT RS XAMTF, RS XWVO, RS XFADF, RS WRVFGJAU SC GFUFRVWRP GFTV, RS
YFATMGFYFRV SC VWYF. VESMPE ZAOT ARZ RWPEVT DWGDUFZ AT GFPMUAGUO AT IEFR
VWYF IAT OSMRP, ARZ VEF FJFRWRP ARZ YSGRWRP IFGF VEF CWGTV ZAO, SVEFG
DSMRV SC VWYF VEFGF IAT RSRF. ESUZ SC WV IAT USTV WR VEF GAPWRP CFJFG
SC A RAVWSR, AT WV WT WR VEF CFJFG SC SRF XAVWFRV. RSI, HGFAKWRP VEF
MRRAVMGAU TWUFRDF SC A IESUF DWVO, VEF FQFDMVWSRFG TESIFZ VEF XFSXUF VEF
EFAZ SC VEF KWRP--ARZ RSI, WV TFFYFZ AUYSTV WR VEF TAYF HGFAVE, VEF
EFAZ SC EWT CAWG IWCF IEWDE EAZ EAZ FWPEV IFAGO YSRVET SC WYXGWTSRFZ
IWZSIESSZ ARZ YWTFGO, VS VMGR WV PGFO.

ARZ OFV, SHTFGJWRP VEF TVGARPF UAI SC DSRVGAZWDVWSR IEWDE SHVAWRT WR
AUU TMDE DATFT, VEF VWYF IAT USRP, IEWUF WV CUAYFZ HO TS CATV. A
GFJSUMVWSRAGO VGWHMRAU WR VEF DAXWVAU, ARZ CSGVO SG CWCVO VESMTARZ
GFJSUMVWSRAGO DSYYWVVFFT AUU SJFG VEF UARZ; A UAI SC VEF TMTXFDVFZ,
IEWDE TVGMDK AIAO AUU TFDMGWVO CSG UWHFGVO SG UWCF, ARZ ZFUWJFGFZ SJFG
ARO PSSZ ARZ WRRSDFRV XFGTSR VS ARO HAZ ARZ PMWUVO SRF; XGWTSRT PSGPFZ
IWVE XFSXUF IES EAZ DSYYWVVFZ RS SCCFRDF, ARZ DSMUZ SHVAWR RS EFAGWRP;
VEFTF VEWRPT HFDAYF VEF FTVAHUWTEFZ SGZFG ARZ RAVMGF SC AXXSWRVFZ
VEWRPT, ARZ TFFYFZ VS HF ARDWFRV MTAPF HFCSGF VEFO IFGF YARO IFFKT SUZ.
AHSJF AUU, SRF EWZFSMT CWPMGF PGFI AT CAYWUWAG AT WC WV EAZ HFFR HFCSGF
VEF PFRFGAU PABF CGSY VEF CSMRZAVWSRT SC VEF ISGUZ--VEF CWPMGF SC VEF
TEAGX CFYAUF DAUUFZ UA PMWUUSVWRF.

WV IAT VEF XSXMUAG VEFYF CSG LFTVT; WV IAT VEF HFTV DMGF CSG EFAZADEF,
WV WRCAUUWHUO XGFJFRVFZ VEF EAWG CGSY VMGRWRP PGFO, WV WYXAGVFZ A
XFDMUWAG ZFUWDADO VS VEF DSYXUFQWSR, WV IAT VEF RAVWSRAU GABSG IEWDE
TEAJFZ DUSTF: IES KWTTFZ UA PMWUUSVWRF, USSKFZ VEGSMPE VEF UWVVUF IWRZSI
ARZ TRFFBFZ WRVS VEF TADK. WV IAT VEF TWPR SC VEF GFPFRFGAVWSR SC VEF
EMYAR GADF. WV TMXFGTFZFZ VEF DGSTT. YSZFUT SC WV IFGF ISGR SR HGFATVT
CGSY IEWDE VEF DGSTT IAT ZWTDAGZFZ, ARZ WV IAT HSIFZ ZSIR VS ARZ
HFUWFJFZ WR IEFGF VEF DGSTT IAT ZFRWFZ.

WV TEFAGFZ SCC EFAZT TS YARO, VEAV WV, ARZ VEF PGSMRZ WV YSTV XSUUMVFZ,
IFGF A GSVVFR GFZ. WV IAT VAKFR VS XWFDFT, UWKF A VSO-XMBBUF CSG A OSMRP
ZFJWU, ARZ IAT XMV VSPFVEFG APAWR IEFR VEF SDDATWSR IARVFZ WV. WV EMTEFZ
VEF FUSNMFRV, TVGMDK ZSIR VEF XSIFGCMU, AHSUWTEFZ VEF HFAMVWCMU ARZ
PSSZ. VIFRVO-VIS CGWFRZT SC EWPE XMHUWD YAGK, VIFRVO-SRF UWJWRP ARZ SRF
ZFAZ, WV EAZ USXXFZ VEF EFAZT SCC, WR SRF YSGRWRP, WR AT YARO YWRMVFT.
VEF RAYF SC VEF TVGSRP YAR SC SUZ TDGWXVMGF EAZ ZFTDFRZFZ VS VEF DEWFC
CMRDVWSRAGO IES ISGKFZ WV; HMV, TS AGYFZ, EF IAT TVGSRPFG VEAR EWT
RAYFTAKF, ARZ HUWRZFG, ARZ VSGF AIAO VEF PAVFT SC PSZ'T SIR VFYXUF FJFGO
ZAO.

AYSRP VEFTF VFGGSGT, ARZ VEF HGSSZ HFUSRPWRP VS VEFY, VEF ZSDVSG IAUKFZ
IWVE A TVFAZO EFAZ: DSRCWZFRV WR EWT XSIFG, DAMVWSMTUO XFGTWTVFRV WR EWT
FRZ, RFJFG ZSMHVWRP VEAV EF ISMUZ TAJF UMDWF'T EMTHARZ AV UATV. OFV VEF
DMGGFRV SC VEF VWYF TIFXV HO, TS TVGSRP ARZ ZFFX, ARZ DAGGWFZ VEF VWYF
AIAO TS CWFGDFUO, VEAV DEAGUFT EAZ UAWR WR XGWTSR SRF OFAG ARZ VEGFF
YSRVET IEFR VEF ZSDVSG IAT VEMT TVFAZO ARZ DSRCWZFRV. TS YMDE YSGF
IWDKFZ ARZ ZWTVGADVFZ EAZ VEF GFJSUMVWSR PGSIR WR VEAV ZFDFYHFG YSRVE,
VEAV VEF GWJFGT SC VEF TSMVE IFGF FRDMYHFGFZ IWVE VEF HSZWFT SC VEF
JWSUFRVUO ZGSIRFZ HO RWPEV, ARZ XGWTSRFGT IFGF TESV WR UWRFT ARZ TNMAGFT
MRZFG VEF TSMVEFGR IWRVGO TMR. TVWUU, VEF ZSDVSG IAUKFZ AYSRP VEF
VFGGSGT IWVE A TVFAZO EFAZ. RS YAR HFVVFG KRSIR VEAR EF, WR XAGWT AV
VEAV ZAO; RS YAR WR A TVGARPFG TWVMAVWSR. TWUFRV, EMYARF, WRZWTXFRTAHUF
WR ESTXWVAU ARZ XGWTSR, MTWRP EWT AGV FNMAUUO AYSRP ATTATTWRT ARZ
JWDVWYT, EF IAT A YAR AXAGV. WR VEF FQFGDWTF SC EWT TKWUU, VEF
AXXFAGARDF ARZ VEF TVSGO SC VEF HATVWUUF DAXVWJF GFYSJFZ EWY CGSY AUU
SVEFG YFR. EF IAT RSV TMTXFDVFZ SG HGSMPEV WR NMFTVWSR, ARO YSGF VEAR WC
EF EAZ WRZFFZ HFFR GFDAUUFZ VS UWCF TSYF FWPEVFFR OFAGT HFCSGF, SG IFGF
A TXWGWV YSJWRP AYSRP YSGVAUT.




J. VEF ISSZ-TAIOFG


SRF OFAG ARZ VEGFF YSRVET. ZMGWRP AUU VEAV VWYF UMDWF IAT RFJFG
TMGF, CGSY ESMG VS ESMG, HMV VEAV VEF PMWUUSVWRF ISMUZ TVGWKF SCC EFG
EMTHARZ'T EFAZ RFQV ZAO. FJFGO ZAO, VEGSMPE VEF TVSRO TVGFFVT, VEF
VMYHGWUT RSI LSUVFZ EFAJWUO, CWUUFZ IWVE DSRZFYRFZ. USJFUO PWGUT; HGWPEV
ISYFR, HGSIR-EAWGFZ, HUADK-EAWGFZ, ARZ PGFO; OSMVET; TVAUIAGV YFR ARZ
SUZ; PFRVUF HSGR ARZ XFATARV HSGR; AUU GFZ IWRF CSG UA PMWUUSVWRF, AUU
ZAWUO HGSMPEV WRVS UWPEV CGSY VEF ZAGK DFUUAGT SC VEF USAVETSYF XGWTSRT,
ARZ DAGGWFZ VS EFG VEGSMPE VEF TVGFFVT VS TUAKF EFG ZFJSMGWRP VEWGTV.
UWHFGVO, FNMAUWVO, CGAVFGRWVO, SG ZFAVE;--VEF UATV, YMDE VEF FATWFTV VS
HFTVSI, S PMWUUSVWRF!

WC VEF TMZZFRRFTT SC EFG DAUAYWVO, ARZ VEF IEWGUWRP IEFFUT SC VEF VWYF,
EAZ TVMRRFZ VEF ZSDVSG'T ZAMPEVFG WRVS AIAWVWRP VEF GFTMUV WR WZUF
ZFTXAWG, WV ISMUZ HMV EAJF HFFR IWVE EFG AT WV IAT IWVE YARO. HMV, CGSY
VEF ESMG IEFR TEF EAZ VAKFR VEF IEWVF EFAZ VS EFG CGFTE OSMRP HSTSY WR
VEF PAGGFV SC TAWRV ARVSWRF, TEF EAZ HFFR VGMF VS EFG ZMVWFT. TEF IAT
VGMFTV VS VEFY WR VEF TFATSR SC VGWAU, AT AUU VEF NMWFVUO USOAU ARZ PSSZ
IWUU AUIAOT HF.

AT TSSR AT VEFO IFGF FTVAHUWTEFZ WR VEFWG RFI GFTWZFRDF, ARZ EFG CAVEFG
EAZ FRVFGFZ SR VEF GSMVWRF SC EWT AJSDAVWSRT, TEF AGGARPFZ VEF UWVVUF
ESMTFESUZ AT FQADVUO AT WC EFG EMTHARZ EAZ HFFR VEFGF. FJFGOVEWRP EAZ
WVT AXXSWRVFZ XUADF ARZ WVT AXXSWRVFZ VWYF. UWVVUF UMDWF TEF VAMPEV,
AT GFPMUAGUO, AT WC VEFO EAZ AUU HFFR MRWVFZ WR VEFWG FRPUWTE ESYF. VEF
TUWPEV ZFJWDFT IWVE IEWDE TEF DEFAVFZ EFGTFUC WRVS VEF TESI SC A HFUWFC
VEAV VEFO ISMUZ TSSR HF GFMRWVFZ--VEF UWVVUF XGFXAGAVWSRT CSG EWT TXFFZO
GFVMGR, VEF TFVVWRP ATWZF SC EWT DEAWG ARZ EWT HSSKT--VEFTF, ARZ VEF
TSUFYR XGAOFG AV RWPEV CSG SRF ZFAG XGWTSRFG FTXFDWAUUO, AYSRP VEF YARO
MREAXXO TSMUT WR XGWTSR ARZ VEF TEAZSI SC ZFAVE--IFGF AUYSTV VEF SRUO
SMVTXSKFR GFUWFCT SC EFG EFAJO YWRZ.

TEF ZWZ RSV PGFAVUO AUVFG WR AXXFAGARDF. VEF XUAWR ZAGK ZGFTTFT, AKWR VS
YSMGRWRP ZGFTTFT, IEWDE TEF ARZ EFG DEWUZ ISGF, IFGF AT RFAV ARZ AT IFUU
AVVFRZFZ VS AT VEF HGWPEVFG DUSVEFT SC EAXXO ZAOT. TEF USTV EFG DSUSMG,
ARZ VEF SUZ ARZ WRVFRV FQXGFTTWSR IAT A DSRTVARV, RSV AR SDDATWSRAU,
VEWRP; SVEFGIWTF, TEF GFYAWRFZ JFGO XGFVVO ARZ DSYFUO. TSYFVWYFT, AV
RWPEV SR KWTTWRP EFG CAVEFG, TEF ISMUZ HMGTV WRVS VEF PGWFC TEF EAZ
GFXGFTTFZ AUU ZAO, ARZ ISMUZ TAO VEAV EFG TSUF GFUWARDF, MRZFG EFAJFR,
IAT SR EWY. EF AUIAOT GFTSUMVFUO ARTIFGFZ: “RSVEWRP DAR EAXXFR VS EWY
IWVESMV YO KRSIUFZPF, ARZ W KRSI VEAV W DAR TAJF EWY, UMDWF.”

VEFO EAZ RSV YAZF VEF GSMRZ SC VEFWG DEARPFZ UWCF YARO IFFKT, IEFR EFG
CAVEFG TAWZ VS EFG, SR DSYWRP ESYF SRF FJFRWRP:

“YO ZFAG, VEFGF WT AR MXXFG IWRZSI WR VEF XGWTSR, VS IEWDE DEAGUFT DAR
TSYFVWYFT PAWR ADDFTT AV VEGFF WR VEF ACVFGRSSR. IEFR EF DAR PFV VS
WV--IEWDE ZFXFRZT SR YARO MRDFGVAWRVWFT ARZ WRDWZFRVT--EF YWPEV TFF OSM
WR VEF TVGFFV, EF VEWRKT, WC OSM TVSSZ WR A DFGVAWR XUADF VEAV W DAR
TESI OSM. HMV OSM IWUU RSV HF AHUF VS TFF EWY, YO XSSG DEWUZ, ARZ FJFR
WC OSM DSMUZ, WV ISMUZ HF MRTACF CSG OSM VS YAKF A TWPR SC GFDSPRWVWSR.”

“S TESI YF VEF XUADF, YO CAVEFG, ARZ W IWUU PS VEFGF FJFGO ZAO.”

CGSY VEAV VWYF, WR AUU IFAVEFGT, TEF IAWVFZ VEFGF VIS ESMGT. AT VEF
DUSDK TVGMDK VIS, TEF IAT VEFGF, ARZ AV CSMG TEF VMGRFZ GFTWPRFZUO AIAO.
IEFR WV IAT RSV VSS IFV SG WRDUFYFRV CSG EFG DEWUZ VS HF IWVE EFG, VEFO
IFRV VSPFVEFG; AV SVEFG VWYFT TEF IAT AUSRF; HMV, TEF RFJFG YWTTFZ A
TWRPUF ZAO.

WV IAT VEF ZAGK ARZ ZWGVO DSGRFG SC A TYAUU IWRZWRP TVGFFV. VEF ESJFU
SC A DMVVFG SC ISSZ WRVS UFRPVET CSG HMGRWRP, IAT VEF SRUO ESMTF AV VEAV
FRZ; AUU FUTF IAT IAUU. SR VEF VEWGZ ZAO SC EFG HFWRP VEFGF, EF RSVWDFZ
EFG.

“PSSZ ZAO, DWVWBFRFTT.”

“PSSZ ZAO, DWVWBFR.”

VEWT YSZF SC AZZGFTT IAT RSI XGFTDGWHFZ HO ZFDGFF. WV EAZ HFFR
FTVAHUWTEFZ JSUMRVAGWUO TSYF VWYF APS, AYSRP VEF YSGF VESGSMPE XAVGWSVT;
HMV, IAT RSI UAI CSG FJFGOHSZO.

“IAUKWRP EFGF APAWR, DWVWBFRFTT?”

“OSM TFF YF, DWVWBFR!”

VEF ISSZ-TAIOFG, IES IAT A UWVVUF YAR IWVE A GFZMRZARDO SC PFTVMGF (EF
EAZ SRDF HFFR A YFRZFG SC GSAZT), DATV A PUARDF AV VEF XGWTSR, XSWRVFZ
AV VEF XGWTSR, ARZ XMVVWRP EWT VFR CWRPFGT HFCSGF EWT CADF VS GFXGFTFRV
HAGT, XFFXFZ VEGSMPE VEFY LSDSTFUO.

“HMV WV'T RSV YO HMTWRFTT,” TAWZ EF. ARZ IFRV SR TAIWRP EWT ISSZ.

RFQV ZAO EF IAT USSKWRP SMV CSG EFG, ARZ ADDSTVFZ EFG VEF YSYFRV TEF
AXXFAGFZ.

“IEAV? IAUKWRP EFGF APAWR, DWVWBFRFTT?”

“OFT, DWVWBFR.”

“AE! A DEWUZ VSS! OSMG YSVEFG, WT WV RSV, YO UWVVUF DWVWBFRFTT?”

“ZS W TAO OFT, YAYYA?” IEWTXFGFZ UWVVUF UMDWF, ZGAIWRP DUSTF VS EFG.

“OFT, ZFAGFTV.”

“OFT, DWVWBFR.”

“AE! HMV WV'T RSV YO HMTWRFTT. YO ISGK WT YO HMTWRFTT. TFF YO TAI! W
DAUU WV YO UWVVUF PMWUUSVWRF. UA, UA, UA; UA, UA, UA! ARZ SCC EWT EFAZ
DSYFT!”

VEF HWUUFV CFUU AT EF TXSKF, ARZ EF VEGFI WV WRVS A HATKFV.

“W DAUU YOTFUC VEF TAYTSR SC VEF CWGFISSZ PMWUUSVWRF. TFF EFGF APAWR!
USS, USS, USS; USS, USS, USS! ARZ SCC _EFG_ EFAZ DSYFT! RSI, A DEWUZ.
VWDKUF, VWDKUF; XWDKUF, XWDKUF! ARZ SCC _WVT_ EFAZ DSYFT. AUU VEF
CAYWUO!”

UMDWF TEMZZFGFZ AT EF VEGFI VIS YSGF HWUUFVT WRVS EWT HATKFV, HMV WV IAT
WYXSTTWHUF VS HF VEFGF IEWUF VEF ISSZ-TAIOFG IAT AV ISGK, ARZ RSV HF WR
EWT TWPEV. VEFRDFCSGVE, VS TFDMGF EWT PSSZ IWUU, TEF AUIAOT TXSKF VS EWY
CWGTV, ARZ SCVFR PAJF EWY ZGWRK-YSRFO, IEWDE EF GFAZWUO GFDFWJFZ.

EF IAT AR WRNMWTWVWJF CFUUSI, ARZ TSYFVWYFT IEFR TEF EAZ NMWVF CSGPSVVFR
EWY WR PABWRP AV VEF XGWTSR GSSC ARZ PGAVFT, ARZ WR UWCVWRP EFG EFAGV
MX VS EFG EMTHARZ, TEF ISMUZ DSYF VS EFGTFUC VS CWRZ EWY USSKWRP AV EFG,
IWVE EWT KRFF SR EWT HFRDE ARZ EWT TAI TVSXXFZ WR WVT ISGK. “HMV WV'T
RSV YO HMTWRFTT!” EF ISMUZ PFRFGAUUO TAO AV VESTF VWYFT, ARZ ISMUZ
HGWTKUO CAUU VS EWT TAIWRP APAWR.

WR AUU IFAVEFGT, WR VEF TRSI ARZ CGSTV SC IWRVFG, WR VEF HWVVFG IWRZT SC
TXGWRP, WR VEF ESV TMRTEWRF SC TMYYFG, WR VEF GAWRT SC AMVMYR, ARZ APAWR
WR VEF TRSI ARZ CGSTV SC IWRVFG, UMDWF XATTFZ VIS ESMGT SC FJFGO ZAO AV
VEWT XUADF; ARZ FJFGO ZAO SR UFAJWRP WV, TEF KWTTFZ VEF XGWTSR IAUU.
EFG EMTHARZ TAI EFG (TS TEF UFAGRFZ CGSY EFG CAVEFG) WV YWPEV HF SRDF WR
CWJF SG TWQ VWYFT: WV YWPEV HF VIWDF SG VEGWDF GMRRWRP: WV YWPEV HF, RSV
CSG A IFFK SG A CSGVRWPEV VSPFVEFG. WV IAT FRSMPE VEAV EF DSMUZ ARZ ZWZ
TFF EFG IEFR VEF DEARDFT TFGJFZ, ARZ SR VEAV XSTTWHWUWVO TEF ISMUZ EAJF
IAWVFZ SMV VEF ZAO, TFJFR ZAOT A IFFK.

VEFTF SDDMXAVWSRT HGSMPEV EFG GSMRZ VS VEF ZFDFYHFG YSRVE, IEFGFWR EFG
CAVEFG IAUKFZ AYSRP VEF VFGGSGT IWVE A TVFAZO EFAZ. SR A UWPEVUO-TRSIWRP
ACVFGRSSR TEF AGGWJFZ AV VEF MTMAU DSGRFG. WV IAT A ZAO SC TSYF IWUZ
GFLSWDWRP, ARZ A CFTVWJAU. TEF EAZ TFFR VEF ESMTFT, AT TEF DAYF AUSRP,
ZFDSGAVFZ IWVE UWVVUF XWKFT, ARZ IWVE UWVVUF GFZ DAXT TVMDK MXSR VEFY;
AUTS, IWVE VGWDSUSMGFZ GWHHSRT; AUTS, IWVE VEF TVARZAGZ WRTDGWXVWSR
(VGWDSUSMGFZ UFVVFGT IFGF VEF CAJSMGWVF), GFXMHUWD SRF ARZ WRZWJWTWHUF.
UWHFGVO, FNMAUWVO, CGAVFGRWVO, SG ZFAVE!

VEF YWTFGAHUF TESX SC VEF ISSZ-TAIOFG IAT TS TYAUU, VEAV WVT IESUF
TMGCADF CMGRWTEFZ JFGO WRZWCCFGFRV TXADF CSG VEWT UFPFRZ. EF EAZ PSV
TSYFHSZO VS TDGAIU WV MX CSG EWY, ESIFJFG, IES EAZ TNMFFBFZ ZFAVE WR
IWVE YSTV WRAXXGSXGWAVF ZWCCWDMUVO. SR EWT ESMTF-VSX, EF ZWTXUAOFZ XWKF
ARZ DAX, AT A PSSZ DWVWBFR YMTV, ARZ WR A IWRZSI EF EAZ TVAVWSRFZ EWT
TAI WRTDGWHFZ AT EWT “UWVVUF TAWRVF PMWUUSVWRF”--CSG VEF PGFAV TEAGX
CFYAUF IAT HO VEAV VWYF XSXMUAGUO DARSRWTFZ. EWT TESX IAT TEMV ARZ EF
IAT RSV VEFGF, IEWDE IAT A GFUWFC VS UMDWF, ARZ UFCV EFG NMWVF AUSRF.

HMV, EF IAT RSV CAG SCC, CSG XGFTFRVUO TEF EFAGZ A VGSMHUFZ YSJFYFRV
ARZ A TESMVWRP DSYWRP AUSRP, IEWDE CWUUFZ EFG IWVE CFAG. A YSYFRV
ACVFGIAGZT, ARZ A VEGSRP SC XFSXUF DAYF XSMGWRP GSMRZ VEF DSGRFG HO VEF
XGWTSR IAUU, WR VEF YWZTV SC IESY IAT VEF ISSZ-TAIOFG EARZ WR EARZ IWVE
VEF JFRPFARDF. VEFGF DSMUZ RSV HF CFIFG VEAR CWJF EMRZGFZ XFSXUF, ARZ
VEFO IFGF ZARDWRP UWKF CWJF VESMTARZ ZFYSRT. VEFGF IAT RS SVEFG YMTWD
VEAR VEFWG SIR TWRPWRP. VEFO ZARDFZ VS VEF XSXMUAG GFJSUMVWSR TSRP,
KFFXWRP A CFGSDWSMT VWYF VEAV IAT UWKF A PRATEWRP SC VFFVE WR MRWTSR.
YFR ARZ ISYFR ZARDFZ VSPFVEFG, ISYFR ZARDFZ VSPFVEFG, YFR ZARDFZ
