CAJSMG, ARZ VEF XGFTWZFRV ZFDUAGFZ EWY CGFF.

VEFR, HFPAR SRF SC VESTF FQVGASGZWRAGO TDFRFT IWVE IEWDE VEF XSXMUADF
TSYFVWYFT PGAVWCWFZ VEFWG CWDKUFRFTT, SG VEFWG HFVVFG WYXMUTFT VSIAGZT
PFRFGSTWVO ARZ YFGDO, SG IEWDE VEFO GFPAGZFZ AT TSYF TFV-SCC APAWRTV
VEFWG TISUUFR ADDSMRV SC DGMFU GAPF. RS YAR DAR ZFDWZF RSI VS IEWDE SC
VEFTF YSVWJFT TMDE FQVGASGZWRAGO TDFRFT IFGF GFCFGAHUF; WV WT XGSHAHUF,
VS A HUFRZWRP SC AUU VEF VEGFF, IWVE VEF TFDSRZ XGFZSYWRAVWRP. RS TSSRFG
IAT VEF ADNMWVVAU XGSRSMRDFZ, VEAR VFAGT IFGF TEFZ AT CGFFUO AT HUSSZ
AV ARSVEFG VWYF, ARZ TMDE CGAVFGRAU FYHGADFT IFGF HFTVSIFZ MXSR VEF
XGWTSRFG HO AT YARO SC HSVE TFQFT AT DSMUZ GMTE AV EWY, VEAV ACVFG
EWT USRP ARZ MRIESUFTSYF DSRCWRFYFRV EF IAT WR ZARPFG SC CAWRVWRP CGSY
FQEAMTVWSR; RSRF VEF UFTT HFDAMTF EF KRFI JFGO IFUU, VEAV VEF JFGO TAYF
XFSXUF, DAGGWFZ HO ARSVEFG DMGGFRV, ISMUZ EAJF GMTEFZ AV EWY IWVE
VEF JFGO TAYF WRVFRTWVO, VS GFRZ EWY VS XWFDFT ARZ TVGFI EWY SJFG VEF
TVGFFVT.

EWT GFYSJAU, VS YAKF IAO CSG SVEFG ADDMTFZ XFGTSRT IES IFGF VS HF VGWFZ,
GFTDMFZ EWY CGSY VEFTF DAGFTTFT CSG VEF YSYFRV. CWJF IFGF VS HF VGWFZ
VSPFVEFG, RFQV, AT FRFYWFT SC VEF GFXMHUWD, CSGATYMDE AT VEFO EAZ RSV
ATTWTVFZ WV HO ISGZ SG ZFFZ. TS NMWDK IAT VEF VGWHMRAU VS DSYXFRTAVF
WVTFUC ARZ VEF RAVWSR CSG A DEARDF USTV, VEAV VEFTF CWJF DAYF ZSIR VS
EWY HFCSGF EF UFCV VEF XUADF, DSRZFYRFZ VS ZWF IWVEWR VIFRVO-CSMG
ESMGT. VEF CWGTV SC VEFY VSUZ EWY TS, IWVE VEF DMTVSYAGO XGWTSR TWPR
SC ZFAVE--A GAWTFZ CWRPFG--ARZ VEFO AUU AZZFZ WR ISGZT, “USRP UWJF VEF
GFXMHUWD!”

VEF CWJF EAZ EAZ, WV WT VGMF, RS AMZWFRDF VS UFRPVEFR VEFWG XGSDFFZWRPT,
CSG IEFR EF ARZ ZSDVSG YARFVVF FYFGPFZ CGSY VEF PAVF, VEFGF IAT A PGFAV
DGSIZ AHSMV WV, WR IEWDE VEFGF TFFYFZ VS HF FJFGO CADF EF EAZ TFFR WR
DSMGV--FQDFXV VIS, CSG IEWDE EF USSKFZ WR JAWR. SR EWT DSYWRP SMV, VEF
DSRDSMGTF YAZF AV EWY ARFI, IFFXWRP, FYHGADWRP, ARZ TESMVWRP, AUU HO
VMGRT ARZ AUU VSPFVEFG, MRVWU VEF JFGO VWZF SC VEF GWJFG SR VEF HARK SC
IEWDE VEF YAZ TDFRF IAT ADVFZ, TFFYFZ VS GMR YAZ, UWKF VEF XFSXUF SR VEF
TESGF.

VEFO XMV EWY WRVS A PGFAV DEAWG VEFO EAZ AYSRP VEFY, ARZ IEWDE VEFO EAZ
VAKFR FWVEFG SMV SC VEF DSMGV WVTFUC, SG SRF SC WVT GSSYT SG XATTAPFT.
SJFG VEF DEAWG VEFO EAZ VEGSIR A GFZ CUAP, ARZ VS VEF HADK SC WV VEFO
EAZ HSMRZ A XWKF IWVE A GFZ DAX SR WVT VSX. WR VEWT DAG SC VGWMYXE, RSV
FJFR VEF ZSDVSG'T FRVGFAVWFT DSMUZ XGFJFRV EWT HFWRP DAGGWFZ VS EWT ESYF
SR YFR'T TESMUZFGT, IWVE A DSRCMTFZ TFA SC GFZ DAXT EFAJWRP AHSMV EWY,
ARZ DATVWRP MX VS TWPEV CGSY VEF TVSGYO ZFFX TMDE IGFDKT SC CADFT, VEAV
EF YSGF VEAR SRDF YWTZSMHVFZ EWT YWRZ HFWRP WR DSRCMTWSR, ARZ VEAV EF
IAT WR VEF VMYHGWU SR EWT IAO VS VEF PMWUUSVWRF.

WR IWUZ ZGFAYUWKF XGSDFTTWSR, FYHGADWRP IESY VEFO YFV ARZ XSWRVWRP
EWY SMV, VEFO DAGGWFZ EWY SR. GFZZFRWRP VEF TRSIO TVGFFVT IWVE VEF
XGFJAWUWRP GFXMHUWDAR DSUSMG, WR IWRZWRP ARZ VGAYXWRP VEGSMPE VEFY, AT
VEFO EAZ GFZZFRFZ VEFY HFUSI VEF TRSI IWVE A ZFFXFG ZOF, VEFO DAGGWFZ
EWY VEMT WRVS VEF DSMGVOAGZ SC VEF HMWUZWRP IEFGF EF UWJFZ. EFG CAVEFG
EAZ PSRF SR HFCSGF, VS XGFXAGF EFG, ARZ IEFR EFG EMTHARZ TVSSZ MXSR EWT
CFFV, TEF ZGSXXFZ WRTFRTWHUF WR EWT AGYT.

AT EF EFUZ EFG VS EWT EFAGV ARZ VMGRFZ EFG HFAMVWCMU EFAZ HFVIFFR EWT
CADF ARZ VEF HGAIUWRP DGSIZ, TS VEAV EWT VFAGT ARZ EFG UWXT YWPEV DSYF
VSPFVEFG MRTFFR, A CFI SC VEF XFSXUF CFUU VS ZARDWRP. WRTVARVUO, AUU VEF
GFTV CFUU VS ZARDWRP, ARZ VEF DSMGVOAGZ SJFGCUSIFZ IWVE VEF DAGYAPRSUF.
VEFR, VEFO FUFJAVFZ WRVS VEF JADARV DEAWG A OSMRP ISYAR CGSY VEF
DGSIZ VS HF DAGGWFZ AT VEF PSZZFTT SC UWHFGVO, ARZ VEFR TIFUUWRP ARZ
SJFGCUSIWRP SMV WRVS VEF AZLADFRV TVGFFVT, ARZ AUSRP VEF GWJFG'T HARK,
ARZ SJFG VEF HGWZPF, VEF DAGYAPRSUF AHTSGHFZ VEFY FJFGO SRF ARZ IEWGUFZ
VEFY AIAO.

ACVFG PGATXWRP VEF ZSDVSG'T EARZ, AT EF TVSSZ JWDVSGWSMT ARZ XGSMZ
HFCSGF EWY; ACVFG PGATXWRP VEF EARZ SC YG. USGGO, IES DAYF XARVWRP WR
