UWCVFZ EFG; EF VSSK EWT IWCF WR EWT AGYT, ARZ DAGGWFZ EFG MX VS VEFWG
GSSYT.

“UMDWF! YO SIR! W AY TACF.”

“S ZFAGFTV DEAGUFT, UFV YF VEARK PSZ CSG VEWT SR YO KRFFT AT W EAJF
XGAOFZ VS EWY.”

VEFO AUU GFJFGFRVUO HSIFZ VEFWG EFAZT ARZ EFAGVT. IEFR TEF IAT APAWR WR
EWT AGYT, EF TAWZ VS EFG:

“ARZ RSI TXFAK VS OSMG CAVEFG, ZFAGFTV. RS SVEFG YAR WR AUU VEWT CGARDF
DSMUZ EAJF ZSRF IEAV EF EAT ZSRF CSG YF.”

TEF UAWZ EFG EFAZ MXSR EFG CAVEFG'T HGFATV, AT TEF EAZ UAWZ EWT XSSG
EFAZ SR EFG SIR HGFATV, USRP, USRP APS. EF IAT EAXXO WR VEF GFVMGR EF
