TVGFRPVE. “OSM YMTV RSV HF IFAK, YO ZAGUWRP,” EF GFYSRTVGAVFZ; “ZSR'V
VGFYHUF TS. W EAJF TAJFZ EWY.”




JWW. A KRSDK AV VEF ZSSG


“W EAJF TAJFZ EWY.” WV IAT RSV ARSVEFG SC VEF ZGFAYT WR IEWDE EF EAZ
SCVFR DSYF HADK; EF IAT GFAUUO EFGF. ARZ OFV EWT IWCF VGFYHUFZ, ARZ A
JAPMF HMV EFAJO CFAG IAT MXSR EFG.

AUU VEF AWG GSMRZ IAT TS VEWDK ARZ ZAGK, VEF XFSXUF IFGF TS XATTWSRAVFUO
GFJFRPFCMU ARZ CWVCMU, VEF WRRSDFRV IFGF TS DSRTVARVUO XMV VS ZFAVE SR
JAPMF TMTXWDWSR ARZ HUADK YAUWDF, WV IAT TS WYXSTTWHUF VS CSGPFV VEAV
YARO AT HUAYFUFTT AT EFG EMTHARZ ARZ AT ZFAG VS SVEFGT AT EF IAT VS
EFG, FJFGO ZAO TEAGFZ VEF CAVF CGSY IEWDE EF EAZ HFFR DUMVDEFZ, VEAV EFG
EFAGV DSMUZ RSV HF AT UWPEVFRFZ SC WVT USAZ AT TEF CFUV WV SMPEV VS HF.
VEF TEAZSIT SC VEF IWRVGO ACVFGRSSR IFGF HFPWRRWRP VS CAUU, ARZ FJFR RSI
VEF ZGFAZCMU DAGVT IFGF GSUUWRP VEGSMPE VEF TVGFFVT. EFG YWRZ XMGTMFZ
VEFY, USSKWRP CSG EWY AYSRP VEF DSRZFYRFZ; ARZ VEFR TEF DUMRP DUSTFG VS
EWT GFAU XGFTFRDF ARZ VGFYHUFZ YSGF.

EFG CAVEFG, DEFFGWRP EFG, TESIFZ A DSYXATTWSRAVF TMXFGWSGWVO VS VEWT
ISYAR'T IFAKRFTT, IEWDE IAT ISRZFGCMU VS TFF. RS PAGGFV, RS TESFYAKWRP,
RS SRF EMRZGFZ ARZ CWJF, RSGVE VSIFG, RSI! EF EAZ ADDSYXUWTEFZ VEF VATK
EF EAZ TFV EWYTFUC, EWT XGSYWTF IAT GFZFFYFZ, EF EAZ TAJFZ DEAGUFT. UFV
VEFY AUU UFAR MXSR EWY.

VEFWG ESMTFKFFXWRP IAT SC A JFGO CGMPAU KWRZ: RSV SRUO HFDAMTF VEAV IAT
VEF TACFTV IAO SC UWCF, WRJSUJWRP VEF UFATV SCCFRDF VS VEF XFSXUF, HMV
HFDAMTF VEFO IFGF RSV GWDE, ARZ DEAGUFT, VEGSMPESMV EWT WYXGWTSRYFRV,
EAZ EAZ VS XAO EFAJWUO CSG EWT HAZ CSSZ, ARZ CSG EWT PMAGZ, ARZ VSIAGZT
VEF UWJWRP SC VEF XSSGFG XGWTSRFGT. XAGVUO SR VEWT ADDSMRV, ARZ
XAGVUO VS AJSWZ A ZSYFTVWD TXO, VEFO KFXV RS TFGJARV; VEF DWVWBFR ARZ
DWVWBFRFTT IES ADVFZ AT XSGVFGT AV VEF DSMGVOAGZ PAVF, GFRZFGFZ VEFY
SDDATWSRAU TFGJWDF; ARZ LFGGO (AUYSTV IESUUO VGARTCFGGFZ VS VEFY HO
YG. USGGO) EAZ HFDSYF VEFWG ZAWUO GFVAWRFG, ARZ EAZ EWT HFZ VEFGF FJFGO
RWPEV.

WV IAT AR SGZWRARDF SC VEF GFXMHUWD SRF ARZ WRZWJWTWHUF SC UWHFGVO,
FNMAUWVO, CGAVFGRWVO, SG ZFAVE, VEAV SR VEF ZSSG SG ZSSGXSTV SC FJFGO
ESMTF, VEF RAYF SC FJFGO WRYAVF YMTV HF UFPWHUO WRTDGWHFZ WR UFVVFGT
SC A DFGVAWR TWBF, AV A DFGVAWR DSRJFRWFRV EFWPEV CGSY VEF PGSMRZ. YG.
LFGGO DGMRDEFG'T RAYF, VEFGFCSGF, ZMUO FYHFUUWTEFZ VEF ZSSGXSTV ZSIR
HFUSI; ARZ, AT VEF ACVFGRSSR TEAZSIT ZFFXFRFZ, VEF SIRFG SC VEAV RAYF
EWYTFUC AXXFAGFZ, CGSY SJFGUSSKWRP A XAWRVFG IESY ZSDVSG YARFVVF EAZ
FYXUSOFZ VS AZZ VS VEF UWTV VEF RAYF SC DEAGUFT FJGFYSRZF, DAUUFZ
ZAGRAO.

WR VEF MRWJFGTAU CFAG ARZ ZWTVGMTV VEAV ZAGKFRFZ VEF VWYF, AUU VEF MTMAU
EAGYUFTT IAOT SC UWCF IFGF DEARPFZ. WR VEF ZSDVSG'T UWVVUF ESMTFESUZ, AT
WR JFGO YARO SVEFGT, VEF AGVWDUFT SC ZAWUO DSRTMYXVWSR VEAV IFGF IARVFZ
IFGF XMGDEATFZ FJFGO FJFRWRP, WR TYAUU NMARVWVWFT ARZ AV JAGWSMT TYAUU
TESXT. VS AJSWZ AVVGADVWRP RSVWDF, ARZ VS PWJF AT UWVVUF SDDATWSR AT
XSTTWHUF CSG VAUK ARZ FRJO, IAT VEF PFRFGAU ZFTWGF.

CSG TSYF YSRVET XATV, YWTT XGSTT ARZ YG. DGMRDEFG EAZ ZWTDEAGPFZ VEF
SCCWDF SC XMGJFOSGT; VEF CSGYFG DAGGOWRP VEF YSRFO; VEF UAVVFG, VEF
HATKFV. FJFGO ACVFGRSSR AV AHSMV VEF VWYF IEFR VEF XMHUWD UAYXT IFGF
UWPEVFZ, VEFO CAGFZ CSGVE SR VEWT ZMVO, ARZ YAZF ARZ HGSMPEV ESYF
TMDE XMGDEATFT AT IFGF RFFZCMU. AUVESMPE YWTT XGSTT, VEGSMPE EFG USRP
ATTSDWAVWSR IWVE A CGFRDE CAYWUO, YWPEV EAJF KRSIR AT YMDE SC VEFWG
UARPMAPF AT SC EFG SIR, WC TEF EAZ EAZ A YWRZ, TEF EAZ RS YWRZ WR VEAV
ZWGFDVWSR; DSRTFNMFRVUO TEF KRFI RS YSGF SC VEAV “RSRTFRTF” (AT TEF IAT
XUFATFZ VS DAUU WV) VEAR YG. DGMRDEFG ZWZ. TS EFG YARRFG SC YAGKFVWRP
IAT VS XUMYX A RSMR-TMHTVARVWJF AV VEF EFAZ SC A TESXKFFXFG IWVESMV ARO
WRVGSZMDVWSR WR VEF RAVMGF SC AR AGVWDUF, ARZ, WC WV EAXXFRFZ RSV VS HF
VEF RAYF SC VEF VEWRP TEF IARVFZ, VS USSK GSMRZ CSG VEAV VEWRP, UAO ESUZ
SC WV, ARZ ESUZ SR HO WV MRVWU VEF HAGPAWR IAT DSRDUMZFZ. TEF AUIAOT
YAZF A HAGPAWR CSG WV, HO ESUZWRP MX, AT A TVAVFYFRV SC WVT LMTV XGWDF,
SRF CWRPFG UFTT VEAR VEF YFGDEARV EFUZ MX, IEAVFJFG EWT RMYHFG YWPEV HF.

“RSI, YG. DGMRDEFG,” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT, IESTF FOFT IFGF GFZ IWVE CFUWDWVO;
“WC OSM AGF GFAZO, W AY.”

LFGGO ESAGTFUO XGSCFTTFZ EWYTFUC AV YWTT XGSTT'T TFGJWDF. EF EAZ ISGR
AUU EWT GMTV SCC USRP APS, HMV RSVEWRP ISMUZ CWUF EWT TXWKO EFAZ ZSIR.

“VEFGF'T AUU YARRFG SC VEWRPT IARVFZ,” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT, “ARZ IF TEAUU
EAJF A XGFDWSMT VWYF SC WV. IF IARV IWRF, AYSRP VEF GFTV. RWDF VSATVT
VEFTF GFZEFAZT IWUU HF ZGWRKWRP, IEFGFJFG IF HMO WV.”

“WV IWUU HF YMDE VEF TAYF VS OSMG KRSIUFZPF, YWTT, W TESMUZ VEWRK,”
 GFVSGVFZ LFGGO, “IEFVEFG VEFO ZGWRK OSMG EFAUVE SG VEF SUZ MR'T.”

“IES'T EF?” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT.

YG. DGMRDEFG, IWVE TSYF ZWCCWZFRDF, FQXUAWRFZ EWYTFUC AT YFARWRP “SUZ
RWDK'T.”

“EA!” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT, “WV ZSFTR'V RFFZ AR WRVFGXGFVFG VS FQXUAWR VEF
YFARWRP SC VEFTF DGFAVMGFT. VEFO EAJF HMV SRF, ARZ WV'T YWZRWPEV YMGZFG,
ARZ YWTDEWFC.”

“EMTE, ZFAG! XGAO, XGAO, HF DAMVWSMT!” DGWFZ UMDWF.

“OFT, OFT, OFT, W'UU HF DAMVWSMT,” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT; “HMV W YAO TAO
AYSRP SMGTFUJFT, VEAV W ZS ESXF VEFGF IWUU HF RS SRWSRO ARZ VSHADDSFO
TYSVEFGWRPT WR VEF CSGY SC FYHGADWRPT AUU GSMRZ, PSWRP SR WR VEF
TVGFFVT. RSI, UAZOHWGZ, RFJFG OSM TVWG CGSY VEAV CWGF VWUU W DSYF HADK!
VAKF DAGF SC VEF ZFAG EMTHARZ OSM EAJF GFDSJFGFZ, ARZ ZSR'V YSJF OSMG
XGFVVO EFAZ CGSY EWT TESMUZFG AT OSM EAJF WV RSI, VWUU OSM TFF YF APAWR!
YAO W ATK A NMFTVWSR, ZSDVSG YARFVVF, HFCSGF W PS?”

“W VEWRK OSM YAO VAKF VEAV UWHFGVO,” VEF ZSDVSG ARTIFGFZ, TYWUWRP.

“CSG PGADWSMT TAKF, ZSR'V VAUK AHSMV UWHFGVO; IF EAJF NMWVF FRSMPE SC
VEAV,” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT.

“EMTE, ZFAG! APAWR?” UMDWF GFYSRTVGAVFZ.

“IFUU, YO TIFFV,” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT, RSZZWRP EFG EFAZ FYXEAVWDAUUO, “VEF
TESGV ARZ VEF USRP SC WV WT, VEAV W AY A TMHLFDV SC EWT YSTV PGADWSMT
YALFTVO KWRP PFSGPF VEF VEWGZ;” YWTT XGSTT DMGVTFOFZ AV VEF RAYF; “ARZ
AT TMDE, YO YAQWY WT, DSRCSMRZ VEFWG XSUWVWDT, CGMTVGAVF VEFWG KRAJWTE
VGWDKT, SR EWY SMG ESXFT IF CWQ, PSZ TAJF VEF KWRP!”

YG. DGMRDEFG, WR AR ADDFTT SC USOAUVO, PGSIUWRPUO GFXFAVFZ VEF ISGZT
ACVFG YWTT XGSTT, UWKF TSYFHSZO AV DEMGDE.

“W AY PUAZ OSM EAJF TS YMDE SC VEF FRPUWTEYAR WR OSM, VESMPE W IWTE OSM
EAZ RFJFG VAKFR VEAV DSUZ WR OSMG JSWDF,” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT, AXXGSJWRPUO.
“HMV VEF NMFTVWSR, ZSDVSG YARFVVF. WT VEFGF”--WV IAT VEF PSSZ DGFAVMGF'T
IAO VS ACCFDV VS YAKF UWPEV SC AROVEWRP VEAV IAT A PGFAV ARQWFVO
IWVE VEFY AUU, ARZ VS DSYF AV WV WR VEWT DEARDF YARRFG--“WT VEFGF ARO
XGSTXFDV OFV, SC SMG PFVVWRP SMV SC VEWT XUADF?”

“W CFAG RSV OFV. WV ISMUZ HF ZARPFGSMT CSG DEAGUFT OFV.”

“EFWPE-ES-EMY!” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT, DEFFGCMUUO GFXGFTTWRP A TWPE AT TEF
PUARDFZ AV EFG ZAGUWRP'T PSUZFR EAWG WR VEF UWPEV SC VEF CWGF, “VEFR IF
YMTV EAJF XAVWFRDF ARZ IAWV: VEAV'T AUU. IF YMTV ESUZ MX SMG EFAZT ARZ
CWPEV USI, AT YO HGSVEFG TSUSYSR MTFZ VS TAO. RSI, YG. DGMRDEFG!--ZSR'V
OSM YSJF, UAZOHWGZ!”

VEFO IFRV SMV, UFAJWRP UMDWF, ARZ EFG EMTHARZ, EFG CAVEFG, ARZ VEF
DEWUZ, HO A HGWPEV CWGF. YG. USGGO IAT FQXFDVFZ HADK XGFTFRVUO CGSY VEF
HARKWRP ESMTF. YWTT XGSTT EAZ UWPEVFZ VEF UAYX, HMV EAZ XMV WV ATWZF WR
A DSGRFG, VEAV VEFO YWPEV FRLSO VEF CWGF-UWPEV MRZWTVMGHFZ. UWVVUF UMDWF
TAV HO EFG PGARZCAVEFG IWVE EFG EARZT DUATXFZ VEGSMPE EWT AGY: ARZ EF,
WR A VSRF RSV GWTWRP YMDE AHSJF A IEWTXFG, HFPAR VS VFUU EFG A TVSGO SC
A PGFAV ARZ XSIFGCMU CAWGO IES EAZ SXFRFZ A XGWTSR-IAUU ARZ UFV SMV
A DAXVWJF IES EAZ SRDF ZSRF VEF CAWGO A TFGJWDF. AUU IAT TMHZMFZ ARZ
NMWFV, ARZ UMDWF IAT YSGF AV FATF VEAR TEF EAZ HFFR.

“IEAV WT VEAV?” TEF DGWFZ, AUU AV SRDF.

“YO ZFAG!” TAWZ EFG CAVEFG, TVSXXWRP WR EWT TVSGO, ARZ UAOWRP EWT EARZ
SR EFGT, “DSYYARZ OSMGTFUC. IEAV A ZWTSGZFGFZ TVAVF OSM AGF WR! VEF
UFATV VEWRP--RSVEWRP--TVAGVUFT OSM! _OSM_, OSMG CAVEFG'T ZAMPEVFG!”

“W VESMPEV, YO CAVEFG,” TAWZ UMDWF, FQDMTWRP EFGTFUC, IWVE A XAUF CADF
ARZ WR A CAUVFGWRP JSWDF, “VEAV W EFAGZ TVGARPF CFFV MXSR VEF TVAWGT.”

“YO USJF, VEF TVAWGDATF WT AT TVWUU AT ZFAVE.”

AT EF TAWZ VEF ISGZ, A HUSI IAT TVGMDK MXSR VEF ZSSG.

“SE CAVEFG, CAVEFG. IEAV DAR VEWT HF! EWZF DEAGUFT. TAJF EWY!”

“YO DEWUZ,” TAWZ VEF ZSDVSG, GWTWRP, ARZ UAOWRP EWT EARZ MXSR EFG
TESMUZFG, “W _EAJF_ TAJFZ EWY. IEAV IFAKRFTT WT VEWT, YO ZFAG! UFV YF PS
VS VEF ZSSG.”

EF VSSK VEF UAYX WR EWT EARZ, DGSTTFZ VEF VIS WRVFGJFRWRP SMVFG GSSYT,
ARZ SXFRFZ WV. A GMZF DUAVVFGWRP SC CFFV SJFG VEF CUSSG, ARZ CSMG GSMPE
YFR WR GFZ DAXT, AGYFZ IWVE TAHGFT ARZ XWTVSUT, FRVFGFZ VEF GSSY.

“VEF DWVWBFR FJGFYSRZF, DAUUFZ ZAGRAO,” TAWZ VEF CWGTV.

“IES TFFKT EWY?” ARTIFGFZ ZAGRAO.

“W TFFK EWY. IF TFFK EWY. W KRSI OSM, FJGFYSRZF; W TAI OSM HFCSGF VEF
VGWHMRAU VS-ZAO. OSM AGF APAWR VEF XGWTSRFG SC VEF GFXMHUWD.”

VEF CSMG TMGGSMRZFZ EWY, IEFGF EF TVSSZ IWVE EWT IWCF ARZ DEWUZ DUWRPWRP
VS EWY.

“VFUU YF ESI ARZ IEO AY W APAWR A XGWTSRFG?”

“WV WT FRSMPE VEAV OSM GFVMGR TVGAWPEV VS VEF DSRDWFGPFGWF, ARZ IWUU
KRSI VS-YSGGSI. OSM AGF TMYYSRFZ CSG VS-YSGGSI.”

ZSDVSG YARFVVF, IESY VEWT JWTWVAVWSR EAZ TS VMGRFZ WRVS TVSRF, VEAV EF
TVSSZ IWVE VEF UAYX WR EWT EARZ, AT WC EF IFGF A TVAVMF YAZF VS ESUZ WV,
YSJFZ ACVFG VEFTF ISGZT IFGF TXSKFR, XMV VEF UAYX ZSIR, ARZ DSRCGSRVWRP
VEF TXFAKFG, ARZ VAKWRP EWY, RSV MRPFRVUO, HO VEF USSTF CGSRV SC EWT GFZ
ISSUUFR TEWGV, TAWZ:

“OSM KRSI EWY, OSM EAJF TAWZ. ZS OSM KRSI YF?”

“OFT, W KRSI OSM, DWVWBFR ZSDVSG.”

“IF AUU KRSI OSM, DWVWBFR ZSDVSG,” TAWZ VEF SVEFG VEGFF.

EF USSKFZ AHTVGADVFZUO CGSY SRF VS ARSVEFG, ARZ TAWZ, WR A USIFG JSWDF,
ACVFG A XAMTF:

“IWUU OSM ARTIFG EWT NMFTVWSR VS YF VEFR? ESI ZSFT VEWT EAXXFR?”

“DWVWBFR ZSDVSG,” TAWZ VEF CWGTV, GFUMDVARVUO, “EF EAT HFFR ZFRSMRDFZ VS
VEF TFDVWSR SC TAWRV ARVSWRF. VEWT DWVWBFR,” XSWRVWRP SMV VEF TFDSRZ IES
EAZ FRVFGFZ, “WT CGSY TAWRV ARVSWRF.”

VEF DWVWBFR EFGF WRZWDAVFZ RSZZFZ EWT EFAZ, ARZ AZZFZ:

“EF WT ADDMTFZ HO TAWRV ARVSWRF.”

“SC IEAV?” ATKFZ VEF ZSDVSG.

“DWVWBFR ZSDVSG,” TAWZ VEF CWGTV, IWVE EWT CSGYFG GFUMDVARDF, “ATK RS
YSGF. WC VEF GFXMHUWD ZFYARZT TADGWCWDFT CGSY OSM, IWVESMV ZSMHV OSM AT
A PSSZ XAVGWSV IWUU HF EAXXO VS YAKF VEFY. VEF GFXMHUWD PSFT HFCSGF AUU.
VEF XFSXUF WT TMXGFYF. FJGFYSRZF, IF AGF XGFTTFZ.”

“SRF ISGZ,” VEF ZSDVSG FRVGFAVFZ. “IWUU OSM VFUU YF IES ZFRSMRDFZ EWY?”

“WV WT APAWRTV GMUF,” ARTIFGFZ VEF CWGTV; “HMV OSM DAR ATK EWY SC TAWRV
ARVSWRF EFGF.”

VEF ZSDVSG VMGRFZ EWT FOFT MXSR VEAV YAR. IES YSJFZ MRFATWUO SR EWT
CFFV, GMHHFZ EWT HFAGZ A UWVVUF, ARZ AV UFRPVE TAWZ:

“IFUU! VGMUO WV WT APAWRTV GMUF. HMV EF WT ZFRSMRDFZ--ARZ PGAJFUO--HO
VEF DWVWBFR ARZ DWVWBFRFTT ZFCAGPF. ARZ HO SRF SVEFG.”

“IEAV SVEFG?”

“ZS _OSM_ ATK, DWVWBFR ZSDVSG?”

“OFT.”

“VEFR,” TAWZ EF SC TAWRV ARVSWRF, IWVE A TVGARPF USSK, “OSM IWUU HF
ARTIFGFZ VS-YSGGSI. RSI, W AY ZMYH!”




JWWW. A EARZ AV DAGZT


EAXXWUO MRDSRTDWSMT SC VEF RFI DAUAYWVO AV ESYF, YWTT XGSTT VEGFAZFZ EFG
IAO AUSRP VEF RAGGSI TVGFFVT ARZ DGSTTFZ VEF GWJFG HO VEF HGWZPF SC VEF
XSRV-RFMC, GFDKSRWRP WR EFG YWRZ VEF RMYHFG SC WRZWTXFRTAHUF XMGDEATFT
TEF EAZ VS YAKF. YG. DGMRDEFG, IWVE VEF HATKFV, IAUKFZ AV EFG TWZF. VEFO
HSVE USSKFZ VS VEF GWPEV ARZ VS VEF UFCV WRVS YSTV SC VEF TESXT VEFO
XATTFZ, EAZ A IAGO FOF CSG AUU PGFPAGWSMT ATTFYHUAPFT SC XFSXUF, ARZ
VMGRFZ SMV SC VEFWG GSAZ VS AJSWZ ARO JFGO FQDWVFZ PGSMX SC VAUKFGT. WV
IAT A GAI FJFRWRP, ARZ VEF YWTVO GWJFG, HUMGGFZ VS VEF FOF IWVE HUABWRP
UWPEVT ARZ VS VEF FAG IWVE EAGTE RSWTFT, TESIFZ IEFGF VEF HAGPFT IFGF
TVAVWSRFZ WR IEWDE VEF TYWVET ISGKFZ, YAKWRP PMRT CSG VEF AGYO SC VEF
GFXMHUWD. ISF VS VEF YAR IES XUAOFZ VGWDKT IWVE _VEAV_ AGYO, SG PSV
MRZFTFGJFZ XGSYSVWSR WR WV! HFVVFG CSG EWY VEAV EWT HFAGZ EAZ RFJFG
PGSIR, CSG VEF RAVWSRAU GABSG TEAJFZ EWY DUSTF.

EAJWRP XMGDEATFZ A CFI TYAUU AGVWDUFT SC PGSDFGO, ARZ A YFATMGF SC SWU
CSG VEF UAYX, YWTT XGSTT HFVESMPEV EFGTFUC SC VEF IWRF VEFO IARVFZ.
ACVFG XFFXWRP WRVS TFJFGAU IWRF-TESXT, TEF TVSXXFZ AV VEF TWPR SC VEF
PSSZ GFXMHUWDAR HGMVMT SC ARVWNMWVO, RSV CAG CGSY VEF RAVWSRAU XAUADF,
SRDF (ARZ VIWDF) VEF VMWUFGWFT, IEFGF VEF ATXFDV SC VEWRPT GAVEFG
VSSK EFG CARDO. WV EAZ A NMWFVFG USSK VEAR ARO SVEFG XUADF SC VEF TAYF
ZFTDGWXVWSR VEFO EAZ XATTFZ, ARZ, VESMPE GFZ IWVE XAVGWSVWD DAXT, IAT
RSV TS GFZ AT VEF GFTV. TSMRZWRP YG. DGMRDEFG, ARZ CWRZWRP EWY SC EFG
SXWRWSR, YWTT XGSTT GFTSGVFZ VS VEF PSSZ GFXMHUWDAR HGMVMT SC ARVWNMWVO,
AVVFRZFZ HO EFG DAJAUWFG.

TUWPEVUO SHTFGJARV SC VEF TYSKO UWPEVT; SC VEF XFSXUF, XWXF WR YSMVE,
XUAOWRP IWVE UWYX DAGZT ARZ OFUUSI ZSYWRSFT; SC VEF SRF HAGF-HGFATVFZ,
