VEF SVEFGT UWTVFRWRP VS EWY; SC VEF IFAXSRT ISGR, SG UAWZ ATWZF VS HF
GFTMYFZ; SC VEF VIS SG VEGFF DMTVSYFGT CAUUFR CSGIAGZ ATUFFX, IES WR VEF
XSXMUAG EWPE-TESMUZFGFZ TEAPPO HUADK TXFRDFG USSKFZ, WR VEAV AVVWVMZF,
UWKF TUMYHFGWRP HFAGT SG ZSPT; VEF VIS SMVUARZWTE DMTVSYFGT AXXGSADEFZ
VEF DSMRVFG, ARZ TESIFZ IEAV VEFO IARVFZ.

AT VEFWG IWRF IAT YFATMGWRP SMV, A YAR XAGVFZ CGSY ARSVEFG YAR WR A
DSGRFG, ARZ GSTF VS ZFXAGV. WR PSWRP, EF EAZ VS CADF YWTT XGSTT. RS
TSSRFG ZWZ EF CADF EFG, VEAR YWTT XGSTT MVVFGFZ A TDGFAY, ARZ DUAXXFZ
EFG EARZT.

WR A YSYFRV, VEF IESUF DSYXARO IFGF SR VEFWG CFFV. VEAV TSYFHSZO IAT
ATTATTWRAVFZ HO TSYFHSZO JWRZWDAVWRP A ZWCCFGFRDF SC SXWRWSR IAT VEF
UWKFUWFTV SDDMGGFRDF. FJFGOHSZO USSKFZ VS TFF TSYFHSZO CAUU, HMV SRUO
TAI A YAR ARZ A ISYAR TVARZWRP TVAGWRP AV FADE SVEFG; VEF YAR IWVE AUU
VEF SMVIAGZ ATXFDV SC A CGFRDEYAR ARZ A VESGSMPE GFXMHUWDAR; VEF ISYAR,
FJWZFRVUO FRPUWTE.

IEAV IAT TAWZ WR VEWT ZWTAXXSWRVWRP ARVW-DUWYAQ, HO VEF ZWTDWXUFT SC VEF
PSSZ GFXMHUWDAR HGMVMT SC ARVWNMWVO, FQDFXV VEAV WV IAT TSYFVEWRP JFGO
JSUMHUF ARZ USMZ, ISMUZ EAJF HFFR AT TS YMDE EFHGFI SG DEAUZFAR VS YWTT
