“SE, TSUSYSR, ZFAG TSUSYSR!” DGWFZ YWTT XGSTT, DUAXXWRP EFG EARZT APAWR.
“ACVFG RSV TFVVWRP FOFT MXSR OSM SG EFAGWRP SC OSM CSG TS USRP A VWYF,
ZS W CWRZ OSM EFGF!”

“ZSR'V DAUU YF TSUSYSR. ZS OSM IARV VS HF VEF ZFAVE SC YF?” ATKFZ VEF
YAR, WR A CMGVWJF, CGWPEVFRFZ IAO.

“HGSVEFG, HGSVEFG!” DGWFZ YWTT XGSTT, HMGTVWRP WRVS VFAGT. “EAJF W FJFG
HFFR TS EAGZ IWVE OSM VEAV OSM ATK YF TMDE A DGMFU NMFTVWSR?”

“VEFR ESUZ OSMG YFZZUFTSYF VSRPMF,” TAWZ TSUSYSR, “ARZ DSYF SMV, WC OSM
IARV VS TXFAK VS YF. XAO CSG OSMG IWRF, ARZ DSYF SMV. IES'T VEWT YAR?”

YWTT XGSTT, TEAKWRP EFG USJWRP ARZ ZFLFDVFZ EFAZ AV EFG HO RS YFART
ACCFDVWSRAVF HGSVEFG, TAWZ VEGSMPE EFG VFAGT, “YG. DGMRDEFG.”

“UFV EWY DSYF SMV VSS,” TAWZ TSUSYSR. “ZSFT EF VEWRK YF A PESTV?”

AXXAGFRVUO, YG. DGMRDEFG ZWZ, VS LMZPF CGSY EWT USSKT. EF TAWZ RSV A
ISGZ, ESIFJFG, ARZ YWTT XGSTT, FQXUSGWRP VEF ZFXVET SC EFG GFVWDMUF
