ACCFDVWSR.”

“VEFGF. DSRCSMRZ WV! VEFGF,” TAWZ TSUSYSR, YAKWRP A ZAH AV YWTT XGSTT'T
UWXT IWVE EWT SIR. “RSI AGF OSM DSRVFRV?”

YWTT XGSTT SRUO TESSK EFG EFAZ ARZ IFXV WR TWUFRDF.

“WC OSM FQXFDV YF VS HF TMGXGWTFZ,” TAWZ EFG HGSVEFG TSUSYSR, “W AY RSV
