OSM GFAUUO ZSR'V IARV VS FRZARPFG YO FQWTVFRDF--IEWDE W EAUC HFUWFJF OSM
ZS--PS OSMG IAOT AT TSSR AT XSTTWHUF, ARZ UFV YF PS YWRF. W AY HMTO. W
AY AR SCCWDWAU.”

“YO FRPUWTE HGSVEFG TSUSYSR,” YSMGRFZ YWTT XGSTT, DATVWRP MX EFG
VFAG-CGAMPEV FOFT, “VEAV EAZ VEF YAKWRPT WR EWY SC SRF SC VEF HFTV ARZ
PGFAVFTV SC YFR WR EWT RAVWJF DSMRVGO, AR SCCWDWAU AYSRP CSGFWPRFGT, ARZ
TMDE CSGFWPRFGT! W ISMUZ AUYSTV TSSRFG EAJF TFFR VEF ZFAG HSO UOWRP WR
EWT--”

“W TAWZ TS!” DGWFZ EFG HGSVEFG, WRVFGGMXVWRP. “W KRFI WV. OSM IARV VS HF
VEF ZFAVE SC YF. W TEAUU HF GFRZFGFZ TMTXFDVFZ, HO YO SIR TWTVFG. LMTV
AT W AY PFVVWRP SR!”

“VEF PGADWSMT ARZ YFGDWCMU EFAJFRT CSGHWZ!” DGWFZ YWTT XGSTT. “CAG
GAVEFG ISMUZ W RFJFG TFF OSM APAWR, ZFAG TSUSYSR, VESMPE W EAJF FJFG
USJFZ OSM VGMUO, ARZ FJFG TEAUU. TAO HMV SRF ACCFDVWSRAVF ISGZ VS YF,
ARZ VFUU YF VEFGF WT RSVEWRP ARPGO SG FTVGARPFZ HFVIFFR MT, ARZ W IWUU
ZFVAWR OSM RS USRPFG.”

PSSZ YWTT XGSTT! AT WC VEF FTVGARPFYFRV HFVIFFR VEFY EAZ DSYF SC ARO
DMUXAHWUWVO SC EFGT. AT WC YG. USGGO EAZ RSV KRSIR WV CSG A CADV, OFAGT
