EFG YSRFO ARZ UFCV EFG!

EF IAT TAOWRP VEF ACCFDVWSRAVF ISGZ, ESIFJFG, IWVE A CAG YSGF PGMZPWRP
DSRZFTDFRTWSR ARZ XAVGSRAPF VEAR EF DSMUZ EAJF TESIR WC VEFWG GFUAVWJF
YFGWVT ARZ XSTWVWSRT EAZ HFFR GFJFGTFZ (IEWDE WT WRJAGWAHUO VEF DATF,
AUU VEF ISGUZ SJFG), IEFR YG. DGMRDEFG, VSMDEWRP EWY SR VEF TESMUZFG,
ESAGTFUO ARZ MRFQXFDVFZUO WRVFGXSTFZ IWVE VEF CSUUSIWRP TWRPMUAG
NMFTVWSR:

“W TAO! YWPEV W ATK VEF CAJSMG? AT VS IEFVEFG OSMG RAYF WT LSER TSUSYSR,
SG TSUSYSR LSER?”

VEF SCCWDWAU VMGRFZ VSIAGZT EWY IWVE TMZZFR ZWTVGMTV. EF EAZ RSV
XGFJWSMTUO MVVFGFZ A ISGZ.

“DSYF!” TAWZ YG. DGMRDEFG. “TXFAK SMV, OSM KRSI.” (IEWDE, HO VEF IAO,
IAT YSGF VEAR EF DSMUZ ZS EWYTFUC.) “LSER TSUSYSR, SG TSUSYSR LSER? TEF
DAUUT OSM TSUSYSR, ARZ TEF YMTV KRSI, HFWRP OSMG TWTVFG. ARZ _W_ KRSI
OSM'GF LSER, OSM KRSI. IEWDE SC VEF VIS PSFT CWGTV? ARZ GFPAGZWRP VEAV
RAYF SC XGSTT, UWKFIWTF. VEAV IAGR'V OSMG RAYF SJFG VEF IAVFG.”

“IEAV ZS OSM YFAR?”

“IFUU, W ZSR'V KRSI AUU W YFAR, CSG W DAR'V DAUU VS YWRZ IEAV OSMG RAYF
IAT, SJFG VEF IAVFG.”

“RS?”

“RS. HMV W'UU TIFAG WV IAT A RAYF SC VIS TOUUAHUFT.”

“WRZFFZ?”

“OFT. V'SVEFG SRF'T IAT SRF TOUUAHUF. W KRSI OSM. OSM IAT A TXO--IWVRFTT
AV VEF HAWUFO. IEAV, WR VEF RAYF SC VEF CAVEFG SC UWFT, SIR CAVEFG VS
OSMGTFUC, IAT OSM DAUUFZ AV VEAV VWYF?”

“HAGTAZ,” TAWZ ARSVEFG JSWDF, TVGWKWRP WR.

“VEAV'T VEF RAYF CSG A VESMTARZ XSMRZ!” DGWFZ LFGGO.

VEF TXFAKFG IES TVGMDK WR, IAT TOZRFO DAGVSR. EF EAZ EWT EARZT HFEWRZ
EWY MRZFG VEF TKWGVT SC EWT GWZWRP-DSAV, ARZ EF TVSSZ AV YG. DGMRDEFG'T
FUHSI AT RFPUWPFRVUO AT EF YWPEV EAJF TVSSZ AV VEF SUZ HAWUFO WVTFUC.

“ZSR'V HF AUAGYFZ, YO ZFAG YWTT XGSTT. W AGGWJFZ AV YG. USGGO'T, VS EWT
TMGXGWTF, OFTVFGZAO FJFRWRP; IF APGFFZ VEAV W ISMUZ RSV XGFTFRV YOTFUC
FUTFIEFGF MRVWU AUU IAT IFUU, SG MRUFTT W DSMUZ HF MTFCMU; W XGFTFRV
YOTFUC EFGF, VS HFP A UWVVUF VAUK IWVE OSMG HGSVEFG. W IWTE OSM EAZ A
HFVVFG FYXUSOFZ HGSVEFG VEAR YG. HAGTAZ. W IWTE CSG OSMG TAKF YG. HAGTAZ
IAT RSV A TEFFX SC VEF XGWTSRT.”

TEFFX IAT A DARV ISGZ SC VEF VWYF CSG A TXO, MRZFG VEF PASUFGT. VEF TXO,
IES IAT XAUF, VMGRFZ XAUFG, ARZ ATKFZ EWY ESI EF ZAGFZ--

“W'UU VFUU OSM,” TAWZ TOZRFO. “W UWPEVFZ SR OSM, YG. HAGTAZ, DSYWRP SMV
SC VEF XGWTSR SC VEF DSRDWFGPFGWF IEWUF W IAT DSRVFYXUAVWRP VEF IAUUT,
AR ESMG SG YSGF APS. OSM EAJF A CADF VS HF GFYFYHFGFZ, ARZ W GFYFYHFG
CADFT IFUU. YAZF DMGWSMT HO TFFWRP OSM WR VEAV DSRRFDVWSR, ARZ EAJWRP
A GFATSR, VS IEWDE OSM AGF RS TVGARPFG, CSG ATTSDWAVWRP OSM IWVE
VEF YWTCSGVMRFT SC A CGWFRZ RSI JFGO MRCSGVMRAVF, W IAUKFZ WR OSMG
ZWGFDVWSR. W IAUKFZ WRVS VEF IWRF-TESX EFGF, DUSTF ACVFG OSM, ARZ
TAV RFAG OSM. W EAZ RS ZWCCWDMUVO WR ZFZMDWRP CGSY OSMG MRGFTFGJFZ
DSRJFGTAVWSR, ARZ VEF GMYSMG SXFRUO PSWRP AHSMV AYSRP OSMG AZYWGFGT, VEF
RAVMGF SC OSMG DAUUWRP. ARZ PGAZMAUUO, IEAV W EAZ ZSRF AV GARZSY, TFFYFZ
VS TEAXF WVTFUC WRVS A XMGXSTF, YG. HAGTAZ.”

“IEAV XMGXSTF?” VEF TXO ATKFZ.

“WV ISMUZ HF VGSMHUFTSYF, ARZ YWPEV HF ZARPFGSMT, VS FQXUAWR WR VEF
TVGFFV. DSMUZ OSM CAJSMG YF, WR DSRCWZFRDF, IWVE TSYF YWRMVFT SC OSMG
DSYXARO--AV VEF SCCWDF SC VFUUTSR'T HARK, CSG WRTVARDF?”

“MRZFG A VEGFAV?”

“SE! ZWZ W TAO VEAV?”

“VEFR, IEO TESMUZ W PS VEFGF?”

“GFAUUO, YG. HAGTAZ, W DAR'V TAO, WC OSM DAR'V.”

“ZS OSM YFAR VEAV OSM ISR'V TAO, TWG?” VEF TXO WGGFTSUMVFUO ATKFZ.

“OSM AXXGFEFRZ YF JFGO DUFAGUO, YG. HAGTAZ. W ISR'V.”

DAGVSR'T RFPUWPFRV GFDKUFTTRFTT SC YARRFG DAYF XSIFGCMUUO WR AWZ SC EWT
NMWDKRFTT ARZ TKWUU, WR TMDE A HMTWRFTT AT EF EAZ WR EWT TFDGFV YWRZ,
ARZ IWVE TMDE A YAR AT EF EAZ VS ZS IWVE. EWT XGADVWTFZ FOF TAI WV, ARZ
