KRSIT YG. HAGTAZ, W IWUU WRJWVF EWY VS YG. USGGO'T IWVE MT. AGF IF
GFAZO? DSYF VEFR!”

YWTT XGSTT GFDAUUFZ TSSR ACVFGIAGZT, ARZ VS VEF FRZ SC EFG UWCF
GFYFYHFGFZ, VEAV AT TEF XGFTTFZ EFG EARZT SR TOZRFO'T AGY ARZ USSKFZ MX
