XMGXSTF WR VEF AGY ARZ A KWRZ SC WRTXWGAVWSR WR VEF FOFT, IEWDE RSV SRUO
DSRVGAZWDVFZ EWT UWPEV YARRFG, HMV DEARPFZ ARZ GAWTFZ VEF YAR. TEF IAT
VSS YMDE SDDMXWFZ VEFR IWVE CFAGT CSG VEF HGSVEFG IES TS UWVVUF ZFTFGJFZ
EFG ACCFDVWSR, ARZ IWVE TOZRFO'T CGWFRZUO GFATTMGARDFT, AZFNMAVFUO VS
EFFZ IEAV TEF SHTFGJFZ.

VEFO UFCV EFG AV VEF DSGRFG SC VEF TVGFFV, ARZ DAGVSR UFZ VEF IAO VS YG.
USGGO'T, IEWDE IAT IWVEWR A CFI YWRMVFT' IAUK. LSER HAGTAZ, SG TSUSYSR
XGSTT, IAUKFZ AV EWT TWZF.

YG. USGGO EAZ LMTV CWRWTEFZ EWT ZWRRFG, ARZ IAT TWVVWRP HFCSGF A DEFFGO
UWVVUF USP SG VIS SC CWGF--XFGEAXT USSKWRP WRVS VEFWG HUABF CSG VEF
XWDVMGF SC VEAV OSMRPFG FUZFGUO PFRVUFYAR CGSY VFUUTSR'T, IES EAZ USSKFZ
WRVS VEF GFZ DSAUT AV VEF GSOAU PFSGPF AV ZSJFG, RSI A PSSZ YARO OFAGT
