IEWDE EF TAI A TVGARPFG.

“YWTT XGSTT'T HGSVEFG, TWG,” TAWZ TOZRFO. “YG. HAGTAZ.”

“HAGTAZ?” GFXFAVFZ VEF SUZ PFRVUFYAR, “HAGTAZ? W EAJF AR ATTSDWAVWSR
IWVE VEF RAYF--ARZ IWVE VEF CADF.”

“W VSUZ OSM OSM EAZ A GFYAGKAHUF CADF, YG. HAGTAZ,” SHTFGJFZ DAGVSR,
DSSUUO. “XGAO TWV ZSIR.”

AT EF VSSK A DEAWG EWYTFUC, EF TMXXUWFZ VEF UWRK VEAV YG. USGGO IARVFZ,
HO TAOWRP VS EWY IWVE A CGSIR, “IWVRFTT AV VEAV VGWAU.” YG. USGGO
WYYFZWAVFUO GFYFYHFGFZ, ARZ GFPAGZFZ EWT RFI JWTWVSG IWVE AR MRZWTPMWTFZ
USSK SC AHESGGFRDF.

“YG. HAGTAZ EAT HFFR GFDSPRWTFZ HO YWTT XGSTT AT VEF ACCFDVWSRAVF
HGSVEFG OSM EAJF EFAGZ SC,” TAWZ TOZRFO, “ARZ EAT ADKRSIUFZPFZ VEF
GFUAVWSRTEWX. W XATT VS ISGTF RFIT. ZAGRAO EAT HFFR AGGFTVFZ APAWR.”

TVGMDK IWVE DSRTVFGRAVWSR, VEF SUZ PFRVUFYAR FQDUAWYFZ, “IEAV ZS OSM
VFUU YF! W UFCV EWY TACF ARZ CGFF IWVEWR VEFTF VIS ESMGT, ARZ AY AHSMV
VS GFVMGR VS EWY!”

“AGGFTVFZ CSG AUU VEAV. IEFR IAT WV ZSRF, YG. HAGTAZ?”

“LMTV RSI, WC AV AUU.”

“YG. HAGTAZ WT VEF HFTV AMVESGWVO XSTTWHUF, TWG,” TAWZ TOZRFO, “ARZ W
EAJF WV CGSY YG. HAGTAZ'T DSYYMRWDAVWSR VS A CGWFRZ ARZ HGSVEFG TEFFX
SJFG A HSVVUF SC IWRF, VEAV VEF AGGFTV EAT VAKFR XUADF. EF UFCV VEF
YFTTFRPFGT AV VEF PAVF, ARZ TAI VEFY AZYWVVFZ HO VEF XSGVFG. VEFGF WT RS
FAGVEUO ZSMHV VEAV EF WT GFVAKFR.”

YG. USGGO'T HMTWRFTT FOF GFAZ WR VEF TXFAKFG'T CADF VEAV WV IAT USTT
SC VWYF VS ZIFUU MXSR VEF XSWRV. DSRCMTFZ, HMV TFRTWHUF VEAV TSYFVEWRP
YWPEV ZFXFRZ SR EWT XGFTFRDF SC YWRZ, EF DSYYARZFZ EWYTFUC, ARZ IAT
TWUFRVUO AVVFRVWJF.

“RSI, W VGMTV,” TAWZ TOZRFO VS EWY, “VEAV VEF RAYF ARZ WRCUMFRDF SC
ZSDVSG YARFVVF YAO TVARZ EWY WR AT PSSZ TVFAZ VS-YSGGSI--OSM TAWZ EF
ISMUZ HF HFCSGF VEF VGWHMRAU APAWR VS-YSGGSI, YG. HAGTAZ?--”

“OFT; W HFUWFJF TS.”

“--WR AT PSSZ TVFAZ VS-YSGGSI AT VS-ZAO. HMV WV YAO RSV HF TS. W SIR
VS OSM, W AY TEAKFR, YG. USGGO, HO ZSDVSG YARFVVF'T RSV EAJWRP EAZ VEF
XSIFG VS XGFJFRV VEWT AGGFTV.”

“EF YAO RSV EAJF KRSIR SC WV HFCSGFEARZ,” TAWZ YG. USGGO.

“HMV VEAV JFGO DWGDMYTVARDF ISMUZ HF AUAGYWRP, IEFR IF GFYFYHFG ESI
WZFRVWCWFZ EF WT IWVE EWT TSR-WR-UAI.”

“VEAV'T VGMF,” YG. USGGO ADKRSIUFZPFZ, IWVE EWT VGSMHUFZ EARZ AV EWT
DEWR, ARZ EWT VGSMHUFZ FOFT SR DAGVSR.

“WR TESGV,” TAWZ TOZRFO, “VEWT WT A ZFTXFGAVF VWYF, IEFR ZFTXFGAVF PAYFT
AGF XUAOFZ CSG ZFTXFGAVF TVAKFT. UFV VEF ZSDVSG XUAO VEF IWRRWRP PAYF; W
