“OSM RFFZ EAJF PSSZ DAGZT, TWG,” TAWZ VEF TXO.

“W'UU GMR VEFY SJFG. W'UU TFF IEAV W ESUZ,--YG. USGGO, OSM KRSI IEAV A
HGMVF W AY; W IWTE OSM'Z PWJF YF A UWVVUF HGARZO.”

WV IAT XMV HFCSGF EWY, ARZ EF ZGARK SCC A PUATTCMU--ZGARK SCC ARSVEFG
PUATTCMU--XMTEFZ VEF HSVVUF VESMPEVCMUUO AIAO.

“YG. HAGTAZ,” EF IFRV SR, WR VEF VSRF SC SRF IES GFAUUO IAT USSKWRP
SJFG A EARZ AV DAGZT: “TEFFX SC VEF XGWTSRT, FYWTTAGO SC GFXMHUWDAR
