ZWCCWDMUV VS CWRZ. VEAV'T A DAGZ RSV VS HF HFAVFR. EAJF OSM CSUUSIFZ YO
EARZ, YG. HAGTAZ?”

“RSV VS MRZFGTVARZ OSMG XUAO,” GFVMGRFZ VEF TXO, TSYFIEAV MRFATWUO.

“W XUAO YO ADF, ZFRMRDWAVWSR SC YG. HAGTAZ VS VEF RFAGFTV TFDVWSR
DSYYWVVFF. USSK SJFG OSMG EARZ, YG. HAGTAZ, ARZ TFF IEAV OSM EAJF. ZSR'V
