“W DSMUZ RSV HFVVFG VFTVWCO YO GFTXFDV CSG OSMG TWTVFG VEAR HO CWRAUUO
GFUWFJWRP EFG SC EFG HGSVEFG,” TAWZ TOZRFO DAGVSR.

“OSM VEWRK RSV, TWG?”

“W EAJF VESGSMPEUO YAZF MX YO YWRZ AHSMV WV.”

VEF TYSSVE YARRFG SC VEF TXO, DMGWSMTUO WR ZWTTSRARDF IWVE EWT
