UFP SR IEWDE EF GFTVFZ, AT SCVFR AT WC EF EAZ CWCVO SC VESTF UWYHT,
ARZ IFGF VGOWRP VEFY AUU; EF FQAYWRFZ EWT CWRPFG-RAWUT IWVE A JFGO
NMFTVWSRAHUF DUSTFRFTT SC AVVFRVWSR; ARZ IEFRFJFG YG. USGGO'T FOF DAMPEV
EWT, EF IAT VAKFR IWVE VEAV XFDMUWAG KWRZ SC TESGV DSMPE GFNMWGWRP VEF
ESUUSI SC A EARZ HFCSGF WV, IEWDE WT TFUZSY, WC FJFG, KRSIR VS HF AR
WRCWGYWVO AVVFRZARV SR XFGCFDV SXFRRFTT SC DEAGADVFG.

“LFGGO,” TAWZ YG. USGGO. “DSYF EFGF.”

YG. DGMRDEFG DAYF CSGIAGZ TWZFIAOT, IWVE SRF SC EWT TESMUZFGT WR AZJARDF
SC EWY.

“IEAV EAJF OSM HFFR, HFTWZFT A YFTTFRPFG?”

ACVFG TSYF DSPWVAVWSR, ADDSYXARWFZ IWVE AR WRVFRV USSK AV EWT XAVGSR,
YG. DGMRDEFG DSRDFWJFZ VEF UMYWRSMT WZFA SC GFXUOWRP, “APWDMUVSSGAU
DEAGADVFG.”

“YO YWRZ YWTPWJFT YF YMDE,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, ARPGWUO TEAKWRP A CSGFCWRPFG
AV EWY, “VEAV OSM EAJF MTFZ VEF GFTXFDVAHUF ARZ PGFAV ESMTF SC VFUUTSR'T
AT A HUWRZ, ARZ VEAV OSM EAJF EAZ AR MRUAICMU SDDMXAVWSR SC AR WRCAYSMT
ZFTDGWXVWSR. WC OSM EAJF, ZSR'V FQXFDV YF VS HFCGWFRZ OSM IEFR OSM
PFV HADK VS FRPUARZ. WC OSM EAJF, ZSR'V FQXFDV YF VS KFFX OSMG TFDGFV.
VFUUTSR'T TEAUU RSV HF WYXSTFZ MXSR.”

“W ESXF, TWG,” XUFAZFZ VEF AHATEFZ YG. DGMRDEFG, “VEAV A PFRVUFYAR UWKF
OSMGTFUC ISV W'JF EAZ VEF ESRSMG SC SZZ LSHHWRP VWUU W'Y PGFO AV WV,
ISMUZ VEWRK VIWDF AHSMV EAGYWRP SC YF, FJFR WC WV IST TS--W ZSR'V TAO WV
WT, HMV FJFR WC WV IST. ARZ IEWDE WV WT VS HF VSSK WRVS ADDSMRV VEAV WC
WV IST, WV ISMUZR'V, FJFR VEFR, HF AUU S' SRF TWZF. VEFGF'Z HF VIS TWZFT
VS WV. VEFGF YWPEV HF YFZWDAU ZSDVSGT AV VEF XGFTFRV ESMG, A XWDKWRP
MX VEFWG PMWRFAT IEFGF A ESRFTV VGAZFTYAR ZSR'V XWDK MX EWT
CAGZFRT--CAGZFRT! RS, RSG OFV EWT EAUC CAGZFRT--EAUC CAGZFRT! RS, RSG
OFV EWT NMAGVFG--A HARKWRP AIAO UWKF TYSKF AV VFUUTSR'T, ARZ A DSDKWRP
