TOZRFO DAGVSR VSSK RS EFFZ, ARZ VEF DEFYWTV TAWZ:

“CSG OSM, DWVWBFR?”

“CSG YF.”

“OSM IWUU HF DAGFCMU VS KFFX VEFY TFXAGAVF, DWVWBFR? OSM KRSI VEF
