USRP APS, IEFR EF EAZ HFFR CAYSMT AYSRP EWT FAGUWFTV DSYXFVWVSGT AT A
OSMVE SC PGFAV XGSYWTF, EF EAZ CSUUSIFZ EWT CAVEFG VS VEF PGAJF. EWT
YSVEFG EAZ ZWFZ, OFAGT HFCSGF. VEFTF TSUFYR ISGZT, IEWDE EAZ HFFR
GFAZ AV EWT CAVEFG'T PGAJF, AGSTF WR EWT YWRZ AT EF IFRV ZSIR VEF ZAGK
TVGFFVT, AYSRP VEF EFAJO TEAZSIT, IWVE VEF YSSR ARZ VEF DUSMZT TAWUWRP
SR EWPE AHSJF EWY. “W AY VEF GFTMGGFDVWSR ARZ VEF UWCF, TAWVE VEF USGZ:
EF VEAV HFUWFJFVE WR YF, VESMPE EF IFGF ZFAZ, OFV TEAUU EF UWJF: ARZ
IESTSFJFG UWJFVE ARZ HFUWFJFVE WR YF, TEAUU RFJFG ZWF.”

WR A DWVO ZSYWRAVFZ HO VEF AQF, AUSRF AV RWPEV, IWVE RAVMGAU TSGGSI
GWTWRP WR EWY CSG VEF TWQVO-VEGFF IES EAZ HFFR VEAV ZAO XMV VS ZFAVE,
ARZ CSG VS-YSGGSI'T JWDVWYT VEFR AIAWVWRP VEFWG ZSSY WR VEF XGWTSRT,
ARZ TVWUU SC VS-YSGGSI'T ARZ VS-YSGGSI'T, VEF DEAWR SC ATTSDWAVWSR VEAV
HGSMPEV VEF ISGZT ESYF, UWKF A GMTVO SUZ TEWX'T ARDESG CGSY VEF ZFFX,
YWPEV EAJF HFFR FATWUO CSMRZ. EF ZWZ RSV TFFK WV, HMV GFXFAVFZ VEFY ARZ
IFRV SR.

