EAZ SC EFG.

“'WT TEF ZFAZ?' ATKFZ VEF YAGNMWT, IESY W IWUU TVWUU ZFTDGWHF AT VEF
FUZFG HGSVEFG, DSYWRP HSSVFZ WRVS VEF GSSY CGSY EWT ESGTF.

“'RSV ZFAZ,' TAWZ W; 'HMV UWKF VS ZWF.'

“'IEAV TVGFRPVE VEFGF WT WR VEFTF DSYYSR HSZWFT!' EF TAWZ, USSKWRP ZSIR
