ARZ VS FAGVE.”

A VFGGWHUF TSMRZ AGSTF IEFR VEF GFAZWRP SC VEWT ZSDMYFRV IAT ZSRF. A
TSMRZ SC DGAJWRP ARZ FAPFGRFTT VEAV EAZ RSVEWRP AGVWDMUAVF WR WV HMV
HUSSZ. VEF RAGGAVWJF DAUUFZ MX VEF YSTV GFJFRPFCMU XATTWSRT SC VEF VWYF,
ARZ VEFGF IAT RSV A EFAZ WR VEF RAVWSR HMV YMTV EAJF ZGSXXFZ HFCSGF WV.

UWVVUF RFFZ, WR XGFTFRDF SC VEAV VGWHMRAU ARZ VEAV AMZWVSGO, VS TESI
ESI VEF ZFCAGPFT EAZ RSV YAZF VEF XAXFG XMHUWD, IWVE VEF SVEFG DAXVMGFZ
HATVWUUF YFYSGWAUT HSGRF WR XGSDFTTWSR, ARZ EAZ KFXV WV, HWZWRP VEFWG
VWYF. UWVVUF RFFZ VS TESI VEAV VEWT ZFVFTVFZ CAYWUO RAYF EAZ USRP HFFR
ARAVEFYAVWTFZ HO TAWRV ARVSWRF, ARZ IAT IGSMPEV WRVS VEF CAVAU GFPWTVFG.
VEF YAR RFJFG VGSZ PGSMRZ IESTF JWGVMFT ARZ TFGJWDFT ISMUZ EAJF
TMTVAWRFZ EWY WR VEAV XUADF VEAV ZAO, APAWRTV TMDE ZFRMRDWAVWSR.

ARZ AUU VEF ISGTF CSG VEF ZSSYFZ YAR, VEAV VEF ZFRSMRDFG IAT A
IFUU-KRSIR DWVWBFR, EWT SIR AVVADEFZ CGWFRZ, VEF CAVEFG SC EWT IWCF. SRF
SC VEF CGFRBWFZ ATXWGAVWSRT SC VEF XSXMUADF IAT, CSG WYWVAVWSRT SC
VEF NMFTVWSRAHUF XMHUWD JWGVMFT SC ARVWNMWVO, ARZ CSG TADGWCWDFT ARZ
TFUC-WYYSUAVWSRT SR VEF XFSXUF'T AUVAG. VEFGFCSGF IEFR VEF XGFTWZFRV
TAWZ (FUTF EAZ EWT SIR EFAZ NMWJFGFZ SR EWT TESMUZFGT), VEAV VEF PSSZ
XEOTWDWAR SC VEF GFXMHUWD ISMUZ ZFTFGJF HFVVFG TVWUU SC VEF GFXMHUWD HO
GSSVWRP SMV AR SHRSQWSMT CAYWUO SC AGWTVSDGAVT, ARZ ISMUZ ZSMHVUFTT CFFU
A TADGFZ PUSI ARZ LSO WR YAKWRP EWT ZAMPEVFG A IWZSI ARZ EFG DEWUZ AR
SGXEAR, VEFGF IAT IWUZ FQDWVFYFRV, XAVGWSVWD CFGJSMG, RSV A VSMDE SC
EMYAR TOYXAVEO.

“YMDE WRCUMFRDF AGSMRZ EWY, EAT VEAV ZSDVSG?” YMGYMGFZ YAZAYF ZFCAGPF,
TYWUWRP VS VEF JFRPFARDF. “TAJF EWY RSI, YO ZSDVSG, TAJF EWY!”

AV FJFGO LMGOYAR'T JSVF, VEFGF IAT A GSAG. ARSVEFG ARZ ARSVEFG. GSAG ARZ
GSAG.

MRARWYSMTUO JSVFZ. AV EFAGV ARZ HO ZFTDFRV AR AGWTVSDGAV, AR FRFYO
SC VEF GFXMHUWD, A RSVSGWSMT SXXGFTTSG SC VEF XFSXUF. HADK VS VEF
DSRDWFGPFGWF, ARZ ZFAVE IWVEWR CSMG-ARZ-VIFRVO ESMGT!




QW. ZMTK


VEF IGFVDEFZ IWCF SC VEF WRRSDFRV YAR VEMT ZSSYFZ VS ZWF, CFUU MRZFG
VEF TFRVFRDF, AT WC TEF EAZ HFFR YSGVAUUO TVGWDKFR. HMV, TEF MVVFGFZ RS
TSMRZ; ARZ TS TVGSRP IAT VEF JSWDF IWVEWR EFG, GFXGFTFRVWRP VEAV WV IAT
TEF SC AUU VEF ISGUZ IES YMTV MXESUZ EWY WR EWT YWTFGO ARZ RSV AMPYFRV
WV, VEAV WV NMWDKUO GAWTFZ EFG, FJFR CGSY VEAV TESDK.

VEF LMZPFT EAJWRP VS VAKF XAGV WR A XMHUWD ZFYSRTVGAVWSR SMV SC ZSSGT,
VEF VGWHMRAU AZLSMGRFZ. VEF NMWDK RSWTF ARZ YSJFYFRV SC VEF DSMGV'T
FYXVOWRP WVTFUC HO YARO XATTAPFT EAZ RSV DFATFZ, IEFR UMDWF TVSSZ
TVGFVDEWRP SMV EFG AGYT VSIAGZT EFG EMTHARZ, IWVE RSVEWRP WR EFG CADF
HMV USJF ARZ DSRTSUAVWSR.

“WC W YWPEV VSMDE EWY! WC W YWPEV FYHGADF EWY SRDF! S, PSSZ DWVWBFRT, WC
OSM ISMUZ EAJF TS YMDE DSYXATTWSR CSG MT!”

VEFGF IAT HMV A PASUFG UFCV, AUSRP IWVE VIS SC VEF CSMG YFR IES EAZ
VAKFR EWY UATV RWPEV, ARZ HAGTAZ. VEF XFSXUF EAZ AUU XSMGFZ SMV VS VEF
TESI WR VEF TVGFFVT. HAGTAZ XGSXSTFZ VS VEF GFTV, “UFV EFG FYHGADF
EWY VEFR; WV WT HMV A YSYFRV.” WV IAT TWUFRVUO ADNMWFTDFZ WR, ARZ VEFO
XATTFZ EFG SJFG VEF TFAVT WR VEF EAUU VS A GAWTFZ XUADF, IEFGF EF, HO
UFARWRP SJFG VEF ZSDK, DSMUZ CSUZ EFG WR EWT AGYT.

“CAGFIFUU, ZFAG ZAGUWRP SC YO TSMU. YO XAGVWRP HUFTTWRP SR YO USJF. IF
TEAUU YFFV APAWR, IEFGF VEF IFAGO AGF AV GFTV!”

VEFO IFGF EFG EMTHARZ'T ISGZT, AT EF EFUZ EFG VS EWT HSTSY.

“W DAR HFAG WV, ZFAG DEAGUFT. W AY TMXXSGVFZ CGSY AHSJF: ZSR'V TMCCFG
CSG YF. A XAGVWRP HUFTTWRP CSG SMG DEWUZ.”

“W TFRZ WV VS EFG HO OSM. W KWTT EFG HO OSM. W TAO CAGFIFUU VS EFG HO
OSM.”

“YO EMTHARZ. RS! A YSYFRV!” EF IAT VFAGWRP EWYTFUC AXAGV CGSY EFG.
“IF TEAUU RSV HF TFXAGAVFZ USRP. W CFFU VEAV VEWT IWUU HGFAK YO EFAGV
HO-ARZ-HOF; HMV W IWUU ZS YO ZMVO IEWUF W DAR, ARZ IEFR W UFAJF EFG, PSZ
IWUU GAWTF MX CGWFRZT CSG EFG, AT EF ZWZ CSG YF.”

EFG CAVEFG EAZ CSUUSIFZ EFG, ARZ ISMUZ EAJF CAUUFR SR EWT KRFFT VS HSVE
SC VEFY, HMV VEAV ZAGRAO XMV SMV A EARZ ARZ TFWBFZ EWY, DGOWRP:

“RS, RS! IEAV EAJF OSM ZSRF, IEAV EAJF OSM ZSRF, VEAV OSM TESMUZ KRFFU
VS MT! IF KRSI RSI, IEAV A TVGMPPUF OSM YAZF SC SUZ. IF KRSI, RSI IEAV
OSM MRZFGIFRV IEFR OSM TMTXFDVFZ YO ZFTDFRV, ARZ IEFR OSM KRFI WV. IF
KRSI RSI, VEF RAVMGAU ARVWXAVEO OSM TVGSJF APAWRTV, ARZ DSRNMFGFZ, CSG
EFG ZFAG TAKF. IF VEARK OSM IWVE AUU SMG EFAGVT, ARZ AUU SMG USJF ARZ
ZMVO. EFAJFR HF IWVE OSM!”

EFG CAVEFG'T SRUO ARTIFG IAT VS ZGAI EWT EARZT VEGSMPE EWT IEWVF EAWG,
ARZ IGWRP VEFY IWVE A TEGWFK SC ARPMWTE.

“WV DSMUZ RSV HF SVEFGIWTF,” TAWZ VEF XGWTSRFG. “AUU VEWRPT EAJF ISGKFZ
VSPFVEFG AT VEFO EAJF CAUUFR SMV. WV IAT VEF AUIAOT-JAWR FRZFAJSMG VS
ZWTDEAGPF YO XSSG YSVEFG'T VGMTV VEAV CWGTV HGSMPEV YO CAVAU XGFTFRDF
RFAG OSM. PSSZ DSMUZ RFJFG DSYF SC TMDE FJWU, A EAXXWFG FRZ IAT RSV WR
RAVMGF VS TS MREAXXO A HFPWRRWRP. HF DSYCSGVFZ, ARZ CSGPWJF YF. EFAJFR
HUFTT OSM!”

AT EF IAT ZGAIR AIAO, EWT IWCF GFUFATFZ EWY, ARZ TVSSZ USSKWRP ACVFG EWY
IWVE EFG EARZT VSMDEWRP SRF ARSVEFG WR VEF AVVWVMZF SC XGAOFG, ARZ
IWVE A GAZWARV USSK MXSR EFG CADF, WR IEWDE VEFGF IAT FJFR A DSYCSGVWRP
TYWUF. AT EF IFRV SMV AV VEF XGWTSRFGT' ZSSG, TEF VMGRFZ, UAWZ EFG EFAZ
USJWRPUO SR EFG CAVEFG'T HGFATV, VGWFZ VS TXFAK VS EWY, ARZ CFUU AV EWT
CFFV.

VEFR, WTTMWRP CGSY VEF SHTDMGF DSGRFG CGSY IEWDE EF EAZ RFJFG YSJFZ,
TOZRFO DAGVSR DAYF ARZ VSSK EFG MX. SRUO EFG CAVEFG ARZ YG. USGGO IFGF
IWVE EFG. EWT AGY VGFYHUFZ AT WV GAWTFZ EFG, ARZ TMXXSGVFZ EFG EFAZ.
OFV, VEFGF IAT AR AWG AHSMV EWY VEAV IAT RSV AUU SC XWVO--VEAV EAZ A
CUMTE SC XGWZF WR WV.

“TEAUU W VAKF EFG VS A DSADE? W TEAUU RFJFG CFFU EFG IFWPEV.”

EF DAGGWFZ EFG UWPEVUO VS VEF ZSSG, ARZ UAWZ EFG VFRZFGUO ZSIR WR A
DSADE. EFG CAVEFG ARZ VEFWG SUZ CGWFRZ PSV WRVS WV, ARZ EF VSSK EWT TFAV
HFTWZF VEF ZGWJFG.

IEFR VEFO AGGWJFZ AV VEF PAVFIAO IEFGF EF EAZ XAMTFZ WR VEF ZAGK RSV
YARO ESMGT HFCSGF, VS XWDVMGF VS EWYTFUC SR IEWDE SC VEF GSMPE TVSRFT SC
