VEF TVAWGDATF VS VEFWG GSSYT. VEFGF, EF UAWZ EFG ZSIR SR A DSMDE, IEFGF
EFG DEWUZ ARZ YWTT XGSTT IFXV SJFG EFG.

“ZSR'V GFDAUU EFG VS EFGTFUC,” EF TAWZ, TSCVUO, VS VEF UAVVFG, “TEF WT
HFVVFG TS. ZSR'V GFJWJF EFG VS DSRTDWSMTRFTT, IEWUF TEF SRUO CAWRVT.”

“SE, DAGVSR, DAGVSR, ZFAG DAGVSR!” DGWFZ UWVVUF UMDWF, TXGWRPWRP MX ARZ
VEGSIWRP EFG AGYT XATTWSRAVFUO GSMRZ EWY, WR A HMGTV SC PGWFC. “RSI VEAV
