TAJF XAXA! S, USSK AV EFG, ZFAG DAGVSR! DAR OSM, SC AUU VEF XFSXUF IES
USJF EFG, HFAG VS TFF EFG TS?”

EF HFRV SJFG VEF DEWUZ, ARZ UAWZ EFG HUSSYWRP DEFFK APAWRTV EWT CADF. EF
XMV EFG PFRVUO CGSY EWY, ARZ USSKFZ AV EFG MRDSRTDWSMT YSVEFG.

“HFCSGF W PS,” EF TAWZ, ARZ XAMTFZ--“W YAO KWTT EFG?”

WV IAT GFYFYHFGFZ ACVFGIAGZT VEAV IEFR EF HFRV ZSIR ARZ VSMDEFZ EFG CADF
IWVE EWT UWXT, EF YMGYMGFZ TSYF ISGZT. VEF DEWUZ, IES IAT RFAGFTV VS
