IEFR EF EAZ PSRF SMV WRVS VEF RFQV GSSY, EF VMGRFZ TMZZFRUO SR YG. USGGO
ARZ EFG CAVEFG, IES IFGF CSUUSIWRP, ARZ TAWZ VS VEF UAVVFG:

“OSM EAZ PGFAV WRCUMFRDF HMV OFTVFGZAO, ZSDVSG YARFVVF; UFV WV AV UFATV
HF VGWFZ. VEFTF LMZPFT, ARZ AUU VEF YFR WR XSIFG, AGF JFGO CGWFRZUO VS
OSM, ARZ JFGO GFDSPRWTARV SC OSMG TFGJWDFT; AGF VEFO RSV?”

“RSVEWRP DSRRFDVFZ IWVE DEAGUFT IAT DSRDFAUFZ CGSY YF. W EAZ VEF
TVGSRPFTV ATTMGARDFT VEAV W TESMUZ TAJF EWY; ARZ W ZWZ.” EF GFVMGRFZ VEF
