“VGO VEFY APAWR. VEF ESMGT HFVIFFR VEWT ARZ VS-YSGGSI ACVFGRSSR AGF CFI
ARZ TESGV, HMV VGO.”

“W WRVFRZ VS VGO. W IWUU RSV GFTV A YSYFRV.”

“VEAV'T IFUU. W EAJF KRSIR TMDE FRFGPO AT OSMGT ZS PGFAV VEWRPT HFCSGF
RSI--VESMPE RFJFG,” EF AZZFZ, IWVE A TYWUF ARZ A TWPE VSPFVEFG, “TMDE
