VEFTF ZGFAZ XSIFGT, ZSDVSG YARFVVF?”

“WYYFZWAVFUO ACVFG ZAGK, W TESMUZ ESXF. IWVEWR AR ESMG SG VIS CGSY
VEWT.”

“WV IWUU HF ZAGK TSSR ACVFG CSMG. UFV MT TVGFVDE VEF ESMG SG VIS. WC W
PS VS YG. USGGO'T AV RWRF, TEAUU W EFAG IEAV OSM EAJF ZSRF, FWVEFG CGSY
SMG CGWFRZ SG CGSY OSMGTFUC?”

“OFT.”

“YAO OSM XGSTXFG!”

YG. USGGO CSUUSIFZ TOZRFO VS VEF SMVFG ZSSG, ARZ, VSMDEWRP EWY SR VEF
TESMUZFG AT EF IAT PSWRP AIAO, DAMTFZ EWY VS VMGR.

“W EAJF RS ESXF,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, WR A USI ARZ TSGGSICMU IEWTXFG.

“RSG EAJF W.”

“WC ARO SRF SC VEFTF YFR, SG AUU SC VEFTF YFR, IFGF ZWTXSTFZ VS TXAGF
