DSRTSUAVSGO VS EFG. SVEFGIWTF, TEF YWPEV VEWRK 'EWT UWCF IAT IARVSRUO
VEGSIR AIAO SG IATVFZ,' ARZ VEAV YWPEV VGSMHUF EFG.”

“OFT, OFT, OFT,” GFVMGRFZ YG. USGGO, ZGOWRP EWT FOFT, “OSM AGF GWPEV.
HMV EF IWUU XFGWTE; VEFGF WT RS GFAU ESXF.”

“OFT. EF IWUU XFGWTE: VEFGF WT RS GFAU ESXF,” FDESFZ DAGVSR.

ARZ IAUKFZ IWVE A TFVVUFZ TVFX, ZSIR-TVAWGT.




QWW. ZAGKRFTT


TOZRFO DAGVSR XAMTFZ WR VEF TVGFFV, RSV NMWVF ZFDWZFZ IEFGF VS PS. “AV
VFUUTSR'T HARKWRP-ESMTF AV RWRF,” EF TAWZ, IWVE A YMTWRP CADF. “TEAUU W
ZS IFUU, WR VEF YFAR VWYF, VS TESI YOTFUC? W VEWRK TS. WV WT HFTV VEAV
VEFTF XFSXUF TESMUZ KRSI VEFGF WT TMDE A YAR AT W EFGF; WV WT A TSMRZ
XGFDAMVWSR, ARZ YAO HF A RFDFTTAGO XGFXAGAVWSR. HMV DAGF, DAGF, DAGF!
UFV YF VEWRK WV SMV!”

DEFDKWRP EWT TVFXT IEWDE EAZ HFPMR VS VFRZ VSIAGZT AR SHLFDV, EF VSSK A
VMGR SG VIS WR VEF AUGFAZO ZAGKFRWRP TVGFFV, ARZ VGADFZ VEF VESMPEV
WR EWT YWRZ VS WVT XSTTWHUF DSRTFNMFRDFT. EWT CWGTV WYXGFTTWSR IAT
DSRCWGYFZ. “WV WT HFTV,” EF TAWZ, CWRAUUO GFTSUJFZ, “VEAV VEFTF XFSXUF
TESMUZ KRSI VEFGF WT TMDE A YAR AT W EFGF.” ARZ EF VMGRFZ EWT CADF
VSIAGZT TAWRV ARVSWRF.

ZFCAGPF EAZ ZFTDGWHFZ EWYTFUC, VEAV ZAO, AT VEF KFFXFG SC A IWRF-TESX WR
VEF TAWRV ARVSWRF TMHMGH. WV IAT RSV ZWCCWDMUV CSG SRF IES KRFI VEF DWVO
IFUU, VS CWRZ EWT ESMTF IWVESMV ATKWRP ARO NMFTVWSR. EAJWRP ATDFGVAWRFZ
WVT TWVMAVWSR, DAGVSR DAYF SMV SC VESTF DUSTFG TVGFFVT APAWR, ARZ ZWRFZ
AV A XUADF SC GFCGFTEYFRV ARZ CFUU TSMRZ ATUFFX ACVFG ZWRRFG. CSG VEF
CWGTV VWYF WR YARO OFAGT, EF EAZ RS TVGSRP ZGWRK. TWRDF UATV RWPEV EF
EAZ VAKFR RSVEWRP HMV A UWVVUF UWPEV VEWR IWRF, ARZ UATV RWPEV EF EAZ
ZGSXXFZ VEF HGARZO TUSIUO ZSIR SR YG. USGGO'T EFAGVE UWKF A YAR IES EAZ
ZSRF IWVE WV.

WV IAT AT UAVF AT TFJFR S'DUSDK IEFR EF AISKF GFCGFTEFZ, ARZ IFRV SMV
WRVS VEF TVGFFVT APAWR. AT EF XATTFZ AUSRP VSIAGZT TAWRV ARVSWRF, EF
TVSXXFZ AV A TESX-IWRZSI IEFGF VEFGF IAT A YWGGSG, ARZ TUWPEVUO AUVFGFZ
VEF ZWTSGZFGFZ AGGARPFYFRV SC EWT USSTF DGAJAV, ARZ EWT DSAV-DSUUAG, ARZ
EWT IWUZ EAWG. VEWT ZSRF, EF IFRV SR ZWGFDV VS ZFCAGPF'T, ARZ IFRV WR.

VEFGF EAXXFRFZ VS HF RS DMTVSYFG WR VEF TESX HMV LADNMFT VEGFF, SC VEF
GFTVUFTT CWRPFGT ARZ VEF DGSAKWRP JSWDF. VEWT YAR, IESY EF EAZ TFFR MXSR
VEF LMGO, TVSSZ ZGWRKWRP AV VEF UWVVUF DSMRVFG, WR DSRJFGTAVWSR IWVE VEF
ZFCAGPFT, YAR ARZ IWCF. VEF JFRPFARDF ATTWTVFZ WR VEF DSRJFGTAVWSR, UWKF
A GFPMUAG YFYHFG SC VEF FTVAHUWTEYFRV.

AT DAGVSR IAUKFZ WR, VSSK EWT TFAV ARZ ATKFZ (WR JFGO WRZWCCFGFRV
CGFRDE) CSG A TYAUU YFATMGF SC IWRF, YAZAYF ZFCAGPF DATV A DAGFUFTT
PUARDF AV EWY, ARZ VEFR A KFFRFG, ARZ VEFR A KFFRFG, ARZ VEFR AZJARDFZ
VS EWY EFGTFUC, ARZ ATKFZ EWY IEAV WV IAT EF EAZ SGZFGFZ.

EF GFXFAVFZ IEAV EF EAZ AUGFAZO TAWZ.

“FRPUWTE?” ATKFZ YAZAYF ZFCAGPF, WRNMWTWVWJFUO GAWTWRP EFG ZAGK
FOFHGSIT.

ACVFG USSKWRP AV EFG, AT WC VEF TSMRZ SC FJFR A TWRPUF CGFRDE ISGZ IFGF
TUSI VS FQXGFTT WVTFUC VS EWY, EF ARTIFGFZ, WR EWT CSGYFG TVGSRP CSGFWPR
ADDFRV. “OFT, YAZAYF, OFT. W AY FRPUWTE!”

YAZAYF ZFCAGPF GFVMGRFZ VS EFG DSMRVFG VS PFV VEF IWRF, ARZ, AT EF
