ZFCAGPF HGSMPEV EWY VEF IWRF, ARZ PAJF EWY PSSZ FJFRWRP.

“ESI?”

“PSSZ FJFRWRP.”

“SE! PSSZ FJFRWRP, DWVWBFR,” CWUUWRP EWT PUATT. “AE! ARZ PSSZ IWRF. W
ZGWRK VS VEF GFXMHUWD.”

ZFCAGPF IFRV HADK VS VEF DSMRVFG, ARZ TAWZ, “DFGVAWRUO, A UWVVUF UWKF.”
 YAZAYF TVFGRUO GFVSGVFZ, “W VFUU OSM A PSSZ ZFAU UWKF.” LADNMFT VEGFF
XADWCWDAUUO GFYAGKFZ, “EF WT TS YMDE WR OSMG YWRZ, TFF OSM, YAZAYF.”
 VEF AYWAHUF JFRPFARDF AZZFZ, IWVE A UAMPE, “OFT, YO CAWVE! ARZ OSM
AGF USSKWRP CSGIAGZ IWVE TS YMDE XUFATMGF VS TFFWRP EWY SRDF YSGF
VS-YSGGSI!”

DAGVSR CSUUSIFZ VEF UWRFT ARZ ISGZT SC EWT XAXFG, IWVE A TUSI
CSGFCWRPFG, ARZ IWVE A TVMZWSMT ARZ AHTSGHFZ CADF. VEFO IFGF AUU UFARWRP
VEFWG AGYT SR VEF DSMRVFG DUSTF VSPFVEFG, TXFAKWRP USI. ACVFG A TWUFRDF
SC A CFI YSYFRVT, ZMGWRP IEWDE VEFO AUU USSKFZ VSIAGZT EWY IWVESMV
ZWTVMGHWRP EWT SMVIAGZ AVVFRVWSR CGSY VEF LADSHWR FZWVSG, VEFO GFTMYFZ
VEFWG DSRJFGTAVWSR.

“WV WT VGMF IEAV YAZAYF TAOT,” SHTFGJFZ LADNMFT VEGFF. “IEO TVSX? VEFGF
WT PGFAV CSGDF WR VEAV. IEO TVSX?”

“IFUU, IFUU,” GFATSRFZ ZFCAGPF, “HMV SRF YMTV TVSX TSYFIEFGF. ACVFG AUU,
VEF NMFTVWSR WT TVWUU IEFGF?”

“AV FQVFGYWRAVWSR,” TAWZ YAZAYF.

“YAPRWCWDFRV!” DGSAKFZ LADNMFT VEGFF. VEF JFRPFARDF, AUTS, EWPEUO
AXXGSJFZ.

“FQVFGYWRAVWSR WT PSSZ ZSDVGWRF, YO IWCF,” TAWZ ZFCAGPF, GAVEFG
VGSMHUFZ; “WR PFRFGAU, W TAO RSVEWRP APAWRTV WV. HMV VEWT ZSDVSG EAT
TMCCFGFZ YMDE; OSM EAJF TFFR EWY VS-ZAO; OSM EAJF SHTFGJFZ EWT CADF IEFR
VEF XAXFG IAT GFAZ.”

“W EAJF SHTFGJFZ EWT CADF!” GFXFAVFZ YAZAYF, DSRVFYXVMSMTUO ARZ ARPGWUO.
“OFT. W EAJF SHTFGJFZ EWT CADF. W EAJF SHTFGJFZ EWT CADF VS HF RSV VEF
CADF SC A VGMF CGWFRZ SC VEF GFXMHUWD. UFV EWY VAKF DAGF SC EWT CADF!”

“ARZ OSM EAJF SHTFGJFZ, YO IWCF,” TAWZ ZFCAGPF, WR A ZFXGFDAVSGO YARRFG,
“VEF ARPMWTE SC EWT ZAMPEVFG, IEWDE YMTV HF A ZGFAZCMU ARPMWTE VS EWY!”

“W EAJF SHTFGJFZ EWT ZAMPEVFG,” GFXFAVFZ YAZAYF; “OFT, W EAJF SHTFGJFZ
EWT ZAMPEVFG, YSGF VWYFT VEAR SRF. W EAJF SHTFGJFZ EFG VS-ZAO, ARZ W
EAJF SHTFGJFZ EFG SVEFG ZAOT. W EAJF SHTFGJFZ EFG WR VEF DSMGV, ARZ
W EAJF SHTFGJFZ EFG WR VEF TVGFFV HO VEF XGWTSR. UFV YF HMV UWCV YO
CWRPFG--!” TEF TFFYFZ VS GAWTF WV (VEF UWTVFRFG'T FOFT IFGF AUIAOT SR
EWT XAXFG), ARZ VS UFV WV CAUU IWVE A GAVVUF SR VEF UFZPF HFCSGF EFG, AT
WC VEF AQF EAZ ZGSXXFZ.

“VEF DWVWBFRFTT WT TMXFGH!” DGSAKFZ VEF LMGOYAR.

“TEF WT AR ARPFU!” TAWZ VEF JFRPFARDF, ARZ FYHGADFZ EFG.

“AT VS VEFF,” XMGTMFZ YAZAYF, WYXUADAHUO, AZZGFTTWRP EFG EMTHARZ, “WC WV
ZFXFRZFZ SR VEFF--IEWDE, EAXXWUO, WV ZSFT RSV--VESM ISMUZTV GFTDMF VEWT
YAR FJFR RSI.”

“RS!” XGSVFTVFZ ZFCAGPF. “RSV WC VS UWCV VEWT PUATT ISMUZ ZS WV! HMV W
ISMUZ UFAJF VEF YAVVFG VEFGF. W TAO, TVSX VEFGF.”

“TFF OSM VEFR, LADNMFT,” TAWZ YAZAYF ZFCAGPF, IGAVECMUUO; “ARZ TFF OSM,
VSS, YO UWVVUF JFRPFARDF; TFF OSM HSVE! UWTVFR! CSG SVEFG DGWYFT AT
VOGARVT ARZ SXXGFTTSGT, W EAJF VEWT GADF A USRP VWYF SR YO GFPWTVFG,
ZSSYFZ VS ZFTVGMDVWSR ARZ FQVFGYWRAVWSR. ATK YO EMTHARZ, WT VEAV TS.”

“WV WT TS,” ATTFRVFZ ZFCAGPF, IWVESMV HFWRP ATKFZ.

“WR VEF HFPWRRWRP SC VEF PGFAV ZAOT, IEFR VEF HATVWUUF CAUUT, EF CWRZT
VEWT XAXFG SC VS-ZAO, ARZ EF HGWRPT WV ESYF, ARZ WR VEF YWZZUF SC VEF
RWPEV IEFR VEWT XUADF WT DUFAG ARZ TEMV, IF GFAZ WV, EFGF SR VEWT TXSV,
HO VEF UWPEV SC VEWT UAYX. ATK EWY, WT VEAV TS.”

“WV WT TS,” ATTFRVFZ ZFCAGPF.

“VEAV RWPEV, W VFUU EWY, IEFR VEF XAXFG WT GFAZ VEGSMPE, ARZ VEF UAYX WT
HMGRV SMV, ARZ VEF ZAO WT PUFAYWRP WR AHSJF VESTF TEMVVFGT ARZ HFVIFFR
VESTF WGSR HAGT, VEAV W EAJF RSI A TFDGFV VS DSYYMRWDAVF. ATK EWY, WT
VEAV TS.”

“WV WT TS,” ATTFRVFZ ZFCAGPF APAWR.

“W DSYYMRWDAVF VS EWY VEAV TFDGFV. W TYWVF VEWT HSTSY IWVE VEFTF VIS
EARZT AT W TYWVF WV RSI, ARZ W VFUU EWY, 'ZFCAGPF, W IAT HGSMPEV MX
AYSRP VEF CWTEFGYFR SC VEF TFA-TESGF, ARZ VEAV XFATARV CAYWUO TS WRLMGFZ
HO VEF VIS FJGFYSRZF HGSVEFGT, AT VEAV HATVWUUF XAXFG ZFTDGWHFT, WT YO
CAYWUO. ZFCAGPF, VEAV TWTVFG SC VEF YSGVAUUO ISMRZFZ HSO MXSR VEF PGSMRZ
IAT YO TWTVFG, VEAV EMTHARZ IAT YO TWTVFG'T EMTHARZ, VEAV MRHSGR DEWUZ
IAT VEFWG DEWUZ, VEAV HGSVEFG IAT YO HGSVEFG, VEAV CAVEFG IAT YO CAVEFG,
VESTF ZFAZ AGF YO ZFAZ, ARZ VEAV TMYYSRT VS ARTIFG CSG VESTF VEWRPT
ZFTDFRZT VS YF!' ATK EWY, WT VEAV TS.”

“WV WT TS,” ATTFRVFZ ZFCAGPF SRDF YSGF.

“VEFR VFUU IWRZ ARZ CWGF IEFGF VS TVSX,” GFVMGRFZ YAZAYF; “HMV ZSR'V
VFUU YF.”

HSVE EFG EFAGFGT ZFGWJFZ A ESGGWHUF FRLSOYFRV CGSY VEF ZFAZUO RAVMGF
SC EFG IGAVE--VEF UWTVFRFG DSMUZ CFFU ESI IEWVF TEF IAT, IWVESMV TFFWRP
EFG--ARZ HSVE EWPEUO DSYYFRZFZ WV. ZFCAGPF, A IFAK YWRSGWVO, WRVFGXSTFZ
A CFI ISGZT CSG VEF YFYSGO SC VEF DSYXATTWSRAVF IWCF SC VEF YAGNMWT; HMV
SRUO FUWDWVFZ CGSY EWT SIR IWCF A GFXFVWVWSR SC EFG UATV GFXUO. “VFUU
VEF IWRZ ARZ VEF CWGF IEFGF VS TVSX; RSV YF!”

DMTVSYFGT FRVFGFZ, ARZ VEF PGSMX IAT HGSKFR MX. VEF FRPUWTE DMTVSYFG
XAWZ CSG IEAV EF EAZ EAZ, XFGXUFQFZUO DSMRVFZ EWT DEARPF, ARZ ATKFZ, AT
A TVGARPFG, VS HF ZWGFDVFZ VSIAGZT VEF RAVWSRAU XAUADF. YAZAYF ZFCAGPF
VSSK EWY VS VEF ZSSG, ARZ XMV EFG AGY SR EWT, WR XSWRVWRP SMV VEF GSAZ.
VEF FRPUWTE DMTVSYFG IAT RSV IWVESMV EWT GFCUFDVWSRT VEFR, VEAV WV YWPEV
HF A PSSZ ZFFZ VS TFWBF VEAV AGY, UWCV WV, ARZ TVGWKF MRZFG WV TEAGX ARZ
ZFFX.

HMV, EF IFRV EWT IAO, ARZ IAT TSSR TIAUUSIFZ MX WR VEF TEAZSI SC VEF
XGWTSR IAUU. AV VEF AXXSWRVFZ ESMG, EF FYFGPFZ CGSY WV VS XGFTFRV
EWYTFUC WR YG. USGGO'T GSSY APAWR, IEFGF EF CSMRZ VEF SUZ PFRVUFYAR
IAUKWRP VS ARZ CGS WR GFTVUFTT ARQWFVO. EF TAWZ EF EAZ HFFR IWVE UMDWF
MRVWU LMTV RSI, ARZ EAZ SRUO UFCV EFG CSG A CFI YWRMVFT, VS DSYF ARZ
KFFX EWT AXXSWRVYFRV. EFG CAVEFG EAZ RSV HFFR TFFR, TWRDF EF NMWVVFZ VEF
HARKWRP-ESMTF VSIAGZT CSMG S'DUSDK. TEF EAZ TSYF CAWRV ESXFT VEAV EWT
YFZWAVWSR YWPEV TAJF DEAGUFT, HMV VEFO IFGF JFGO TUWPEV. EF EAZ HFFR
YSGF VEAR CWJF ESMGT PSRF: IEFGF DSMUZ EF HF?

YG. USGGO IAWVFZ MRVWU VFR; HMV, ZSDVSG YARFVVF RSV GFVMGRWRP, ARZ
EF HFWRP MRIWUUWRP VS UFAJF UMDWF ARO USRPFG, WV IAT AGGARPFZ VEAV EF
TESMUZ PS HADK VS EFG, ARZ DSYF VS VEF HARKWRP-ESMTF APAWR AV YWZRWPEV.
WR VEF YFARIEWUF, DAGVSR ISMUZ IAWV AUSRF HO VEF CWGF CSG VEF ZSDVSG.

EF IAWVFZ ARZ IAWVFZ, ARZ VEF DUSDK TVGMDK VIFUJF; HMV ZSDVSG YARFVVF
ZWZ RSV DSYF HADK. YG. USGGO GFVMGRFZ, ARZ CSMRZ RS VWZWRPT SC EWY, ARZ
HGSMPEV RSRF. IEFGF DSMUZ EF HF?

VEFO IFGF ZWTDMTTWRP VEWT NMFTVWSR, ARZ IFGF AUYSTV HMWUZWRP MX TSYF
IFAK TVGMDVMGF SC ESXF SR EWT XGSUSRPFZ AHTFRDF, IEFR VEFO EFAGZ EWY SR
VEF TVAWGT. VEF WRTVARV EF FRVFGFZ VEF GSSY, WV IAT XUAWR VEAV AUU IAT
USTV.

IEFVEFG EF EAZ GFAUUO HFFR VS ARO SRF, SG IEFVEFG EF EAZ HFFR AUU VEAV
VWYF VGAJFGTWRP VEF TVGFFVT, IAT RFJFG KRSIR. AT EF TVSSZ TVAGWRP AV
VEFY, VEFO ATKFZ EWY RS NMFTVWSR, CSG EWT CADF VSUZ VEFY FJFGOVEWRP.

“W DARRSV CWRZ WV,” TAWZ EF, “ARZ W YMTV EAJF WV. IEFGF WT WV?”

EWT EFAZ ARZ VEGSAV IFGF HAGF, ARZ, AT EF TXSKF IWVE A EFUXUFTT USSK
TVGAOWRP AUU AGSMRZ, EF VSSK EWT DSAV SCC, ARZ UFV WV ZGSX SR VEF CUSSG.

“IEFGF WT YO HFRDE? W EAJF HFFR USSKWRP FJFGOIEFGF CSG YO HFRDE, ARZ W
DAR'V CWRZ WV. IEAV EAJF VEFO ZSRF IWVE YO ISGK? VWYF XGFTTFT: W YMTV
CWRWTE VESTF TESFT.”

VEFO USSKFZ AV SRF ARSVEFG, ARZ VEFWG EFAGVT ZWFZ IWVEWR VEFY.

“DSYF, DSYF!” TAWZ EF, WR A IEWYXFGWRP YWTFGAHUF IAO; “UFV YF PFV VS
ISGK. PWJF YF YO ISGK.”

GFDFWJWRP RS ARTIFG, EF VSGF EWT EAWG, ARZ HFAV EWT CFFV MXSR VEF
PGSMRZ, UWKF A ZWTVGADVFZ DEWUZ.

“ZSR'V VSGVMGF A XSSG CSGUSGR IGFVDE,” EF WYXUSGFZ VEFY, IWVE A ZGFAZCMU
DGO; “HMV PWJF YF YO ISGK! IEAV WT VS HFDSYF SC MT, WC VESTF TESFT AGF
RSV ZSRF VS-RWPEV?”

USTV, MVVFGUO USTV!

WV IAT TS DUFAGUO HFOSRZ ESXF VS GFATSR IWVE EWY, SG VGO VS GFTVSGF EWY,
VEAV--AT WC HO APGFFYFRV--VEFO FADE XMV A EARZ MXSR EWT TESMUZFG, ARZ
TSSVEFZ EWY VS TWV ZSIR HFCSGF VEF CWGF, IWVE A XGSYWTF VEAV EF TESMUZ
EAJF EWT ISGK XGFTFRVUO. EF TARK WRVS VEF DEAWG, ARZ HGSSZFZ SJFG VEF
FYHFGT, ARZ TEFZ VFAGT. AT WC AUU VEAV EAZ EAXXFRFZ TWRDF VEF PAGGFV
VWYF IFGF A YSYFRVAGO CARDO, SG A ZGFAY, YG. USGGO TAI EWY TEGWRK WRVS
VEF FQADV CWPMGF VEAV ZFCAGPF EAZ EAZ WR KFFXWRP.

ACCFDVFZ, ARZ WYXGFTTFZ IWVE VFGGSG AT VEFO HSVE IFGF, HO VEWT TXFDVADUF
SC GMWR, WV IAT RSV A VWYF VS OWFUZ VS TMDE FYSVWSRT. EWT USRFUO
ZAMPEVFG, HFGFCV SC EFG CWRAU ESXF ARZ GFUWARDF, AXXFAUFZ VS VEFY HSVE
VSS TVGSRPUO. APAWR, AT WC HO APGFFYFRV, VEFO USSKFZ AV SRF ARSVEFG IWVE
SRF YFARWRP WR VEFWG CADFT. DAGVSR IAT VEF CWGTV VS TXFAK:

“VEF UATV DEARDF WT PSRF: WV IAT RSV YMDE. OFT; EF EAZ HFVVFG HF VAKFR
VS EFG. HMV, HFCSGF OSM PS, IWUU OSM, CSG A YSYFRV, TVFAZWUO AVVFRZ VS
YF? ZSR'V ATK YF IEO W YAKF VEF TVWXMUAVWSRT W AY PSWRP VS YAKF, ARZ
FQADV VEF XGSYWTF W AY PSWRP VS FQADV; W EAJF A GFATSR--A PSSZ SRF.”

“W ZS RSV ZSMHV WV,” ARTIFGFZ YG. USGGO. “TAO SR.”

VEF CWPMGF WR VEF DEAWG HFVIFFR VEFY, IAT AUU VEF VWYF YSRSVSRSMTUO
GSDKWRP WVTFUC VS ARZ CGS, ARZ YSARWRP. VEFO TXSKF WR TMDE A VSRF AT
VEFO ISMUZ EAJF MTFZ WC VEFO EAZ HFFR IAVDEWRP HO A TWDK-HFZ WR VEF
RWPEV.

DAGVSR TVSSXFZ VS XWDK MX VEF DSAV, IEWDE UAO AUYSTV FRVARPUWRP EWT
CFFV. AT EF ZWZ TS, A TYAUU DATF WR IEWDE VEF ZSDVSG IAT ADDMTVSYFZ VS
DAGGO VEF UWTVT SC EWT ZAO'T ZMVWFT, CFUU UWPEVUO SR VEF CUSSG. DAGVSR
VSSK WV MX, ARZ VEFGF IAT A CSUZFZ XAXFG WR WV. “IF TESMUZ USSK
AV VEWT!” EF TAWZ. YG. USGGO RSZZFZ EWT DSRTFRV. EF SXFRFZ WV, ARZ
FQDUAWYFZ, “VEARK _PSZ!_”

“IEAV WT WV?” ATKFZ YG. USGGO, FAPFGUO.

“A YSYFRV! UFV YF TXFAK SC WV WR WVT XUADF. CWGTV,” EF XMV EWT EARZ WR
EWT DSAV, ARZ VSSK ARSVEFG XAXFG CGSY WV, “VEAV WT VEF DFGVWCWDAVF IEWDE
FRAHUFT YF VS XATT SMV SC VEWT DWVO. USSK AV WV. OSM TFF--TOZRFO DAGVSR,
AR FRPUWTEYAR?”

YG. USGGO EFUZ WV SXFR WR EWT EARZ, PABWRP WR EWT FAGRFTV CADF.

“KFFX WV CSG YF MRVWU VS-YSGGSI. W TEAUU TFF EWY VS-YSGGSI, OSM
GFYFYHFG, ARZ W EAZ HFVVFG RSV VAKF WV WRVS VEF XGWTSR.”

“IEO RSV?”

“W ZSR'V KRSI; W XGFCFG RSV VS ZS TS. RSI, VAKF VEWT XAXFG VEAV ZSDVSG
YARFVVF EAT DAGGWFZ AHSMV EWY. WV WT A TWYWUAG DFGVWCWDAVF, FRAHUWRP EWY
ARZ EWT ZAMPEVFG ARZ EFG DEWUZ, AV ARO VWYF, VS XATT VEF HAGGWFG ARZ VEF
CGSRVWFG! OSM TFF?”

“OFT!”

“XFGEAXT EF SHVAWRFZ WV AT EWT UATV ARZ MVYSTV XGFDAMVWSR APAWRTV FJWU,
OFTVFGZAO. IEFR WT WV ZAVFZ? HMV RS YAVVFG; ZSR'V TVAO VS USSK; XMV WV
MX DAGFCMUUO IWVE YWRF ARZ OSMG SIR. RSI, SHTFGJF! W RFJFG ZSMHVFZ MRVWU
IWVEWR VEWT ESMG SG VIS, VEAV EF EAZ, SG DSMUZ EAJF TMDE A XAXFG. WV WT
PSSZ, MRVWU GFDAUUFZ. HMV WV YAO HF TSSR GFDAUUFZ, ARZ, W EAJF GFATSR VS
VEWRK, IWUU HF.”

“VEFO AGF RSV WR ZARPFG?”

“VEFO AGF WR PGFAV ZARPFG. VEFO AGF WR ZARPFG SC ZFRMRDWAVWSR HO YAZAYF
ZFCAGPF. W KRSI WV CGSY EFG SIR UWXT. W EAJF SJFGEFAGZ ISGZT SC VEAV
ISYAR'T, VS-RWPEV, IEWDE EAJF XGFTFRVFZ VEFWG ZARPFG VS YF WR TVGSRP
DSUSMGT. W EAJF USTV RS VWYF, ARZ TWRDF VEFR, W EAJF TFFR VEF TXO. EF
DSRCWGYT YF. EF KRSIT VEAV A ISSZ-TAIOFG, UWJWRP HO VEF XGWTSR IAUU,
WT MRZFG VEF DSRVGSU SC VEF ZFCAGPFT, ARZ EAT HFFR GFEFAGTFZ HO
YAZAYF ZFCAGPF AT VS EWT EAJWRP TFFR EFG”--EF RFJFG YFRVWSRFZ UMDWF'T
RAYF--“YAKWRP TWPRT ARZ TWPRAUT VS XGWTSRFGT. WV WT FATO VS CSGFTFF VEAV
VEF XGFVFRDF IWUU HF VEF DSYYSR SRF, A XGWTSR XUSV, ARZ VEAV WV IWUU
WRJSUJF EFG UWCF--ARZ XFGEAXT EFG DEWUZ'T--ARZ XFGEAXT EFG CAVEFG'T--CSG
HSVE EAJF HFFR TFFR IWVE EFG AV VEAV XUADF. ZSR'V USSK TS ESGGWCWFZ. OSM
IWUU TAJF VEFY AUU.”

“EFAJFR PGARV W YAO, DAGVSR! HMV ESI?”

“W AY PSWRP VS VFUU OSM ESI. WV IWUU ZFXFRZ SR OSM, ARZ WV DSMUZ ZFXFRZ
SR RS HFVVFG YAR. VEWT RFI ZFRMRDWAVWSR IWUU DFGVAWRUO RSV VAKF XUADF
MRVWU ACVFG VS-YSGGSI; XGSHAHUO RSV MRVWU VIS SG VEGFF ZAOT ACVFGIAGZT;
YSGF XGSHAHUO A IFFK ACVFGIAGZT. OSM KRSI WV WT A DAXWVAU DGWYF, VS
YSMGR CSG, SG TOYXAVEWTF IWVE, A JWDVWY SC VEF PMWUUSVWRF. TEF ARZ EFG
CAVEFG ISMUZ MRNMFTVWSRAHUO HF PMWUVO SC VEWT DGWYF, ARZ VEWT ISYAR (VEF
WRJFVFGADO SC IESTF XMGTMWV DARRSV HF ZFTDGWHFZ) ISMUZ IAWV VS AZZ VEAV
TVGFRPVE VS EFG DATF, ARZ YAKF EFGTFUC ZSMHUO TMGF. OSM CSUUSI YF?”

“TS AVVFRVWJFUO, ARZ IWVE TS YMDE DSRCWZFRDF WR IEAV OSM TAO, VEAV CSG
VEF YSYFRV W USTF TWPEV,” VSMDEWRP VEF HADK SC VEF ZSDVSG'T DEAWG, “FJFR
SC VEWT ZWTVGFTT.”

“OSM EAJF YSRFO, ARZ DAR HMO VEF YFART SC VGAJFUUWRP VS VEF TFADSATV
AT NMWDKUO AT VEF LSMGRFO DAR HF YAZF. OSMG XGFXAGAVWSRT EAJF HFFR
DSYXUFVFZ CSG TSYF ZAOT, VS GFVMGR VS FRPUARZ. FAGUO VS-YSGGSI EAJF OSMG
ESGTFT GFAZO, TS VEAV VEFO YAO HF WR TVAGVWRP VGWY AV VIS S'DUSDK WR VEF
ACVFGRSSR.”

“WV TEAUU HF ZSRF!”

EWT YARRFG IAT TS CFGJFRV ARZ WRTXWGWRP, VEAV YG. USGGO DAMPEV VEF
CUAYF, ARZ IAT AT NMWDK AT OSMVE.

“OSM AGF A RSHUF EFAGV. ZWZ W TAO IF DSMUZ ZFXFRZ MXSR RS HFVVFG YAR?
VFUU EFG, VS-RWPEV, IEAV OSM KRSI SC EFG ZARPFG AT WRJSUJWRP EFG DEWUZ
ARZ EFG CAVEFG. ZIFUU MXSR VEAV, CSG TEF ISMUZ UAO EFG SIR CAWG EFAZ
HFTWZF EFG EMTHARZ'T DEFFGCMUUO.” EF CAUVFGFZ CSG AR WRTVARV; VEFR IFRV
SR AT HFCSGF. “CSG VEF TAKF SC EFG DEWUZ ARZ EFG CAVEFG, XGFTT MXSR EFG
VEF RFDFTTWVO SC UFAJWRP XAGWT, IWVE VEFY ARZ OSM, AV VEAV ESMG. VFUU
EFG VEAV WV IAT EFG EMTHARZ'T UATV AGGARPFYFRV. VFUU EFG VEAV YSGF
ZFXFRZT MXSR WV VEAR TEF ZAGF HFUWFJF, SG ESXF. OSM VEWRK VEAV EFG
CAVEFG, FJFR WR VEWT TAZ TVAVF, IWUU TMHYWV EWYTFUC VS EFG; ZS OSM RSV?”

“W AY TMGF SC WV.”

“W VESMPEV TS. NMWFVUO ARZ TVFAZWUO EAJF AUU VEFTF AGGARPFYFRVT YAZF WR
VEF DSMGVOAGZ EFGF, FJFR VS VEF VAKWRP SC OSMG SIR TFAV WR VEF DAGGWAPF.
VEF YSYFRV W DSYF VS OSM, VAKF YF WR, ARZ ZGWJF AIAO.”

“W MRZFGTVARZ VEAV W IAWV CSG OSM MRZFG AUU DWGDMYTVARDFT?”

“OSM EAJF YO DFGVWCWDAVF WR OSMG EARZ IWVE VEF GFTV, OSM KRSI, ARZ IWUU
GFTFGJF YO XUADF. IAWV CSG RSVEWRP HMV VS EAJF YO XUADF SDDMXWFZ, ARZ
VEFR CSG FRPUARZ!”

“IEO, VEFR,” TAWZ YG. USGGO, PGATXWRP EWT FAPFG HMV TS CWGY ARZ TVFAZO
EARZ, “WV ZSFT RSV AUU ZFXFRZ SR SRF SUZ YAR, HMV W TEAUU EAJF A OSMRP
ARZ AGZFRV YAR AV YO TWZF.”

“HO VEF EFUX SC EFAJFR OSM TEAUU! XGSYWTF YF TSUFYRUO VEAV RSVEWRP IWUU
WRCUMFRDF OSM VS AUVFG VEF DSMGTF SR IEWDE IF RSI TVARZ XUFZPFZ VS SRF
ARSVEFG.”

“RSVEWRP, DAGVSR.”

“GFYFYHFG VEFTF ISGZT VS-YSGGSI: DEARPF VEF DSMGTF, SG ZFUAO WR WV--CSG
ARO GFATSR--ARZ RS UWCF DAR XSTTWHUO HF TAJFZ, ARZ YARO UWJFT YMTV
WRFJWVAHUO HF TADGWCWDFZ.”

“W IWUU GFYFYHFG VEFY. W ESXF VS ZS YO XAGV CAWVECMUUO.”

“ARZ W ESXF VS ZS YWRF. RSI, PSSZ HOF!”

VESMPE EF TAWZ WV IWVE A PGAJF TYWUF SC FAGRFTVRFTT, ARZ VESMPE EF FJFR
XMV VEF SUZ YAR'T EARZ VS EWT UWXT, EF ZWZ RSV XAGV CGSY EWY VEFR. EF
EFUXFZ EWY TS CAG VS AGSMTF VEF GSDKWRP CWPMGF HFCSGF VEF ZOWRP FYHFGT,
AT VS PFV A DUSAK ARZ EAV XMV MXSR WV, ARZ VS VFYXV WV CSGVE VS CWRZ
IEFGF VEF HFRDE ARZ ISGK IFGF EWZZFR VEAV WV TVWUU YSARWRPUO HFTSMPEV
VS EAJF. EF IAUKFZ SR VEF SVEFG TWZF SC WV ARZ XGSVFDVFZ WV VS VEF
DSMGVOAGZ SC VEF ESMTF IEFGF VEF ACCUWDVFZ EFAGV--TS EAXXO WR
VEF YFYSGAHUF VWYF IEFR EF EAZ GFJFAUFZ EWT SIR ZFTSUAVF EFAGV VS
WV--SMVIAVDEFZ VEF AICMU RWPEV. EF FRVFGFZ VEF DSMGVOAGZ ARZ GFYAWRFZ
VEFGF CSG A CFI YSYFRVT AUSRF, USSKWRP MX AV VEF UWPEV WR VEF IWRZSI SC
EFG GSSY. HFCSGF EF IFRV AIAO, EF HGFAVEFZ A HUFTTWRP VSIAGZT WV, ARZ A
CAGFIFUU.




QWWW. CWCVO-VIS


WR VEF HUADK XGWTSR SC VEF DSRDWFGPFGWF, VEF ZSSYFZ SC VEF ZAO AIAWVFZ
VEFWG CAVF. VEFO IFGF WR RMYHFG AT VEF IFFKT SC VEF OFAG. CWCVO-VIS IFGF
VS GSUU VEAV ACVFGRSSR SR VEF UWCF-VWZF SC VEF DWVO VS VEF HSMRZUFTT
FJFGUATVWRP TFA. HFCSGF VEFWG DFUUT IFGF NMWV SC VEFY, RFI SDDMXARVT
IFGF AXXSWRVFZ; HFCSGF VEFWG HUSSZ GAR WRVS VEF HUSSZ TXWUUFZ OFTVFGZAO,
VEF HUSSZ VEAV IAT VS YWRPUF IWVE VEFWGT VS-YSGGSI IAT AUGFAZO TFV
AXAGV.

VIS TDSGF ARZ VIFUJF IFGF VSUZ SCC. CGSY VEF CAGYFG-PFRFGAU SC TFJFRVO,
IESTF GWDEFT DSMUZ RSV HMO EWT UWCF, VS VEF TFAYTVGFTT SC VIFRVO, IESTF
XSJFGVO ARZ SHTDMGWVO DSMUZ RSV TAJF EFG. XEOTWDAU ZWTFATFT, FRPFRZFGFZ
WR VEF JWDFT ARZ RFPUFDVT SC YFR, IWUU TFWBF SR JWDVWYT SC AUU ZFPGFFT;
ARZ VEF CGWPEVCMU YSGAU ZWTSGZFG, HSGR SC MRTXFAKAHUF TMCCFGWRP,
WRVSUFGAHUF SXXGFTTWSR, ARZ EFAGVUFTT WRZWCCFGFRDF, TYSVF FNMAUUO
IWVESMV ZWTVWRDVWSR.

DEAGUFT ZAGRAO, AUSRF WR A DFUU, EAZ TMTVAWRFZ EWYTFUC IWVE RS
CUAVVFGWRP ZFUMTWSR TWRDF EF DAYF VS WV CGSY VEF VGWHMRAU. WR FJFGO UWRF
SC VEF RAGGAVWJF EF EAZ EFAGZ, EF EAZ EFAGZ EWT DSRZFYRAVWSR. EF EAZ
CMUUO DSYXGFEFRZFZ VEAV RS XFGTSRAU WRCUMFRDF DSMUZ XSTTWHUO TAJF EWY,
VEAV EF IAT JWGVMAUUO TFRVFRDFZ HO VEF YWUUWSRT, ARZ VEAV MRWVT DSMUZ
AJAWU EWY RSVEWRP.

RFJFGVEFUFTT, WV IAT RSV FATO, IWVE VEF CADF SC EWT HFUSJFZ IWCF CGFTE
HFCSGF EWY, VS DSYXSTF EWT YWRZ VS IEAV WV YMTV HFAG. EWT ESUZ SR UWCF
IAT TVGSRP, ARZ WV IAT JFGO, JFGO EAGZ, VS USSTFR; HO PGAZMAU FCCSGVT
ARZ ZFPGFFT MRDUSTFZ A UWVVUF EFGF, WV DUFRDEFZ VEF VWPEVFG VEFGF; ARZ
IEFR EF HGSMPEV EWT TVGFRPVE VS HFAG SR VEAV EARZ ARZ WV OWFUZFZ,
VEWT IAT DUSTFZ APAWR. VEFGF IAT A EMGGO, VSS, WR AUU EWT VESMPEVT,
A VMGHMUFRV ARZ EFAVFZ ISGKWRP SC EWT EFAGV, VEAV DSRVFRZFZ APAWRTV
GFTWPRAVWSR. WC, CSG A YSYFRV, EF ZWZ CFFU GFTWPRFZ, VEFR EWT IWCF ARZ
DEWUZ IES EAZ VS UWJF ACVFG EWY, TFFYFZ VS XGSVFTV ARZ VS YAKF WV A
TFUCWTE VEWRP.

HMV, AUU VEWT IAT AV CWGTV. HFCSGF USRP, VEF DSRTWZFGAVWSR VEAV VEFGF
IAT RS ZWTPGADF WR VEF CAVF EF YMTV YFFV, ARZ VEAV RMYHFGT IFRV VEF TAYF
GSAZ IGSRPCMUUO, ARZ VGSZ WV CWGYUO FJFGO ZAO, TXGARP MX VS TVWYMUAVF
EWY. RFQV CSUUSIFZ VEF VESMPEV VEAV YMDE SC VEF CMVMGF XFADF SC YWRZ
FRLSOAHUF HO VEF ZFAG SRFT, ZFXFRZFZ SR EWT NMWFV CSGVWVMZF. TS,
HO ZFPGFFT EF DAUYFZ WRVS VEF HFVVFG TVAVF, IEFR EF DSMUZ GAWTF EWT
VESMPEVT YMDE EWPEFG, ARZ ZGAI DSYCSGV ZSIR.

HFCSGF WV EAZ TFV WR ZAGK SR VEF RWPEV SC EWT DSRZFYRAVWSR, EF EAZ
VGAJFUUFZ VEMT CAG SR EWT UATV IAO. HFWRP AUUSIFZ VS XMGDEATF VEF YFART
SC IGWVWRP, ARZ A UWPEV, EF TAV ZSIR VS IGWVF MRVWU TMDE VWYF AT VEF
XGWTSR UAYXT TESMUZ HF FQVWRPMWTEFZ.

EF IGSVF A USRP UFVVFG VS UMDWF, TESIWRP EFG VEAV EF EAZ KRSIR RSVEWRP
SC EFG CAVEFG'T WYXGWTSRYFRV, MRVWU EF EAZ EFAGZ SC WV CGSY EFGTFUC,
ARZ VEAV EF EAZ HFFR AT WPRSGARV AT TEF SC EWT CAVEFG'T ARZ MRDUF'T
GFTXSRTWHWUWVO CSG VEAV YWTFGO, MRVWU VEF XAXFG EAZ HFFR GFAZ. EF EAZ
AUGFAZO FQXUAWRFZ VS EFG VEAV EWT DSRDFAUYFRV CGSY EFGTFUC SC VEF RAYF
EF EAZ GFUWRNMWTEFZ, IAT VEF SRF DSRZWVWSR--CMUUO WRVFUUWPWHUF RSI--VEAV
EFG CAVEFG EAZ AVVADEFZ VS VEFWG HFVGSVEAU, ARZ IAT VEF SRF XGSYWTF EF
EAZ TVWUU FQADVFZ SR VEF YSGRWRP SC VEFWG YAGGWAPF. EF FRVGFAVFZ EFG,
CSG EFG CAVEFG'T TAKF, RFJFG VS TFFK VS KRSI IEFVEFG EFG CAVEFG EAZ
HFDSYF SHUWJWSMT SC VEF FQWTVFRDF SC VEF XAXFG, SG EAZ EAZ WV GFDAUUFZ
VS EWY (CSG VEF YSYFRV, SG CSG PSSZ), HO VEF TVSGO SC VEF VSIFG, SR
VEAV SUZ TMRZAO MRZFG VEF ZFAG SUZ XUARF-VGFF WR VEF PAGZFR. WC EF EAZ
XGFTFGJFZ ARO ZFCWRWVF GFYFYHGARDF SC WV, VEFGF DSMUZ HF RS ZSMHV VEAV
EF EAZ TMXXSTFZ WV ZFTVGSOFZ IWVE VEF HATVWUUF, IEFR EF EAZ CSMRZ RS
YFRVWSR SC WV AYSRP VEF GFUWDT SC XGWTSRFGT IEWDE VEF XSXMUADF EAZ
ZWTDSJFGFZ VEFGF, ARZ IEWDE EAZ HFFR ZFTDGWHFZ VS AUU VEF ISGUZ. EF
HFTSMPEV EFG--VESMPE EF AZZFZ VEAV EF KRFI WV IAT RFFZUFTT--VS DSRTSUF
EFG CAVEFG, HO WYXGFTTWRP EWY VEGSMPE FJFGO VFRZFG YFART TEF DSMUZ VEWRK
SC, IWVE VEF VGMVE VEAV EF EAZ ZSRF RSVEWRP CSG IEWDE EF DSMUZ LMTVUO
GFXGSADE EWYTFUC, HMV EAZ MRWCSGYUO CSGPSVVFR EWYTFUC CSG VEFWG LSWRV
TAKFT. RFQV VS EFG XGFTFGJAVWSR SC EWT SIR UATV PGAVFCMU USJF ARZ
HUFTTWRP, ARZ EFG SJFGDSYWRP SC EFG TSGGSI, VS ZFJSVF EFGTFUC VS VEFWG
ZFAG DEWUZ, EF AZLMGFZ EFG, AT VEFO ISMUZ YFFV WR EFAJFR, VS DSYCSGV EFG
CAVEFG.

VS EFG CAVEFG EWYTFUC, EF IGSVF WR VEF TAYF TVGAWR; HMV, EF VSUZ EFG
CAVEFG VEAV EF FQXGFTTUO DSRCWZFZ EWT IWCF ARZ DEWUZ VS EWT DAGF. ARZ
EF VSUZ EWY VEWT, JFGO TVGSRPUO, IWVE VEF ESXF SC GSMTWRP EWY CGSY ARO
ZFTXSRZFRDO SG ZARPFGSMT GFVGSTXFDV VSIAGZT IEWDE EF CSGFTAI EF YWPEV HF
VFRZWRP.

VS YG. USGGO, EF DSYYFRZFZ VEFY AUU, ARZ FQXUAWRFZ EWT ISGUZUO ACCAWGT.
VEAV ZSRF, IWVE YARO AZZFZ TFRVFRDFT SC PGAVFCMU CGWFRZTEWX ARZ IAGY
AVVADEYFRV, AUU IAT ZSRF. EF RFJFG VESMPEV SC DAGVSR. EWT YWRZ IAT TS
CMUU SC VEF SVEFGT, VEAV EF RFJFG SRDF VESMPEV SC EWY.

EF EAZ VWYF VS CWRWTE VEFTF UFVVFGT HFCSGF VEF UWPEVT IFGF XMV SMV. IEFR
EF UAO ZSIR SR EWT TVGAI HFZ, EF VESMPEV EF EAZ ZSRF IWVE VEWT ISGUZ.

HMV, WV HFDKSRFZ EWY HADK WR EWT TUFFX, ARZ TESIFZ WVTFUC WR TEWRWRP
CSGYT. CGFF ARZ EAXXO, HADK WR VEF SUZ ESMTF WR TSES (VESMPE WV EAZ
RSVEWRP WR WV UWKF VEF GFAU ESMTF), MRADDSMRVAHUO GFUFATFZ ARZ UWPEV SC
EFAGV, EF IAT IWVE UMDWF APAWR, ARZ TEF VSUZ EWY WV IAT AUU A ZGFAY, ARZ
EF EAZ RFJFG PSRF AIAO. A XAMTF SC CSGPFVCMURFTT, ARZ VEFR EF EAZ FJFR
TMCCFGFZ, ARZ EAZ DSYF HADK VS EFG, ZFAZ ARZ AV XFADF, ARZ OFV VEFGF
IAT RS ZWCCFGFRDF WR EWY. ARSVEFG XAMTF SC SHUWJWSR, ARZ EF AISKF WR VEF
TSYHGF YSGRWRP, MRDSRTDWSMT IEFGF EF IAT SG IEAV EAZ EAXXFRFZ, MRVWU WV
CUATEFZ MXSR EWT YWRZ, “VEWT WT VEF ZAO SC YO ZFAVE!”

VEMT, EAZ EF DSYF VEGSMPE VEF ESMGT, VS VEF ZAO IEFR VEF CWCVO-VIS EFAZT
IFGF VS CAUU. ARZ RSI, IEWUF EF IAT DSYXSTFZ, ARZ ESXFZ VEAV EF DSMUZ
YFFV VEF FRZ IWVE NMWFV EFGSWTY, A RFI ADVWSR HFPAR WR EWT IAKWRP
VESMPEVT, IEWDE IAT JFGO ZWCCWDMUV VS YATVFG.

EF EAZ RFJFG TFFR VEF WRTVGMYFRV VEAV IAT VS VFGYWRAVF EWT UWCF. ESI
EWPE WV IAT CGSY VEF PGSMRZ, ESI YARO TVFXT WV EAZ, IEFGF EF ISMUZ HF
TVSSZ, ESI EF ISMUZ HF VSMDEFZ, IEFVEFG VEF VSMDEWRP EARZT ISMUZ HF ZOFZ
