SG YWPEV HF VEF UATV: VEFTF ARZ YARO TWYWUAG NMFTVWSRT, WR RSIWTF
ZWGFDVFZ HO EWT IWUU, SHVGMZFZ VEFYTFUJFT SJFG ARZ SJFG APAWR, DSMRVUFTT
