CFAG. GAVEFG, VEFO SGWPWRAVFZ WR A TVGARPF HFTFVVWRP ZFTWGF VS KRSI IEAV
VS ZS IEFR VEF VWYF DAYF; A ZFTWGF PWPARVWDAUUO ZWTXGSXSGVWSRAVF VS VEF
CFI TIWCV YSYFRVT VS IEWDE WV GFCFGGFZ; A ISRZFGWRP VEAV IAT YSGF UWKF
VEF ISRZFGWRP SC TSYF SVEFG TXWGWV IWVEWR EWT, VEAR EWT SIR.

VEF ESMGT IFRV SR AT EF IAUKFZ VS ARZ CGS, ARZ VEF DUSDKT TVGMDK VEF
RMYHFGT EF ISMUZ RFJFG EFAG APAWR. RWRF PSRF CSG FJFG, VFR PSRF CSG
FJFG, FUFJFR PSRF CSG FJFG, VIFUJF DSYWRP SR VS XATT AIAO. ACVFG A EAGZ
DSRVFTV IWVE VEAV FDDFRVGWD ADVWSR SC VESMPEV IEWDE EAZ UATV XFGXUFQFZ
