IWCF, ZFAG ZAGRAO.”

VEF XGWTSRFG IGMRP EWT EARZ.

“W HGWRP OSM A GFNMFTV CGSY EFG.”

“IEAV WT WV?”

“A YSTV FAGRFTV, XGFTTWRP, ARZ FYXEAVWD FRVGFAVO, AZZGFTTFZ VS OSM
WR VEF YSTV XAVEFVWD VSRFT SC VEF JSWDF TS ZFAG VS OSM, VEAV OSM IFUU
GFYFYHFG.”

VEF XGWTSRFG VMGRFZ EWT CADF XAGVUO ATWZF.

“OSM EAJF RS VWYF VS ATK YF IEO W HGWRP WV, SG IEAV WV YFART; W EAJF
RS VWYF VS VFUU OSM. OSM YMTV DSYXUO IWVE WV--VAKF SCC VESTF HSSVT OSM
