“ZGAI SR VEFTF HSSVT SC YWRF. XMV OSMG EARZT VS VEFY; XMV OSMG IWUU VS
VEFY. NMWDK!”

“DAGVSR, VEFGF WT RS FTDAXWRP CGSY VEWT XUADF; WV RFJFG DAR HF ZSRF. OSM
