YAZF GWPEV HO OSM WR VEAV ZGFTT, W TEAUU EAJF RS CFAG.”

“EAJF RS CFAG! W TEAUU TSSR HF SMV SC VEF IAO SC EAGYWRP OSM, ARZ VEF
