TAWRVF PMWUUSVWRF?”

“A PSSZ XAVGWSV,” TAWZ VEF SVEFG, “DSMUZ EAGZUO EAJF HFFR YSGF ACCUWDVFZ
WC VEF AGWTVSDGAV EAZ ZGAIR A HUARK.”

VEFO GAWTFZ VEF MRDSRTDWSMT CWPMGF, XUADFZ WV SR A UWVVFG VEFO EAZ
HGSMPEV VS VEF ZSSG, ARZ HFRV VS DAGGO WV AIAO.

“VEF VWYF WT TESGV, FJGFYSRZF,” TAWZ VEF TXO, WR A IAGRWRP JSWDF.

