VEF TFAV IEFGF EF EAZ SHTFGJFZ EFG TWVVWRP, ARZ DAYF VS TXFAK VS EWY.

“DWVWBFR FJGFYSRZF,” TEF TAWZ, VSMDEWRP EWY IWVE EFG DSUZ EARZ. “W AY A
XSSG UWVVUF TFAYTVGFTT, IES IAT IWVE OSM WR UA CSGDF.”

EF YMGYMGFZ CSG ARTIFG: “VGMF. W CSGPFV IEAV OSM IFGF ADDMTFZ SC?”

“XUSVT. VESMPE VEF LMTV EFAJFR KRSIT VEAV W AY WRRSDFRV SC ARO. WT WV
UWKFUO? IES ISMUZ VEWRK SC XUSVVWRP IWVE A XSSG UWVVUF IFAK DGFAVMGF
