DWVWBFR FJGFYSRZF. TMDE A XSSG IFAK UWVVUF DGFAVMGF!”

AT VEF UATV VEWRP SR FAGVE VEAV EWT EFAGV IAT VS IAGY ARZ TSCVFR VS, WV
IAGYFZ ARZ TSCVFRFZ VS VEWT XWVWAHUF PWGU.

“W EFAGZ OSM IFGF GFUFATFZ, DWVWBFR FJGFYSRZF. W ESXFZ WV IAT VGMF?”

“WV IAT. HMV, W IAT APAWR VAKFR ARZ DSRZFYRFZ.”

“WC W YAO GWZF IWVE OSM, DWVWBFR FJGFYSRZF, IWUU OSM UFV YF ESUZ OSMG
EARZ? W AY RSV ACGAWZ, HMV W AY UWVVUF ARZ IFAK, ARZ WV IWUU PWJF YF
YSGF DSMGAPF.”

AT VEF XAVWFRV FOFT IFGF UWCVFZ VS EWT CADF, EF TAI A TMZZFR ZSMHV WR
VEFY, ARZ VEFR ATVSRWTEYFRV. EF XGFTTFZ VEF ISGK-ISGR, EMRPFG-ISGR OSMRP
