“AGF OSM ZOWRP CSG EWY?” TEF IEWTXFGFZ.

“ARZ EWT IWCF ARZ DEWUZ. EMTE! OFT.”

“S OSM IWUU UFV YF ESUZ OSMG HGAJF EARZ, TVGARPFG?”

“EMTE! OFT, YO XSSG TWTVFG; VS VEF UATV.”

