VEF TAYF TEAZSIT VEAV AGF CAUUWRP SR VEF XGWTSR, AGF CAUUWRP, WR VEAV
TAYF ESMG SC VEF FAGUO ACVFGRSSR, SR VEF HAGGWFG IWVE VEF DGSIZ AHSMV
