“IES PSFT EFGF? IESY EAJF IF IWVEWR? XAXFGT!”

VEF XAXFGT AGF EARZFZ SMV, ARZ GFAZ.

“AUFQARZGF YARFVVF. XEOTWDWAR. CGFRDE. IEWDE WT EF?”

VEWT WT EF; VEWT EFUXUFTT, WRAGVWDMUAVFUO YMGYMGWRP, IARZFGWRP SUZ YAR
XSWRVFZ SMV.

“AXXAGFRVUO VEF DWVWBFR-ZSDVSG WT RSV WR EWT GWPEV YWRZ? VEF
GFJSUMVWSR-CFJFG IWUU EAJF HFFR VSS YMDE CSG EWY?”

PGFAVUO VSS YMDE CSG EWY.

“EAE! YARO TMCCFG IWVE WV. UMDWF. EWT ZAMPEVFG. CGFRDE. IEWDE WT TEF?”

VEWT WT TEF.

“AXXAGFRVUO WV YMTV HF. UMDWF, VEF IWCF SC FJGFYSRZF; WT WV RSV?”

WV WT.

“EAE! FJGFYSRZF EAT AR ATTWPRAVWSR FUTFIEFGF. UMDWF, EFG DEWUZ. FRPUWTE.
VEWT WT TEF?”

TEF ARZ RS SVEFG.

