FTDAXF YWPEV ZFXFRZ SR VEF TAJWRP SC SRUO A CFI TFDSRZT EFGF ARZ VEFGF.
CWRAUUO, EF EAZ XGSXSTFZ, ACVFG ARQWSMT DSRTWZFGAVWSR, VEAV YWTT XGSTT
