VEGFF S'DUSDK WR VEF UWPEVFTV-IEFFUFZ DSRJFOARDF KRSIR VS VEAV XFGWSZ.
MRFRDMYHFGFZ IWVE UMPPAPF, VEFO ISMUZ TSSR SJFGVAKF VEF DSADE, ARZ,
XATTWRP WV ARZ XGFDFZWRP WV SR VEF GSAZ, ISMUZ SGZFG WVT ESGTFT WR
