YG. DGMRDEFG VESMPEV WV YWPEV HF HFTV.

“IEFGF DSMUZ OSM IAWV CSG YF?” ATKFZ YWTT XGSTT.

YG. DGMRDEFG IAT TS HFIWUZFGFZ VEAV EF DSMUZ VEWRK SC RS USDAUWVO HMV
