VSIFGT?”

“RS, YWTT,” ARTIFGFZ YG. DGMRDEFG.

“VEFR, UWKF VEF HFTV SC YFR,” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT, “PS VS VEF XSTVWRP-ESMTF
