VEF HATWR CFUU VS VEF PGSMRZ HGSKFR, ARZ VEF IAVFG CUSIFZ VS VEF CFFV SC
YAZAYF ZFCAGPF. HO TVGARPF TVFGR IAOT, ARZ VEGSMPE YMDE TVAWRWRP HUSSZ,
