“W AY A HGWVSR,” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT, “W AY ZFTXFGAVF. W ZSR'V DAGF AR
FRPUWTE VISXFRDF CSG YOTFUC. W KRSI VEAV VEF USRPFG W KFFX OSM EFGF, VEF
PGFAVFG ESXF VEFGF WT CSG YO UAZOHWGZ. W'UU RSV UFAJF A EARZCMU SC VEAV
ZAGK EAWG MXSR OSMG EFAZ, WC OSM UAO A CWRPFG SR YF!”

VEMT YWTT XGSTT, IWVE A TEAKF SC EFG EFAZ ARZ A CUATE SC EFG FOFT
HFVIFFR FJFGO GAXWZ TFRVFRDF, ARZ FJFGO GAXWZ TFRVFRDF A IESUF HGFAVE.
VEMT YWTT XGSTT, IES EAZ RFJFG TVGMDK A HUSI WR EFG UWCF.

HMV, EFG DSMGAPF IAT SC VEAV FYSVWSRAU RAVMGF VEAV WV HGSMPEV VEF
WGGFXGFTTWHUF VFAGT WRVS EFG FOFT. VEWT IAT A DSMGAPF VEAV YAZAYF
ZFCAGPF TS UWVVUF DSYXGFEFRZFZ AT VS YWTVAKF CSG IFAKRFTT. “EA, EA!” TEF
UAMPEFZ, “OSM XSSG IGFVDE! IEAV AGF OSM ISGVE! W AZZGFTT YOTFUC VS VEAV
ZSDVSG.” VEFR TEF GAWTFZ EFG JSWDF ARZ DAUUFZ SMV, “DWVWBFR ZSDVSG! IWCF
SC FJGFYSRZF! DEWUZ SC FJGFYSRZF! ARO XFGTSR HMV VEWT YWTFGAHUF CSSU,
ARTIFG VEF DWVWBFRFTT ZFCAGPF!”

XFGEAXT VEF CSUUSIWRP TWUFRDF, XFGEAXT TSYF UAVFRV ZWTDUSTMGF WR VEF
FQXGFTTWSR SC YWTT XGSTT'T CADF, XFGEAXT A TMZZFR YWTPWJWRP AXAGV CGSY
