“WC VEFO AGF RSV WR VEAV GSSY, VEFO AGF PSRF, ARZ DAR HF XMGTMFZ ARZ
HGSMPEV HADK,” TAWZ YAZAYF ZFCAGPF VS EFGTFUC.

“AT USRP AT OSM ZSR'V KRSI IEFVEFG VEFO AGF WR VEAV GSSY SG RSV, OSM AGF
MRDFGVAWR IEAV VS ZS,” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT VS EFGTFUC; “ARZ OSM TEAUU RSV
KRSI VEAV, WC W DAR XGFJFRV OSMG KRSIWRP WV; ARZ KRSI VEAV, SG RSV KRSI
VEAV, OSM TEAUU RSV UFAJF EFGF IEWUF W DAR ESUZ OSM.”

“W EAJF HFFR WR VEF TVGFFVT CGSY VEF CWGTV, RSVEWRP EAT TVSXXFZ YF,
W IWUU VFAG OSM VS XWFDFT, HMV W IWUU EAJF OSM CGSY VEAV ZSSG,” TAWZ
