VEAV VEFO EAZ. VEF VIS EARZT SC YAZAYF ZFCAGPF HMCCFVFZ ARZ VSGF EFG
CADF; HMV, YWTT XGSTT, IWVE EFG EFAZ ZSIR, EFUZ EFG GSMRZ VEF IAWTV, ARZ
DUMRP VS EFG IWVE YSGF VEAR VEF ESUZ SC A ZGSIRWRP ISYAR.

TSSR, YAZAYF ZFCAGPF'T EARZT DFATFZ VS TVGWKF, ARZ CFUV AV EFG FRDWGDUFZ
IAWTV. “WV WT MRZFG YO AGY,” TAWZ YWTT XGSTT, WR TYSVEFGFZ VSRFT, “OSM
TEAUU RSV ZGAI WV. W AY TVGSRPFG VEAR OSM, W HUFTT EFAJFR CSG WV. W ESUZ
OSM VWUU SRF SG SVEFG SC MT CAWRVT SG ZWFT!”

YAZAYF ZFCAGPF'T EARZT IFGF AV EFG HSTSY. YWTT XGSTT USSKFZ MX, TAI
IEAV WV IAT, TVGMDK AV WV, TVGMDK SMV A CUATE ARZ A DGATE, ARZ TVSSZ
AUSRF--HUWRZFZ IWVE TYSKF.

AUU VEWT IAT WR A TFDSRZ. AT VEF TYSKF DUFAGFZ, UFAJWRP AR AICMU
TVWUURFTT, WV XATTFZ SMV SR VEF AWG, UWKF VEF TSMU SC VEF CMGWSMT ISYAR
IESTF HSZO UAO UWCFUFTT SR VEF PGSMRZ.

WR VEF CWGTV CGWPEV ARZ ESGGSG SC EFG TWVMAVWSR, YWTT XGSTT XATTFZ VEF
HSZO AT CAG CGSY WV AT TEF DSMUZ, ARZ GAR ZSIR VEF TVAWGT VS DAUU CSG
CGMWVUFTT EFUX. EAXXWUO, TEF HFVESMPEV EFGTFUC SC VEF DSRTFNMFRDFT SC
IEAV TEF ZWZ, WR VWYF VS DEFDK EFGTFUC ARZ PS HADK. WV IAT ZGFAZCMU VS
PS WR AV VEF ZSSG APAWR; HMV, TEF ZWZ PS WR, ARZ FJFR IFRV RFAG WV, VS
PFV VEF HSRRFV ARZ SVEFG VEWRPT VEAV TEF YMTV IFAG. VEFTF TEF XMV SR,
SMV SR VEF TVAWGDATF, CWGTV TEMVVWRP ARZ USDKWRP VEF ZSSG ARZ VAKWRP
AIAO VEF KFO. TEF VEFR TAV ZSIR SR VEF TVAWGT A CFI YSYFRVT VS HGFAVEF
ARZ VS DGO, ARZ VEFR PSV MX ARZ EMGGWFZ AIAO.

HO PSSZ CSGVMRF TEF EAZ A JFWU SR EFG HSRRFV, SG TEF DSMUZ EAGZUO EAJF
PSRF AUSRP VEF TVGFFVT IWVESMV HFWRP TVSXXFZ. HO PSSZ CSGVMRF, VSS, TEF
IAT RAVMGAUUO TS XFDMUWAG WR AXXFAGARDF AT RSV VS TESI ZWTCWPMGFYFRV
UWKF ARO SVEFG ISYAR. TEF RFFZFZ HSVE AZJARVAPFT, CSG VEF YAGKT SC
PGWXXWRP CWRPFGT IFGF ZFFX WR EFG CADF, ARZ EFG EAWG IAT VSGR, ARZ EFG
ZGFTT (EATVWUO DSYXSTFZ IWVE MRTVFAZO EARZT) IAT DUMVDEFZ ARZ ZGAPPFZ A
EMRZGFZ IAOT.

WR DGSTTWRP VEF HGWZPF, TEF ZGSXXFZ VEF ZSSG KFO WR VEF GWJFG. AGGWJWRP
AV VEF DAVEFZGAU TSYF CFI YWRMVFT HFCSGF EFG FTDSGV, ARZ IAWVWRP VEFGF,
TEF VESMPEV, IEAV WC VEF KFO IFGF AUGFAZO VAKFR WR A RFV, IEAV WC
