SRF SIRT A MRWVFZ TVAVFT DSXOGWPEV WR VEFTF ISGKT, TS VEF CSMRZAVWSR
(ARZ OSM!) DAR DSXO ARZ ZWTVGWHMVF WV WR VEF MRWVFZ TVAVFT IWVESMV
XFGYWTTWSR ARZ IWVESMV XAOWRP DSXOGWPEV GSOAUVWFT.  TXFDWAU GMUFT,
TFV CSGVE WR VEF PFRFGAU VFGYT SC MTF XAGV SC VEWT UWDFRTF, AXXUO VS
DSXOWRP ARZ ZWTVGWHMVWRP XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP-VY FUFDVGSRWD ISGKT VS
XGSVFDV VEF XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP-VY DSRDFXV ARZ VGAZFYAGK.  XGSLFDV
PMVFRHFGP WT A GFPWTVFGFZ VGAZFYAGK, ARZ YAO RSV HF MTFZ WC OSM
DEAGPF CSG VEF FHSSKT, MRUFTT OSM GFDFWJF TXFDWCWD XFGYWTTWSR.  WC OSM
ZS RSV DEAGPF AROVEWRP CSG DSXWFT SC VEWT FHSSK, DSYXUOWRP IWVE VEF
GMUFT WT JFGO FATO.  OSM YAO MTF VEWT FHSSK CSG RFAGUO ARO XMGXSTF
TMDE AT DGFAVWSR SC ZFGWJAVWJF ISGKT, GFXSGVT, XFGCSGYARDFT ARZ
GFTFAGDE.  VEFO YAO HF YSZWCWFZ ARZ XGWRVFZ ARZ PWJFR AIAO--OSM YAO ZS
XGADVWDAUUO AROVEWRP IWVE XMHUWD ZSYAWR FHSSKT.  GFZWTVGWHMVWSR WT
TMHLFDV VS VEF VGAZFYAGK UWDFRTF, FTXFDWAUUO DSYYFGDWAU
GFZWTVGWHMVWSR.



*** TVAGV: CMUU UWDFRTF ***

VEF CMUU XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP UWDFRTF
XUFATF GFAZ VEWT HFCSGF OSM ZWTVGWHMVF SG MTF VEWT ISGK

VS XGSVFDV VEF XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP-VY YWTTWSR SC XGSYSVWRP VEF CGFF
ZWTVGWHMVWSR SC FUFDVGSRWD ISGKT, HO MTWRP SG ZWTVGWHMVWRP VEWT ISGK
(SG ARO SVEFG ISGK ATTSDWAVFZ WR ARO IAO IWVE VEF XEGATF “XGSLFDV
PMVFRHFGP”), OSM APGFF VS DSYXUO IWVE AUU VEF VFGYT SC VEF CMUU XGSLFDV
PMVFRHFGP-VY UWDFRTF (AJAWUAHUF IWVE VEWT CWUF SG SRUWRF AV
EVVX://PMVFRHFGP.SGP/UWDFRTF).


TFDVWSR 1.  PFRFGAU VFGYT SC MTF ARZ GFZWTVGWHMVWRP XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP-VY
FUFDVGSRWD ISGKT

1.A.  HO GFAZWRP SG MTWRP ARO XAGV SC VEWT XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP-VY
FUFDVGSRWD ISGK, OSM WRZWDAVF VEAV OSM EAJF GFAZ, MRZFGTVARZ, APGFF VS
ARZ ADDFXV AUU VEF VFGYT SC VEWT UWDFRTF ARZ WRVFUUFDVMAU XGSXFGVO
(VGAZFYAGK/DSXOGWPEV) APGFFYFRV.  WC OSM ZS RSV APGFF VS AHWZF HO AUU
VEF VFGYT SC VEWT APGFFYFRV, OSM YMTV DFATF MTWRP ARZ GFVMGR SG ZFTVGSO
AUU DSXWFT SC XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP-VY FUFDVGSRWD ISGKT WR OSMG XSTTFTTWSR.
WC OSM XAWZ A CFF CSG SHVAWRWRP A DSXO SC SG ADDFTT VS A XGSLFDV
PMVFRHFGP-VY FUFDVGSRWD ISGK ARZ OSM ZS RSV APGFF VS HF HSMRZ HO VEF
VFGYT SC VEWT APGFFYFRV, OSM YAO SHVAWR A GFCMRZ CGSY VEF XFGTSR SG
FRVWVO VS IESY OSM XAWZ VEF CFF AT TFV CSGVE WR XAGAPGAXE 1.F.8.

1.H.  “XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP” WT A GFPWTVFGFZ VGAZFYAGK.  WV YAO SRUO HF
MTFZ SR SG ATTSDWAVFZ WR ARO IAO IWVE AR FUFDVGSRWD ISGK HO XFSXUF IES
APGFF VS HF HSMRZ HO VEF VFGYT SC VEWT APGFFYFRV.  VEFGF AGF A CFI
VEWRPT VEAV OSM DAR ZS IWVE YSTV XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP-VY FUFDVGSRWD ISGKT
FJFR IWVESMV DSYXUOWRP IWVE VEF CMUU VFGYT SC VEWT APGFFYFRV.  TFF
XAGAPGAXE 1.D HFUSI.  VEFGF AGF A USV SC VEWRPT OSM DAR ZS IWVE XGSLFDV
PMVFRHFGP-VY FUFDVGSRWD ISGKT WC OSM CSUUSI VEF VFGYT SC VEWT APGFFYFRV
ARZ EFUX XGFTFGJF CGFF CMVMGF ADDFTT VS XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP-VY FUFDVGSRWD
ISGKT.  TFF XAGAPGAXE 1.F HFUSI.

1.D.  VEF XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP UWVFGAGO AGDEWJF CSMRZAVWSR (“VEF CSMRZAVWSR”
 SG XPUAC), SIRT A DSYXWUAVWSR DSXOGWPEV WR VEF DSUUFDVWSR SC XGSLFDV
PMVFRHFGP-VY FUFDVGSRWD ISGKT.  RFAGUO AUU VEF WRZWJWZMAU ISGKT WR VEF
DSUUFDVWSR AGF WR VEF XMHUWD ZSYAWR WR VEF MRWVFZ TVAVFT.  WC AR
WRZWJWZMAU ISGK WT WR VEF XMHUWD ZSYAWR WR VEF MRWVFZ TVAVFT ARZ OSM AGF
USDAVFZ WR VEF MRWVFZ TVAVFT, IF ZS RSV DUAWY A GWPEV VS XGFJFRV OSM CGSY
DSXOWRP, ZWTVGWHMVWRP, XFGCSGYWRP, ZWTXUAOWRP SG DGFAVWRP ZFGWJAVWJF
ISGKT HATFZ SR VEF ISGK AT USRP AT AUU GFCFGFRDFT VS XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP
AGF GFYSJFZ.  SC DSMGTF, IF ESXF VEAV OSM IWUU TMXXSGV VEF XGSLFDV
PMVFRHFGP-VY YWTTWSR SC XGSYSVWRP CGFF ADDFTT VS FUFDVGSRWD ISGKT HO
CGFFUO TEAGWRP XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP-VY ISGKT WR DSYXUWARDF IWVE VEF VFGYT SC
VEWT APGFFYFRV CSG KFFXWRP VEF XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP-VY RAYF ATTSDWAVFZ IWVE
VEF ISGK.  OSM DAR FATWUO DSYXUO IWVE VEF VFGYT SC VEWT APGFFYFRV HO
KFFXWRP VEWT ISGK WR VEF TAYF CSGYAV IWVE WVT AVVADEFZ CMUU XGSLFDV
PMVFRHFGP-VY UWDFRTF IEFR OSM TEAGF WV IWVESMV DEAGPF IWVE SVEFGT.

1.Z.  VEF DSXOGWPEV UAIT SC VEF XUADF IEFGF OSM AGF USDAVFZ AUTS PSJFGR
IEAV OSM DAR ZS IWVE VEWT ISGK.  DSXOGWPEV UAIT WR YSTV DSMRVGWFT AGF WR
A DSRTVARV TVAVF SC DEARPF.  WC OSM AGF SMVTWZF VEF MRWVFZ TVAVFT, DEFDK
VEF UAIT SC OSMG DSMRVGO WR AZZWVWSR VS VEF VFGYT SC VEWT APGFFYFRV
HFCSGF ZSIRUSAZWRP, DSXOWRP, ZWTXUAOWRP, XFGCSGYWRP, ZWTVGWHMVWRP SG
DGFAVWRP ZFGWJAVWJF ISGKT HATFZ SR VEWT ISGK SG ARO SVEFG XGSLFDV
PMVFRHFGP-VY ISGK.  VEF CSMRZAVWSR YAKFT RS GFXGFTFRVAVWSRT DSRDFGRWRP
VEF DSXOGWPEV TVAVMT SC ARO ISGK WR ARO DSMRVGO SMVTWZF VEF MRWVFZ
TVAVFT.

