TFDVWSR  2.  WRCSGYAVWSR AHSMV VEF YWTTWSR SC XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP-VY

XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP-VY WT TORSROYSMT IWVE VEF CGFF ZWTVGWHMVWSR SC
FUFDVGSRWD ISGKT WR CSGYAVT GFAZAHUF HO VEF IWZFTV JAGWFVO SC DSYXMVFGT
WRDUMZWRP SHTSUFVF, SUZ, YWZZUF-APFZ ARZ RFI DSYXMVFGT.  WV FQWTVT
HFDAMTF SC VEF FCCSGVT SC EMRZGFZT SC JSUMRVFFGT ARZ ZSRAVWSRT CGSY
XFSXUF WR AUU IAUKT SC UWCF.

JSUMRVFFGT ARZ CWRARDWAU TMXXSGV VS XGSJWZF JSUMRVFFGT IWVE VEF
ATTWTVARDF VEFO RFFZ, AGF DGWVWDAU VS GFADEWRP XGSLFDV PMVFRHFGP-VY'T
